NK069(tu)001:1: // mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi /
NK069(tu)001:2: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba'i snying po bzhugs pa lags so //
NK069(tu)001:4: rgyud kyi rgyal po gsang ba snying po 'di bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:5: dbang po rab la mtshan bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:10: dbang po rab kyis rtsa la rten nas /
NK069(tu)001:12: mtshan gyis rgyud dbu' zhabs kyi don rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13: 'bring dang tha mas glegs bam tshegs chung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:14: bsdus pa'i don la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:15: gang bstan na rgyud kyi mtshan bstan /
NK069(tu)001:16: gang gis bstan na bsdud pa pos bstan /
NK069(tu)001:17: gang du ji ltar bstan na dbu' dang le'u 'tshams su bstan /
NK069(tu)001:18: bstan pa'i dgos pa mtshan gyi 'og tu don kun 'dus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20: skad gang yin ngos bzung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:22: skad gang yin ngos bzung na gnyis ste /
NK069(tu)001:26: sgra skad la 'jug pa b+h+ya ska ra na'i skad dang /
NK069(tu)001:27: chos skad thams cad la 'jug pa b+h+ya ga ta yug ti'i skad dang /
NK069(tu)001:28: sgyur thams cad la 'jug pa bing pa ta'i skad do //
NK069(tu)001:30: d+he ba b+ha sa zhes bya ba sang kri ta legs par sbyangs pa'i lha'i skad dang /
NK069(tu)001:31: a su ram b+ha zhes bya ba a ba brag
NK069(tu)001:32: shi ta zur chag pa lha ma yin gyi skad
NK069(tu)001:33: dang / pre ta b+ha sa zhes bya ba 'bre
NK069(tu)001:34: sha tsi ta sha za yi dwags kyi skad dang
NK069(tu)001:35: dang / / yo ga b+ha sa zhes bya ba
NK069(tu)001:36: pra kri ta phal pa 'jig rten pa'i skad las
NK069(tu)001:37: dang / / / 'dir sang kri ta'i skad do //
NK069(tu)001:38: mtshan gyi don bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:39: rgyud ltar na sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:40: lung ltar na lung gi spyi dang /
NK069(tu)001:41: man ngag ltar na gsang ba snying po'o //
NK069(tu)001:43: dang po phyi ltar sgro 'dogs gcod pa'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:46: mang la 'brel ba d+r+wa ba'i don //
NK069(tu)001:48: gnyis pa nang rtsa gnas kyi sgyu 'phrul dra ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:50: gnas bzhi gar thabs sgyu ma la //
NK069(tu)001:51: nam mkha'i ye shes cir yang gsal //
NK069(tu)001:52: cir gsal bdag nyid rig par 'brel //
NK069(tu)001:53: dra ba'i don du nga yis bshad //
NK069(tu)001:55: gsum pa gsang ba snyoms 'jug pa dgongs pa'i sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:57: shes rab thabs rol sgyu ma las //
NK069(tu)001:58: rang bzhin sgyu 'phrul chen por shar //
NK069(tu)001:59: thabs dang thabs byung 'brel ba nyid //
NK069(tu)001:60: thams cad kun gyi gzhir gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:62: bzhi pa de kho na nyid kyi sgyu 'phrul dra ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:63: stong zhing dben pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK069(tu)001:64: rigs dang kha dog dbyibs myed de //
NK069(tu)001:65: cir yang myed las cir yang snang //
NK069(tu)001:67: sems kyi sgyu 'phrul chen po yin //
NK069(tu)001:69: lung ltar na lung gi spyi ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:70: drang don ston pa mtshan nyid kyi lung /
NK069(tu)001:71: nges par zad pa sngags kyi lung /
NK069(tu)001:72: de kho na nyid dbyer med pa'i lung 'adi'o //
NK069(tu)001:73: de yang 'di nyid kyi le'u tha ma nas /
NK069(tu)001:74: mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi /
NK069(tu)001:75: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba /
NK069(tu)001:77: man ngag ltar na gsang ba snying po ni /
NK069(tu)001:78: mtshan gyi dngos bstan 'di kho na ltar yin te //
NK069(tu)001:90: rgya gar gyi yul ni ston pas zhabs kyis bcags
NK069(tu)001:91: pa'i gnas yin pas byin brlabs che zhing bkra shis
NK069(tu)001:92: pa dang / dkar po'i chos 'byung sa yin pas khungs btsun pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:93: sang kri ta'i sgra skad bzang po la blo sbyangs pas /
NK069(tu)001:94: bag chags bzang po sog pa'i dgos pa yod pas /
NK069(tu)001:95: rgya gar skad klad du smos pa yin no ////
NK069(tu)001:96: khagtar kas gags sel ba'i tshig klag khra mo gzan la 'jums pa ltar bshad pas /
NK069(tu)001:98: sems dang ye shes rang snang bar bston pa'i rgyud
NK069(tu)001:99: dpal gsang ba snying po 'di la mtshan gsum ste
NK069(tu)001:100: / rgyud dang skyes bu'i mtshan thun mong du bstan pa rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba /
NK069(tu)001:101: lung ltar na lung thams cad kyi spyi'i lung /
NK069(tu)001:102: man ngag ltar na gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa gsum las /
NK069(tu)001:104: man ngag ltar kho na nges pa ci zhes na /
NK069(tu)001:105: de ni rgyud man ngag ltar bshad pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:106: gal che zhing gtso' che ba'i dbang du smos pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:112: grol lam dang sbyar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:113: thabs lam dang sbyar nas bshad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:119: rang bzhin gyi gsang ba la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:121: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:122: ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:123: gzhan du min la shin tu gsang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:125: don dam gnyis myed rang chas su yod kyang ngo ma shes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:126: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:127: don dam de nyid kun rdzob tu mi bzad pa
NK069(tu)001:128: rgyan gyi 'khor lor shar ba ngo ma shes pa'o
NK069(tu)001:129: // ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:130: bden pa dbyer myed yul sems las grol ba yin yang ngo ma shes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:131: gzhan du min la shin tu gsang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:132: rig pa spyod yul dang bral ba las /
NK069(tu)001:133: 'bras bu gzhan na yod pa ma yin yang /
NK069(tu)001:134: de nyid rang ngo rang gis ma shes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:135: de yang le'u gnyis pa las /
NK069(tu)001:136: e ma'o ye nas gsang ba'i chos /
NK069(tu)001:137: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK069(tu)001:138: ngo bo nyid kyis rab tu gsang //
NK069(tu)001:139: gzhan du min la shin du gsang zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:140: gnyis pa sbas pa'i gsang ba ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:141: gang sbas na spyod pa sbyor sgrol la sogs pa sbas /
NK069(tu)001:142: gang du sbas na tsam du yi ge'i rgyud du sbas /
NK069(tu)001:143: gang gis sbas na ston pas sbas /
NK069(tu)001:144: ci'i phyir sbas na ra chod can sun dbyung ba'i phyir sbas so //
NK069(tu)001:145: de yang rol pa'i le'u gsum pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:146: rgyud chen gsang ba'i don rnams kun //
NK069(tu)001:147: sbas bshad brda' yis rnam par 'byed //
NK069(tu)001:149: gsum pa gab pa'i gsang ba la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:150: gang gab na gsang ba'i man ngag gab /
NK069(tu)001:151: gang du gab na rdo rje slob dpon gyi thugs la gab /
NK069(tu)001:152: gang la gab na ma rtogs pa la gab /
NK069(tu)001:153: ci'i phyir gab na rgyud dang rig pa 'brel ba'i phyir gab bo //
NK069(tu)001:154: de yang le'u bcu gsum pa las /
NK069(tu)001:155: kho na gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK069(tu)001:156: ston pa rdo rje'i thugs la gnas //
NK069(tu)001:162: bcud 'dus pa don gyi snying po'o //
NK069(tu)001:164: rgyud 'di'i byin brlabs las theg pa thun mong ba la shar te /
NK069(tu)001:166: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po ni //
NK069(tu)001:167: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi //
NK069(tu)001:168: 'byung gnas stan la nges par 'bebs zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:170: theg pa gang gi lam nas bgrod kyang /
NK069(tu)001:171: mthar thug rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'o don mngon du byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:172: de yang le'u tha ma nas /
NK069(tu)001:173: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK069(tu)001:174: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK069(tu)001:176: bcud 'dus pa don gyi snying po ni /
NK069(tu)001:177: gtan tshigs kyi sgo gang nas gtan la phab kyang /
NK069(tu)001:178: mthar thug gi 'bras bu rtog tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis las myi mnga' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:180: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK069(tu)001:181: gsang ba 'di las gzhan myi mnga' //
NK069(tu)001:182: sgro dang skur pa zhi ba yi //
NK069(tu)001:183: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK069(tu)001:184: nyid do nges pa'i dbyings phyung //
NK069(tu)001:188: de kho na nyid la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:189: ma bcos pa'i de kho na nyid /
NK069(tu)001:190: ma nor ba'i de kho na nyid /
NK069(tu)001:191: gzhan ma yin pa'i de kho na nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:192: ma bcos pa'i de kho na nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:193: gnyis myed kyi ye shes la blos ma bcos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:194: thal ba'i le'u bzhi pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:195: rang bzhin ye nas ma bcos pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:196: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor mngon par rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:198: ma nor ba'i de kho na nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:199: ma bcos pa de nyid ye shes kyi phyag rgya sna tshogs par snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:200: de yang rol pa'i le'u gnyis pa las /
NK069(tu)001:201: 'bras bu sku mchog ye shes che //
NK069(tu)001:202: rang bzhin byin brlabs shugs kyis snang //
NK069(tu)001:204: gzhan ma yin pa'i de kho na nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:205: de ltar snang yang rang rig nyid snang ba las /
NK069(tu)001:207: de yang le'u gnyis pa las /
NK069(tu)001:208: nyid las gzhan zhes bya ba'i chos /
NK069(tu)001:209: rtsal yang rgyal bas mi snyems so //
NK069(tu)001:218: gzhi'i sgro skur dang bral bar nges pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:219: le'u gnyis pa las sgro dang skur pa zhi ba'i //
NK069(tu)001:220: gsang ba snying po de kho na //
NK069(tu)001:221: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung //
NK069(tu)001:224: 'bras bu nyid lam du byed par nges te /
NK069(tu)001:227: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK069(tu)001:230: rang gi ngo bos 'bras bu nyid lam du byed par nges te /
NK069(tu)001:232: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus la //
NK069(tu)001:233: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don myed //
NK069(tu)001:235: gnyis pa thabs lam dang sbyar nas bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:237: lus la gnas pa'i rtsa 'khor lo drug gzhal yas khang du ma shes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:238: rtsa la rten pa'i khams thig le lha skur ma shes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:239: thig le las grub pa'i sngags yi ge gsung du ma shes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:240: de dag la khyab pa'i snying po rlung thugs su ma shes pas gsang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:241: de yang thal ba'i le'u lnga pa las /
NK069(tu)001:244: am yig dbyangs kyi yi ges brgyan //
NK069(tu)001:247: de ltar gnas pa de nyams su len pa'i man ngag sgom pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:248: thal ba'i le'u de nyid las //
NK069(tu)001:249: me rlung sbyor bas skul byas ste //
NK069(tu)001:251: smin byed khyab pas bde ba'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:252: rang gi gnas su rnam par 'khyil //
NK069(tu)001:255: dga' ba bzhi'i nyams skyes pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:256: tha' ba'i le'u lnga pa las /
NK069(tu)001:257: dga' dang rjes su dga' ba dang //
NK069(tu)001:258: dga' bral lhan cig skyes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:262: 'di nyid kyi le'u bcu gcig pa las /
NK069(tu)001:263: bsgrub pa nyi zla'i snying po de //
NK069(tu)001:264: dkyil 'khor rdo rje lce yis blang //
NK069(tu)001:266: yid bzhin sprin gyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:271: rgyud kyi ston pa la phyag 'tshal ba ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:276: ston pa phyag 'tshal bas phyi rabs rnams tshogs skye zhing sgrib pa 'byang bar 'gyur pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:277: ston pa de la phyag 'tshal bas rgyud 'di thams
NK069(tu)001:278: cad kun tu bzang por sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin
NK069(tu)001:281: yul gang la 'tshal na ston pa la'o //
NK069(tu)001:282: gang gis 'tshal na sdud pa bos /
NK069(tu)001:283: tshul ji ltar btsal na tha mi dad pa'i tshul gyis so //
NK069(tu)001:284: ci'i phyir btsal na ma 'ongs pa'i tshogs bsags pa'i phyir btsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:286: ston pa la phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:287: dbang po tha ma'i don du bshad thabs kyi man ngag bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:288: ston pa la phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:290: 1 / 'dir gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:291: phyag ni ston pa nyid la nyid 'tshal bar mi 'os na /
NK069(tu)001:293: ston pas ma gsungs bar 'god par mi 'os so zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:295: 'khor lo dbus kyi lte ba la //
NK069(tu)001:296: bdag po kun bzang 'khor lo bskor //
NK069(tu)001:297: skyes bu bka' sdod mdun na gnas //
NK069(tu)001:298: rjod pa myed par sgro ba mdzad //
NK069(tu)001:299: 'khor gyi nang na skal mchog ldan //
NK069(tu)001:300: lag na rdo rjes sdud par mdzad //
NK069(tu)001:304: sdud pos tshig gnyer ba'i tshe rang gi ston pa la mchod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:307: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la nyid 'chad /
NK069(tu)001:311: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid de bzhin gshegs pa la ched du brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:314: ma rtogs pa'i don du mtshan ma brda'i phyag btsal /
NK069(tu)001:315: rtogs pa'i don du rig pa ye shes kyi phyag btsal lo /
NK069(tu)001:319: yid rang 'byung gi ye shes chen po la las
NK069(tu)001:320: kyi sgrib pas ma gos pas nyon mongs pa'i bdud
NK069(tu)001:321: bcom / ye shes sgyu ma lta bu'i sku la
NK069(tu)001:322: nyer len gyi phung po lnga ma grub pas phung
NK069(tu)001:323: bcom / po'i bdud bcom / de la 'dod khams
NK069(tu)001:324: kyi lha me tog gi mda' can gyis bar du
NK069(tu)001:325: gcad du myed pas lha'i bu'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:326: rang 'byung ye shes skye 'gag las grol bas 'chi bdag bcom /
NK069(tu)001:328: ldan pa ni yid rang 'byung gi ye shes de yang legs pa drug dang ldan de /
NK069(tu)001:337: rgyu yid kyi rnam shes dmyigs pa las 'das /
NK069(tu)001:338: lam rang 'byung gi ye shes bsgrib pa las 'das /
NK069(tu)001:339: 'bras bu kun tu bzang po mtha' thams cad las 'das pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:342: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dpal sems nyid dang /
NK069(tu)001:343: rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa'i dpal rang ngo rang gis shes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:344: thugs rje chen po zhar la 'byung ba'i dpal 'gro don mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:346: kun tu bzang po ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:347: rang bzhin kun tu bzang po ni gnyer pos bcos su myed pa'i sems nyid mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK069(tu)001:348: rtogs pa kun tu bzang po ni sems can la
NK069(tu)001:349: gnas pa'i yid sku gsung thugs dbyer med du rtogs
NK069(tu)001:350: pa dang / spyod pa kun tu bzang po ni
NK069(tu)001:351: de ltar rtogs na ci spyod kyang blang dor myed
NK069(tu)001:353: dus kun tu bzang po ni 'das ma 'ongs da
NK069(tu)001:354: ltar gsum dbyer myed pas dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid
NK069(tu)001:355: du rtogs pa'o // la zhes pa ngo bo de yul du byas pa'o ////
NK069(tu)001:356: 3 gnyis pa dbang po tha ma'i don du bshad thabs kyi man ngag la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:357: bshad tshul nyes pa'i skyon brgyad spang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:358: 'dren pa'i tshig bcu 'phrul par bya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:359: dgos pa'i dmyigs bzhi bzung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:360: ngag don gyi mngon rtogs sdeb pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:361: dang po bshad tshul nyes pa'i skyon brgyad spang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:362: gong 'og gi 'khrugs sdeb ma shes na rin po che rtsar 'chol ba'i bshad pa dang gcig /
NK069(tu)001:363: rtog ge ba'i gags sel ma shes na 'dzangs pa lce gdum gyi bshad pa dang gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:364: myi 'thun pa'i tshig don sdeb ma shes na shes rab long ba'i bshad pa dang gsum /
NK069(tu)001:365: 'brel tshul gnyis dang ma 'brel na snyon pa'i snyon tshig lta bu'i bshad pa dang bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:366: spyi dang khyad par gyi dgos ched myed na don myed phyal ba'i bshad pa dang lnga /
NK069(tu)001:367: mngon par rtogs pa'i go rims sdeb ma shes na bdud rtsi ro nyams kyi bshang pa dang drug /
NK069(tu)001:368: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa dang 'bras bu rdo
NK069(tu)001:369: rje'i theg pa gnyis khyad myed par bshad na rdo
NK069(tu)001:370: rje'i theg pa na babs pa'i bshad pa dang bdun
NK069(tu)001:371: / gsang sngags phyi nang 'dres mar bshad na snyan
NK069(tu)001:372: bsgrub bzhi'i don las gol te 'brog 'chol ba'i bshad
NK069(tu)001:374: de las skyon dang po'i dbang du mi gtang ba'i phyir na 'khrugs sdeb pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:376: 'dren pa'i tshig bcu 'phrugs par bya ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:377: rang bzhin lta ba'i tshig khyung nam mkha' la lding ba ltar bshad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:379: rnam par 'byed pa'i tshig rtag gi 'chongs pa ltar bshad de /
NK069(tu)001:381: spyi don bsdud pa'i tshig seng ge'i rtsal stobs ltar bshad de /
NK069(tu)001:383: 'brel pa sbyor ba'i tshig bya ngang mo'i 'byol 'gros ltar bshad de /
NK069(tu)001:385: rang rkyen gnyer gyi tshig ru sbal gyi mnur 'gros ltar bshad de /
NK069(tu)001:386: de ni gong 'og gi 'bru mnan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:387: ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshig sna phrug brag la 'dzeg pa ltar bshad de /
NK069(tu)001:388: de ni ldem dgongs brgyad do //
NK069(tu)001:389: gtar kas gags gsal ba'i tshig klag gzan la 'jums pa ltar bshad de /
NK069(tu)001:391: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi tshig dus kyi 'brug char ltar bshad de /
NK069(tu)001:392: de ni lta spyod kyi khyad par bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:393: snol mtshams 'phen bsdud kyi tshig seng phrug rtsal sbyong ba ltar bshad de /
NK069(tu)001:395: mtshon pa dpe'i tshig me long g.ya' dag pa ltar bshad de /
NK069(tu)001:396: de ni go bar ka ba dpes mtshon pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:397: dgos pa'i dmigs bzhi bzung ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:398: drang don dang nges don dang /
NK069(tu)001:399: dgongs bshad dang dgongs min dang /
NK069(tu)001:400: sgra ji bzhin dang ji bzhin ma yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:401: mdo rgyas dang rtsa bshad gnyis te zung bzhi ya brgyad ni /
NK069(tu)001:402: rdo rje'i tshig don so sor 'brel ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:403: ngag don gyi mngon rtogs sdebs pa ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:407: 'gro ba'i don du snang phyir yongs su bzung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:408: rgyu gleng gzhi la lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:413: sdud pa po gang gis bsdus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:414: dus ni sgro skur dang bral ba'i dus su bla na myed pa'i 'khor lo skor ro //
NK069(tu)001:418: rang bzhin chos sku rgyas par drug bsdus par bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:419: byang chub chen po'i rang bzhin dang /
NK069(tu)001:420: chos rnams rol pa chen por longs spyod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:421: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bde bar gshegs pa'i bdag po dang /
NK069(tu)001:422: chos so lcog dang dbyer myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:423: ston pa'i mdzad spyod ni gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:424: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku rnal 'byor pa sa bcu thob pa la snang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:425: sprul pa'i sku rnal 'byor ba las dag pa la snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:426: longs sku ni ston pa'i ngo bo yin te /
NK069(tu)001:427: de yang ston pa'i bdag nyid kun tu bzang po dang /
NK069(tu)001:430: zhi bas 'dus ba la thub drug /
NK069(tu)001:431: khro bos 'dul ba la drag por bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:435: gsang ba yum gyi b+ha ga'o //
NK069(tu)001:440: lhan cig pa la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:441: nyid las mi zhan pa'i 'khor rigs lnga yab yum dang /
NK069(tu)001:443: gdug pa 'dul ba khro bo'i 'khor dang /
NK069(tu)001:445: 'di dag yang rim pa yin myin du 'khor dang ston par yang 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:446: go phye ba rgyu'i sems dapa'o //
NK069(tu)001:447: dad pas 'dus pa lha chen brgyad rang bzhin gyi 'khor du'o //
NK069(tu)001:448: bsdud pa po ni kun tu bzang po nyid la nyid bshad nyid la nyid bsdus pa'o ////
NK069(tu)001:449: gtar kas bde gshegs gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:450: rgyud dang mdo' sde thams cad kyi nang nas /
NK069(tu)001:451: dus la 'di skad bdag gis thos pa bshad pa la /
NK069(tu)001:452: 'dir ni 'di skad bshad pa zer ba'i gnad ka ci zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:453: log par rtogs pa bzhi dgag pa'i phyir ston pa nyid kyis bsdus pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:456: nyung bar skur pa 'debs pa gnyis kyi log rtogs bkag /
NK069(tu)001:459: ston pas bshad pa bzhin du 'khor gyis ma rtogs pa'i skyon gsal lo ////
NK069(tu)001:470: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi' la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:471: phyi sku lnga lhun grub du bshad /
NK069(tu)001:472: nang snying chos kyi 'khor lo dang sbyar nas bshad /
NK069(tu)001:473: gsang ba gsang dbang dang sbyar nas bshad /
NK069(tu)001:474: de kho na nyid dbyer myed du bshad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:475: phyi sku lnga lhun grub tu sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:481: rig pa rang snang gi 'khor ro //
NK069(tu)001:483: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po'o //
NK069(tu)001:485: kun tu bzang po rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa'i dus so //
NK069(tu)001:486: de yang sgyu 'phrul bla ma'i le'u dang po nas /
NK069(tu)001:487: sangs rgyas kun gyi bla ma de //
NK069(tu)001:488: rnal 'byor kun gyi gsang mchog bde //
NK069(tu)001:489: gnas gsang ba na bzhugs nas su //
NK069(tu)001:490: snying po bla mas 'di skad bshad //
NK069(tu)001:492: nang snying ka chos kyi 'khor lo dang sbyar nas bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:494: snying rin po che gur phub pa'i nang na rtsa
NK069(tu)001:495: 'phrin las bzhi'i dbyibs can snod kyi 'od dang bcas
NK069(tu)001:496: pa'o // skad ni ston pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:497: rig pa chos kyi sku srog mi shigs pa'i thig ler bzhugs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:499: yid kyi rnam shes rang la rang gis go ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:500: pa'i zhes pa stan pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:501: don zab mo rang 'byung gi ye shes rang la nyams su myong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:503: ye nas rang bzhin lhun grub kyi sangs rgyas rang la rang chas su yod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:504: de yang bshad rgyud rgya mtsho' las //
NK069(tu)001:506: 'od bzhi e sogs dbyibs gnas su //
NK069(tu)001:507: mi shigs thig le bam dbyibs bdag /
NK069(tu)001:508: rang la bde' ba gsal byed pa //
NK069(tu)001:509: pa ra ma ta don zab mo //
NK069(tu)001:510: ye shes nam mkha'i gzugs skyes pa //
NK069(tu)001:511: bde' ba'i dus nyid snga phyi bral //
NK069(tu)001:512: dus gsum kun gyi ngo bor 'dod //
NK069(tu)001:514: gsang ba b+ha ga la gsang dbang dang sbyar nas bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:516: yum gyi mkha' 'phrin las bzhi'i dbyibs can no //
NK069(tu)001:518: gsang ba'i rdo rje bde' ba chen po'i thig le' byang chub sems gsal bar byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:520: yid kyi rnam par shes pas rlung sems g.yo' ba
NK069(tu)001:521: dang bcas pas bde gsal mi rtog pa'i bde ba
NK069(tu)001:522: go ba'o // pa'i zhes pa stan pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:523: dngos po lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes khu ba dkar dmar la rten nas /
NK069(tu)001:524: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa zag bral nyams su myong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:526: bsam gyis mi khyab pa pa'i dus na yod pa de /
NK069(tu)001:527: yab yum kha sbyor ba'i dus na nyams su myong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:528: de yang bshad rgyud thal ba zhes kyang bya /
NK069(tu)001:529: sgyu 'phrul rol ba'i le'u gsum pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:530: 'di zhes ste bar mtshon pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:531: e sogs rnam bzhi'i dbyibs can gnas //
NK069(tu)001:532: skad ces gsal byed las ming can //
NK069(tu)001:533: bam dbyibs thig ler bcas ston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:534: ma da ma nu stom byed yid //
NK069(tu)001:535: las can rnam shes de dag la //
NK069(tu)001:536: gsal bar go ba bshad par 'dod //
NK069(tu)001:537: pa tra don dam nges pa'i rgyud //
NK069(tu)001:538: yang dag theg chen 'di nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:539: dus ni bsam gyis mi khyab par //
NK069(tu)001:540: de ming kun tu mtshon par byed //
NK069(tu)001:542: de kho na nyid dbyer med du bshad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:544: yul rnam par dag par shes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:546: rang sems rang gis shes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:548: sems de nyid bag chags dang bcas pas shes bya yod pas so //
NK069(tu)001:550: rang gsang ba'i snying po sems dang ye shes rang snang bar go ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:552: rang gi yid rang 'byung lhun grub kyi ston pa de /
NK069(tu)001:553: rtogs pa mngon du gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:554: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid du shes pa de'o //
NK069(tu)001:555: de yang sgyu 'phrul rgya bcu pa las /
NK069(tu)001:556: 'bru ltar ldan pa'i thabs chen po //
NK069(tu)001:557: 'gro ba kun la rang bzhin gnas //
NK069(tu)001:559: de ltar phun sum tshogs pa rnam pa lnga rang la rang chas su yod pa de /
NK069(tu)001:560: rtogs pa'i dus ston pas 'gro ba la bshad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:562: ston pa'i rang bzhin chos sku'i mtshan la bsdus par bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:563: dang po byang chub chen po'i rang bzhin du bstan pa /
NK069(tu)001:564: ston pa'i rang bzhin don dam pa chos sku'i mtshan rgyas par stan pa la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:568: dang po ji ltar grol ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:569: de'i mtshan nyid rnam grangs so //
NK069(tu)001:570: dang po ji ltar grol ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:571: rgyu rang gi yid gnyis myed kyi rig pa rang 'byung gi ye shes chen po de la /
NK069(tu)001:573: de nyid lam du goms pas /
NK069(tu)001:574: mngon du gyur nas zhen pa mtha' dag dang bral ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:575: de'i mtshan gyi rnam grangs ni bdun te /
NK069(tu)001:576: dang po gzhi ji lta bar son pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:578: gzhi de bzhin nyid lhun gyis grub pa gnyis myed kyi rig pa ye shes ma bcos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:580: ye shes de nyid lam gyis mngon du byang nas goms pas zhen pa mtha' dag las grol ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:581: rgya bcu pa'i le'u bcu gcig pa las /
NK069(tu)001:582: bde gshegs dbyings nyid de bzhin nyid gnas pa //
NK069(tu)001:583: dus bzhi rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par 'ub //
NK069(tu)001:585: gnyis pa yon tan thams cad brtsal ba myed par lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:586: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i zhes pa /
NK069(tu)001:588: rgyu bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs kyang yang dag par bsags shing rdzogs pa'i mthar phyin la /
NK069(tu)001:589: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes kyang yang dag par bsags shing rdzogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:590: yang na yang bya gang yang myi dmyigs pas na yang dag /
NK069(tu)001:591: 'bras bu yon tan gyi chos thams cad ma btsal bar lhun gyis grub pas rdzogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:592: gsum pa lta ba ngan pa'i dri ma dang bral
NK069(tu)001:593: zhing ye shes mtha' dbus myed par rdal ba ni
NK069(tu)001:596: 'khor ba'i lta ngan dang ma rig pa rnyid dang 'dra ba ni sangs /
NK069(tu)001:597: yon tan mtha' dbus myed pa la mkhyen pa'i ye
NK069(tu)001:598: shes kyis yul shes bya la pad ma kha phye
NK069(tu)001:599: ba bzhin rgyas pas na sangs rgyas zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:600: bzhi pa yon tan thams cad rang la lhun gyis
NK069(tu)001:601: grub kyang rang gi ngo bo 'di zhes stan du
NK069(tu)001:604: las kyi bag chags myed pas nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:605: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa myed pas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:606: shes bya'i sgrib pa myed pas lha'i bu'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:607: thams cad rang rig tu dag pas 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:609: bdud thams cad rang rig du bcom nas yangs pa phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan /
NK069(tu)001:610: ye shes phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan /
NK069(tu)001:612: ngo bo 'di zhes bya ba ma grub de stan du myed do //
NK069(tu)001:613: gnyis pa chos rnams rol par longs spyod pa bstan /
NK069(tu)001:615: lnga pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid chen por mnga'
NK069(tu)001:616: mdzad kyang spyod yul dang bral ba la gnyis te
NK069(tu)001:618: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i longs spyod do //
NK069(tu)001:620: 'dod yon rnam lnga chos nyid kyi rgyan du rig
NK069(tu)001:621: par byas nas dga' ba de'i longs spyod dang yang
NK069(tu)001:622: ldan la / 'das pa'i longs spyod ye shes chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:624: chos nyid la ye shes kyis longs spyod pa dang yang ldan pa mi 'gal lo //
NK069(tu)001:625: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i longs spyod gnyis su myed pas na chen po zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:626: rgya bcu pa'i le'u gcig pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:627: rdo rje mnyam nyid thugs su chud pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:628: mnyam rdzogs chen po'i lhun la rol pa mdzad /
NK069(tu)001:630: gsum pa phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bde gshegs kyi bdag por bstan /
NK069(tu)001:631: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i bdag nyid /
NK069(tu)001:632: drug pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi spyi gzugs can
NK069(tu)001:633: yin yang gcig dang du ma'i mtha' las grol ba
NK069(tu)001:634: ni / 'o na ston pa de sangs rgyas thams cad dang gcig gam tha dad zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:637: 'das ma 'ongs da ltar gyi dus gsum dang dbyer myed pa mnyam pa nyid dang /
NK069(tu)001:638: phyogs bcu dus bzhi na bzhugs pa'i de ba thams cad kyi /
NK069(tu)001:641: thugs rdo rje thams cad kyi bdag nyid du yang kun tu bzang po de 'gyur ba yin no //
NK069(tu)001:642: de yang thal ba'i le'u bzhi pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:643: mi bzad rgyan gyi 'khor lo nyid //
NK069(tu)001:644: kun nas sku gsung thugs kyi bdag /
NK069(tu)001:645: yon tan 'phrin las rdzogs pa'i stobs //
NK069(tu)001:646: nyi shu rtsa lnga'i bdag nyid can //
NK069(tu)001:648: rgya bcu pa'i le'u bcu gcig pa las /
NK069(tu)001:649: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i dbyings nas mthar btugs pa //
NK069(tu)001:650: rang rig rgyal po che'i rtogs par 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:652: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:654: ston pa 'di phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rang bzhin yin na /
NK069(tu)001:655: nyan thos kyi sgor zhugs pas kyang ma h+aa'i 'bras bu tshe 'di nyid la thob bam /
NK069(tu)001:658: thob na nyan thos dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:659: 'di' rang bzhin de ltar yin yang /
NK069(tu)001:660: gdul bya'i blo log pa'i dbang gis /
NK069(tu)001:661: tshe 'di nyid la myi thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:662: nyan thos kyi lam sbyangs sgrod nas 'jug 'dir thob pa mi 'gal lo //
NK069(tu)001:663: ma lus mi lus lus pa myed pa thams cad dang /
NK069(tu)001:664: bzhi pa chos so lcog dang dbyer myed par bstan /
NK069(tu)001:665: bdun pa gnyis su myed pa'i bdag nyid chen po
NK069(tu)001:666: la dus gsum 'du 'bral myed par bstan pa ni
NK069(tu)001:667: gnyis te / ston pa de dus gsum gyi 'khor 'das dang gcig pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:668: don dam kun rdzob dbyer myed kyi chos dang tha mi dad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:669: dang po 'khor 'das dus gsum gyi chos dang gcig pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:670: ma lus pa ni 'khor ba dang 'das pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:671: myi lus pa ni ma 'ongs pa rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:672: lus pa myed pa ni da ltar ba rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:673: de ltar dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i 'khor 'das rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:674: de ltar na 'khor ba'i sems can rnams kyi yid yang kun tu bzang po yin la /
NK069(tu)001:675: 'das pa'i thugs rig pa'i ye shes kun tu bzang po yin no //
NK069(tu)001:676: so so ma yin tha mi dad dbyer myed pa'i rang bzhin te /
NK069(tu)001:677: gnyis pa don dam pa'i dang /
NK069(tu)001:678: kun rdzob dbyer myed kyi chos dang tha mi dad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:679: de ltar dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i 'khor ba'i chos dang /
NK069(tu)001:680: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos kun yang /
NK069(tu)001:681: kun rdzob tu ni so so ma yin /
NK069(tu)001:682: don dam du ni tha mi dad /
NK069(tu)001:683: bden pa gnyis su yang dbyer myed //
NK069(tu)001:684: de ltar 'khor 'das gnyis myed kyi ye shes de ni /
NK069(tu)001:686: de ni lhag ma dang bcas pa'i tshig gis snyeg pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:687: de la nye ba la snyeg pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:688: de lta bu de gnas ga na bzhugs zhe na 'og min na bzhugs zhes snyeg la /
NK069(tu)001:689: ring ba la snyeg pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:690: ston pa'i rang bzhin gnyis myed kyi ye shes de /
NK069(tu)001:691: gdul bya la snang tshul rang ji ltar snang zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:692: sku mdun dang rgyab myed pa ces pas /
NK069(tu)001:693: ston pa'i ngo bo ston pa la snyeg go //
NK069(tu)001:694: gnyis pa thabs lam dang sbyar nas bshad na bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:695: dang po byang chub chen po'i rang bzhin ni /
NK069(tu)001:697: rang gi lus khams bdud rtsi'o //
NK069(tu)001:699: gsang ba'i rdo rje la byang sems phab pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:701: tha mal gyi zhen pa dag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:703: dga' ba bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:705: yang bya la ltos pa'i dga' ba bzhi sangs nas /
NK069(tu)001:706: rang gi ngo bo la ltos pa'i dga' ba bzhi rgyas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:708: thig le de nyid lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes su snang bas bdud bzhi bcom /
NK069(tu)001:709: bde stong gi nyams dang ldan /
NK069(tu)001:710: de nyid ngo bos stong pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:711: gnyis pa chos rnams rol par longs spyod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:712: longs spyod chen po ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:713: thig le des rgyal ba mchod pa'i rdzas dang /
NK069(tu)001:714: sems can gyi dbang rdzas su spyod pa la /
NK069(tu)001:715: 'khor 'das kyi brjod bya ma lus par rdzogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:716: gsum pa phyogs dus kyi bde gshegs thams cad kyi bdag po bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:717: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:718: rang gi lus la rtsa gnas pa'i nang na /
NK069(tu)001:719: khams kyi thig le lha tshogs su gnas pa'i rtog tshogs rnams dang /
NK069(tu)001:720: ye shes kyi lha dbyer myed pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:721: bzhi pa chos so lcog dang dbyer myed pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:722: ma lus mi lus bcas sogs ni /
NK069(tu)001:723: ma dag pa 'khrul pa'i snang ba'i skabs na /
NK069(tu)001:724: khu ba thig ler snang yang /
NK069(tu)001:725: dag pa ye shes kyi snang ba'i skabs na /
NK069(tu)001:726: lus kyi rtog tshogs sangs rgyas so //
NK069(tu)001:727: de ltar snang bas gnyis su phye yang /
NK069(tu)001:728: 'khor 'das kun yang so sor dbyer myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:729: de yang bshad rgyud sgyu 'phrul rol pa'i le'u gsum pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:730: bcud 'dus thig le chen po ni //
NK069(tu)001:731: snang dang ston pa la sogs pa //
NK069(tu)001:732: brjod bya ma lus rdzogs par snang //
NK069(tu)001:733: rtog tshogs sangs rgyas bzhi bcu lnga //
NK069(tu)001:734: snang bas phye phyir gnyis su myed //
NK069(tu)001:737: ma lus mi lus 'khor ba'i chos nyid yin na /
NK069(tu)001:738: so so ma yin pas 'khor ba'i chos dang yang
NK069(tu)001:739: ston pa tha mi dad dbyer myed pa yin na
NK069(tu)001:740: / 'khor ba sdig pa byed pa dang yang spyod pa spyod pa yin nam /
NK069(tu)001:741: myin na ma lus mi lus pa dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:742: don de ltar yin yang 'khor ba yin pa ma shes pas 'gal ba myed do //
NK069(tu)001:743: rgyas pa'i le'u bdun cu gnyis pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:744: chos rnams ma lus thams cad kun //
NK069(tu)001:745: ye nas rnam par dag pa la //
NK069(tu)001:746: rnam rtog rkyen gyis glo bur du //
NK069(tu)001:747: khams gsum 'khor ba'i rtson rar gnas //
NK069(tu)001:748: rang rig sgrib myed dag pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:750: rang bzhin myed pa'i don rtogs na //
NK069(tu)001:751: sangs rgyas zhing du rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:754: gnas kyi rang bzhin stan pa ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:759: srid pa'i rtse mo'i gnas te /
NK069(tu)001:762: rtsang ma'i rigs dag yangs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:763: 'og myin chen po'i gnas mchog na //
NK069(tu)001:767: de ni rtogs pa kun gyi blar gyur cing /
NK069(tu)001:768: gnas gang gi yang 'og tu ma gyur bas so //
NK069(tu)001:770: dus gsum du myi 'gyur zhing 'dus ma byas pas na /
NK069(tu)001:771: de la mtha' dbus kyi tshad bzung du myed do //
NK069(tu)001:772: de yang rol pa'i le'u dang po nas /
NK069(tu)001:773: 'og min lhun gyis grub pa'i gnas //
NK069(tu)001:774: mtha' dang dbus myed 'khyil ba'i bdag /
NK069(tu)001:777: yum gyi mkha' bde stong gi rnam pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:778: khro bo chen po stobs kyi dbang phyug gi rgyud las /
NK069(tu)001:779: dga' ba'i gzhal yas khang na /
NK069(tu)001:780: dbyer myed pa'i bde ba dang ldan pa ces so //
NK069(tu)001:781: bde ba la mtha' dbus myed par gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:783: grol lam du bshad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:786: 'dod chags dang bral ba'i tshul gyis sangs rgya ba la dgongs pa shas che la /
NK069(tu)001:788: 'dod chags dang bcas pa'i tshul gyis sangs rgya ba la dgongs pa shas che'o //
NK069(tu)001:789: de yang grol lam gzhung rang bshad /
NK069(tu)001:790: thabs lam bshad rgyud kyis bkrol ba'i dgongs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:791: mtha' dang dbus myed pa na /
NK069(tu)001:792: gzhi' tshad myed pa'i ye shes kyi 'khor lor gsal ba la /
NK069(tu)001:794: gnas kyi gzhi' bstan pa ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:798: rgyu ni tshad myed pa bzhi las grub pas /
NK069(tu)001:799: che chung yang tshad myed do //
NK069(tu)001:801: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud rdo rje ra bas skor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:803: lte ba chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:804: shar me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:807: byang bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su gsal ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:808: de ni dbus kyi pho brang du snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:810: tshad myed ye shes 'khor lo'o gnas //
NK069(tu)001:811: tshogs rdzogs mtshan ma'i gnas 'joms shing //
NK069(tu)001:813: ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK069(tu)001:815: gnas kyi rgyu bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:819: rgyu ni ye shes rnam pa lnga las grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:821: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che la kha dog sna lngar 'bar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:823: sems can gyi bloos gzhal bar mi nus yang /
NK069(tu)001:824: ye shes lha'i bzhugs gnas kyi rgyur gyur pas gzhal yas khang grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:826: ma bkod ye nas rgyan pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:827: rigs kyi yon tan kun 'byung gnas //
NK069(tu)001:828: yang dag tshul gyis log lta 'joms //
NK069(tu)001:830: rgya phyogs bcu yongs su ma chad pa /
NK069(tu)001:832: gzhal yas khang gi rgya khyon che chung gi tshad ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:833: rgya chung bar ma chad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:835: chung bar ma chad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:836: de bzhin gshegs pas stong gsum nyungs 'bru gcig gi nang du yang chud par gdul byas mthong la /
NK069(tu)001:837: che bar ma chad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:838: chos kyi dbyings kyis gar khyab par yang gzhal yas khang gis yang khyab pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:839: de las 'dir rgya che ba'i dgongs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:840: 'o na phyal bar 'gyur ro mnyam pa la /
NK069(tu)001:842: yon tan dpag tu myed pa rgyas pa'i phyir gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK069(tu)001:844: gzhal yas khang gi phyi'i dbyibs la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:848: kun tu bzang po'i thugs rig pa'i ye shes dpag tu myed par rgyas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:851: gzhal yas khang gi dbyibs kyang gru bzhir 'byung ba de /
NK069(tu)001:852: gru bzhi 'phrin las bzhi las rgyas pa'i dbyibs yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:854: mya ngan kun bral grong khyer che //
NK069(tu)001:855: khang pa gru bzhi sgo khyud bcas //
NK069(tu)001:857: lhag pa'i ye shes rin po che'i /
NK069(tu)001:860: glo 'bur gyi dbyibs ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:865: don rang 'byung gi ye shes chen po gcig las /
NK069(tu)001:867: ye shes bzhi las lhag pa'i ye shes rin po che re re la yang bzhi bzhir snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:869: rin po che sna bzhi las grub pa'i glo 'bur
NK069(tu)001:870: 'khar thams bzhis gzhal yas khang gi phyogs bzhir mdzes
NK069(tu)001:871: par byas pa'o // kha dog ni /
NK069(tu)001:872: shar rkang ka ri ltar dkar ba /
NK069(tu)001:873: lho gser zhun ma ltar ser ba /
NK069(tu)001:874: nub pad ma ra ga ltar dmar ba /
NK069(tu)001:875: byang in tra ni la ltar ljang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:877: chos nyid snang ba'i bdag nyid can //
NK069(tu)001:878: ye shes nyi shu rtsa lnga'i bdag /
NK069(tu)001:879: rang rig don mthun rtags kyi tshul //
NK069(tu)001:881: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:882: rgya phyogs bcu yongs su ma chad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:883: gru bzhir gyur pa 'gal mnyam pa la /
NK069(tu)001:884: de snang ba gnyis kyi dbang smos pas mi 'gal te /
NK069(tu)001:885: rang bzhin gyi snang ba'i dbang du chos nyid la rgya chad myed pa'i dbang du smos /
NK069(tu)001:886: 'o na dbyibs myed do phyal bar gyur to mnyam pa la /
NK069(tu)001:887: gdul bya'i snang ba'i dbang du rgyas pa mtshon pa'i gru bzhir smos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:888: rtse mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi /
NK069(tu)001:889: dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad //
NK069(tu)001:890: so so ma yin ngo bo nyid cig pa'i ye shes kun tu 'khyil ba /
NK069(tu)001:892: rtse mo dbu' rtse lta bu'i dbyibs ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:899: sangs rgyas kyi sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:900: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi ngo bor gcig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:902: gzhal yas khang gi rtse mo ye shes lnga'i 'od
NK069(tu)001:903: dpung du 'khyil ba'i rin po che 'bar bas te
NK069(tu)001:904: / dpen na rma bya'i mdongs lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:906: rtse mo nor bu 'bar ba la //
NK069(tu)001:907: rigs kyi mtshan ma brgyan du byas //
NK069(tu)001:908: ngo bo gnyis myed 'khyil ba'i bdag /
NK069(tu)001:910: 'o na cig du 'dres nas dbyer med dam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:911: ye shes bsam gyis myi khyab pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:913: rin po che pha gu'i rgyan /
NK069(tu)001:914: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK069(tu)001:915: rin po che'i rgyan bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:916: ye shes so so'i mtshan nyid dang /
NK069(tu)001:917: bye brag gi cha 'dzin pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:918: thugs che ba'i yon tan rin po che lta bu bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan de /
NK069(tu)001:920: de las bsam yas grangs myed pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:922: ye shes rin po che'i dbyibs dang kha dog la rtsogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:923: rnam pa tha dad ma 'dres pa 'ja' ltar snang ba /
NK069(tu)001:925: khyad theg pa gzhan las sam gzhal yas khang gzhan las /
NK069(tu)001:928: lha mis dpag par dka' ba /
NK069(tu)001:930: rgyu ye shes las grub pa /
NK069(tu)001:931: rtags rin po cher snang ba /
NK069(tu)001:932: dbyibs dang kha dog dkar la zlum pa shar na yod /
NK069(tu)001:933: lho na gru bzhi ser po /
NK069(tu)001:934: nub na dmar po zla kham /
NK069(tu)001:935: byang na gru gsum ljang khu /
NK069(tu)001:936: de ma yin pa rnam pa mi 'dra ba /
NK069(tu)001:938: bye brag mong po yod de /
NK069(tu)001:939: lta bas mi ngoms pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:940: theg pa gzhan las khyad par du gyur pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:942: tshad gzung du myed pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:943: rin po che pha gu sna tshogs kyis rtsig pa byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:945: de las bsam yas grangs myed pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:946: tha dad sna tshogs 'jigs pa myed //
NK069(tu)001:947: bde bzhin nyid snang de bzhin nyid //
NK069(tu)001:948: dbyibs dang kha dog rnams dpag pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:949: rnam pa tha dad bye brag mchog /
NK069(tu)001:950: khyad par yon tan gnas kyis mdzes //
NK069(tu)001:951: lha dang mi sogs tshad 'das shing //
NK069(tu)001:952: dpag myed rigs kyi rgyan rnams dang //
NK069(tu)001:954: ye shes rin po che sna tshogs kyis 'phreng ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:955: rgyu ye shes las ni grub /
NK069(tu)001:956: rtags rin po cher ni snang /
NK069(tu)001:957: rnam pa bye brag sna tshogs su ni ma 'dres pas /
NK069(tu)001:958: thugs rje rgyun mi chad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:959: myi brjed pa'i gzungs thob pas na /
NK069(tu)001:960: rin po che'i 'phreng bas rgyan de dra bar byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:961: dra ba dra phyed kyi rgyan /
NK069(tu)001:963: bden pa gnyis dbyer myed pa'i rtags su chun 'phyang dang /
NK069(tu)001:964: thabs shes rab kyis don so sor mdzad pas na
NK069(tu)001:965: shar bu'i rgyan rnams kyis d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba
NK069(tu)001:967: de yang ye shes kyi rgyun thag la /
NK069(tu)001:968: rin po che'i yon tan rgyus pa'i rgyan rnams ni /
NK069(tu)001:969: nam mkha'i 'ja' tshon ltar snang la rang bzhin myed pa /
NK069(tu)001:970: gsal la ma 'dres par gsal ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:972: kun nas rgya yongs ma chad pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:979: gzugs kyi lha mo dkar mo phyag na me long thogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:980: rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs pas spras pa /
NK069(tu)001:981: de lta bu'i gzugs mdzes pa mang po gnas pas na sna tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:984: sgra'i lha mo ser mo phyag na pi wang dang /
NK069(tu)001:986: sgra'i rol mo sna tshogs pa mang po bsnams pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:989: lag na gdug spos lta bu la sogs pa dri sna tshogs thogs pa rnams dang /
NK069(tu)001:992: lag na zhal zas ro mchog brgya ldan sna tshogs thogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:993: reg bya sna tshogs kyis phyogs bcur 'khrigs pa //
NK069(tu)001:994: reg bya'i lha mo mthing ka /
NK069(tu)001:995: phyag na lha'i na bza' la sogs pa reg bya 'jam po sna tshogs thogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:996: de dag phyogs bcu nas sprin bzhin 'khrigs so //
NK069(tu)001:997: rol pa'i le'u dang po nas /
NK069(tu)001:998: kun nas sprul pa lha mo'i tshogs //
NK069(tu)001:999: ye shes bkod pa ma 'dres pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:1000: 'dod yon tshogs kyis rnam par slubs //
NK069(tu)001:1001: phyogs bcu kun nas 'khrigs pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:1002: sprin phung lta bus rab tu brgyan //
NK069(tu)001:1004: rgyan spyi'i mtshan nyid bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:1006: mi sgrib par gsal ba'i rgyan //
NK069(tu)001:1007: gzhal yas khang gi rgyan de dag mtshan nyid ci zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:1008: rgyu rkyen gzhan gyis ma skyed par /
NK069(tu)001:1009: gzhal yas khang la rang 'byung du grub pas na /
NK069(tu)001:1010: kun bzang gi che ba'i yon tan rang 'byung du shar ba /
NK069(tu)001:1011: gcig la gcig mi sgrib pa ni dar le'u rgan
NK069(tu)001:1012: gyi thag pas shel 'phreng rgyus pa dang 'dra ba
NK069(tu)001:1013: / gsal ba ni me long gi gzugs brnyan ltar snang la rang bzhin myed pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:1014: lha dang mi bsam gyis myi khyab pas phyogs thams cad nas slubs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1015: bsam gyis mi khyab par slubs pa //
NK069(tu)001:1017: rang 'byung zhi rgyas dbang drag brgyan //
NK069(tu)001:1018: mtha' yas mdzad pa kun ston cing //
NK069(tu)001:1019: tha dad dpag pa'i tshul gyis gnas //
NK069(tu)001:1020: sgrib myed gsal ba'i bdag nyid can //
NK069(tu)001:1021: bsam 'das rgya chen grangs myed slubs //
NK069(tu)001:1023: sgo dang sgo khyud pa stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:1024: rnam par thar pa bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug pa'i sgo khyud can /
NK069(tu)001:1026: shar rnam par thar pa'i sgo stong pa nyid dang /
NK069(tu)001:1027: lho mtshan ma myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1028: nub smon pa myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1029: byang rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1030: sgo de bzhi nas ma h+aa yo gar 'jug pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1031: sgo khyud ni mtshon sna ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin pan tsa rags phyogs thams cad 'khor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1033: stod smon mtshan myed 'od gsal sgo //
NK069(tu)001:1034: sangs rgyas thog pas rnam par spras //
NK069(tu)001:1036: rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi rta babs dang ldan pa //
NK069(tu)001:1038: nyon mongs pa'i 'ching ba las grol ba'i rnam par thar pa brgyad dang /
NK069(tu)001:1039: them skas kyi rgyan du gyur pa'i rnam par thar pa brgyad dang /
NK069(tu)001:1040: lta babs kyi rgyan brgyad do //
NK069(tu)001:1042: gzugs can gzugs la lta ba'i rnam par thar pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1043: nang gzugs myed par 'du shes nas phyi rol gyi
NK069(tu)001:1044: gzugs rnams la lta ba'i rnam par thar pa dang
NK069(tu)001:1045: / sdug pa'i rnam par thar pa lus kyi mngon sum du byas nas rdzogs par gnas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1046: nam mkha' mtha' yas kyi skye mched rdzogs par byas nas gnas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1047: rnam par shes pa mtha' yas so mnyam nas rnam
NK069(tu)001:1048: shes mtha' yas skye mched rdzogs par byas nas gnas
NK069(tu)001:1049: pa dang / ci yang myed do mnyam nas ci
NK069(tu)001:1050: yang myed pa'i skye mched rdzogs par bya ba dang
NK069(tu)001:1051: pa dang / / 'du shes myed 'du shes myed
NK069(tu)001:1052: min gyi skye mched rdzogs par byas nas gnas pa
NK069(tu)001:1053: pa dang / / dang / 'du shes dang tshor
NK069(tu)001:1054: ba 'gog pa lus kyis mngon sum du byas te
NK069(tu)001:1056: rta babs kyi rgyan du gyur pa'i rnam par thar pa brgyad ni /
NK069(tu)001:1066: zhabs dang ma chags za rang rtsags //
NK069(tu)001:1068: sna tshogs khyung mgo rim par 'khrigs //
NK069(tu)001:1070: them skas su gyur pa'i rta babs brgyad ni //
NK069(tu)001:1071: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1080: phyi nang gsang ba zab mo yi //
NK069(tu)001:1081: rnam thar brgyad kyi rta babs ldan //
NK069(tu)001:1083: phyi dang nang myed par kun tu yang nang du gyur pa na /
NK069(tu)001:1084: gzhal yas khang gi rang bzhin ni /
NK069(tu)001:1086: phyi nas ltas na nang gsal la /
NK069(tu)001:1087: nang nas ltas na phyi gsal te /
NK069(tu)001:1089: kun tu yang nang du gyur ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:1090: phyi gzhal yas khang du snang yang /
NK069(tu)001:1091: kun tu bzang po'i che ba yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:1093: phyi yang ye shes su song ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1095: 'o na phyi myed pa'i nang 'ba' zhig tu smos pa 'gal zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:1096: mi 'gal te 'di de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba'i dbang du byas pas /
NK069(tu)001:1097: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba la phyi nang myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1099: phyi dang nang myed ye shes dngos //
NK069(tu)001:1100: mtha' dbus myed pa'i bde chen dbyings //
NK069(tu)001:1103: phyi sems can gyi sems dang /
NK069(tu)001:1104: nang sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa gnyis myed /
NK069(tu)001:1105: shes bya chos kyi dbyings dang /
NK069(tu)001:1106: shes byed rig pa'i cha gnyis myed /
NK069(tu)001:1107: don dam pa dang kun rdzob kyi cha gnyis myed de /
NK069(tu)001:1108: bden pa dbyer myed ma rtogs pa de rtogs par byed pa'i phyir smos so //
NK069(tu)001:1109: gnas 'di nyid rig pa'i 'og min yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:1110: rig pa la phyi nang myed /
NK069(tu)001:1111: rig cing go bas na thams cad nang du 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:1112: brgya bcu pa'i le'u drug cu gsum pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:1113: chos rnams rang bzhin nyid kyis stong //
NK069(tu)001:1114: nang dang nang gi phyi rol gyi //
NK069(tu)001:1115: rnam tog sna tshogs 'dzin pa yang //
NK069(tu)001:1116: dngos po myed dbyings skad cig ma //
NK069(tu)001:1118: gnyis pa gnas thabs lam du bshad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:1120: yum gyi b+ha ga 'khor lo rim pa gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:1124: nang ma de las dang yon tan gnyis kyis phyi
NK069(tu)001:1125: ma las khyad par du gyur pas na 'og min
NK069(tu)001:1126: no // sbyor ba'i las dang byang sems kyi bcud mtha' bzhi dang bral bas so //
NK069(tu)001:1128: gzhi tshad myed pa ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:1129: dga' ba bzhi'i ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:1131: ye shes rin po che ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:1132: byang chub sems la thun mong dang khyad par gyi dgos pa 'byung zhing ldan pas so //
NK069(tu)001:1133: gzhal yas khang gi rgya khyon ni /
NK069(tu)001:1135: dga' ba bzhi'i ngo bo la blos dpag par dka' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1136: gzhal yas khang gi phyi'i dbyibs ni /
NK069(tu)001:1137: yon tan dpag tu myed pa ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:1138: blos dpag par dka' ba'i dga' ba bzhir gyur pas so //
NK069(tu)001:1139: glo bur ni lhag pa'i ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:1140: dga' ba'i ye shes lnga dang ldan par 'khor lor skor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1142: rtse mo phyogs bcur ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:1145: de sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo ste /
NK069(tu)001:1146: bde ba chen po'i 'khor lo spyi bor 'khyil bas so //
NK069(tu)001:1148: ye shes bsam gyis myi khyab ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:1149: rdo rje dbyings phyug ma'i sna rtse nyungs dkar tsam gyis gzhan las dpag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1150: rtsa sa ya bcu gsum du bde ba sna tshogs
NK069(tu)001:1151: rgyas pas na ye shes rin po che sna tshogs
NK069(tu)001:1154: khu ba mchod par byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1155: de rnams ni bshad rgyud rol pa'i le'u gsum pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:1156: de gnas pad+ma rim gsum po //
NK069(tu)001:1157: gnyis gsum brgyan kyi khyad par can //
NK069(tu)001:1158: tha ma gnas dang yon tan gyis //
NK069(tu)001:1159: mngon par mtho bas 'og myin te //
NK069(tu)001:1160: las dang bcud kyis mtha' bral ba //
NK069(tu)001:1161: ye shes bzhi la dpag myi rigs //
NK069(tu)001:1162: dgos pa 'byung ldan rin po che //
NK069(tu)001:1164: sangs rgyas ngo bo snod bcud kyi //
NK069(tu)001:1165: spyi bo shin tu 'khyil bar gnas //
NK069(tu)001:1166: nyungs dkar son gyis dpag pa ni //
NK069(tu)001:1167: sa ya bcu gsum bde bas rgyan //
NK069(tu)001:1168: 'dod yon khyad par can gyis mdzes //
NK069(tu)001:1171: rnam par thar pa bzhi ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:1172: yum gyi b+ha ga la rnam tog nub pas na 'og min /
NK069(tu)001:1173: b+ha ga pad+ma 'dab brgyad chags pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa'i gdan la /
NK069(tu)001:1174: rgyal ba kun bzhugs pa dang 'byung bas na dus gsum gyi bde ba 'char /
NK069(tu)001:1175: bde ba de'i rnam pa dga' ba bzhi'o //
NK069(tu)001:1176: dga' ba de phyag rgya bzhi dang ltan te /
NK069(tu)001:1180: snying po rlung gi phyag rgya'o //
NK069(tu)001:1182: dbang ma thob pa'i skye bo sogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:1183: skal myed nyan thos la gsang bas na /
NK069(tu)001:1187: rnam par thar pa brgyad ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:1189: phyag rgya bzhi ste brgyad do //
NK069(tu)001:1190: de yang sgyu 'phrul rgyas pa las /
NK069(tu)001:1191: nub phyogs 'og min gnas mchog tu //
NK069(tu)001:1192: ma chags pad+ma'i gdan sting ba //
NK069(tu)001:1193: dus gsum sangs rgyas bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK069(tu)001:1194: rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhi la //
NK069(tu)001:1195: phyag rgya bzhi dang nges par ldan //
NK069(tu)001:1196: dbang dang skal med gsal ba'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:1197: nang gtan phyi rim lcags dang ldan //
NK069(tu)001:1199: gzhal yas khang gi rang bzhin ni /
NK069(tu)001:1200: phyi dang nang myed pa ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:1201: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes kyi bde ba'i ngo bo la /
NK069(tu)001:1202: phyi nang gi rnam rtog bral ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1203: gzhal yas khang gi gdan ni /
NK069(tu)001:1205: byang chub sems kyi bde ba'i ro nyid la /
NK069(tu)001:1208: myi 'jigs pa bzhi la sogs pa rdzogs soha&a&a&a /
NK069(tu)001:1209: yum gyi khu ba zla ba /
NK069(tu)001:1210: yab kyi khu ba nyi ma /
NK069(tu)001:1211: de la sems nyid sangs rgyas bzhugs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1213: gang yang bde byed phyi nang bral //
NK069(tu)001:1214: bde ba chen po'i ro nyid la //
NK069(tu)001:1215: 'bras bu'i chos kun rdzogs par ldan //
NK069(tu)001:1216: byang chub mchog tu nyi zla shar //
NK069(tu)001:1217: de nyid bzhugs gnas yin par bshad //
NK069(tu)001:1219: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:1220: 'og min sangs rgyas kyi gnas su seng ge la
NK069(tu)001:1221: sogs pa'i byol song yong ba ci te zhe na
NK069(tu)001:1223: byang chub sems dpas lus gdan du phul ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:1224: yang na mi 'jigs pa dang stobs rnams che ba
NK069(tu)001:1225: sems can la stan pa'i rdar sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK069(tu)001:1226: gzugs so // sdos pa can ma yin pas 'gal ba myed do //
NK069(tu)001:1227: mi 'jigs pa seng ge'i khri dang /
NK069(tu)001:1230: sems can gyi gdan la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:1235: lha ni rdo rje sems pa'i gdan no //
NK069(tu)001:1236: don ni me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis zhe
NK069(tu)001:1237: sdang 'dul ba'i phyir myi 'jigs pa bzhi dang ldan
NK069(tu)001:1238: te / da rung mngon par sangs ma rgyas zer ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1239: zag pa ma zad pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:1240: bar chad 'byung nges par ma byung zer ba bzhis 'jigs pa dang bral te /
NK069(tu)001:1242: mngon par sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1244: gzhan gyis bar mi chod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1245: nges par 'khor ba la byung ste /
NK069(tu)001:1246: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i 'jigs myed pa'i thugs kyis chos kyi 'khor lo ston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1248: seng ge gcan gzan gzhan gyi 'jigs pa dang bral ba de gdan du sting ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1250: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi dbus na 'byung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1251: stobs glang po che'i khri dang /
NK069(tu)001:1253: lha gang gi gdan yin na /
NK069(tu)001:1256: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyis gti mug 'dul ba'i phyir stobs bcu dang ldan te /
NK069(tu)001:1257: gnas dang gnas myin gang yang mkhyen pa'i stobs dang /
NK069(tu)001:1258: dus gsum 'das pa'i rnam smin mkhyen pa'i dang /
NK069(tu)001:1259: khams sna tshogs mkhyen pa'i dang /
NK069(tu)001:1260: pha rol gyi mos pa mkhyen pa'i dang /
NK069(tu)001:1261: dbang po mchog dang mchog ma yin pa mkhyen pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1262: kun tu 'gro ba'i lam mkhyen pa'i dang /
NK069(tu)001:1263: bsam gtan mthar phyin nyon mongs pa mkhyen pa'i dang /
NK069(tu)001:1264: sngon gyi gnas mkhyen pa'i dang /
NK069(tu)001:1265: skye ba dang 'chi 'pho ba mkhyen pa'i dang /
NK069(tu)001:1266: zag pa zad myed sems grol mkhyen pa'i stobs bcus /
NK069(tu)001:1267: sems can la mngon shes drug ston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1269: glang po che'i rgyab tu shong tshad theg pas na stobs che ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1270: gnas ni 'khor lo'i shar gyi rtsibs stengs su bzhugs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1272: lha gang gi gdan yin na /
NK069(tu)001:1273: rin chen 'byung ldan gyi gdan no //
NK069(tu)001:1275: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis nga rgyal 'dul
NK069(tu)001:1276: ba'i phyir yon tan rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi
NK069(tu)001:1277: ste / 'dun ba'i ting nge 'dzin spong ba'i 'du
NK069(tu)001:1278: byed dang ldan pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa dang
NK069(tu)001:1279: ste / / sems kyi ting nge 'dzin spong ba'i
NK069(tu)001:1280: 'du byed dang ldan pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa
NK069(tu)001:1281: ste / / dang / brtson 'grus kyi ting nge
NK069(tu)001:1282: 'dzin spong ba'i 'du byed dang ldan pa'i rdzu 'phrul
NK069(tu)001:1284: spyod pa'i ting nge 'dzin spong ba'i 'du byed pa'i ldan pa'i rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhis /
NK069(tu)001:1289: ye shes bzhi 'gro ba ston pas so //
NK069(tu)001:1291: rta rdzu 'phrul can gyi gdan no //
NK069(tu)001:1294: gdan la ngag don bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:1295: chos kyi 'khor lo skor ba'i gdan dang /
NK069(tu)001:1296: yon gyi che ba bcom pa'i gdan dang /
NK069(tu)001:1297: thugs rjes 'gro don mdzad pa'i gdan dang /
NK069(tu)001:1298: sa'i khyad par sgrod pa'i gdan no //
NK069(tu)001:1299: chos kyi 'khor lo skor ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:1300: gzhal yas khang gi dbus 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1301: yon tan gyi che ba bcom pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:1302: seng ge'i gdan ni yon tan mi 'jigs pa bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1303: des gzhan gyi che ba 'joms pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1305: thugs rjes 'gro don mdzad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:1306: rin po che'i khri rkang gi gdan las sems can la dgos 'dod yid bzhin du 'byung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1307: sa'i khyad par bsgrod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:1308: sa bcu thob pa'i rgyu'i byang chub sems dpa' las khyad par du gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:1309: 'bras bu sku gsum gyi sa thob pas na /
NK069(tu)001:1310: bcu gcig kun tu 'od la sprul sku /
NK069(tu)001:1311: bcu gnyis ma chags pad ma can la longs sku /
NK069(tu)001:1312: bcu gsum yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa la chos sku ste /
NK069(tu)001:1317: de yang sems can gyi gdan 'di dag la 'dod lugs gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:1318: sangs rgyas kyi che ba'i yon tan gzhan la ston pa'i brda ston pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1319: byang chub sems dpa' lus gdan du sprul nas rna
NK069(tu)001:1320: bas chos nyan cing shes bya'i sgrib pa sbyong ba'o
NK069(tu)001:1322: mtshan ma rtags kyi gnas rdzogs shing //
NK069(tu)001:1323: thugs rje'i byang chub sems nyid ldan //
NK069(tu)001:1326: lha gang gi gdan yin na /
NK069(tu)001:1329: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyis 'dod chags 'dul ba'i phyir dbang bcu' ste /
NK069(tu)001:1330: yo byad la dbang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1331: skye ba la dbang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1339: mos pa la dbang ba dang bcus /
NK069(tu)001:1340: khams gsum gyi dbang phyug tu bston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1342: rma bya spu gdug cing yid gdung ba'i don te /
NK069(tu)001:1344: nub phyogs kyi 'khor lo'i rtsibs stengs su'o //
NK069(tu)001:1345: thogs pa myed pa nam mkha' lding gi khri dang /
NK069(tu)001:1346: lha gang gi gdan yin na /
NK069(tu)001:1348: don brtags ci dang ldan na /
NK069(tu)001:1349: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyis phrag dog can 'dul ba'i phyir 'phrin las bzhi 'grub ste /
NK069(tu)001:1353: drag po'i las la thogs pa myed par lhun grub tu ston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1354: rtags gang byung na mkha' lding shang shang mi dang bya'i nus pa kun yod pa byung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:1355: gnas gang la dbang na byang phyogs so //
NK069(tu)001:1356: de dag yang rol ba'i rgyud las /
NK069(tu)001:1357: rgyu rkyen lam dang thabs kyi chos //
NK069(tu)001:1358: de dag 'bras bu'i bdag nyid can //
NK069(tu)001:1359: mi 'jigs rnam bzhi stobs bcu dang //
NK069(tu)001:1360: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa dbang bcu yi //
NK069(tu)001:1361: thogs myed gsang chen mtshon lnga'i bdag /
NK069(tu)001:1362: nyi zla'i gdan stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:1363: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK069(tu)001:1365: nang yid rang 'byung gi ye shes la sgrib pa myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1366: lam du thabs dang shes rab kyi rang bzhin dang /
NK069(tu)001:1367: nyi ma shes rab stong pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1368: zla ba thabs rgya che bar stan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1369: nang sems nyid rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba /
NK069(tu)001:1370: lam bar chad kyi sgrib pa myed pa'i sa thob /
NK069(tu)001:1371: rtags nyi ma dang zla ba'i dkyil 'khor rigs lnga
NK069(tu)001:1372: 'khor dang bcas pa'i gdan du gding bar bsam mo
NK069(tu)001:1374: kun tu sgrib pa myed pa'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:1375: thams cad rang gi dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK069(tu)001:1377: gos pa myed pa pad ma'i /
NK069(tu)001:1383: rang rig pa la nyes pa'i skyon gyis mi gos pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:1384: rigs lnga'i thugs nyes pa'i skyon dang bral ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1385: de'i rtags su pad+ma bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:1386: pad+ma la 'dam gyi skyon gyi mi gos par 'dam yon tan du 'gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:1391: de bas na rang gi rig pa la 'khor ba'i skyon gyis mi gos shing /
NK069(tu)001:1394: kun nas ma chags rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:1398: rin po che'i khri rkang la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:1403: re re la rin po che'i khri rkang /
NK069(tu)001:1404: mdzod dmyig bdun bdun yod pa /
NK069(tu)001:1405: ka ba brgyad kyis bteg pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1407: rgyal srid rin po che dpung bdun tshang ba /
NK069(tu)001:1408: sems can gyi dgos 'dod yid bzhin du skong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1410: kun 'byung rin chen rtsigs pa'i khri //
NK069(tu)001:1411: de dag nyi shu rtsa lnga'i gdan //
NK069(tu)001:1414: sku mdun dang rgyab myed par thams cad zhal thal bar gsal zhing /
NK069(tu)001:1416: ston pa'i ngo bo dngos su bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:1417: grol lam du bshad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1421: 'chad pa'i skyes bu mtshan thun mong du bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:1422: dang po sku'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:1423: rgyu sems can gyi sems la phyi nang myed /
NK069(tu)001:1424: lam ye shes la phyi nang myed /
NK069(tu)001:1425: 'bras bu chos sku la phyi nang myed pas /
NK069(tu)001:1426: ye shes sgyu ma lta bu'i sku la mdun rgyab ma grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1427: thams cad du zhal thal bar gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:1428: longs sku rdos cas ma yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1429: 'khor thams cad la mnyam par dgongs pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:1430: zhal thams cad la ston pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1431: thugs phyogs ris myed pas thams cad la khyab /
NK069(tu)001:1432: zhal sgrib pa spangs pas phyogs bcur gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:1434: rnam par bkod pa'i sku chen po //
NK069(tu)001:1435: thams cad gsal bar byed pa'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:1436: thams cad ma 'gags theg pa'i tshul //
NK069(tu)001:1437: zab mo rgya chen gsang ba'i sngags //
NK069(tu)001:1438: don kun nges par gcod byed pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:1439: rang rig ye shes 'gyur ba myed //
NK069(tu)001:1441: 'dir gtar kas gags bsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:1442: sku la mdun rgyab myed pas zhal gsal rgyu mi yong snyam pa la /
NK069(tu)001:1444: ston pa rdos bcas kyi lus las grol bas tsha
NK069(tu)001:1445: reg dang grang reg spangs pa'i sku la phyi nang
NK069(tu)001:1446: myed pa chos skur bzhugs te /
NK069(tu)001:1447: nam mkha' 'ja' lta bu gang nas ltas kyang gsal ba la /
NK069(tu)001:1448: gdul bya'i blos btags pa phyogs gcig tu 'dzin pa dgag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1449: mdun rgyab tu 'dzin pa'i rtog pa bral ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1450: de yang 'khor la dgongs pas gdul bya'i blo la zhal yang nga la stan la /
NK069(tu)001:1451: thugs kyang nga la mnyes par gtod snyam pa'i bsam pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1456: spyir mtshan dpe' la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:1460: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK069(tu)001:1461: dpe' byad bzang po brgyad cu'o //
NK069(tu)001:1463: phyag dang zhabs kyi thil la 'khor lo'i mtshan dang ldan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1464: zhabs shin du gnas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1465: phyag dang zhabs d+r+wa bas 'bral ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1466: phyag dang zhabs gzhon zhing 'jam pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1467: bdun shin tu mtho' ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1470: sku che zhing drang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1472: yan lag gi pu gyen du 'khyil ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1473: ri dwags e na ya'i byin pa lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:1474: phyag rla drang por sleb pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1475: gsang ba'i gnas sbubs su nub pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1476: gser gyi kha dog lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:1480: zhal mdzod spus brgyan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1481: seng+ge'i ro stod lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:1482: 'phrag pa'i lhun mdzes par grub pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1483: phrag pa shin du rgyas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1485: shing na gro ta ltar chu zheng gab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1486: dbu' spyi tsug dang ldan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1487: ljags shin du yangs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1490: tshems shin du dkar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1493: tshems bzhi bcu tshang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1494: spyan dkar nag phyed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1497: sen mo zangs ltar dmar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1502: sor mo rims kyis bzhol ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1504: rtsa la mdud pa myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1505: long bu myi mngon pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1506: zhabs myi mnyam pa myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1508: glang po che'i 'gros su bzhud pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1509: ngang pa'i stabs su bzhud pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1510: khyu mchog gi stabs su bzhud pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1511: g.yas phyogs su bzhud pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1513: mi g.yo bar bzhud pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1514: sku shin du legs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1515: sku shin du sbyangs ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1516: sku rims kyis bzhol ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1517: sku shin tu gtsang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1519: sku shin du rnam par dag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1520: dpe' byad shin tu rdzogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1521: sku che zhing mdzes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1522: sku legs par mnyam pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1523: sku shin du gzhon pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1524: sku zhum pa myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1525: sku shin du rgyas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1527: yan lag dang nying lag dpa' bar mdzes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1528: snang ba rab rib myed cing rnam par dag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1530: phyal shin du byang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1534: lte ba g.yas phyogs su 'khyil ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1536: kun spyod pa shin du gtsang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1537: sku la rme ba myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1538: phyag shing bal ltar 'jam pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1539: phyag gi ri mo snum pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1540: phyag gi ri mo zab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1541: phyag gi ri mo ring ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1542: zhal ha cang mi ring ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1543: zhal gzugs brnyan snang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1545: ljags shin tu srab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1546: ljags shin du dmar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1547: glang po'i nga ro dang 'brug gi dbyangs dang ldan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1548: snyan cing 'jam pa dang nyams su bde' ba'i gsung dang ldan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1549: tshems mche' ba zlum pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1550: tshems mche' ba rno ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1551: tshems mche' ba dkar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1552: tshems mche' ba mnyam pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1553: tshems mche' ba ring zhing bzhol ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1554: shangs legs par mtho' ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1555: shangs legs par gtsang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1556: spyan gyi kyus ring ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1557: spyan rnam par dag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1559: spyan dkar nag phyed cing pad mo'i 'dab ma lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:1562: smin ma'i spu mnyam pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1563: smin ma'i spu snum pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1564: snyan legs shing snyan shal ring ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1566: snyan gyi dbang po ma nyams pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1567: zhal phral ba legs par grub pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1568: zhal phral ba yangs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1569: dbu' shin du rgyas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1570: dbu' bung ba ltar gnag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1574: dbu' skra mi rtsub pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1576: phyag dang zhabs dpal gyi be'u dang bkra shis dang dga' ba 'khyil pas rgyan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1577: khyad par gyi mtshan dpe' ni /
NK069(tu)001:1578: ye shes chen po dang ldan pa'i rtags su gyur pa'i sras sems dpa' dang /
NK069(tu)001:1579: sems ma'i tshogs kyi phyag rgyar snang bas kun nas skor zhing bzhugs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1580: ci'i phyir mtshan dang dpe' byad du zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:1581: dge shis kyi rtags su gyur pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1582: gsal ba so sor dbyer ba'i phyir rgyan du gyur bas so //
NK069(tu)001:1583: de yang mtshan dpe' thun mong ba 'di rnams ni /
NK069(tu)001:1584: sprul pa'i sku dang longs sku gnyis ka la ldan la /
NK069(tu)001:1585: khyad par gyi mtshan dpe 'di rnams ni /
NK069(tu)001:1588: gsang ba'i gnas snubs su nub pa ni sprul sku la ldan la /
NK069(tu)001:1589: longs sku la mi ldan te /
NK069(tu)001:1590: longs sku gsang ba'i yum dang mkha' sbyor snyoms 'jug tu bzhugs pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:1591: 'dir gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:1592: 'og min gyi gnas na thub pa drug yod dam myed /
NK069(tu)001:1593: yod na le'u dang po 'og min gyi gleng gzhir ma byung /
NK069(tu)001:1594: myed na rjes 'jug gis spyan drang ba'i yul myed do //
NK069(tu)001:1596: de gdul bya'i dbang ni te /
NK069(tu)001:1597: 'og min na thub drug gis 'dul ba'i gdul bya myed pas sku mngon du ma phyung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:1598: don kun tu bzang po la tshang bas rjes 'jug lam pa'i nyams len dang mi 'gal lo //
NK069(tu)001:1599: de bas na bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad
NK069(tu)001:1600: du sku gsung thugs sna tshogs pa kun tu snang
NK069(tu)001:1603: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las /
NK069(tu)001:1604: thugs rje chen po'i byin gyis rlabs zhes bya ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:1605: rig pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug /
NK069(tu)001:1606: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang /
NK069(tu)001:1610: de bas na sprul pa'i sku spros pa dngos ni
NK069(tu)001:1611: le'u gsum pa sprul pa sku'i gleng gzhi' na gsal
NK069(tu)001:1612: lo // snang tshul bstan pa la /
NK069(tu)001:1613: bsam gyis myi khyab pa thams cad du /
NK069(tu)001:1615: sna tshogs pa kun tu snang ba /
NK069(tu)001:1617: ston pa'i mdzad pa ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:1621: nyi shu rtsa lnga lhun gyis grub pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:1626: rdo rje'i sku stong nyid dang /
NK069(tu)001:1627: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku rig pa rang gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:1629: skye myed don gyi gsung dang /
NK069(tu)001:1631: sna tshogs tshig gi gsung dang /
NK069(tu)001:1632: grag stong dbyer myed kyi gsung dang /
NK069(tu)001:1633: rig pa sgyu ma'i gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:1635: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes stong pa nyid dang /
NK069(tu)001:1636: me long lta bu'i ye shes rang gsal dang /
NK069(tu)001:1637: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes mi 'byed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1638: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes ma 'gags pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1639: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes mthar thug pa'i thugs so //
NK069(tu)001:1653: rang la de dag rdzogs pa'i nad kas /
NK069(tu)001:1654: gdul bya bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad du snang ba la /
NK069(tu)001:1655: de dag 'dul ba'i sku gsung thugs kyang sna tshogs pa kun du snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:1656: de yang zhi khro la sogs pa'i sku sna tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:1657: lha dang mi dang dri za la sogs pa skad sna tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:1658: dus gsum mkhyen pa'i thugs sna tshogs su snang ste /
NK069(tu)001:1661: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:1663: chos kun spyi'i bdag nyid can //
NK069(tu)001:1664: nyi shu rtsa lnga'i gnas rdzogs pas //
NK069(tu)001:1665: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor mtha' yas dag /
NK069(tu)001:1666: nyi shu rtsa lnga mngon par rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:1667: bsam gyis mi khyab thams cad kun //
NK069(tu)001:1668: sku dang gsung thugs bdag nyid che zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:1669: mdor na sku gsum thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor bzhugs pa'i nad kas /
NK069(tu)001:1672: thugs kyi mkhyen pa ma rmongs par 'char zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:1674: rigs bdag phyag rgya lhun grub sku //
NK069(tu)001:1675: cig dang du ma rnam yangs pa //
NK069(tu)001:1676: sangs rgyas kun gyi spyi gzugs de //
NK069(tu)001:1677: gdod nas theg mchog ston mdzad phyir //
NK069(tu)001:1678: sgrib pa'i mtha' yangs gdul bya la //
NK069(tu)001:1679: skad cig gcig gis snang bar mdzad //
NK069(tu)001:1682: thabs dang shes rab kyi zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i brtul zhugs kyi dkyil mo bkrung du bzhugs pa /
NK069(tu)001:1685: de ltar gdul bya la thugs myi gnas pa'i ye shes kyis 'gro don mdzad na /
NK069(tu)001:1686: thabs shes rab gnyis la rten dgos pas na /
NK069(tu)001:1687: yab kyi thabs rdo rje'i dkyil krung dang /
NK069(tu)001:1688: yum gyi zhabs pad+ma'i dkyil krung shes rab mas 'khyud nas /
NK069(tu)001:1689: yab kyi gsang ba'i ling ka dang /
NK069(tu)001:1690: yum gyi gsang ba'i b+ha ga gnyis rtse sprad pas /
NK069(tu)001:1691: tha mal pa'i rtog pa brtul nas /
NK069(tu)001:1692: bde' ba ye shes la zhugs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1694: a li ka li mnyam gnas pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:1695: zhabs gnyis pad+mara bsnol ba'i rgya //
NK069(tu)001:1696: btul shugs dkyil krung rigs kyi bdag /
NK069(tu)001:1697: kun nas thabs dang shes rab rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:1699: yum shes rab kyi zhabs dang /
NK069(tu)001:1700: yab thabs kyi zhabs gnyis yin par ni /
NK069(tu)001:1702: nyi zla thabs dang shes rab kyis //
NK069(tu)001:1703: ro gnyis mnyam par btul zhags bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:1705: yang gtso'i chos kyi mdzod snyoms pa /
NK069(tu)001:1706: kun bzang yum dang 'khril ba'i tshul lo //
NK069(tu)001:1708: ye shes rin po che'i phyag rgya 'bar ba can /
NK069(tu)001:1710: phyag stan pa ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:1713: phyag ni drug tu byung ste /
NK069(tu)001:1714: don ye shes drug dang ldan pas so //
NK069(tu)001:1721: mi gnas pa mda' ka thugs kyi ye shes drug go //
NK069(tu)001:1723: rgyu ye shes las grub pa /
NK069(tu)001:1724: rtags rin po che 'od 'bar ba'i rnam pa can /
NK069(tu)001:1732: phyag mtshan drug po yang ye shes drug dang ldan pa can no //
NK069(tu)001:1733: bshad pa'i rgyud sgyu 'phrul rol pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:1734: ye shes drug gi bdag nyid kyis //
NK069(tu)001:1735: phyag rgya rin chen 'bar ba'i mtshan //
NK069(tu)001:1736: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK069(tu)001:1740: le'u dang por yum kun tu bzang mo ma byung ba de /
NK069(tu)001:1742: yod kyang ma bkod zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:1743: myed na le'u gnyis par sta na pa de yang /
NK069(tu)001:1744: mo sham gyi bu'am ri bong rwa ltar mi bden rdzun par thal la /
NK069(tu)001:1745: yod na ma bkod pa'i 'thad pa ci yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:1747: yum gyi zhal phyag gsal bar ma bkod yang /
NK069(tu)001:1749: thabs dang shes rab kyi zhabs gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:1751: yum myed par mnyam pa'i brtul shugs mi yong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:1752: de yang zhal phyag ma stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:1753: yab byung na yum lus dang grib ma bzhin te /
NK069(tu)001:1754: thabs shes rab dbyer myed dam /
NK069(tu)001:1755: dbyings ye shes 'du 'bral myed pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:1759: dbu' bstan ces pa de la /
NK069(tu)001:1760: zhal stan pa ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:1764: de ltar gzhan la yang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:1766: rnam par thar pa gsum bsgom pa'i 'bras bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:1768: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:1769: sku gsung thugs mi bzad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1770: de yang sku'i gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1772: gsung gi gsang ba bsam gyi mi khyab pa 'dre /
NK069(tu)001:1778: de ltar gzhan la yang sbyar ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:1779: 'khor rigs lnga gzhan yang dbu' gsum phyag drug du ldan zhes 'phro 'tshol lo //
NK069(tu)001:1781: mthil ka dkar dang dmar ba'i mdangs //
NK069(tu)001:1782: rigs kyi rigs chen dbu' rgyan mdzes //
NK069(tu)001:1783: gcod pan sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag /
NK069(tu)001:1784: drug pa rigs rnams kun gyi gnas //
NK069(tu)001:1785: zhal gsum phyag drug mnyam pa'i stabs //
NK069(tu)001:1786: rin chen 'bar ba'i nye bar spras //
NK069(tu)001:1788: gnyis pa thabs lam du bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:1789: dang po sku mtshan nyid stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:1790: sku mdun dang rgyab myed pa ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:1791: lus kyi bcud la dwangs ma'i thig le dang /
NK069(tu)001:1792: snyigs ma dri chen la sogs pa myed de /
NK069(tu)001:1793: bcud lnga dwangs snyigs myed par ye shes kho nar gsal ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1795: mtshan dang dpe' byad ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:1796: spyi bo bde' ba chen po'i 'khor lo na rtsa
NK069(tu)001:1797: 'dab ma sum cu rtsa gnyis kyi yi ge ni
NK069(tu)001:1798: mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis so //
NK069(tu)001:1799: lte ba'i rtsa drug cu rtsa bzhi dang /
NK069(tu)001:1800: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi yig bcu drug ni dpe' brgyad cu'o //
NK069(tu)001:1802: bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad du /
NK069(tu)001:1804: rtsa sa ya bcu gsum gyi nang du /
NK069(tu)001:1805: bde' skye ba ni brda' sprod pas gsung /
NK069(tu)001:1806: bde' 'gags te thim pa ni thugs /
NK069(tu)001:1807: bde' ba gnas pa ni sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:1809: rten can thig le kun tu snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:1811: thabs dang shes rab ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:1812: ma las 'byung ba'i rak+ta nyi ma /
NK069(tu)001:1813: pha las 'byung ba'i byang sems zla ba /
NK069(tu)001:1814: de gnyis kyi ro mnyam par nyams su myong bas btul shugs so //
NK069(tu)001:1817: dwangs ma'i thig le lnga ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:1818: snyigs ma'i thig le dang drug go //
NK069(tu)001:1821: thig le snang stong dbyer myed du snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1823: bcud lnga ye shes kho na'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:1824: dwangs snyigs myed par kun tu gsal //
NK069(tu)001:1825: sgra dbyangs gsung gi gnas gzhi'i //
NK069(tu)001:1826: dbye' ba gsum gsum ngos gnyis dang //
NK069(tu)001:1827: bzhi bcu gnyis su 'gyur ba yin //
NK069(tu)001:1828: sa ya bcu gsum la sogs pa //
NK069(tu)001:1829: skye 'gag gnas pa'i ngo bo yang //
NK069(tu)001:1830: rten can ji bzhin rten de bzhin //
NK069(tu)001:1831: nyi zla thams dang shes rab kyis //
NK069(tu)001:1832: ro gnyis mnyam par dus gsum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:1833: dwangs ma'i thig le chen po ni //
NK069(tu)001:1834: bde bas dngos po'ang ye shes snang //
NK069(tu)001:1837: sku gsung thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1838: dbu' gsum dang ldan pa gnyis myi 'gal lam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:1840: sku gsung thugs kyi dgongs pa rgya che ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:1841: gdul byas dpag par dka' ste /
NK069(tu)001:1842: sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa sprul la /
NK069(tu)001:1844: bsam gyis myi khyab pa mtshon pa'i brdar stan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1847: nyid las mi zhan pa'i 'khor la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:1851: bcoma pa ni bdud bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:1852: nyon mongs pa lnga ma sang pa gnas su dag pas nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:1853: phung po lnga rigs lngar snang bas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:1854: yul sgyu mar snang bas lha'i bu'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:1855: chos thams cad ma skyes par rtogs pas 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1856: rgyas pa'i le'u bdun cu gnyis pa las /
NK069(tu)001:1857: nyon mongs pa nyid rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:1858: phung po lnga nyid mngon sangs rgyas //
NK069(tu)001:1860: skye shi myed par g.yung drung gnas //
NK069(tu)001:1861: bdud bzhi bcom pa'i skyes mchog gis //
NK069(tu)001:1862: dregs pa chen po thams cad bcom //
NK069(tu)001:1866: gang la na longs sku rigs lnga'o //
NK069(tu)001:1869: thugs ma rmongs pa'i mkhyen pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1870: yon tan rang byung du ldan /
NK069(tu)001:1871: 'phrin las ma 'gags par ldan pas na ldan no //
NK069(tu)001:1873: mtha' bzhi'i dri ma las 'adsa so //
NK069(tu)001:1876: ston pa dang sbyar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1877: 'jig rten chos lugs dang sbyar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:1879: ston pa kun tu bzang po sangs rgyas pa de bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:1882: dper na pha ma'i rgyu dang /
NK069(tu)001:1883: dri za nye 'khor gyi rkyen gyis /
NK069(tu)001:1884: sems can gyi lus ngag yid gsum du 'grub pa'i 'bras bu myong ba bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:1885: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gnas skabs na yang /
NK069(tu)001:1886: rgyu sems can gyi sems chos nyid byang chub sems su ni rtog /
NK069(tu)001:1887: rkyen shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin du ni ldan /
NK069(tu)001:1888: 'bras bu sku gsung thugs su grub nas /
NK069(tu)001:1889: 'gro ba'i don la gshegs pas na /
NK069(tu)001:1890: de bzhin gshegs pa zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:1891: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang /
NK069(tu)001:1894: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po ni brgyad de /
NK069(tu)001:1895: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa las dkar nag gi rnam smin gsog pa'i gzhi dang /
NK069(tu)001:1896: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid ngar sems dang bcas par 'dzin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1897: yid kyi rnam shes rnam par rig pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:1898: dbang po sgo lnga'i rnam shes 'dzin pa dang bcas pa dang brgyad do //
NK069(tu)001:1899: de dag rig cing grol bas na /
NK069(tu)001:1900: rgyal po ste rdo rje sems dapa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1901: de yang sgyu 'phrul gyi mdo' ye shes rngam pa klog gi 'khor lo'i le'u lnga pa nas //
NK069(tu)001:1902: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:1903: rnam smin ngar sems rnam rig pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:1904: shes brgyad rnam shes phung po kun //
NK069(tu)001:1905: rig pa'i dbyings las shar bas na //
NK069(tu)001:1906: zhe sdang chen po'i ye shes las //
NK069(tu)001:1907: rdo rje sems dpa'i rang bzhin yin //
NK069(tu)001:1909: rgyal ba rigs lnga 'di rnams la ngag don du drug ste /
NK069(tu)001:1910: ma dag pa'i phu nga po dang sbyar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:1916: ma dag pa'i phung po dang sbyar na lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:1917: rnam par shes pa'i phung po rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK069(tu)001:1918: gzugs kyi phung po rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK069(tu)001:1919: tshor ba'i phung po rin chen 'byung ldan dang /
NK069(tu)001:1920: 'du shes kyi phung po snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK069(tu)001:1921: 'du byed kyi phung po don yod grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1923: rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni /
