NK069(tu)001:1924: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas lnga ru grags //
NK069(tu)001:1927: shes rab kyi phung po rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK069(tu)001:1928: tshul khrims kyi phung po rnam snang /
NK069(tu)001:1929: ting nge 'dzin gyi phung po rin chen 'byung ldan /
NK069(tu)001:1930: rnam par grol ba'i phung po snang ba mtha' yas /
NK069(tu)001:1931: rnam par grol ba'i ye shes mthong ba'i phung po don yod grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1933: sems can kun gyi sems chen po //
NK069(tu)001:1934: rang bzhin dag pas dri ma myed //
NK069(tu)001:1935: phung po lnga don sangs rgyas lnga //
NK069(tu)001:1938: zhe sdang rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK069(tu)001:1939: gti' mug rnam par snang mdzad /
NK069(tu)001:1943: de yang brgya bcu pa'i le'u don gsum nas /
NK069(tu)001:1944: mi rig pa ni rig par gyur //
NK069(tu)001:1945: phyin ci log nyid yang dag ste //
NK069(tu)001:1946: nyon mongs lnga po de bzhin gshegs //
NK069(tu)001:1947: dngos myed rtogs na byang chub lam //
NK069(tu)001:1949: ye shes dang sbyar na lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:1950: me long lta bu'i ye shes rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK069(tu)001:1951: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes rnam snang /
NK069(tu)001:1952: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes rin 'byung /
NK069(tu)001:1953: so sor brtog pa'i ye shes snang mtha' /
NK069(tu)001:1954: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes don grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:1955: brgya bcu pa'i le'u bdun du brgyad pa las /
NK069(tu)001:1956: rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor bsdus bskus shing /
NK069(tu)001:1959: rlung dang sbyar ba ni lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:1960: nam mkha'i rlung rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK069(tu)001:1964: rlung gi rlung don grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:1965: de yang khro bo chen po stobs kyi dbang phyug rnal 'byor grub pa'i rgyud las /
NK069(tu)001:1966: snang stong nam mkha'i dbyings la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK069(tu)001:1967: gzugs 'dzin stan pa'i sa la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK069(tu)001:1968: rin chen 'bar ba'i me la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK069(tu)001:1969: mtha' yas chos kyi chu la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK069(tu)001:1970: don yod skyod pa'i rlung la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK069(tu)001:1971: 'byung lnga bde bar gshegs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK069(tu)001:1974: byang chub sems rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK069(tu)001:1975: dri chen rnam par snang mdzad /
NK069(tu)001:1977: rag ta snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK069(tu)001:1978: dri chu don yod grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:1980: byang sems dkar bas rdo rje sems //
NK069(tu)001:1981: dri chen gser mdog rnam snang mdzad //
NK069(tu)001:1982: mngas sa rin chen 'byung ldan te //
NK069(tu)001:1983: rag ta chags myed snang mtha' yas //
NK069(tu)001:1984: dri chu ljang khu don yod grub //
NK069(tu)001:1998: sa dang chu dang me dang rlung ste 'byung ba chen po bzhi'o //
NK069(tu)001:1999: 'bras bu'i gzugs la bcu gcig ste /
NK069(tu)001:2001: de rnams kyi yul lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:2002: rnam par rig byed ma yin pa'i gzugs dang bcu gcig go //
NK069(tu)001:2003: rgyal po ni rnam snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:2005: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2006: rgyu dang 'bras bu'i gzugs rnams kun //
NK069(tu)001:2007: chos kyi dbyings las byung bas na //
NK069(tu)001:2008: 'byed myed don gyi gti mug pas //
NK069(tu)001:2009: rnam par snang mdzad rang bzhin yin //
NK069(tu)001:2020: tshor ba bde' ba ra ro chang 'thungs pa lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:2021: tshor ba sdug bsngal ba mya ngan gyi rnam pa lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:2022: bde sdug gnyis ka ma yin pa dang gsum mo //
NK069(tu)001:2023: rgyal po ni rin chen 'byung ldan no //
NK069(tu)001:2025: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2026: bde sdug gnyis ka ma yin pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:2027: tshor ba'i phung po thams cad kun //
NK069(tu)001:2028: mnyam nyid dbyings su snang bas na //
NK069(tu)001:2029: nga rgyal chen po'i rang bzhin pas //
NK069(tu)001:2030: myong ba rin chen rang bzhin ces so //
NK069(tu)001:2031: 'dir sems can la gnas pa'i nye bar len pa'i phung po dang /
NK069(tu)001:2032: de bzhin gshegs pa la mnga' ba'i zag myed kyi phung po rgyu 'bras su sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:2033: rnam par shes pa'i phung po yang shes shing rig pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:2034: shes rab kyi phung po yang spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid dbyer myed pa yin pas sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:2035: gzugs kyi phung po yang de bzhin du rung la /
NK069(tu)001:2036: tshul khrims kyi phung po yang tshul khrims ma yin
NK069(tu)001:2037: pa 'chal ba'i tshul khrims kyi phung pos 'jigs pas
NK069(tu)001:2038: / tshul khrims dang gzugs su sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:2039: tshor ba yang nyams su myong bar byed pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:2040: ting nge 'dzin yang ting nge 'dzin gyi ro nyams su myong bar byed pa dang sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:2041: 'du shes kyang yul la mtshan mar 'dzin la /
NK069(tu)001:2042: rnam par grol ba'i phung po yang ye shes kyi che ba'i yon tan thams cad 'dzin par sbyar /
NK069(tu)001:2043: 'du byed yang dge' ba dang myi dge' ba'i las la 'du byed la /
NK069(tu)001:2044: rnam par grol ba'i ye shes mthong ba'i phung po
NK069(tu)001:2045: yang ye shes kyi dbyings rtogs sam mthong ba'i dus
NK069(tu)001:2046: na / mi rtog pa'i don la 'jug par byed pas na 'du byed dang sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:2047: de bas na sems can gyi sems nye bar len pa'i phung po zag bcas dang /
NK069(tu)001:2048: de bzhin gshegs pa'i zag myed kyi phung po lnga rgyu dang 'bras bu'i tshul du sbyar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:2050: de bzhin gshegs pa 'du shes kyi rgyal po dang /
NK069(tu)001:2052: de bzhin ni sngon gyi rgyal ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:2053: gshegs pa ni de dang lam mthun par gshegs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2055: 'du shes phra ba khab dmig du skud pa 'dzud lta bu rgya chung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:2056: rgya che ba rags pa yul mkhar rtsigs pa lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:2057: tshad myed pa cir yang snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:2058: rgyal po ni rnam snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:2060: srid gsum sems can thams cad la //
NK069(tu)001:2061: yul la 'du shes phra rags kyis //
NK069(tu)001:2062: byed pa'i phung po thams cad kun //
NK069(tu)001:2063: ma 'dres dbyings las snang bas na //
NK069(tu)001:2064: shes rab rlabs kyi 'dod chags pas //
NK069(tu)001:2065: snang ba mtha' yas rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2069: ston pa kun tu bzang po gshegs pa bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:2070: don yod grub pa yang sangs rgyas su gshegs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2075: sems dang ldan pa lnga bcu rtsa gcig /
NK069(tu)001:2076: sems dang mi ldan pa bcu bzhi'o //
NK069(tu)001:2080: 'du byed kyi phung po ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:2083: dang po la spyir drug ste /
NK069(tu)001:2085: lnga yul so sor nges pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2087: drug rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2088: nyi shu nye ba'i nyon mongs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2089: bzhi gzhan dbang du gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2091: reg pas yul dang dbang po rnam shes gsum gcod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2092: yid la byed pa dmyigs pa la sems 'jug pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2093: tshor bas dge myi dge' lung ma stan gyi 'bras bu myong ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:2094: 'du shes kyi bye brag 'byed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2095: sems dpa' skyon yon shes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2096: lnga yul so sor nges pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:2097: 'dun pas bsam pa'i dngos po la gtod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2098: mos pas nges par 'dzin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2099: dran pas mi brjed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2100: ting nge 'dzin gyis sems rtse gcig pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2101: shes rab kyis rnam par 'byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2114: drug rtsa ba'i nyon mongs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:2121: nyi shu nye ba'i nyon mongs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:2142: bzhi gzhan dbang du gyur pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:2147: sems dang mi ldan pa la bcu bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:2163: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2164: dge' dang myi dge gnyis ka myed //
NK069(tu)001:2165: sems las byung dang ma byung ba'i //
NK069(tu)001:2166: 'du byed phung po thams cad kun //
NK069(tu)001:2167: spro bsdu' dbyings las byung bas na //
NK069(tu)001:2168: rnam par grol ba'i 'phrag dog pas //
NK069(tu)001:2169: don yod grub pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2171: gnyis pa thabs lam dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:2173: gnas pa rtsa'i 'khor los nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:2174: rten pa thig les phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:2175: grub pa yi ges lha'i bu'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:2176: skyod pa rlung gis 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom mo //
NK069(tu)001:2177: rtsa rlung thig le yi ge bzhi la ldan pa'i bde ba chen por ldan /
NK069(tu)001:2178: bde ba rang gi ngo bo ma grub pas 'das so //
NK069(tu)001:2179: de bzhin gshegs pa ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:2180: thig le bde ba'i rang bzhin te /
NK069(tu)001:2181: yum gyis mkha' la lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes su gshegs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2182: rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:2183: rtsa lus kyi 'khor lo stong pa nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:2184: gzugs kyi rgyal po ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:2185: thig le gzugs su grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2187: sngags kyi yi ge'i sgra 'byin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2191: rlung gi dgag sgrub kyis kun skyod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2192: yang na rtsa drag pos te mi skyod pa /
NK069(tu)001:2193: thig le zhi ba ste rnam snang /
NK069(tu)001:2195: rlung sems dbang ste snang mtha' /
NK069(tu)001:2196: rlung lhun grub ste don grub kyi las so //
NK069(tu)001:2197: yang na rtsa bzhugs pa'i gnas /
NK069(tu)001:2202: mtshan nyid kun bcom bde chen po //
NK069(tu)001:2203: rang gi ngo bo ma grub pa //
NK069(tu)001:2204: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2205: bcom ldan de bzhin gshegs zhes bya //
NK069(tu)001:2206: gzugs sogs lhag pa'i thig le ni //
NK069(tu)001:2207: las dang yon tan don ldan phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2208: rigs kyi bdag po nyid du brjod //
NK069(tu)001:2210: 'dir rigs lnga la ngag don gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:2211: rang bzhin gyi snang ba'i dbang du byas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2212: gdul bya'i snang ba'i dbang du byas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2213: bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba'i dbang du byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2214: rang bzhin gyi snang ba'i dbang ni bzhi yin te /
NK069(tu)001:2215: rang bzhin gyi snang ba'i dbang du rnam par shes
NK069(tu)001:2216: pa'i phung po ye nas mi skyod pa'i rang bzhin
NK069(tu)001:2217: yin pa dang / gzugs kyi phung po ye nas rnam par snang mdzad kyi rang bzhin yin te /
NK069(tu)001:2219: gdul bya'i snang ba lam la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:2220: 'khrul pa'i snang ba ma dag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2221: gdul bya'i snang ba rnal 'byor pa nyams kyi snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:2222: de la ma dag pa 'khrul pa'i snang ba'i dbang du na /
NK069(tu)001:2223: de bzhin gshegs pa ni lha'o //
NK069(tu)001:2224: rnam par shes pa ni rtog pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2225: rgyal po ni lha dang rtog pa ngo sprad pa te /
NK069(tu)001:2226: mdor na rang bzhin rtog bcas brgya bcu rigs lngar ngo sprad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2227: rtogs ldan rnal 'byor pa nyams kyi snang ba'i dbang du na /
NK069(tu)001:2229: rtog tshogs ni 'khor du snang ste /
NK069(tu)001:2230: rgyal po ni zag pa myed pa'i longs spyod yongs su rdzogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2231: rang rang gi 'khor lo dbang sgyur ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:2232: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:2233: bde bar gshegs pa 'bras bu'i snang ba'i dbang du byas na /
NK069(tu)001:2234: sems can gyi rtogs pa ye nas bka' dag par
NK069(tu)001:2235: thugs su chud pa'i rigs lnga 'khor bcas su snang
NK069(tu)001:2236: ba'o // de yang thal ba'i le'u gnyis pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:2237: rang bzhin bde gshegs gdul bya yi //
NK069(tu)001:2238: snang ba gsum gyi ngo bo la //
NK069(tu)001:2240: tha snyad rtog pa'i chos rnams snang //
NK069(tu)001:2242: bya ba chen po'i gnas rdzogs shing //
NK069(tu)001:2244: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i khog gzhung thugs kyi thig pa na tshig gong ma gnyis pa de bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:2245: rigs lnga spyi'i sku mdog stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:2249: sku mdog ni rigs kyi dkyil 'khor dang bcas pa rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:2250: sku mdog la grol lam dang /
NK069(tu)001:2258: zhe sdang me long lta bu'i ye shes su mkhyen pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2261: dper na bal nag tshos kyis mi 'gyur ba bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2263: mi skyod pa'i sku mdog tu shar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:2267: gti mug chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes su mkhyen pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2269: chos nyid la nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa'i sku mdog go //
NK069(tu)001:2271: rnam pa snang mdzad kyi sku mdog go //
NK069(tu)001:2275: nga rgyal mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes su shes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2277: thugs che ba'i ye shes rgyas pa'i rtags su sku mdog ser po'o //
NK069(tu)001:2283: 'dod chags so sor rtog pa'i ye shes su mkhyen /
NK069(tu)001:2285: sems can la thugs rjes chags pa'i rtags su /
NK069(tu)001:2287: snang ba mtha' yas kyi sku mdog dmar por snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:2288: ljang khu'i mdog tu mtsher ba /
NK069(tu)001:2291: 'phrag dog bya ba grub pa'i ye shes su mkhyen pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2293: 'phrin las sna tshogs mdzad pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:2295: don grub sku mdog ljang khu'o //
NK069(tu)001:2297: chos dbyings me long mnyam pa nyid //
NK069(tu)001:2298: so so kun tog bya ba grub //
NK069(tu)001:2299: nyon mongs las kun rnam dag pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:2300: rigs kyi bde gshegs thams cad mkhyen //
NK069(tu)001:2302: nang thugs ye shes su mkhyen pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2304: byang chub sems nyid 'gyur ba med //
NK069(tu)001:2305: ma 'dres las kun rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:2306: yon tan tshogs rdzogs lhun grub cing //
NK069(tu)001:2307: chags pa chen pos kun spyod pa //
NK069(tu)001:2308: de dag 'phrin las sna tshogs kyis //
NK069(tu)001:2309: rang gi zhing khams chen por spyod //
NK069(tu)001:2311: sku mdog thabs lam du bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:2312: g.yas ro ma dmar po'i bcud dang khu ba khrag g.yon rkyang ma thig le ljang /
NK069(tu)001:2314: mkha' rtsa sngon po'i khu ga long rtsa khu ba ser po dang bcas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2315: rgyu de lnga las gnas rtsa nang na gnas /
NK069(tu)001:2316: kha dog dwangs ma'i thig le lnga 'od du 'bar ro //
NK069(tu)001:2317: ra dong las kyang rigs lnga'i mtshan 'dzin no //
NK069(tu)001:2319: bcud lnga khu ba thig le ni //
NK069(tu)001:2320: rgyu dang las kyi kha dog ldan //
NK069(tu)001:2321: ra dong las kyang de bzhin te //
NK069(tu)001:2322: rang gi mtshan nyid kun tu snang //
NK069(tu)001:2324: 'dir sku mdog stan pa la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:2325: rang bzhin gyi sku mdog ye shes lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:2326: mtshon pa'i sku mdog gdul bya la bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2327: dang po rang bzhin gyi sku mdog ni /
NK069(tu)001:2328: mi 'gyur ba nam mkha' lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:2329: skyon med pa dung lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:2330: dang ba zla ba lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:2331: snum la 'dril ba sku muta lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:2332: gsal la mtsher ba nyi ma lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:2333: mtshon pa'i sku mdog la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:2336: thugs ye shes chen po lnga dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2338: sems can gyi lus la ye shes yod pa de /
NK069(tu)001:2339: ma rtogs pas de rtogs par bya ba'i phyir ram /
NK069(tu)001:2340: mtshon par rigs lnga 'khor bcas kyi sku mdog stan pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:2341: brgya bcu pa'i le'u bdun cu gsum pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:2342: sems can ma lus thams cad la //
NK069(tu)001:2343: ye shes lnga yis kun khyab kyang //
NK069(tu)001:2344: rang gi nyam rtog sgrib byas pas //
NK069(tu)001:2345: ye shes lnga'i don ma mthong //
NK069(tu)001:2346: ma mthong rmongs pa thams cad la //
NK069(tu)001:2347: ye shes mtshan nyid stan pa'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2348: dkar dang ser dang dmar ba dang //
NK069(tu)001:2349: ljang khu la sogs gnag stan phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2350: 'di yis lhun grub rtogs par ces //
NK069(tu)001:2352: 'dir sku mdog la gtar kas gags gsal na /
NK069(tu)001:2353: rigs lnga yab yum gyi sku mdog yin nam /
NK069(tu)001:2355: rigs lnga yab yum gyi yin na /
NK069(tu)001:2356: lha gzhan la sku mdog myed dam /
NK069(tu)001:2357: gzhan gyi yin na 'dir lnga las myed byas pa la /
NK069(tu)001:2359: gdul bya'i dbang du smos pa yin te /
NK069(tu)001:2360: 'og min na gdul bya mdzad pa rdzogs pa yod pas /
NK069(tu)001:2361: sku mdog kyang ye shes lngar stan /
NK069(tu)001:2362: rtsa ba yang ye shes lngar 'dus so //
NK069(tu)001:2363: gdul bya mos pa spyod pa sku mdog tha dad
NK069(tu)001:2364: la mos na nyi shu rtsa lnga'i rigs su yang
NK069(tu)001:2366: ljang khu la sogs sna tshogs pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:2369: rigs lnga'i yum stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:2372: spyad par bya ba'i yul du gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2374: snod 'byung ba lnga chos kyi dbyings su gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2378: snang ba'i nam mkha' dbyings stong pa /
NK069(tu)001:2382: rdo rje sems dpa'i yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:2384: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kyi /
NK069(tu)001:2385: gsal stong mi bsgrib go'i byed pa /
NK069(tu)001:2386: snang stong nam mkha'i khams rnams kun //
NK069(tu)001:2387: stong zhi dbyings las shar bas na //
NK069(tu)001:2388: thams cad gnas pa'i rten yin pas //
NK069(tu)001:2389: rdo rje dbyings phyug rang bzhin //
NK069(tu)001:2397: rnam par snang mdzad kyi yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:2399: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2400: sra brten skye 'khrung rten rnams kun //
NK069(tu)001:2401: sa yi khams su grags pa rnams //
NK069(tu)001:2402: mi 'gyur dbyings las shar bas na //
NK069(tu)001:2403: thams cad skyed pa'i rten yin pas //
NK069(tu)001:2404: de bzhin dbyings phyug rang bzhin yin //
NK069(tu)001:2412: de rin chen 'byung ldan gyi yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:2414: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2416: gnyen bstud bsher ba'i mtshan nyid kun //
NK069(tu)001:2417: chu'i khams su rnam par grags //
NK069(tu)001:2418: kun bstud dbyings las shar bas na //
NK069(tu)001:2419: yon tan tshogs chen kun bstud pas //
NK069(tu)001:2420: rin chen dbyings phyug rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2427: snang ba mtha' yas kyi yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:2429: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2430: gsal gro'i ngo bo thams cad kun //
NK069(tu)001:2431: me'i khams su rnam par grags //
NK069(tu)001:2432: snang gsal dbyings las shar bas na //
NK069(tu)001:2433: gsal gro skyad pa'i rang bzhin pas //
NK069(tu)001:2434: pad+ma dbyings phyug rang bzhin yin //
NK069(tu)001:2436: bskyod pa'i dbyings la sogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:2439: rlung skyod pa'i las can ni /
NK069(tu)001:2441: don yod grub pa'i yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:2443: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2444: yang g.yo 'degs skyod thams cad kun //
NK069(tu)001:2445: rlung gi khams su grags pa ste //
NK069(tu)001:2446: skyod chen dbyings las shar bas na //
NK069(tu)001:2447: thogs myed shugs skyod rang bzhin pas //
NK069(tu)001:2448: las kyi dbyings phyug rang bzhin yin //
NK069(tu)001:2452: phyi nam mkha' la sogs pa 'byung ba lnga'i rtsal snang bas /
NK069(tu)001:2453: nang ye shes kyi 'byung ba lnga'i las kyis /
NK069(tu)001:2454: bde ba'i ye shes skyed pa'i phyir na btsun mo'o //
NK069(tu)001:2455: de yang nam mkha'i rlung srog 'dzin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2457: nang sa'i dwangs ma rtsa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2460: rlung gi dwangs ma dbugs lngas /
NK069(tu)001:2461: phung po lnga gnas par byed /
NK069(tu)001:2464: 'byung bar byed pas na yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:2466: khams bsogs nang gi 'byung las snang //
NK069(tu)001:2467: ye shes 'byung lnga'i las dag gis //
NK069(tu)001:2468: skyed phyir dbyings su brjod pa ste //
NK069(tu)001:2469: btsun mo'i dngos por des 'dod do //
NK069(tu)001:2471: btsun mo'i tshogs dang gnyis su myed par /
NK069(tu)001:2474: 'byung ba re re las mi 'dra ba du ma byed pas na tshogs so //
NK069(tu)001:2480: thabs shes rab gnyis myed do //
NK069(tu)001:2482: 'byung ba che gnas rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:2483: gsal snang rdo rje dbang phyug dbyings //
NK069(tu)001:2484: sra 'khregs bde gshegs phyag rgya ste //
NK069(tu)001:2485: bstud cing blan byed yon tan dbyings //
NK069(tu)001:2486: gsal gro smin pas pad+ma'i tshogs //
NK069(tu)001:2487: skyod pa'i 'phrin las las kun rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:2488: don mthun rtags kyi phyag rgya nyid //
NK069(tu)001:2489: thun mong dam pa'i cha lugs kyis //
NK069(tu)001:2490: de dag dkyil 'khor stan par mdzad //
NK069(tu)001:2493: chos kyi dbyings mtha' yas khyab pa ni 'di lta ste /
NK069(tu)001:2495: gnyis su myed par bzhugs tshul gyi tshad bstan pa ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:2500: chos kyi dbyings kyis khyab tshad du gnas kyi bdag pos kyang khyab pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2502: til gyi gang bu 'brus khengs nas gnas pa ltar ro //
NK069(tu)001:2504: thig le'i snod rtsa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:2505: rtsas lus thams cad la khyab ste /
NK069(tu)001:2506: de'i khyad par gyis thig les kyang lus thams cad la khyab pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2507: dper na til gang dang 'dra ba yum gyi b+ha ga la /
NK069(tu)001:2508: gang ba ni thig les so //
NK069(tu)001:2509: khyab pa ni bde bas so //
NK069(tu)001:2511: thig le snod kyi khyad par gyis /
NK069(tu)001:2512: til gang lta bur mkha' gang ba /
NK069(tu)001:2513: dkyil 'khor tshogs chen brjod mi lang ces so //
NK069(tu)001:2514: dper na til gyi gang bu bzhin du gang nas khyab par gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:2516: dper na til gyi gang bu bzhin du til 'brus khyab /
NK069(tu)001:2517: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad na /
NK069(tu)001:2518: chos can mtshan ma'i rnam par snang ba thams cad ni /
NK069(tu)001:2519: chos nyid skye ba myed pas khyab la /
NK069(tu)001:2520: chos nyid kyis gar khyab pa thams cad du rig pa'i ye shes kyis khyab /
NK069(tu)001:2521: dbyings dang ye shes kyis gar khyab par rigs lnga
NK069(tu)001:2522: yab yum gyis yang gang nas khyab par bzhugs so
NK069(tu)001:2524: chos kyi dbyings la tha dbus myed par bshad /
NK069(tu)001:2525: lha b+hu ta bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su bshad pa la /
NK069(tu)001:2526: chos kyi dbyings lhas khyab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2528: myi 'gal bar dgongs pa ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:2529: don dam par dbyings kyi nang ye shes kyi 'od kyis rgyas gdab /
NK069(tu)001:2530: sems can thams cad yang rang bzhin gyis sangs rgyas yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:2531: yang na sangs rgyas gang+ga rlung gi bye ma snyed bshad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2532: chos kyi dbyings gcig las myed pas so //
NK069(tu)001:2533: de nas byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:2536: rig pa khyad par can gyi 'khor rgyal sras sems dpa' la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:2537: dang po nang gi sems dpa' bstan /
NK069(tu)001:2543: rigs lnga bshad pa'i rjes su'o //
NK069(tu)001:2544: byang chub ni rtogs pa'i bdag nyid rang don no //
NK069(tu)001:2545: chen po ni gzhan las khyad 'phags pa ste gzhan don no //
NK069(tu)001:2546: rdo rje ni stong pa nyid /
NK069(tu)001:2547: mthong ba ni rtsa 'bar ba gzhung ring gi nang
NK069(tu)001:2548: na dmyig gi rnam shes zar ma'i me tog lta
NK069(tu)001:2549: bu'o // de ni byang chub sems dpa' pa'i snying po sku'i rigs su shes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:2551: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2552: kha dog dbyibs la gcod pa kun //
NK069(tu)001:2553: myig gi rnam shes zhes su grags //
NK069(tu)001:2554: mthong ba'i ye shes nyid yin phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2555: sa'i snying po'i rang bzhin yin //
NK069(tu)001:2557: byang chub chen po rdo rje thos pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2558: phyag na rdo rje las kyi rigs /
NK069(tu)001:2560: ces byang chub kyi don gong dang 'dra /
NK069(tu)001:2562: rna ba'i rtsa sgra 'byin gyi nang na /
NK069(tu)001:2563: sna'i rnam shes gro ba bcus pa 'dra ba de /
NK069(tu)001:2564: byang chub sems pa phyag na rdo rje las kyi rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:2566: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2567: sgra rnams kun la spyod pa kun //
NK069(tu)001:2568: rna ba'i rnam shes zhes su grags //
NK069(tu)001:2569: thos pa'i ye shes nyid yin phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2570: phyag na rdo rje'i rang bzhin yin //
NK069(tu)001:2572: byang chub chen po rdo rje bsnom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2574: nam mkha'i snying po yon tan gyi rigs /
NK069(tu)001:2576: sna'i rtsa kun tu rgyal mas dri tshor ro //
NK069(tu)001:2577: sna'i rnam shes zangs kyi mo khab lta bu'i thig le ni /
NK069(tu)001:2578: byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha'i snying po yon tan gyi rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:2580: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2581: dri rnams kun la gcod pa kun //
NK069(tu)001:2582: sna yi rnam shes zhes su grags //
NK069(tu)001:2583: tshor ba'i ye shes yin pa'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2584: nam mkha'i snying po'i rang bzhin no ces so //
NK069(tu)001:2585: byang chub chen po rdo rje myong ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:2586: spyan ras gzigs gsung gi rigs /
NK069(tu)001:2587: myong ba ni lce'i rnam shes kyis ro myong ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:2588: rtsa rngam byed ma'i nang na /
NK069(tu)001:2589: lce'i rnam shes dar le'u rgan lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:2590: de byang chub sems dpa' spyan ras gzigs gsung gi rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:2592: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2593: ro rnams kun la spyod pa kun //
NK069(tu)001:2594: lce'i rnam shes zhes su grags //
NK069(tu)001:2595: myong ba'i ye shes yin pa'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2596: spyan ras gzigs kyi rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2599: byang chub chen po rdo rje ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:2601: las kyi sgrib pa sbyong bas na byang /
NK069(tu)001:2602: ngo bo bde ba thob pas na chub /
NK069(tu)001:2603: bde bas rtog pa'i nyes pa 'joms pas rdo rje /
NK069(tu)001:2604: dmyig gi rnam shes thig le dkar pos mthong /
NK069(tu)001:2605: rna ba'i rnam shes thig le mthing kas thos /
NK069(tu)001:2606: sna'i rnam shes thig le ser pos tshor /
NK069(tu)001:2607: lce'i rnam shes thig le dmar pos myong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:2609: dmig bsogs rang gi thig le ni //
NK069(tu)001:2610: las dang ngo bo 'bras bu'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2611: sems dpa' chen po nyid du brjod //
NK069(tu)001:2612: nyes zad byed phyir rdo rje ste //
NK069(tu)001:2613: rang gi gnas kyis phye ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:2615: btsun mo mthong ba ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:2616: dmyig gi thig le las rlung sems 'dres nas /
NK069(tu)001:2617: nang gi thig le de nyid phyir yul la 'jug /
NK069(tu)001:2618: des gzugs sgra dri ro la sogs spyad nas /
NK069(tu)001:2619: rnal 'byor pa'i rtsa nang gi bcud thig le la bde ba skyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2621: gzugs bsogs nang nyid phyir snang ste //
NK069(tu)001:2622: rang gi rtsa bcud bcas pa las //
NK069(tu)001:2623: bde bskyed pas btsun mo'i ces so //
NK069(tu)001:2624: des na thabs lam dang sbyar nas bshad pa'i rgyud kyi rjes su 'dras pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2625: 'dir sems dpa' la ngag don du chos gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:2626: rnam shes dang dbang po'i de smon nyid gang yin /
NK069(tu)001:2627: yab yum gyi 'thad pa cis byed /
NK069(tu)001:2628: dbang po dang rnam shes cig gam tha dad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2629: rnam shes dang dbang po'i de kho na nyid ni lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:2630: ldang zhing rgyu ba'i rlung dmig la yod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2631: rnam par rgyu ba rna ba la /
NK069(tu)001:2632: yang dag rgyu ba sna la /
NK069(tu)001:2633: rab du rgyu ba lce la /
NK069(tu)001:2634: nges par rgyu ba lus la'o //
NK069(tu)001:2635: de rnams kyis thig le lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:2637: de yang khro bo stobs kyi rgyud las /
NK069(tu)001:2638: rgyu ba'i gnas ni spyan yin te //
NK069(tu)001:2639: rnam par rgyu ba rna ba la //
NK069(tu)001:2640: yang dag sgyu ba sna dang ni //
NK069(tu)001:2641: rab tu rgyu ba lce la gnas //
NK069(tu)001:2642: nges par rgyu ba lus la gnas //
NK069(tu)001:2644: de yang rnam shes thig le nang na gsal //
NK069(tu)001:2645: dbang po'i thig le phyir gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:2646: yab yum gyi 'thad pa cis byed pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:2647: rlung dang rnam shes 'dres nas yul la spyod pas na yab yum du 'brel lo //
NK069(tu)001:2648: dbang po dang rnam shes cig gam tha dad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:2649: ngo bo cig la las kyi dbye bas tha dad de /
NK069(tu)001:2650: ngo bo cig pas sems su 'dus /
NK069(tu)001:2651: las kyi dbye ba tha dad de /
NK069(tu)001:2652: rnam shes ni nang na thig le dang yid 'dres nas gzugs sgra dri ro shes la /
NK069(tu)001:2653: dbang po ni don mi go yang 'phral mthong bya ma lus kyi rnam shes la /
NK069(tu)001:2656: reg bya shes pa'i rnam shes /
NK069(tu)001:2657: reg pa dang bcas pa'i las bzhi las /
NK069(tu)001:2663: rnam par shes pa'i phur po rdo rje sems dpa' yin na /
NK069(tu)001:2664: 'dir rnam shes sems par sbyar ba dang 'gal te /
NK069(tu)001:2665: rnam shes gcig la bzang ngan can yin te /
NK069(tu)001:2666: 'khor dang gtso bor song bas so //
NK069(tu)001:2668: mi gcig na ji ltar mi gcig zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:2670: tshogs brgyad spyi'i mtshan nyid rnam par shes pa'i phung po /
NK069(tu)001:2671: tshogs brgyad las mig gi rnam par shes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2672: 'di rnams rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin pa sems dpa' 'o //
NK069(tu)001:2674: btsun mo mthong bar bya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:2676: nang gi sems ma bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:2677: rnam shes lnga'i spyad byar gyur pas na btsun mo'o //
NK069(tu)001:2678: mthong bar bya ba ni gzugs mdzes sdug gnyis ka ma yin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2679: de ni lha mo sku la se ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:2681: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kun //
NK069(tu)001:2682: kha dog dbyibs dang mtshan ma rnams //
NK069(tu)001:2683: gzugs kyi skye mched nyid du grags //
NK069(tu)001:2684: mthong bar bya ba'i yul yin pas //
NK069(tu)001:2685: gzugs mdzes ma yi rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2691: sgra snyan mi snyan gnyis ka ma yin pa rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:2692: de ni lha mo las rigs nir ti ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:2694: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kun //
NK069(tu)001:2695: zin dang ma zin gnyis ka las //
NK069(tu)001:2697: thos par bya ba'i yul yin pas //
NK069(tu)001:2698: nir ti ma'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2704: snas dri zhim myi zhim gnyis ka ma yin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2705: de ni lha mo yon ma le'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2707: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2708: lhan cig skyes dang sbyar dang gyur //
NK069(tu)001:2709: zhim dang dri nga de las bzhan //
NK069(tu)001:2710: dri'i khams dang skye mched de //
NK069(tu)001:2711: snam par bya ba'i yul yin pas //
NK069(tu)001:2712: ma le ma'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2715: myong bar bya ba'i tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:2718: lces ro bro mi bro gnyis ka ma yin pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:2719: gsung rigs g+hir ti ma'i rang bzhin ni /
NK069(tu)001:2721: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2722: kha mngar la sogs ri rnams kun //
NK069(tu)001:2723: ro yi skye mched nyid du grags //
NK069(tu)001:2724: myong bar bya ba'i yul yin pas //
NK069(tu)001:2725: g+hir ti ma'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2727: tshogs ni yul ro drug la sogs par snang bas na tshogs so //
NK069(tu)001:2728: gnyis pa dbang po'i sems dpa' yab yum stan /
NK069(tu)001:2729: byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong byed dang /
NK069(tu)001:2731: gnyis pa phyi'i byang chub sems dpa' bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:2732: byang chub ni sgrib pa byang nas ye shes chub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2733: chen po ni rang bzhin gyi don spyod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2734: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2735: mthong byed ni dmyig gi dbang po'o //
NK069(tu)001:2737: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2738: mthong byed dang ba'i dag nyid de //
NK069(tu)001:2739: myig gi khams zhes bya bar grags //
NK069(tu)001:2740: mthong ba'i bya ba byed pa'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2741: byams pa mi tri'i rang bzhin yin //
NK069(tu)001:2744: byang chub chen po rdo rje thos byed dang /
NK069(tu)001:2746: rna ba'i dbang pos sgra thos par byed pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:2747: las rigs byang chub sems dpa' sgrib pa rnam par sel ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:2749: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2750: thos byed dang ba'i bdag nyid de //
NK069(tu)001:2751: rna ba'i khams zhes bya bar grags //
NK069(tu)001:2752: thos pa'i bya ba byed pa'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2753: sgrib pa kun sel rang bzhin yin //
NK069(tu)001:2756: byang chub chen po rdo rje snom byed dang /
NK069(tu)001:2758: snom byed sna'i dbang po ni /
NK069(tu)001:2759: yon tan gyi rigs 'jam dpal gzhon nu ste /
NK069(tu)001:2761: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2762: snom byed dang ba'i bdag nyid de //
NK069(tu)001:2763: sna'i khams zhes bya bar grags //
NK069(tu)001:2764: tshor ba'i bya ba byed pa'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2765: 'jam pa'i dpal gyi rang bzhin yin //
NK069(tu)001:2767: gsung gi rigs kun tu bzang po /
NK069(tu)001:2768: byang chub chen po rdo rje myong byed dang /
NK069(tu)001:2770: myong byed lce'i dbang pos ro myong ba ni kun tu bzang pos ste /
NK069(tu)001:2772: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyis //
NK069(tu)001:2773: myong bar byed pa'i bdag nyid de //
NK069(tu)001:2774: lce'i khams zhes bya bar grags //
NK069(tu)001:2775: myong ba'i bya ba byed pas na //
NK069(tu)001:2776: kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin yin //
NK069(tu)001:2778: 'dir gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:2779: le'u 'dir rtog tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su 'dod dam mi 'dod /
NK069(tu)001:2780: mi 'dod na lha rtogs tshogs dang sbyar ba dang 'gal /
NK069(tu)001:2781: 'dod na kun tu bzang po ye shes kyi skur smos te /
NK069(tu)001:2782: sku mdun dang rgyab myed pa zhes bshad /
NK069(tu)001:2783: sgo ma bzhi mtha' bzhi yangs par bshad de /
NK069(tu)001:2784: rtag par ma yin pa dang ces pas /
NK069(tu)001:2785: mtha' bzhi dang bral ba ni ye shes chos kyi sku yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:2786: de la lha la la ye shes kyi skur smos /
NK069(tu)001:2787: la la rtog tshogs su smos pas 'gal lo zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:2789: gdul bya'i snang ba la dgongs pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:2790: 'og min na 'khor theg pa mas sbyangs la shes bya'i sgrib pa yod pas /
NK069(tu)001:2791: de sbyong ba'i ched du ston pa kun tu bzang po shes bya dag pa'i skur ldan /
NK069(tu)001:2792: de la rigs lnga la sogs pa nyid las mi zhan pa'i 'khor yin yang /
NK069(tu)001:2793: gtso 'khor khyad par du bya ba'i phyir rtog tshogs su smos /
NK069(tu)001:2794: 'og min du theg pa mas sbyangs pa'i 'khor rang
NK069(tu)001:2795: la yang gdul bya dang bstun nas snod du rung
NK069(tu)001:2797: sgo ba rnams khro bor rmos so //
NK069(tu)001:2798: snod du mi rung ba'i nyes pa mtha' bzhi yin pa'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:2799: de dag par bya ba'i phyir sgo ma rnams mtha' yangs par rmos so //
NK069(tu)001:2800: yang na ston pa ni kun tu bzang po sku lnga lhun grub yin la /
NK069(tu)001:2801: 'khor ni ston pa'i khyad par las snang bas gdul bya dang stun nas sprul pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2806: dus bzhi spyad pa'i yul du gyur pas na btsun mo /
NK069(tu)001:2807: 'das pa ni rgyu 'bras spyad zin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2808: de yang spyid kyi dus ni 'das pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2809: de ni lha mo gdug spos ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:2811: snod bcud sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2812: rgyu 'bras kun tu rnam par spyad //
NK069(tu)001:2813: sngon 'das dus su rnam par grags //
NK069(tu)001:2814: sngon 'das spyid kyi rang bzhin ni //
NK069(tu)001:2815: spos me ma'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2820: rgyu 'bras 'tshogs pa ni da ltar te /
NK069(tu)001:2822: de ni lha mo me tog ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:2824: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2825: rgyu spyad 'bras bu ma spyad kun //
NK069(tu)001:2826: da lta nyid kyi dus su grags //
NK069(tu)001:2827: da lta dbyar gyi rang bzhin te //
NK069(tu)001:2828: me tog ma'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2834: rgyu 'bras 'byung bar ma nges pa ni gu na g+han d+he ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:2836: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2838: ma 'ongs rgun gyi rang bzhin yin //
NK069(tu)001:2839: g+han d+he ma'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2840: ces pas 'jam dpal gyi yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:2844: rgyu 'bras yongs kyis ma spyad pa 'am /
NK069(tu)001:2845: yul du ma gyur ba ni ma byon pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:2848: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2849: rgyu 'bras yongs kyis ma spyad pa //
NK069(tu)001:2850: ma 'ongs dus su rab tu grags //
NK069(tu)001:2851: ma byon me tog rang bzhin ni //
NK069(tu)001:2852: a lo ka'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2853: ces pas sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'i yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:2854: nang thabs lam dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:2855: byang chub chen po rdo rje mthong byed /
NK069(tu)001:2857: rnal 'byor pas stod kyi rlung mnan /
NK069(tu)001:2860: nyams de shar ba'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:2864: lces chos nyid kyi ro myong ba ni sems dapa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2865: deng sa mthong ba'i ye shes zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:2866: thos pa'i ye shes zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:2869: rlung phyir la thon pa ni 'das pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2870: khong na gnas pa ni da lta ba /
NK069(tu)001:2872: de dag las srog dang rtsal bar gyur pa ni ma byon pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2873: de yang dbang po bzhi rlung bzhis grub par byed pas na btsun mo yin no //
NK069(tu)001:2875: dus ni rlung gis sgo phye ste //
NK069(tu)001:2876: byams pa la sogs ye shes bzhi //
NK069(tu)001:2877: de bde rim pa skye ba yang //
NK069(tu)001:2878: ting 'dzin dbang du nges par gsungs //
NK069(tu)001:2880: 'dir gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:2881: btsun mo ni spyad par bya ba'i yul du gyur pa yin na /
NK069(tu)001:2882: 'byung bar ma nges pa cir 'gyur cha myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2883: ma byon pa yul du ma gyur ba gnyis spyad pa'i yul du ci ste 'gro zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:2884: de ni sems can gyi rtog pa 'gag pa'i che yin te /
NK069(tu)001:2885: dus gsum spyi'i mtshan nyid 'das ma byung da ltar gsum yin yang /
NK069(tu)001:2886: de gang rung gcig rang la yang dus gsum tshang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:2887: dbyar dgun ston dpyid bzhi la dus bzhi rang gi mtshan nyid cha bshad pas na /
NK069(tu)001:2888: da ltar gyi sems can dbyar dgun ston dpyid kyi dus bzhir 'dzin pa yod de /
NK069(tu)001:2889: de dbang po'i spyod yul du gyur bas na yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:2890: rtogs pa dang ldan pa'i gang zag la dus bzhi la dbyer myed do //
NK069(tu)001:2891: de yang sgyu 'phrul rgya bcu pa'i le'u nyi shu bdun pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:2894: snga phyi myed par mnyam yin te //
NK069(tu)001:2895: nges pa myed par yang dag gsung //
NK069(tu)001:2898: 'joms pa chen po reg pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:2900: gdug pa 'dul ba'i 'khor la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:2901: grol lam dang du bshad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2905: sku gsung thugs kyi 'phrin las kyis //
NK069(tu)001:2907: chen po ni 'jig rten pa'i khro bo las khyad par du byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2908: reg pa ni lus kyi rnam par shes pa 'jam rtsub shes pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:2911: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2912: reg bya kun la gcod pa kun //
NK069(tu)001:2913: lus kyi rnam shes zhes su grags //
NK069(tu)001:2914: reg pa'i ye shes yin pa'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2915: rnam par rgyal ba'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2918: 'joms pa chen po reg byed dang /
NK069(tu)001:2920: reg byed kyi dbang po ni gshin rje gshed de /
NK069(tu)001:2922: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2923: reg byed dang ba'i bdag nyid de //
NK069(tu)001:2924: lus kyi khams zhes bya bar grags //
NK069(tu)001:2925: reg byed reg par byed pas na //
NK069(tu)001:2926: gshin rje 'joms pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2928: 'joms pa chen po reg bya dang /
NK069(tu)001:2931: reg bya ni yul te rta mgrin dang sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:2933: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2935: reg par bya'i yul yin pas //
NK069(tu)001:2936: rta mchog dbang gi rang bzhin yin //
NK069(tu)001:2938: 'joms pa chen po reg shes dang /
NK069(tu)001:2941: reg byed ni lus kyi yul dang /
NK069(tu)001:2943: rnam par shes pa gsum 'dus pa'i sems las byung ba reg shes te /
NK069(tu)001:2946: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2947: tshogs drug 'gags pa'i de ma thag /
NK069(tu)001:2948: go 'byed gsal ba'i rang bzhin nyid //
NK069(tu)001:2949: yid kyi khams zhes bya bar grags //
NK069(tu)001:2950: nges gcod bya ba byed pa'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2951: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa'i rang bzhin yin //
NK069(tu)001:2953: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:2956: myed na 'joms pa chen po dang 'gal /
NK069(tu)001:2957: yod na 'og min na khro bos 'dul ba'i gdul bya yod dam myed /
NK069(tu)001:2958: yod na gdul bya gang yin /
NK069(tu)001:2959: myed na gdul bya myed pa'i 'dul byed mi dgos /
NK069(tu)001:2961: de ni 'di ltar du bzhed de /
NK069(tu)001:2962: 'og min na gdul bya rang rgyud pa ru tra lta bu myed /
NK069(tu)001:2963: khro bos 'dul dgos pa'i gdul bya yod de /
NK069(tu)001:2964: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor mas sbyangs yod pa rnams /
NK069(tu)001:2966: rang gi lta ba la da rung mngon par zhen
NK069(tu)001:2967: pa yod pas ma ti'i snod du ma gyur ba
NK069(tu)001:2968: dang / shes bya'i sgrib pa la srab 'thug yod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2969: de dag 'dul ba'i phyir sgo bsrungs khro bor smos so //
NK069(tu)001:2971: nub phyogs 'og min gnas mchog na //
NK069(tu)001:2972: ma chags pad ma'i gdan steng pa //
NK069(tu)001:2973: dus gsum sangs rgyas bzhugs pa'i gnas //
NK069(tu)001:2974: rnam par thar pa'i sgo bzhi la //
NK069(tu)001:2975: ye shes bzhi'i rgya dang ldan //
NK069(tu)001:2976: dbang dang skal myed gsal ba'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2977: nang stan phyi rim lcags dang ldan //
NK069(tu)001:2979: btsun mo rtag par ma yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2983: rtag pa ni skad cig ma gnyis par mi 'gyur bar 'dzin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:2984: rtag par lta ba de gnas 'gyur ba de yum stobs chen mas te /
NK069(tu)001:2986: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:2987: 'jigs dang skad cig mi rtag pa //
NK069(tu)001:2988: rtag par ma yin zhes su grags //
NK069(tu)001:2989: sgyu ma lta bu yin pa'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:2990: lcags kyu ma'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:2992: chad par ma yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:2996: las dang dkon mchog bden par 'dod pa rnams myed par 'dzin pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:2997: de gnas 'gyur te chad par ma yin pa ni yum gshad ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:2999: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:3000: kun tog gzhan dbang myed min pa //
NK069(tu)001:3001: chad par ma yin zhes su grags //
NK069(tu)001:3002: rmi lam lta bur sems snang phyir //
NK069(tu)001:3003: zhags pa ma'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:3005: bdag du ma yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:3008: bdag ni gang zag dang chos kyi bdag yod par lta te /
NK069(tu)001:3009: de ma yin pa ni lha mo mgrin pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:3011: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:3012: gzung 'dzin dngos por ma grub pa //
NK069(tu)001:3013: mtshan mar ma yin zhes su grags //
NK069(tu)001:3014: smyig rgyu lta bur sems snang phyir //
NK069(tu)001:3015: lcags sgrog ma'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:3017: mtshan mar ma yin pa'i tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:3020: mtshan ma ni gzung 'dzin du lta ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:3021: de ma yin pa ni bdud rtsi 'khyil ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:3023: snod bcud 'gro ba thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:3024: skyes bu'i byed pa ma grub pa //
NK069(tu)001:3025: bdag du ma yin zhes su grags //
NK069(tu)001:3026: sgra snyan lta bur sems snang phyir //
NK069(tu)001:3027: rdo rje 'bebs ma'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:3030: log par lta ba thams cad dag par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:3033: gsang ba'i yul yum gyi b+ha ga dang /
NK069(tu)001:3034: gsang ba'i dbang po rdo rje dang /
NK069(tu)001:3035: gsang ba'i rnam shes bde ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:3036: de gsum gyis lus kyi rnam shes so //
NK069(tu)001:3037: de bzhis rtog pa 'joms pas khro bo'o //
NK069(tu)001:3038: bzhi ni mtshan nyid dang las kyis phye ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:3043: mtshan ma bzhir mi gnas pa 'am /
NK069(tu)001:3044: mtshan ma ngan pa mi skye ba ni yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:3046: gsang yum dbang po rnam shes reg /
NK069(tu)001:3047: lus kyi chos bzhi 'dus spyad pas //
NK069(tu)001:3048: ma lus 'joms phyir khro bo ste //
NK069(tu)001:3049: mtshan nyid las kyis phye ba yin //
NK069(tu)001:3050: gsang gsum thabs kyi spyod pa nyid //
NK069(tu)001:3051: rtag bsogs mtshan ma las skyed phyir //
NK069(tu)001:3052: btsun mo zhes su stan pa ste //
NK069(tu)001:3053: las kyi skabs kyis mi gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3055: 'dir gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:3057: rigs lnga sangs rgyas thams cad kyi rtsa ba rtog tshogs su bshad nas /
NK069(tu)001:3058: sgo ma bzhi mtha' bzhi dang bral bar bshad pas nor zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:3060: sems can gyi rtog tshogs la dgongs pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:3061: rnam par shes pa la sogs pa'i phung po lnga ni gtso bo yin la /
NK069(tu)001:3062: gtso bo'i 'phrin las byed par sgo ma bzhi sprul pa yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:3063: gtso bo'i che ba 'byin pas mi 'gal lo //
NK069(tu)001:3065: rtog tshogs su smos pa'i 'khor 'di rnams /
NK069(tu)001:3066: thugs ye shes rig pa rang snang ba'i 'khor yin nam /
NK069(tu)001:3072: gcig gi rgyud la rigs lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:3073: sems dpa' la sogs pa tha dad pa 'ong bar mi rigs /
NK069(tu)001:3074: rgyud tha dad pa sbyangs zer na yang /
NK069(tu)001:3075: 'dir gang zag gcig gi shes rgyud la yod pa rnams las ma smos pas /
NK069(tu)001:3076: 'gro la shes rgyud gnyis 'chang yod dam zhes bya //
NK069(tu)001:3077: yang rang snang ba yin na yang /
NK069(tu)001:3078: mas sbyangs pa yod dam myed /
NK069(tu)001:3080: myed na yang gdul bya myed pa'i 'dul byed mi srid do //
NK069(tu)001:3081: 'o na ji ltar shes par bya na /
NK069(tu)001:3082: 'di rnams thugs ye shes rig pa rang snang ba yin /
NK069(tu)001:3083: shes rgyud mas sbyangs yang yod de /
NK069(tu)001:3084: kri yog la sogs pa'i sems dpa' ma ha'i chos nyan pa yod do //
NK069(tu)001:3086: de bzhin thugs kyi khyad par las //
NK069(tu)001:3087: rang snang rgyal ba'i sems bsogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:3088: dang po sangs rgyas sar rgyal ba //
NK069(tu)001:3089: sems dpa' che dang 'joms pa che //
NK069(tu)001:3090: brjod kyis mi lang tshad myed dag /
NK069(tu)001:3091: rnam gnyis tshul du 'dug pa yin //
NK069(tu)001:3094: de lta bu'i tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:3095: gnyis su med par bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:3097: spyi'i bzhugs tshul bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:3098: de lta bu'i tshogs brjod kyis mi lang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:3099: gnyis su myed par bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:3100: de lta bu'i tshogs ni dad pas 'dus pa gtam
NK069(tu)001:3101: nyan pa'i rgyu'i sems dpa' la sogs pa rnams so
NK069(tu)001:3102: // brjod kyis mi lang ba ni grangs so //
NK069(tu)001:3103: gnyis su myed par bzhugs pa ni dgu ste /
NK069(tu)001:3104: rang bzhin gyi snang ba'i dbang du bdag nyid chen por sku dang ye shes sel myed par bzhugs /
NK069(tu)001:3105: thun mong ma yin dbang du ston 'khor thams cad rtog tshogs dang gnyis su myed par bzhugs /
NK069(tu)001:3106: 'og myin du 'tshogs tshad gnas la gnyis su myed par bzhugs /
NK069(tu)001:3107: rigs lnga ston pa dang dgongs pa gnyis su myed par bzhugs /
NK069(tu)001:3108: sems dpa' dang khro bo ston pa dang gnas la gnyis su myed par bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:3109: thams cad kyang sku spyod lam gyis bzhugs /
NK069(tu)001:3110: gsung mdzad pa sgro zhing bzhugs /
NK069(tu)001:3111: thugs ting nge 'dzin rdzu 'phrul gyis bzhugs /
NK069(tu)001:3112: don dbyings ye shes gnyis myed du bzhugs /
NK069(tu)001:3113: rtags thabs dang shes rab gnyis myed du bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:3115: phyi nang dkyil 'khor stan mdzad cing //
NK069(tu)001:3116: rigs kyi 'khor lo kun rdzogs bdag /
NK069(tu)001:3117: stong khams kun tu mtha' yas par //
NK069(tu)001:3118: de dag dkyil 'khor gsal bar snang //
NK069(tu)001:3119: gnyis myed mnyam pa chen po'i sku //
NK069(tu)001:3120: drangs myed brjod kyis mi lang ba //
NK069(tu)001:3121: gnyis su myed par brtan bzhugs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3123: gnyis su myed par bzhugs pa la gtar ka gags gsal na gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:3124: dgongs pa la gnyis su myed par bzhugs sam /
NK069(tu)001:3125: gnas la gnyis su myed par bzhugs sam /
NK069(tu)001:3126: bzhugs tshul gnyis su myed par bzhugs zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:3127: dgongs pa la gnyis su myed par bzhugs pa na /
NK069(tu)001:3128: ston 'khor dgongs pa la khyad myed par thal /
NK069(tu)001:3129: gnas la gnyis su myed par bzhugs na /
NK069(tu)001:3133: sems dpa' rtsibs 'chan la sogs pa na bzhugs te 'gal lo //
NK069(tu)001:3134: bzhugs tshul gnyis su myed zer na /
NK069(tu)001:3138: bsgo ba dor thabs zer bas 'gal lo //
NK069(tu)001:3140: lha rnams yab yum thabs dang shes rab gnyis su myed par bzhugs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3141: de bas na sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zer ro //
NK069(tu)001:3142: de yang sgyu 'phrul bla ma nas /
NK069(tu)001:3143: shes rab thabs rol sgyu ma las //
NK069(tu)001:3144: rang bzhin sgyu 'phrul chen por shar //
NK069(tu)001:3145: thabs dang thabs byung 'brel pa nyid //
NK069(tu)001:3146: thams cad kun gyi gzhir gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3148: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa //
NK069(tu)001:3150: 'dir gleng gzhi sdus pa la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:3152: sngon 'byung du phun sum tshogs pa dang dgongs pa brdas go nas sdus pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:3153: rjes 'jug la dgongs pa la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:3154: gong du rgyas par shes pa de 'dir sdus par go bar bya ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:3155: gong du ma shes pa de 'dir shes par byed pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:3156: gdul bya gleng gzhi rgyas pa la mos pa la gong du bshad pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:3157: sdus pa la mos pa 'dir sdus te stan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3158: spyi don gnyis pa sdus don ni /
NK069(tu)001:3159: stan pa brdas go nas ston 'khor dbyer myed kyis sdus so //
NK069(tu)001:3162: gleng gzhi rgyas par bshad pa'i rjes de nas /
NK069(tu)001:3165: rigs lnga sems dpa' khro bo ste yab rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:3168: rigs lnga sems ma khro mo rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:3169: gnyis su myed pa'i gsang ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:3171: lha yab thabs rgya che ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:3172: yum shes rab zab pa gnyis myed do //
NK069(tu)001:3175: ye nas sems can gyi rtogs tshogs rnams sku dang
NK069(tu)001:3176: ye shes su sangs rgyas de rtogs par dka' bas
NK069(tu)001:3180: sangs rgyas pa de mtshon par byed pa'i rgyud 'di nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:3188: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku lnga dbyer myed do //
NK069(tu)001:3189: gdul bya'i snang bar 'chad pa'i skyes bu sku rnams snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:3195: sgrags stong dbyer myed kyi gsung /
NK069(tu)001:3197: sna tshogs tshig gi gsung lnga dbyer myed do //
NK069(tu)001:3205: bya ba grub pa lnga dbyer myed /
NK069(tu)001:3206: 'khor ni thugs mi skyod pa 'chad pa'i skyes bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:3215: yon tan lnga lhun grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:3217: yon tan rin chen 'byung ldan no //
NK069(tu)001:3224: 'chad pa'i skyes bu las kyi rigs don grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:3227: ston pa sku lnga lhun grub dang /
NK069(tu)001:3228: 'khor 'chad pa'i skyes bu rigs lnga dbyer med du dgongs pas brda' 'byal ba las phyung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:3235: che ba 'am ngom pa ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:3239: rang rig pa nyid ston pa kun tu bzang po
NK069(tu)001:3240: zhal phyag gi rnam par snang ba ngo mtshar che
NK069(tu)001:3241: ba dang / rang rig pa nyid ye shes kyi gzhal yas khang du snang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:3242: rang rig pa'i ye shes nyid 'khor du snang ba la ngom pa dang gsum mo //
NK069(tu)001:3244: gong du gsungs pa'i phung po khams dang skye mched kyis sdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:3245: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas te gnas pa de ni /
NK069(tu)001:3248: ye nas de ltar sangs rgyas par rtogs pa la ngo mtshar skyes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3249: 'dir gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:3250: phun sum tshogs pa lnga yod pa la /
NK069(tu)001:3251: ngom pa gsum las myed pa'i gtan tshigs gang zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:3252: de ni ston pa dang gnas 'khor gsum la ngom pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:3253: de gsum la ngom pa'i 'thad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:3254: ston pa dang gnas 'khor gsum tshang na /
NK069(tu)001:3255: dus dang ston pa gnyis shugs la yong ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:3256: ston pa ma gsungs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:3257: dus da rung ma rdzogs pas na'o //
NK069(tu)001:3259: phung po sangs rgyas su ye nas gnas pa la rtogs pas ngom mo //
NK069(tu)001:3265: dang po de bzhin nyid kyi snang ba /
NK069(tu)001:3266: le'u sdud dang po la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:3270: snang ba rnam pa gsum du bsdus te /
NK069(tu)001:3271: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid du gnas kyi rang bzhin dang /
NK069(tu)001:3273: de bzhin nyid la phyi nang myed pas na /
NK069(tu)001:3274: phyi dang nang myed par kun tu yang nang du gyur pa bsdu /
NK069(tu)001:3276: chos kyi dbyings mtha' dbus myed pa de /
NK069(tu)001:3277: 'og myin gyi gnas mtha' dang dbus myed pa bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:3278: de ltar de bzhin nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su ye nas gnas pas na /
NK069(tu)001:3279: de ni rang bzhin gyi snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:3282: gnyis pa gdul bya'o snang ba la gnyis las /
NK069(tu)001:3285: dbyings de la yid rang 'byung gi ye shes rtogs pas dbang sgyur bas na /
NK069(tu)001:3286: ston pa'i ngo bo bsdus te /
NK069(tu)001:3287: sku mdun dang rgyab myed pa la sogs pa bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:3288: de yang de ltar rtogs pa'i ye shes nyid ston pa'i ngo bor snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:3290: rtogs pa'i ye shes nyid rig pa'i ngang du gsal
NK069(tu)001:3291: ba'i bye brag las 'khor 'das su snang ba tha
NK069(tu)001:3292: myi dad de / der ston pa'i rang bzhin bsdu /
NK069(tu)001:3293: de bzhin gshegs pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK069(tu)001:3294: rgyas longs spyod chen po phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i ces
NK069(tu)001:3298: de bas na ston pa'i ngo bo dang /
NK069(tu)001:3301: rgya chad phyogs lhung myed pa'i thugs rje chen po'i ngang zhes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3302: de ltar rtogs pa'i rig pa la 'khor 'das tha mi dad pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:3304: rang snang ba nyid ces pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:3305: gnas kyi ngo bo bsdud de /
NK069(tu)001:3306: rig pa la ye shes lngar snang bas na /
NK069(tu)001:3309: ye shes rin po che bsdu /
NK069(tu)001:3310: rig pa spros pa dang bral ba la rgya phyogs bcu bsdu /
NK069(tu)001:3311: rtogs pa'i ye shes rgyu dang 'bras bu kun tu rdzogs pas gru bzhi dang /
NK069(tu)001:3313: rgyan thams cad rang snang bar rung /
NK069(tu)001:3314: de yan chad kyis lta ba rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3318: rnam par thar pa bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug pa bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:3319: mtshan ma myed pa la sogs pa'i sgo bzhi nas zhugs nas bsgoms pas na de ni sgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3323: theg pa'i rgyan gyi sgo nas chos sku mtshon dgos pas /
NK069(tu)001:3325: them skas rta babs kyi gzugs brnyan bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3326: rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi rta babs dang ldan pa ces bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:3329: sems can gyi gdan bsdud de /
NK069(tu)001:3331: stobs la sogs pa'i 'bras bu'i chos su snang bas na /
NK069(tu)001:3332: de'i rtags su seng+ge la sogs pa'i gdan sgyu ma sgo /
NK069(tu)001:3333: mi 'jigs pa seng+ge'i khri dang ces pa sogs bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:3336: pad ma dang rin po che'i gdan bsdud de /
NK069(tu)001:3337: thams cad rang rig tu shes pas ci spyad kyang nyes skyon dang bral bas na /
NK069(tu)001:3339: de'i rtags su pad+ma rin chen bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3340: gos pa myed pa pad+ma rin po che bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:3344: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su myed par gsal ba'i phyir nyi zla'i gdan bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3345: rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba nyi zla'i dal bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:3346: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan 'phrin las /
NK069(tu)001:3350: yon tan yid bzhin rin po che /
NK069(tu)001:3352: 'khor dang tshad bsdu ste rtog tshogs sku dang ye shes su sel myed do //
NK069(tu)001:3354: mtshan mar ma yin pa yan chad bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:3355: sku mdog bsdus te yon tan rin po che shel gyi ga'ura cug pa ltar /
NK069(tu)001:3357: de dag kyang mthing ka dang ces pa sogs bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:3358: de ltar blta ba dang ting nges gdul bya'i snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:3359: nyid las mi gzhan pa'i 'khor lha bsdud de /
NK069(tu)001:3360: phung po dang 'byung ba lnga ye nas dkar dag pa'i lha yab yum bcu ste /
NK069(tu)001:3361: sku rnam snang yab yum dang /
NK069(tu)001:3362: gsung snang mtha' yab yum dang /
NK069(tu)001:3363: thugs mi skyod pa yab yum dang /
NK069(tu)001:3364: yon tan rin 'byung yab yum dang /
NK069(tu)001:3365: 'phrin las don grub yab yum rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:3366: de rnams yang rtog tshogs yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:3367: bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par shes pa'i rgyal po dang ces sogs bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:3368: thams cad chos kyi dbyings na gnas pas /
NK069(tu)001:3369: dper na til gyi gang bu bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:3370: don bsdu ba ni bcu gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:3371: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:3375: ye shes kyi dbang sgyur bas na /
NK069(tu)001:3376: rang bzhin nyid kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK069(tu)001:3381: thugs rjes 'dul ba'i ngang yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:3383: rang snang ba nyid ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:3384: rang snang dang dbyer myed pas /
NK069(tu)001:3388: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK069(tu)001:3390: rten mtshon par byed pas na /
NK069(tu)001:3393: de kho na nyid mtshon pas na /
NK069(tu)001:3394: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK069(tu)001:3397: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK069(tu)001:3399: byang chub sems cir yang snang bas na /
NK069(tu)001:3400: lhag pa byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK069(tu)001:3404: mi bzad par ldan ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:3406: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor rnams 'dus par gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:3407: mi bzad par ldan rgyan gyi 'khor lo //
NK069(tu)001:3409: de ltar bsgoms pa'i 'bras bu cir snang zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:3410: bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:3411: rtogs pa'i dus na rtog tshogs thams cad sku gsung
NK069(tu)001:3412: thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor rang snang
NK069(tu)001:3413: ngo // de yang sku mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo ni /
NK069(tu)001:3414: sku'i gsang ba bsam gyis myi khyab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:3417: rgyan rang bzhin gyi don byed pas mdzes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3418: 'khor lo mdzad pa bcu gnyis rgyun mi chad do //
NK069(tu)001:3419: rdo rje mchog gi gnas nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:3421: rdo rje ni 'joms pas te rnam tog go //
NK069(tu)001:3422: mchog gi sku lnga lhun grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:3423: de lta bur rtogs pa'i gnas nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:3424: zhes rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig du'o //
NK069(tu)001:3426: rdo rje'i theg pa rtogs par bka' bas na gsang ba /
NK069(tu)001:3427: de la mtshon pa'i tshig tu'o zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:3428: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:3430: gsang ba ni rtogs par bka' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:3431: snying po ni bcud 'dus pa don gyi snying po'o //
NK069(tu)001:3432: de kho na nyid ni mi bslu ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:3433: nges pa ni yang dag pa'i don no //
NK069(tu)001:3434: de lta bu'i rgyud las ces so //
NK069(tu)001:3435: gleng gzhi'i le'u ste dang po'o //
NK069(tu)001:3439: thun mong dang mthun par byas na /
NK069(tu)001:3440: phun sum tshogs pa lnga 'tshogs nas /
NK069(tu)001:3441: gleng slangs 'byung ba'i gzhir gyur pas na gleng gzhi /
NK069(tu)001:3443: phun sum tshogs pa'i gnas skabs na /
NK069(tu)001:3444: rgyud dbu zhabs kyi don 'dus par stan pas na /
NK069(tu)001:3445: khyad par gleng gzhir bstan pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:3446: 'dir le'u'i sdud la gtar kas gags gsal na /
NK069(tu)001:3447: le'u sdud 'di ston pa yin nam min /
NK069(tu)001:3448: ston pa min na sku gsung thugs rdo rje las phyung ba dang 'gal la /
NK069(tu)001:3449: yin na ston pas gsungs sam /
NK069(tu)001:3452: gleng slangs myed par stan pa gsung bar mi rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:3453: 'khor ram sdud pa pos gsungs zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:3454: ston pas ma gsungs par sdud pa pos gsung bar mi rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:3455: 'o na ji ltar shes bya zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:3456: le'u sdud 'di ston pa yin te /
NK069(tu)001:3457: sku gsung thugs rdo rje las phyung ngo zhes pas so //
NK069(tu)001:3459: snang ba gsum gyi dbang du ste /
NK069(tu)001:3460: de lta rang bzhin gyi snang ba gzhi /
NK069(tu)001:3462: bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba 'bras bu ste /
NK069(tu)001:3463: rang bzhin gyi snang ba la /
NK069(tu)001:3464: 'og min du phun sum tshogs pa lnga tshogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:3465: chos gsung ba yang tshig tu gsung mi dgos te /
NK069(tu)001:3467: zhu ba yang tshig tu zhu mi dgos te /
NK069(tu)001:3468: 'khor gyis bsams pa ston pas mkhyen no //
NK069(tu)001:3469: de bas na ston pa'i dgongs pas /
NK069(tu)001:3470: 'khor la sems can gyi rtog tshogs sangs rgyas su drangs srid pas /
NK069(tu)001:3472: de bas na 'di skad bshad ces so //
NK069(tu)001:3474: de ltar 'khor mas sbyangs kyis go tsam na /
NK069(tu)001:3475: 'di lta bu'i chos 'gro la'ang bshad par zhu byas pas /
NK069(tu)001:3476: le'u gnyis par gleng slang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:3477: de bas na snang ba dbyer med du rtogs pa 'bras bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:3478: le'u dang po'i rtog tshogs las gzhan mi mnga' bas na le'u bsdus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3479: le'u gnyis pa gleng slang ba la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:3482: gleng slang ba la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:3483: yab kyis 'khor 'das thams cad rang byung gi ye
NK069(tu)001:3484: shes chen por gtan la phab pa'i gleng slang ba
NK069(tu)001:3485: dang / yum gyis 'khor 'das thams cad chos kyi dbyings su gtan la phab ste gleng slang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:3487: don dam pa byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:3488: kun rdzob byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3489: dang po don dam la lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:3490: skye ba myed pa chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes su bstan /
NK069(tu)001:3491: 'gag pa myed pa me long lta bu'i ye shes su bstan /
NK069(tu)001:3492: gnas pa myed pas mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes su bstan /
NK069(tu)001:3493: dmyigs pa myed pas so sor rtog pa'i ye shes bstan /
NK069(tu)001:3494: 'gro 'ong myed pas bya ba grub pa'i ye shes bstan no //
NK069(tu)001:3495: kun rdzob tu sems bskyed pa la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:3496: don ma rtogs pa rnams gsang ba bzhis mchod pa yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:3497: 'khrul pa'i zhen pa zlog pa'i phyir snying rje skyes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:3498: bcings grol myed pa'i theg pas 'gro don mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3499: yab yum 'jug par dgongs pa stan /
NK069(tu)001:3500: de bzhin bcom ldan 'das byed pa po yid rdo rje kun tu bzang po /
NK069(tu)001:3501: thams cad ma lus pa'i rang bzhin gyi tshul rdo rjes /
NK069(tu)001:3503: yab yum la 'jug par dgongs pa'i don gsungs pa lo rgyus su brjod pa ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:3507: glengs pa'i 'bras bu gang yin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3509: ston pa kun tu bzang pos so //
NK069(tu)001:3511: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la nyid glengs /
NK069(tu)001:3513: thams cad sangs rgyas par glengs /
NK069(tu)001:3515: de ltar thams cad kyis rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3521: legs pa'i yon tan drug dang ldan /
NK069(tu)001:3524: mu stegs ltar phya'am dbang phyug gi byed pos byas par 'dod pa lta bu ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:3525: 'dir yid kyi rnam par shes pas 'khor 'das thams cad kyi byed pa po byas te /
NK069(tu)001:3526: yid kyi rnam shes ma rig pas slad pa'i dus na ni 'khor ba thams cad byas la /
NK069(tu)001:3527: rtogs pa'i dus na mya ngan las 'das pa thams cad byas /
NK069(tu)001:3528: lam gyi dus na ston pa rgyud dang dal gyi byed pa por shar ro //
NK069(tu)001:3530: yid rdo rje kun tu bzang po ces so //
NK069(tu)001:3531: yid gnas su dag par rtogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:3532: rdo rje lta bu'i ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:3533: de ni dus thams cad du blang dor thams cad dang bral bas na kun du bzang po'o //
NK069(tu)001:3536: rtog myed ye shes kyi yid las ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:3537: yid des snang ba 'khor 'das su grub par byed pas na /
NK069(tu)001:3538: thams cad ma lus pa'i ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:3539: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos ma lus pa thams cad do //
NK069(tu)001:3541: ye nas 'khor 'das gnyis med kyi rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:3543: 'khor 'das gnyis kyang dbyer mi phyed pa'i tshul lo //
NK069(tu)001:3544: rdo rje ni ye nas snang stong dbyer mi phyed pa kho na la'o //
NK069(tu)001:3545: btsun mo bya ba mo chos kun tu bzang mo la 'jug pa gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:3550: gnas par bya ba'i don no //
NK069(tu)001:3552: yid kyi yul du bya ba byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3554: 'dus byas kyi chos thams cad kyi bya ba byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3555: kun tu bzang mo ni blang dor mtha' dag dang bral ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:3557: thabs shes rab gnyis med dam /
NK069(tu)001:3558: dbyings ye shes gnyis med dam /
NK069(tu)001:3559: yid chos dbyer myed par gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3560: de yang rtogs par bya ba'i yul chos kyi dbyings logs zhig na yod pa la /
NK069(tu)001:3561: ye shes bya ba'i rig pa zhig 'jug par ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:3562: dbyings rig pa dang ldan na ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:3563: ye shes spros pa dang bral na chos dbyings /
NK069(tu)001:3564: dbyings rig pa gnyis med na don rang gi mtshan nyid rang gis rtogs par gyur pa la /
NK069(tu)001:3566: bzhugs pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:3567: dgongs pa rang gi ngo bo bstan /
NK069(tu)001:3568: gcig gi rang bzhin du dbyer med pas /
NK069(tu)001:3570: dgongs pa rang gi ngo bo ni //
NK069(tu)001:3572: dus bzhir gshegs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa ma lus pa thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:3573: phyi ltar na kun tu bzang po'i thugs ye shes su gcig /
NK069(tu)001:3574: kun tu bzang po'i thugs ye shes dbyer med do //
NK069(tu)001:3575: yang na nang ltar na phyogs bcu dus bzhis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad dang /
NK069(tu)001:3576: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du gcig /
NK069(tu)001:3577: sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du dbyer myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3579: 'khor 'das gnyis kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes su gcig ste /
NK069(tu)001:3580: dbyer myed pa'i dgongs pas so //
NK069(tu)001:3581: 'o na sems can la de bzhin gshegs pa ci'i phyir bya zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:3582: sems can rnams kyang 'byung bar ma nges pa'i dus kyi dam pa yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:3585: 'gro ba sems can rnams gong du sangs rgyas pa'i
NK069(tu)001:3586: rang bzhin du dbyer myed pa'i rang bzhin du stan
NK069(tu)001:3587: pas nyid la nyid ces bya ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:3588: de bzhin gshegs pa 'di ston pa /
NK069(tu)001:3591: ched du brjod pa pa'i tshig rnams dgongs pas /
NK069(tu)001:3594: brjod pa ni 'gro ba'i don la thugs kyis dgongs pa tsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:3595: ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor du bstan pa la
NK069(tu)001:3596: phung po lnga rigs lngar sangs rgyas la bstan pa
NK069(tu)001:3597: ni / e ma'o rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni /
NK069(tu)001:3598: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rigs lnga ru grags //
NK069(tu)001:3599: zhes pa'i rgyu bsod nams dang 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:3600: e ma'o ni ngam tshig ngo mtshar ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:3602: phung po khams dang skye mched rdo rje lta bu'i
NK069(tu)001:3603: ye shes su gnas pa la ngo mtshar skyes ba'o
NK069(tu)001:3604: // rdo rje phung po'i yan lag ni /
NK069(tu)001:3605: ye shes rdo rje lta bu dbyer med cig la /
NK069(tu)001:3606: phung po lnga'i yan lag lta bur snang /
NK069(tu)001:3607: snang ba de yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK069(tu)001:3608: rigs lnga yin par grags pa'i rgyud kun las grags
NK069(tu)001:3609: so // de yang ji ltar yin na /
NK069(tu)001:3610: thal ba'i le'u gnyis pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:3611: nang gi 'gro gnas ma lus kun //
NK069(tu)001:3612: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa nyid //
NK069(tu)001:3613: gzugs su rnam par snang mdzad de //
NK069(tu)001:3614: tshor ba rin chen 'byung ldan yin //
NK069(tu)001:3615: 'du shes snang ba mtha' yas bdag /
NK069(tu)001:3616: 'du byed don yod grub pa'i sku //
NK069(tu)001:3617: rnam shes rdo rje mi skyod pa //
NK069(tu)001:3618: ye shes rnam pa lnga bdag nyid //
NK069(tu)001:3623: sems la sbyar na gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:3624: ma rtogs pa 'khrul pa'i dus dang /
NK069(tu)001:3625: rtogs pa nyams kyis dus so //
NK069(tu)001:3626: ma rtogs pa 'khrul pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:3627: ye shes lnga phung po lngar snang /
NK069(tu)001:3628: ye shes kyi khyad par skye mched du snang /
NK069(tu)001:3629: chos kyi dbyings 'byung ba lngar snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:3630: rtogs ldan nyams kyi dus na /
NK069(tu)001:3631: nyer len gyi phung po la sangs rgyas rigs lngar snang /
NK069(tu)001:3632: khams dang skye mched sems dpa' sems mar snang /
NK069(tu)001:3633: 'byung ba lnga yum lngar snang ste /
NK069(tu)001:3634: sku dang ye shes kho nar gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:3635: kyus dbang can du bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:3636: e ma'o rdo rje phung po'i yan lag /
NK069(tu)001:3638: khams dang skye mched sems dpa' dang /
NK069(tu)001:3639: sems mar sangs rgyas pa bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:3640: skye mched khams rnams mang po kun //
NK069(tu)001:3641: byang chub sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK069(tu)001:3643: mig la rten nas gzugs skye bas na skye mched /
NK069(tu)001:3644: byed pa myed par rang gi mtshan nyid 'dzin pas na khams /
NK069(tu)001:3646: rnam shes nang gi skye mched dang /
NK069(tu)001:3647: dbang po phyi'i skye mched dang /
NK069(tu)001:3648: mig gi yul gyi khams la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3649: de rnams byang chub sems dpa' yab yum gyi lhar gnas pa nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:3650: de yang phung po'i sangs rgyas su gyur phan chad /
NK069(tu)001:3651: khams dang skye mched yang sangs rgyas kyi sras so //
NK069(tu)001:3653: rags pa thabs kyi phyag rgya ste //
NK069(tu)001:3654: mtshan nyid myed pa shes rab yum //
NK069(tu)001:3655: gnyis myed sbyor ba'i byin brlabs las //
NK069(tu)001:3656: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor rgya chen po //
NK069(tu)001:3657: khams dang skye mched rnam dag pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:3658: byang chub sems dpas gnas kun mdzes //
NK069(tu)001:3659: rang bzhin ma bcos lhun gyis grub //
NK069(tu)001:3661: sa chu spyan dang ma ma ki //
NK069(tu)001:3662: me rlung gos dkar sgrol ma ste //
NK069(tu)001:3663: nam mkha' dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma //
NK069(tu)001:3665: sa sangs rgyas spyan thams cad mkhyen pa'i ming can /
NK069(tu)001:3666: chu ma ma ki thugs rje rgyun mi chad pa'i ming can /
NK069(tu)001:3667: me gos dkar mo nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pa'i ming can /
NK069(tu)001:3668: rlung dam tshig sgrol ma 'phrin las kyi ming can /
NK069(tu)001:3669: nam mkha' kun tu bzang mo chos nyid 'byung khungs kyi ming can no //
NK069(tu)001:3671: byang chub sems kyi snang ba las //
NK069(tu)001:3672: rang bzhin rdzogs pas gnas kun sbyong //
NK069(tu)001:3673: phyi rol 'byung tshogs yul rnams kun //
NK069(tu)001:3674: thabs dang shes rab gnyis myed par //
NK069(tu)001:3675: sra brtan rdo rje spyan ma ste //
NK069(tu)001:3676: gsher bsdud lha mo ma ma ki //
NK069(tu)001:3677: smin byed sreg mdzad gos dkar mo //
NK069(tu)001:3678: yang zhing g.yo ba sgrol ma'i mkha' //
NK069(tu)001:3679: stong gsal nam mkha' kun bzang mo //
NK069(tu)001:3681: srid gsum ye nas sangs rgyas zhing //
NK069(tu)001:3685: 'og ngan 'gro'i srid pa gsum gyis sdus pa'i sems can rnams kyi phung po lnga rigs lnga /
NK069(tu)001:3687: phyi'i skye mched dang nang gi skye mched sems dpa' dang khro bo /
NK069(tu)001:3688: de'i yul sems ma dang khro mor gnas pa de /
NK069(tu)001:3689: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin yin zhing /
NK069(tu)001:3690: ma bcos shing ma sgyur bar gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3691: ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor du sel myed /
NK069(tu)001:3692: thams cad ma lus chos pa chog /
NK069(tu)001:3694: thams cad ni 'khor 'das thams cad do //
NK069(tu)001:3695: ma lus pa ni 'khor ba'i sems nyid la /
NK069(tu)001:3696: rang bzhin rtog bcas rgya bcu ste /
NK069(tu)001:3697: rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad /
NK069(tu)001:3701: 'du byed la lnga bcu gcig go //
NK069(tu)001:3703: mya ngan las 'das pas bsdus pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:3704: chos so lcog thams cad do //
NK069(tu)001:3705: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan ma yin //
NK069(tu)001:3707: btags pa'i tha snyad brtsal na mi rnyed pas kyang sangs rgyas yin /
NK069(tu)001:3708: rang rig sku dang ye shes su ka dag cing lhun gyis grub pas kyang sangs rgyas yin /
NK069(tu)001:3709: don dam nyid snang ba ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur gnas pas kyang sangs rgyas yin /
NK069(tu)001:3710: sems rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal bas kyang 'bu ta'o //
NK069(tu)001:3711: sangs rgyas nyid las gzhan pa'i chos //
NK069(tu)001:3713: rang nyid sangs rgyas su ma shes na /
NK069(tu)001:3714: de las gzhan pa'i sangs rgyas yod zhes 'chad pa'i chos ni /
NK069(tu)001:3715: gzhan nas rnyed par dka' ste /
NK069(tu)001:3716: smun long nam mkha'i mtha' tshol ba dang 'dra bas mi rnyed do //
NK069(tu)001:3717: sangs rgyas nyid kyis mi snyems so //
NK069(tu)001:3720: stong gsum 'jig rten grangs myed pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:3721: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor mtha' yas kun //
NK069(tu)001:3722: kun bzang ye shes rnam bkod pas //
NK069(tu)001:3723: thams cad ma 'dres yongs su rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:3724: kun rdzob snang ba bsam yas par //
NK069(tu)001:3725: me long chu zla 'ja' tshon ltar //
NK069(tu)001:3726: snang la ma 'gags kun rten cing //
NK069(tu)001:3727: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor mngon gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3728: kun tu bzang po'i chos rnams kun //
NK069(tu)001:3729: sangs rgyas bstan pas rdzogs pa nyid //
NK069(tu)001:3730: de las lhag pa'i don smra ba //
NK069(tu)001:3731: dmigs pa'i yul rtog kun dang bral //
NK069(tu)001:3733: khams gsum sems can thams cad kyi rtog bcas tshogs brgyad cu lhar bshad pa na /
NK069(tu)001:3735: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad mnyes par gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:3736: zhes brjod pa'i don la mnyes /
NK069(tu)001:3738: brjod pas 'grel ba'i lta ba la mnyes so //
NK069(tu)001:3739: de nas btsun mo bya ba mo chos kun tu bzang mos /
NK069(tu)001:3741: yab kyis gleng slang ba'i barjesa de nas /
NK069(tu)001:3742: yum gyis gleng slang ba ston pas so //
NK069(tu)001:3743: btsun mo ni dpyad par bya ba'i yul du gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3744: 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas kyi chos thams cad dag pa ni yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:3745: kun tu bzang mo ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:3746: rang bzhin kun tu bzang mo /
NK069(tu)001:3747: rtogs pa kun tu bzang mo /
NK069(tu)001:3748: phyag rgya kun tu bzang mo /
NK069(tu)001:3750: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje'i yid kun tu bzang po dang gnyis su myed par gyur nas /
NK069(tu)001:3751: zhes pa bdud bzhi ngang gis bcom /
NK069(tu)001:3752: sku dang ye shes shugs kyis ldan /
NK069(tu)001:3754: rtag bcas 'khor ba'i yid gnas su dag pas na /
NK069(tu)001:3755: rtog myed ye shes kyi yid kho na la /
NK069(tu)001:3757: spyod yul thams cad yongs su dag pas na kun tu bzang mo'o //
NK069(tu)001:3758: ye shes kyi yul chos kyi dbyings /
NK069(tu)001:3759: ye shes kyis mi rtogs su mi stub pa 'am /
NK069(tu)001:3760: gnyis su myed pa'i mtshan nyid rang gis rtogs pas na /
NK069(tu)001:3761: gnyis su myed par gyur nas zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:3762: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:3763: ces 'gro ba'i ched du stan par dgongs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3764: ye shes sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:3771: yum gyis yab la bos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3772: shar lho nub byang phyogs bzhi dang /
NK069(tu)001:3773: mtshams brgyad steng 'og phyogs bcu yang sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3775: gling bzhi ri rab tshangs pa'i 'jig rten dang bcas pa stong pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:3776: stong chung ngu'i 'jig rten gyi khams so //
NK069(tu)001:3777: de lta bu stong la ni /
NK069(tu)001:3778: stong gnyis pa bar ma'i 'jig rten gyi khams so //
NK069(tu)001:3779: de lta bu gcig du bsgrangs pa stong la ni /
NK069(tu)001:3780: stong gsum gyi stong chen po 'jig rten gyi khams so //
NK069(tu)001:3782: 'dod khams gnas ris nyi shu dang /
NK069(tu)001:3783: gzugs khams gnas ris bcu bdun dang /
NK069(tu)001:3784: gzugs myed skye mched mu bzhi'o //
NK069(tu)001:3785: de ltar na phyogs bcu dang /
NK069(tu)001:3787: khams gsum du snang ba thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:3788: ye nas sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams so //
NK069(tu)001:3789: chos kyi dbyings mu mtha' dang bral ba yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:3791: stong pa nyid kyi tshig bla gdags so //
NK069(tu)001:3793: phyogs bcu'i mtha' rnams zhi ba nyid //
NK069(tu)001:3794: ye nas ma bcos dben par gnas //
NK069(tu)001:3796: srid pa gsum ni dag pa'i zhing //
NK069(tu)001:3797: zhes steng lha'i srid pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:3805: gling bzhi gling phran brgyad dang bcas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3806: 'og ngan song gi srid pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:3810: de dag ni sangs rgyas kyi zhing /
NK069(tu)001:3815: de yang chags pa sprul sku /
NK069(tu)001:3817: stongs pa chos kyi sku'i zhing khams rnam par dag par gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3818: snyigs ma lnga nyid bde ldan gnas //
NK069(tu)001:3821: dus lnga brgya'i tha ma la bab pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3822: tshe'i snyigs ma ni tshe lo bcu pa'i dus so //
NK069(tu)001:3824: pha ngo bus mi shes te bsad gcad kyi las byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3826: rtag chad kyi mthar zhen pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3827: nyon mongs pa'i snyigs ma ni /
NK069(tu)001:3828: nyon mongs pa lnga bdag 'dzin du zhen pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3829: de lta bu'i snyigs ma lnga nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:3831: bde ba dang ldan pa'i gnas te /
NK069(tu)001:3832: pad ma can la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3833: yang na snyigs mar gyur pa'i sa chu me rlung
NK069(tu)001:3834: nam mkha' lngas bsdus pa'i gnas 'di bde ba'i gnas
NK069(tu)001:3835: yin no // phung po lnga nyid mngon sangs rgyas //
NK069(tu)001:3837: gzugs kyi phung po skye 'jig can nyid rnam snang du mngon par rdzogs sangs rgyas par shes /
NK069(tu)001:3838: rnam par shes pa rno ltul can gyi phung po rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK069(tu)001:3839: bde sdug can gyi tshor ba rin 'byung /
NK069(tu)001:3840: rgya che chung can gyi 'du shes snang mtha' /
NK069(tu)001:3841: mi gnas par kun la spyod pa'i 'du byed don yod grub pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:3842: ma rtogs pa'i dus na phung po lngar snang yang /
NK069(tu)001:3843: rtogs pa'i dus na rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas so //
NK069(tu)001:3844: 'dir don gyis gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:3846: 'khor la gsang dbang skur bar 'dod dam mi 'dod /
NK069(tu)001:3848: yab yum la snyoms par zhugs pa la dgos pa myed do //
NK069(tu)001:3849: gsang ba'i dbang bskur bar 'dod na /
NK069(tu)001:3850: gsang dbang la dbang rdzas byang sems dkar dmar dgos pa la /
NK069(tu)001:3851: kun tu bzang po ye shes kyi sku la /
NK069(tu)001:3852: byang sems dkar dmar myed pas dbang myi thob bo zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:3853: de ye shes kyi ro myong ba ci lto zhes pa la /
NK069(tu)001:3854: des mi 'ong ste dbang rdzas myed pa'i dbang bskur bar mi rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:3857: kun tu bzang po yab yum ye shes sgyu ma'i sku yin la /
NK069(tu)001:3858: des ye shes sgyu ma'i tsam gyi byang sems dkar dmar la rten nas /
NK069(tu)001:3861: gnas brtan rtsa dang thig le las //
NK069(tu)001:3862: rigs kyi ye shes gzugs su skye //
NK069(tu)001:3864: kun tu bzang po ye shes kyi sku la /
NK069(tu)001:3865: ye shes kyi nyi zla byang sems phyung nas /
NK069(tu)001:3867: dbang thob nas rgyud zhu ba'i spobs pa dang ldan par gyur pas na /
NK069(tu)001:3872: sems la sbyar na gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:3873: ma rtogs 'khrul pa'i dbang du byas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:3874: rnal 'byor pa rtogs ldan nyams kyi snang ba'i dbang du byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3876: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba ni sems su 'dus so //
NK069(tu)001:3877: sems kyi chos nyid byang chub sems de ma rtogs pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:3881: yul ngam grog dang g.yang sa /
NK069(tu)001:3883: mthon dman dang bde sdug can du snang /
NK069(tu)001:3884: srid pa gsum po ni 'khor ba'i 'khor sa /
NK069(tu)001:3885: snyigs ma lnga po ni log par bcal pa'i gnas /
NK069(tu)001:3886: phung po lnga po sdug bsngal gyi gtan zhing ngo //
NK069(tu)001:3887: rtogs ldan nyams kyi snang bas dbang du byas na /
NK069(tu)001:3888: sems can gyi chos nyid byang chub kyi sems ji lta ba bzhin du rtogs pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:3889: phyogs bcu'i stong khams nyid ye nas yod myed kyi mtha' las dben /
NK069(tu)001:3890: srid pa gsum nyid sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag pa bde ba can dang /
NK069(tu)001:3892: lcang lo can dang 'thug po bkod par snang /
NK069(tu)001:3893: snyigs ma lnga nyid sku dang ye shes kyi bde ba /
NK069(tu)001:3894: phung po lnga nyid rigs lnga'i sangs /
NK069(tu)001:3895: 'khor ba thams cad ni mya ngan las 'das pa'i yon tan mchog gi snying po'am /
NK069(tu)001:3896: byang chub mchog gi snying po zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:3897: sku dang ye shes yongs su dag pa'i zhing khams rnam par dag pa'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:3899: kye ma'o phyogs bcu'i stong khams ye nas dben /
NK069(tu)001:3901: thams cad mchog gi snying po bas //
NK069(tu)001:3906: dmyigs sgyu lta bu'i rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:3907: de bas na 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal thams cad ma spangs par gnas 'gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:3909: sangs rgyas su gyur pa ni mchog gi snying po'o //
NK069(tu)001:3910: de lam dang sgrub bya ma nor bar stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:3911: gzhan du rgyal bas chos mi brtsal //
NK069(tu)001:3913: de ltar na sems kyi chos nyid rtogs par bya ba las ma rtogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:3915: gzhan nas sangs rgyas kyi chos zab mo thob par 'dod na /
NK069(tu)001:3916: shin tu rnyed par dka' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:3917: nyid las gzhan zhes bya ba'i chos //
NK069(tu)001:3919: sems nyid las ma rtogs pa gzhan na chos myed de /
NK069(tu)001:3921: 'khor 'das su snang ba yang rang gi sems snang bas so //
NK069(tu)001:3922: brtsal kyang rgyal ba'i mi snyems so //
NK069(tu)001:3925: sems can gyis lha lta ci smos te /
NK069(tu)001:3926: sangs rgyas nyid kyis kyang don mi rnyed do //
NK069(tu)001:3928: gzhan na myed pa'i phyir ro //
