NK069(tu)001:3931: som nyi myed par rtogs pa brjod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3932: 'dir gtar ka gags bsal pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:3933: sems bskyed pa 'di sleng slang ba yin nam rgyud don yin /
NK069(tu)001:3935: sems lnga bskyed pa de gleng slangs su mi 'gro /
NK069(tu)001:3938: yang gsang ba bzhis chod pa la chos zhus pa'i tshig /
NK069(tu)001:3941: yab yum gyis gleng slang ba'i 'bras bu sems lnga bskyed par byung bas rgyud don yin /
NK069(tu)001:3942: sems bskyed pa'i 'bras bu gsang ba bzhis chod pa
NK069(tu)001:3943: la bshad par zhus pa de kho na rgyud don
NK069(tu)001:3944: zhus pa ste / bdag don du sems bskyed /
NK069(tu)001:3945: gzhan don du bcings grol myed pa'i theg pa 'chad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:3947: thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas par de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis mkhyen to //
NK069(tu)001:3951: ye gdod ma gnas lugs rang nas sangs rgyas te /
NK069(tu)001:3952: rnal 'byor pa rtogs ldan nyams kyi snang ba la yang de ltar snang la /
NK069(tu)001:3953: bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba la yang de ltar yin no //
NK069(tu)001:3954: de nas gnyis su myed pa'i bdag nyid chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:3956: yab yum gyis rtogs pa'i nyams brjod pa'i gleng slang ba'i rjes de nas /
NK069(tu)001:3958: thabs shes rab gnyis su na /
NK069(tu)001:3959: dbyings ye shes gnyis su na /
NK069(tu)001:3961: de ltar ston pa kho na la bdag nyid chen po zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:3962: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i sems ye shes pa bskyed pa 'di gsungs so //
NK069(tu)001:3964: khams gsum 'khor ba'i sems can thams cad ye nas rang bzhin lhun grub du sangs rgyas kyang /
NK069(tu)001:3965: sangs rgyas par ma shes pas na /
NK069(tu)001:3966: sems nyid ye shes lngar gnas pa de /
NK069(tu)001:3967: ye shes lngar bskyed pa'i thabs 'di ston pas gsungs so //
NK069(tu)001:3968: 'dir byang chub sems bskyed pa la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:3969: don dam pa byang chub sems dang /
NK069(tu)001:3970: kun rdzob byang chub sems so //
NK069(tu)001:3971: don dam pa byang chub sems la ngag don bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:3972: dang po gnas 'gyur gyi gzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:3973: kun gzhi chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:3974: yid me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:3975: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid so sor rtog pa /
NK069(tu)001:3976: yid dang kun gzhi mi phyed pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:3977: sgo lnga'i rnam shes bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:3978: gnyis pa ye shes lnga'i dbye ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:3979: dang po chos thams cad stong zhing bdag myed par
NK069(tu)001:3980: rtogs pa'i cha nas gzung na stong nyid kyi ye
NK069(tu)001:3981: shes / gsal la ma 'gags pa'i cha gzung nas me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:3982: rang dang spyi'i mtshan nyid rtogs pa'i cha bzung nas so sor rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:3983: 'khor 'das thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa'i cha gzung nas mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:3984: bdag dang gzhan gyi don spyod pa'i cha gzung nas bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:3985: gsum pa ye shes lnga la gzhi lam 'bras bur stan na /
NK069(tu)001:3986: rang sems la ye shes lnga lhun gyis grub pa de gzhi /
NK069(tu)001:3987: ye nas sangs rgyas pa de ye shes su bskyed pa'i thabs gsungs pa de lam /
NK069(tu)001:3988: bskyed pa'i don mthar phyin pa de 'bras bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:3989: bzhi pa bskyed thabs ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:3991: sems lnga'i dmyigs pa'i yul dang /
NK069(tu)001:3994: 'dod chags kyi spyod pa ni rmad du byung ba'i ye shes lngar snang la /
NK069(tu)001:3995: de nyid thabs kyi theg pa chen po'i chos so //
NK069(tu)001:3997: rang bzhin lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes de /
NK069(tu)001:4002: 'gro 'ong gi mtha' gang du yang ma skyed pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:4003: sems lnga skye ba'i bye brag ni /
NK069(tu)001:4008: gsang dbang dang shes rab ye shes kyi nyams so //
NK069(tu)001:4009: rdzogs pa byang chub kyi sems bde ba chen po'i dbang gi nyams so //
NK069(tu)001:4010: e ma'o ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK069(tu)001:4012: e ma'o ni ngam zhing ngo mtshar ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:4014: tshig la ngo mtshar che la /
NK069(tu)001:4015: don la smad du 'byung ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:4016: theg pa 'og ma bas smad kyang /
NK069(tu)001:4017: dngos grub tu myur ba'i chos yin pas smad kyi chos so //
NK069(tu)001:4019: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK069(tu)001:4021: de'i gnas gang yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4022: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i dus gsum gyis sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs la gnag pa'i gsang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:4023: skye ba myed las thams cad skyes //
NK069(tu)001:4025: gsang ba de dngos gang yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4027: chos thams cad ni ye gdod ma nas ma byung
NK069(tu)001:4028: skyes skye ba myed pa chos kyi dbyings yin pa'o
NK069(tu)001:4029: // de ltar yin pa'i gtan tshigs ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:4030: rgyu rkyen gzhan gyis ma skyed pa'i phyir na skye ba myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4031: byed pa po gzhan gyis ma byas pa'i phyir na skye ba myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4032: dus glo bur du ma byung ba'i phyir na skye ba myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4033: skye ba'i dngos po 'di 'dra zhes ma rnyed pa'i phyir na skye ba myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4034: 'o na mtshan ma myed pa'i stong pa phyogs cig tu 'gags shing thim pa yin nam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4036: skye ba myed pa'i don de nyid mtshan ma sna
NK069(tu)001:4037: tshogs pa thams cad du snang bas na thams cad
NK069(tu)001:4038: skyes zhes bya'o // skyes pa nyid na skye ba myed //
NK069(tu)001:4039: ces bye brag gi ngo bo stan /
NK069(tu)001:4040: de ltar skyes ba nyid na skye ba myed pa'i mthar phyin te /
NK069(tu)001:4042: skyes pa yang gnyis su myed pas na /
NK069(tu)001:4043: skyes pa'i mtshan ma nyid ngo bor ma grub ste /
NK069(tu)001:4044: skyes tsam nyid na stong pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4045: skyes pa nyid na skye ba myed zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:4046: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:4047: gzhi rang sems dang sbyar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:4048: lam grol lam dang sbyar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:4049: thabs lam gsang dbang dang sbyar ba /
NK069(tu)001:4050: 'bras bu chos sku dang sbyar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:4051: dang po gzhi rang sems dang sbyar na gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:4052: ma rtogs pa 'khrul pa'i gnas skabs dang //
NK069(tu)001:4053: rtogs pa nyams kyi gnas skabs so //
NK069(tu)001:4054: ma rtogs pa 'khrul pa'i gnas skabs ni /
NK069(tu)001:4055: chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba /
NK069(tu)001:4056: rang gi sems kyi mtshan nyid de ni /
NK069(tu)001:4057: ye gdod ma nas ma byung ma skyes skye ba
NK069(tu)001:4058: myed pa stong zhing bdag myed pa chos kyi dbyings
NK069(tu)001:4059: yin la / de ma rtogs pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:4060: sems can gyi las dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa 'khor ba'i chos su snang zhing skyes la /
NK069(tu)001:4061: skyes pa de nyid kyi dus na yang /
NK069(tu)001:4062: ye shes de nyid las g.yos pa myed do //
NK069(tu)001:4064: sems kyi chos nyid de rtogs pa'i dus na ni /
NK069(tu)001:4065: 'phags pa'i sku dang ye shes kyi zhing khams te
NK069(tu)001:4066: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos sna tshogs su snang
NK069(tu)001:4067: zhing skyes la / de ltar skyes tsam nyid na skye ba myed pa'i mthar phyin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4068: de ltar su ma rtogs pa de stong pa nyid kyi ye shes su blo bskyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4070: rang sems sangs rgyas su rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4072: yab yum gnyis su myed pa'i dus su /
NK069(tu)001:4073: skye ba myed pa las lus kyi rtsa gnas nas rten thig le g.yo zhing /
NK069(tu)001:4074: ltang ba ni g.yo ltang byang chub kyi sems so //
NK069(tu)001:4075: 'bras bu chos sku dang sbyar ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:4076: sems kyi chos nyid dbyings rig gnyis su myed pa de /
NK069(tu)001:4077: e ma'o ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK069(tu)001:4079: e ma'o ni ngam zhing ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:4080: chos thams cad skye 'gag med pa las skye 'gag tu snang ba la'o //
NK069(tu)001:4081: de gang gi chos lugs yin na /
NK069(tu)001:4082: gsang ba smad du byung ba ma h+aa yo ga'i chos lugs so //
NK069(tu)001:4084: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK069(tu)001:4086: de gang gi gsung yin na /
NK069(tu)001:4087: sku lnga lhun grub tu gnas pa'i ston pa kun
NK069(tu)001:4088: tu bzang po yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK069(tu)001:4089: kyi gsung yin / de gang gi spyod yul yin na /
NK069(tu)001:4090: theg pa 'og ma pa'i spyod yul du ma gyur bas gsang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:4094: de'i dngos gzhi gang zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4095: me long lta bu'i ye shes ni /
NK069(tu)001:4096: thams cad du gsal la ma 'gags pas 'gag pa myed la /
NK069(tu)001:4097: gsal ba'i dus na rang gi ngo bo stan par dka' bas 'gags zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:4100: bye brag gi ngo bo bstan /
NK069(tu)001:4101: de ltar 'gags pa nyid na 'gag pa myed pa'i mthar phyin te /
NK069(tu)001:4102: skye 'chi las yang dag par 'das pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4103: de yang sems dang sems su snang du snang ba'i chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin yang /
NK069(tu)001:4104: 'gag pa'i dus na 'gag pa myed de /
NK069(tu)001:4105: 'gag pa dang 'gag pa myed pa gnyis myed du
NK069(tu)001:4106: rtogs pa kho na la me long lta bu'i ye
NK069(tu)001:4107: shes su sems bskyed zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:4108: me long lta bu'i ye shes la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:4109: dang po gzhi rang sems dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:4110: sems kyi ngo bo ni 'gag pa myed pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:4111: ma rig pa'i dbang du gnas skabs 'gag pa ltar yang mngon /
NK069(tu)001:4112: yang dag pa'i gnas skabs na /
NK069(tu)001:4114: 'gag pa myed pa gnyis dbyer myed do //
NK069(tu)001:4115: gnyis pa grol lam dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:4116: 'gag pa dang mi 'gag pa dbyer myed spyod yul dang bral ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:4117: gsum pa thabs lam du na /
NK069(tu)001:4118: yab yum gyi bde ba skyes pa ni 'gag pa myed /
NK069(tu)001:4119: bde ba de snga ma 'gags pa ltar snang bas na thams cad 'gag /
NK069(tu)001:4120: snga ma'i bde ba dang phyi ma'i bde ba snga
NK069(tu)001:4121: phyi ma chad par ltar snang ba ni 'gag myed
NK069(tu)001:4122: do // de ni smon 'jug byang chub sems so //
NK069(tu)001:4123: bzhi pa longs sku dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:4124: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i longs spyod
NK069(tu)001:4125: gang yang ma 'gags par sku nyams su gtar bas
NK069(tu)001:4126: na longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:4128: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK069(tu)001:4130: e ma'o ni ngam pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:4131: gang la ngam zhing ngo mtshar zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4132: gsang sngags kyi spyod pa nyid rmad du byung ba'i ye shes lngar snang la /
NK069(tu)001:4133: de kho na theg pa chen po gsang ba ma
NK069(tu)001:4134: h+aa yo ga'i chos yin pas rmad kyi chos so
NK069(tu)001:4135: // rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK069(tu)001:4137: de nyid ni sku lngar rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi rgyud dang ngo bo nyid yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:4138: de phal gyi spyod yul du ma gyur ba'i don gyis na kun gyi gsang zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:4140: gnas pa myed las thams cad gnas //
NK069(tu)001:4142: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes ni /
NK069(tu)001:4143: chos thams cad mnyam nyid thugs su chud pas /
NK069(tu)001:4144: bdag dang gzhan du yang gnas pa myed do //
NK069(tu)001:4145: 'o na gang la yang gnas pa myed pa zhig yin nam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4146: dngos dang mtshan ma kun la khyab par yang gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:4148: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa myed //
NK069(tu)001:4150: de ltar gnas pa nyid rtogs na /
NK069(tu)001:4151: gnas pa myed pa mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kho na'o //
NK069(tu)001:4152: de sus rtogs pa'i gang zag de nyid sems bskyed pa zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:4153: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:4154: dang po gzhi sems nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:4155: sems nyid kyi ngo bo ni gang du yang gnas pa myed /
NK069(tu)001:4156: sems kyi rnam pa ma rtogs pa'i dus na 'gro ba drug gi lus la gnas /
NK069(tu)001:4157: de ltar gnas pa nyid na gnas pa myed do //
NK069(tu)001:4158: gnyis pa grol lam du na /
NK069(tu)001:4159: rang sems gzung 'dzin dang bral ba'i mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4160: gsum pa thabs lam dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:4161: yab yum gyi bde ba la /
NK069(tu)001:4162: dga' ba bzhi'i thig le bab pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:4163: dga' ba de nyid sems yul du gnas car myed pa'i tshul gyis /
NK069(tu)001:4164: sems rang gsal du gnas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4165: gnas pa byang chub sems so //
NK069(tu)001:4166: gzhi lam 'bras bu dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:4167: sems can dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin cing gnas
NK069(tu)001:4168: pa myed pa'i cha bzung nas rtogs pa'i dus na
NK069(tu)001:4169: / mngon par byang chub pa'i sku zhes gdags so //
NK069(tu)001:4171: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK069(tu)001:4173: e ma ni ngo mtshar pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:4175: gsang ba rmad du 'byung ba'i chos 'di la ngo mtshar ro //
NK069(tu)001:4176: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK069(tu)001:4177: de gang gi spyod yul yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4178: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:4180: dmyigs pa myed las thams cad dmyigs /
NK069(tu)001:4182: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes ni /
NK069(tu)001:4183: chos spyi'i mtshan nyid stong zhing bdag myed par rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:4184: 'khor ba'i mtha' la dmyigs pa myed la /
NK069(tu)001:4185: rang gi mtshan nyid ma 'dres par mkhyen pas mya
NK069(tu)001:4186: ngan las 'das pa'i mtha' la dmyigs pa myed do
NK069(tu)001:4187: // de ltar snang tsam na spyi dang rang gi
NK069(tu)001:4188: mtshan nyid shes pas thams cad la dmyigs pa myed
NK069(tu)001:4190: dmyigs pa nyid na dmyigs pa myed //
NK069(tu)001:4192: de ltar spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid dmyigs bya
NK069(tu)001:4193: dmyigs byed dbyer myed du shes pa kho na sus
NK069(tu)001:4194: rtogs pa de / so sor rtog pa'i ye shes su sems bskyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4195: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:4196: dang po rgyu sems can dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:4197: sems nyid kyis spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid ma 'dres par mkhyen pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4198: gnyis pa grol lam dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:4199: sems kyi rang bzhin ni dmyigs pa myed pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:4200: rnam pa ni dmigs pa can yin te /
NK069(tu)001:4201: de ltar snang tsam dmyigs pa dang dmyigs pa myed pa dbyer myed do //
NK069(tu)001:4203: bde ba'i ye shes gcig las /
NK069(tu)001:4204: nyams kyi snang bas sa 'thon dman la dmigs nas /
NK069(tu)001:4205: snga ma las phyi ma la smon pas na /
NK069(tu)001:4206: smon pa byang chub kyi sems zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:4207: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:4209: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK069(tu)001:4210: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku gsum dang ldan pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:4211: sprul pa'i sku 'gro ba'i don la ngang ngam shugs kyis 'byung bas na /
NK069(tu)001:4212: sprul pa'i sku 'gro don dpag gis mi lang bar /
NK069(tu)001:4214: don phyogs myed du ma zhes bya bar gdags par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:4216: e ma'o ngo mtshor rmad kyi chos //
NK069(tu)001:4218: e ma'o ni ngam zhing ngo mtshar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:4220: theg pa gzhan gyis smad yang /
NK069(tu)001:4221: rang la thun mong ma yin pa'i dngos grub 'byung ba'i chos yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:4222: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK069(tu)001:4224: de ni rtsa sprul pa'i skur rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:4225: yi ge longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:4226: khams bdud rtsi'i thig le chos skur rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:4227: snying po rlung ngo bo nyid kyi skur rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:4230: sku bzhi kun gyi gsang ba'i don yin pas na gsang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:4234: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes ni /
NK069(tu)001:4236: 'o na gang du yang 'gro 'ong myed pa yin nam zhes na /
NK069(tu)001:4238: 'di ltar dngos po dang mtshan ma kun la khyab par gnas pas na /
NK069(tu)001:4239: 'gro dang 'ong zhes brtags pa tsam du zad do //
NK069(tu)001:4243: de ltar thams cad la khyab pa de yang ye
NK069(tu)001:4244: nas gnas pas 'gro 'ong nyid na 'gro 'ong myed
NK069(tu)001:4246: sems dang sems su snang ba yang de yin /
NK069(tu)001:4247: bya grub ye shes su sems bskyed pa de yin /
NK069(tu)001:4248: thabs kyi lam du sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:4249: thig le gyen la bzlog pa'i dga' ba ni 'gro 'ong du byung yang /
NK069(tu)001:4250: don gyi ngo bo la 'gro 'ong gang yang myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4251: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:4252: dang po gzhi sems nyid dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:4253: sems 'gro 'ong can du 'dod pa'i ma rig pa las log pa ni chos can /
NK069(tu)001:4254: yid kun btags kyi zhen pa dang bral ba ni chos nyid /
NK069(tu)001:4255: de gnyis dbyer myed pa gazhi'o //
NK069(tu)001:4257: don dam pa 'gro 'ong myed pa las /
NK069(tu)001:4258: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam du 'gro 'ong ltar yang snang /
NK069(tu)001:4259: de ltar snang tsam nyid na /
NK069(tu)001:4260: don dam pa dang kun rdzob tha mi dad pas na 'gro 'ong myed zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:4261: bzhi pa 'bras bu sku dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:4262: de ltar sprul skus 'gro ba sems can gyi don mdzad na yang /
NK069(tu)001:4263: sems can ltar skye shi myed pas na rdo rje'i sku zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:4264: de bas na chos kyi sku myed ci yang myi 'dra ba ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:4265: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku bde skyed dang che ba'i yon tan gang yang mi 'gog par spyod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4266: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku ni longs sku bde skyid gang yang spyod kyang /
NK069(tu)001:4267: sems can ltar dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin cing gnas pa myed pas mngon par byang chub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4268: sprul pa'i skus 'gro don byed pa'i dus na snying
NK069(tu)001:4269: rje dang snying rje'i yul tha dad du myi dmyigs
NK069(tu)001:4270: pa'o // de ltar don byed pa nyid sems can
NK069(tu)001:4271: ltar 'gro 'ong myed pa kho na rdo rje'i sku'o
NK069(tu)001:4272: pa'o // // de ltar go bar bya ba ni sems bskyed pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:4273: kun rdzob byang chub tu sems bskyed pa bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4274: 'di man chad kun rdzob tu sems bskyed pa bstan /
NK069(tu)001:4277: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang //
NK069(tu)001:4278: btsun mo'i tshogs thams cad kyang mnyes pas khyab par gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:4279: zhes pa de la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:4281: skyes pa tsam na skye ba myed /
NK069(tu)001:4283: gnas pa tsam na gnas pa myed /
NK069(tu)001:4284: dmyigs pa tsam na dmyigs pa myed /
NK069(tu)001:4285: 'gro 'ong tsam na 'gro 'ong myed pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:4286: de ltar su zhig gis rtogs pa de ni ye shes lngar blo bskyed cing /
NK069(tu)001:4287: sku lnga thob pa yin no zhes brjod pa la /
NK069(tu)001:4289: ye shes lnga thams cad la khyab par gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:4293: bde ba chen po'i dbang thun mong du bskur bas /
NK069(tu)001:4294: shes pa bde stong dbyer myed du nyams su myong de /
NK069(tu)001:4295: gzhi ji bzhin du son nas /
NK069(tu)001:4296: rdo rje gsang ba'i gral du 'khod pa ni mnyes pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:4297: gtso 'khor dgongs pa tha mi dad du gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4298: 'di man chad kun rdzob tu sems bskyed pa stan /
NK069(tu)001:4299: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:4301: btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas pas //
NK069(tu)001:4302: de ltar ston pas gleng slang ba de nas /
NK069(tu)001:4304: don dam du sems bskyed pa de nas /
NK069(tu)001:4305: kun rdzob tu sems bskyed pa ston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4306: 'khor gyis de bzhin gshegs pa yum dang bcas pa rnams kyis /
NK069(tu)001:4307: de ltar yin pa ma rtogs te /
NK069(tu)001:4308: sems can thams cad gsang ba bzhis mchod pas /
NK069(tu)001:4309: de'i don du thugs rje chen po bskyed la bcings
NK069(tu)001:4310: grol myed pa'i stan pa gsungs pa zhes brjod do
NK069(tu)001:4311: // ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:4313: gsang ba bzhis chod pa stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4314: e ma'o ye nas gsang ba'i chos //
NK069(tu)001:4316: e ma'o ni ngo mtshar che bas te /
NK069(tu)001:4318: chos thams cad sangs rgyas pa yang ngo mtshar che la /
NK069(tu)001:4319: de ltar ma rtogs pa yang ngo mtshar che ste /
NK069(tu)001:4320: sangs rgyas ba de yang da bzod sangs rgyas pa lta bu ma yin zhing /
NK069(tu)001:4321: ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:4322: ma rtogs pa yang bzod ma rtogs pa ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:4323: ye nas ma rtogs pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:4324: de lta bu de la ye thog ma nyid nas gsang ba'i chos zhes gsungs pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:4325: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang //
NK069(tu)001:4327: de ltar ma rtogs pa de kog tu sbas pa zhig yin nam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4329: rtogs par bya ba ni sna tshogs par snang ba 'di kun yin la /
NK069(tu)001:4330: de'i rang bzhin ma rtogs pas rang gsang chen por gyur pas na /
NK069(tu)001:4331: rang bzhin gyi gsang ba zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:4332: ngo bo nyid kyi rab tu gsang //
NK069(tu)001:4334: chos thams cad kun rdzob tu mtshan ma sna tshogs par snang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:4335: sku ngo bo nyid rang bzhin du sangs rgyas la /
NK069(tu)001:4336: don dam par rang bzhin myed par ni /
NK069(tu)001:4337: gsung ngo bo nyid kyi rang bzhin du sangs rgyas /
NK069(tu)001:4338: don dam pa dang kun rdzob dbyer myed pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4339: thugs ngo bo nyid kyi rang bzhin du sangs rgyas /
NK069(tu)001:4340: de ltar chos thams cad sku gsung thugs kyi ngo
NK069(tu)001:4341: bo nyid dam rang bzhin du gnas pa de ltar
NK069(tu)001:4342: ma rtogs pas na rab tu gsang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:4343: gzhan du min las shin du gsang //
NK069(tu)001:4345: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor bya ba de yang /
NK069(tu)001:4346: gzhan du myed de bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum du dag pa de yin la /
NK069(tu)001:4347: de shin du rtogs par dka' bas na shin tu gsang zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:4348: de ltar ma 'ong pa'i sems can 'di rnams la
NK069(tu)001:4349: bden pa dbyer myed kyi don rang chas su gnas
NK069(tu)001:4350: kyang / gsang ba bzhi po 'di rnams kyis chod pas ma rtogs pa 'di rnams /
NK069(tu)001:4351: kun tu bzang po'i zhal ma mthong dbang ma thob pas /
NK069(tu)001:4352: mthar thug gi 'bras bu mngon du byed mi nus te /
NK069(tu)001:4353: 'di rnams kyi don du lam rkyen gyi rgyud 'di nyid dang /
NK069(tu)001:4354: lam stegs kyi theg pa gzhan zhig gsung du gsol zhes zhus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4355: ston pa don du zhus pa 'di la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:4356: gzhi lam 'bras bur bsdus pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4357: snang ba bzhir bsdus pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4361: ye nas gsang bzhi'i gnas lugs de ngo bo nyid /
NK069(tu)001:4362: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang ba 'khrul bas rtags pa /
NK069(tu)001:4363: ngo bo nyid kyis gsang ba lam /
NK069(tu)001:4364: gzhan du min la gsang ba 'bras bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:4366: ye nas gsang ba rang bzhin gyi snang ba /
NK069(tu)001:4367: sna tshogs snang ba ma rtogs 'khrul pa'i snang ba /
NK069(tu)001:4368: ngo bo nyid kyis gsang ba gdul bya nyams kyi snang ba /
NK069(tu)001:4369: gzhan du min la gsang ba bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:4371: ye nas gsang ba don dam /
NK069(tu)001:4372: sna tshogs snang la rang bzhin gsang ba 'khrul pas btags pa /
NK069(tu)001:4373: ngo bo nyid kyis gsang ba dbyer myed /
NK069(tu)001:4374: gzhan du min las gsang ba dbyer myed spyod yul dang 'bral ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:4376: rang byung gi ye shes rang la rang chas su
NK069(tu)001:4377: yod kyang yod par ma shes pa ni ye nas
NK069(tu)001:4378: gsang ba / rang byung gi ye shes de nyid rtogs tshogs su rang snang la /
NK069(tu)001:4379: rtog tshogs thams cad sku gsung thugs mi bzad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor rang bzhin gyis gnas te /
NK069(tu)001:4380: de rtog pa sna tshogs kyis sgribs nas ma rtogs pa ni rang bzhin gyis gsang ba /
NK069(tu)001:4381: rang byung ye shes kyi ngo bo nyid yul sems
NK069(tu)001:4382: gnyis bden pa gnyis la sogs pa'i ngo bo gsum
NK069(tu)001:4383: du yang ma grub ste brjod pa tsam dang yang
NK069(tu)001:4384: bral bas / rang gi ngo bo nyid yul du ma dmigs te /
NK069(tu)001:4385: de ma rtogs pa ni ngo bo nyid kyis gsang ba /
NK069(tu)001:4386: de lta bu'i rang byung gi ye shes der sems nyid las gzhan myed pa bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:4389: lta ba'i sgrib pa rang la yod par ma rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:4390: gzhan nas tshol ba ni dbul mo'i gter ram gyad kyi nor bu dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:4391: gzhan nas myi rnyed pas shin du gsang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:4393: ye nas gsang ba chen po'i chos //
NK069(tu)001:4394: rang bzhin gsang bas gzhir 'gyur zhing //
NK069(tu)001:4395: don dam kun rdzob rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:4397: ngo bo nyid kyis lam gsang ba //
NK069(tu)001:4398: shin tu gsang bas 'bras bur rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:4401: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang /
NK069(tu)001:4402: 'dir thugs rje rang gi ngo bo sangs rgyas dang
NK069(tu)001:4403: sems can gnyis su myed par rtogs par stan te
NK069(tu)001:4404: / de bzhina gshegas pa thams cada ni 'das pa'i chos so //
NK069(tu)001:4405: thugs rje rang gi ngo bo stan /
NK069(tu)001:4406: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bo
NK069(tu)001:4407: nyid du gcig pa'i mtshan nyid pas dbyer myed na
NK069(tu)001:4409: chos thams cad ni 'khor ba'i chos so //
NK069(tu)001:4410: ye nas ni gzhi dngos po'i gnas lugs nas so //
NK069(tu)001:4411: sangs rgyas pa'i ngo bo nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:4412: don dam du chos skur sangs rgyas /
NK069(tu)001:4413: kun rdzob du sku gsung thugs mi bzad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor sangs rgyas /
NK069(tu)001:4415: sems can gyi sems rang gi ngo bo nyid sangs rgyas su gcig go //
NK069(tu)001:4416: thugs rje skye ba'i yul bstan /
NK069(tu)001:4417: 'gro ba'i rnam par rtog pa ma rig pa las /
NK069(tu)001:4419: thugs rje skye ba'i yul ni /
NK069(tu)001:4420: phyin ci log du 'gro ba rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:4421: de'i sems kyi rnam par rtog pa ni ma rig pa las yin te /
NK069(tu)001:4422: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pas gzhi lam gol /
NK069(tu)001:4423: kun tu btags pa'i ma rig pas mtshams sbyar nas /
NK069(tu)001:4424: 'gro ba lnga'i rigs bsam gyis mi khyab par smin pa las /
NK069(tu)001:4427: nyon mongs pa lnga'i dbang du 'gro ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:4428: nga rgyal dang 'phrag dog las lha /
NK069(tu)001:4433: ser sna dang nga rgyal ngo bo cig pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:4435: de re re yang rigs bsam gyis myi khyab pas /
NK069(tu)001:4436: las dang bag chags su bcas par smin no //
NK069(tu)001:4437: thugs rje skye tshul lam thabs stan pa /
NK069(tu)001:4438: thugs rje chen pos sangs rgyas kyi ye shes chen po skyes nas /
NK069(tu)001:4439: zhes myi dmyigs pa'i thugs rje rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:4440: rtag pa rgyun du skye ba'i thugs rje ni chu
NK069(tu)001:4441: bo'i rgyun ltar chad pa myed par skyes pa dang
NK069(tu)001:4442: / rang bzhin shugs kyis skye ba'i thugs rje nyi ma'i 'od dang 'dra /
NK069(tu)001:4443: skul zhing gsol ba btab pas skye ba'i thugs rje ni /
NK069(tu)001:4444: sprang po zas skom slong ba lta bu /
NK069(tu)001:4445: yul dang phrad nas skye ba'i thugs rje ni mdzes
NK069(tu)001:4446: sprang rkang chad lag rdum dang phrad pa ltar skye'o
NK069(tu)001:4447: // de yang sems nyid sangs rgyas su ye nas
NK069(tu)001:4448: sangs rgyas par shes pa'i thugs rje chen po gzhan
NK069(tu)001:4450: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:4451: thugs rje chen pos sangs rgyas kyi ye shes chen po skyes nas /
NK069(tu)001:4453: gong du yab yum gleng slang ba de /
NK069(tu)001:4454: 'gro ba'i don du gleng slang ba myin nam /
NK069(tu)001:4455: yin na da sdod thugs rje skyes pa dang 'gal la /
NK069(tu)001:4456: 'gro ba'i don du gleng slang ba myen na /
NK069(tu)001:4457: gleng gang gi don du slang zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4459: gong ma yang 'gro ba'i don du kleng ba yin yang /
NK069(tu)001:4460: 'gro ba la 'khor gyis rgyud bshad par ma zhus pas 'gal ba myed /
NK069(tu)001:4461: 'dir 'gro ba'i don du bshad par zhus pas /
NK069(tu)001:4462: thugs rje chen pos sangs rgyas kyi ye shes chen po sems can la skyes pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:4463: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:4465: 'gro ba 'khrul pa ma rtogs pa rnams kyi don ched du 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:4466: gang gi don du bshad pa'i 'khrul tshul bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4467: e ma'o bde gshegs snying po las /
NK069(tu)001:4469: e ma'o ni ngom pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:4470: snang ba mthar thug cig las myed pa las du mar 'khrul ba la ngam pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4472: sems nyid la gnyis su snang ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:4473: gzhi don gyi kun gzhi ni rang bzhin rnam dag gi ngo bo ste /
NK069(tu)001:4474: 'das pa bskyed par byed pa'i rgyu'i snying po'o //
NK069(tu)001:4475: sbyor ba don gyi kun gzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:4476: bag chags sog pa'i gnas te /
NK069(tu)001:4477: 'khor ba skyed par byed pa'i rgyu'o //
NK069(tu)001:4479: 'dir bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ni /
NK069(tu)001:4480: gzhi don gyi kun gzhi la bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:4481: spros pa'i zug rngu dang bral ba 'das pa'i rgyu de las /
NK069(tu)001:4482: de nyid 'khrul gzhir gyur pa de las so //
NK069(tu)001:4483: rang gi rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK069(tu)001:4484: zhes pa rgyu gang las na /
NK069(tu)001:4485: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas kyi rgyu can las so //
NK069(tu)001:4487: rang gi rnam rtog gi nyon mongs pa lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:4489: kyis ces pa byed pa'i tshig yin te /
NK069(tu)001:4490: rgyu rkyen gnyis kyis 'bras bu dngos po bshis la myed pa gcig blo bur du sprul zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:4491: sna tshogs lus dang longs spyod dang //
NK069(tu)001:4494: lus sna tshogs ni bzang ngan che chung can la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4495: de yang bsdu na drug ste /
NK069(tu)001:4497: lha ma yin sprul pa'i lus /
NK069(tu)001:4498: mi dang byol song sha khrag gi lus /
NK069(tu)001:4499: yi dwags rtsa dbugs kyi lus /
NK069(tu)001:4500: dmyal ba las kyi lus so //
NK069(tu)001:4501: longs spyod sna tshogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4503: 'thab rtsod lha ma yin gyi longs spyod /
NK069(tu)001:4505: sdug bsngal byol song gi longs spyod /
NK069(tu)001:4506: ser sna yi dwags kyi longs spyod de /
NK069(tu)001:4507: gtso bsreg sbrebs pa'i tsha grang gi sdug bsngal la gnas pa dmyal ba'i longs spyod do //
NK069(tu)001:4508: gnas dang sdug bsngal la sogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:4511: lha la dga' ldan gyi gnas dang /
NK069(tu)001:4512: lha ma yin la 'thab rtsod kyi gnas dang /
NK069(tu)001:4514: byol song nyams ldan gyi gnas dang /
NK069(tu)001:4515: yi dwags mid ldan gyi gnas dang /
NK069(tu)001:4516: dmyal ba bzod ldan gyi gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:4518: lha la ltung ba'i sdug bsngal /
NK069(tu)001:4520: mi la spyi dang bye brag /
NK069(tu)001:4521: spyir skye rgas na 'chi bye brag brgyad do //
NK069(tu)001:4525: sogs ni bye brag mi 'dra ba du ma yod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4526: bdag dang bdag gir so sor 'dzin //
NK069(tu)001:4528: phyi gzung ba'i yul la bdag gis 'dzin /
NK069(tu)001:4530: dgra zun la sogs pa so sor 'dzin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4531: sus kyang ma bcings bcings myed de //
NK069(tu)001:4536: 'ching bar byed pa'i rtson rdzi lta bu'am /
NK069(tu)001:4537: bcings par bya ba yod ma yin //
NK069(tu)001:4538: bcing par bya ba'i brtson lta bu yang yod pa ma yin /
NK069(tu)001:4540: de ltar bdag gzhan du 'dzin pa'i dus na yang /
NK069(tu)001:4541: gzhan su zhig gis bcings pa ma yin pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4545: don dam par bcing bar bya ba'i gzhi yang yod pa ma yin no //
NK069(tu)001:4546: rnam rtog bdag tu 'dzin pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:4549: rang gi rnam par rtog pas bdag gzhan du 'dzin pa des bcings /
NK069(tu)001:4552: nam gyi mkha' la mdud pa 'dor //
NK069(tu)001:4554: mi snyon pas nam mkha' stong pa la mdud pa 'dor ba dang 'dra ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:4555: thang phrom zos pa'i mis nam ka la skra shad 'jag par mthong ba ltar /
NK069(tu)001:4556: rang sems stong pa la 'khrul pa'i mdud pa 'dor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:4557: dngos pa gang bshad pa'i tshul lo //
NK069(tu)001:4558: bcings myed rnam par grol myed pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:4562: cings pa myed pas na gro ba yang myed /
NK069(tu)001:4563: de ltar bcings pa myed tsam na /
NK069(tu)001:4564: de las ltos pa'i grol ba yang myed pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:4565: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK069(tu)001:4568: chos thams cad ye nas sku dang ye shes kyi
NK069(tu)001:4569: dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa
NK069(tu)001:4570: de rang bzhin rnam dag gi ngo bo yang yin
NK069(tu)001:4571: / rgyud dag pa'i sangs rgyas kyis thugs su chud pa'i chos yang de yin /
NK069(tu)001:4572: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa rdzogs pa chen por sangs rgyas pa yang de yin no //
NK069(tu)001:4573: stan phyir spro ba sna tshogs mdzad //
NK069(tu)001:4575: de'i don stan pa'i phyir ram /
NK069(tu)001:4576: de'i 'jug pa'i lam stegs stan pa'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:4578: theg pa sna tshogs zhig spro bar mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4579: zhes de bzhin gshegs pa nyid /
NK069(tu)001:4581: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched du gleng ngo //
NK069(tu)001:4584: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:4585: 'dir bcing grol myed pa'i chos gsung bar byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:4586: 'og tu rdzogs chen gyi chos lta bu zhig 'ong la thang pa la /
NK069(tu)001:4587: ma h+aa yo ga'i lta bsgom lnga byung ba dang 'gal /
NK069(tu)001:4591: yo ga ba 'am kri ya ltar rang la myed
NK069(tu)001:4592: pa gcig rtsal nas kun btags su rang rgyud par
NK069(tu)001:4593: sgom pa lta bu min te /
NK069(tu)001:4594: lha nyid rang la rtog tshogs su yod pa kho
NK069(tu)001:4595: na bcings grol myed pa'i chos yin par shes par
NK069(tu)001:4596: bya'o // gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:4597: zhes gsang ba ni rtogs par dka' ba /
NK069(tu)001:4599: de kho na nyid ni chos thams cad kyi de kho nyid /
NK069(tu)001:4600: nges pa ni yang dag pa'i nges pa'i don kho na'o //
NK069(tu)001:4601: don dam pa dang kun rdzob kyi byang chub kyi
NK069(tu)001:4602: sems ye shes su bskyed pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o
NK069(tu)001:4605: skye ba myed las thams cad skyes ces pa la sogs ni /
NK069(tu)001:4606: don dam par sems bskyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4608: yab yum gyi thig le dkar dmar ni /
NK069(tu)001:4609: kun rdzob du sems bskyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4610: bde stong nyams su myong ba ni don dam du sems bskyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4611: sems can gyi sems ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ye shes su blo bskyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4612: gleng slangs bas sems bskyed 'byung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:4613: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las /
NK069(tu)001:4616: le'u gnyis par 'og min gyi ston pa mthong ba'i skal ba myed pa /
NK069(tu)001:4617: gsang ba bzhi ma rtogs pa rnams la stan pa spro bar zhus pas /
NK069(tu)001:4618: spro bar mdzad pa'i barjesa de nas so //
NK069(tu)001:4619: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las ni /
NK069(tu)001:4620: kun tu bzang po rgyal ba thams cad kyi spyi gzugs can las so //
NK069(tu)001:4621: thugs rje chen po'i byin gyis brlabs zhes bya ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:4623: dper na nyi ma bar snang la shar bas 'od 'dzam bu gling du gsal ba de /
NK069(tu)001:4624: nyi ma nyid yin nam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4625: nyi ma'i byin rlabs yin bya ba dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:4626: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rje'i byin rlabs sam /
NK069(tu)001:4627: rang bzhin nyid thub pa chen po drug lhar snang ba la bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:4628: rig pa'i skyes bu thub pa drug /
NK069(tu)001:4630: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las thon to //
NK069(tu)001:4632: mnyam pa nyid kyi don rig pa'i dus so //
NK069(tu)001:4633: skyes bu ni byang chub sems las skyes pas skyes bu /
NK069(tu)001:4634: thub pa ni lus ngag yid gsum gsungs pa myed par thub pa /
NK069(tu)001:4635: drug ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul pa grangs myed na yang /
NK069(tu)001:4636: thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don bya ba'i gnas 'jig rten drug yod pas /
NK069(tu)001:4637: de dang sbyar ba'i sprul pa drug stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4638: lha la thub pa chen po srid thub 'dzin dang /
NK069(tu)001:4639: lha ma yin la rnam par rgyal ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:4641: byol song la rnam par gnon dang /
NK069(tu)001:4642: dmyal ba la chos kyi rgyal po'o //
NK069(tu)001:4643: sprul sku 'jig rten du snang bar gyur pa tsam la thon te zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:4644: le'u gsum pa la ngag don du gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:4645: gtan la 'bebs pa'i phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4646: gtan la phab pa'i chos so //
NK069(tu)001:4647: gtan la 'bebs pa ni lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:4652: gdul bya gang gi don mdzad zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:4653: sprul pa gang las phyung na /
NK069(tu)001:4654: ston pa rdo rje 'chang kun tu bzang po'i sku gsung thugs las phyung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:4656: thub pa drug gi ston no //
NK069(tu)001:4658: stong gsum gyi stong chen po 'jig rten gyi khams rnams su ston no //
NK069(tu)001:4661: 'gro ba sems can lnga'i don mdzad /
NK069(tu)001:4662: gdul bya gang gi don byed na /
NK069(tu)001:4663: nyon mongs pa stong phrag brgya bcu rtsa bzhi'i gnyen por /
NK069(tu)001:4664: chos kyi sgo mo stong phrag brgya bcu rtsa bzhi gsungs so //
NK069(tu)001:4665: gtan la phab pa'i chos ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:4666: theg pa spyi'i gnas lugs dang /
NK069(tu)001:4669: thon nas kyang las kyi dbang gis /
NK069(tu)001:4676: zhes pa thon nas kyang ces pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4678: sems can gyi las la dge sdig gnyis dpyad pa'i
NK069(tu)001:4679: dbang gis gnas yang mi mthun pa ston pas na
NK069(tu)001:4681: gzhi ni ljid phred du phebs pas te thad ka'o //
NK069(tu)001:4685: le'u dang po gleng gzhi byung /
NK069(tu)001:4687: gsum par yang gleng gzhi byung bas /
NK069(tu)001:4690: le'u dang po rang bzhin gyi snang ba la dgongs /
NK069(tu)001:4691: gnyis par de bzhin gshegs pas rang gi sa go yang /
NK069(tu)001:4692: 'gro ba 'khrul pa la chos bshad par zhus pas /
NK069(tu)001:4693: bde bar gshegs pa'i snang ba la dgongs so //
NK069(tu)001:4694: 'og min mthong ba'i skal ba myed pa la sprul sku stan pas /
NK069(tu)001:4695: le'u gsum par sprul sku'i gleng gzhi ston no //
NK069(tu)001:4696: 'di man chad 'khrul pa'i snang ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4697: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu myed pa'i stong gsum gyi stong chen po re rer /
NK069(tu)001:4699: phyi snod 'jig pa la nang bcud 'jig pa rten pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4700: drug ni rigs drug gi gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:4701: de re re la yang phyogs bcu'o //
NK069(tu)001:4704: mtshon pa tsam du grangs bzung na gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:4705: gling bzhi gling phran mtha' lcags ris skor ba steng 'og dang bcas pa /
NK069(tu)001:4706: gcig nas gnyis su grangs pa stong la /
NK069(tu)001:4708: stong spyi phud kyi 'jig rten gyi khams so //
NK069(tu)001:4709: stong chung rgyun gcig nas gnyis su grangs pa stong
NK069(tu)001:4710: pa ni stong 'bring po 'am stong gnyis pa bar
NK069(tu)001:4711: ma zhes bya'o // stong 'bring po gcig nas gnyis
NK069(tu)001:4712: su grangs pa stong la ni stong gsum gyi stong
NK069(tu)001:4714: stong gsum gyi stong chen po de lta bu gnas re re zhes bya ba'i don te /
NK069(tu)001:4719: gdul bya'i snang ba dang btun pa'i ston pa ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:4720: ji snyad par bstan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4723: dper na zla ba gcig las myed yang /
NK069(tu)001:4724: chu snod brgya rtsa brgyad du snang ba ltar /
NK069(tu)001:4725: sprul pa gcig gis gdul bya kun la snang bar sprul lo //
NK069(tu)001:4727: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sprul pas 'jig rten khams gcig
NK069(tu)001:4728: tu yang bsam gyis mi khyab pas don mdzad de
NK069(tu)001:4729: / re shig mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i lugs kyis mi srid pa'i tshes bzhi dang /
NK069(tu)001:4730: myi 'gal bar bya ba'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:4731: mdzad pa mthar phyin pa'i sprul sku re res don mdzad par stan pa'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:4732: re res zhes smos pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:4736: de ltar don mdzad pa de yang nan gyis byed pa ma yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:4741: dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4745: de dag kun kyang 'di lta ste /
NK069(tu)001:4749: rdzu 'phrul gyi 'dul ba ni mngon shes so //
NK069(tu)001:4750: bsod nams ni dge ba la 'dzud pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4751: rig pas ni rig pa dang mi 'gal bar phyin ci log yong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:4755: 'gro ba rigs drug re re'i nang na nyon mongs pa lnga tshang ba la dgongs pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:4756: gti mug gi mun pa sel /
NK069(tu)001:4759: d+harma tsanyatra &&&'am btang snyoms don grub /
NK069(tu)001:4764: byang chub kyi shing klag sha la 'jus nas 'chan khung g.yas su sku ltam mo //
NK069(tu)001:4766: zhes mchod rten rnam dag gi rtsar /
NK069(tu)001:4767: rang gi dbu skra rang gis bzhar te 'khor ba las rab tu byung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:4769: zhes chu bo na ra dza ra'i 'gram du dka' thub lo bdun mdzad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4771: zhes yul ma h+aa bo der rdo rje'i gdan la sangs rgyas /
NK069(tu)001:4772: yang na rdo rje gdan la srod la bdud btul /
NK069(tu)001:4775: zhes de nas yul ma ga dar bdud bzhi btul nas rgol ba ngan tshar gcod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4776: chos kyi 'khor lo skor ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:4777: zhes de nas yul ba ra na ser bden pa bzhi'i chos kyi 'khor lo skor /
NK069(tu)001:4778: bya rgod phung po'i ri la mtshan ma myed pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo skor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:4779: cho 'phrul chen po bstan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4780: zhes de nas yul gnyan yod du cho 'phrul chen
NK069(tu)001:4781: po bstan nas mu stegs kyi ston pa drug btul
NK069(tu)001:4782: lo // mdzad pa bcu gnyis la ngag don du gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:4785: 'jig rten pa'i mdzad pa ni drug ste /
NK069(tu)001:4787: kun tu bzang po'i thugs las ye shes kyi rtsal shar nas yum gyi lhums su zhugs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4789: dga' ldan gyi gnas nas sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa' dam pa tog dkar po la /
NK069(tu)001:4790: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyis skul nas /
NK069(tu)001:4791: 'jig rten sems can gyi don mdzad pa bzhi la gzigs nas lhums su zhugs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4792: gnyis pa sku ltam pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4794: byang chub kyi shing klag sha la yum gyi phyag g.yas pa 'jus nas /
NK069(tu)001:4795: ma'i mchan khung g.yas su sku ltam /
NK069(tu)001:4796: de la lha ka shi kas lag tu blangs /
NK069(tu)001:4797: tshangs pa dang brgya byin gyis pha ma'i tshul du byas /
NK069(tu)001:4798: klu'i rgyal pos ri rab kyi byang phyogs d+har na 'dzin nas chu blangs nas sku khrus gsol /
NK069(tu)001:4799: bram ze mtshan mkhan la mtshan btags /
NK069(tu)001:4800: ming rgyal bu don thams cad grub par btags so //
NK069(tu)001:4801: gsum pa gzhon nu rol rtsed mdzad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4802: rang gi na mnyam dang rol rtsed mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4803: bzhi pa 'jig rten pa'i slob dpon mdzad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4804: gzo dang rigs byed thams cad slabs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4805: lnga pa rgyal srid gzung ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:4806: sh+aakya'i lag na be con gyi bu mo shag gza' sa mtsho ma khab tu bzhes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4807: drug pa rab tu byung ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:4808: grong khyer skyid pa'i 'byung gnas kyi sgo bzhir skye rgas na 'chi sdug bsngal mthong nas /
NK069(tu)001:4809: khyim nas khyim myed par rab tu 'byung bzhed pa la ma btang ba la /
NK069(tu)001:4810: rgyal po bzhis nam mkha' la spyan drangs nas /
NK069(tu)001:4811: mchod rten rnam dag gi rtsar rang gi dbu skra rang rig bzhar nas rab tu byung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:4812: 'das pa'i mdzad pa ni drug ste /
NK069(tu)001:4813: dang po dka' thub mdzad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4814: chu bo ne ra dza ra'i 'gram du dka' thub
NK069(tu)001:4815: lo gsum du 'bras sa lu ljang pa re dang
NK069(tu)001:4817: lo gsum du ci yang ma gsol yang bskres shing snyel ba myed do //
NK069(tu)001:4818: gnyis pa bdud btul ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:4819: yul ma ga d+ha ra bdud bzhi btul te /
NK069(tu)001:4820: lha me tog gi mda' can dang /
NK069(tu)001:4821: lha mo mdzes sdug rten pa gnyis rang sar btul lo //
NK069(tu)001:4822: gsum pa sangs rgyas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4823: yul ma h+aa b+ho dir rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin brnyes te sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4824: bzhi pa chos kyi 'khor lo skor ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:4825: yul ba ra na ser bden pa bzhi gsungs /
NK069(tu)001:4826: bya rgod phung po'i ri la yum chen mo gsungs so //
NK069(tu)001:4827: lnga pa cho 'phrul chen po bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4828: yul gnyen yod kyi gling du mu stegs kyi ston pa drug btul nas /
NK069(tu)001:4830: drug pa mya ngan las 'das pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4831: grong khyer rtsa mchog tu sku mya ngan las 'das nas /
NK069(tu)001:4832: sku gdung dang ring srel bsgos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4833: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:4834: chos kyi 'khor lo skor ba dang ces pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4836: skus chos kyi 'khor lo skor bar mi 'thad zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4837: sku bzhugs tsam na chos gsungs pa de sku'i mdzad pa /
NK069(tu)001:4838: gsung pa de spo ti glegs bam la bsdus pa de gsung gi mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4839: yang na mngon sum gyis 'dul ba'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:4840: chos kyi 'khor lo bka' rim pa gsum du skor la /
NK069(tu)001:4841: rigs pas 'dul ba'i dus na stong phrag brgya bcu la sogs pa gsungs pas yang mi 'gal lo //
NK069(tu)001:4842: mya ngan las 'das pa la sogs par /
NK069(tu)001:4843: bde byed gzhon nu'am khams gsum bde rgyas so //
NK069(tu)001:4845: zhes yul yangs pa can gyi nye 'khor na /
NK069(tu)001:4846: shing sa la zung gcig gi tshal du mya ngan las 'das te /
NK069(tu)001:4847: bsogs pa ni sku gdung dgos pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4849: gzhon nu rol rtsed mdzad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4851: 'jig rten gyi slob dpon mdzad pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:4852: mdor na ma tshang ba rnams bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:4853: dus kyi mngon shes bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4854: dus bzhi kun tu mkhyen pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4855: zhes nang gi mngon shes ni /
NK069(tu)001:4859: 'byung bar ma nges pa'i gnas tha mi dad de /
NK069(tu)001:4863: sngon gyi gtan tshigs rnams zhag gsum lon pa lta bu'i dus bzhin dran /
NK069(tu)001:4864: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:4865: dus bzhi thad kar mkhyen na mngon shes su mi 'gro /
NK069(tu)001:4866: tha mi dad du mkhyen na yang rtag pa gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:4867: dngos po'i gnas lugs la ma yin pa cig tha
NK069(tu)001:4868: mi dad du mkhyen na rgyal ba'i dgongs pa kun
NK069(tu)001:4869: btags su 'gro / dngos po'i gnas lugs la yin pa cig tha mi dad du mkhyen na /
NK069(tu)001:4871: skye myed du mkhyen na de mngon shes su mi 'gro /
NK069(tu)001:4873: dper na chos can chags shing lta bu gcig la /
NK069(tu)001:4874: 'das pa yal ga lo ma can dang /
NK069(tu)001:4875: ma 'ongs pa mer bus na thal bar 'gro ba gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:4876: da lta'i chags shing la ji ltar sgrub zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4878: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dngos nas sgrubs na snang ba tha dad 'di brtsal na ma rnyed pas na /
NK069(tu)001:4879: da ltar gyi chags shing la 'das ma 'ongs gnyis tshang /
NK069(tu)001:4880: stong pa la tha dad myed pa'i phyir yang da ltar 'das ma 'ongs gnyis tshang /
NK069(tu)001:4881: bsams na snang du rung ba'i phyir yang da ltar la 'das ma 'ongs gnyis tshang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:4883: 'das ma 'ongs da ltar gsum gcig gi go sa gcig gis ma bkag ste /
NK069(tu)001:4884: de nyid las gzhan du 'gyur ba yang ma yin no //
NK069(tu)001:4885: pha rol gyi sems shes pa'i mngon shes bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4886: thams cad kyi sems nyid kyi rgyud kun tu mkhyen pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4888: pha rol gyi sems shes pa'i mngon shes ni /
NK069(tu)001:4889: sems can 'di ni zhe sdang can no //
NK069(tu)001:4894: 'di ni zhe sdang dang bral ba'o 'am /
NK069(tu)001:4895: 'di ni dug lnga dang bral ba'o zhes /
NK069(tu)001:4896: sems kyi rgyud tha dad pa rnams mkhyen pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4897: spyan gyi mngon shes bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4898: rdzu 'phrul gyi spyan gyis thams cad du gzigs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4899: zhes pa la spyan gyi mngon shes ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:4901: sangs rgyas rnams nyid kyi gnas gang na bzhugs pa mthong /
NK069(tu)001:4903: snod bcud che chung can rnams dper na skyu ru
NK069(tu)001:4904: ra rlon pa lag thil du gzhag pa ltar mthong
NK069(tu)001:4905: / snyan gyi mngon shes bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4906: rdzu 'phrul gyi snyan gyis kun tu bsan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4907: zhes snyan gyi mngon shes ni /
NK069(tu)001:4908: sangs rgyas kyi gsung zhing khams tha dad pa ltar na sgrogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4909: sems can so so'i skad mi cig pa rnams thos pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4910: dper na da ltar rang gi rna ba'i drung na 'khod pa ltar thos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4912: rdzu 'phrul gyi cho gas kun tu spyod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4913: zhes rdzu 'phrul gyi mngon shes bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:4914: sems can gang la gang 'dul la /
NK069(tu)001:4915: sangs rgyas 'khor dang bcas pas cho 'phrul rnam pa
NK069(tu)001:4916: sna tshogs bstan nas sems can de'i don byed pa'o
NK069(tu)001:4917: // zag pa myed pa'i spyod pa rdzogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4918: zag pa myed pa'i kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa /
NK069(tu)001:4919: zhes mngon shes kyi khyad par ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:4920: zag pa dang bcas pa phyogs cig pa'i mngon shes ni /
NK069(tu)001:4921: 'jig rten gyi lha klu'i mngon shes lta bu ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:4922: 'gro ba ma lus pa'i don mdzad yang rang la zag pa myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4923: yongs su rdzogs pa'i mngon par shes pa chen po drug dang /
NK069(tu)001:4924: zhes ci'i phyir zag pa myed na /
NK069(tu)001:4925: 'gro ba'i don la blang dor myed de kun tu bzang po'i spyod pa rdzogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:4926: tshogs gnyis rdzogs par gyur pas zag pa myed do //
NK069(tu)001:4928: lkog tu gyur pa'i don mngon du shes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4931: drug ni thun mong ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:4937: rdzu 'phrul gyi mngon shes dang drug go //
NK069(tu)001:4938: 'dir mngon shes la gags gsal na /
NK069(tu)001:4939: zag myed kyi mngon shes la /
NK069(tu)001:4940: rdzu 'phrul du 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ci yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4941: rdzu 'phrul shan pa'i gzugs su sprul yang sdig pas mi gos pas zag pa myed /
NK069(tu)001:4942: shan pa dang sman 'tshong mas 'dul bar shes na yang der sprul bas na rdzu 'phrul lo //
NK069(tu)001:4943: mngon par shes so chen po drug zer yang lnga las ma byung ba ci zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4944: mngon shes lnga kun tu bzang po'i spyod pas 'dul ba dang drug gam /
NK069(tu)001:4945: yang na dus mkhyen pa la gnas mkhyen pa dabye'o //
NK069(tu)001:4946: kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4947: zhes zhi bas 'dul ba la zhi ba'i skur ston /
NK069(tu)001:4948: khro bos 'dul ba la khro bo'i skur ston /
NK069(tu)001:4953: gcan gzan la sogs pa gang la gang 'dul du ston pas na /
NK069(tu)001:4955: kun tu thugs bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4957: zhi ba'i sems kyis thul na dang ba'i sems dang /
NK069(tu)001:4958: rgyas pa'i thugs kyis 'dul na dga' ba'i sems dang /
NK069(tu)001:4959: dbang gi thugs kyis 'dul na chags pa'i sems dang /
NK069(tu)001:4960: drag pos 'dul na khros pa'i sems te /
NK069(tu)001:4961: thugs bsam gyis mi khyab par zad do //
NK069(tu)001:4962: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:4964: mngon sum gyis 'dul ba mdzad pa bcu gnyis bstan /
NK069(tu)001:4965: rdzu 'phrul gyis 'dul ba mngon par shes pa lnga'am drug tu bstan /
NK069(tu)001:4966: bsod nams kyis 'dul ba la bsam gyis mi khyab pa bzhir bstan /
NK069(tu)001:4967: rig pas 'dul ba la lha mi'i theg pa la sogs pa'i chos gsungs pa la /
NK069(tu)001:4968: gong ma'am gzhan rnams bsam gyis mi khyab par 'dus sam ma 'dus /
NK069(tu)001:4970: ma 'dus na bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang 'gal zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:4972: rgyud 'di'i tshig gi dbang du byas pa ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:4973: 'gro ba tha dad kyi bsam pa la dgongs pa'i dbang du byas pas 'gal ba myed do //
NK069(tu)001:4974: kun tu zhal bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4975: zhes pa zhal gyis 'dul bar dgongs na /
NK069(tu)001:4977: za byed stag gi zhal dang /
NK069(tu)001:4978: gtum pa dom gyi zhal dang /
NK069(tu)001:4979: myos byed phag gi gdong dang /
NK069(tu)001:4980: mgyogs myur rta'i zhal la sogs pa sna tshogs par ston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:4981: kun tu gsung bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:4982: zhes gsung gis 'dul bar dgongs na /
NK069(tu)001:4983: lha 'dus na sang kri ta'i skad dang /
NK069(tu)001:4984: lha ma yin la a su ram b+ha'i skad dang /
NK069(tu)001:4985: mi la pra tri ta 'jig rten phal pa'i skad dang /
NK069(tu)001:4986: lha srin la b+he sha tsi pa sha za yi
NK069(tu)001:4987: dwags kyi skad la sogs pa sna tshogs par ston
NK069(tu)001:4988: pa'o // bsam gyis mi khyab pa grangs myed pa phyogs bcur snang bar gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:4989: zhes pas de ltar skus 'dul na kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab ste /
NK069(tu)001:4990: sangs rgyas chu bo gang+ga'i bye ma bas kyang mang /
NK069(tu)001:4991: gsung gis 'dul na gsung bsam yas te /
NK069(tu)001:4992: thams cad kyi skad du ston /
NK069(tu)001:4995: mdor na gdul bya la grangs myed pas /
NK069(tu)001:4996: 'dul byed la yang grangs myed la /
NK069(tu)001:4997: 'dul thabs la yang grangs myed de /
NK069(tu)001:4998: phyogs bcur khyab par snang ba kho na'o //
NK069(tu)001:4999: 'dir gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:5000: bsam gyis mi khyab pa de /
NK069(tu)001:5001: gdul bya re re la re re ston pa yin nam myin /
NK069(tu)001:5002: gdul bya re re la 'dul byed re re ston na /
NK069(tu)001:5003: gong gi thub pa drug dang grangs 'gal /
NK069(tu)001:5004: mi ston na bsam gyis myi khyab pa dang 'gal zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:5006: thub pa drug gcig la yang bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i 'dul thabs 'di rnams dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5007: 'o na sku bsam gyis myi khyab par sprul na /
NK069(tu)001:5008: shan pa'i gzugs su sprul lam mi sprul /
NK069(tu)001:5009: sprul na shan pa byed dgos /
NK069(tu)001:5010: ma byas na sprul pa la dgos pa myed /
NK069(tu)001:5011: shan pa byed na sangs rgyas yang ngan 'gro'i sdig spyod du thal /
NK069(tu)001:5013: gsad gso nus pa'i shan pa byed pa la 'gal ba myed la /
NK069(tu)001:5014: bsad gso mi nus pa'i shan pa myed na bsam
NK069(tu)001:5015: gyis myi khyab pa'i go ba dang 'gal bas shan
NK069(tu)001:5016: pa byed de / bsad gso nus pas so //
NK069(tu)001:5017: de bas na bsod nams kyis btul nas dge ba la 'god pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:5018: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i yon tan gyi mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5019: de dag thams cad kyang 'di ltar te /
NK069(tu)001:5022: 'jig rten pa'i theg pa bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5023: lha dang mi'i theg pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5024: zhes pa de dag ni gong du 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i tshul bstan pa rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:5025: thams cad ni gong ma ma lus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5026: 'di ltar te ni 'dul thabs stan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5027: gdul bya so so'i sngon gyi las 'phro dang snod du sbyar nas 'dul ba'i dbang gis na'o //
NK069(tu)001:5028: lha dang mi'i theg pa la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:5032: lta ba ni phyal ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:5038: tshangs pa'i gnas bzhi bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5039: dge ba bcu spyod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5044: kha 'don la sogs pa byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5045: yang na lus kyi sgo nas /
NK069(tu)001:5046: ma byin pa len pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5047: mi tshangs pa spyod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5057: log par lta ba gsum spong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5059: bu gcig pa'i ma lta bu'i byams pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5060: bdag gi bde ba dang gzhan gyi sdug bsngal barje phod pa'i snying rje dang /
NK069(tu)001:5061: bde bas kun la khyab par 'dod pa'i dga' ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:5062: kun la snyoms par 'dod pa'i btang snyoms so //
NK069(tu)001:5063: 'bras bu ni bsam gtan bzhi la sogs pa'i mtho ris kyi lha gnas thob pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5065: myi dge bcu las zlog byed cing //
NK069(tu)001:5066: tshad myed bzhir bcas bsam gtan bzhi //
NK069(tu)001:5067: lha dang mi yi gnas rdzogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:5068: dge tshogs kun nas ma sgribs pa //
NK069(tu)001:5069: legs spyad sdom pa bzang las byung //
NK069(tu)001:5070: las kyi bag chags dag byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5072: 'das pa'i theg pa bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5073: nyan thos kyi theg pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5074: zhes pa mos pa chung ba'i nyan thos la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:5076: gang zag dang chos kyi bdag gnyis yod par 'dod /
NK069(tu)001:5077: lam ni bden pa bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:5078: sdug bsngal gyi bden pa ni shas par 'dod /
NK069(tu)001:5079: kun 'byung gi bden pa ni spong bar 'dod /
NK069(tu)001:5080: 'gog pa'i bden pa mngon du bya bar 'dod /
NK069(tu)001:5081: lam gyi bden pa rgyud la rten par 'dod /
NK069(tu)001:5082: de la sdug bsngal dang kun 'byung gnyis ni 'khor ba'i chos gtan la 'bebs /
NK069(tu)001:5083: 'gog pa dang lam gyis mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos su 'dod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5089: de yang sgyu 'phrul rol pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:5092: rgyu dang 'bras bu rnam dag pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:5093: rgyun zhugs lan cig phyir 'ong dang //
NK069(tu)001:5094: mi ldog dgra bcom brtul shugs mchog /
NK069(tu)001:5097: lha dang mi'i theg pa dang ces pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5098: gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i ces pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5099: 'dul ba mdo sde ces lan gsum brdabs so zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:5101: 'dul ba'i dbang ni theg pa'i ming ngam rnam grangs so //
NK069(tu)001:5103: theg pa'i don bstan pa'i tshul yin la /
NK069(tu)001:5104: 'dul ba mdo sde ni rgyud 'di'i che ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:5105: 'dir 'jug pa'i lam stegs lta bu bstan pas brdabs pa myed do //
NK069(tu)001:5106: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5107: zhes dmyigs pa phra ba'i rang sangs rgyas ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:5110: chos kyi khams phyogs gcig la bdag myed par rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5127: rang sangs rgyas gzung ba'i yul spangs pas phyi mi 'dod do //
NK069(tu)001:5132: ma rig pa'i rkyen gyis 'du byed /
NK069(tu)001:5133: 'du byed kyi rkyen gyis rnam par shes pa /
NK069(tu)001:5134: de bzhin du ming dang gzugs /
NK069(tu)001:5143: de ni 'khor ba'i rgyu 'bras thabs dang ces par 'dod do //
NK069(tu)001:5146: keng rus kyi ri rab 'di ci las byung rtags shi ba las byung /
NK069(tu)001:5147: shi ba gang las byung rtags pas /
NK069(tu)001:5149: tha ma ma rig pa la thug te /
NK069(tu)001:5151: de ni mya ngan las 'das pa'i rgyu 'bras blang bya thabs dang bcas par 'dod do //
NK069(tu)001:5153: bse ru ltar gcig pu dang /
NK069(tu)001:5154: ne tso ltar khyus lding ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5156: rang rgyal byang chub rdzogs pa'i lam //
NK069(tu)001:5159: mya ngan 'das lam mngon par gnyer //
NK069(tu)001:5160: ma rig 'du byed rnam shes dang //
NK069(tu)001:5161: mi tshogs gzugs dang skye mched drug /
NK069(tu)001:5162: reg pa tshor ba sred pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5163: len pa srid pa skye rgas shi //
NK069(tu)001:5164: chos rnams mngon par dga' ba'i mthus //
NK069(tu)001:5165: 'phags pa'i ye shes zag pa myed //
NK069(tu)001:5166: nyon mongs las dang sdug bsngal gyi //
NK069(tu)001:5167: cha shes rgyun gyi yul las 'das //
NK069(tu)001:5169: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5170: zhes theg pa chen po la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:5171: lta ba ni don dam skye myed dang /
NK069(tu)001:5172: kun rdzob mtshan nyid bzhi ldan no //
NK069(tu)001:5176: bdag don gyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5179: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu ni /
NK069(tu)001:5182: bzod pa gsum la brtson 'grus kyis grogs byas pas rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:5183: bsam gtan dang shes rab la brtson 'grus kyis grogs byas pas 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:5187: ye shes ni shes rab kyi cha las tags so //
NK069(tu)001:5198: de la lam bzhi ni mtshan nyid pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5199: mthar phyin pa'i lam ni btags pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:5200: 'bras bu la lam du btags pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5202: byang chub kyi phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun rdzogs te /
NK069(tu)001:5203: dran pa nye bar bzhag pa bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:5204: yang dag par spong ba bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:5205: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:5206: tshogs lam du tshogs bzhi gsum bcu gnyis rdzogs so //
NK069(tu)001:5207: sbyor lam du lnga gnyis bcu rdzogs te /
NK069(tu)001:5210: mthong lam du byang chub kyi yan lag bdun rdzogs so //
NK069(tu)001:5211: sgom lam du 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad rdzogs so //
NK069(tu)001:5212: gzhan don ni bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:5219: lhag myed kyis kun tu 'od kyi sa non pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5221: yang dag dgra bcom chen po'i sku //
NK069(tu)001:5222: dngos myed nam mkha' dwangs ba'i bdag /
NK069(tu)001:5223: shes rab snying stobs las kyi mthus //
NK069(tu)001:5224: sbyin dang yang dag sbyangs pa'i bdag /
NK069(tu)001:5225: rnam par grol bas gzhan rgyud sel //
NK069(tu)001:5226: theg pa chen po'i mtshan nyid can //
NK069(tu)001:5227: bdag gzhan rgyud rnams grol ba'i blos //
NK069(tu)001:5228: yang dag ye shes spyod pa spyod //
NK069(tu)001:5229: pha rol phyin pa rnam pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:5230: sa bcu'i ye shes rdzogs mdzad cing //
NK069(tu)001:5231: byang chub phyogs kyi chos rnams dag /
NK069(tu)001:5232: ma 'dres gzungs kyis spyad byas te //
NK069(tu)001:5233: yang dag theg pa'i gnas rdzogs pas //
NK069(tu)001:5234: 'gro ba thams cad mgron du gnyer //
NK069(tu)001:5235: tshad myed bsdu ba'i dngos po yis //
NK069(tu)001:5236: spyod pa rgya chen 'dzin dang bral //
NK069(tu)001:5237: yang dag bsod nams ye shes dag /
NK069(tu)001:5238: thams cad rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu nyid //
NK069(tu)001:5239: ces bshad rgyud nas rgyas par bshad pa rnams bkrol lo //
NK069(tu)001:5240: bla na myed pa'i theg pas /
NK069(tu)001:5241: zhes pa 'bras bu gsang sngags bla na myed pa'i theg pa ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:5242: phyi pa thub pa'i rgyud dang /
NK069(tu)001:5243: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud kyi theg pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5244: phyi pa thub pa'i rgyud ni /
NK069(tu)001:5245: khrus dang gtsang sbra gtso che ba kri ya dang /
NK069(tu)001:5246: spyod pa kri yar spyod cing lta ba yo gar lta ba'i u pa ya dang /
NK069(tu)001:5248: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud ni /
NK069(tu)001:5249: sku'i rgyud rnal 'byor chen po skyed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5250: gsung gi rgyud rjes su rnal 'byor rdzogs pa dang
NK069(tu)001:5251: thugs kyi rgyud shin tu rnal 'byor rdzogs pa chen
NK069(tu)001:5253: rgyu yang gsang la 'bras bu'ang gsang //
NK069(tu)001:5254: snying po chos kyi don las byung //
NK069(tu)001:5255: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi bdag /
NK069(tu)001:5256: rgyud chen sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba nyid //
NK069(tu)001:5257: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor sna tshogs gzhi //
NK069(tu)001:5258: rdo rje'i theg pa bla na myed //
NK069(tu)001:5260: de dag gis ci byed zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:5261: ma rig pa gnyis las byung ba'i rnam par rtog pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:5262: nyon mongs pa stong phrag rgya bcu rtsa bzhi'i gnyan po byed pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:5263: dngos su na phyi rgyud sde gsum gsungs par mngon no //
NK069(tu)001:5264: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:5265: bla na myed pa'i theg pas zhes pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5266: 'bras bu bskyed rdzogs gsum yin nam myin /
NK069(tu)001:5268: sa dang rnam thar la spyad pas //
NK069(tu)001:5269: byang chub thob par gyur pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:5270: 'dren pa'i theg pa rnam gsum mo //
NK069(tu)001:5271: gang dag rim par bkod lags na //
NK069(tu)001:5272: zhes mtshan nyid sde gsum sh+aaka thub kyis gsungs nas /
NK069(tu)001:5274: mnyam pas blang dor myed spyod cing /
NK069(tu)001:5275: byang chub gzhan nas ma tshal ba'i //
NK069(tu)001:5276: nges pa'i theg pa yongs ma gsungs //
NK069(tu)001:5278: rgyud lung man ngag gsum nam gsung bar 'gyur ces /
NK069(tu)001:5279: rig 'dzin gyi rgyal po kun dza ras zhus pa dang 'gal lo //
NK069(tu)001:5280: der sh+aaka thub kyis bskyed rdzogs gsum ma gsungs na /
NK069(tu)001:5281: thub drug kun tu bzang po'i thugs las sprul nas /
NK069(tu)001:5282: gsang sngags bskyed rdzogs gsum mi gsung ba ci te zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:5286: kri yo ga sde gsum bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa'i zhal nas gsungs la /
NK069(tu)001:5287: rjes su snang ba ni bskyed rdzogs gsum yin te /
NK069(tu)001:5288: sh+aaka thub kyis lung bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5289: nga ni 'di na mi snang nas /
NK069(tu)001:5290: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na /
NK069(tu)001:5291: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /
NK069(tu)001:5292: rgyal po dza zhes bya ba la //
NK069(tu)001:5293: thugs rje mthun pa'i byin rlabs dag /
NK069(tu)001:5294: lag na rdo rjes snang bar byed zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:5295: de bas na lha mi phal pa la /
NK069(tu)001:5296: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsang sngags kri yog gsungs /
NK069(tu)001:5297: khyad par du gyur pa la bskyed rdzogs gsum gsungs /
NK069(tu)001:5298: rgyud 'dir byung ba la bstan pa spyi'i byung tshul dang /
NK069(tu)001:5299: rgyud 'di rang gi che bar bstan pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:5301: zhes pa rgyu ma rig pa las byung ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:5302: gzung 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5303: nyon mongs pa stong phrag brgya bcu rtsa bzhi'i gnyer por /
NK069(tu)001:5304: zhes pa'i nyon mongs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5305: 'dod chags su rigs gcig pa la nang mi mthun pa nyi khri chig stong /
NK069(tu)001:5306: zhe sdang du rigs cig pa la nang mi mthun pa nyi khri chig stong /
NK069(tu)001:5307: gti mug tu rigs cig pa la nang mi mthun pa nyi khri chig stong /
NK069(tu)001:5308: de gsum cha mnyam pa las nyi khri chig stong ste /
NK069(tu)001:5309: nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:5310: chos stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'i gsungs so //
NK069(tu)001:5312: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen por chos nyi khri chig stong /
NK069(tu)001:5313: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen por nyi khri chig stong /
NK069(tu)001:5314: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen por nyi khri chig stong /
NK069(tu)001:5315: de gsum cha mnyam pa 'dul ba'i gnyen por nyi khri chig stong ste /
NK069(tu)001:5316: de ltar chos kyi sgo mo stong phrag brgyad cu
NK069(tu)001:5317: rtsa bzhi nyon mongs pa stong phrag brgyad cu rtsa
NK069(tu)001:5318: bzhi'i gnyen por / 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis sngar yang gsungs so //
NK069(tu)001:5320: da ltar bzhugs pa rnams yang gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:5322: zhes phyis 'byung ba'i sangs rgyas de bzhin gshegs pa rnams yang gsungs bar 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:5323: nyon mongs pa stong phrag ces pa la sogs pa'i gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:5324: bstan pa'i 'byung gnas spyi'i gleng gzhi 'di bstan pa yin nam myin /
NK069(tu)001:5326: gleng gzhi'i nges tshig gis gsal /
NK069(tu)001:5327: yin na rgyu gleng gzhi dang rkyen gleng slang ba
NK069(tu)001:5328: gnyis lan gnyis 'byung bar mi rigs so zhe na
NK069(tu)001:5330: 'di gsang ba snying po'i bstan pa myin /
NK069(tu)001:5331: bstan pa 'byung ba spyi'i gleng gzhi yin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5332: de yang gsang ba snying po las thams cad spros pa'i che bar gyur pas so //
NK069(tu)001:5334: zhes pa'i de dag ni gong gi theg pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5335: chos kyi sgo mo rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:5337: nyon mongs pa dang sbyar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:5338: de'i gnyen po dang sbyar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5340: zhes nyon mongs pa dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:5341: nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong po de dag thams cad gang du 'dus zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:5345: phyi nang gi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba /
NK069(tu)001:5346: zhes gzung ba'i yul myed par gzung bas /
NK069(tu)001:5348: 'dzin pa'i sems myed par 'dzin pa'i sems su bzung bas /
NK069(tu)001:5350: gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i phyi nang gi rten 'brel bar 'byung ba dang zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:5352: zhes 'dzin pa'i sems 'khrul pa nyid yul du snang ba yin pa las /
NK069(tu)001:5353: de ltar ma rtogs nas yul gyi ngo bo zhig logs zhig na yod do zhes rtog pas na /
NK069(tu)001:5355: las dang las kyi 'bras bu chud mi za ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:5359: mtho ris dang ngan song chud mi za /
NK069(tu)001:5361: de yang kun rdzob tu las dang las kyi 'bras bu ni chud mi za la /
NK069(tu)001:5362: don dam par ni las dang las kyi 'bras bus mi gos so //
NK069(tu)001:5363: nyon mongs pa 'dul ba'i gnyen po dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:5364: chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong po de dag thams cad kyang bsdu na /
NK069(tu)001:5366: 'bras bu'i theg pa gnyis su 'dus te /
NK069(tu)001:5367: rgyu'i theg pa dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:5369: nyan thos phyi gzung ba'i yul la chos kyi bdag tu lta /
NK069(tu)001:5370: nang 'dzin pa'i sems la gang zag gi bdag tu lta bas /
NK069(tu)001:5371: nyan thos la bden pa bzhi'i sgo nas don mdzad cing chos bston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5372: phyi nang gi rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:5373: rang sangs rgyas phyi nang gi rten 'brel bcu gnyis
NK069(tu)001:5374: kyi sgo nas don mdzad cing chos ston pa dang
NK069(tu)001:5375: sbyar / 'dzin pas khrul pa la 'dogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5377: sems 'dzin pas 'khor ba gcig nas gcig tu long rtags pas /
NK069(tu)001:5378: de la lha dang mi'i theg pa rnams la dge
NK069(tu)001:5379: bcu dang tshangs pa'i gnas gzhi don mdzad cing chos
NK069(tu)001:5380: ston pa'o // las dang las kyi 'bras bu chud mi za ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:5381: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pas bden pa gnyis su rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:5382: ji ltar spyad kyang las rgyu 'bras kyi 'bras bu chud mi za bar thob ste /
NK069(tu)001:5383: byang chub kyi spyod pa la zhugs pas so //
NK069(tu)001:5384: las dang las kyi 'bras bus mi gos pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5385: kri yog sde gsum dang sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:5386: mchod pa phul ba'i las kyis bsod nams tshogs rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:5387: de'i las kyi 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs la rnam par rtog pas mi gos so //
NK069(tu)001:5391: lha dang lha mor shes so //
NK069(tu)001:5392: gos su myed par ston pa'i mthar thug pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5394: 'o na da lta las dang las kyi 'bras bus mi gos /
NK069(tu)001:5396: phyis kyang gos par mi 'gyur ram zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:5397: gos su yang yong myed de /
NK069(tu)001:5398: gos par bya ba'i gnas kun gzhi yang ye nas rnam par dag cing sangs rgyas la /
NK069(tu)001:5399: go bar byed pa'i bag chags kyang ye nas rnam par dag cing sangs rgyas pas /
NK069(tu)001:5400: gang gis gang la go ste /
NK069(tu)001:5401: gos su myed pa ston pa'i mthar thug go //
NK069(tu)001:5402: tshig 'di rnams sems can la go ba bde bas theg pa rim par sbyar ba tsam las /
NK069(tu)001:5403: gzhung nyid ni theg pa thams cad kyi spyi tshig tu dril nas bstan pa yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:5404: don ma nor bar shes par bya /
NK069(tu)001:5405: tshig theg pa tha dad du ma sbyar yang chog go //
NK069(tu)001:5406: las dang las kyi 'bras bus mi gos /
NK069(tu)001:5407: zhes gzung 'dzin dang bral ba rnams la /
NK069(tu)001:5408: las dang las kyi 'bras bus ma gos so //
NK069(tu)001:5410: gzung 'dzin dang bral na las kyi 'bras bus gos par mi 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:5411: gos su myed par ston pa'i mthar thug go //
NK069(tu)001:5413: sgo bya'i kun gzhi myed la /
NK069(tu)001:5414: sgo rgyu'i bag chags myed par ston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5415: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:5416: zhes pa de yan chad du kri ya'i don 'dul ba'i dbang du bshad pa de nas /
NK069(tu)001:5417: da ni nges pa'i don ston pas de nas ce'am /
NK069(tu)001:5418: de yan chad du gleng gzhi dang gleng slang rdzogs pa de nas lta ba ston no //
NK069(tu)001:5419: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad ces pa kun tu
NK069(tu)001:5420: bzang po sangs rgyas thams cad kyi spyi gzugs thams
NK069(tu)001:5421: cad / ji skad bos kyang 'gal ba med pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:5422: sangs rgyas thams cad dgongs pa gcig tu gyur bas na /
NK069(tu)001:5424: de gnyis ka yang khyad par myed par lta ba
NK069(tu)001:5425: 'ba' zhig tu ston pa ni rgyud don lta ba
NK069(tu)001:5426: dang sbyar ba dang dngos don theg pa dang sbyar
NK069(tu)001:5427: ba gnyis las / thabs lam du bshad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5428: dang por sprul pa 'byung ba'i gnas ni /
NK069(tu)001:5429: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:5430: byang sems thig le zung 'jug gi bde bar gshegs pa'i byin rlabs las /
NK069(tu)001:5431: dga' ba bcu drug las bde ba thon pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5433: thon nas kyang las kyi dbang gis /
NK069(tu)001:5435: lus kyi rtsa 'khor lo drug go //
NK069(tu)001:5437: thub pa chen po zhes pa /
NK069(tu)001:5438: rtsa 'khor lo drug tu sprul pa'i thig le drug tu shar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5442: bltams pa dang zhes pa la sogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5443: rtsa gnas nas theg le ltam /
NK069(tu)001:5444: thig le bde bar rab tu byung /
NK069(tu)001:5445: thig le snod du blugs pa dka' thub mdzad /
NK069(tu)001:5446: slob ma la byin pa sangs rgyas pa /
NK069(tu)001:5447: sgrib pa dral ba bdud btul ba /
NK069(tu)001:5450: rtogs pa thob pa mya ngan 'das pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5454: thig le la mngon shes lnga tshang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5456: kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK069(tu)001:5462: de dag thams cad kyang 'di lta ste /
NK069(tu)001:5464: rtsa gnas kyi yi ge bstan par shar ro //
NK069(tu)001:5466: thig le zung 'jug bde ba ni //
NK069(tu)001:5467: sems mtha' ldog pas go phye nas //
NK069(tu)001:5468: 'khor lo drug gi yul rnams su //
NK069(tu)001:5469: sprul pa'i thig le rang shar ba //
NK069(tu)001:5470: snang ba'i mdzad pa bsam mi khyab //
NK069(tu)001:5471: chags sogs nyon mongs las rtog rol //
NK069(tu)001:5472: 'dul phyir sprul pa zhes su bshad //
NK069(tu)001:5473: sgra dbyangs gsum gi bstan pa rnams //
NK069(tu)001:5474: nges par grags pa kho na nyid //
NK069(tu)001:5476: 'khor ba spyi'i mtshan nyid bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5478: zhes pa ji snyed ni mang por gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5479: 'jig rten ni rigs drug gi gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:5482: 'khrul pas 'khor ba'i chos sna tshogs par snang bas na 'khrul pa'i chos zhes bya ba yin no //
NK069(tu)001:5483: 'khrul pa'i ngo bo bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5485: rgyu ma rig pa las byung ba'i rnam par rtog pa las /
NK069(tu)001:5486: sems rang bzhin gyis 'od gsal yang /
NK069(tu)001:5487: nges pa'i shes pa ma snyed pa ni ma rig go //
NK069(tu)001:5489: zhes yul sems phyi nang gi gzung 'dzin gyis /
NK069(tu)001:5492: phyi nang rten 'brel 'khor tshul gnyis su 'khor //
NK069(tu)001:5493: zhes phyi'i rten cing 'brel bas phyi snod du 'khor /
NK069(tu)001:5494: nang gi rten cing 'brel bas nang bcud du 'khor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5495: phyi nang lugs 'byung du ni skyes /
NK069(tu)001:5497: rgyun ma chad pa ni 'brel pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5498: mi nyes pa mthun bde sdug myong bar 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:5499: zhes 'gro ba drug nang ris mi mthun /
NK069(tu)001:5502: 'gro ba so so'i nang du yang /
NK069(tu)001:5503: bde dang sdug bsngal rigs myi mthun pa du ma nyams su myong bar byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5504: rang bzhin rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa myed //
NK069(tu)001:5505: ces de ltar mi mthun pa'i bde sdug rnam pa
NK069(tu)001:5506: sna tshogs pa nyams su myong ba de yang rang
NK069(tu)001:5507: sems 'khrul ba'i dbang gis phyin ci log gi rtog
NK069(tu)001:5508: pa de nyid de ltar snang bar zad kyis /
NK069(tu)001:5509: yang dag pa'i dbyings la ni g.yo ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:5510: nyams pa rdul tsam yang myed do //
NK069(tu)001:5512: theg pa spyi dang sbyar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:5513: 'khrul pa'i chos thams cad kyi gzhir bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5514: theg pa spyi dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:5515: ji snyed 'jig rten 'khrul pa'i chos ni /
NK069(tu)001:5521: phyi nang rten 'brel gnyis su 'khor ni /
NK069(tu)001:5522: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5523: mi mthun bde sdug myong bar gyur ni /
NK069(tu)001:5524: la bzla ba'i lta ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:5525: so so'i lta ba mi mthun pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5526: sems can gyi sdug bsngal yang /
NK069(tu)001:5527: 'khrul pa de nyid rang snang ba las ma rtogs pa las /
NK069(tu)001:5528: sems nyid chos kyi dbyings la nyams pa myed do //
NK069(tu)001:5529: gnyis pa 'khrul pa'i snang ba chos thams cad kyi gzhir bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5530: ji snyed 'khrul pa'i chos 'di rgyu ci las byung na /
NK069(tu)001:5533: las dang nyon mongs pa'i gzung 'dzin gyis byas /
NK069(tu)001:5537: mtho ris ngan song gi bde sdug 'di yin /
NK069(tu)001:5539: sangs rgyas las ma rtogs pa'i sems nyid la nyams pa myed do //
NK069(tu)001:5540: 'di man chad 'khor ba rang gi mtshan nyid bstan /
NK069(tu)001:5541: yang dag sgyu ma'i tshul gnyis su //
NK069(tu)001:5542: zhes pa yang dag pa ni don dam pa'i bden pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5543: sgyu ma ni kun rdzob kyi bden pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5544: de ltar bden pa gnyis kyi tshul gyis kyang /
NK069(tu)001:5545: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan myed de //
NK069(tu)001:5546: rnam dag dbyings nyid tshul gcig go //
NK069(tu)001:5547: zhes bdag ni dbang po gzugs can dang /
NK069(tu)001:5548: bdag gi yul gzugs sgra la sogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5549: de gnyis las rten nas byung ba'i rnam par rtog pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5550: gzhan gyi dngos por grub pa ni rdul tsam yang myed pa'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:5551: gzung 'dzin gnyis ka rnam par dag pa'i ye shes dang /
NK069(tu)001:5552: chos kyi dbyings tshul gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:5554: theg pa spyi dang sbyar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:5555: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i lta ba dang sbyar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5556: theg pa spyi dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:5557: yang dag sgyu ma'i tshul gnyis su //
NK069(tu)001:5559: bden pa gnyis kyi don rtogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5560: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:5561: de la ni bdag dang bdag gir 'dzin pa'i tshul gnyis myed de /
NK069(tu)001:5562: rnam par dag pa chos kyi dbyings su tshul cig pas so //
NK069(tu)001:5563: de yang bdag gzhan gyi rtog pa tsam de don du ni myed la /
NK069(tu)001:5564: log pa'i rgyu nyid rnyogs na rang sems skad cig ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:5565: de ni gzhi rtsa myed pa chos kyi dbyings so //
NK069(tu)001:5566: de lta bu bla na myed pa'i dngos grub gzhan nas re ba yang /
NK069(tu)001:5567: bdag gzhan du rtog pa yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:5569: nyid la nyid dbang sgyur ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5571: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i lta ba dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:5572: de nyid kho na yang ma h+aa'i lta bar la zla yang /
NK069(tu)001:5573: 'dir ni las dang po pas gtan tshig bden pa gsum gyis gtan la dbab ste /
NK069(tu)001:5574: don dam pa'i bden pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5577: don dam pa'i bden pa la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:5579: de bsgrub par byed pa'i rig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5581: skye myed spros bral snang stong ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5582: de sgrub pa'i rig pa la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:5583: rgyu rkyen gzhan gyis ma skyes pa'i phyir skye ba myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5584: byed pa po gzhan gyis ma byas pa'i phyir skye ba myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5585: skyes pa'i dngos po 'di 'drar bya ba myi rnyed pa'i phyir skye ba myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5586: kun rdzob kyi bden pa la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:5590: rig pa sgyu ma'i snang ba de /
NK069(tu)001:5591: rig pa rang rgyud pa myen pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:5592: phyogs gcig tu grub pa myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5593: de sgrub pa'i rig pa gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:5594: snang ba yangs pas mi yongs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5595: snang ba 'di myed na yang skyon du 'gyur ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5596: bden pa dbyer myed la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:5600: snang ba la stong pa'i rtsis ma zin pa myed /
NK069(tu)001:5601: stong pa la snang ba'i rtsis ma zin pa myed de /
NK069(tu)001:5602: snang stong ngo mnyam gyis gnyis myed chen po'o //
NK069(tu)001:5603: de bsgrub par byed pa'i rig pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5604: snang stong gang gi yang mthar ma lhung ba'i phyir dbyer myed do //
NK069(tu)001:5605: de yang don dam shes pas stong pa'i mthar ma lhung la /
NK069(tu)001:5606: kun rdzob shes pas snang ba'i mthar ma lhung ste /
NK069(tu)001:5607: de kho na la bden pa dbyer myed chen po zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:5608: 'khor ba log rtog la dbang sgyur ba bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5609: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan rnams ni //
NK069(tu)001:5610: log par rtogs pa tsam nyid las //
NK069(tu)001:5611: zhes 'o na dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su myed pa'i tshul gcig pa yin na /
NK069(tu)001:5612: bdag dang gzhan gyi rnam par rtog pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5613: gzhan yong ji lta ba zhig yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:5614: log par rtogs ces pas ma rig pa las byung ba'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:5615: phyin ci log gi rnam par rtog pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:5616: 'khrul pa'i sems nyid yul dang dbang po dang rnam par shes par snang ba tsam du zad kyis /
NK069(tu)001:5618: myong ba phung po'i bdag dang /
NK069(tu)001:5620: phra zhing zab pa'ang yod ma yin //
NK069(tu)001:5622: yang dag pa las log par rtogs pa tsam nyid las /
NK069(tu)001:5623: phra te rdul phra rab kyi dngos por yang grub pa myed la /
NK069(tu)001:5624: zab ste stong ba bdag myed pa tsam gyi ngang du yang yod pa ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:5625: yang na phra te sha'i myig gis yang ltar myed la /
NK069(tu)001:5626: zab ste ni shes rab kyi spyod yul du yang yod pa ma yin no //
NK069(tu)001:5628: log par rtogs pa tsam nyid las /
NK069(tu)001:5629: phra zhing zab pa yang yod pa ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:5630: log rtog nyid la nyid spyod de //
NK069(tu)001:5632: 'khrul pa'i sems yul du byas nas bag chags kyi
NK069(tu)001:5633: mthu ltas las log par rtog pa skad cig ma
NK069(tu)001:5634: phyi mas spyod mi 'jug pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:5635: log rtog nyid la log rtog spyod pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:5636: 'khrul pa nyid spyod par zad kyis zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:5637: gzhan du g.yo ba ci yang myed //
NK069(tu)001:5638: ces pa yul gzhan zhig na snang ba yod pa ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:5639: gzhan du g.yo ba ci yang zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:5640: grub mtha' rtogs pa bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:5641: rgyu gcig par rtogs pa log rtog la gsum ste /
