NK069(tu)001:5642: gzhal bya 'das kyi zhen snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:5643: go ba'am rtogs pa gang skye na /
NK069(tu)001:5644: 'khor 'das sems su rgyu cig par rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5646: 'khor 'das tha dad du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa grol lo //
NK069(tu)001:5647: yig 'bru'i tshul du rtogs rnam dag pa la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:5648: gzhal bya 'khor 'das kyi zhen snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:5649: go ba 'am rtogs pa gang skye na /
NK069(tu)001:5650: +aahmh'u gsum gyi sgo nas lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs su rtogs so //
NK069(tu)001:5652: 'bras bu gzhan nas thob pa mnyam nas gzhan nas tshol ba'i zhen pa grol ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5653: byin gyis rlabs kyis rtogs pa nyid la dbang sgyur pa gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:5656: rgyu cig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul gyis rtogs pa'i mthu ngo shes nas rtan par rtogs so //
NK069(tu)001:5658: mi tan pa'i zhen pa grol nas tan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5659: mngon nyid spyod phyir sum par rtogs pa la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:5662: mthu ngo shes nas tan pa de sgra tsam ma yin par blo gting du go //
NK069(tu)001:5664: sgra bzhin du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa las grol lo //
NK069(tu)001:5665: log rtog gi rang bzhin shes nas 'das pa la dbang sgyur ba bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5666: log rtog rgyu 'bras rgyun nyid kyang //
NK069(tu)001:5667: zhes log rtog snga ma ni rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:5668: log rtog phyi ma ni 'bras bu /
NK069(tu)001:5669: yang na rgyu ni nyon mongs pa /
NK069(tu)001:5671: rgyu log rtog rgyun ma chad pas /
NK069(tu)001:5672: 'bras bu sdug bsngal yang rgyun mi chad pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:5674: gzhi rtsa myed dbyings skad cig ma //
NK069(tu)001:5675: zhes de ltar sems kyi log rtog dang /
NK069(tu)001:5676: 'bras bu sdug bsngal gyi rgyun de nyid kyang /
NK069(tu)001:5680: gzhi dang rtsa ba myed pa'i chos kyi dbyings dang /
NK069(tu)001:5681: ye shes skad cig mar rang snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5682: rnam par dag pas dbyings nyid tshul //
NK069(tu)001:5683: zhes gzung 'dzin rnam par dag pa'i ye shes dang /
NK069(tu)001:5684: chos kyi dbyings tshul gcig pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:5685: rnam par dag pa chos kyi dbyings stong pa nyid kyi tshul lo //
NK069(tu)001:5686: nyid la dbang sgyur nyid spyod phyir //
NK069(tu)001:5687: zhes pa 'phags pa'i dus na gzung 'dzin dang bral
NK069(tu)001:5688: ba'i rig pa'i ye shes nyid sna tshogs par snang
NK069(tu)001:5689: la / de la rol cing spyod pa yang ye shes nyid yin te /
NK069(tu)001:5690: ye shes la ye shes rol /
NK069(tu)001:5691: ye shes la ye shes dbang sgyur ba'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:5692: bdag dang gzhan dang rtog pa'i rgyun //
NK069(tu)001:5693: zhes pa bdag ni dbang po gzugs can /
NK069(tu)001:5694: gzhan ni yul gzugs sgra la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5696: de nyid la rten te byung ba'i rnam par rtog pa rgyun chags pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5697: rnam dag bla na myed pa'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:5698: ces pa dbang po lha'i dkyil 'khor du rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:5699: yul gzugs sgra lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:5700: de nyid la rten te byung ba'i rnam par rtog pa /
NK069(tu)001:5701: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rnam par dag pas rnam par dag ces bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:5702: de ltar dag pa rnams kyi tshul du rtogs pa de ni /
NK069(tu)001:5703: theg pa gang gi lugs kyis rtogs zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:5704: theg pa gzhan gyi lugs kyis mi rtogs te /
NK069(tu)001:5705: gsang sngags kyi theg pa bla na myed pa 'di'i lugs kyis rtogs pas theg pa'i mchog ces so //
NK069(tu)001:5706: yang na dbang po lha'i dkyil 'khor du rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:5707: rnam par rtog pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:5708: de ltar ston pa'i gong na yon tan du bya
NK069(tu)001:5709: ba gzhan myed pa'i phyir rnam dag bla med ces
NK069(tu)001:5710: bya'o // de ni theg pa thams cad kyi mchog yin pas na mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:5712: zhes lha mi'i theg pa dge ba bcu dang /
NK069(tu)001:5713: nyan thos kyi theg pa bden pa bzhi dang /
NK069(tu)001:5714: rang sangs rgyas kyi theg pa rten 'brel bcu gnyis dang /
NK069(tu)001:5715: byang chub sems dpa'i theg pa bden pa gnyis kyis ni /
NK069(tu)001:5716: 'bras bu ni 'khor ba las nges par 'byung bar byed la /
NK069(tu)001:5717: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK069(tu)001:5718: zhes gsang sngags rdo rje theg pas ni /
NK069(tu)001:5719: 'bras bu bla na myed pa'i byang chub tu grub par byed pas 'bras bur gnas zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:5720: yang dag rtogs pas rab brtags na //
NK069(tu)001:5721: rang bzhin myed las cir yang 'grub //
NK069(tu)001:5722: ces pa yang dag par ma nor bar rtogs pas rab tu brtags na /
NK069(tu)001:5723: rang bzhin myed pa las rtogs pa'i khyed par gyis cir yang 'grub ste /
NK069(tu)001:5724: ma nor ma rtogs pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:5725: sangs rgyas kyi sku gsung thugs la sogs te /
NK069(tu)001:5726: mya ngan las 'das pa'i yon tan sna tshogs yang 'grub la /
NK069(tu)001:5727: ma rtogs shing 'khrul ba'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:5728: 'khor ba'i chos sna tshogs yang 'grub pas /
NK069(tu)001:5729: rang bzhin myed las cir yang 'grub zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:5730: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'da' //
NK069(tu)001:5731: zhes de bzhin gshegs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5733: chos kyi skur bzhugs pas na /
NK069(tu)001:5734: chos kyi sku de la ni mya ngan las 'da' ba myi mnga' bas /
NK069(tu)001:5735: sangs rgyas mya ngan las yongs mi 'da' zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:5736: chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur te //
NK069(tu)001:5737: zhes sangs rgyas sku mya ngan las ma 'das pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5738: de'i zhal nas gsungs pa'i chos kyang nub par mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5739: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:5740: gong nas mya ngan las 'das pa la sogs pa ston pa'i thub pas zhes bshad nas /
NK069(tu)001:5741: 'dir sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'da' zhes pas 'gal zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:5743: gong ma de ni theg pa thun mong dang byung tshul stun pa'i dbang du yin la /
NK069(tu)001:5744: 'di ni theg pa chen po bas /
NK069(tu)001:5745: don dam la sangs rgyas la mya ngan las 'da' ba mi mnga' la /
NK069(tu)001:5746: chos la yang dar nub myed de /
NK069(tu)001:5747: de ltar snang ba de gdul bya ma rtogs pa'i snang ba yin la /
NK069(tu)001:5748: rtogs ldan nyams kyi snang ba la de gar yang ma grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:5749: ma rig smin mdzad gdul bya'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:5751: zhes pa 'o na sangs rgyas mya ngan mi 'da' na /
NK069(tu)001:5752: dang po yum gyi lhums nas bltams pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5753: mjug mya ngan las 'das pa'i bar gyi tshul ni ji ltar yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:5754: sems can ma rig pa las byung ba'i rnam par smin pa grol bar mdzad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5755: gdul bya'i rgyud smin par bya ba'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:5756: yum gyi lhums nas bltams pa dang mya ngan las 'da' bar ston par mdzad pas /
NK069(tu)001:5757: gdul bya le lo can brtson 'grus la 'god pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:5758: 'dul ba mdo sde chos mngon dang //
NK069(tu)001:5759: zhes nyon mongs rta rgod dang 'dra ba khrims nyi rgya lnga bcus 'dul ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:5760: drang don dang nges don ston pa'i mdo sde dang /
NK069(tu)001:5761: shes rab kyis yang dag pa'i don mngon par ston pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:5762: mtshan nyid kyi sde snod gsum nyan rang byang sems so //
NK069(tu)001:5763: dam tshig sgrub dang grub pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:5764: zhes srung ba'i dam tshig ston pa'i kri ya dang /
NK069(tu)001:5765: sgrub pa'i thabs ston pa u pa ya dang /
NK069(tu)001:5766: grub pa'i 'bras bu ston pa yo ga ste /
NK069(tu)001:5767: phyi pa thub pa'i rgyud zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:5770: rnal 'byor phyi pa'i rgyud gsum du bston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5771: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NK069(tu)001:5772: ces sku'i rgyud bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga /
NK069(tu)001:5773: gsung gi rgyud rdzogs pa a nu yo ga /
NK069(tu)001:5774: thugs kyi rgyud rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga gsum /
NK069(tu)001:5775: rnal 'byor bla na med pa'i theg pa thams cad do //
NK069(tu)001:5776: phyogs bcu kun tu rab grags pa //
NK069(tu)001:5777: zhes de ltar 'gro ba sems can rnams kyi don du /
NK069(tu)001:5778: mtshan nyid kyi sde snod gsum /
NK069(tu)001:5780: rnal 'byor nang pa bla na myed pa'i rgyud gsum por grangs pa rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:5781: gsang ba snying po las 'phros te //
NK069(tu)001:5782: zhes de rnams yang mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad
NK069(tu)001:5783: kyi rtsa ba gsang ba'i snying po las phros pa'o
NK069(tu)001:5784: // blo sman pa skal ba myed pa la gsang /
NK069(tu)001:5786: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'dis //
NK069(tu)001:5788: sde snod kun dang rgyud kun gyi //
NK069(tu)001:5789: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po 'di /
NK069(tu)001:5790: kun tu bzang po'i thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:5791: de bas na thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes las 'phros pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5792: thugs yang dag pa'i rtags kyi phyag rgya 'di rtogs par dka' bas gsang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:5794: zhes pa dper na chu bran thams cad byung yang phyi'i rgya mtsho las 'byung la /
NK069(tu)001:5796: chos thams cad byung yang kun tu bzang po'i thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes las byung la /
NK069(tu)001:5797: gtan la yang thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes kho nar 'bebs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5798: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:5799: gsang ba snying po 'di las theg pa thams cad 'phros pa dang 'gal zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:5801: rang bzhin gsang ba'i snying po ni /
NK069(tu)001:5803: chos sku des thams cad stan pa yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5804: thams cad spros pa yin pas 'gal ba myed do //
NK069(tu)001:5805: chos rnams ming du rtags pa tsam //
NK069(tu)001:5806: zhes chos thams cad ni yang dag par na /
NK069(tu)001:5807: dngos po cir yang ma grub cing /
NK069(tu)001:5808: tshig dang yi ge las 'das te /
NK069(tu)001:5809: brjod pa'i tha snyad dang bral ba bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:5810: kun rdzob tu ming dang mtshan ma tsam yin pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:5811: chos rnams ming du rtags pa tsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:5813: ston pas don dang mthun phyogs su //
NK069(tu)001:5814: zhes pa ston pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang ldan pa des /
NK069(tu)001:5815: don chos nyid dang mthun pa'i phyogs su ston pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5816: ming dang tshig tu brtags nas bstan //
NK069(tu)001:5817: zhes dper na mun khung du gser tshol ba sgron me la rten nas tshol ba ltar /
NK069(tu)001:5818: tshig gi sgron mes don gyi gser tshol lo //
NK069(tu)001:5819: ming la rten nas tshig mtshon no //
NK069(tu)001:5820: ston ming tshig la dngos po myed //
NK069(tu)001:5822: don dam par na yang dag pa'i sangs rgyas ston pa'o nyid dang /
NK069(tu)001:5823: ming dang tshig tu brtags nas bstan pa'i chos thams cad la /
NK069(tu)001:5824: dngos por grub pa rdul tsam yang myed pas /
NK069(tu)001:5825: ston ming tshig la dngos po myed zhes brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:5827: dang po 'khrul ba'i snang ba bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5830: phung po rtogs tshogs sgyu mar snang ba'i thig le rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:5831: mnyam pa bzhi bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5832: yang dag sgyu ma'i tshul gnyis su //
NK069(tu)001:5834: nyi zla byang sems kun rdzob tu mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:5835: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes su mnyam pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5836: de la rtsad pa spang ba ni //
NK069(tu)001:5837: bdag dang bdag gi gzhan rnams ni //
NK069(tu)001:5838: zhes pa la sogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5839: bde ba dang theg le dbyer med pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5840: rtogs pa bzhi'i gtan tshig ni //
NK069(tu)001:5841: log rtog rgyu 'bras rgyun nyid ni //
NK069(tu)001:5843: thig le ma skyes par mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:5846: lhan skyes mngon sum du myong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:5847: dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshig ni //
NK069(tu)001:5848: bdag dang gzhan dang rtog pa'i rgyun //
NK069(tu)001:5851: phung po lha'i dal du shes /
NK069(tu)001:5852: rtog pa bde bar shes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5853: de ltar 'grub pa'i theg pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5854: theg pa bzhi'i nges 'byung zhes pa la sogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5855: dga' ba rang snang rang rig mngon sum du gsal ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5856: bstan pa dar nub myed pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:5857: thig le dus gsum du mi 'gyur ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:5858: sangs rgyas mya ngan yongs mi 'ada'o //
NK069(tu)001:5859: bstan pa thams cad 'di las byung ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:5861: srog dang rtsol ba las klung byung yang /
NK069(tu)001:5862: srog dang rtsol bar thim pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5865: log rtog sgyu mar snang tsam las //
NK069(tu)001:5866: nyi zla'i gdan gnyis las nyid kyis //
NK069(tu)001:5867: ma skyes mnyam la gnas 'gyur zhing //
NK069(tu)001:5869: rang snang rang rig mngon sum gsal //
NK069(tu)001:5871: theg 'di thabs dang rdo rjer bshad //
NK069(tu)001:5872: snying po'i don kun rin chen mdangs //
NK069(tu)001:5873: kha dog sna lnga'i bdag nyid la //
NK069(tu)001:5874: srog dang rtsal bas ched 'dzin cing //
NK069(tu)001:5875: phyi nang yul kun spro bar mdzad //
NK069(tu)001:5876: ces bshad rgyud sgyu 'phrul thal bas krol ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5877: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa gnyis su myed pa'i
NK069(tu)001:5878: dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyi gsang ba 'di nyid
NK069(tu)001:5885: zhes bstan pa bshad pa'i rjes de nas /
NK069(tu)001:5887: rigs lnga la sogs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dam /
NK069(tu)001:5888: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rang bzhin ston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5889: 'khor dang ston pa gnyis myed do //
NK069(tu)001:5891: thugs ye shes kyi gsang ba 'di nyid /
NK069(tu)001:5896: mdzad pa'i las rnams dbyer myed pa'i rdo rje las phyung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:5898: zhes pa a ma skyes pa /
NK069(tu)001:5900: ma skyes pa'i don la dgyes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5903: zhes pa khams gsum du 'khor zhing sdug bsngal sna tshogs nyams su myong ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:5906: nyes dmigs ci las byung zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:5907: ma rig pa las byung ba'i nyes pas /
NK069(tu)001:5908: gzung ba dang 'dzin pa'i rnam par rtog pa las byung zhing 'phros pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5910: ma rig rtogs pa'i gzung 'dzin gyis //
NK069(tu)001:5913: zhes pa gang du 'phros zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:5914: 'gro ba rigs drug gi sems can sna tshogs kyi gnas su skyes shing lus blangs pa /
NK069(tu)001:5915: so so'i bde skyid dang sdug bsngal skye 'chi la
NK069(tu)001:5916: sogs pa sna tshogs pa nyams su myong ba'i phyir
NK069(tu)001:5917: ro // phyi nang rten 'brel gnyis su 'khor //
NK069(tu)001:5919: spyir le'u bsdud la don gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:5922: 'dir don bsdu ba gtsor ston pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:5923: a skye ba myed pa chos kyi dbyings la /
NK069(tu)001:5924: ho thabs mchog cho 'phrul rol pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5925: srid pa gsum gyi 'khrul 'khor thams cad kun //
NK069(tu)001:5926: log rtog nyid las ci yang ma yin zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:5927: der ji snyed 'jig rten 'khrul pa'i chos zhes pa man chad de /
NK069(tu)001:5928: 'khor ba yongs su shes pa'i lta ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:5929: 'das pa yongs su shes pa'i lta ba rnams bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:5930: rang rig ye shes bdag myed kyi thugs ni /
NK069(tu)001:5931: bya byed myed par kun la dbang bsgyur ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:5932: de nyid yon tan zhing rab yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:5933: gzhan myed rang rig de ltar snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:5934: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las /
NK069(tu)001:5935: thugs rje chen po'i byin gyis brlabs zhes bya ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:5937: gos su myed pa ston pa'i mthar thug go //
NK069(tu)001:5940: de yang bstan pa spyi'i tshul rnams der bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:5942: a ho srid rtsa nyes dmigs /
NK069(tu)001:5944: gnas dang sdug bsngal 'khrul 'khor la sogs pa //
NK069(tu)001:5945: zhes spyi'i gnas 'byung ba chen po lnga'o //
NK069(tu)001:5946: khyad par rang gi sdug bsngal gnas su snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:5948: rgyud drug cig nas cig tu 'khrul zhing 'khor ba shing rta'i 'phang lo lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:5949: bsogs pa ni sdug bsngal las thar ba myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5950: mi mthun bde sdug myong bar 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:5952: log rtog nyid las gzhan du ci yang myed //
NK069(tu)001:5953: ces pa de yang rang rig 'khrul pa'i dbang gis sems nyid log par rtogs par mthong bar zad /
NK069(tu)001:5954: gzhan nas g.yos shing 'byung bar myed do //
NK069(tu)001:5955: rang bzhin nyid las nyams pa myed //
NK069(tu)001:5957: ston ming tshig la dngos po myed //
NK069(tu)001:5959: stong nyid bdag myed ye mkhyen rang rig thugs //
NK069(tu)001:5961: chos thams cad ye nas stong pa'i rang bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:5962: stong pa la bdag gi dngos por grub pa myed pas bdag myed /
NK069(tu)001:5963: stong pa dang bdag myed pa'i don ji lta ba bzhin mkhyen pas ye mkhyen /
NK069(tu)001:5964: ji ltar mkhyen pa de rang gi rig pa'am thugs
NK069(tu)001:5965: yang dag pa'i ye shes yin pas rang rig thugs
NK069(tu)001:5966: so // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las /
NK069(tu)001:5967: thugs rje chen po zhes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5968: dmyigs bya dmyigs byed myed par dran dbang bsgyur //
NK069(tu)001:5969: zhes dmyigs bya chos kyi dbyings la /
NK069(tu)001:5970: dmyigs byed rig pa'i ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:5971: de yang log na myed de /
NK069(tu)001:5972: spros pa dang bral ba'i cha nas ni chos kyi dbyings /
NK069(tu)001:5973: shes shing rtogs pa'i cha nas rig pa'i ye shes de /
NK069(tu)001:5975: rig pa spros pa dang bral bas gnyis myed de /
NK069(tu)001:5976: dbyings ye shes gnyis myed rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:5977: 'khor 'das la yid dran pa'i dbang po ji ltar 'dod par dbang sgyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:5978: thon nas kyang las kyi dbang gis zhes pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:5979: thub pa bcom ldan 'das re res /
NK069(tu)001:5981: ngo mtshar sku gsung yon tan zhing khams las //
NK069(tu)001:5982: zhes shin tu ngo mtshar ya mtshan che ste /
NK069(tu)001:5983: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las dang /
NK069(tu)001:5984: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams yongs su dag pa la sogs pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:5987: 'dul ba rnam pa bzhis don mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:5996: kun tu sku bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:5999: sbrel gzhi dag zhes pa bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:6000: gzhan na myed de de nyid de ltar yin //
NK069(tu)001:6001: zhes bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs kyis skor ba'i rig pa'i ye shes nyid /
NK069(tu)001:6002: mya ngan las 'das pa'i che ba'i yon tan sna tshogs su snang ba de ltar yin no //
NK069(tu)001:6003: zhes rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig du'o //
NK069(tu)001:6004: zhes rdo rje ni thugs so //
NK069(tu)001:6005: gsang ba ni ye shes rtogs par dka' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:6006: mdor na thugs gsang ba'i ye shes rtogs par dka' ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:6008: thub pa drug gi sprul pa grangs myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:6009: zhes 'dzam bu gling bye ba phrag brgyar /
NK069(tu)001:6010: sprul pa'i sku bye ba phrag brgyas chos gsungs pa kun dang /
NK069(tu)001:6011: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad las zhes pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:6012: bsam gyis mi khyab grangs myed pa phyogs bcur snang bar gyur to zhes pa'i bar bsdus so //
NK069(tu)001:6013: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis gsungs pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:6014: zhes dus gsum du gshegs shing phyogs bcu na bzhugs
NK069(tu)001:6015: pa rnams kyis 'gro ba'i don du gsungs pa yang
NK069(tu)001:6016: / de dag thams cad kyang 'di lta ste /
NK069(tu)001:6018: ston ming tshig la dngos po myed zhes brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:6019: zhes pa yan chad bsdus so //
NK069(tu)001:6020: de dag du 'dus par de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyis mkhyen to //
NK069(tu)001:6021: zhes le'u bsdud tshig bzhi tshig tu bcad pa gnyis
NK069(tu)001:6022: po der thams cad 'dus par de ba nyid kyis
NK069(tu)001:6023: yang mkhyen / de dang 'dra ba 'ga' dang 'gal kyang shes so //
NK069(tu)001:6024: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:6025: zhes kun tu bzang po'i thugs rtogs par dka' bas gsang /
NK069(tu)001:6026: de kho na ye shes kyi snying po /
NK069(tu)001:6027: de ni thams cad kyi de kho na nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:6028: chos thams gtan la phab pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6030: // 'khor ba'i chos dang mya ngan 'das pa'i chos rnam pa gnyis gtan la phab ste /
NK069(tu)001:6031: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad ni 'khrul pa'i sems rang snang bar gtan la phab /
NK069(tu)001:6032: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad ni rtogs
NK069(tu)001:6033: pa'i ye shes rang snang bar gtan la phab bo
NK069(tu)001:6034: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dgongs pa gcig tu gyur nas /
NK069(tu)001:6035: zhes le'u gsum pa'i rjes de nas le'u bzhi pa bstan par bzhed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6036: rigs lnga la sogs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:6037: yi ge 'khor lo'i le'u 'di bstan pa la dgongs pa gcig tu gyur pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:6039: yang na de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rang
NK069(tu)001:6040: bzhin ston pa kun tu bzang po nyid yi ge
NK069(tu)001:6041: 'khor lo'i bstan pa la dgongs pa gcig tu gyur
NK069(tu)001:6042: pa'am / yang na yi ge 'khor lo 'di shin tu zab pas /
NK069(tu)001:6043: 'di bshad cing bstan par dka' bas /
NK069(tu)001:6044: de bzhin gshegs pa 'ga' dang 'gas ston myi spyod pas /
NK069(tu)001:6045: de bzhin gshegs pa kun sgros sam /
NK069(tu)001:6046: blos nas bshad dgos pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:6047: dgongs pa gcig tu gyur nas so //
NK069(tu)001:6048: mnyam pa chen po'i tshul rdo rje'i dbyings su /
NK069(tu)001:6049: zhes pa chos thams cad don dam par ma skyes par mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:6050: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid du mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:6051: don dam pa dang kun rdzob tu dbyer myed par mnyam pas mnyam pa chen po'o //
NK069(tu)001:6052: yang na chos thams cad sangs rgyas par mnyam pas mnyam pa chen po'o //
NK069(tu)001:6053: tshul gang du mnyam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6054: dbyings dang ye shes tha mi dad pa'i ngang du mnyam mo //
NK069(tu)001:6055: rdo rje ni rig pa'i ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:6056: dbyings ni chos kyi dbyings kyi /
NK069(tu)001:6057: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ting nge 'dzin las ma g.yos par /
NK069(tu)001:6058: zhes pa de ltar dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med par ngang du /
NK069(tu)001:6059: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ting nge 'dzin las mi g.yo bar bzhugs pa nges bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:6060: de yang chos thams cad ni /
NK069(tu)001:6061: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das bsdus pa'i chos thams cad la bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:6062: de ltar 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad kyang /
NK069(tu)001:6065: ye nas rnam par dag cing sangs rgyas par rtogs nas /
NK069(tu)001:6066: rtogs pa'i don la ting nge 'dzin gyis ma yengs
NK069(tu)001:6067: par bya ba la ni ting nge 'dzin las ma
NK069(tu)001:6069: yang na de ltar chos thams cad de ltar sangs
NK069(tu)001:6070: rgyas pa'i rang bzhin las mi 'da' ba la yang
NK069(tu)001:6071: ting nge 'dzin las ma g.yo bar zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:6072: chos thams cad ming tsam du gnas pa'i yi ge'i /
NK069(tu)001:6074: sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:6075: zhes pa chos thams cad ni /
NK069(tu)001:6076: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad la bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:6077: de yang ming gi mtshan nyid tsam mam /
NK069(tu)001:6078: brtags tsam du yod pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:6079: ming tsam du gnas pa zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:6080: yi ge zhes pa ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:6085: yi ge'i rang bzhin ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:6086: yi ge ye nas rnam par dag cing sangs rgyas pa /
NK069(tu)001:6087: dbyings dang ye shes tha mi dad pas /
NK069(tu)001:6088: thabs dang shes rab mnyam zhing dbyer myi phyed pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:6089: mnyam pa nyid gnyis su myed pa'i rang bzhin du gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:6091: a seng ge blal ba 'dra ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:6092: ka pi wang rtag gyed 'dra ba zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:6093: yi ge'i gzugs sam dbyibs kyi don ston pa la bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:6094: de yang dper na seng ge blal ba'i khar srog chags song na /
NK069(tu)001:6095: mi mngon pa'am mi snang ba dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:6096: chos thams cad chos kyi dbyings su grol nas mi dmyigs par togs pa la bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:6097: ka pi wang rtag gyed 'dra ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:6098: dper na pi wang gi sgra skad snyan pos rna
NK069(tu)001:6099: ba'i dbang po tshim par byed pa dang 'dra bar
NK069(tu)001:6100: / ka kar ma'i sgra las grangs na 'phrin las te /
NK069(tu)001:6101: de bzhin gshegs pa'i 'phrin las kyis 'gro ba sems
NK069(tu)001:6102: can rnams kyi rgyud smin cing grol bar mdzad pa'am
NK069(tu)001:6107: de yang sgra mi 'gyur pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:6113: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i don de /
NK069(tu)001:6114: dngos po dang mtshan mar nam yang mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:6115: byan t+ta na zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:6117: dper na tsha bas khrid nas zan brdegs par byed pa dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:6118: yi ges khrid nas don gtan du phebs par byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6121: de yang yi ge la rten nas don gsal bar byed pas na gsal byed do //
NK069(tu)001:6123: gsal byed ka'i sde tshan dang /
NK069(tu)001:6124: dbyangs yig a'i sde tshan rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:6126: yig 'bru bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rin po che'i 'phreng ba ltar mdzes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6128: yi ge de nyid ye nas dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin yin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6129: de ltar yig 'bru bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po 'di
NK069(tu)001:6130: kun tu bzang po'i sku gsung thugs rda rje las
NK069(tu)001:6131: phyung ba'o // yi ge a la sems sbyang ba ba stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6132: a rab du bstan 'gyur a dkar las /
NK069(tu)001:6133: zhes pa chos kyi dbyings kyi ngang du /
NK069(tu)001:6134: rang gi sems yi ge a dkar por gsal bar bsgoms te /
NK069(tu)001:6135: de yang gsal ba'i tshad brgyad de /
NK069(tu)001:6141: rab tu mi g.yo ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:6144: 'o na dang po a gcig po lhag par bsgoms ci ste zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6145: a ni chos nyid stong pa nyid yin la /
NK069(tu)001:6146: stong pa nyid kyi chos nyid mtshon pa'i a la sems sbyong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:6147: chos nyid de bstan zhing mi 'gyur ba yin pas
NK069(tu)001:6148: de la 'gris pa ni rab tu stan 'gyur ro
NK069(tu)001:6149: // rang gi byang chub sems mtshon pa'i a dkar
NK069(tu)001:6150: po kha dog 'od 'bar ba mdun gyi nam mkhar
NK069(tu)001:6151: sgom pa ni a dkar po /
NK069(tu)001:6153: shin tu phra ba'i a rnams spro //
NK069(tu)001:6154: phyogs bcu gang bar gsal gyur nas //
NK069(tu)001:6155: zhes pa a de las a phra mo sdus bris
NK069(tu)001:6156: pa lta bu a pa ra na phata zhes pas
NK069(tu)001:6157: / phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams gang bar 'phros pas 'phags pa'i thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK069(tu)001:6161: thugs kyi snang ba thob par byas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6163: de la a sa ha ra na h'u zhes bsdus te /
NK069(tu)001:6164: dngos grub tu byin rlabs nas thim pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6166: zhes pa de gsal ba'i tshad ni /
NK069(tu)001:6167: sngar a spros pas chung du ma song la /
NK069(tu)001:6168: phyis bsdus pas a cher ma song ste /
NK069(tu)001:6171: shin tu bstan par gyur nas so //
NK069(tu)001:6172: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:6176: dang po rgyu'i a bsgom pa ston pa ci ste zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6177: de ni cir las dang po bas a stong pa nyid kyi yi ge la sems sbyongs na /
NK069(tu)001:6178: las thams cad grub pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:6179: a gcig po bsgoms pas 'phra mo las su rung na gzhan sbyang sla ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:6180: spyir gsung yi ge gcig pu bsgom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:6181: sku gcig pu bsgom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:6182: thugs stong pa gcig pu 'grub pa tha dad du yod pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6183: 'dir gsung yi ge gcig pu la dgongs pa'i gsung /
NK069(tu)001:6184: ming tshogs gzhan la sems sbyang bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6185: de las ming tshogs gsal 'bar kun //
NK069(tu)001:6186: zhes pa yi ge a de las /
NK069(tu)001:6188: tshig gi tshogs ston par byed pa'i ka kha ga g+ha nga la sogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:6189: kha dog gsal ba 'od 'bar ba kun yang /
NK069(tu)001:6190: spro zhing bsdu ba'ang de bzhin te //
NK069(tu)001:6191: zhes sa ra na pha ra na phata kyis /
NK069(tu)001:6192: 'jig rten khams gang bar spro ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:6193: sang ha ra na h'u gis tshur bsdu ba yang /
NK069(tu)001:6194: a'i spro bsdu de bzhin du tshul mthun par bya ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:6195: 'di ni rdo rje dngos grub kyi //
NK069(tu)001:6196: zhes pa a'i spro bsdu bya ba 'di ni /
NK069(tu)001:6197: sku gsung thugs rdo rje lta bu'i dngos grub kyi rgyu ni /
NK069(tu)001:6198: ting nge 'dzin 'di bstan pa las 'byung ste zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:6199: sems sbyangs pa'i yon tan ni /
NK069(tu)001:6200: bstan 'byung ye shes rgyu yin no //
NK069(tu)001:6201: zhes de ltar blo sbyangs shing 'phro 'du goms shing bstan pa las /
NK069(tu)001:6202: myur du dngos grub 'byung ba'i rgyu'am /
NK069(tu)001:6204: ye shes rdo rje dang 'dra ba'i mchog gi gnas yin no //
NK069(tu)001:6205: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes thob par byed pa'i rgyu lta bu ni /
NK069(tu)001:6206: a li ka li la sems sbyangs pa'i thabs de yin no //
NK069(tu)001:6207: de ni sbyong ba'i ting nge 'dzin to //
NK069(tu)001:6208: dang po sbyang ba'i ting nge 'dzin la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:6209: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i dbang du dang /
NK069(tu)001:6210: rdzogs pa'i rim pa'i dbang du'o //
NK069(tu)001:6212: gnas lus kyi lte ba na /
NK069(tu)001:6213: kun gzhi kun tu bzang po'i sa bon /
NK069(tu)001:6214: thig le nyungs kar tsam pa /
NK069(tu)001:6215: ma lte bu lte 'brel nas 'khor ba thams cad bskyed pa'i rgyu ste /
NK069(tu)001:6216: yi ge a dkar por bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6217: de bstan pa dang lus kyi rtsa rnams a phra mo'i bde bas 'gengs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6218: bde ba de yang 'phel 'grib myed par gyur pas bstan pa thob pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:6219: yang thig le de nyid las ka kha la sogs pa'i yang /
NK069(tu)001:6223: snang la ngo bo ma grub par spros nas /
NK069(tu)001:6224: bde gsal mi rtog pa'i nyams la 'jug pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6226: rdo rje lta bu'i dngos grub bstan par 'byung bas na /
NK069(tu)001:6227: lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes thob par byed pa'i rgyu de yin no //
NK069(tu)001:6228: bskyed pa'i rim pa'i rim pa'i dbang du gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:6229: 'phra mo'i ting nge 'dzin las su rung bar bya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:6230: ting nge 'dzin gsum sgom pa'i gnas skabs so //
NK069(tu)001:6231: phra mo'i ting nge 'dzin las su rung bar sbyong na /
NK069(tu)001:6232: gnas ni rang gi snying kar sgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:6233: a li ka li'i spro bsdu de yang /
NK069(tu)001:6234: snying kar nyi ma zla ba'i dal bkod nas sbyang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:6235: ting nge 'dzin gsum sgom pa'i gnas skabs su bya na /
NK069(tu)001:6236: gnas ni nam mkha' la sgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:6237: de ni rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin du 'dod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6238: de rnams nang du sgom yang spro bsdu ni a rab tu zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:6244: a skye ba myed pa chos kyi dbyings la /
NK069(tu)001:6245: k+sha rang 'byung gi ye shes chen po shar bas /
NK069(tu)001:6246: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su myed pa'i don /
NK069(tu)001:6247: lhag pa chen po chos kyi skur gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6249: ta tha la sogs pa rigs lnga yab yum longs sku'i gtso bo /
NK069(tu)001:6250: ka kha dang pa pha la sogs pa sems dpa' sems ma longs sku'i 'khor du gnas pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:6251: longs sku thabs shes rab kyi sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bar gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:6253: i nas e yan chad de /
NK069(tu)001:6254: sprul pa'i sku thub pa drug gi sems can thams cad kyi don yongs su rdzogs par mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6255: sku gsum po de rnams yang bsdu na gsum /
NK069(tu)001:6260: tig ni shes rab ste sprul sku /
NK069(tu)001:6267: ni kun tu bzang po'i sa bon /
NK069(tu)001:6269: ni byang chub sems dpa'i snying po /
NK069(tu)001:6277: ni sgo ba gshin rje gshed po /
NK069(tu)001:6279: ni lha mo la se sgeg mo /
NK069(tu)001:6287: ni sgo ba stobs po che'o //
NK069(tu)001:6297: ni don yod grub pa'i sa bon bskyed pa'i rgyu'o //
NK069(tu)001:6298: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi yig 'bru'i dkyil 'khor la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:6302: lha rnams dang sbyar te spyod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6305: ka'i sde tshan ge ba nas 'byung /
NK069(tu)001:6306: tsa'i sde tshan lce rtsa dang po las 'byung /
NK069(tu)001:6307: ta log gi sde tshan lce rtse dang kan las 'byung /
NK069(tu)001:6308: ta ma log pa'i sde tshan lce las 'byung /
NK069(tu)001:6309: sa'i sde tshan zhal gyi sgros mchu las 'byung /
NK069(tu)001:6312: la lce dang so las so //
NK069(tu)001:6313: sha dang sa ni lce dang so las so //
NK069(tu)001:6319: dbye ba'i rnam grangs ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:6323: sde tshan gyi yi ge dang /
NK069(tu)001:6327: bod pa'i sgra ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:6339: ta log ni ra sta can no //
NK069(tu)001:6345: lha rnams dang sbyar te bskyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6346: a a nud sarba d+harma'i sgra las drangs na /
NK069(tu)001:6347: chos thams cad ma skyes skye ba myed de /
NK069(tu)001:6348: kun tu bzang mor bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:6349: ka ka ru ni thugs rje byang chub sems te /
NK069(tu)001:6351: tsa tsar ya ni spyad par bya ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:6353: ta tha ga ta ni de bzhin gshegs pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:6355: ta log gams skor te yab kun rdzob kyi cha 'dzin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6356: ma log pa g.yon skor te yum don dam gyi cha 'dzin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6357: pa pa ra mi ta don dam pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:6358: don dam pa'i sems dpa' byams pa la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6359: ya ya ra ni dus bzhi ste sems ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:6360: nga nya na ma bzhi ni yi ge'i las byed klad skor te sgo ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:6361: sha bi sha na dag byed de sgo ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:6362: k+sha ra na rtog pa zad byed kyi yid rang 'byung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:6363: a a ri sa ri ni sgra ni /
NK069(tu)001:6366: i la sogs pa gu gu 'greng bu'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK069(tu)001:6367: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:6368: 'dir ta tha la sogs pa rnams rigs lnga'i yi
NK069(tu)001:6369: ge yin la ka kha sems dpa'i yi ge yin
NK069(tu)001:6372: tha ni sgyu 'phrul rdo rje nyid dang 'gal zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6373: de ni rtog pa'i dbang du dgongs te /
NK069(tu)001:6374: ka kha na dmigs la sogs pa'i skye mched dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:6375: lus la sngon dbang po sgo lngas brda' sprod dgos pas ka kha sngon stan /
NK069(tu)001:6376: sgo lnga brda sprad nas phung po lnga shes dgos pas /
NK069(tu)001:6377: ta tha de nas bstan no //
NK069(tu)001:6378: 'khor bya ba byed pas sngon stan /
NK069(tu)001:6379: gtso bo dbus su bstan no //
NK069(tu)001:6393: ni sgrib pa rnam par sel ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:6419: ni lha'i thub pa srid thub 'dzin /
NK069(tu)001:6421: ni lha ma yin gyi rnam par rgyal ba /
NK069(tu)001:6423: ni myi'i thub pa sh+aakya seng ge /
NK069(tu)001:6425: ni byol song gi thub pa rnam par gnon pa /
NK069(tu)001:6427: ni yi dwags kyi rnam par snang byed /
NK069(tu)001:6429: ni dmyal ba'i chos kyi rgyal po'o //
NK069(tu)001:6434: 'di dag phyung bas 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa /
NK069(tu)001:6436: zhes pa yi ge'i mthu bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6438: phyung ba ni ston pa kun tu bzang po'o sku gsung thugs las so //
NK069(tu)001:6442: 'jig rten drug po re re la phyogs bcu yod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6443: rnam pa drug tu g.yos pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6449: mtha' mtho na dbus dma' ba dang drug go //
NK069(tu)001:6451: pa ni drag tu g.yos pa la rab tu g.yos zhes bya ba yin no //
NK069(tu)001:6452: kun tu rab tu g.yos nas /
NK069(tu)001:6453: ni 'dir g.yos la 'dir mi g.yos bya ba lta bu ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:6454: rnam pa thams cad du g.yos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6455: chos thams cad ming gi mtshan nyid tsam du gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:6456: zhes ming gi mtshan nyid dam /
NK069(tu)001:6457: chos su brtags pa yod pa tsam du gyur pa 'am /
NK069(tu)001:6458: yang na yi ge las ming yong la /
NK069(tu)001:6461: dang po ming du 'byung bar gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:6463: zhes a ni ma skyes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6466: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis /
NK069(tu)001:6468: ched du brjod pa spyir gong du /
NK069(tu)001:6471: zhes de yan chad du lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK069(tu)001:6472: kyi yi ge'i 'bru mthu dang bcas pa bstan pa
NK069(tu)001:6473: de nas / 'di man chad du yi ge'i don ston pas so //
NK069(tu)001:6474: rigs lnga la sogs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dam /
NK069(tu)001:6475: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rang bzhin can
NK069(tu)001:6476: gyi ston pa'i bdag nyid kun tu bzang po nyid
NK069(tu)001:6479: a ni stong dang mi stong gi //
NK069(tu)001:6480: zhes a ni rang bzhin gyis ma skyes shing /
NK069(tu)001:6481: dus gsum du 'dus ma byas pas /
NK069(tu)001:6482: stong pa'i mthar phyin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:6483: don dam par stong dang zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:6484: de nyid rnam pa sna tshogs par snang bas na /
NK069(tu)001:6485: mi stong ba'i mthar phyin te /
NK069(tu)001:6486: kun rdzob tsam du mi stong gi zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:6487: dbu ma'ang dmigs su yod ma yin //
NK069(tu)001:6488: zhes de ltar gnyis ka mthar phyin te gnas tsam na /
NK069(tu)001:6490: dbu ma chos kyi dbyings tsam du yang dmigs su yod pa ma yin no //
NK069(tu)001:6491: de nyid kho na dbyer myed do //
NK069(tu)001:6493: thams cad ming tsam sangs rgyas kun //
NK069(tu)001:6494: zhes chos thams cad ni ming gi mtshan nyid tsam mam /
NK069(tu)001:6495: btags pa yod pa tsam du gnas pa la /
NK069(tu)001:6496: ye nas dag cing sangs rgyas pa bas /
NK069(tu)001:6497: thams cad ming btags pa tsam te /
NK069(tu)001:6499: yi ge'i 'phreng ba nyid la gnas //
NK069(tu)001:6500: zhes de ltar chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i don de gang gis bstan zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6502: yang na yi ge ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:6504: bstan pa'i chos thams cad dang /
NK069(tu)001:6505: rnyad pa'i chos thams cad kyang /
NK069(tu)001:6506: ye nas sangs rgyas pas na /
NK069(tu)001:6507: yi ge yi 'phreng ba nyid la sangs rgyas gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:6508: 'o na yi ge ye nas sangs rgyas na /
NK069(tu)001:6509: sangs rgyas la sku gsum mnga' bas /
NK069(tu)001:6510: yi ge la sku gsum tshang ngam na tshang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:6512: a nyid sna tshogs par snang ba'i //
NK069(tu)001:6513: a skye ba myed pa de nyid //
NK069(tu)001:6514: so so'i don gyi bya ba byed nus pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:6515: mtshan ma'i rnam pa sna tshogs par snang la /
NK069(tu)001:6516: snang tsam nyid na mtshan ma myed pa chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos te /
NK069(tu)001:6517: ma g.yos bzhin du sna tshogs su snang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:6518: chos kyi sku gzung 'dzin spangs pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK069(tu)001:6519: spros pa dang bral bar yul chos kyi dbyings rtogs te /
NK069(tu)001:6520: dbyings dang ye shes tha mi dad pa de ni chos kyi sku yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:6521: a skye ba myed pa de nyid so so'i don
NK069(tu)001:6522: gyi mtshan ma byed nus pa'i mtshan ma'i rnam pa
NK069(tu)001:6524: snang tsam nyid na mtshan ma'i myed pa chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos te /
NK069(tu)001:6525: mtshan ma dang mtshan ma myed pa gnyis su myed pa de ni chos kyi sku yin no //
NK069(tu)001:6527: ka la sogs pa'i bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK069(tu)001:6528: zhes ka la sogs pa'i yig 'bru bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ni /
NK069(tu)001:6529: ye nas lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor
NK069(tu)001:6530: gyi rang bzhin bde ba chen po lhun gyis grub
NK069(tu)001:6532: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:6533: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni /
NK069(tu)001:6534: mtshan gyi me tog la dape'u byed kyi 'bru chags pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6535: 'khor 'das kyi longs spyod gang yang ma kag par sku nyams su tar ba yin pa ltar /
NK069(tu)001:6536: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis skur grub ste /
NK069(tu)001:6537: ye nas chos sku las longs skur snang ba ni a las ka kha byung ba dang 'dra'o //
NK069(tu)001:6539: sgra'i ming gis thams cad bsdus //
NK069(tu)001:6540: zhes sprul pa'i sku dang sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:6542: 'gro ba'i don mthar phyin par byed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:6543: ka la sogs pa yig 'bru bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis /
NK069(tu)001:6546: tshig gi tshogs thams cad brjod par byed /
NK069(tu)001:6547: ston par byed pas na sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:6548: ka la sogs pa'i yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyis /
NK069(tu)001:6556: tshig gis don thams cad bsdus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6557: sku gsum po der gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:6558: mngon rdzogs rgyal po de nyid nges //
NK069(tu)001:6559: zhes yi ges bsdus pa'i chos thams cad kyang /
NK069(tu)001:6560: mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa'i gtan tshigs su des nges so //
NK069(tu)001:6561: e ma'o ngo mtshar ya mtshan gyi //
NK069(tu)001:6562: zhes e ma'o zhes ngam ste /
NK069(tu)001:6563: yi ge nyid kyang ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin pa la /
NK069(tu)001:6564: yi ge yi ges bsdus pa'i chos thams cad kyang sangs rgyas pa de /
NK069(tu)001:6570: 'phrul chen bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i ming //
NK069(tu)001:6571: zhes ngo mtshar che ba'i yig 'bru bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la /
NK069(tu)001:6575: gsum mnan pas rtsa lnga gyur pa'i sgra byung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:6578: tshig rnams ma lus 'dzin pa'i gnas //
NK069(tu)001:6580: tshig rnams mi brjed par 'dzin pa'i gnas su yi ge nyid gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6589: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis mtshan mar yang gsal bas na ngo mtshar che'o //
NK069(tu)001:6591: mtshan ma myed pa las ma g.yos pas ngo mtshar che /
NK069(tu)001:6593: mtshan ma dang mtshan ma myed pa gnyis myed par bsgoms pa las /
NK069(tu)001:6594: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub dang che ba'i yon
NK069(tu)001:6595: tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa gcig 'byung bas 'phrul
NK069(tu)001:6596: che'o // dngos lha bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i ming gi yi ges /
NK069(tu)001:6598: 'dzin pa'i gnas su gyur pa dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:6599: yig 'bru bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis las lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis snang /
NK069(tu)001:6600: snang tsam nyid na mtshan ma myed /
NK069(tu)001:6601: mtshan ma dang mtshan ma myed pa dbyer myed par ston no //
NK069(tu)001:6602: yi ge rang la sbyar na e ma'o ces pa la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6603: sna tshogs don chen smra zhing ston //
NK069(tu)001:6604: zhes tshig gi sgron mes don gyi gser tshol te /
NK069(tu)001:6605: yi ges de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs gtan
NK069(tu)001:6606: la phab pa man cad nas 'jig rten gyi yi
NK069(tu)001:6607: ge phra mo yan chad ston pas na /
NK069(tu)001:6608: don chen po zab mo sna tshogs smra zhing ston te /
NK069(tu)001:6609: sna tshogs ni rgya che ba la dgongs /
NK069(tu)001:6610: don chen ni zab pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6611: dngos myed yi ge'i rang bzhin sems //
NK069(tu)001:6612: zhes ji ltar yi ge la dngos po myed pa bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:6613: sems la dngos po myed do //
NK069(tu)001:6614: yang na sems la dngos po myed pa bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:6615: sems kyi rang bzhin yi ger snang ba la yang dngos po myed do //
NK069(tu)001:6616: dngos po myed pa'i yi ge'i rang bzhin ni rang gi sems so //
NK069(tu)001:6617: bdag myed mtha' bral mi dmyigs kyang //
NK069(tu)001:6618: zhes sems dngos po myed pa de la ni nga
NK069(tu)001:6619: dang bdag tu myed pa'i phyir yang bdag myed ces
NK069(tu)001:6620: bya / mtha' rnam pa gnyis dang bral bas na mtha' bral zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:6621: dngos po dang mtshan ma ji lta bur yang dmyigs su myed yang /
NK069(tu)001:6622: de ni sprul sku 'am thugs sam yi ge'i mtshan nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:6623: dbyibs dang kha dog ming tshogs kyis //
NK069(tu)001:6624: zhes sems dang yi ge'i ngo bo ma grub yang /
NK069(tu)001:6626: kha dog de yi sku mdog dang /
NK069(tu)001:6630: ming gi tshogs rnam pa sna tshogs pa rnams kyis /
NK069(tu)001:6631: rol pa cir yang sprul cing ston //
NK069(tu)001:6632: zhes sems dang yi ge la dngos po dang mtshan ma myed yang /
NK069(tu)001:6633: che ba'i yon tan la rol pa cir yang ma 'gags par snang bas na /
NK069(tu)001:6634: gdul bya la ci yang sprul nas ston no //
NK069(tu)001:6635: sprul pa'i sku'am yi ge'i mtshan nyid de ltar ston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6636: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:6639: phyogs bcu dus bzhir mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas pa'i rgyal ba /
NK069(tu)001:6641: ye shes sems dpa' sku gsung thugs //
NK069(tu)001:6642: zhes ye shes chen pos chos kyi dbyings la sems dpa'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:6644: de dag snang grags kyi dran rtog thams cad sku gsung thugs su rdzogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6645: de yang sku yi ge'i dbyibs /
NK069(tu)001:6648: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa lnga nyid //
NK069(tu)001:6649: ces b+hud+d+ha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK069(tu)001:6650: de la sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum ste bzhi bcu rtsa lnga po nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:6651: de yang bzhi bcu gnyis las /
NK069(tu)001:6652: sku gsung thugs gsum du 'phro ba nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:6653: yi ge'i mgo nas k+sha la rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:6654: zhes yi ge'i mgo'i ber ka ris la sku rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:6655: bar na ti ga la gsung rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:6658: mjug k+sha'i bar la sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:6659: de yang lus kyi yi ge ni /
NK069(tu)001:6661: yan lag gi yi ge ni a +aa i +ai la sogs pa'i dbyangs yig rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:6662: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:6663: b+hud+d+ha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis yod pa la /
NK069(tu)001:6664: 'dir dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa lnga nyid //
NK069(tu)001:6667: lha dang yi ger sbyar ba'i dbang du ste /
NK069(tu)001:6668: yi ge bzhi bcu gnyis lha dang sbyar /
NK069(tu)001:6669: khyab 'jug gi yi ge gsum sku gsung thugs dang sbyar nas /
NK069(tu)001:6670: spyir grangs pas bzhi bcu rtsa lnga nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:6672: 'phrul chen bzhi bcu rtsa lnga'i ming /
NK069(tu)001:6674: 'o na yi ge'i mgo nas k+sha la rdzogs na /
NK069(tu)001:6675: k+sha'i 'og na thub drug gi a yod pa 'jog gam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6676: de ni mgo'i a la rdzogs so //
NK069(tu)001:6677: sems kyi rang bzhin yi ge ste //
NK069(tu)001:6678: zhes sems sna tshogs su snang ba nyid /
NK069(tu)001:6679: yi ge sna tshogs su snang ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:6680: kun gzhi ni yi ge ar snang /
NK069(tu)001:6681: yid kyi rnam par shes pa ni yi ge k+shar snang /
NK069(tu)001:6682: phung po lnga ni +aa h'u s+w+aa h+aa 'am ta tha las s+w+aa bar snang /
NK069(tu)001:6683: 'byung ba lnga ta tha la sogs par snang /
NK069(tu)001:6684: rnam shes ka kha la sogs par snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:6685: yi ge'i dngos po yod ma yin //
NK069(tu)001:6686: zhes sems la dngos po myed pa'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:6687: yi ge la dngos po yod pa ma yin no //
NK069(tu)001:6688: de'i phyir na sems sna tshogs su snang ba nyid /
NK069(tu)001:6689: yi ge sna tshogs su snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:6693: sgo lnga na ro gu gu 'dra'o //
NK069(tu)001:6694: dmyigs myed de nyid sna tshogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:6695: zhes sems dmigs myed de nyid kho na /
NK069(tu)001:6696: sku gsung thugs sna tshogs par snang ste /
NK069(tu)001:6697: de bas na yi ge sna tshogs par snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:6698: sku gsung thugs kyi 'khor lo che //
NK069(tu)001:6699: zhes phung po lnga la sogs par snang ba'i dus na sku /
NK069(tu)001:6700: yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la sogs par snang ba'i dus na gsung /
NK069(tu)001:6701: rtog pa tha dad las grol pa'i dus na thugs /
NK069(tu)001:6702: de rnams ngo bo gcig las ldog pa tha dad pa ni 'khor lo chen po yin no //
NK069(tu)001:6703: sku gsung thugs kyi ngo mtshar gyis //
NK069(tu)001:6704: zhes sku gsung thugs mi bzad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor mnga' ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:6705: phyin ci log gi 'jig rten srid pa gsum na myed pa de ngo mtshar gyis /
NK069(tu)001:6707: zhes de lta bu'i ya mtshan can gyi 'phrul ni /
NK069(tu)001:6708: stong gsum nyungs 'brur bzhugs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:6709: nyungs 'brus stong gsum 'gengs par byed pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:6711: yi ge lha'i dkyil 'khor du bsgoms pas so //
NK069(tu)001:6712: dbyings la dbyings kyis bris pa ste //
NK069(tu)001:6713: zhes kun gzhi gnas 'gyur ba chos kyi dbyings la /
NK069(tu)001:6714: yid gnas 'gyur ba dbyings stong pa'i ye shes ste /
NK069(tu)001:6715: dbyings la ye shes 'byor ba ni bris pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:6716: chos kyi dbyings stong pa la /
NK069(tu)001:6717: ka la sogs pa byung ba ni bris pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6718: yi ge zhes ni de phyir brjod //
NK069(tu)001:6719: ces brjod pa'i sgra sna tshogs par 'byung bar bris pa ni yi ge ste /
NK069(tu)001:6720: dbyings stong pa las brjod pa'i sgra sna tshogs 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:6721: khyab mjug gi yi ge gsum stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6722: mgo ni ma nor lam yin te //
NK069(tu)001:6723: zhes ngo bo ni yig mgo /
NK069(tu)001:6724: don ni ma nor bar rtogs pa'i lam /
NK069(tu)001:6725: thabs shes rab las dbyer myed /
NK069(tu)001:6726: lus ngag yid gsum las thugs so //
NK069(tu)001:6727: tig ni shes rab ming du smra //
NK069(tu)001:6728: zhes ngo bo ni tig te tshag /
NK069(tu)001:6729: don ni ming du smra ba /
NK069(tu)001:6730: thabs shes rab las shes rab stong pa /
NK069(tu)001:6731: lus ngag yid gsum las gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:6732: shad ni thabs chen tshigs su gcod //
NK069(tu)001:6734: don ni tshigs su gcod pa /
NK069(tu)001:6735: thabs shes rab las thabs rgya che ba /
NK069(tu)001:6736: lus ngag yid gsum las sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:6737: thugs rje chen po thabs mkhas pas tshigs su gcod cing /
NK069(tu)001:6740: a ni skye myed de bzhin nyid //
NK069(tu)001:6741: ces rgyu sems can gyi dus na chos 'dus byas dang /
NK069(tu)001:6742: 'dus ma byas gnas su dag pa chos kyi dbyings so //
NK069(tu)001:6743: lha'i gnas skabs na kun tu bzang mo dang /
NK069(tu)001:6744: yi ge'i gnas skabs na ar snang ba gsum dbyer myed de /
NK069(tu)001:6745: chos kyi dbyings skye ba myed pa /
NK069(tu)001:6746: chos thams cad kyi de kho na nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:6747: 'di rnams la rang bzhin mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu rtog tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:6748: skyed pa'i sa bon yi ge dang /
NK069(tu)001:6749: skyed thabs kyi rim pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:6750: yongs su grub pa'i lha'i ngo bo dang /
NK069(tu)001:6752: gtar ka gags bsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:6753: a yi ge kun gyi 'go bor bzhag pa'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6754: a chos kyi dbyings yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:6755: de las thams cad 'byung bas so //
NK069(tu)001:6756: de yang sgyu 'phrul pin tar ta las /
NK069(tu)001:6757: yi ge kun gyi gzhi bo'i rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:6758: yin pa'i phyir na 'go bar bzhag /
NK069(tu)001:6761: rigs lnga'i yi ge bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6762: tha ni sgyu 'phrul rdo rje nyid //
NK069(tu)001:6764: sems can gyi dus na rnam par shes pa'i phung po ni rang bzhin mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:6766: 'bras bu ni rdo rje sems dpa' nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:6767: ta ni snang ba'i sgyu 'phrul nyid //
NK069(tu)001:6769: sems can gyi dus na gzugs kyi phung po ni rang bzhin mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:6770: rig pas ta las skyed pa 'phrul /
NK069(tu)001:6771: lha ni rnam par snang mdzad nyid grub po //
NK069(tu)001:6772: da ni sgyu 'phrul yid bzhin nyid //
NK069(tu)001:6773: ces yi ge da dang tshor ba'i phung po ni rang bzhin mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:6774: de ting nges lhar skyed pa ni 'phrul /
NK069(tu)001:6775: lha ni rin chen 'byung ldan yid bzhin gyi nor
NK069(tu)001:6776: bu dang 'dra ba che ba'i yon tan thams cad
NK069(tu)001:6778: d+ha ni sgyu 'phrul rnam dag nyid //
NK069(tu)001:6779: ces yi ge d+ha dang 'du shes kyi phung po ni rang bzhin mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:6780: de ltar ting nges bsgoms pa 'phrul /
NK069(tu)001:6781: snang ba mtha' yas gsung gi lha /
NK069(tu)001:6782: nyes pa'i skyon gyi ma gos pas rnam dag nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:6783: na ni kun tu sgyu 'phrul nyid //
NK069(tu)001:6784: ces yi ge na dang 'du byed kyi phung po ni rang bzhin mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:6785: des ting nges skyed pa ni 'phrul /
NK069(tu)001:6786: don yod grub pa la kun tu las zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:6787: de yang yi ger snang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:6788: sems can du snang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:6789: lhar snang ba gsum dbyer myed pas nyid zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:6790: tha log la sogs pa la yab tu 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ni ci yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6792: tha log la sogs pa g.yas skor yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:6793: g.yas skor yab tu 'jog pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:6794: tha ma log pa la sogs pa g.yon skor yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:6796: yab la sgyu 'phrul du 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6797: yab thabs yin pa sgyu 'phrul lo //
NK069(tu)001:6798: yum shes rab yin pas drang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:6799: yang 'dir mgor ta tha byung bas yi ge'i gral 'khrugs zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6800: sngon la ka kha mi ston pa ci yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6801: de ni lha dang yi ge brang sprod byas pa'i nad kas /
NK069(tu)001:6802: rigs lnga gtso bo'o yi ge sngon la bstan no //
NK069(tu)001:6803: rigs kyi yum lnga'i yi ge bstan /
NK069(tu)001:6804: tha nas dra bas mngon rdzogs nyid //
NK069(tu)001:6805: ces pa yi ge tha ni go ma'i ta log dang 'bral bas na dra ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:6806: gong ma'i tha ni phung po las skyes pas na thabs /
NK069(tu)001:6807: 'di 'byung ba ni ka las skyed pas na shes rab /
NK069(tu)001:6808: thabs shes rab tu 'brel bas na dra ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:6809: yum rdo rje dbyings phyug mar mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:6810: ta ni dra bas bstan pa nyid //
NK069(tu)001:6811: ces gong gi ta sa'i rlung dang /
NK069(tu)001:6812: 'di 'byung bas yi ta 'brel pa ni dra ba /
NK069(tu)001:6813: de ni rtan pa sa'i rang bzhin sa sangs rgyas spyan nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:6814: da ni dra bas lha me nyid //
NK069(tu)001:6815: ces me'i rlung rang la gnas pa 'du shes kyi phung po dang /
NK069(tu)001:6817: me gos dkar mo nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:6818: lha mo ni gsal la g.yer ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:6819: d+ha ni dra bas 'khril pa nyid //
NK069(tu)001:6820: ces gong gi d+ha dang 'di gnyis nang tshor ba chu'i rang bzhin dang /
NK069(tu)001:6821: phyi'i yul 'byung ba chu gnyis 'brel bas dra ba /
NK069(tu)001:6822: 'khril ba ni chu la ma ma ki nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:6823: na ni dra bas kun du 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:6824: ces gong gi na log ni 'du shes kyi phung po dang /
NK069(tu)001:6825: 'di 'byung ba rlung gnyis 'brel bas na dra ba /
NK069(tu)001:6826: kun du 'gyur ba ni 'byung ba rlung ste /
NK069(tu)001:6830: yum lnga dbyer myed pa'i rang bzhin du sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:6831: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:6832: tha ma log pa'i sde tshan la dra bar 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ci yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6833: yum lnga skyed pa'i yi ge yin pa'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:6834: yum ni yab dang 'brel bas dra bar smos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6835: rnam shes kyi sems dpa' dang /
NK069(tu)001:6836: gshin rje gshed kyi yi ge bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6837: ka ni spyan gyi thugs kyi mchog /
NK069(tu)001:6838: ces yi ge ar snang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:6839: sems can gyi myig gi rnam shes rig cing gsal ba'i thugs lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:6840: lha byang chub sems dpa' sa'i snying po gsum dbyer myed pa ni mchog yin no //
NK069(tu)001:6841: kha ni snyan gyi thugs kyi mchog /
NK069(tu)001:6843: sems can gyi sna'i dbang po rig cing gsal ba thugs lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:6844: byang chub sems dpa' phyag na rdo rje gsum dbyer myed par rtogs pa mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:6845: ga ni shangs kyi thugs kyi mchog /
NK069(tu)001:6847: sems can gyi sna'i dbang po rig cing gsal bar rtogs pa lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:6848: byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha'i snying po gsum dang dbyer myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6849: g+ha ni ljags kyi thugs kyi mchog /
NK069(tu)001:6851: sems can gyi lce'i dbang po rig cing gsal ba thugs lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:6852: byang chub sems dpa' spyan ras gzigs gsum dbyer myed pas na mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:6853: nga ni thugs kyang 'jigs byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6854: zhes yi ge na nga'i yi ge klad skor /
NK069(tu)001:6855: sems can na lus reg pa rnam shes kyi las byed /
NK069(tu)001:6856: lha ni khro bo gshin rje gshed po /
NK069(tu)001:6857: lha tshogs rnams thugs mtshan mar snang ba'i ngo bo ste /
NK069(tu)001:6858: mtshan ma myed pa las ma g.yos par byed pas na 'jigs byed do //
NK069(tu)001:6859: nga nya ma o la khro bo'i yi ger 'jog pa ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6860: rgya gar gyi yi ge la ka'i sde tshan gyi klad skor nga yin /
NK069(tu)001:6861: tsa'i sde tshan gyi klad skor nya yin /
NK069(tu)001:6862: pa'i sde tshan gyi klad skor ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:6864: khro bos lha'i las byed pas chos mthun pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:6865: lus kyi rtog pa dang lha brang sprad pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:6866: lus kyi dbang pos las byed pas na khro bor bshad pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:6867: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:6868: ka'i sde tshan la thugs su 'jog pa'i ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6869: rnam par shes pa nang na rig cing gsal ba ni thugs yin pa te /
NK069(tu)001:6870: de yang sngags kyi mdo rgyan dam pa las /
NK069(tu)001:6871: rnam par shes pa kun yid yin //
NK069(tu)001:6872: yid kyi rnam shes gcod byed pa //
NK069(tu)001:6873: thugs nyid pas na sna tshogs pas //
NK069(tu)001:6874: de phyir thugs kyi mchog zhes bya //
NK069(tu)001:6875: zhes legs par gsungs pas nas gal ba myed do //
NK069(tu)001:6876: nang gi sems ma dang stob po che'i yi ge bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6877: tsa ni spyan gyi sku'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:6878: ces yi ge tsa ni myig gi yul gzugs gnas
NK069(tu)001:6879: su dag pa lha mo sgeg mo'i sku skyed pa'i
NK069(tu)001:6881: tsa'i sde tshan la skur 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ci yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6882: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:6883: rtog tshogs kyi dbang gis 'gyur ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:6884: tsa'i sde tshan lha mo rnams kyi yi ge yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:6885: yul phyi rol gzugs su grub pa la dgongs nas skur bshad pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:6886: tsha ni snyan gyi sku'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:6887: ces tsha ni rna ba'i yul sgra gnas su dag pa /
NK069(tu)001:6888: lha mo gar ma can ma'i sku skyed pa'i sa bon mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:6889: dza ni shangs kyi sku'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:6890: ces dza ni sna'i dbang po dri gnas su dag pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:6891: lha mo 'phreng ba ma'i sku skyed pa'i yig 'bru mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:6892: dz+ha ni ljags kyi sku'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:6893: ces dz+ha ni lce'i dbang po yul ro gnas su dag pa /
NK069(tu)001:6894: lha mo g+hir ti klu ma sku skyed pa'i yig 'bru'i mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:6895: nya ni sku yang 'jigs byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6896: zhes nya ni yul du 'dzin pa rnam shes bde
NK069(tu)001:6897: ba'i ye shes su 'jig par byed pa khro bo
NK069(tu)001:6898: stobs po che'o // de yang sku'i rang bzhin ma 'gags par snang /
NK069(tu)001:6899: ma 'gags pa nyid mtshan ma myed pa las ma g.yos par byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6900: dbang po'i byang chub sems dpa' dang /
NK069(tu)001:6901: rta mgrin gyi yi ge bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6902: pa ni spyan gyi gsung gi mchog /
NK069(tu)001:6903: ces pa ni dmig gi dbang pos yul la brda sprod pas gsung ste /
NK069(tu)001:6904: byang chub sems dpa' byams pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6905: pa'i sde tshan la gsung du bzhag pa'i rgyu mtshan ci zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6907: pa'i sde tshan dbang po'i byang chub sems dpa' skyed pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:6908: dbang pos yul la go bar brda sprod pa'i dngos nas gsungs so //
NK069(tu)001:6909: de yang rdo rje g.yung drung gi mdo las /
NK069(tu)001:6910: 'khyil zhung gnas pas sku gsung thugs //
NK069(tu)001:6913: pha ni snyan gyi gsung gi mchog /
NK069(tu)001:6914: ces pha ni rna ba'i dbang pos brda sprod pa gsung lta bu ste /
NK069(tu)001:6916: ba ni shangs kyi gsung gi mchog /
NK069(tu)001:6917: ces pa ni sna'i dbang po dri la brda sprod pa'i gsung lta bu ste /
NK069(tu)001:6918: byang chub sems dpa' 'jam dpal lo //
NK069(tu)001:6919: b+ha ni ljags kyi gsung gi mchog /
NK069(tu)001:6920: ces b+ha ha ne lce'i dbang po ro la brda sprod pas gsung ste kun bzang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:6921: ma ni gsung yang 'jigs byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6922: zhes ma ni lus kyi rnam shes thams cad bde bar 'jigs byed khro bo rta mgrin no //
NK069(tu)001:6924: don gyi gsung spros pa myed par rtogs par byed pa'i mthu can no //
NK069(tu)001:6925: dus bzhi'i lha mo bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6926: ya ni skye ba rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:6928: phyi snod skye ba ltar snang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:6931: lha mor shes pa kho na rnam par dag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6932: wa ni gnas pa dag pa yin //
NK069(tu)001:6933: ces yi ge wa ni phyi snod du gnas par 'dzin pa gnas su dag pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6934: lha mo me tog ma'i rang bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:6935: ra ni 'jig pa dag pa yin //
NK069(tu)001:6936: zhes ra ni phyi snod 'jig par 'dzin pa gnas
NK069(tu)001:6937: su dag par rtogs pa lha mo mar me'i rang
NK069(tu)001:6938: bzhin no // la ni stong pa dag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6939: zhes phyi snod stong par 'dzin pa gnas su dag par sbyong ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:6941: de skyed pa'i yi ge la'o //
NK069(tu)001:6942: sha ni rtag myed dag pa ste //
NK069(tu)001:6943: zhes yi ge sha ni khro mo lcags kyu ma skyed pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:6944: de ni rtag par lta ba dag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6945: sha ni chad pa'ang yod ma yin //
NK069(tu)001:6946: zhes sha ni khro mo zhags pa ma skyed pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:6947: des chad par lta ba ma yin par rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:6948: sha'i sde tshan la mtha' bzhi yangs par 'jog pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6949: sgo ma bzhis mtha' bzhi yod /
NK069(tu)001:6950: mtha' bzhir zhen pa las grol na sgo ma yin /
NK069(tu)001:6951: sgo ma bzhi skyed pa'i yi ge yin pa na'o //
NK069(tu)001:6952: 'dir gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:6954: btsun mo 'das pa dang zhes pa'i dus bzhir byung /
NK069(tu)001:6955: 'das dang da ltar ma 'ongs 'byung bar ma nges pa bzhir byung /
NK069(tu)001:6956: 'dir yang na skye ba rnam par dag zhes pas /
NK069(tu)001:6957: skye ba gnas pa 'jig pa stong pa bzhir byung /
NK069(tu)001:6958: yang dbyar rgun ston spyid ma byung bas thams cad 'gal lo zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:6960: dus ring ba'i dbang du 'jig chags stong gnas bzhi yin /
NK069(tu)001:6961: dus bar ma ni 'das ma 'ongs da ltar 'byung bar ma nges pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:6962: dus nye ba ni dbyar dgun ston spyid bzhi yin no //
NK069(tu)001:6964: ya'i sde tshan la 'jig chags stong gnas su 'jog pa'i 'thad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6965: phyi rol yul ni 'jig chags stong gnas bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:6967: dus bzhir 'dzin pa dag pa'i phyi'i lha mo bzhi yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:6968: de'i skyed yig yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:6969: sa ni mtha' bral bdag myed pa //
NK069(tu)001:6970: zhes sa ni lcags sgrog ma skyed pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:6971: des mtha' thams cad dang bral bas chos nyid bdag myed par rtogs so //
NK069(tu)001:6972: ha ni mtshan ma myed pa nyid //
NK069(tu)001:6973: ces ha ni khro mo dril bu ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:6974: des chos thams cad mtshan ma myed par rtogs so //
NK069(tu)001:6976: k+sha ni ye shes thugs kyi thugs //
NK069(tu)001:6977: zhes k+sha ni yid rang 'byung gi ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:6978: rnam shes kyi gnas yongs su dag pa'i thugs so //
NK069(tu)001:6979: de yang yid kyi rnam shes dang /
NK069(tu)001:6980: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid dang /
NK069(tu)001:6981: rnam shes kyi yid rtogs so //
NK069(tu)001:6982: k+sha thub pa drug du byung ba'i 'thad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6983: tsa ki ta yan gyi tan tra las /
NK069(tu)001:6984: k+sha ni kun tu bzang po ste /
NK069(tu)001:6985: kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' las ni //
NK069(tu)001:6986: bdag gi phyag rgya'i klong yangs su //
NK069(tu)001:6987: chos nyid yangs pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK069(tu)001:6988: 'bras bu kun tu bzang por shar //
NK069(tu)001:6989: bdag dang gnyis myed rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:6990: bde chen rgyal ba kun gyi thugs //
NK069(tu)001:6991: de rtogs pa las thub drug 'byung //
NK069(tu)001:6993: sprul pa sku'i yi ge bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:6994: i ni rdul snyed lha rnams su //
NK069(tu)001:6995: zhes i las thub pa srid thub 'dzin skyed de /
NK069(tu)001:6996: gdul bya lha'i rigs rdul phra rab snyed dang mnyam pa 'dul ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:6997: +ai ni rdul snyed lha ma yin //
NK069(tu)001:6998: zhes i las thub pa rnam par rgyal ba skyed de /
NK069(tu)001:6999: gdul bya lha ma yin gyi ris rdul snyed yod pa rnams 'dul lo //
NK069(tu)001:7000: u ni rdul snyed mi rnams su //
NK069(tu)001:7001: zhes u las sh+aakya seng ge skyed pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:7002: gdul bya mi rdul snyed 'dul ba'i gnyen po'o //
NK069(tu)001:7003: +au ni rdul snyed byol song rnams //
NK069(tu)001:7004: zhes +au las rnam par gnon pa skyed de /
NK069(tu)001:7005: gdul bya byol song gi rigs rdul snyed 'dul ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:7006: e ni rdul snyed yi dwags su //
NK069(tu)001:7007: zhes e las thub pa rnam par snang byed skyed de /
NK069(tu)001:7008: yi dwags kyi rigs rdul snyed yod pa 'dul lo //
NK069(tu)001:7009: +ae ni rdul snyed dmyal ba rnams //
NK069(tu)001:7010: zhes e las thub pa chen po chos kyi rgyal po skyed de /
NK069(tu)001:7011: gdul bya dmyal ba'i rigs rdul phra rab dang mnyam pa 'dul ba'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:7012: a thub pa drug tu 'jog pa'i rgyu mtshan ni ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:7013: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:7014: a drug gis skye ba myed pa mtshon la /
NK069(tu)001:7015: gu gu 'greng bus skye ba'i cho 'phrul mtshon te /
NK069(tu)001:7017: yang na a li ni shes rab kyi yi ge te /
NK069(tu)001:7018: thub pa drug yul spangs pa dang mthun no //
NK069(tu)001:7019: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i yi ge bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:7020: o ni thams cad 'jigs par byed //
NK069(tu)001:7022: +ao ni thams cad zhig pa yin //
NK069(tu)001:7025: bdud rtsi ni lus kyi khams bdud rtsi byang chub sems /
NK069(tu)001:7028: gsang ba'i dbang po rdo rje dang /
NK069(tu)001:7029: gsang ba'i rnam shes bde ba skyes pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:7030: khams bco brgyad dang phyin ci log thams cad bde bar 'jig par byed /
NK069(tu)001:7031: bde ba nyid kyang brjod pa dang bral ba'i ngang ye shes lngar zhig pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:7033: zhes yi ge nyid ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin pa la /
NK069(tu)001:7034: yi ge thun mong du snang ba'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:7035: rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs gsogs /
NK069(tu)001:7036: yi ge lhar snang bas 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs /
NK069(tu)001:7037: sku gsung thugs kyi 'phreng ba bsdus //
NK069(tu)001:7038: zhes chos thams cad sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK069(tu)001:7039: du sangs rgyas shing breng ma chad pas na 'phreng
NK069(tu)001:7040: ba / der thams cad 'dus pas bsdus so //
NK069(tu)001:7041: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:7042: o ni thams cad zhig pa yin zhes la /
NK069(tu)001:7046: yi ge zhig na myed la thams cad zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:7048: spyir yi ge lha dang brang sprad /
NK069(tu)001:7049: lha rtog pa dang brang sprad pas /
NK069(tu)001:7050: lus kyi rtog pa rang ka ma lha dang sbyar /
NK069(tu)001:7051: rtog pa de rnams lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes
NK069(tu)001:7052: su rtogs par byed pa lus kyi dbang po yin
NK069(tu)001:7053: pas na / rtog pa ye shes su zhing pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7059: zhes a skye ba myed pa'i dbyings las /
NK069(tu)001:7060: ho 'gag pa myed pa'i yi ger shar ba las /
NK069(tu)001:7062: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang
NK069(tu)001:7063: gnyis su myed pa'i dkyil 'khor de dag nyid gsang
NK069(tu)001:7064: ba 'di nyid / ces le'u rgyas par bshad pa'i rjes de nas stus pa ston pas so //
NK069(tu)001:7066: ngo bo sangs rgyas yab yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:7067: don dbyings dang ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:7068: rtags thabs dang shes rab bo //
NK069(tu)001:7070: nang thabs dang shes rab gnyis myed //
NK069(tu)001:7071: gsang ba dbyings gnyis myed do //
NK069(tu)001:7072: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan 'phrin las rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:7073: zhes yang dag pa'i ye shes nyid snang ba'i dngos nas sku /
NK069(tu)001:7079: de lnga yang dag pa'i ye shes su cig pas na rdo rje'o //
NK069(tu)001:7080: de lta bu las phyung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:7081: de bas na le'u dbyer du sdud pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7083: zhes a ma skyes pa stong pa /
NK069(tu)001:7085: snang stong ngo mnyam gyi rig pa la dgyes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7087: thabs dang shes rab dgyes sprin /
NK069(tu)001:7088: zhes thabs ni yab ste gtso bo sku'i phyag rgya /
NK069(tu)001:7089: shes rab yum te gtso bo sku'i phyag rgya /
NK069(tu)001:7090: yab yum gyi dgyes sprin byang chub sems so //
NK069(tu)001:7091: yang na thabs rang rig pa'i ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:7093: shes rab kyis dbyings rtogs pas dgyes sprin no //
NK069(tu)001:7094: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dgongs pa gcig tu gyur nas /
NK069(tu)001:7096: sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las phyung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:7098: a rab tu bstan 'gyur a kar nas /
NK069(tu)001:7099: bstan 'byung ye shes rgyu yin no //
NK069(tu)001:7100: zhes pa'i bar rnams bsdus pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:7101: byang chub sems tshogs rgyu 'khor lo //
NK069(tu)001:7102: zhes lhag pa byang chub sems kyi tshogs las dngos grub dang /
NK069(tu)001:7105: des lha'i 'khor lo grub pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:7106: a ka kha ga g+ha nga zhes pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:7107: a ho zhes pa'i bar rnams 'dir 'dus pas na bsdus so //
NK069(tu)001:7110: de'i 'bras bu ni rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi
NK069(tu)001:7111: dkyil 'khor du smin par byed grub par byed pas
NK069(tu)001:7112: / de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis zhes pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:7113: mngon rdzogs rgyal po de nyid nges zhes pa'i bar du bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:7114: ngo mtshar ming tshogs bzhi bcu gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:7115: zhes dngos grub dngos su gang grub zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:7116: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor thob cing grub pas par byed na ngo mtshar to //
NK069(tu)001:7117: a ni skye med de bzhin nyid zhes pa nas
NK069(tu)001:7118: os ni thams cad zhig pa yin zhes pa'i bar
NK069(tu)001:7119: du bsdu'o // 'dus ma byas nyid 'dus byas /
NK069(tu)001:7121: 'dus ma byas kyi chos kyi dbyings nyid 'dus byas
NK069(tu)001:7122: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du snang
NK069(tu)001:7123: ba'o // e ma ngo mtshar ya mtshan gyi /
NK069(tu)001:7125: rol pa cir yang sprul cing ston zhes pa'i bar bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:7127: zhes don dam par yi ge bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis 'dus ma byas su gnas pa las /
NK069(tu)001:7128: 'dus byas lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor 'byin pa las ma 'da' ba'i dam tshig go //
NK069(tu)001:7129: der ni phyogs bcu dus bzhir rdzogs pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:7131: yi ge'i 'og nas k+sha la rdzogs zhes pa'i bar du bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:7133: mda' bar mi mdzad dbang myed /
NK069(tu)001:7134: rgyu rkyen 'tshogs pa'i mthu chen yin /
NK069(tu)001:7135: zhes rgyu sa bon skyes bu la /
NK069(tu)001:7136: rkyen rtsi chu lud la sogs pa 'tshogs na /
NK069(tu)001:7137: 'bras bu myu gu sngon po rang dbang myed par skye ba dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:7138: rgyu chos nyid dag pa las /
NK069(tu)001:7139: rkyen thabs dang shes rab tu ldan na /
NK069(tu)001:7140: 'bras bu sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rang dbang myed par thob par byed pas na /
NK069(tu)001:7144: rgyu rkyen tshogs pa'i mthu las grub pas so //
NK069(tu)001:7145: der ni sems kyi rang bzhin yi ge ste zhes pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:7146: shad ni thabs chen tshigs su gcod /
NK069(tu)001:7148: yang na yi ge'i 'khor lo tshogs chen 'di /
NK069(tu)001:7149: sku gsung thugs kyi 'phrang bar bsdus //
NK069(tu)001:7152: zhes le'u der 'dus pa la rab tu dgyes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7153: zhes rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK069(tu)001:7156: gsang ba ni thugs de rtogs par dka' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:7157: de yang thugs la thugs kyis brjod /
NK069(tu)001:7159: don dam par na gang yang brjod pa myed pas na rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig go //
NK069(tu)001:7160: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad yi ge'i 'khor lo gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:7161: zhes de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad yi ger gyur /
NK069(tu)001:7162: yi ge ye nas sangs rgyas pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:7163: yi ge dang de bzhin gshegs pa dbyer myed par gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:7164: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:7165: zhes gsang ba rtogs par dka' ba /
NK069(tu)001:7167: de kho na nyid mi slu ba /
NK069(tu)001:7169: yi ge'i 'phreng ba 'khor lor bskod pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7171: // zhes yi ge ni bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis so //
NK069(tu)001:7172: 'phreng ba ni rin po che'i 'phreng ba rgyus pa bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:7175: yang na che ba'i yon tan 'phreng ba lta bur ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7176: 'khor lo ni yi ge nyid kyi lha'i 'khor lo'o //
NK069(tu)001:7177: bskod pa ni tha dad myed bzhin du tha dad pa'i rnam par bkod pa ste le'u bzhi pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7178: de nas yi ge 'khor lo'i sprin dkod pa las /
NK069(tu)001:7179: zhes yi ge phreng ba'i le'u bstan pa'i rjes de nas /
NK069(tu)001:7180: sgyu 'phrul sgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin ston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7181: yig 'bru bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du bkod do //
NK069(tu)001:7183: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor che ba'i yon tan sna tshogs par 'byung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:7184: cir yang sgrub tu rung ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:7188: sa gzhi las skyes 'khrungs skye ba dang 'dra ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:7189: sgyu 'phrul rnam par 'phros gang 'phros pa 'di ched du brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:7190: zhes sgyu ni shes rab stong pa /
NK069(tu)001:7192: de gnyis tha dad pa myed bzhin du tha dad
NK069(tu)001:7193: pa'i rnam par 'phro ba 'di 'gro ba'i ched du
NK069(tu)001:7194: brjod pa'o // rtsa ba myed pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK069(tu)001:7195: zhes kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems ni ye sdod ma nas rnam par dag ste /
NK069(tu)001:7196: cig dang du ma'i ngo bo dang bral ba /
NK069(tu)001:7199: ji lta bu'i ngo bor yang grub pa myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7200: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK069(tu)001:7201: zhes kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems ji lta ba bzhin du phyin ci ma log pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:7202: rig pa mngon du shar ba de gnas 'gyur ba'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:7203: sku dang ye shes la sogs te mya ngan las
NK069(tu)001:7204: 'das pa'i che ba'i yon tan sna tshogs su yang
NK069(tu)001:7205: rang snang la / ma rtogs pa'am 'khrul pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:7206: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad du yang snang bas /
NK069(tu)001:7207: rtogs ma rtogs kyi dbang gis /
NK069(tu)001:7208: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:7209: rgyu ni kun gzhi byang chub kyi sems yin pa'i phyir na rtsa ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:7210: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK069(tu)001:7211: zhes sems ni ci'i ngo bor yang ma grub la /
NK069(tu)001:7212: sems yi ger snang yang yi ge la dngos po ma grub ste /
NK069(tu)001:7213: sems dang yi ge dbyer myi phyed pa'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:7214: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te /
NK069(tu)001:7216: yi ge yid bzhin rin chen sprin //
NK069(tu)001:7217: zhes sems yi ger rang snang la /
NK069(tu)001:7218: yi ge dkyil 'khor du bkod de bsgoms pa las /
NK069(tu)001:7219: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzu 'phrul dang /
NK069(tu)001:7221: che ba'i yon tan sna tshogs par 'byung zhing /
NK069(tu)001:7222: sgrub pa dang sgyur du stub pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:7223: dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che
NK069(tu)001:7224: la rtog pa myed bzhin du sems can gyi dgos
NK069(tu)001:7225: 'dod skong ba'am / nam mkha' la rtog pa myed bzhin du sprin las char bab nas /
NK069(tu)001:7226: sa gzhi la skye 'khrungs smin pa ltar /
NK069(tu)001:7227: yi ge las dngos grub sna tshogs pa grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7229: zhes rgyu ni yig 'bru bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis mtshan
NK069(tu)001:7230: ma'i rnam pa kha dog gsal zhing 'od 'phro bar
NK069(tu)001:7231: bsgom pa'am / 'phrul ni de las lha bzhi bcu
NK069(tu)001:7232: rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor du sku mdog dang mtshan
NK069(tu)001:7233: ma'i rnam par gsal bar bsgom pa la bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:7234: dra ba'i dkyil 'khor mngon rdzogs pas //
NK069(tu)001:7235: zhes dra ba ni de ltar yig 'bru dang lha'i mtshan mar gsal ba yang /
NK069(tu)001:7236: gsal tsam nyid na mtshan ma myed pa las ma g.yos te /
NK069(tu)001:7237: mtshan ma dang mtshan ma myed pa gnyis shes rab kyis rtog par bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:7238: ting nge 'dzin gyis dgongs pa rtse gcig tu yang
NK069(tu)001:7239: ngang yang du 'dris par bsgom pa'i mthus 'bras bu
NK069(tu)001:7241: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:7242: zhes de ltar mtshan ma'i rnam pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:7243: spros pa dang bral ba gnyis med du rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:7244: ting nge 'dzin las su rung nas mngon du gyur pa'i dus su /
NK069(tu)001:7245: phyogs bcu dus bzhi thams cad gnas pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:7247: zhes phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i sangs rgyas
NK069(tu)001:7248: kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi
NK069(tu)001:7250: mya ngan las 'das pa'i che ba'i yon tan thams cad grub cing thob par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:7257: bdag rnam par snang mdzad du bsgoms nas /
NK069(tu)001:7258: thugs ka nas a dkar po spros la /
NK069(tu)001:7259: dug la phog pas bdud rtsir sbyangs nas /
NK069(tu)001:7261: rang rnam snang gi nga rgyal gyis snying khar a las lus bdud rtsir khengs par bsgoms na /
NK069(tu)001:7263: +amo 'dzi na 'dzig a smri te h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK069(tu)001:7265: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad sel zhing //
NK069(tu)001:7266: zhes nad rtsa ba bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:7270: dug gsum cha mnyam pa las 'dus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7272: de re re la brgya bargya'o //
NK069(tu)001:7274: bdag rdo rje sems dpar bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:7275: thugs kar rdo rje la a bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:7277: as bdud rtsis nad gsal nus so //
NK069(tu)001:7279: ro ga pra sha ma na s+w+aa h+aa /
NK069(tu)001:7283: thugs kar rin po che la swa bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:7284: swa rata na 'drig ma ma ba su spus ting ku ru ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK069(tu)001:7286: longs spyod ci 'dod nam mkha' las char du bab bo //
NK069(tu)001:7288: zhes bdag snang ba mtha' yas su bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:7289: thugs kar pad ma la a bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:7291: ngan song gsum gyi sdug bsngal 'joms par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:7296: ces bdag don yod grub par bsgoms pa'i thugs khar rdo rje rgya gram la ha bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:7297: de las rang ji ltar bsam pa bzhin du sgom ste /
NK069(tu)001:7298: rang ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du sgyur du yang stub /
NK069(tu)001:7299: gang bsgrubs pa yang 'grub par 'gyur ro /
NK069(tu)001:7302: 'dir lha thams cad kyi las tshogs byung nas /
NK069(tu)001:7303: sgo ba dang kun bzang yab yum gyi dang thub
NK069(tu)001:7304: pa drug la las tshogs ma byung ba ci te
NK069(tu)001:7305: zhe na / de ni kun bzang yab yum gsung ba'i ston pa yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:7306: thub drug 'gro drug la chos ston pas le'u gsum par gsungs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:7307: sgo bas zhi rgyas dbang drag gi las byed pas /
NK069(tu)001:7308: 'di dag thams cad kyang zhi rgyas dbang drag tu 'dus pas ma gsungs so //
NK069(tu)001:7309: yang na longs sku 'khor bcas rnams gsungs so /
NK069(tu)001:7311: nam mkha' rdo rje sra 'byung zhing //
NK069(tu)001:7312: zhes bdag nam mkha' dbyings phyug mar bsgoms nas /
NK069(tu)001:7313: thugs ka nas sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor nam mkhar bsgoms na /
NK069(tu)001:7314: nam mkha' nyid rdo rje brag bzhin du sra bar dmyigs na yang /
NK069(tu)001:7316: bar na me yang 'tshig pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:7317: zhes bdag gos dkar mo'i thugs ka nas /
NK069(tu)001:7318: ram las me 'bar bar sgom na /
NK069(tu)001:7319: thams cad me 'bar nas thal bar 'gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:7320: de bas tshig cing sreg pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:7322: zhes bdag ma ma ki'i thugs ka nas /
NK069(tu)001:7326: sa skam las kyang chu 'byung ba yang de bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:7328: zhes bdag dam tshig sgrol ma'i thugs ka nas /
NK069(tu)001:7329: yam las ye shes kyi rlung bsgoms na /
NK069(tu)001:7330: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad rlung gis 'thor nus so //
NK069(tu)001:7331: thams cad stongs shing ltung bar 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:7332: zhes bdag sangs rgyas spyan du bsgoms pa'i thugs ka nas /
NK069(tu)001:7333: lam las gser gyi sa gzhir bsgoms nas /
NK069(tu)001:7334: de je chung je 'phra la 'thar stong par bsgoms na /
NK069(tu)001:7336: sa la rten pa'i sems can thams cad rten sa myed de ltung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:7338: zhes nang gi sems dpa' yab yum gyis bstan /
NK069(tu)001:7340: yab yum la se sgeg mor bsgoms nas /
NK069(tu)001:7341: sbyor ba las byang sems lha mo bzhir sprul te /
NK069(tu)001:7342: dgra'i rnam par shes pa mar me ma lta bu dgug pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:7343: bgegs kyi rnam shes dud ka kug na /
NK069(tu)001:7345: bud myed yang rgyal po dang blon po yang khugs /
NK069(tu)001:7346: gang dbang du bya ba de yang khugs par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:7348: zhes bdag phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK069(tu)001:7349: yum nir ti mar bsgoms nas /
NK069(tu)001:7350: yam las rlung tog nas zhing khams gzhan du gtang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:7351: dgra la sprul pa'i pho nyar gtang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:7352: ro lang la sogs pa'i cho 'phrul btang ba yang grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:7354: zhes bdag spyan ras gzigs dang yum g+tir klu mar
NK069(tu)001:7355: bsgoms thugs ka nas ye shes lnga'i 'od kyis dgra
NK069(tu)001:7357: dgra bgegs kyi kha rdo rje rgya gram gyis rgya pa na ngag bcing pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7359: zhes bdag nam mkha'i snying po dang yum ma le 'phreng ba mar bsgoms nas /
NK069(tu)001:7363: rkang lag 'khums pa dang zha grum du song ba la spros na /
NK069(tu)001:7364: byad grol zhing zha grum sos par 'ag+r+yura ro //
NK069(tu)001:7365: spyi'i sems dpa' yab yum gyi bstan /
NK069(tu)001:7367: bdag byams pa dang yum d+hush+pe spos mar bsgoms nas /
NK069(tu)001:7368: nam mkha' la sprin bsgoms na sad thub /
NK069(tu)001:7369: thugs ka nas a las bdud rtsir sbyangs na 'chi ba gsos /
NK069(tu)001:7370: rlung gis sprin gtor na ser ba thub /
