NK069(tu)001:7371: lo tog dang nad la sogs pa'i gso ba'i yul
NK069(tu)001:7372: gang la dmigs pa thams cad gsos par 'gyur ro
NK069(tu)001:7374: zhes bdag 'jam dpal dang yum g+han d+he dri chab mar bsgoms nas /
NK069(tu)001:7375: bdag gis dgra bo'i ling ka kug nas /
NK069(tu)001:7377: dgra'i rnam par shes pa gsod pa'i nus pa dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:7379: zhes bdag sgrib sel dang yum me tog mar bsgoms nas /
NK069(tu)001:7380: thugs ka nas sprul pas dgra'i rkang lag bcings par bsams na /
NK069(tu)001:7381: dgra'i g.yul pham par bya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:7383: zhes bdag kun bzang dang mar me mar bsgoms nas /
NK069(tu)001:7384: thugs ka nas dmag dpon rin po che sprul nas gtang na /
NK069(tu)001:7385: bdag gzhan gyi g.yul las rgyal bar 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:7387: zhes de ltar sgyu 'phrul gyi ting nge 'dzin la bsgoms na /
NK069(tu)001:7388: ji ltar dmyigs pa bzhin du sgyur du tub ste /
NK069(tu)001:7389: sgyu 'phrul gyi ting nge 'dzin 'dis las thams cad byed par 'gyur /
NK069(tu)001:7390: thun mong gi dngos grub thams cad thob par 'gyur ro /
NK069(tu)001:7392: de nyid ye shes rang snang ba'i //
NK069(tu)001:7393: zhes ting nge 'dzin gyis ji ltar bsam pa ltar 'grub pa de nyid /
NK069(tu)001:7394: de ltar 'grub pa ci ste na /
NK069(tu)001:7395: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams
NK069(tu)001:7396: cad ye shes rang snang du mkhyen cing 'byongs pas
NK069(tu)001:7397: 'grub bo // ming tshig gzugs bsogs yid bzhin gyis //
NK069(tu)001:7398: zhes ming tshig ni ngag gsung du rtogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:7399: gzugs ni lus skur rtogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:7400: bsogs ni sems thugs su rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7401: de las thams cad 'byung ba'i dpe ni /
NK069(tu)001:7402: yid bzhin gyi nor nu rin po che la rtog pa myed par dgos 'dod 'byung ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:7403: de bzhin du snang ba de nyid ye shes rang
NK069(tu)001:7404: snang du rtogs pa'i dus na 'dod pa 'byung ba'o
NK069(tu)001:7405: // mun la snang 'gyur ji bzhin du //
NK069(tu)001:7406: zhes mun pa'i nang du sgron me steg na /
NK069(tu)001:7407: mun pa nyid snang bar 'gyur ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:7408: de bzhin du snang ba nyid ye shes rang snang du rtogs na cir yang sgyur du btub pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:7409: 'gyur bas gser gyur sman gyi tshul //
NK069(tu)001:7410: zhes zangs srang stong gi nang du gser 'gyur gyi rtsi zho gcig brtab pas /
NK069(tu)001:7411: zangs nyid gser du 'gyur ba bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:7412: ting nge 'dzin phra mos snang ba 'di nyid ye shes rang snang du 'gyur /
NK069(tu)001:7413: dug bum pa gang gi nang du /
NK069(tu)001:7414: rtsi ma ki ta thigs pa gcig blugs pas /
NK069(tu)001:7415: dug nyid sman du 'gyur ba ltar /
NK069(tu)001:7416: lus ngag yid ltar bsgoms pas rtogs na /
NK069(tu)001:7417: snang ba ji ltar sgyur sgyur du stub bo //
NK069(tu)001:7419: ston pa mchod brtson rtogs pa gsal //
NK069(tu)001:7420: zhes ston pa rdo rje slob dpon ni /
NK069(tu)001:7421: phyi nang gsang ba de kho na nyid kyi mchod pa la brtson pa /
NK069(tu)001:7422: rang gi sems nyid phyin ci ma log par rtogs pa de /
NK069(tu)001:7423: lta ba yang dag pa'i don rtogs /
NK069(tu)001:7424: bsgoms pa zhi ba'i lha rnams ting nge 'dzin gyis gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:7425: dam tshig sngags dang phyag rgya dang //
NK069(tu)001:7426: ma nyams shes shing yo byad ldan //
NK069(tu)001:7427: zhes rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyams par srung /
NK069(tu)001:7428: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags dang /
NK069(tu)001:7430: skul ba las kyi sngags gsum dang /
NK069(tu)001:7432: dam tshig gi phyag rgya 'phro 'du dang /
NK069(tu)001:7433: las kyi phyag rgya yum dang /
NK069(tu)001:7434: zhi ba chos kyi phyag rgya bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:7435: de ltar sngags dang phyag rgya shes shing /
NK069(tu)001:7436: phyi nang gsang ba de kho na nyid la sogs pa'i yo byad dang ldan no //
NK069(tu)001:7438: zhes ston pa de lta bus sgyu 'phrul gyi don 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:7442: byang chub sems kyi rtogs pa dang mi ldan na /
NK069(tu)001:7443: sgrubs kyang tshe 'dir ni sgrub pa'i don myed la /
NK069(tu)001:7444: phyi mar byang chub kyi 'bras bu myed cing rlag par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:7446: dus gsum rgyal bas thugs chud pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:7449: ma 'ongs pa'i rgyal bas thugs su chud par 'gyur ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:7450: dus gsum gyi rgyal bas byang chub sems thugs su chud nas mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas so //
NK069(tu)001:7451: thugs su chud pa dngos gang zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:7452: dngos grub mchog gi snying po ni //
NK069(tu)001:7453: zhes dngos grub la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:7458: byang chub kyi sems rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7459: de bas na mchog ni chos sku yin no //
NK069(tu)001:7460: zad pa'i dus myed ye shes mdzod //
NK069(tu)001:7461: ces thun mong gi dngos grub gzhan la ni /
NK069(tu)001:7462: zad cing mthar thug pa yod la /
NK069(tu)001:7463: byang chub sems rtogs pa la ni /
NK069(tu)001:7464: zad cing bri ba myed de /
NK069(tu)001:7465: ye shes kyi mdzod yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:7468: zhes dngos grub gzhan la ni res yod res myed 'byung la /
NK069(tu)001:7469: byang chub sems rtogs pa'i dngos grub la ni /
NK069(tu)001:7471: bri zhing rlag pa myed par 'byung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:7472: dngos po myed las dngos po sprin //
NK069(tu)001:7473: zhes dngos po dang mtshan ma cir yang ma grub pa'i chos nyid /
NK069(tu)001:7475: ye shes rang snang ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub sprin dang 'dra ba 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:7477: zhes de yang sna tshogs su yang snang la /
NK069(tu)001:7478: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du sgyur du sgyur du yang btub ste /
NK069(tu)001:7479: legs pa'i yon tan du 'gyur ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:7481: dngos rnams nyid na dngos myed pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:7482: zhes kun rdzob tu dngos por snang ba nyid na /
NK069(tu)001:7483: don dam par dngos po myed pas /
NK069(tu)001:7484: snang phyogs kyi stong pa'i ngo bo nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:7485: stong phyogs kyi stong pa'i ngo bo nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:7486: rtog pa'i dbang bsgyur ting 'dzin yin //
NK069(tu)001:7487: zhes de ltar shes rab kyis gnyis myed de rtogs par byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:7488: ting nge 'dzin gyis dbang sgyur na /
NK069(tu)001:7490: snang stong gnyis myed kyi ngo bo nyid du rtogs nas /
NK069(tu)001:7491: des rang gi rtog pa la dbang sgyur ba'i ting nge yis /
NK069(tu)001:7492: lta ba'i gol sa bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:7493: gang gis dmyigs myed mi shes pa //
NK069(tu)001:7494: zhes rnal 'byor pa gang yang rung bas /
NK069(tu)001:7495: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ye nas dmyigs pa myed pa yin pa la /
NK069(tu)001:7496: ye nas dmyigs su myed pa'i don mi shes pa de yis /
NK069(tu)001:7497: de yis chos kyi dbyings mi shes //
NK069(tu)001:7498: zhes de ltar chos thams cad dmyigs su myed pa
NK069(tu)001:7499: mi shes pa des chos kyi dbyings zab cing rgya
NK069(tu)001:7500: che ba de shes pa lta ga la 'gyur te
NK069(tu)001:7502: gol sa gcad pa'i gtan tshigs bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:7503: de phyir dngos dang dngos myed pas //
NK069(tu)001:7504: 'jig pas dmyigs myed shes par gyis //
NK069(tu)001:7505: zhes chos kyi dbyings mi shes pa de'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:7506: dngos po yod pa'i chos dang /
NK069(tu)001:7507: dngos po myed pa'i chos la /
NK069(tu)001:7508: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyi gtan tshigs kyis yod myed kyi mtha' rnam pa gnyis bshig nas /
NK069(tu)001:7509: dngos po thams cad dngos myed du 'jig pas /
NK069(tu)001:7510: thams cad dmyigs su myed pa'i don du shes rab kyis shes par gyis zhes bsdams so //
NK069(tu)001:7511: 'dir lta ba dang sbyar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:7512: byang sems bzhir bstan pa la /
NK069(tu)001:7514: 'jig pa byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK069(tu)001:7515: ldang ba byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK069(tu)001:7516: gnas pa byang chub kyi sems dang /
NK069(tu)001:7517: smon pa byang chub kyi sems so //
NK069(tu)001:7518: 'jig pa byang chub kyi sems ni /
NK069(tu)001:7519: so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyi gtan tshigs kyis /
NK069(tu)001:7520: dngos po dang mtshan ma'i chos thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:7521: dngos po dang mtshan ma myed pa'i ngang du 'jig pa la bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:7523: dngos po dang mtshan ma bshig nas /
NK069(tu)001:7524: mtshan ma myed pa'i ngang du ldang ba ni ldang ba byang chub kyi sems zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:7526: de ltar dngos po dang mtshan ma bshig /
NK069(tu)001:7527: mtshan ma myed pa la langs nas /
NK069(tu)001:7528: mtshan ma myed pa la gnas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:7529: gnas pa byang chub kyi sems zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:7531: de ltar dngos po dang mtshan ma myed par bshig nas /
NK069(tu)001:7532: smon lam mthar phyin par lhun gyis grub pa ni smon pa byang sems so //
NK069(tu)001:7534: sems gzhir rtogs pa kho na lta ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:7535: lta ba 'dres pa kho na bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7536: gzhi rtsa myed pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK069(tu)001:7540: mtha' dang dbus myed de gang yin na /
NK069(tu)001:7541: rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems yin no //
NK069(tu)001:7542: pho mo ma yin ma ning min //
NK069(tu)001:7543: zhes rang gi rig pa nyid /
NK069(tu)001:7548: rig pa byang chub sems ni /
NK069(tu)001:7549: snang pho'i rnam par yang snang la /
NK069(tu)001:7550: grub pa ni pho'i rnam par yang ma grub /
NK069(tu)001:7551: mo dang ma ning yang des 'adre'o //
NK069(tu)001:7552: mtshan myed ma yin rigs rgyud min //
NK069(tu)001:7553: zhes pho mo'i mtshan ma myed pa yang ma yin /
NK069(tu)001:7554: rgyal rigs sam rje'u rigs la sogs pa'i rigs rgyud yang ma yin /
NK069(tu)001:7556: snang ni mtshan myed dam rigs rgyud can du snang la /
NK069(tu)001:7558: rigs rgyud kyi rnam par yang ma grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7559: kha dog ma yin dbyibs ma yin //
NK069(tu)001:7560: zhes rigs gcig nas gcig tu rgyud pa ma yin /
NK069(tu)001:7561: dkar po la sogs pa'i kha dog lnga yang ma yin /
NK069(tu)001:7562: gru bzhi la sogs pa'i dbyibs can yang ma yin pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:7564: snang ni kha dog dang dbyibs kyi ngo bor yang snang la /
NK069(tu)001:7565: grub ni kha dog dang dbyibs kyi ngo bor yang ma grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7566: gnas su ma yin gang yang min //
NK069(tu)001:7567: zhes phyi dang nang gi gnas /
NK069(tu)001:7568: lus ngag yid gsum gyi gnas su yang dngos por yod pa ma yin /
NK069(tu)001:7569: ji lta bu'i ngo bor yang ma grub pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:7571: snang ni phyi nang gi gnas sam /
NK069(tu)001:7572: lus ngag yid gsum du yang snang la /
NK069(tu)001:7573: grub ni de dag gi ngo bor yang ma grub pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:7574: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:7575: gzhi rtsa myed pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK069(tu)001:7577: ma h+aa'i gzhed pa yin nam /
NK069(tu)001:7579: ma h+aa'i gzhed pa yin na /
NK069(tu)001:7580: sems stong pa phyad phyod du bstan pas mu stegs chad par lta ba dang 'dra /
NK069(tu)001:7582: nyams len dang 'dod gzhung myed par spyi'i rnam par dgos pa myed do //
NK069(tu)001:7584: sems spyi'i rnam pa de lta bur gnas par 'dod pa la /
NK069(tu)001:7585: spyi'i rnam pa de thams cad rgyu yin par tan la 'bebs pas /
NK069(tu)001:7586: nang bzung ba myed par shes pa las thams cad skyed pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:7587: rgyu de shes nas 'di rang gi gzhung du thabs shes rab kyi lam du klong ste /
NK069(tu)001:7588: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes ste /
NK069(tu)001:7589: thabs kyi phyag rgya kun gyi rgyu //
NK069(tu)001:7591: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK069(tu)001:7592: zhes 'o na ji lta bu zhig yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:7593: chos thams cad kyi de kho na nyid dang /
NK069(tu)001:7595: dbyings rtogs pa'i ye shes ni /
NK069(tu)001:7596: byang chub kyi sems de yin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7597: thabs kyi phyag rgya kun gyi rgyu //
NK069(tu)001:7598: zhes dbyings rtogs pa'i gzung 'dzin dang bral ba de nyid /
NK069(tu)001:7599: thabs sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyar snang zhing /
NK069(tu)001:7600: de skyed cing sgrub pa'i rgyu kho na'o //
NK069(tu)001:7602: las thabs byung lam rtogs thabs dang /
NK069(tu)001:7603: thabs kyi 'bras bu rtogs pa thabs kyi ngo bo /
NK069(tu)001:7605: zhes thabs sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya las /
NK069(tu)001:7606: thabs sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya 'byung /
NK069(tu)001:7607: byung ba de nyid sna tshogs shing bsam yas so //
NK069(tu)001:7609: thabs rtogs par byed pa las /
NK069(tu)001:7610: thabs rtogs pa'i ye shes byung /
NK069(tu)001:7611: thugs kyi phyag rgya de nyid bsam gyis mi khyab pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7612: thabs dad min la tha dad pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:7614: don dam par tha dad pa ma sangs rgyas sems can /
NK069(tu)001:7616: kun rdzob sangs rgyas sems can /
NK069(tu)001:7618: nang dang nang gi phyi rol gyi //
NK069(tu)001:7619: zhes nang ni rnam shes dang dbang po dang phung po /
NK069(tu)001:7620: nang gi phyi rol ni 'byung ba dang yul gzugs sgra la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7621: dkyil 'khor bsam yas ye shes rol //
NK069(tu)001:7622: zhes thams cad dkyil 'khor du ma gyur ba myed de /
NK069(tu)001:7624: bsam yas pa nyid ye shes yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:7625: ye shes nyid ye shes la rol lo //
NK069(tu)001:7630: 'byung bas bsdus pa'i chos thams cad ni /
NK069(tu)001:7631: sangs ma rgyas pa gcig kyang myed de /
NK069(tu)001:7634: rnam par shes pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor te /
NK069(tu)001:7635: 'jigs myed kun bzang phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:7636: ces de la ni 'khor ba dang ngan song gi 'jigs pa myed de /
NK069(tu)001:7637: thams cad kun tu bzang po'i thugs ye shes kyi phyag rgya /
NK069(tu)001:7638: che ba'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa'i mchog dang ldan pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:7639: gang zhig glang chen myos 'dra'i sems //
NK069(tu)001:7640: zhes dper na byol song glang po che de /
NK069(tu)001:7641: ye nas blun zhing gti mug pa'i steng du /
NK069(tu)001:7642: 'phral blo bur du rgun 'brum gyi chang gis sems slad de myos pa dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:7643: sems can ye nas lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa dang ldan pa'i steng du /
NK069(tu)001:7644: kun nas btags pa'i phyin ci log gi rtog pas blo bur du slad pas so //
NK069(tu)001:7645: mnyam par bzhag la btul nas su //
NK069(tu)001:7646: dper na byol song glang po che de /
NK069(tu)001:7647: ye nas blun zhing gti mug pa rgun chang gis myos nas spyad du ma tub pa de /
NK069(tu)001:7648: glang rdzi glang po 'dul ba'i thabs la mkhas pa des /
NK069(tu)001:7649: sna nas 'dzin pa'i lcags kyu ni thogs /
NK069(tu)001:7650: rna bar snyan pa'i glu ni blangs /
NK069(tu)001:7651: mig la mdzes pa'i ba dan dmar po ni phyar nas /
NK069(tu)001:7653: spyad du btub par byas pa bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:7654: sems can gyi sems glang po che myos pa 'dra ba de /
NK069(tu)001:7655: gzhan gang gis yang mi thul te /
NK069(tu)001:7656: chos nyid la blo mnyam par bzhag pas thul bar 'gyur ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:7657: sngags dang phyag rgya rab bstan na //
NK069(tu)001:7658: zhes de ltar chos nyid la blo mnyam par bzhag pas sems thul nas /
NK069(tu)001:7659: sngags dang phyag rgya'i don bstan pa'am sngags dang phyag
NK069(tu)001:7660: rgyas lus ngag yid gsum bstan zhing mi 'gyur bar
NK069(tu)001:7661: bsgoms na / dngos grub ya mtshan chen por 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:7663: zhes yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi /
NK069(tu)001:7664: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub ya mtshan chen po thob par 'gyur zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:7665: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa nyid gzigs mos mnyes par gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:7666: zhes chos nyid skye ba myed pa las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:7667: skye ba'i cho 'phrul sna tshogs par snang ba'i gzigs mos de ba nyid mnyes par gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:7668: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:7669: snod ngan pa la gasnga ba'i chos kyi snyinga pa /
NK069(tu)001:7670: yang dag pa'i don da kho na nyada /
NK069(tu)001:7671: mi slu ngesa par ston pa lasa /
NK069(tu)001:7672: sgyu 'phrul sgrub pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi le'u ste lnga pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7674: // sgyu 'phrula sna tshogs su sgruba pa nyid /
NK069(tu)001:7675: tinga nge 'dzina gyis bsgrub dgos pas sam /
NK069(tu)001:7676: yang na mchog gi dngos grub chos sku dang /
NK069(tu)001:7677: thun mong gi dngos grub las sna tshogs pa'i le'u ste lnga pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7678: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rang bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:7679: zhes de sgyu 'phrul sna tshogs bsgrub pa'i le'u bstan pa'i rjes de nas /
NK069(tu)001:7680: dkyil 'khor spro ba'i le'u ston pas so //
NK069(tu)001:7681: rigs lnga la sogs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:7682: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rang bzhin nam bdag nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:7683: ston pa kun tu bzang po'o //
NK069(tu)001:7684: gcig dang du ma myed pa'i bdag nyid thams cad kyis /
NK069(tu)001:7685: zhes ston pa kun tu bzang po ni /
NK069(tu)001:7686: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:7687: gcig dang du ma myed pa thams cad du bdag nyid du gnas pa'i phyir bdag nyid /
NK069(tu)001:7688: de thams cad kyi ngo bor snang ba'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:7691: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad la /
NK069(tu)001:7692: zhes 'gro ba rigs drug na gnas pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:7693: snod bcud thams cad kyis phyogs bcu thams cad du khyab par /
NK069(tu)001:7694: nyid kyi che ba'i dkyil 'khor 'byung bar bzhed nas /
NK069(tu)001:7695: zhes ston pa kun tu bzang po nyid kyi mya ngan las 'das pa la sogs pa'i che ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:7696: rigs lnga la sogs pa'i che ba'i yon tan gyis /
NK069(tu)001:7697: lha'i dkyil 'khor 'jig rten drug tu snang bar 'dod pa'am bzhed nas /
NK069(tu)001:7698: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:7699: zhes 'gro ba drug gi sems sangs rgyas pa'i che
NK069(tu)001:7700: ba'i dkyil 'khor rang la yod pa de gzhan la
NK069(tu)001:7702: 'gro ba drug gi sems can gyi don ched du 'di brjod cing gsungs so //
NK069(tu)001:7703: lam cig char ba'i sgom pa bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:7704: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:7705: zhes rig pa'i mtshan nyid gsal la rtog pa myed pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:7706: shar me long lta bu'i ye shes ste /
NK069(tu)001:7707: mngon par dga' ba'i zhing khams so //
NK069(tu)001:7708: thams cad yon tan du snang ba ni lho phyogs te dpal dang ldan pa'i zhing ngo //
NK069(tu)001:7709: ma rig pa nubs pa'i dus na nub phyogs te bde ba can gyi zhing ngo //
NK069(tu)001:7710: sgrib pa byang bas na byang ste byang phyogs rnam dag bkod pa'i zhing dang /
NK069(tu)001:7711: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:7712: dbus byang chub snying po ni chos kyi dbyings so //
NK069(tu)001:7713: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK069(tu)001:7714: ces sems can gyis brtags pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:7715: phyogs bzhi dbus dang lngar thams cad 'dus la /
NK069(tu)001:7716: phyogs bzhi dbus dang lnga ni sangs rgyas rigs lnga'i zhing khams yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:7717: stong gsum gyi stong la sogs pa sems can gyis
NK069(tu)001:7718: bsam yas pa yang ye sdod ma nas sangs rgyas
NK069(tu)001:7719: kyi zhing rnam par dag par lhun gyis grub par
NK069(tu)001:7720: gnas so // rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK069(tu)001:7722: ces chos thams cad ni rnam par dag pas /
NK069(tu)001:7723: ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i ngang du rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:7725: skyon gyi rnam pa kun ye shes su 'byung /
NK069(tu)001:7726: de theg pa chen po yin /
NK069(tu)001:7727: de lta bu'i rnal 'byor pas sgom pa'i ting nge ni /
NK069(tu)001:7728: ye shes de nyid sangs rgyas kyi dal chen por sgom pa la spyod ces so //
NK069(tu)001:7729: 'di man chad lam rims kyis pa'i bsgom pa bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:7730: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud bcas //
NK069(tu)001:7731: zhes dkyil 'khor gyi dbus kyi lte ba ni chos kyi dbyings /
NK069(tu)001:7732: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi ni ye shes bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:7733: dbus dang phyi rim gyi mu chud zlum po rdo rje'i ra ba dang bcas par bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7734: 'di rnams le'u dang po dang mthun par bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:7735: gru chad bzhis yis rgyan pa'i khyams //
NK069(tu)001:7736: zhes de'i phyi rim na gru chad bzhi ser po /
NK069(tu)001:7737: rgyan pa ni blo 'bur bzhi mkhar thabs /
NK069(tu)001:7738: bar khyams ni lha snam ste kha dog phyogs dang mthun par gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7739: kun tu gru bzhi sgo khyud ldan //
NK069(tu)001:7740: zhes phyogs kun nas gru bzhir gyur pa'i sgo khyud ni pan tsa ra ga'i rtsig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7741: ldan ces pa sgo bzhi rta babs dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7742: rol mo sna tshogs sprin phung bzhin //
NK069(tu)001:7749: chos kyi lha mo rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:7750: sna tshogs pa'i gzugs can de /
NK069(tu)001:7751: mang nyung gi tshad dper na nam ka'i sprin phung bzhin du 'thibs par gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:7752: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis kyis brgyan //
NK069(tu)001:7754: de lta bu'i dkyil 'khor de la /
NK069(tu)001:7755: sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bzhugs pas gzhal yas khang mdzes pas na rgyan ces bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:7756: de yang lha'i che ba'i yon tan la gzhal yas khang /
NK069(tu)001:7757: gzhal yas khang la lhas mdzes par byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7758: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:7759: gzhal yas khang gi rgyan du lha 'gro ba ni 'thad pa ni ci yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:7760: snga phyi la dgongs pa yin te /
NK069(tu)001:7761: sngon la gzhal yas khang bskyed nas /
NK069(tu)001:7762: de nas lha bskyed pa'i dbang du rtsis pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:7763: lhas gzhal yas khang mdzes par byas pas na /
NK069(tu)001:7764: rgyu'i ming 'bras bu la tags pa lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:7765: seng ge glang chen rta dang khyung //
NK069(tu)001:7766: nam mkha' lding gi khri chen la //
NK069(tu)001:7768: dbus su mi 'jigs pa bzhi mtshon pa'i seng ge'i gdan ni rdo rje gdan no //
NK069(tu)001:7769: shar du rnam snang la stobs bcu mtshon pa glang po'i gdan /
NK069(tu)001:7770: lhor rin 'byung la rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi mtshon pa rta mchog gi gdan /
NK069(tu)001:7771: nub tu snang ba mtha' yas la dbang bcu mtshon pa rma bya'i gdan /
NK069(tu)001:7772: byang don grub 'phrin las thogs pa myed pa shang shang khyung gi gdan rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:7773: nyi zla pad ma rin po che //
NK069(tu)001:7774: zhes shes rab thogs pa myed pa mtshon pa nyi ma'i gdan /
NK069(tu)001:7775: thabs 'gag pa myed pa mtshon pa zla ba'i gdan /
NK069(tu)001:7776: dgos 'dod thams cad 'byung ba rin po che'i khri rkang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:7777: de la rigs lnga la lnga rtsegs te /
NK069(tu)001:7778: rin po che'i khri rkang gi bar na sems can brgyad brgyad kha phyir lta ba /
NK069(tu)001:7780: sems dpa' dang kun bzang yab yum la nyi zla pad+ma gsum rtseg go //
NK069(tu)001:7781: khro bo la rdo rje brag gi steng na nyi ma rkyang pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7783: gdan la rdzogs dang sems dpa'i tshul //
NK069(tu)001:7785: de lta bu'i dkyil 'khor de la gong gi gdan la /
NK069(tu)001:7786: rigs lnga rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas yin pas rdo rje'i dkyil krung du bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:7787: yum rnams ni yab kyi skur rgyab na pad+ma'i dkyil mo krung zhabs thil sprad pa'i tshul du'o //
NK069(tu)001:7788: sems dpa' phyad dkyil du bzhugs /
NK069(tu)001:7789: thub pa 'gro don mdzad pas bzhengs thabs su bzhugs /
NK069(tu)001:7790: sgo ba bdug pa 'dul bas gyad kyi dor thabs su bzhugs /
NK069(tu)001:7791: kun bzang yab yum chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang la sku rdzogs tshul du bzhugs /
NK069(tu)001:7792: rigs lnga bzhugs pa bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:7793: 'khor lor rgyal po rgyal mo dang //
NK069(tu)001:7808: rnam shes kyi sems dpa' bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:7809: g.yas nas mthong thos snom pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:7810: zhes dbus kyi gtso bo zhal shar du gzigs pa'i g.yas kyi rtsibs mchan la /
NK069(tu)001:7811: mthong ba dmig gi rnam shes sa'i snying po /
NK069(tu)001:7812: thos pa rna ba'i rnam shes phyag na rdo rje /
NK069(tu)001:7813: snom pa sna'i rnam shes nam ka'i snying po /
NK069(tu)001:7814: myong ba lce'i rnam shes spyin ras gzigs dang bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:7815: gzhal yas khang gi rtsibs mchan la bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:7816: myong dang btsun mo'i tshogs su bcas //
NK069(tu)001:7817: zhes btsun mo ni yum ste /
NK069(tu)001:7818: gzugs kyi lha mo sgeg mo sa snying gi yum dang /
NK069(tu)001:7819: sgra'i lha mo nir ti ma phyag na rdo rje'i yum dang /
NK069(tu)001:7820: dri'i lha mo ma le ma nam snying gi yum dang /
NK069(tu)001:7821: ro'i lha mo g+hir ti ma spyan ras gzigs kyi yum dang /
NK069(tu)001:7822: sems dpar bcas pa bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:7823: dbang po'i sems dpa' yab yum ni /
NK069(tu)001:7824: gru chad la ni mthong byed dang //
NK069(tu)001:7825: zhes phyi'i gru chad bzhi la /
NK069(tu)001:7826: mthong byed myig gi dbang po byams pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:7827: thos byed snom byed myong byed rnams //
NK069(tu)001:7828: zhes thos byed rna ba'i dbang po 'jam dpal dang /
NK069(tu)001:7829: snom byed sna'i dbang po sgrib sel dang /
NK069(tu)001:7830: myong byed lce'i dbang po kun tu bzang po rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:7831: btsun mo'i tshogs dang ldan par gnas //
NK069(tu)001:7832: zhes btsun mo ni de rnams kyi yum ste /
NK069(tu)001:7833: 'das pa dpyid kyi dus spos ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:7834: da ltar dbyar gyi dus me tog ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:7835: ma 'ongs pa dgun gyi dus g+han d+he ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:7836: ma byon pa ston gyi dus a lo ka'o //
NK069(tu)001:7837: sems dpa' rnams yum dang bcas pa gru chad la gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:7838: kun bzang yab yum thub drug bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:7839: bar khyams la ni thub drug dang //
NK069(tu)001:7840: zhes dal gyi rab khyams la ni /
NK069(tu)001:7841: shar lhor lha'i thub pa srid thub 'dzin /
NK069(tu)001:7842: lhor mi'i thub pa sh+aakya seng ge /
NK069(tu)001:7843: lho nub lha ma yin gyi thub pa rnam par rgyal ba /
NK069(tu)001:7844: nub byang byol song gi thub pa rnam par gnon pa /
NK069(tu)001:7845: byang du yi dwags thub pa rnam par snang byed /
NK069(tu)001:7846: byang shar du dmyal ba'i thub pa chos kyi rgyal po bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:7847: mdun dang rgyab du byed pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:7848: bya ba dag ni gnas par bstan //
NK069(tu)001:7849: zhes rdo rje sems dpa'i mdun sngos shar du yid byed pa po kun tu bzang po bzhugs /
NK069(tu)001:7850: rdo rje sems dpa'i rgyab nub tu chos bya ba
NK069(tu)001:7851: mo kun tu bzang mo bzhugs pa'i gnas su bstan
NK069(tu)001:7852: no // gtar ka gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:7853: kun bzang yab yum 'khor du song bas /
NK069(tu)001:7854: dkyil 'khor gtso 'khor go log zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:7856: dper na 'jig rten slab gzhi dang tshul bstun nas /
NK069(tu)001:7857: bu phog nas pha ma khyim logs su gdod pa dang 'dra ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:7858: yang na phya mkhan gyi tshul de /
NK069(tu)001:7859: dper na rang gis bzo byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:7860: rang gis legs mi legs lta ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:7861: yang na kun bzang yab yum gyi thugs las sprul pas thub pa drug dang gnas gcig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7862: sgo khyud bzhi la 'joms pa ni //
NK069(tu)001:7863: zhes sgo bzhi'i sgo khyud nang du /
NK069(tu)001:7865: shar du gshin rje gshed po /
NK069(tu)001:7868: byang du bdud rtsi 'khyil ba bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:7869: btsun mo'i tshogs dang ldan par gnas //
NK069(tu)001:7870: zhes khro bo bzhi'i btsun mo ni /
NK069(tu)001:7875: sgo skyong gi khro bo bzhi yum dang ldan par gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:7877: rdo rje rdo rje sems dpa'i /
NK069(tu)001:7881: pad+ma snang ba mtha' yas kyi /
NK069(tu)001:7886: 'khor gyi phyag mtshan bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:7889: shing la pas gzhan rnams bsdus shing de rnams /
NK069(tu)001:7893: pa'i tshul mnyes phyag na mchod pas /
NK069(tu)001:7895: bshad rgyud rdo rje'i dbang du byas na /
NK069(tu)001:7896: rdo rje sems pa'i phyag mtshan ni /
NK069(tu)001:7897: rdo rje 'khor lo ral gri g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:7898: dril bu rin chen pad+ma g.yon no //
NK069(tu)001:7900: 'khor lo rdo rje ral gri g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:7901: dril bu pad ma rin chen g.yon no //
NK069(tu)001:7903: rin chen 'khor lo rdo rje g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:7904: dril bu pad ma ral gri g.yon no //
NK069(tu)001:7906: pad ma rdo rje 'khor lo g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:7907: dril bu rin chen ral gri g.yon no //
NK069(tu)001:7909: ral gri 'khor lo rdo rje g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:7910: dril bu rin chen pad+ma g.yon no //
NK069(tu)001:7912: g.yon rang brtags gtso dang mthun no //
NK069(tu)001:7915: dril bu pad+ma rin po che //
NK069(tu)001:7917: gzhan gang gnas su rdo rje shes /
NK069(tu)001:7918: dang po thugs dang g.yon 'khyud pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7921: sa'i snying po rin chen myu gu bsnams /
NK069(tu)001:7922: nam mkha'i snying po ral gri /
NK069(tu)001:7923: spyan ras gzigs pad+ma dkar po /
NK069(tu)001:7924: phyag na rdo rje rdo rje'o //
NK069(tu)001:7927: sgrib sel chos kyi po ti /
NK069(tu)001:7928: kun bzang rin chen snye ma bsnams te /
NK069(tu)001:7930: rin chen myu gu ral gri 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:7931: pad+ma dkar po rdo rje che //
NK069(tu)001:7932: ud dpal klu shing po ti snye //
NK069(tu)001:7944: gzugs mdzes rin chen 'phreng ba dang //
NK069(tu)001:7945: pi wang gar sgyur spos me ma //
NK069(tu)001:7946: byug pa gtso bo'i rim shes bya //
NK069(tu)001:7952: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba rdo rje rgya gram /
NK069(tu)001:7953: shar gyi sgo ma lcags kyu /
NK069(tu)001:7958: n+ri mgo rdo rje thod rgya gram /
NK069(tu)001:7959: lcags kyu zhags pa s+pho ta to //
NK069(tu)001:7961: thub drug dang kun bzang ni /
NK069(tu)001:7962: kun tu bzang po mnyam bzhag steng na rdo rje rtse lnga la ye shes lnga'i 'od 'phro ba /
NK069(tu)001:7963: kun tu bzang mo mnyam bzhag steng na dril bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:7964: lha'i thub pa srid thub 'dzin pi wang /
NK069(tu)001:7965: mi'i thub pa sh+aakya seng ge srog shing dang par bu /
NK069(tu)001:7966: lha min thub pa rnam par rgyal ba go mtshon /
NK069(tu)001:7967: byol song thub pa rnam par rnon pa po ti /
NK069(tu)001:7968: yi dwags thub pa rnam par snang byed rin chen sgrom bu /
NK069(tu)001:7969: dmyal ba'i thub pa chos kyi rgyal po g.yas me dpung g.yon chu'i bum pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:7972: ye shes rtse lnga chos khams dril //
NK069(tu)001:7973: thugs la bstan pa nyid du gsungs //
NK069(tu)001:7974: thub pa nges par phyag gnyis shes //
NK069(tu)001:7975: sreg par pi wang go mtshon sdeb //
NK069(tu)001:7976: sgrom stob po ti chos 'chad tshul //
NK069(tu)001:7977: me dpung bum par shes par bya //
NK069(tu)001:7978: ces bshad pa'i rgyud rdo rje las gsungs pas shes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:7979: mthing ka dkar po ser le'u rgan //
NK069(tu)001:7980: ljang khu la sogs sna tshogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:7981: zhes pa rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum ni chos nyid myi 'gyur ba'i sku mdog mthing ka /
NK069(tu)001:7982: rnam par snang mdzad yab yum mnyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos pas sku mdog dkar po /
NK069(tu)001:7983: rin chen 'byung ldan yab yum che ba'i yon tan rgyas pas sku mdog ser po /
NK069(tu)001:7984: snang ba mtha' yas yab yum thugs rjes chags pa'i rtags su sku mdog dmar po /
NK069(tu)001:7985: don yod grub pa yab yum 'phrin las sna tshogs mdzad pas sku mdog ljang khu'o //
NK069(tu)001:7986: kun tu bzang po yab yum chos kyi dbyings mtshon pas sku mdog mthing ka'o //
NK069(tu)001:7987: la sogs ni sems dpa' dang sems ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:7988: sa snying dang sgeg mo dkar ba /
NK069(tu)001:7989: nam ka'i snying po dang ma le ser ba /
NK069(tu)001:7990: spyan ras gzigs dang g+hir ti ma dmar ba /
NK069(tu)001:7991: phyag na rdo rje dang nir ti ma ljang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:7993: byams pa dang spos ma dkar /
NK069(tu)001:7994: sgrib sel dang me tog ma ser /
NK069(tu)001:7995: kun bzang dang mar me ma dmar /
NK069(tu)001:7996: 'jam dpal dang g+han d+he ma ljang khu'o //
NK069(tu)001:7997: de dag nyi shu rtsa lngar yod pas bsogs so //
NK069(tu)001:7999: gshin rje gshed yab yum smug nag /
NK069(tu)001:8000: stobs chen yab yum ser nag /
NK069(tu)001:8001: rta mgrin yab yum dmar nag /
NK069(tu)001:8002: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba yab yum ljang nag go //
NK069(tu)001:8004: sgo ba bzhi yang rigs lnga'i sku mdog go //
NK069(tu)001:8005: thub pa drug gi sku mdog la nges pa myed de 'gro ba gang 'dul du ston pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:8006: phal cher che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'i rtags su
NK069(tu)001:8007: sku mdog ser po gser gtso ma lta bu kho
NK069(tu)001:8008: na'o // yum rnams kyi tshul ni /
NK069(tu)001:8009: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can //
NK069(tu)001:8010: zhes zhi ba'i tshul ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:8012: nga rgyal gyi ri snyil bas sku gnyen pa can yin /
NK069(tu)001:8013: zhe sdang gi me bsad pas sku lcug pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:8014: 'dod chags kyi dug phyung bas sku 'khril ba yin /
NK069(tu)001:8015: 'phrag dog gi lcags grol bas sku ldem bab can yin /
NK069(tu)001:8016: gti mug gi mun khang gsal bas sku gzhon tshul chags pa yin te /
NK069(tu)001:8017: mdor na nyon mongs pa lnga las grol ba'i sku yin no //
NK069(tu)001:8018: yum gyi tshul du yang bzhed pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:8020: gsal mtsher lhun sdug gzi brjid ldan //
NK069(tu)001:8021: zhes ye shes kyi tshul ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:8022: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes dkar la gsal /
NK069(tu)001:8023: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dmar la mtsher /
NK069(tu)001:8024: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes lhun sdug /
NK069(tu)001:8025: me long lta bu'i ye shes gzi brjid dang ldan pas ste /
NK069(tu)001:8026: ye shes sam sku mdog gi tshul lo //
NK069(tu)001:8027: yab kyi tshul du yang bzhed do //
NK069(tu)001:8028: sku dang ye shes gnyis las tshul dgur bzhed do //
NK069(tu)001:8031: zhes bya ba grub pa'i ye shes mthar phyin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:8032: lha re re'i ba spu'i bu ga nas /
NK069(tu)001:8033: 'od zer bye ba rgya stong khrag khrig 'phro ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:8034: tshogs chen po ni gtso 'khor thams cad la tshang bar gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8037: ces sgo bzhi khro bo ni /
NK069(tu)001:8038: thugs la rtogs pa'i me 'bar bas sems kyi gdug pa 'dul /
NK069(tu)001:8039: yul la thugs rje'i me 'bar bas 'byung po gdug pa 'dul /
NK069(tu)001:8040: me dpung phyi nang du 'brel bas 'phreng ba /
NK069(tu)001:8041: bar mtshams myed par 'khrigs pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:8042: ba spu'i bu ga nas 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:8043: yang na srid pa'i rtse mo nas dmyal ba'i gnas yan chad kyi don byed pas na 'khrigs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8044: mtha' dbus myed par khyab pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:8045: zhes dkyil 'khor de dag gi yon tan ni /
NK069(tu)001:8046: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gyis rgyu byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:8047: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu myed par khyab pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8048: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK069(tu)001:8049: ces dkyil 'khor bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i 'bad rtsol
NK069(tu)001:8050: myed par lhun gyis grub par gdul bya la snang
NK069(tu)001:8051: ngo // sku'i thams cad 'byung ba'i gzhi /
NK069(tu)001:8052: sku'i phyag rgya che mchog ni //
NK069(tu)001:8053: zhes chos kyi sku dri ma myed pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8054: spang bya ma rig pa'i snang ba spang nas /
NK069(tu)001:8055: thob bya ye shes thob pas na /
NK069(tu)001:8056: sku phyag rgya yon tan mchog dang ldan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8058: de bzhin nyid las ma g.yos kyang //
NK069(tu)001:8059: zhes de bzhin nyid chos kyi dbyings sam /
NK069(tu)001:8060: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos kyang /
NK069(tu)001:8061: gdul bya'i snang ba la don mdzad pa ma 'gags par snang ste /
NK069(tu)001:8063: gzugs bstan pa las longs sku bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8064: yang dag thar pa'i gzugs sku dang //
NK069(tu)001:8065: zhes byang chub sems dpa'i sa thob pa lta bu la /
NK069(tu)001:8066: 'phags pa'i skus 'dul bar 'os pa rnams la ni /
NK069(tu)001:8067: yang dag par 'khor ba las thar pa ni gzugs
NK069(tu)001:8068: sku mtshan dang dpe byed du ldan par ston pa
NK069(tu)001:8069: dang / 'dir zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:8074: gtso bo rigs lnga gang yang gang yab yum gnyis la /
NK069(tu)001:8075: 'khor rigs chung dang rigs bye brag pa ma nges pa yab yum brgyad de bcu /
NK069(tu)001:8076: sgo ba yab yum brgyad de bco brgyad do //
NK069(tu)001:8078: gong ltar sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis so //
NK069(tu)001:8080: rigs lnga yab yum la rang gi rigs chung gis skor bas lnga bcu /
NK069(tu)001:8081: phyi nang gi sems dpa' yab yum bcu drug /
NK069(tu)001:8084: sgo ba yab yum brgyad de /
NK069(tu)001:8086: yang na phyi rim skal pa'i me ri la mtshams
NK069(tu)001:8087: kyi lha khro bo bcu yab yum nyi shu ste
NK069(tu)001:8091: sgrub pa thams zhi ba 'od kyi rim pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8092: de ma yin pa bsam yas lhun grub pa slob pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8097: zhes las dang nyon mongs pa'i dbang du 'gro bas /
NK069(tu)001:8098: rigs drug ma lus pa 'dul ba'i phyir na ni /
NK069(tu)001:8099: mthun byas sku ni sna tshogs ston //
NK069(tu)001:8100: zhes sems can so so'i lus dang mthun par byas pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:8101: sprul pa'i sku ni sna tshogs par ston //
NK069(tu)001:8102: yang dag pa las ma g.yos par don byed pa bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8103: ston nyid sgyu ma dmyigs yor tshul //
NK069(tu)001:8104: zhes de ltar sku sna tshogs par ston pas /
NK069(tu)001:8105: ston pa'i dus nyid na dngos por ma grub pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8107: dmyigs yor gyi tshul du gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:8108: sku dbyer myed bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8109: tshul nyid dbyings las g.yos pa myed //
NK069(tu)001:8110: ces sgyu ma'i tshul du sna tshogs par gnas pa nyid na /
NK069(tu)001:8111: chos kyi dbyings las g.yos pa rdul tsam yang myed do //
NK069(tu)001:8112: 'dir sku lan mang du gsungs pa 'dabs so zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:8114: sku'i phyag rgya che mchog ni zhes pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8115: dang po chos sku las sems can la longs skur snang ba'i rim pa bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8116: de tsho 'gro drug thams cad la /
NK069(tu)001:8117: zhes pa la sogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8118: sku 'gro don byed tshul bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8119: 'og min bla myed gnas mchog na zhes pa la sogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8120: sa bcu thob pa'i sgrib pa sbyong tshul lo //
NK069(tu)001:8122: ces pa la sogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8126: 'bras bu'i sa gsum non tshul lo //
NK069(tu)001:8129: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i 'bras bu sku lnga lhun grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:8130: ma g.yos bzhin du sna tshogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:8131: zhes de ltar don chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:8132: gdul bya la sprul pa sna tshogs lus su snang la /
NK069(tu)001:8133: chos nyid kyis ma bcos yang las 'phros snang ba bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8134: de tshe myi mthun sna tshogs la //
NK069(tu)001:8135: zhes sna tshogs par snang ba de'i tshe /
NK069(tu)001:8136: las dang bag chags myi mthun pa'i sems can sna tshogs pa yod pa la /
NK069(tu)001:8137: so so 'dra bar snang ba ni //
NK069(tu)001:8138: zhes gdul bya so so'i lus dang 'dra bar 'dul byed snang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:8139: de bzhin nyid kyis ma bcos kyang //
NK069(tu)001:8140: zhes de bzhin nyid chos kyi dbyings rtogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis ma bcos kyang /
NK069(tu)001:8141: las 'phro'i dbang gis so sor snang //
NK069(tu)001:8142: zhes skal ba che chung gi las 'phro'i dbang gis /
NK069(tu)001:8143: gdul bya la 'dul byed so sor mthun par snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:8144: dper na me long chu zla bzhin //
NK069(tu)001:8145: zhes dbyings las ma g.yos bzhin du snang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:8146: dper na bzhin gcig gi mdun na /
NK069(tu)001:8147: me long mang po bzhag pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:8148: me long re re'i nang du bzhin gyi gzugs brnyan re re snang ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:8149: zla ba la chur snang ba'i rtog pa myed bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:8150: zla ba'i gzugs brnyan chu tha dad pa'i bye brag thams cad snang ba dang 'dra ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:8151: lha mi la snang tshul bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8152: de tsho 'gro drug thams cad la //
NK069(tu)001:8153: zhes sna tshogs mang por snang ba de'i tshe /
NK069(tu)001:8154: ji ltar snang na 'gro ba rigs drug ma lus pa thams cad la snang tshul ni /
NK069(tu)001:8155: sdig spong gzugs su rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:8156: ces ston pas sdig pa myi dge ba spong zhing /
NK069(tu)001:8157: dge ba sna tshogs pa la 'jug pa'i sprul sku'i gzugs kyi rnam par bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8158: nyan thos la snang tshul bstan /
NK069(tu)001:8159: dge tshul rnams la dgra bcom gzugs //
NK069(tu)001:8160: zhes dge ba'i tshul 'dzin pa'i nyan thos kyi 'dul ba'i rig can rnams la ni /
NK069(tu)001:8161: 'phags pa dgra bcom pa dug chen sgyings pa lta bu'i gzugs kyis yang 'dul bar snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:8162: rang rgyal la snang tshul bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8163: rang rgyal rnams la bse ru'i tshul //
NK069(tu)001:8164: ces rang sangs rgyas kyis 'dul ba'i gdul bya la ni /
NK069(tu)001:8166: bse ru ltar cig pur gnas pa'i tshul du yang snang la /
NK069(tu)001:8168: ne tsho bzhin du khyus ldings pa'i tshul du yang ston no //
NK069(tu)001:8169: theg chen la snang tshul ston pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8170: gzhan yang theg mchog rim pa bzhin //
NK069(tu)001:8171: zhes gzhan yang theg pa rab dang /
NK069(tu)001:8172: rab kyi yang mchog la sogs pa rnams la yang /
NK069(tu)001:8173: blo'i rim pa bzhin du gang la gang 'dul du ston no //
NK069(tu)001:8175: 'og min bla myed gnas mchog tu //
NK069(tu)001:8176: zhes byang chub sems dpa' sngags kyi theg pas 'dul ba rnams la ni /
NK069(tu)001:8177: gnas gzhan las mchog tu gyur pa 'og min gyi gnas su /
NK069(tu)001:8179: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK069(tu)001:8180: zhes ston pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dpal rnam
NK069(tu)001:8181: par snang mdzad kyi sku'i tshul du ston par mdzad
NK069(tu)001:8183: byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la //
NK069(tu)001:8184: zhes 'khor byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyi don ched dam /
NK069(tu)001:8185: sa bcu'i byang chub sems dpa'i 'khor rnams la /
NK069(tu)001:8187: de bzhin gsung mchog mi smra te //
NK069(tu)001:8188: zhes sems can la bstan pa de bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:8189: tshig gi gsung yon tan mchog gis chos mi ston te /
NK069(tu)001:8190: 'o na gang gis ston zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:8191: sku yis chos rnams mja' bar ston //
NK069(tu)001:8192: zhes sku mtshan dang dpe byad du ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:8193: chos rnams kyi brda' mjal bar ston pa'i dape'o //
NK069(tu)001:8196: 'di'i 'og min la khyad yod dam myed /
NK069(tu)001:8198: yod na ji ltar yod zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:8200: le'u dang po dang khyad myed /
NK069(tu)001:8202: le'u dang po rgyud 'chad pa'i gleng gzhi yin /
NK069(tu)001:8203: 'di mtshan sa bcu thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa'i ngo la snang ba yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:8204: le'u dang po rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor gnas lugs yin /
NK069(tu)001:8205: 'di 'khor gyis rtogs tshul yin pas 'gal ba myed do //
NK069(tu)001:8206: 'khor gyi sgrib pa dag tshul la dpe bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8207: me long bstan pa'i tshul bzhin du //
NK069(tu)001:8208: zhes chos brdas 'jal bar ston pa'i dper ni /
NK069(tu)001:8209: gzhin gnal ma'i mdun du me long bzhag pas dri ma gsal ba bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:8210: dngos kyi mdog ngan thams cad sel //
NK069(tu)001:8211: zhes me long gi nang na /
NK069(tu)001:8212: byad bzhin dngos la dri ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:8214: gnyer tshogs la sogs gsal bar snang la /
NK069(tu)001:8215: de phyi ba'i thabs thams cad kyang sel bar shes /
NK069(tu)001:8216: gsal bar snang ba dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:8218: 'khor gyis de bzhin sku bltas pas //
NK069(tu)001:8219: zhes 'khor sa bcu pa'i byang chub sems dpas kyang /
NK069(tu)001:8220: ston pa rnam par snang mdzad kyi sku la bltas pa na /
NK069(tu)001:8221: byang chub sgrib pa ting dpag myed //
NK069(tu)001:8222: ces byang chub sems dpa' la sgrib yang /
NK069(tu)001:8224: rgya che ba ma shes pa myed pas na /
NK069(tu)001:8226: me long bzhin du sku la snang //
NK069(tu)001:8227: zhes me long gi gzugs brnyan snang bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:8228: 'khor gyi grib pa gang yin pa thams cad dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi sku'am /
NK069(tu)001:8229: thugs kyi dgongs pa la snang bas so //
NK069(tu)001:8230: sgrib pa dag tshul dngos ni /
NK069(tu)001:8231: de nas sa bcu rim gyis byang //
NK069(tu)001:8232: zhes de ltar sgrib pa snang ba de mthong bas /
NK069(tu)001:8233: gnyen po ye shes kyang thugs la gsal bar snang bas /
NK069(tu)001:8234: sa bcu thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' la shes
NK069(tu)001:8235: bya'i sgrib pa yod de yang rim gyis sam khang
NK069(tu)001:8236: kyis byang ngo // bla med byang chub yang dag 'thob //
NK069(tu)001:8237: ces sgrib pa byang ba'i bla na myed pa'i byang chub sku gsum yang dag par 'thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:8238: thob pa dngos gang zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:8239: chos sku dpag med brjod du med //
NK069(tu)001:8240: ces chos kyi sku yon tan blos dpag tu myed /
NK069(tu)001:8241: ngag gis brjod du myed pa yang 'thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:8242: longs spyod zad myed rin chen gter //
NK069(tu)001:8243: zhes de las longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku /
NK069(tu)001:8244: yon tan zad pa'i dus myed pa /
NK069(tu)001:8245: rin po che'i gter dang 'dra ba rang gis 'thob /
NK069(tu)001:8247: sprul pa bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK069(tu)001:8248: ces de las sprul pa'i sku /
NK069(tu)001:8249: sprul pa'i grangs bye ba dang mnyam pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:8250: bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'gro ba'i don byed pa yang thob /
NK069(tu)001:8252: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:8253: 'dir sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK069(tu)001:8255: longs spyod zad myed rin chen gter //
NK069(tu)001:8257: zad mi shes pa'i gter du 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:8258: ces pa'i longs sku gcig longs sku gsum 'dabs so zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:8260: sku ni rnam par snang mdzad tshul //
NK069(tu)001:8262: mtshan nyid pa sa bcu sgrod pa'i 'og min du zhal mthong ba yin la /
NK069(tu)001:8263: zhal mthong sgrib pa bral nas /
NK069(tu)001:8264: 'bras su sa gsum la sku gsum thob pas na /
NK069(tu)001:8265: longs spyod zad myed smos pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:8266: zad mi shes pa'i gter du 'gyur ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:8267: 'bras bu gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga ba'i sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8268: de bas na 'dabs pa myed do //
NK069(tu)001:8269: mtshan dang dpe byad yang dag rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:8270: zhes dus der thun mong gi mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK069(tu)001:8271: dpe byad bzang po rgya bcu dang /
NK069(tu)001:8272: thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan dpe sems dpa' dang sems ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:8273: thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8274: spyod yul kun tu ma d+ha la //
NK069(tu)001:8275: zhes grub pa mthu thob pa'i rnal 'byor pa de'i /
NK069(tu)001:8276: dbang po dang spyod yul thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor du yang snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:8277: tshogs chen gnyis kyang rdzogs par rol //
NK069(tu)001:8278: zhes rgyu'i dus na 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs bsags pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:8279: rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa de /
NK069(tu)001:8280: 'dir tshogs gnyis kyang rang don du rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:8281: gzhan don du gnyis myed du rol spyod nus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8282: thabs dang shes rab sa'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:8283: ces tshogs chen gnyis ni gang yin na /
NK069(tu)001:8284: kun tu 'od kyi sa thob pa'i rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:8285: thabs bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:8286: shes rab ye shes kyi tshogs yang rdzogs so //
NK069(tu)001:8287: pad+ma spyan gyi sa thob pa'i rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:8288: thabs bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:8289: shes rab ye shes kyi tshogs yang rdzogs so //
NK069(tu)001:8290: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa thob pa'i rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:8291: thabs bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:8292: shes rab ye shes kyi tshogs yang rdzogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:8293: thabs dang shes rab dbyer myed pa'i mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:8294: de la sogs te bsam yas mchog /
NK069(tu)001:8295: ces de dag la sogs te /
NK069(tu)001:8296: sangs rgyas kyi che ba'i yon tan /
NK069(tu)001:8297: mtha' yas pa bsam gyis myi khyab pa'i yon tan mchog dang yang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8299: skye shi myed pa'i g.yung drung sku //
NK069(tu)001:8300: zhes sku lngar sangs rgyas par bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8303: nam du yang 'gyur ba myed pa'i tshe'i g.yung drung gi sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:8304: nyon mongs kun gyi zhing du gnas //
NK069(tu)001:8306: sems can nyon mongs pa kun gyi don byed pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:8307: gzugs sku rnam pa gnyis 'byung ba'i gazhi'am /
NK069(tu)001:8308: rten nam zhing lta bur gnas pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:8310: zad mi shes pa'i gter du 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:8311: zhes longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ni /
NK069(tu)001:8312: che ba'i yon tan thams cad zad mi shes pa /
NK069(tu)001:8313: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che'i gter dang 'dra ba thob par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:8314: 'dir sku lnga thob pa'i rgyu dang /
NK069(tu)001:8317: de la sku lnga thob pa'i rgyu ni /
NK069(tu)001:8318: rang la nyon mongs pa lnga gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8319: sku lnga thob pa'i rkyen ni /
NK069(tu)001:8320: nyon mongs pa ye shes lngar shes /
NK069(tu)001:8321: ye shes lnga rigs lngar bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8322: sku lnga rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK069(tu)001:8323: skye shi myed pa chos kyi sku yin /
NK069(tu)001:8324: che ba'i yon tan zad mi shes pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yin /
NK069(tu)001:8325: stong pa nyid rig pa la 'dzin pa rdo rje'i sku yin /
NK069(tu)001:8326: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes shar ba mngon par byang chub pa'i sku yin /
NK069(tu)001:8327: sems can thams cad la mnyam par don dbyer myed du mdzad pa sprul pa'i sku yin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8328: sku lnga po de yang sku gsum du 'dus te /
NK069(tu)001:8329: rdo rje'i sku chos kyi skur 'dus /
NK069(tu)001:8330: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur 'dus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8332: rdo rje rig pa 'dzin pa'i sku //
NK069(tu)001:8334: rdo rje ni mi 'gyur ba yin te /
NK069(tu)001:8335: mi 'gyur ba'i don rig pa la 'dzin pas na sku /
NK069(tu)001:8336: rdo rje'i sku de lta bu de yang thob par 'gyur ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:8338: thams cad dbyer myed mnyam pa'i sku //
NK069(tu)001:8340: sems can thams cad dang dbyer myed par mnyam pa'i don mdzad pa yin de /
NK069(tu)001:8341: sprul pa'i sku de lta bu yang thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:8343: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes sku //
NK069(tu)001:8344: zhes mngon par byang chub pa'i sku ni /
NK069(tu)001:8345: 'khor 'das thams cad mngon par mkhyen pa'i ye shes yin la /
NK069(tu)001:8346: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi sku yang thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:8347: de tshe sku lnga kun kyang rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:8350: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa de'i tshe /
NK069(tu)001:8352: dbyer myed par lhun gyis grub ste /
NK069(tu)001:8353: sku lnga lhun grub tu rdzogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8354: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas mu myed pa thams cad du //
NK069(tu)001:8355: zhes gong gi dkyil 'khor de dag gis rgyu byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:8358: dkyil 'khor brjod kyis mi lang ba zhing gi rdul snyed du gsal bar gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:8360: sems can gyis brjod du mi lang ba /
NK069(tu)001:8361: sangs rgyas kyi zhing rdul phra mo snyed dang grangs mnyam pa thams cad du gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:8362: sku snang ba gsung grag pa /
NK069(tu)001:8367: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang thabs /
NK069(tu)001:8368: shes rab gnyis su myed pa'i rigs drug tu snang
NK069(tu)001:8369: ba'i dkyil 'khor de dag nyid kyi gsang ba'i rgyud
NK069(tu)001:8370: 'di nyid / le'u rgyas par bstan pa'i rjes de nas /
NK069(tu)001:8375: gsang ba snying po'i le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis la /
NK069(tu)001:8376: le'u sdud bzhi las mi 'ong ba'i 'thad pa gang yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:8378: le'u nyi shu rtsa gnyis yod yang /
NK069(tu)001:8379: gzhi lam 'bras bu gsum du 'dus pas so //
NK069(tu)001:8380: 'o na lhag par dang po dang gsum pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:8381: drug par 'ong ba ci ste zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:8382: le'u dang po gzhi yin pas sdus /
NK069(tu)001:8383: lam lta sgom gnyis yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:8384: le'u gsum par lta ba sdus /
NK069(tu)001:8385: le'u bzhi par yi ges mtshon nas bsgom pa bsdus /
NK069(tu)001:8386: 'bras bu'i rtsa ba'am gzhi lta bu sku lnga yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:8391: dmyigs bya dmyigs byed mi dmyigs dpag myed bsam mi khyab //
NK069(tu)001:8393: dang po phyi ltar bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:8396: myi dmyigs pa gnyis myed stong pa /
NK069(tu)001:8397: dpag myed de rtogs par dka' ba /
NK069(tu)001:8398: bsam gyis mi khyab rgya che bar gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8399: gnyis pa nang ltar bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:8401: dmyigs byed nang gi rnam shes /
NK069(tu)001:8402: de gnyis dngos po dang mtshan mar mi dmigs /
NK069(tu)001:8403: de blos bsam gyis mi khyab bo //
NK069(tu)001:8404: gsum pa gsang ba ltar bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:8405: dmyigs bya yul chos kyi dbyings /
NK069(tu)001:8406: dmyigs byed rang gi rig pa'i ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:8407: dmyigs bya chos kyi dbyings de /
NK069(tu)001:8408: dmyigs byed rang gi rig pa'i ye shes kyis rtogs nas /
NK069(tu)001:8409: dbyings dang rig pa gnyis su myed pas /
NK069(tu)001:8410: dngos po dang mtshan ma myed par mthar phyin pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:8411: mtshan ma myed pa'i don de ni blos dpag tu myed pa /
NK069(tu)001:8412: sems kyi bsam pa'i yul las 'das pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8413: bzhi pa de kho na ltar bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:8414: dmyigs bya chos kyi dbyings ni /
NK069(tu)001:8415: yul spros pa dang bral ba yin la /
NK069(tu)001:8416: dmyigs byed rig pa'i ye shes ni /
NK069(tu)001:8417: dbyings rig pa dang ldan pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:8418: dbyings dang ye shes de gnyis so so'am tha dad du mi dmyigs la /
NK069(tu)001:8419: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer myed pa de las /
NK069(tu)001:8420: che ba'i yon tan sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK069(tu)001:8421: dpag tu myed cing bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'byung
NK069(tu)001:8422: ba yin no // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rang bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:8424: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub /
NK069(tu)001:8426: ye shes rang rig dkyil 'khor sna tshogs brjod mi lang //
NK069(tu)001:8427: zhes de ltar 'byung ba'i rgyu gang yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:8428: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su myed pa'i don /
NK069(tu)001:8429: ngang gi mtshan nyid rig cing rtogs pa'i rig pa'i ye shes kyi gzugs brnyan de nyid /
NK069(tu)001:8430: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor sna tshogs brjod kyis mi lang bar snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:8432: sku yi phyag rgya che mchog ni /
NK069(tu)001:8434: gzhan yang theg mchog rim pa bzhin //
NK069(tu)001:8436: mnyam dang mi mnyam kun khyab khyab myed khyab pa'i dbyings //
NK069(tu)001:8437: zhes de las gang la khyab na /
NK069(tu)001:8438: mnyam pa thabs kyi rgyud dang /
NK069(tu)001:8440: rgyud gzhan theg pa 'og ma ba lta bu kun la /
NK069(tu)001:8441: sangs rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor gyis khyab pas kun khyab /
NK069(tu)001:8442: khyab tsam na dngos por grub pa myed pas khyab med /
NK069(tu)001:8443: de lta bu'i rang bzhin yin pas khyab pa'i dbyings so //
NK069(tu)001:8445: 'og min bla med gnas mchog nas //
NK069(tu)001:8447: sprul pa bye ba bsam mi khyab //
NK069(tu)001:8449: ye nas kun gsal dkyil 'khor rnam 'phro spros pa myed //
NK069(tu)001:8451: zhes rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK069(tu)001:8452: zhes gsang sngags rdo rje'i tshig tu de skad mtshon nas ston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8453: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:8454: gasnga ba ni rtogs par dka' ba /
NK069(tu)001:8455: snying po ni bcud 'dus pa 'don gyi snying po /
NK069(tu)001:8456: de kho na nyida ni mi slu ba /
NK069(tu)001:8457: ngesa pa yang dag pa'i don de lasa /
NK069(tu)001:8458: gong gi dkyil 'khor de kun gyi rang bzhin ji lta bu yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:8459: rang bzhin ye nas dngos dang mtshan mar myi dmyigs /
NK069(tu)001:8460: skyon gyis ma gos par 'od gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:8462: sna tshogs par snang ba ni myed pa'i skyon gyis ma sgribs par 'od gsal la /
NK069(tu)001:8463: snang tsam na mtshan ma myed pa'i ngang las ma g.yos pas ni /
NK069(tu)001:8464: yod pa'i skyon gyis ma sgribs par 'od gsal bas ye nas kun gsal /
NK069(tu)001:8465: de las dkyil 'khor bsam gyis myi khyab par snang ba ni rnam 'aphro'o //
NK069(tu)001:8466: de tsam na mtshan ma myed pa'i ngang las ma g.yos pas spros pa myed do //
NK069(tu)001:8468: mtshan dang dpe byad thams cad rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:8470: de'i tshe sku lnga kun kyang rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:8472: dkyil 'khor spro ba'i le'u ste drug pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8474: // ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyala 'akhara bsgom don du spros /
NK069(tu)001:8475: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor 'gro don mdzad par spro ba'i le'u ste drug pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8476: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa btsun mo'i tshogs dang bcas pa thams cad kyis /
NK069(tu)001:8477: zhes dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i rjes de nas /
NK069(tu)001:8478: de bskyed cing bsgrub pa'i sngags ston te /
NK069(tu)001:8479: de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga yab yum dang bcas pa thams cad dam /
NK069(tu)001:8480: ston pa nyid rigs lnga spyi'i bdag nyid can du gnas pas so //
NK069(tu)001:8481: sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las 'di phyung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:8485: mtshon par snang ba thugs so //
NK069(tu)001:8486: gzhal yas khang bskyed pa la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:8490: b+h+r+aum ni bcom ldan 'das gtsug tor 'khor lo sgyur ba'i snying po 'bru gcig pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:8491: bcom ldan 'das gtsug tor 'khor lo sgyur ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:8492: dang po byang chub tu sems bskyed pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:8493: bdag ni dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa'i bzhugs
NK069(tu)001:8494: gnas gzhal yas khang du gyur cig par smon lam
NK069(tu)001:8496: de bzhin gshegs pa ni smon gnas lhun gyis grub pa yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:8497: b+h+r+aum brjod pa'i 'phro 'du tsam gyis gzhal yas khang du gsal gyis bskyed do //
NK069(tu)001:8498: de yang yi ge b+h+r+aum gyi rnam par snang ba gang yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:8499: bzhugs gnas gzhal yas khang dang /
NK069(tu)001:8500: sangs rgyas gtsug tor 'khor lo sgyur ba gsum dbyer myed do //
NK069(tu)001:8501: bi sha ni sna tshogs de /
NK069(tu)001:8502: rgyu ni rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8503: bi shud d+he ni dag pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:8505: bskyed thabs 'khor lo brtsibs bzhi mu khyud bcas //
NK069(tu)001:8508: b+h+r+aum ni yum gyi ba ga yi ge b+h+r+aum gyi dbyibs can dgos 'dod 'byung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:8509: bi sha ni sna tshogs de /
NK069(tu)001:8516: stobs kyi h+aum drag gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8517: bi shud de ni dag pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:8518: sbyor pa'i las kyis nyon mongs pa nyid ye shes kyi ngo bor dag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8519: des yon tan 'byung zhing byin gyis skyob pa kho na gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8521: b+h+r+aum dbyibs ba gar sna tshogs 'dus //
NK069(tu)001:8522: las dang ngo bo dag pa nyid //
NK069(tu)001:8523: sangs rgyas rin chen za ma tog /
NK069(tu)001:8524: byin brlabs skyob phyir sngags su brjod //
NK069(tu)001:8527: zhes ni gzhal yas khang gi sa bon no //
NK069(tu)001:8534: h+aum ni rnam par shes pa'i phung po thugs kyi sa bon no //
NK069(tu)001:8535: badz+ra 'draga ni rdo rje 'dzin pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:8536: mi skyod pa'i mtshan sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8538: +aa ni gzugs kyi phung po sku'i sa bon no //
NK069(tu)001:8540: rgyal ba rgyal zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:8541: sku rnam par snang mdzad kyi mtshan sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8543: swa ni tshor ba'i phung po rin chen 'byung ldan gyi rigs kyi sa bon no //
NK069(tu)001:8544: rada na 'draga ni rin chen 'dzin pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:8545: yon tan rin chen 'byung ldan gyi ming sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8547: a ni 'du shes kyi phung po gsung gi rigs kyi sa bon no //
NK069(tu)001:8548: a ro lag ni chags bsogs mchog ste /
NK069(tu)001:8549: gsung snang ba mtha' yas kyi ming sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8551: ha ni 'du byed kyi phung po las kyi rigs kyi sa bon no //
NK069(tu)001:8554: 'phrin las don yod grub pa'i mtshan sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8556: snying ka chos kyi 'khor lo'i nang na /
NK069(tu)001:8557: khams lnga'i bcud 'dus pa'i rtsa la /
NK069(tu)001:8558: h+aum mthing ka rdo rje'i rang bzhin stong pa /
NK069(tu)001:8559: +amo dkar po sku'i rang bzhin 'khor ba las rgyal ba /
NK069(tu)001:8560: swa ser po yon tan gyi rang bzhin rin po che lta bu /
NK069(tu)001:8561: dmar po gsung chos thams cad kyi 'byung gnas /
NK069(tu)001:8562: ha ljang khu shes rab kyi rang bzhin las thams cad la khyab pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:8563: khams kyi bcud lnga yi ge'i gzugs dang ldan pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:8565: mi rtog par skyob pas na sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8567: tsit+ta khams lnga'i gshi ra la //
NK069(tu)001:8568: rdo rje rgyal ba rin chen mos //
NK069(tu)001:8569: shes rab rigs ldan bcud kyi gzugs //
NK069(tu)001:8570: nges par 'dzin pa gsang ba'i sngags //
NK069(tu)001:8575: mum ne stong pa nyid de nam mkha'o //
NK069(tu)001:8576: da du shwa ri ni dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:8577: rdo rje sems dpa'i yum nam ka dbyings phyug ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:8579: la ni sa'i sa bon te /
NK069(tu)001:8580: ta shwa ra ti ni gti mug dga' ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:8581: gti mug pa'i rang bzhin sangs rgyas spyan no //
NK069(tu)001:8585: ma ha ra ti ni zhe sdang dga' ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:8586: chu ma ma ko rin 'byung gi yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:8588: bam ni me'i sa bon te /
NK069(tu)001:8589: ra ga ra ta ni 'dod chags dga' ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:8590: me gos dkar mo snang ba mtha' yas kyi yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:8592: ta ni rlung gi rang bzhin te /
NK069(tu)001:8593: badz+ra ra te rdo rje dga' ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:8594: rlung dam tshig sgrol ma don yod grub pa'i yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:8596: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo'i nang na /
NK069(tu)001:8597: khams ye shes lnga'i bcud kyi dkyil na /
NK069(tu)001:8598: mum nam mkha'i dngas ma stong pa /
NK069(tu)001:8599: lam sa'i dngas ma dar dkar gyi skud pa /
NK069(tu)001:8600: mam chu'i dngas ma khrag 'tshal khu tsam /
NK069(tu)001:8601: bam me'i dngas ma me long nyi ma la bzhag pa'i ngad tsam /
NK069(tu)001:8602: tam rlung gi dngas ma gser sa 'og tu sbas pa'i rlangs pa tsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:8603: yang na bcud lnga'i dngas ma ye shes lnga yi gnas ni dbyings phyug ma'i /
NK069(tu)001:8604: de la ma rig pa dag pa gti mug dga' ma /
NK069(tu)001:8605: nyon mongs pa bzhi po nyid zhe sdang dga' ma /
NK069(tu)001:8606: de rnams dang mi phyed pa 'dod chags dga' ma /
NK069(tu)001:8607: nyon mongs pas mi sgrib pa 'phrag dog te rdo rje dga' ma /
NK069(tu)001:8608: yid skyobs pas na yum sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8610: de nyid dwangs ma'i ye shes lnga //
NK069(tu)001:8611: ma rig gnyis bsogs bzhi po dang //
NK069(tu)001:8612: mi phyed 'phrag dog rdo rje'i sngags //
NK069(tu)001:8613: dbyings skyob pa dag dga' mar brjod //
NK069(tu)001:8616: rnam shes kyi sems dpa'i sngags /
NK069(tu)001:8618: k+sha ni myig gi rnam shes bcud dang rlung gi thig le yi ger gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8619: ha ra tsa ya ni sa'i rgyal po ste /
NK069(tu)001:8620: byang chub sems dpa' sa'i snying po'i ming sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8622: tra ni sna'i rnam shes bcud dang rlung 'dres pa'i thig le tram gyi gzugs can te /
NK069(tu)001:8623: a kara rba ya ni stong pa'i snying po ste /
NK069(tu)001:8624: byang chub sems dpa' nam mkha'i snying po'i ming ngo //
NK069(tu)001:8625: h+r+ai ha h+aum pad ma ba d+ha ma /
NK069(tu)001:8626: h+r+ai ni lce'i rnam shes la bcud dang rlung 'dres pa'i thig le yi ge'i gzugs su gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8627: ha h+aum pada ma ba d+ha ma ni /
NK069(tu)001:8628: pad ma'i phyag zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:8629: byang chub sems dpa' spyan ras gzigs kyi sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8630: dzim ku ru pa na h+r+ai /
NK069(tu)001:8631: dzima ni rna ba'i dbang po bcud dang rlung sems 'dres pa'i thig ler gnas pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:8632: ku ru pa na h+r+ai ni rgyal byed phyag zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:8633: byang chub sems dpa' phyag na rdo rje'i sa bon nam ming sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8634: nang gi sems dpa'i sngags ni /
NK069(tu)001:8635: h+aum la se sa sgeg pa ma ya stmo /
NK069(tu)001:8636: bdag ni khyod kyi dam tshig ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:8638: bde bas sgeg pa'i dam tshig ma zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:8639: chags pa'i yid g.yos pas sam smon par bya ba'i yul yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:8640: smon pa byang chub kyi sems sam /
NK069(tu)001:8641: g.yo ba byang chub kyi sems de la kyi bde bas sgegs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8642: chags pa'i dam tshig dus yin no //
NK069(tu)001:8643: ces thal ba nas bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:8646: khyod ni bdag gi dam tshig ma'o zhes phan tshun
NK069(tu)001:8647: gyi bde ba 'phel bas dam tshig gis dgyes ma
NK069(tu)001:8648: zhes bya ste / yul de la chags pa'i yid ltang ba'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:8649: ltang ba byang chub kyi sems zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:8650: slar yang lan gyis 'brel pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8651: gnyis ka dgyes pa'i mchog tu bshad /
NK069(tu)001:8655: bdag gi khyod kyi rjes su chags par byed pa
NK069(tu)001:8656: zhes bde ba'i dbyangs myong ba la bdag chags pa
NK069(tu)001:8657: zhes bya ste / gsang ba'i yul la gsang ba'i dbang po 'jug par byed pas /
NK069(tu)001:8658: 'jug pa byang chub kyi sems te /
NK069(tu)001:8659: ha dang po'i bde sgra dag /
NK069(tu)001:8660: bdag gis chags pa thob pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8662: a nir ti ra gar ma ga ya mi /
NK069(tu)001:8663: khyod ni bdag gi rjes su chags par byed pa
NK069(tu)001:8664: zhes skul skyod kyis bde ba 'bebs pas chags par
NK069(tu)001:8666: gsang ba'i dbang po yul la gnas pas /
NK069(tu)001:8667: gnas pa byang chub sems zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:8668: shin du skyod pa'i bde ba nyid /
NK069(tu)001:8669: kun nas skyod pa rlung zhes bya zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:8670: yang na sbyor ba'i brda' brda' yi las dang yang sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:8671: sa ma ya stmo ni yum gyis skul ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:8672: dam tshig gi dus la bab bo zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:8673: sa ma ya ho ni yab kyi skul ba'am lan byin pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:8674: dam tshig gis mnyes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:8677: bdag ni khyod kyi rjes su chags pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8679: yab kyis skul te lan byin pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:8680: rjes su chags pas mnyes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:8681: lha mo bzhis chags pa'i las byed pa dang sbyar nas yang bshad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8682: dbang po'i sems dpa'i sngags ni /
NK069(tu)001:8683: me d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK069(tu)001:8684: zhes dmyig gi dbang po rlung sems 'dres pa'i thig le yi ge mer gnas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8686: de ni byang chub sems dpa' byams ma me tri'i sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8687: th+l+him swa ram pa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK069(tu)001:8688: zhes sna'i dbang po rlung sems 'dres pa'i thig le
NK069(tu)001:8689: ni yi ge th+l+him du gnas pa ni sa bon
NK069(tu)001:8690: no // de las byang chub sems dpa' sgrib sel gyi sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8691: h+aum swa ra tsa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK069(tu)001:8692: zhes lce'i dbang po rlung sems 'dres pa'i thig le yi ge h+aum du gnas pa sa bon no //
NK069(tu)001:8693: de las sems dpa' rdo rje rgyal po zhes bya te /
NK069(tu)001:8695: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po'o //
NK069(tu)001:8696: mum sh+r+ai am ram g+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK069(tu)001:8697: zhes snang ba'i dbang po rlung sems 'dres pa'i thig le yi ge mum du gnas pa las /
NK069(tu)001:8698: byang chub sems dpa' bskyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8701: zhes dza lcags kyu'i las kyi byang sems dkar dmar drangs nas /
NK069(tu)001:8703: pra be sha ni yum gyi ba ga'i sgo phye ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:8707: zhes pas lha mo spos me mar bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:8708: h+aum pus pa a be sha /
NK069(tu)001:8709: zhes h+aum ni zhags pa'i las kyis stod smad 'khyud pa /
NK069(tu)001:8710: pus pa ni byang sems gnyis myed kyi ngo bo nyid me tog /
NK069(tu)001:8711: a be sha ni byang chub sems gsang ba'i mkha' la babs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8713: me tog sdus pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK069(tu)001:8714: bdag pa'i zhal du thim par bshad //
NK069(tu)001:8717: bam de pa su gi ni /
NK069(tu)001:8718: zhes pam ni lcags sgrog gi las kyis sdam pa
NK069(tu)001:8719: ste di pa ni bde ba gsal bas mar me
NK069(tu)001:8720: / su gi ni bde ba dgyes pa'i ro sku nyams tar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:8722: shin tu sdams pa'i rigs las byung //
NK069(tu)001:8723: gsal ba'i ye shes bde ba che //
NK069(tu)001:8726: ho g+han d+he tsi ta ho /
NK069(tu)001:8727: zhes ho dril bu'i las kyis dgyes pa bskyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8728: g+han d+he ni rtsa gnas bde bas rgyas pa'i dri chab bo //
NK069(tu)001:8729: tsi tas ni byang chub kyi sems sna tshogs par spros pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8731: kun gsal brjod dang bral ba'i sgra //
NK069(tu)001:8732: gnyis myed thugs su shes par bya //
NK069(tu)001:8736: du pa ni gdug spos te /
NK069(tu)001:8737: spos kyi sna'i dbang po tshim pa bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:8738: byang chub kyi sems phab nas gtso gzungs gsang ba'i dbang po so sor tshim pa la bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:8739: pus pa ni me tog ste /
NK069(tu)001:8740: dkyil 'khor du me tog dor ba yin pa ltar /
NK069(tu)001:8741: byang chub kyi sems gsang ba'i mkha' la spros pa la bya /
NK069(tu)001:8742: a lo'am de pa ni mar me 'am gsal ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:8743: mar mes gsal ba dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:8744: byang chub kyi sems spros nas yab yum gyi sku'am /
NK069(tu)001:8745: bde ba so sor gsal ba la bya /
NK069(tu)001:8746: g+han d+he ni dri chab ste /
NK069(tu)001:8747: dri chab nyug pa'am mthor ba ltar /
NK069(tu)001:8748: byang chub kyi sems gsang ba'i gnas su babs pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:8749: mthor bas bde ba la bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:8751: h+aum ya man ta krid phata /
NK069(tu)001:8752: ces lus kyi reg byed ni lus kyi dbang po ste khro bo gshin rje mthar byed do //
NK069(tu)001:8753: h+aum big nan ta krid phata /
NK069(tu)001:8754: ces lus kyi dbang po reg pa ni khro bo bgegs mthar byed de /
NK069(tu)001:8757: h+aum pad ma ta krid phata /
NK069(tu)001:8758: ces lus kyi dbang po reg bya ni khro bo pad ma mthar byed de /
NK069(tu)001:8760: h'u prad nya ta krid phata /
NK069(tu)001:8761: ces lus kyi dbang po reg shes ni khro bo shes rab mthar byed de /
NK069(tu)001:8772: ces shar du khro mo dbyings phyug ma 'bar ba chen mo rdo rje 'dzin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8773: dngos su rta gdong lcags kyu ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:8782: ces lhor khro mo dbyings phyug ma rin chen 'dzin chen mo 'bar ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:8783: dngos su na phag gdong zhags pa ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:8787: ra ma h+aa kro d+hi khro mo /
NK069(tu)001:8788: shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u 'bar ma /
NK069(tu)001:8790: nub tu khro mo dbyings phyug ma 'bar ma chen mo pad ma 'dzin ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:8791: dngos su nyi zla lcags sgrog ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:8796: d+hi shwa ri dz+wa la ni h'u 'bar ma /
NK069(tu)001:8798: byang du khro mo dbyings phyug ma 'bar ma chen mo las kyi sgrol ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:8799: dngos su thal byed dril bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:8800: kun bzang yab yum gyi sngags ni /
NK069(tu)001:8801: h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra rtsi ta h+aum /
NK069(tu)001:8802: zhes h+aum gsum ni kun gzhi'i yid dang /
NK069(tu)001:8803: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid dang /
NK069(tu)001:8804: yid kyi rnam shes gsum mo //
NK069(tu)001:8805: badz+ra tsi ta ni rdo rje'i thugs so //
NK069(tu)001:8806: h+aum ni ye shes kyi snying po ste /
NK069(tu)001:8807: kun tu bzang po'i sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8809: rnam shes gsum 'das rdo rje ni /
NK069(tu)001:8810: ye shes lngar rdzogs thugs nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:8812: a a a badz+ra pa tra sa man +amo /
NK069(tu)001:8814: mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings de bzhin nyid dang /
NK069(tu)001:8815: chos kyi dbyings stong pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:8816: rang bzhin gyi dbyings spros bral gsum mo //
NK069(tu)001:8818: pa tra sa man ta ni /
NK069(tu)001:8820: a ni gnas su gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8821: dbyings gsum rnam dag 'dus ma byas /
NK069(tu)001:8822: kun tu 'ang de bzhin gnas byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8824: kun tu bzang mo'i sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8827: zhes rang gi nga rgyal 'od kyi thig le kring du gnas pa las /
NK069(tu)001:8828: lha'i thub pa srid thub 'dzin bskyed pa'i sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8829: mu ne h+aum trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK069(tu)001:8830: zhes rang gi khong khro 'od kyi thig le trum du gnas pa las /
NK069(tu)001:8831: lha ma yin gyi thub pa rnam par rgyal ba bskyed pa'i sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8833: zhes rang gi 'dod chags 'od kyi thig le krum du gnas pa las /
NK069(tu)001:8834: myi'i thub pa sh+aakya seng ge skyed pa'i sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:8836: zhes rang gi gti mug 'od kyi thig le bram du gnas pa las /
NK069(tu)001:8837: byol song gi thub pa rnam par gnon pa'i bskyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8839: zhes rang gi ser sna'i 'od kyi thig le k+sham du gnas pa las /
NK069(tu)001:8840: yi dwags kyi thub pa rnam par snang byed du bskyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8842: zhes rang gi zhe sdang gi 'od kyi thig le yer gnas pa las /
NK069(tu)001:8843: dmyal ba'i thub pa chos kyi rgyal po bskyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8844: thub drug gi sngags thabs lam du bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:8845: yum gyi mkha' la 'gro drug gi yi ge tshang ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:8847: lha ma yin gyi su ser po /
NK069(tu)001:8849: yi dwags kyi pri dmar po /
NK069(tu)001:8851: dmyal ba'i tri dmar nag go //
NK069(tu)001:8854: nyon mongs pa drug gi yi ge kring la sogs pa drug tu gnas te /
NK069(tu)001:8855: yab yum bde ba skyis pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:8858: gti mug gi mun pa sel /
NK069(tu)001:8859: nga rgyal gyi ri bo snyil /
NK069(tu)001:8862: de ltar las dang nyon mongs pa thub pas na thub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8863: de skad du yang sgyu 'phrul thal ba nas /
NK069(tu)001:8864: sa bon zung gsum de bde ba //
NK069(tu)001:8865: nges skyes rang rig gyur pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:8872: ma h+aa ka ru ni ka thugs rje chen po /
NK069(tu)001:8874: gzigs gcig gam snang bar mdzod gcig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8875: sa ma ya stmo dam tshig gi dus la bab pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8877: zhes dza las lcags kyu ma dkar mo /
NK069(tu)001:8878: h+aum las zhags pa ma ser /
NK069(tu)001:8880: ho las ljang khu'i dril bu ma bzhis /
NK069(tu)001:8881: mdun gyi nam mkha' la spyan drangs byon par bsam /
NK069(tu)001:8882: spyir yi ge bsdu ba la lugs bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:8883: tshig bshad kyis bsdu ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:8886: sde tshan gyis bsdu ba las /
NK069(tu)001:8887: 'di ni sdebs kyis bsdu ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:8891: badz+ra sa ma ya ni gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:8892: h+aum badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum ni thugs so //
NK069(tu)001:8893: swa badz+ra sa ma ya swa ni /
NK069(tu)001:8895: ha badz+ra sa ma ya ha ni 'phrin las te /
NK069(tu)001:8896: bdag gi ting nge 'dzin gyis bskyed pa'i lha'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK069(tu)001:8897: grub pa'i gnas nas spyan drangs pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:8898: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lnga'i rang bzhin
NK069(tu)001:8899: du thams cad nas thams cad du dbyer myed par
NK069(tu)001:8901: rig pa'i me tog dor ba yin no //
NK069(tu)001:8902: bdag gi lhag pa byang chub sems kyi spro bsdu las /
NK069(tu)001:8903: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bskyed pa de ci 'dra ba gcig /
NK069(tu)001:8904: rang bzhin grub pa'i gnas nas /
NK069(tu)001:8908: de yang bod skad du brjod na /
NK069(tu)001:8910: thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa /
NK069(tu)001:8911: khyod kyi sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor bdag la gnang bar mdzod cig /
NK069(tu)001:8920: +amo ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK069(tu)001:8921: yon tan 'phrin las smad po che //
NK069(tu)001:8922: zhes ye ji bzhin pa'i don mkhyen pa'i ye shes rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:8923: mtha' gnyis las rgyal ba'i rgyal po /
NK069(tu)001:8924: sangs rgyas kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs dang yon
NK069(tu)001:8925: tan phrin las nyi shu rtsa lngar lhun gyis grub
NK069(tu)001:8926: pa'i ngo mtshar smad po che de /
NK069(tu)001:8927: da nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK069(tu)001:8928: zhes dus da lta nyid du /
NK069(tu)001:8929: sangs rgyas kyi sku gsung thugs dang /
NK069(tu)001:8930: bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum mnyam par sbyor bas //
NK069(tu)001:8931: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK069(tu)001:8932: ces khyed kyi phyag rgya chen po sku lnga lhun grub cing 'dra ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:8933: bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum dbyer myed par mnyam par sbyor cig /
NK069(tu)001:8934: ces bod skad du yang skul lo //
NK069(tu)001:8936: 'dir le'u bdun pa gsung gi le'u zer tsam na /
NK069(tu)001:8937: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lnga ka la dngos grub skul ba ci ste zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:8938: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lnga la dngos
NK069(tu)001:8939: grub skul ba kho na gsung gis skul zhing gsol
NK069(tu)001:8943: chos sku nam mkha' ltar brtag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:8944: longs sku 'dod pa la bde bar longs spyod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:8945: sprul sku gang 'dod par 'dul dbang du gtong ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:8946: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku sgyu ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:8947: rdo rje'i sku 'dus ma byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8949: yi ge myed pa chos sku'i gsung brjod pa dang bral ba /
NK069(tu)001:8950: mngon byang rig pa'i gsung rtog pa myed pa /
NK069(tu)001:8951: longs sku'i gsung me long lta bu'i gzugs su snang ba /
NK069(tu)001:8952: sprul sku tshangs pa'i gsung yan lag drug cus brjod pa /
NK069(tu)001:8953: rdo rje'i sku'i gsung 'dus ma byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8955: mi rtog pa'i thugs me long ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:8956: cir yang sa le mkhyen pa'i thugs chos dbyings ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:8957: bde ba chen po'i thugs mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:8958: 'gro ba sgrol ba'i thugs so sor rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:8959: rdo rje sku'i thugs bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:8961: zhing khams ni thugs rje sprul pas 'dul ba'i zhing khams /
NK069(tu)001:8962: gzhal yas khang ni byams pa'i khyim du sdud pa'i yon tan /
NK069(tu)001:8963: 'od zer ni btang snyoms kyis kun nas 'phro ba'i yon tan /
NK069(tu)001:8964: gtan khri ni bsgrib sel gyi yon tan rtogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:8965: longs spyod ni gtan bzhugs dga' bas re 'dod skong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:8968: rgyas pas kun tu rang bzhin ma 'gags pa /
NK069(tu)001:8969: dbang gis mngon du gyur pa /
NK069(tu)001:8970: lhun grub kyis rgyu rkyen 'bad brtsol myed par ye nas grub pa /
NK069(tu)001:8972: log lta can gyi mu stegs dang /
NK069(tu)001:8973: sdug bsngal can gyi dmyal ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:8974: bkres skom can gyi yi dwags dang /
NK069(tu)001:8975: khengs sems can gyi sgra skad rnams skad cig la 'joms pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:8976: de ltar re re nas rtsis pas lnga lngar gyur pas na smad po che zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:8978: zhes rgya gar skad du bskul ba /
NK069(tu)001:8979: rdo rje dam tshig gi thugs zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:8981: ni rdo rje dam tshig gi dus la babs so //
NK069(tu)001:8982: rdo rje dam tshig gis mnyes par bya'o ni /
NK069(tu)001:8983: badz+ra sa ma ya ho ni /
NK069(tu)001:8986: bdag ting nge 'dzin gyis bskyed pa la /
NK069(tu)001:8987: dza h+aum bam ho'i phyag rgya bzhis stims nas /
NK069(tu)001:8988: dper na mar me sdong bu gnyis gcig tu thims na /
NK069(tu)001:8989: me lce yang gcig tu 'bar ba dang 'dra bar dbyer myed par bsgom par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:8991: zhes de skad brjod pa'i yon tan ni gang zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:8993: zhes gsung gi dkyil 'khor de dag gis rgyu byas na /
NK069(tu)001:8994: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad khyab par grags so //
NK069(tu)001:8999: de nas bcom ldan 'das byed pa po rdo rje dang /
NK069(tu)001:9000: bya ba mo rdo rje gnyis su myed pa'i dkyil 'khor la thim par mdzad do //
NK069(tu)001:9001: zhes de yan chad du bdag sngon gyi sangs rgyas yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:9002: bdag gi sras su de bzhin gshegs pa bya ba ni bstan nas /
NK069(tu)001:9003: da ni rigs mi nub cing lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:9004: de bzhin gshegs sras su bdag bskyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9005: bdag tha mal pa'i lus su byung nas /
NK069(tu)001:9006: gsol ba btab ste 'od du zhu bas /
NK069(tu)001:9007: gtso bo yab yum la thim pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9008: de yang dkyil 'khor thams cad bskyed na yang bdag
NK069(tu)001:9009: yab yum thabs shes rab gnyis su myed pa bskyed
NK069(tu)001:9010: la / bsdud na yang yab yum gnyis su myed pa la thim par mdzad pas /
NK069(tu)001:9011: bdag sras dang gzhan sras su ngos bzung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9012: de nas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bdag nyid chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:9013: ston pa'i bdag nyid kun tu bzang pos /
NK069(tu)001:9014: bdag nyid chen po'i ye shes dang /
NK069(tu)001:9015: zhes sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bdag nyid chen po
NK069(tu)001:9016: thob par byed na ye shes ye shes lngas dbang
NK069(tu)001:9017: bskur ba dang / dbang rtags kyi lha ni /
NK069(tu)001:9018: rdo rje'i rigs rnams la mi bskyod pa dbu rgyan gyi gtso bo /
NK069(tu)001:9024: kun po yab yum mi skyod pa /
NK069(tu)001:9025: thub drug la dbu rgyan no //
NK069(tu)001:9027: mi skyod byed po yum dang bcas //
NK069(tu)001:9028: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i phyag rgyar ldan //
NK069(tu)001:9029: byams pa sam snying de bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:9030: gzhan dag rang gi phyag rgya ste //
NK069(tu)001:9031: gshin rje gshed po rtag par bshad //
NK069(tu)001:9033: zla dang bral ba dpa' bo che //
NK069(tu)001:9035: byin bsdu ba zhes bya ba 'di /
NK069(tu)001:9036: sku gsung thugs kyi byin brlabs /
NK069(tu)001:9038: skye 'jig myed pa rdo rje'i sku /
NK069(tu)001:9040: brjod pa bral ba rdo rje'i gsung /
NK069(tu)001:9042: snang stong myed pa rdo rje'i thugs /
NK069(tu)001:9043: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba las phyung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:9045: dra ba shes rab ste yum lasa phyung ngo zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:9046: +amo ma h+aa shu dz+ny+aa ta gnya' na badz+ra swa ba b+ha ad ma ko&a ham /
NK069(tu)001:9047: zhes lha rnams kyi spyi bo'i gtsug tu /
NK069(tu)001:9048: rin po che'i khang bu nang na /
