NK069(tu)001:9049: rnam par snang mdzad dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya can bskyed la /
NK069(tu)001:9050: sngags 'di brjod pas stong pa nyid kyi ye shes
NK069(tu)001:9051: gang yin pa nga'am bdag go zhes che ba'i nga
NK069(tu)001:9052: rgyal bya / phyi nang gi chos thams cad stong pa nyid du rtogs par bsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:9053: +amo ma h+aa a ta ri sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK069(tu)001:9054: zhes lha rnams kyi dpral bar rin po che'i khang bu nang du /
NK069(tu)001:9055: mi skyod pa mthing ka sa non gyi phyag rgya can bsams la /
NK069(tu)001:9057: me long lta bu'i ye shes nga'am bdag yin zhes che ba'i nga rgyal bya /
NK069(tu)001:9058: don yang dran par bsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:9059: de yang chos thams cad snang la rang bzhin myed pa gsal la rtog pa myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9060: +amo ma h+aa pra ta pra be sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba ad ma ko ko&a ham /
NK069(tu)001:9061: zhes lha rnams kyi ltag khung du /
NK069(tu)001:9062: rin po che'i khang bu nang na /
NK069(tu)001:9063: snang ba mtha' yas mnyam bzhag dmar po bsams la /
NK069(tu)001:9064: sngags 'di brjod pas che ba'i nga rgyal bya /
NK069(tu)001:9065: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK069(tu)001:9066: chos spyi dang rang gi tshig ma 'dres par mkhyen par bsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:9067: +amo ma h+aa sa man ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK069(tu)001:9068: zhes lha rnams kyi rna ltag g.yas par /
NK069(tu)001:9069: rin po che'i khang bu nang du /
NK069(tu)001:9070: rin chen 'byung ldan ser po sbyin gtong gi phyag rgya can bsam /
NK069(tu)001:9071: sngags 'di brjod pas che ba'i nga rgyal bya /
NK069(tu)001:9072: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis bdag dang chos thams cad dbyer med du rtogs par bsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:9073: +amo ma h+aa kri ta a nu sha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK069(tu)001:9074: zhes lha rnams kyi rna ltag g.yon par /
NK069(tu)001:9075: rin po che'i khang bu nang du /
NK069(tu)001:9076: don yod grub pa ljang khu skyabs sbyin gyi phyag rgya can bsam /
NK069(tu)001:9078: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyi bdag dang gzhan
NK069(tu)001:9079: gyi don yongs su rdzogs pa'i don yid la dran
NK069(tu)001:9080: par bya'o // +amo sarba ta tha ga ta ma
NK069(tu)001:9081: h+aa ka ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba ad ma ko&a
NK069(tu)001:9082: par bya'o // ham / zhes lha rnams kyi spyi bo bde chen la /
NK069(tu)001:9083: +amo las rnam par snang mdzad bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:9084: sngags 'di brjod pas zla dal la rdo rjes mtshan par bsams la /
NK069(tu)001:9085: sku'i gsang ba bsam gyis myi khyab chos sku dang /
NK069(tu)001:9086: sku thams cad la gzugs sku gnyis la sogs pa 'byung ste /
NK069(tu)001:9087: sku rdo rje nga'am bdag yin ces pa'i nga rgyal bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:9088: +amo sarba ta tha ga ta ma h+aa ba ga badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK069(tu)001:9089: zhes mgrin par pad ma longs spyod la /
NK069(tu)001:9090: ang las snang ba mtha' yas bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:9091: sngags 'di 'od du zhu nas pad ma la rdo rje bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:9092: gsung gi gsang ba bsam gyis myi khyab pa yi ge myed pa'i gsung dang /
NK069(tu)001:9093: gsung thams cad pa tshig gi gsung thams cad de /
NK069(tu)001:9094: gsung rdo rje nga'am bdag sgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:9095: sarba ta tha ga ta ma h+aa rtsi ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK069(tu)001:9096: zhes snying kar chos la nyi ma'i steng du /
NK069(tu)001:9097: h+aum las rdo rje sems dpa' bskyed /
NK069(tu)001:9098: sngags 'di brjod pas 'od du zhu nas nyi ma la rdo rje mtshan pa bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:9099: thugs kyi gsang ba bsam gyis mi khyab pa stong pa nyid dang /
NK069(tu)001:9100: thugs thams cad pa cir yang snang bar bsam la /
NK069(tu)001:9101: thugs rdo rje lta bu nga'am bdag yin zhes che ba'i nga rgyal bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:9102: sku gsung thugs byin brlab bo //
NK069(tu)001:9104: gnas gsum khyab 'jug yi ge las //
NK069(tu)001:9106: khams gsum byin rlabs 'od zer bsdus //
NK069(tu)001:9107: rang bzhin rdo rje gsum gnas pa //
NK069(tu)001:9108: rgyu gnyis tshul gyis rang snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9110: sarba ta tha ga ta ma h+aa a nu ra ga badz+ra swa b+h+aa ba ad ma ko&a ham /
NK069(tu)001:9111: zhes lte bar rin po che zur brgyad la yi ge tram las /
NK069(tu)001:9113: de 'od du zhu nas chags pa byang chub sems kyi mchod pa rin po che bsams la /
NK069(tu)001:9114: 'dod yon rnam pa lnga rgyan du rol lo //
NK069(tu)001:9116: lte ba rnam gnyis zla ba la /
NK069(tu)001:9117: sngo ljang yi ge s+w+aa h+aa nyid //
NK069(tu)001:9118: rjes mthun 'od las yon tan las //
NK069(tu)001:9119: yan lag rdzogs pa'i gzi brjid ldan //
NK069(tu)001:9121: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pu tsa badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa ad ma ko&a ham /
NK069(tu)001:9122: zhes gsang bar rdo rje rgya gram las /
NK069(tu)001:9124: sngags 'dis 'od du zhu nas yi ge har gyur /
NK069(tu)001:9125: de las zang zing gi mchod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:9126: ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa la sogs pa'i 'byung gzhir bsam par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:9128: zhes pa de skad brjod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:9129: +amo ma h+aa shu dz+ny+aa ta la sogs pa lnga brjod pas /
NK069(tu)001:9130: bdag ye shes lnga dang ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:9131: gzhan yang ye shes lngar byin gyis rlob nus pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:9132: sarba ta th+aa ga ta la sogs pa gsum brjod pas /
NK069(tu)001:9133: bdag sku gsung thugs rdo rje lta bur gyur nas /
NK069(tu)001:9134: gzhan yang sku gsung thugs su byin gyis rlob nus pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:9135: a nu ra ga la sogs pa gnyis kyi ni /
NK069(tu)001:9136: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la mchod pa stob
NK069(tu)001:9137: nus pa'i che ba dang ldan par gyur bar brjod
NK069(tu)001:9139: ces dbu'i gnas lngar ye shes lnga'i dbang bskur thim pas /
NK069(tu)001:9140: lus ye shes sgyu ma'i lus /
NK069(tu)001:9141: gsal la ma 'dres pa'i nam ka'i 'ja' lta bu'am /
NK069(tu)001:9142: ye shes lnga rang la thim par gyur /
NK069(tu)001:9144: ces sku gsung thugs la byin rlabs dang ldan pas ni /
NK069(tu)001:9145: sku gsung thugs la gzi brjid che zhing gsal bar gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:9147: zhes gsang ba'i gnas su mchod pa 'byung ba'i lha rin chen 'byung ldan dang /
NK069(tu)001:9148: mchod pa'i las thams cad byed pa'i lha don yod grub pa gnyis sgoms nas /
NK069(tu)001:9150: lus las byang chub sems kyis bde ba rgyas shing gang nas /
NK069(tu)001:9151: mchod pa'i tshogs rnams ma lus pa thams cad 'od 'phro zhing 'bar bar gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:9152: e ma'o ngo mtshar smad kyi chos //
NK069(tu)001:9153: zhes e ma ni ngam pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:9155: gzhan na myed pas ngo mtshar che ste /
NK069(tu)001:9156: gzhan gyi smad yang rang la dngos grub 'byung ba'i chos so //
NK069(tu)001:9157: chos de gang yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:9158: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung //
NK069(tu)001:9160: 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs rnam pa gnyis rdzogs pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:9161: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kun gyi don gyi gsung skye ba myed pa yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:9162: de ni gsung gi che ba phun sum tshogs par shes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:9163: sgra dang ming tshig kun las 'das //
NK069(tu)001:9164: zhes gsung gi ngo bo ni /
NK069(tu)001:9167: gsal ba'i tshig kun las 'das te /
NK069(tu)001:9169: btags pa'i ming du ma grub /
NK069(tu)001:9170: bsdud byed tshig 'das pa kho na'o //
NK069(tu)001:9171: de ni don gyi gsung gi mtshan nyid yin no //
NK069(tu)001:9172: sna tshogs sgra rnams gsal bar 'byung //
NK069(tu)001:9175: mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos sna tshogs yang brjod
NK069(tu)001:9176: bral de las so sor ma 'dres par gsal bar
NK069(tu)001:9177: 'byung / de ni gsung tshig gi gsung gi mtshan nyid yin no //
NK069(tu)001:9178: de ltar don gyi gsung dang tshig gi gsung gi
NK069(tu)001:9179: che ba mtshan nyid dang bcas pa la bstan pa'o
NK069(tu)001:9180: // gsung gcig dkyil 'khor yan lag ni //
NK069(tu)001:9181: zhes don gyi gsung skye ba myed pa gcig las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:9182: gsung gi dkyil 'khor yan lag bsam gyis mi khyab par 'byung ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:9183: bsam gyis mi khyab kun tu khyab //
NK069(tu)001:9184: ces 'jig rten gyi khams bsam gyi mi khyab pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:9185: gdul bya yang bsam gyis myi khyab pas /
NK069(tu)001:9186: de kun yongs la gsung gis khyab pas na kun du khyab ces bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:9187: sgra dang ming tshig so sor grags //
NK069(tu)001:9188: shes khyab pa'i tshul ji ltar khyab zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:9189: 'gro ba so so ji ltar mos pa bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:9190: rang gi sgra skad mdangs dang /
NK069(tu)001:9192: ming gis mtshon pa'i don rnams /
NK069(tu)001:9193: gdul bya so so dang mthun par grags so //
NK069(tu)001:9194: thams cad gsung gi phyag rgya'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:9195: ces ji ltar gsungs pa thams cad ni /
NK069(tu)001:9196: don gyi gsung las mi 'da' bas na /
NK069(tu)001:9197: 'khor 'das thams cad gsung gi phyag rgya chen por gnas te /
NK069(tu)001:9198: 'das pa don gyi gsung gi phyag rgya /
NK069(tu)001:9199: 'khor ba tshig gi gsung gi phyag rgya de bas na mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:9200: rgyud mchog rgyud chen d+r+wa ba las //
NK069(tu)001:9201: zhes rgyud thams cad kyi nang nas mchog du gyur pa'i rgyud chen po sgyu 'phrul dra ba las /
NK069(tu)001:9202: bde ldan gsung gi don byung ba //
NK069(tu)001:9203: zhes mya ngan las 'das pa'i bde ba dang ldan pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:9204: don gyi gsung 'di ltar yod do zhes ston cing 'byung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9205: thams cad pad mo'i ngang gyur na //
NK069(tu)001:9206: zhes gsung ji skad gsung pa thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:9207: skyon dang bral ba pad mo lta bu'i ngang du rtogs par gyur na /
NK069(tu)001:9208: grol thar lam dang 'khor ba'i sgra //
NK069(tu)001:9209: zhes 'khor ba na gnas pa'i sems can gyi sgra skad dang /
NK069(tu)001:9210: 'khor ba las grol zhing thar bar byed pa'i lam ste /
NK069(tu)001:9211: theg pa'i bye brag thams cad kyi sgra'o //
NK069(tu)001:9212: ji skad brjod kyang gsung mchog ste //
NK069(tu)001:9213: zhes mdor na brjod bya brjod byed kyi brjod pa ji skad brjod kyang /
NK069(tu)001:9214: skyon dang bral bas gsung mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:9215: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa ji skad brjod kyang /
NK069(tu)001:9216: don gyi gsung yon tan mchog dang ldan pa'i rang bzhin te /
NK069(tu)001:9217: theg pa mthon dman thams cad dang //
NK069(tu)001:9218: zhes sangs rgyas kyi theg pa la lta spyod mtho ba rdzogs chen man cad na /
NK069(tu)001:9219: lta spyod dma' ba nyan thos kyi theg pa yan cad de /
NK069(tu)001:9220: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la gnas pa'i theg pa thams cad dang /
NK069(tu)001:9221: log 'gro ma lus thams cad skad //
NK069(tu)001:9222: ces yang dag pa las log nas /
NK069(tu)001:9223: phyin ci log gi dbang du 'gro ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:9224: 'gro drug ma lus pa thams cad kyi skad dam /
NK069(tu)001:9225: sgra skad ci grag pa thams cad kyi skad yang /
NK069(tu)001:9226: byang chub rdo rje'i gsung du bsdus //
NK069(tu)001:9227: zhes de dag yang don gyi gsung du 'dus pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:9228: don gyi gsung du tha mi dad cing gcig pas na bsdus zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:9229: byang chub ni gsung sgrib pa dang bral ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9230: rdo rje ni don gyi gsung skye ba myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9231: bsdus ni gsung der thams cad 'dus pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:9233: bsdus nyid phyogs bcur rnam par grags //
NK069(tu)001:9234: zhes don ni gsung du bsdus shing /
NK069(tu)001:9235: don gyi gsung las ma g.yos pa nyid na /
NK069(tu)001:9236: phyogs bcu'i gsung rnams kyang de las 'byung bar grags so //
NK069(tu)001:9237: sgra nyid ma chags ngang du gsungs //
NK069(tu)001:9238: zhes sgra sna tshogs su grags pa'i dus nyid na /
NK069(tu)001:9239: sgra skad tha dad par snang yang /
NK069(tu)001:9240: so so'i sgra la ma chags ste /
NK069(tu)001:9241: ma chags ma gos pa don gyi ngang du gsungs so //
NK069(tu)001:9242: gsungs pa nyid na brjod du myed /
NK069(tu)001:9243: gsungs par snang tsam nyid na /
NK069(tu)001:9244: brjod par bya ba dang brjod par byed par yang myed do //
NK069(tu)001:9245: brjod myed de nyid sna tshogs sgra //
NK069(tu)001:9246: zhes brjod par bya ba dang byed pa myed pa nyid bstan pa'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:9247: sna tshogs pa'i sgra tha dad par 'byung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:9248: kun la grags shing so sor 'jal //
NK069(tu)001:9249: zhes sgra de 'gro ba rigs drug kun la grags shing /
NK069(tu)001:9250: don so so'i dbang po dang /
NK069(tu)001:9251: mthun par don so sor go ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9252: dper na de bzhin sbrid bsangs bzhin //
NK069(tu)001:9253: gsung gcig sgra yis thams cad do //
NK069(tu)001:9254: 'di ni gsung mchog rgyal po yin //
NK069(tu)001:9255: zhes rgya gar rdo rje'i gdan na /
NK069(tu)001:9256: khyim bdag ka ri na bya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:9257: nad g.yog pa u nam ka dang /
NK069(tu)001:9258: sman pa ha ri ka gsum yod pa las /
NK069(tu)001:9259: nad yun shin du ring bas /
NK069(tu)001:9262: da yong shi na rung snyam /
NK069(tu)001:9265: 'di shi na nga rang grogs gzhan la 'gro sa snyed snyam /
NK069(tu)001:9267: nor mi ster bar grags dus myed pas shi na rung snyam ste /
NK069(tu)001:9268: gsum blo tha dad du song ba las /
NK069(tu)001:9269: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kyis de'i sgor byon nas /
NK069(tu)001:9270: shangs kyi sbrid pa gcig bsangs pa las /
NK069(tu)001:9271: go stangs gsum du shar te /
NK069(tu)001:9272: go stangs gsum du shar de /
NK069(tu)001:9274: rin chen srog dang ma bral na //
NK069(tu)001:9275: sgyu ma'i nor rdzas brtsal du rnyed //
NK069(tu)001:9276: nad g.yog chung mas go bar /
NK069(tu)001:9277: snga rogs khyo la gzhung myed na /
NK069(tu)001:9278: phyi rogs rnyed pa yong mi 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:9281: sngon ma'i nad pa ma sos na //
NK069(tu)001:9284: der so so tha dad nas skyed gton nas 'bungs pas nad pa sos te /
NK069(tu)001:9286: dpe de bzhin du don gyi gsung sbrid pa lta bu gcig las /
NK069(tu)001:9287: tshig gi gsung theg pa tha dad par go bar snang ba 'di ni /
NK069(tu)001:9288: gsung rnams kyi nang nas mchog gam /
NK069(tu)001:9289: rgyal po lta bu yin no //
NK069(tu)001:9290: theg pa mtho dam na bsam yas kyang //
NK069(tu)001:9291: zhes theg pa mtho ba a ti man cad nas /
NK069(tu)001:9292: dma' ba nyan thos sde snod yan cad gdul bya
NK069(tu)001:9293: so so la snang ba'i chos kyi sgo mo bsam
NK069(tu)001:9295: de bzhin nyid las ma gsungs te //
NK069(tu)001:9296: zhes de bzhin nyid chos kyi dbyings dang /
NK069(tu)001:9297: dbyings rtogs pa'i ye shes dang /
NK069(tu)001:9298: dbyings ye shes rtogs pa'i sangs rgyas chos kyi skus ye ma gsungs te /
NK069(tu)001:9299: gdul bya'i thabs su so sor thos //
NK069(tu)001:9302: so so ji ltar dga' ba bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:9304: dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu la rtog pa myed par dgos 'dod 'byung ba lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:9305: yang dag par gsung gi gnas tshul bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:9306: ji ltar gsung rabs kun brjod kyang //
NK069(tu)001:9307: zhes ji ltar dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kyis gsungs
NK069(tu)001:9308: pa'i gsung rabs chos kyi sde snod rnams brjod par
NK069(tu)001:9309: snang yang / de bzhin nyid kyis gsungs pa myed //
NK069(tu)001:9310: ces de bzhin nyid spros pa dang bral ba des gsungs pa myed do //
NK069(tu)001:9311: yi ge myed dang rig pa'i gsung //
NK069(tu)001:9312: zhes yi ge myed pa kho na don gyi gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:9313: don gyi gsung kho na rig pa'i gsung ro /
NK069(tu)001:9315: rig pa'i gsung brjod bral du rtogs pa la yi ge myed pas so //
NK069(tu)001:9316: ljags kyi rtse mor ma phyung yang //
NK069(tu)001:9317: zhes rig pa'i gsung yi ge myed pa de ni /
NK069(tu)001:9318: ljags sha'i dbang po lce la yang ma phyung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:9320: kun rdzob kyi tshig dang yi ger bshad du ma stub pas so //
NK069(tu)001:9322: gsung de'i byin rlabs 'gro ba sems can la snang tshul ni /
NK069(tu)001:9323: thugs rje gsung gi byin brlabs kyis //
NK069(tu)001:9324: zhes 'o na 'di ltar snang ba'i chos 'di kun ci yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:9325: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sngon byang chub kyi lam du zhugs tsam na /
NK069(tu)001:9326: thugs rjes skyes pa'i smon lam btab pas /
NK069(tu)001:9327: de'i byin rlabs kyis byung ba de /
NK069(tu)001:9328: 'gro don sna tshogs so sor gsal //
NK069(tu)001:9329: zhes 'gro ba rigs drug gi don du /
NK069(tu)001:9330: mi mthun pa la mthun par bshad pas /
NK069(tu)001:9331: so so rang rang gi sems kyi yul du gsal bar thos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9332: thugs rig pa nyid spros pa dang bral ba des /
NK069(tu)001:9333: thams cad du khyab nas rang rang gi don so sor gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:9334: gsal nyid gsung gi rdo rje mchog /
NK069(tu)001:9335: ces gsal tsam nyid na skye ba myed brjod pa nyid na brjod du myed /
NK069(tu)001:9336: gsung de ni skye ba myed pa rdo rje dang 'dra ba'i phyir na mchog yin no //
NK069(tu)001:9337: don dam pa las ma g.yos par kun rdzob 'gro ba snang ba'i dpe bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:9338: de bzhin gsung gi 'gro don rnams //
NK069(tu)001:9339: zhes gong du bstan pa de bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:9340: don gyi gsung gis ma gsung bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:9341: tshig gi gsung gis 'gro ba'i don rnams /
NK069(tu)001:9342: 'gro ba ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin du mdzad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:9343: de bzhin ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK069(tu)001:9345: de bzhin rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi ngang ngam /
NK069(tu)001:9346: rdul tsam yang ma g.yos shing mi rtog yang /
NK069(tu)001:9347: tshig gi gsung 'byung ba'i dpe ni /
NK069(tu)001:9348: dper na brag cha'i sgra bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:9349: zhes brag chen po'i mdun du /
NK069(tu)001:9352: rtas mtsher ba la sogs pa kun /
NK069(tu)001:9353: rkyen ji skad bos pa skad brag chas zer yang /
NK069(tu)001:9354: brag gis sgras pa myed pa dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:9355: sangs rgyas kyi zhal nas ma gsungs yang /
NK069(tu)001:9356: sems can so so'i blo sno ltul dang /
NK069(tu)001:9359: theg pa so sor brda sprad pa de /
NK069(tu)001:9360: sangs rgyas kyis gsungs par rtsi /
NK069(tu)001:9362: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:9363: rtogs par dka' bas na gasnga ba /
NK069(tu)001:9365: ma nor bas de kho na nyida /
NK069(tu)001:9369: gsung gi dkyila 'akhara ji snyed yod pa thams cad gsung sngar bsdusa pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:9370: gsang sngags kyi le'u ste bdun pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9372: // gsung gi nus pa rang la gnas par bya ba'i phyir gsang sngags kyi le'u ste bdun pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9373: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis //
NK069(tu)001:9374: zhes gsung gi le'u bstan pa de nas thugs kyi le'u ston pas so //
NK069(tu)001:9375: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rang bzhin kun tu bzang po des sam /
NK069(tu)001:9376: rigs lnga la sogs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis so //
NK069(tu)001:9377: yan lag thams cad dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub
NK069(tu)001:9378: par byin gyis barloba pa zhes bya ba 'di ched
NK069(tu)001:9379: du brjod do // zhes dbu de bzhin gshegs pa /
NK069(tu)001:9380: lag pa g.yas pa mi skyod pa /
NK069(tu)001:9382: rkang pa g.yas pa snang ba mtha' yas /
NK069(tu)001:9383: rkang pa g.yon pa don yod grub pa /
NK069(tu)001:9384: rang rang rigs kyi sems dpa' khro bo dang bcas par ye nas lhun grub tu gnas pa de /
NK069(tu)001:9385: shes rab kyis rtogs par byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:9386: ting nge 'dzin gyis rtse gcig tu byin gyis barloba pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9387: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa bar mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:9388: zhes sgyu 'phrul ni thabs de yab /
NK069(tu)001:9389: dra ba ni 'brel pa ste shes rab yum /
NK069(tu)001:9390: thabs dang shes rab gnyis myed du mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par /
NK069(tu)001:9391: rang rig pa'i shes rab dri ma myed pas rtogs par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:9392: rtogs pa'i don de ting nge 'dzin gyis kyang de ltar bsgom par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:9393: thams cad byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK069(tu)001:9397: dbang po yul la 'jug pa thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:9398: bla na myed pa'i byang chub /
NK069(tu)001:9399: yon tan mchog ldan gyi thabs kyi phyag rgyar ma gyur ba gang yang myed do //
NK069(tu)001:9400: yang na de ltar rtogs pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:9401: sgo gsum gyi spyod pa spyi spyod thams cad bla
NK069(tu)001:9402: na myed pa'i byang chub mchog ldan du grub pa'i
NK069(tu)001:9403: phyag rgya'o // gsang ba de nyid nges pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:9404: zhes lhun gyis grub pa'i phyag rgya don de ni /
NK069(tu)001:9405: rang bzhin gyis rtogs par dka' bas gsang ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:9406: snod du ma gyur ba la mi bstan pas gsang ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:9407: de kho na nyid nges pa'i don mthar phyin pas nges don lhun grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:9409: zhes lhun gyis grub pa'i phyag rgya de ni /
NK069(tu)001:9410: phyag rgya thams cad 'byung ba'i rgyur gyur pas phyag rgya'i snying po zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:9411: dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyang /
NK069(tu)001:9412: lhun gyis grub pa'i phyag rgya'i rang bzhin las 'da' bar mi mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9413: de ltar rtogs na rnal 'byor pa la yang dam tshig las mi 'da' bar dngos grub gter ro //
NK069(tu)001:9414: dang mum gnyis rtse sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:9415: zhes lag pa g.yas kyi 'dzub mo'i dang /
NK069(tu)001:9416: g.yon gyi gung mo'i mum gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:9417: sor mo'i rtse mo sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:9418: mi skyod nyi ma'i dkyil yi ge //
NK069(tu)001:9419: zhes lag na g.yas mi skyod pa'i rang bzhin sor
NK069(tu)001:9420: mo lnga'i rtse la nyi ma'i dal lnga'i steng du
NK069(tu)001:9425: the 'ong la ha lnga sgom par bya /
NK069(tu)001:9426: rin chen zla ba'i dkyil yi ge //
NK069(tu)001:9427: zhes lag pa g.yon pa rin chen 'byung ldan gyi
NK069(tu)001:9428: rang bzhin sor mo lnga la zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK069(tu)001:9429: gyi steng du / gung mo la mam /
NK069(tu)001:9433: the 'ong la tam lnga sgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:9434: phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu thabs lam du bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:9435: bdag myi skyod par bsgoms pa'i gsang ba'i dbang po rdo rje rtse lnga par bsgoms la /
NK069(tu)001:9437: phyogs bzhir +amo swa a ha bzhi bsam /
NK069(tu)001:9438: de yang gsang ba'i gnas na nyi zla thig ler gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9439: yum dbyings phyug mar bsgoms pa'i b+ha ga rin po che'i par bu'i nang du /
NK069(tu)001:9441: phyogs bzhir lam mam pam tam bzhi bsam /
NK069(tu)001:9442: nyi zla byang chub sems kyi thig le yi ger gnas pa nyid bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9443: de yang lam gyi thig le nyid bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9444: de yang yab kyi thig le nyid ni thabs kyi rang bzhin du gnas /
NK069(tu)001:9445: yum gyi thig le ni shes rab kyi rang bzhin du gnas pas /
NK069(tu)001:9446: de gnyis rtse sprad pa ni lnga gnyis zung du snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9447: de las phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub 'byung ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:9450: mi rtog pa gsum du 'byung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:9451: de yang gsang ba sgyu 'phrul gyi bshad rgyud thal ba nas /
NK069(tu)001:9452: myi skyod rdo rje rtse lnga la //
NK069(tu)001:9453: nyi ma'i thig le yi ge dngos //
NK069(tu)001:9454: rin chen par bu'i nyi zla la //
NK069(tu)001:9455: zla ba'i thig le yi ge nyid //
NK069(tu)001:9456: thig le thabs shes lnga gnyis rnams //
NK069(tu)001:9457: sprad pa'i dus las rang snang ba'i //
NK069(tu)001:9458: phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub 'byung //
NK069(tu)001:9460: lnga gnyis zung du spros pa las //
NK069(tu)001:9461: zhes lag pa g.yas pa yab kyi dpa' bo 'bru lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:9462: g.yon pa yum gyi dpa' mo 'bru lnga gnyis zung du sbyar nas /
NK069(tu)001:9464: tshur 'dus pa las dngos grub blang bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:9465: sbyar bas phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK069(tu)001:9466: zhes rtags ni phyag rgya thal mo sbyar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:9467: don ni dbyings ye shes gnyis myed de /
NK069(tu)001:9469: thabs shes rab gnyis sbyar ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:9471: 'bru brgyad snol nas rtse prad pas //
NK069(tu)001:9472: zhes h+aum dang lam gnyis sbyar /
NK069(tu)001:9475: ha dang pam gnyis sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:9476: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK069(tu)001:9477: zhes phyag rgya de ni dus gsum gyi rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor zhing /
NK069(tu)001:9478: don dbyings ye shes lnga dang dbyer myi phyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9479: bde ba chen po 'byin pa'i rgya //
NK069(tu)001:9480: zhes don ye shes lnga'i rtags kyi phyag rgya de cings pas /
NK069(tu)001:9481: yab yum bde ba gsal ba myi rtog pa dbyer myed pa de /
NK069(tu)001:9482: 'byin pa'i phyag rgya ni de lta bur ces pa la bya //
NK069(tu)001:9483: bshad rgyud thal ba ltar na /
NK069(tu)001:9484: yab ye shes kyi mkha' la +amo /
NK069(tu)001:9485: yum dbyings kyi b+ha ga la mum /
NK069(tu)001:9486: yab kyi rdo rje'i rwa bzhi'i yi ge dang /
NK069(tu)001:9487: yum gyi b+ha ga pad ma bzhi'i yi ge snol nas /
NK069(tu)001:9488: yab yum mnyam par sbyar ba'i thig le 'dres shing sprad pa las /
NK069(tu)001:9489: rgyal ba'i ye shes bde ba chen po myong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9491: dbyings dang ye shes bdag po nyid //
NK069(tu)001:9492: dang mum du rang bzhin gnas //
NK069(tu)001:9493: rwa dang 'dab ma'i thig le rnams //
NK069(tu)001:9494: rang bzhin gnas kyis snol mar 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:9495: rab tu 'dres par gyur pa las //
NK069(tu)001:9496: rgyal ba'i ye shes bde chen po //
NK069(tu)001:9497: myong phyir thob pa zhes su gsungs //
NK069(tu)001:9498: dang mum gnyis rtse sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:9499: ces pa la gtar kas gags gsal na /
NK069(tu)001:9500: 'dir yab yum gyi yig 'bru go log go zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:9502: yab lnga'i yi ge ye shes yin la /
NK069(tu)001:9503: khyad par du +amo ye shes lnga ldan no //
NK069(tu)001:9504: yum lnga'i ye ge dbyings yin la /
NK069(tu)001:9505: khyad par du mum dbyings so //
NK069(tu)001:9506: yab kyi rdo rje la bsam /
NK069(tu)001:9507: mum yum gyi pad ma la bsam /
NK069(tu)001:9509: rwa bzhi dang pad ma snol mar 'gyur bas /
NK069(tu)001:9511: rdo rje sems dpa' phyag brgyad /
NK069(tu)001:9512: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK069(tu)001:9513: zhes swa a ha'i yig 'bru bzhi sbas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:9515: gung mo thugs khar gyen du bkan de /
NK069(tu)001:9516: de ni phyag g.yas pa'i phyag rgya'o //
NK069(tu)001:9517: h+aum sgreng rtse mor rdo rje 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:9518: zhes gung mo'i rtse mo la yi ge h+aum gyen du sgreng la /
NK069(tu)001:9519: de'i rtse mo la rdo rje rtse lnga pa 'od 'bar ba bsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:9520: zla btul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing //
NK069(tu)001:9521: zhes g.yon pa'i zla ba'i yig 'bru rnams btul ba ni rdo rje khu tshur ro //
NK069(tu)001:9522: yig 'bru lag thil du sbas nas dril bu bsil lo //
NK069(tu)001:9523: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la bstan //
NK069(tu)001:9524: zhes dril bu thogs pas yum la 'khril ba'i tshul du bla la bzhag pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:9525: chos yum la 'khril bar bstan no //
NK069(tu)001:9527: spyir phyag rgya so sor bca' ba la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:9528: 'byung ba'i rgyu rdo rje thal mo /
NK069(tu)001:9529: bca' ba'i gnas lta zur g.yas g.yon no //
NK069(tu)001:9531: sgrol ba'i don chos nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:9532: de la sgyur ba'i gnas la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:9535: thabs shes rab gnyis ldan no //
NK069(tu)001:9537: bcing ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya ni /
NK069(tu)001:9538: gnod sbyin khu tshur thugs khar bkan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9539: bsam pa chos kyi phyag rgya ni /
NK069(tu)001:9540: 'dzub mo'i rtse mo la sogs par /
NK069(tu)001:9543: byed pa las kyi phyag rgya ni /
NK069(tu)001:9544: lag pa g.yon pa dril bu bsil zhing /
NK069(tu)001:9546: sku phyag rgya chen po ni /
NK069(tu)001:9547: yab yum 'khril ba'i tshul du bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9549: thugs kar bkan pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:9550: yig 'bru dang phyag mtshan bsgom pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:9551: zla ba'i steng du yig 'bru tul nas dril bu bsil ba ni rin po che'i rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:9555: thugs khar bkan pa rnam snang gi rigs /
NK069(tu)001:9556: dril bu bsil rdo rje'i rigs /
NK069(tu)001:9559: mdangs kyis lta ba pad ma'i rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:9560: thabs dang shes rab gnyis ldan ni /
NK069(tu)001:9561: yab thabs ma 'gags pa'i tshul ni /
NK069(tu)001:9562: phyag g.yas pa gnod sbyin gyi khu tshur byas pa las /
NK069(tu)001:9563: gung mo sgreng ba'i rgyab rang gi thugs khar bstan la /
NK069(tu)001:9564: de'i rtse mo'i h+aum nyid rdo rje rtse lnga 'od 'bar ba bsgom pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:9565: bcing ba dang bsam pa gnyis ka dam tshig gi phyag rgya'o //
NK069(tu)001:9566: yum shes rab stong pa'i tshul ni /
NK069(tu)001:9567: yon tan zla ba'i yi ge khu tshur du byas nas dril bu bsil zhing /
NK069(tu)001:9568: yum la 'khyud pa'i tshul byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:9569: rang gi sku la bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:9570: bcing ba dang bsam pa gnyis ka las kyi phyag rgya ste /
NK069(tu)001:9571: des thabs dang shes rab 'khril sbyor du byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9573: dga' ba bzhi'i thig le gcig tu 'dus pa ni 'bru bzhi sbas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9574: rlung gis gyen du drangs pa ni thugs kar bkan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9575: rtsa zhal nas rdo rje'i lam du bde ba rgyas pa ni h+aum sgreng rtse mo'o //
NK069(tu)001:9576: bde ba rgyas pa ni 'bar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9577: yab kyi khu ba yum gyi raka tas sgribs pa ni zla tul 'bru sbas so //
NK069(tu)001:9578: yum gyi pad ma bde bas rgyas pa ni dril bsil lo //
NK069(tu)001:9579: thig le phyed byung du skyod pa ni 'khril ba'i tshul lo //
NK069(tu)001:9580: thig le b+ha gar mi 'gro bar rlung gis zin pa ni chos la bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9582: thig le bzhi bsdus gcig tu 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:9583: rlung gis bsdus pa bkan par gnas //
NK069(tu)001:9584: zhal gyi lam dag gang rgyas pa //
NK069(tu)001:9585: phyag rgya 'bar ba zhes pa'i sgra //
NK069(tu)001:9586: zla ba nyi mas sgribs pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:9587: chu skyes rab tu rgyas pa ni //
NK069(tu)001:9588: dril ba'i sgra dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9589: phyed 'byung tshul gyis gang skyod pa //
NK069(tu)001:9590: tung ba myed phyir bstan par bshad //
NK069(tu)001:9592: yab lnga'i phyag rgya thabs lam du sbyar nas bshad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9594: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK069(tu)001:9595: zhes g.yon gyi lam mamm pammm tamm bzhi lag tu sbas nas /
NK069(tu)001:9596: lag pa'i rgyab snying khar bstan /
NK069(tu)001:9598: mum bsgreng rtse mo dril bsil 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:9599: zhes gung mo sgreng ba'i rtse mo la mum las dril bu bsam /
NK069(tu)001:9600: lag pas kyang dril bu bsil lo //
NK069(tu)001:9602: zhes lag pa g.yas kyi nyi ma dal la /
NK069(tu)001:9603: yab kyi dpa' bo 'bru lnga po de /
NK069(tu)001:9605: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis lta //
NK069(tu)001:9606: zhes yum gyi lus sems yab la btud nas /
NK069(tu)001:9607: zhal 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis lta ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9609: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK069(tu)001:9610: zhes yab kyi a h+aum s+w+aa h+aa bzhi phyag thil du sbas nas /
NK069(tu)001:9611: lag pa'i rgyab snying khar bstan la /
NK069(tu)001:9612: lag pa'i mdun gyi thil phyir la bstan pa ni kan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9614: zhes 'dzub mo gyen la sgreng ba'i rtse mo la +amo las 'khor lo 'od 'bar bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:9615: zla btul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing //
NK069(tu)001:9616: zhes lag pa g.yon pa zla ba'i yig 'bru nang du btul la sbas te dril bu bsil zhing /
NK069(tu)001:9617: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la bstan //
NK069(tu)001:9618: zhes yab yum 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos yum la phyag rgya 'khril bar bstan /
NK069(tu)001:9620: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK069(tu)001:9621: zhes mum lam pam tam bzhi lag pa g.yon pa
NK069(tu)001:9622: la yod pa de sbas nas rang gi thugs kar
NK069(tu)001:9623: phyir kan no // lam sgreng rtse mo dril bsil 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:9624: zhes 'dzub mo'i rtse mo lam las dril bu bsam la /
NK069(tu)001:9625: dril bu nyid kyang bsil zhing bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:9627: zhes lag pa g.yas kyi nyi ma'i dpa' bo 'bru lnga yab la 'khril zhing /
NK069(tu)001:9628: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis lta //
NK069(tu)001:9629: zhes yab la lus sems btud de zhal 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis yab la lta'o //
NK069(tu)001:9631: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK069(tu)001:9632: zhes +aahh+aum h+aa bzhi g.yas na yod pa nang du sbas /
NK069(tu)001:9633: khu tshur thugs khar bkan no //
NK069(tu)001:9634: swa rtse 'bar ba rin po che //
NK069(tu)001:9635: zhes srin lag gi rtse mo'i s+w+aa las rin po che 'od 'bar ba bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:9636: zla ltul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing //
NK069(tu)001:9637: zhes lag pa g.yon pa'i zla ba'i yig 'bru btul zhing sbas la dril bu bsil zhing /
NK069(tu)001:9638: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la bstan //
NK069(tu)001:9639: zhes yab yum 'khril ba'i tshul gyis so //
NK069(tu)001:9641: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK069(tu)001:9642: zhes g.yon gyi mum lam pam tam bzhi khu tshur nang du sbas nas /
NK069(tu)001:9644: mam sgreng rtse mo dril bsil 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:9645: zhes srin lag gi rtse mo gyen du sgreng ba la mam las dril bu 'bar bar bsil /
NK069(tu)001:9647: zhes lag pa g.yas pa nyi ma'i dpa' bo 'bru lnga yab la 'khril /
NK069(tu)001:9648: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis lta //
NK069(tu)001:9649: zhes dbu btud de zhal 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis /
NK069(tu)001:9652: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK069(tu)001:9653: zhes h+aum swa ha bzhi g.yas pa'i khu tshur nang du sbas nas snying khar bstan /
NK069(tu)001:9654: am sgreng rtse mor pad mor 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:9655: zhes the'u chung gyen du sgreg ba'i rtse mor ang las pad ma 'od 'bar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9656: zla btul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing //
NK069(tu)001:9657: zhes lag pa g.yon pa zla ba'i yig 'bru rdzus nas dril bu bsil zhing /
NK069(tu)001:9658: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la bstan //
NK069(tu)001:9659: zhes yum la 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos yum la bstan //
NK069(tu)001:9661: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK069(tu)001:9662: zhes lag pa g.yon pa'i mum lam mam tam bzhi khu tshur nang du sbas nas snying khar bstan /
NK069(tu)001:9663: pam sgreng rtse mor dril bsil 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:9664: zhes the'u chung sgreng ba'i rtse mor pam las dril bu bsil zhing /
NK069(tu)001:9666: zhes g.yas nyi ma la dpa' bo 'bru lnga /
NK069(tu)001:9668: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis lta //
NK069(tu)001:9669: zhes dbu btud de zhal 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis spyan yab kyi zhal du lta'o //
NK069(tu)001:9671: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK069(tu)001:9672: zhes g.yas pa'i am h+aum swa bzhi khu tshur nang du sbas nas thugs kar phyir bkan /
NK069(tu)001:9673: ha sgring rtse mor ral gri 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:9674: zhes the 'ong gyen du sgreng ba'i rtse mor ha las ral gri 'od 'bar ba bsam /
NK069(tu)001:9675: zla btul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing //
NK069(tu)001:9676: zhes g.yon pa zla ba'i yig 'bru btul zhing /
NK069(tu)001:9677: sbas la dril bu bsil zhing /
NK069(tu)001:9678: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la bstan //
NK069(tu)001:9679: zhes yab yum 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos yum la bstan /
NK069(tu)001:9681: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK069(tu)001:9682: zhes lag pa g.yon pa'i mum lam pam sbas nas thugs khar bkan /
NK069(tu)001:9683: tam sgreng rtse mo dril bsil zhing //
NK069(tu)001:9684: zhes the 'ong gyen du sgreng ba'i rtse mor ltam las dril bu bsams la bsil /
NK069(tu)001:9686: zhes g.yas g.yas nyi ma'i 'bru lngas las yab la 'khril zhing /
NK069(tu)001:9687: bstud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyi lta //
NK069(tu)001:9688: zhes dbu bstud de zhal 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis yab kyi zhal 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis lta'o //
NK069(tu)001:9689: yum gyi phyag rgya thabs lam du na /
NK069(tu)001:9690: thig le bzhi pad ma gcig la 'dus pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:9692: rlung gis zlog pa bkan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9693: rdo rje pad ma 'byor ba dril bsil lo //
NK069(tu)001:9694: bde bas rgyas pa'i las su 'khril ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9695: rtag chad mtha' gnyis bde bas non pa ni 'dzum mdangs kyis lta ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9697: zla ba'i thig le rjes mthun par //
NK069(tu)001:9698: dril bu phyed kyis 'byor dgyes pa //
NK069(tu)001:9699: mtha' gnyis mnon pa'i byang chub sems //
NK069(tu)001:9700: phyag rgya chen po 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:9702: 'di rnams kyis yum rnams phyag rgya bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:9704: uta dpal klu shing la sogs mtshan //
NK069(tu)001:9705: zhes uta dpal ni me tog uta pa la mthing ka ste /
NK069(tu)001:9707: klu shing ni shing bu lo 'dabs dang bcas pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:9711: chos kyi 'khor lo rin chen snye la snyag pa'i tshig go //
NK069(tu)001:9712: yang na g.yon na dril bu bsnams pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9713: rin chen myu gu ral gri 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:9714: zhes sa'i snying po rin po che'i myu gu'o //
NK069(tu)001:9715: nam mkha'i snying po ral gri 'od 'bar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9716: pad ma dkar po rdo rje 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:9717: zhes spyan ras gzigs pad ma dkar po'o //
NK069(tu)001:9718: phyag na rdo rje ni rdo rje rtse lnga pa 'od 'bar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9719: chos kyi 'khor lo rin chen snye //
NK069(tu)001:9720: zhes sgrib pa sel ba ni chos kyi 'khor lo brtsibs brgyad do //
NK069(tu)001:9721: kun tu bzang po rin po che'i snye ma bsnams pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9723: gzugs mdzes rin chen 'phreng ba dang //
NK069(tu)001:9724: zhes sgeg mo ni gzugs mdzes pa 'byung bar rang gsal ba'i me long ngo //
NK069(tu)001:9725: me long ni myi brjed pa'i gzungs thob pa'i rin po che'i 'phreng ba 'dren ni /
NK069(tu)001:9726: pi wang gar mkhan mchog nyid de //
NK069(tu)001:9727: zhes g+hir ti ni glu len pas pi wang ngam /
NK069(tu)001:9729: nir ti ni gar byed pas phyag rgya sgyur ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9730: 'jig rten gyi gar mkhan nam glu mkhan las khyad par du 'phags pas na mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:9731: me tog 'phreng dang spos mchog ma //
NK069(tu)001:9732: zhes dbyar me tog gi lha mo ni /
NK069(tu)001:9733: phyag na me tog gi 'phreng ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9734: dpyid 'das pa'i lha mo phyag na gdugs spos so //
NK069(tu)001:9735: mar me byug pa la sogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:9736: zhes ston ma byon pa'i lha mo phyag na mar me'o //
NK069(tu)001:9737: dgun 'byung bar ma nges dpa'i lha mo phyag na dri chab bsnams pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9739: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan /
NK069(tu)001:9740: ces pa gong ma bzhin du 'dod pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9741: sems dpa' yab yum 'khril tshul ni /
NK069(tu)001:9742: las la 'khril zhing chos la bstan //
NK069(tu)001:9743: zhes yum las yab la 'khril zhing /
NK069(tu)001:9744: yab chos yum la bstan no //
NK069(tu)001:9746: zhes yab kyi dbu rnams yum la 'byo zhing /
NK069(tu)001:9747: yum gyi lus ngag yid dam /
NK069(tu)001:9748: zhal yab la 'dud pa'i tshul lo //
NK069(tu)001:9749: gong gi phyag rgya chen po bzhin //
NK069(tu)001:9750: gnyis myed dbyings kyi ngang du 'khril //
NK069(tu)001:9751: zhes gong ma rigs lnga yab yum bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:9753: the 'ong bzhag la gzhan ma la sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:9754: 'bru gsum sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK069(tu)001:9755: k+shi sgreng rtse mo rin chen 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:9756: zla btul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing //
NK069(tu)001:9757: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la bstan //
NK069(tu)001:9758: 'bru gsum sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK069(tu)001:9759: h'u sgreng rtse mo me long 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:9761: bstud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis ltar //
NK069(tu)001:9764: sgo bzhi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni //
NK069(tu)001:9765: zhes dkyil 'khor gyi sgo bzhi na gnas pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:9766: sgo ba khro bo bzhi'i phyag rgya bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:9767: n+re mgo gdengs dang rdo rje gnon //
NK069(tu)001:9768: zhes gshin rje gshed po g.yas mi mgo'i dbug pa gdengs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:9769: stobs po che g.yas kyi rdo rjes g.yon gyi thod pa gnon pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:9770: thod sbrul chen po mnon pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:9771: zhes rta mgrin g.yon thod pa /
NK069(tu)001:9772: g.yas sbrul chen zhags pas g.yon gyi thod pa mnon pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:9773: rdo rje rgya gram las kyis mnon //
NK069(tu)001:9774: zhes rdo rje rgya gram ni /
NK069(tu)001:9775: las kyi rigs bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i phyag rgya te /
NK069(tu)001:9776: g.yon gyi thod pa mnon pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9778: lcags kyu zhags pa spo ta ho //
NK069(tu)001:9779: zhes shar gyi sgo ma lcags kyu /
NK069(tu)001:9781: nub kyi sgo ma spo ta de lcags sgrog /
NK069(tu)001:9782: byang gi sgo ma ho zhes pa dgyes pa ste dril bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:9783: sgo ba yab yum 'khril tshul ni /
NK069(tu)001:9784: sgo bzhir gnas pa de dag kyang //
NK069(tu)001:9785: dkyil 'khor gyi sgo bazhara gansa pa'i sgo skyong yab yum de daga kyanga /
NK069(tu)001:9787: zhes yum yab la 'dud pa'i tshul dang /
NK069(tu)001:9788: yab yum la 'khril ba'i tshul ni /
NK069(tu)001:9789: gong ma rigs lngar bshad pa bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:9790: 'bru gsum sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK069(tu)001:9791: h+aum sgreng rtse mo myi mgo 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:9792: zla btul 'bru sbas dril bsil zhing //
NK069(tu)001:9793: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la bstan //
NK069(tu)001:9794: 'bru gsum sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK069(tu)001:9795: dza sgreng rtse mo lcags kyu 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:9796: ces par sbyar ram yang na ting nge 'dzin gyis bsgom par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:9797: thub drug phyag rgya sna tshogs te //
NK069(tu)001:9798: zhes thub drug ni gdul bya dang mthun par don mdzad pas /
NK069(tu)001:9799: phyag rgya yang nges par rtag tu myed do sna tshogs par snang ste /
NK069(tu)001:9800: mdor bsdus phyag rgya drug yin no //
NK069(tu)001:9801: zhes gdul bya mdor bsdus na rigs drug yod pas /
NK069(tu)001:9802: de 'dul ba'i phyir phyag mtshan yang drug yin no //
NK069(tu)001:9803: de yang lha skyo nges che bas pi wang gis 'dul /
NK069(tu)001:9804: lha ma yin 'thab rtsod mang bas go mtshon gyis 'dul /
NK069(tu)001:9805: mi 'dzin chags che bas sreg par gyis 'dul /
NK069(tu)001:9806: dud 'gro blo gros blun pas cho kyi spo tis 'dul /
NK069(tu)001:9807: yi dwags ltogs pas rin po che'i sgrom bus 'dul /
NK069(tu)001:9808: dmyal ba tsha grang gis nyes pas me chus 'dul lo //
NK069(tu)001:9809: gtar kas gags gsal ba la /
NK069(tu)001:9810: thub pa drug la yum myed pas phyag rgya bcing rgyu myed do zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:9813: yum ni dmyigs myed chos kyi dbyings /
NK069(tu)001:9815: yum ni dmyigs myed chos kyi dbyings //
NK069(tu)001:9816: zhes thub pa drug sprul pa'i sku 'dod chags spangs
NK069(tu)001:9817: pa'i tshul gyis sangs rgya bar byed pa'i lam ston
NK069(tu)001:9820: don gyi yum chos kyi dbyings dmyigs pa myed pa dang 'du 'bral myed par bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:9821: kun bzang mnyam bzhag ye shes 'phro //
NK069(tu)001:9822: zhes kun tu bzang po ni /
NK069(tu)001:9823: chos sna tshogs pa ye shes las mi zhan pa'i rtags su phyag rgya mnyam bzhag go //
NK069(tu)001:9824: don ye shes lnga nyid sna tshogs par 'phro bas na /
NK069(tu)001:9825: mnyam pa'i phyag rgya las sor mo phral te /
NK069(tu)001:9827: yum 'gyur mnyam rdzogs pad mo'i dkyil //
NK069(tu)001:9828: zhes yum du 'gyur pa kun tu bzang mo ni /
NK069(tu)001:9829: chos kyi dbyings spros pa myed pas phyag rgya mnyam bzhag /
NK069(tu)001:9830: zhabs rkang thil gnyis sbyar te pad ma'i dkyil bkrung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:9831: gzhan yang phyag rgya sna tshogs te //
NK069(tu)001:9832: zhes gzhan yang kun bzang yab yum gyi phyag rgya sna tshogs pa yin de /
NK069(tu)001:9833: ci'i phyir zhe na dbyings ye shes las thams cad 'byung ba'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:9836: yang na de bzhin gshegs nyid dam //
NK069(tu)001:9837: zhes yang na kun bzang yab yum gnyis ni /
NK069(tu)001:9838: de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga nyid dang mthun par yin te /
NK069(tu)001:9839: phyag rgya gang yang kun bzang yab yum las ma 'das pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:9840: yang na rdo rje thal mo nyid //
NK069(tu)001:9841: ces yang na lag pa thal mo sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:9842: don dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su myed pa kho na mtshon pas /
NK069(tu)001:9843: rdo rje'i thal mo khog stong nyid du bca' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9845: kun tu bzang po ji ltar yang bcar stub pas /
NK069(tu)001:9846: phyag rgya bzhi dang 'gal lo zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:9848: kun tu bzang po mnyam bzhag ni dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK069(tu)001:9849: sor mo las ye shes kyi 'od lnga 'phro ba chos kyi phyag rgya /
NK069(tu)001:9850: de ltar shes pa las kyi phyag rgya /
NK069(tu)001:9851: skur gsal ba phyag rgya chen po ste /
NK069(tu)001:9855: phyag rgya chen po'i tshogs mchog ni //
NK069(tu)001:9858: gnyis su myed pas na chen po'o //
NK069(tu)001:9859: de lta bu'i phyag rgya chen po'i tshogs ni /
NK069(tu)001:9860: yon tan mchog dang ldan pas so //
NK069(tu)001:9861: thabs dang shes rab ldan 'byor na //
NK069(tu)001:9862: zhes thabs ye shes te yab /
NK069(tu)001:9863: shes rab chos dbyings te yum /
NK069(tu)001:9865: rtags phyag rgya dang mtshan ma /
NK069(tu)001:9866: mtshan ma dang mtshan ma myed pa shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin du 'byor na /
NK069(tu)001:9867: ma skyod ma bsgul thams cad kun //
NK069(tu)001:9868: zhes lag pas bcings sgrol gyi phyag rgya ma skyod /
NK069(tu)001:9869: byed pa dang sdom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:9870: 'ching ba'i phyag rgya ma bsgul yang /
NK069(tu)001:9872: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas //
NK069(tu)001:9873: zhes phyag rgya chen po dbyer myed pa'i ngang du gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:9875: phyag rgya mching ba ni thabs dang shes rab gnyis myed du 'byor bar 'dod pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:9876: yan lag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ldan //
NK069(tu)001:9877: zhes lus kyi yan lag lnga po ni lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su gnas la /
NK069(tu)001:9878: rtog pa brang sprod du bsgom pas na ldan no //
NK069(tu)001:9879: de nyid yan lag spro bdag te //
NK069(tu)001:9880: de ltar ldan pa de nyid /
NK069(tu)001:9881: yan lag spros pa'i bdag nyid yin te /
NK069(tu)001:9882: thugs ye shes sems dpa' re re dang ldan par spro ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:9884: zhes lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyang /
NK069(tu)001:9885: sku gsung thugs gsum du 'phro bar 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:9886: de ltar ldan pa'i gtso mchog gi //
NK069(tu)001:9887: de ltar rtogs pa'i shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin du ldan pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:9888: rnal 'byor pa ni gtso bo'am mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:9889: yang na gtso bo yab yum la ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor stong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:9890: phyag rgya spros pa la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:9892: sangs rgyas stong gi dal lo //
NK069(tu)001:9893: nyi khri bzhi stong du rtsi na lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:9897: bsam gyis myi khyab pa'i lha dang /
NK069(tu)001:9899: rtsa ba'i lha yab yum gnyis so //
NK069(tu)001:9901: rtsa ba'i lha la bsam pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:9902: yan lag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis ldan ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:9904: yab la bcu bdun gyi steng du thub pa drug mnan la bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:9906: de nyid yan lag spro bdag ste //
NK069(tu)001:9908: thabs kyi lha bzhi bcu'i thugs kar /
NK069(tu)001:9909: ye shes sems dpa' bzhi bcu bsgom ste /
NK069(tu)001:9911: bsam gyi mi khyab pa'i lha ni /
NK069(tu)001:9912: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su ma 'phros 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:9914: thabs kyi lha bzhi po de re re la yang /
NK069(tu)001:9915: sku gsung thugs kyi lha gsum gsum bsgoms pas /
NK069(tu)001:9917: gong gi brgya bcu ste nyi bargya'o //
NK069(tu)001:9918: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor stong ni /
NK069(tu)001:9919: de ltar ldan pa'i gtso mchog gis //
NK069(tu)001:9921: gong gi nyi brgya po de re re la yang /
NK069(tu)001:9922: dbu rgyan lha lnga lnga bsams pas /
NK069(tu)001:9923: nyi brgya tshar lnga la stong gi dal lo //
NK069(tu)001:9924: de'i steng du rigs lnga yab yum la stong tshe lnga ste drug yod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:9925: rgyal ba rgyal mchog de bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:9927: phyi nang gi sems dpa' yab yum zung brgyad la stong tshe brgyad de bcu bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:9928: thub pa drug la stong tsho drug de nyi shu /
NK069(tu)001:9929: sgo ba yab yum zung bzhi la stong tsho bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:9931: de bas na bcu gnyis drug gi 'od 'phro 'bar /
NK069(tu)001:9933: sangs rgyas stong gi dal ni /
NK069(tu)001:9934: shes rab kyi lha ye shes sems dpa' /
NK069(tu)001:9936: dbu rgyan nyi brgya mi sgom par /
NK069(tu)001:9937: de'i dod por thabs shes rab kyi lha rgya bcu sgom /
NK069(tu)001:9938: thabs kyi lha la sku gsung thugs kyi lha brgya nyi shu ste /
NK069(tu)001:9939: nyi brgya sgoms pas stong gi dal lo //
NK069(tu)001:9940: rgyal ba rgyal mchog de bzhin du //
NK069(tu)001:9941: zhes rgyal ba ni sangs rgyas rigs bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:9942: rgyal mchog ni kun tu bzang po /
NK069(tu)001:9944: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum la sgom pa bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:9948: sgo ba bzhi ste bcu gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:9950: sgo ma bzhi ste bcu gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:9953: re re la yang sangs rgyas stong gi dal bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:9954: de la sogs te bsam mi khyab //
NK069(tu)001:9955: ces phyogs bcu gzhal yas khang du sgom /
NK069(tu)001:9956: nyi zla gza' skar rgyan du bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:9957: bde gshegs kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa bsgom ste /
NK069(tu)001:9958: bsam yas lhun grub la slob pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:9960: phyogs bcu dus bzhi bsam yas su //
NK069(tu)001:9963: grangs blos bsam yas gnas su /
NK069(tu)001:9964: 'dul ba'i don rnams so sor bston //
NK069(tu)001:9965: zhes gdul bya 'gro drug 'dul ba'i don du /
NK069(tu)001:9966: phyag rgya rnams yang so sor ston no //
NK069(tu)001:9967: theg pa mthon sman thams cad dang //
NK069(tu)001:9968: zhes theg pa mtho ba rdzogs chen nas /
NK069(tu)001:9970: thams cad sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:9971: phyin ci log rnams bsam yas dang //
NK069(tu)001:9972: zhes lta ba phyin ci log pa mu stegs dang /
NK069(tu)001:9973: spyod pa phyin ci log pa sdig can dang /
NK069(tu)001:9974: bsam pa phyin ci log pa lha srin la sogs pa blos bsam yas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:9975: zhi khro'i tshogs chen thams cad la //
NK069(tu)001:9976: zhes gdul bya cha phra ba zhi bas 'dul ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:9977: gdul bya cha rags pa khro bos 'dul bar 'os pa'i tshogs thams cad la'o //
NK069(tu)001:9980: khro bo sgo ba la zer ram /
NK069(tu)001:9983: phyag rgya bcing rgyu ma bstan par /
NK069(tu)001:9984: 'gro don mdzad tshul yong bar mi rigs /
NK069(tu)001:9985: khro bo sgo ba la zer na /
NK069(tu)001:9986: de zhi khro myen zer ro //
NK069(tu)001:9987: 'di gnas 'gyur gyi khro bo la zer te /
NK069(tu)001:9988: phyag rgya bcing rgyu ma byung yang /
NK069(tu)001:9990: cir yang snang bar mdzad pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:9991: so sor mthun byas kun tu ston //
NK069(tu)001:9992: zhes phyin ci log gis 'dul ba la /
NK069(tu)001:9993: dang po de dang chos mthun par byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:9995: theg pas 'dul ba la theg pa dgu bshad de /
NK069(tu)001:9996: phyag rgya'i rnam grangs la nges pa myed pas /
NK069(tu)001:9997: 'gro ba so so'i bsam pa dang mthun par ston no //
NK069(tu)001:9999: dper na gar mkhan nyid 'dra bar //
NK069(tu)001:10000: zhes dper na gar mkhan la phyogs gcig tu nges pa myed pa bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:10001: de nyid dang 'dra bar sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa dang 'dul thabs grangs mang la rgya che'o //
NK069(tu)001:10002: lus la ma bkod sna tshogs ston //
NK069(tu)001:10003: zhes gar mkhan gyi spyod lam sna tshogs par snang yang /
NK069(tu)001:10004: lus la rang rgyud du bkod pa myed de /
NK069(tu)001:10005: 'gro ba dang dgyes su re nas ston la /
NK069(tu)001:10006: sangs rgyas kyi chos sna tshogs ston yang /
NK069(tu)001:10007: chos nyid kyi bshis la grub pa myed par /
NK069(tu)001:10008: 'gro bas rtogs su re nas ston no //
NK069(tu)001:10010: mdor na phyag rgya thams cad ni //
NK069(tu)001:10011: zhes mdor bsdus nas bstan na /
NK069(tu)001:10012: dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK069(tu)001:10015: sku phyag rgya chen po la sogs pa thams cad ni /
NK069(tu)001:10016: brjod pa dang bral bar gnas te /
NK069(tu)001:10018: 'di zhes cig tu brjod du myed //
NK069(tu)001:10019: ces phyag rgya ni 'di kho na yin no //
NK069(tu)001:10023: mos pa tha dad par snang la /
NK069(tu)001:10024: tha dad 'dul ba'i gnyen por shar ba'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:10026: gnyis dang gsum du rnam par 'phro //
NK069(tu)001:10027: zhes phyag rgya skur snang ba'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:10030: dbu gsum la sogs pa'i rnam par snang /
NK069(tu)001:10031: yang zhal cig phyag gnyis sam /
NK069(tu)001:10033: skyod dang spro ba de bzhin nyid //
NK069(tu)001:10034: ces lus kyis cing zhing skyod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:10035: de las sangs rgyas stong gi dal du spro ba yang /
NK069(tu)001:10036: gong ma de bzhin du snang ba nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:10037: dbyer myed du bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:10038: mdor na skyod bsgul thams cad kun //
NK069(tu)001:10039: zhes phyag rgya gnyis pa myed pa mdor sdu na /
NK069(tu)001:10042: phyag rgya mching ba thams cad kun /
NK069(tu)001:10043: phyag rgya chen po'i ngang du gnas //
NK069(tu)001:10044: zhes phyag rgya chen po ni spros pa mtha' dag
NK069(tu)001:10045: dang bral ba chos kyi sku dri ma myed par
NK069(tu)001:10046: de dang / de'i ngang du phyag rgya thams cad gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10047: gnas nyid myi gnas gnas pa'ang myed //
NK069(tu)001:10048: ces spros dang bral bar gnas pa nyid na /
NK069(tu)001:10049: rol pa sna tshogs su snang ba nyid na /
NK069(tu)001:10051: de tsam gyi mtshan ma la yang gnas pa myed do //
NK069(tu)001:10052: de skad dag mchog nyid kyis bshad //
NK069(tu)001:10053: ces de skad sangs rgyas gang gis gsungs na /
NK069(tu)001:10054: chos thams cad rnam par dag par thugs su chud pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:10055: sangs rgyas kun tu bzang po nyid kyis gsungs so //
NK069(tu)001:10056: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las //
NK069(tu)001:10057: gasnga ba rtogs par dka' ba /
NK069(tu)001:10059: de kho na nyida mi slu ba /
NK069(tu)001:10062: yan lag dkyil 'khor du byin gyis brlabs nas //
NK069(tu)001:10063: lus kyi rtog tshogs yan lag thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:10064: lha'i dkyila 'khora du byin gyisa brlabs nasa /
NK069(tu)001:10065: phyag rgya spros pa'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10067: // sangs rgyas stong gi dala phyag rgya dang /
NK069(tu)001:10069: stong tsho cig tu spros pa'i le'u ste brgyad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10071: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:10073: rdo rje gsang ba'i dam tshig bkod pa la snyoms par zhugs nas /
NK069(tu)001:10075: ched du 'gro ba'i don gyi spyir /
NK069(tu)001:10078: le'u brgyad pa thugs phyag rgya'i le'u bstan pa'i rjes de nas /
NK069(tu)001:10079: rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor ston pas so //
NK069(tu)001:10080: de bzhin gshegs pa ni rigs lnga la sogs pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:10081: ston pa rgyal ba drug pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10083: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i longs spyod rnam gnyis la dgyes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10084: gnyis su myed pas chen po'o //
NK069(tu)001:10085: rdo rje ni rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor sku gsung rdo rje dang 'dra bar ston pas rdo rje /
NK069(tu)001:10086: gsang ba ni dam nyams pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:10088: dam ma 'dres pa la mi ston pas na gsang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:10090: sgom par bya ba las mi 'da' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:10091: bskod pa ni bsgom pa dang rdul tshon tha dad pa ltar snang bas so //
NK069(tu)001:10092: snyoms par zhugs pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa ting nge 'dzin las bzhengs bzhugs mi mnga' yang /
NK069(tu)001:10093: phyi rabs kyi rnal 'byor pa rnams rdul tshon gyi dal tsom na /
NK069(tu)001:10094: ting nge la snyoms par zhugs shig pa'i phyir gdams ngag tu bzhag pa'i tshul yin no //
NK069(tu)001:10095: dgos pa dang ldan pas bya na /
NK069(tu)001:10096: shin tu 'phra ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK069(tu)001:10097: ces dkyil 'khor byed pa'i rnal 'byor pa de yang /
NK069(tu)001:10098: sngon du rdo rje phra mo'i ting nge 'dzin las su rung zhing /
NK069(tu)001:10099: sems la dbang thob pas bya dgos pa'i phyir na shin du phra ba'i ces so //
NK069(tu)001:10100: rdo rje phra mo'i ting nge 'dzin sgom pa las
NK069(tu)001:10101: mi 'da' bas na dam tshig gi mchog yin no
NK069(tu)001:10102: // phra mo'i ting nge 'dzin gyis sems sbyangs nas las su rung dgos pas mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:10104: phyag rgya chen po'i phyag mthil du //
NK069(tu)001:10105: zhes slob dpon lha'i sku phyag rgya chen por sgoms pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:10106: phyag mnyam bzhag du snol ba'i mthil du lha bzhi
NK069(tu)001:10107: bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor sgom zhing bri ba
NK069(tu)001:10108: ni / dal gang du bya zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:10109: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dam pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:10110: zhes thugs rdo rje sems dpas gtso byas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:10111: dkyil 'khor rnams kyi nang nas dam pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:10112: snying po lta bu yin pas ste //
NK069(tu)001:10114: sor ni bzhi'i tshad du bya //
NK069(tu)001:10115: zhes tshad ni sor bzhir bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:10116: de'i dgos pa ni yum gyi mkha' mtshon pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:10117: rgyu ni shing tsan dan nam /
NK069(tu)001:10119: bri thabs 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud dang bcas pa tshon gyis bri bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:10121: yum gyi b+ha ga nam mkha'i stong pa ni phyag rgya chen po /
NK069(tu)001:10123: de la rten nas bde ba skye bas thugs kyi dal /
NK069(tu)001:10125: der yab kyi byang sems 'jug pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10127: phyag rgya chen po nam mkha'i khams //
NK069(tu)001:10128: sor bzhi tshad du yang dag gnas //
NK069(tu)001:10129: bde ba'i ye shes thugs dkyil 'khor //
NK069(tu)001:10130: kha dog dbyibs dang ldan par bya //
NK069(tu)001:10131: thabs kyi rab gnas cho gar bstan //
NK069(tu)001:10133: phra mo la sbyangs na gsang dbang skur du rung bar bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:10134: 'di rnams snol mtshams 'phen sdud du bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:10138: rang bzhin dag par bya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:10146: rang bzhin dag par bya ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:10147: phung po lnga'i rang bzhin rigs kyi yab lngar dag nas 'bras bu gang thob pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:10148: sku lnga'i sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:10151: dang po ngo bo lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:10158: 'byung ba lnga yul lngar dag nas /
NK069(tu)001:10160: 'phrin las bzhi lhun gyis grub pa dang lnga thob //
NK069(tu)001:10162: zhes rin po che lnga la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:10170: 'byung ba ye shes lngar dag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10172: zhing khams rnam par dag pa lnga thob pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10174: snying po lnga la yang gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:10177: shing gi snying po bu ram /
NK069(tu)001:10178: me tog gi snying po sbrang rtsi /
NK069(tu)001:10180: rtsi thog gi snying po mar ro //
NK069(tu)001:10181: dag pa ni rnam shes brgyad dag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10183: thugs ye shes 'bras bu thob pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10185: zhes sman lnga la yang gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:10187: ha sa de ba shu dag dang /
NK069(tu)001:10188: bri ha ti dbang po lag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:10190: kan rta ka re se ba dkar po dang /
NK069(tu)001:10191: a sbra rtsi ta chu srin sder mo'o //
NK069(tu)001:10192: dag pa dbang po lnga dag nas thob pa gsung lnga thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:10193: bdud rtsi lnga ni rab snyams la //
NK069(tu)001:10194: zhes bdud rtsi ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:10196: pad ma raka ta byang chub sems dmar po dang /
NK069(tu)001:10197: ga bur byang chub sems dkar po dang /
NK069(tu)001:10199: bla rtsi te dri chen dang /
NK069(tu)001:10201: dag pa khams bdud rtsi lnga dag nas /
NK069(tu)001:10202: thob pa rigs lnga thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:10203: sum cu po rnams cha mnyam la srab 'thug ran par byug pa bya /
NK069(tu)001:10205: 'di la man ngag gi thig le gzung ste /
NK069(tu)001:10206: rig pas thig ni gdab par bya //
NK069(tu)001:10207: zhes sor bzhi'am 'dzub gang gi dal la /
NK069(tu)001:10208: sa thig dang rnam thig gdab du myed de /
NK069(tu)001:10210: yang na rig pa byang chub sems kyi don rtogs pa dang ldan pas thig gdab bo //
NK069(tu)001:10211: 'dis man ngag thig gi tshig zin no //
NK069(tu)001:10212: lte ba rtsibs dang ldan pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:10213: zhes zhi ba rgyas pa la tshom bu lnga'i dkyil 'khor du byed na /
NK069(tu)001:10214: 'khor lo dbus kyi lte ba la /
NK069(tu)001:10215: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dang ldan par bri //
NK069(tu)001:10216: tshon phyogs dang mthun par tang bar bya /
NK069(tu)001:10217: rtsibs bzhi 'khor lo mu khyud bcas //
NK069(tu)001:10218: zhes phyogs bzhir 'khor lor rtsibs bzhi la /
NK069(tu)001:10219: rtsibs re re la yang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa re bri /
NK069(tu)001:10222: zhing khams rnam par dag pa lnga thob pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10224: snying po lnga la yang gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:10227: shing gi snying po bu ram /
NK069(tu)001:10228: me tog gi snying po sbrang rtsi /
NK069(tu)001:10230: rtsi thog gi snying po mar ro //
NK069(tu)001:10231: dag pa ni rnam shes brgyad dag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10233: thugs ye shes 'bras bu thob pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10235: zhes sman lnga la yang gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:10237: ha sa de ba shu dag dang /
NK069(tu)001:10238: bri ha ti dbang po lag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:10240: kan rta ka ri se ba dkar po dang /
NK069(tu)001:10241: a sbra rtsi ta chu srin sder mo'o //
NK069(tu)001:10242: dag pa dbang po lnga dag nas thob pa gsung lnga thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:10243: bdud rtsi lnga ni rab snyams la //
NK069(tu)001:10244: zhes bdud rtsi ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:10246: pad ma raka ta byang chub sems dmar po dang /
NK069(tu)001:10247: ga bur byang chub sems dkar po dang /
NK069(tu)001:10249: bla rtsi te dri chen dang /
NK069(tu)001:10251: dag pa khams bdud rtsi lnga dag nas /
NK069(tu)001:10252: thob pa rigs lnga thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:10253: sum bcu po rnams cha mnyam la srab 'thug ran par byug pa bya /
NK069(tu)001:10255: 'di la man ngag thig gzung ste /
NK069(tu)001:10256: rig pas thig ni gdab par bya //
NK069(tu)001:10257: zhes sor bzhi'am 'dzub gang gi dal la /
NK069(tu)001:10258: sa thig dang rnam thig gdab du myed de /
NK069(tu)001:10260: yang na rig pa byang chub sems kyi don rtogs pa dang ldan pas thig gdab bo //
NK069(tu)001:10261: 'dis man ngag thig gi tshig zin no //
NK069(tu)001:10262: lte ba rtsibs dang ldan pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:10263: zhes zhi ba rgyas pa la tshom bu lnga'i dkyil 'khor du byed na /
NK069(tu)001:10264: 'khor lo dbus kyi lte ba la /
NK069(tu)001:10265: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi dang ldan par bri /
NK069(tu)001:10266: tshon phyogs dang mthun par tang bar bya /
NK069(tu)001:10267: rtsibs bzhi 'khor lo mu khyud bcas //
NK069(tu)001:10268: zhes phyogs bzhir 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la /
NK069(tu)001:10269: rtsibs re re la yang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa re bri /
NK069(tu)001:10270: 'khor lo thams cad la phyi nang gi mu khyud rdo rje'i 'phreng bas ra bar bskor bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:10271: gru chad bzhi dang gru bzhi dang //
NK069(tu)001:10272: bar khyams sgo khyud ldan par bya //
NK069(tu)001:10273: zhes phyi rol gru chad bzhi ser po /
NK069(tu)001:10274: gru bzhi lha rnams ni phyogs dang mthun /
NK069(tu)001:10278: sgo khyud pan tsa ra ga'i rtsig pa dang ldan pa rta babs so //
NK069(tu)001:10281: shin du phra bar bris pa kho na /
NK069(tu)001:10282: phra mo'i dkyil 'khor du gyur pas phra mo'i dal bri ba yin no //
NK069(tu)001:10288: sen mo zlum po tsam gyi nyi ma'i dal dang /
NK069(tu)001:10290: rgya gar gyi sran ma tsa na ka ni /
NK069(tu)001:10291: bod kyi sran ma 'bring po'o tshad tsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:10292: de tsam pa'i pad+mo'i gdan bri /
NK069(tu)001:10293: de'i steng du de tsam pa'i sku yang bri'o //
NK069(tu)001:10294: nyungs 'bru gsung tsam gyi yi ge la //
NK069(tu)001:10296: nyi zla pad ma'i steng du /
NK069(tu)001:10297: ka kha la sogs pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sam /
NK069(tu)001:10299: tshad nyungs dkar gyi 'bru tsam pa bri /
NK069(tu)001:10302: zhes thugs phyag mtshan gyi dgod na /
NK069(tu)001:10303: nyi zla pad ma'i gdan la /
NK069(tu)001:10304: rdo rje dang 'khor lo la sogs pa rnams /
NK069(tu)001:10305: che chung gi tshad til gyi 'bru tsam pa bri bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:10306: 'di yang snol mtshams 'phen bsdud du bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:10307: bcos bu'i ras ni sna tshogs dang //
NK069(tu)001:10309: ras kha dog sna tshogs su bcos pa la /
NK069(tu)001:10310: mchod pa'i yo byad sna tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:10314: gdung g.yogs la sogs pa byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10315: rgyan 'phreng stung dang bro bas bskor //
NK069(tu)001:10316: zhes dal gyi rgyan mda' dang /
NK069(tu)001:10319: mtshon thag ra ba'i 'phreng ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:10320: stung ba'i rnam pa ro drug la sogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:10322: de dag ni zang zing rdzas kyi mchod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10323: glu tshig bro gar rol mo yis //
NK069(tu)001:10325: gsang sngags zab mo'i tshig tu ldan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:10326: rkang pas kyang bdud bzhi 'dul ba'i bro dang /
NK069(tu)001:10327: lag pas rdo rje'i gar dang /
NK069(tu)001:10328: de lta bu'i rol mo'i dngos sam /
NK069(tu)001:10329: nan tan du ting nge 'dzin gyis mchod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:10330: sprin phung tshogs kyis rab tu mchod //
NK069(tu)001:10331: ces mchod pa de dag yang /
NK069(tu)001:10332: nan tan gyi ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK069(tu)001:10337: dper na nam mkha' stong pa la sprin 'du ba ltar /
NK069(tu)001:10338: sems dang ba'i ting nge 'dzin las /
NK069(tu)001:10339: nam mkha'i sprin phung tsam pa sprul la /
NK069(tu)001:10340: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa rnams la /
NK069(tu)001:10341: rab tu dang ba'i sems kyis mchod pa bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:10342: yum dang 'jo ma sems ma yis //
NK069(tu)001:10343: zhes sbyor ba'i mchod pa byed na /
NK069(tu)001:10344: yum ni rang gi gzungs ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:10345: rigs kyi yum lngar byin gyis brlabs la /
NK069(tu)001:10348: 'jol sgeg dang ldan pa'i lha mo sgeg mo la sogs par byin gyis rlabs la mchod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:10350: mchod pa'i lha mo spos ma la sogs par byin rlabs la mchod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10352: gzungs ma yum du byin gyis rlabs pa yis mchod /
NK069(tu)001:10353: sras mo 'jo mar byin gyis rlab pa /
NK069(tu)001:10354: slob ma sems mar byin gyis rlob bo //
NK069(tu)001:10355: ji ltar 'dod pa'i las bzhin mchod //
NK069(tu)001:10356: ces slob dpon ji ltar dgyes par mchod par ram /
NK069(tu)001:10357: slob ma dngos grub ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin mchod pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:10358: mched bzhi'i rnams las rnam pa bzhi'i khyad par 'dod pa ltar /
NK069(tu)001:10360: mchod pa'i don la gsol ba 'debs pa'i phyir mchod pa yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:10361: dbyibs dang kha dog mtshan ldan 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:10363: dbyings ni zhi ba lnga zlum po /
NK069(tu)001:10366: drag po la gru gsum mo /
NK069(tu)001:10374: rgyas pa la rin po che /
NK069(tu)001:10376: drag po la rdo rje sdengs po 'od kha dog sna tshogs 'bar bas mtshan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10377: zhal du gyur pa'i me bos la //
NK069(tu)001:10378: zhes sreg rdzas zhal du 'bul bar gyur pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:10380: me bos ni me lha spyan drangs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10381: me lha dmar po ra skyes zhon pa /
NK069(tu)001:10382: g+hud+he dang ril ba spyi blugs bsnams pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10384: me lha la bya ba'i rim pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10385: me lha'i lto bar lha bskyed la mchod pa ni ye shes lha la bya ba'i rim pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10386: bza' btung bro ba'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK069(tu)001:10388: zhi ba la bza' ba mar /
NK069(tu)001:10396: drag po la sha dang khrag /
NK069(tu)001:10397: gzhan ro mchog dang ldan pa sna tshogs kyis mchod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10398: yang na zhi ba la 'bras dang zho mar ro //
NK069(tu)001:10401: dbang la tsha dang kyur ba /
NK069(tu)001:10402: drag po la skye tshe lan tsha dug go //
NK069(tu)001:10403: las bzhi'i mchod pas rab tu mchod //
NK069(tu)001:10404: ces lnga dro zhi ba'i las bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:10406: snga dro 'og ma rgyas pa'i las bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:10408: phyi dro dang po dbang gi las te /
NK069(tu)001:10410: gong mo drag po'i las bya te /
NK069(tu)001:10411: khros pa'i sems kyis mchod do //
NK069(tu)001:10412: de rnams pa cho ga dang dbang bskur dang /
NK069(tu)001:10414: mchod pa dus su rab tu mchod par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:10415: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor de bzhin te //
NK069(tu)001:10417: zhes dkyil 'khor sor bzhi pa la khro dal bri /
NK069(tu)001:10430: 'di rnams ni gzhung 'khrugs myed gyi gnas de /
NK069(tu)001:10431: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams rnam par dag pa yang yi ge b+h+r+aum las skyed do //
NK069(tu)001:10433: zhes teg na 'phar mnyam byed pa /
NK069(tu)001:10434: mnan na nem mnyam byed pas na mnyen 'jam mo //
NK069(tu)001:10436: nang du rtogs pa'i ye shes zag myed kyi bde
NK069(tu)001:10437: ba khyad par can skye ba'i gnas su gyur pa
NK069(tu)001:10438: yi ge b+h+r+aum las bskyed de spros la mchod /
NK069(tu)001:10439: snod ma dag pa rnams sbyang bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:10440: sna tshogs rin po che'i gzhi //
NK069(tu)001:10441: zhes rgyu rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i sa gzhi la /
NK069(tu)001:10442: mdzes par bris shing spras pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:10443: zhes rin po che'i mig mngas ris su bris pa /
NK069(tu)001:10444: skabs skabs su rin po che'i 'bur gyis spras pa /
NK069(tu)001:10446: zhes ri thams cad yi ge tram las dgos 'dod
NK069(tu)001:10447: kun yid bzhin du 'byung ba'i rin po che'i phung
NK069(tu)001:10449: dbyibs legs rdzing bu ro mchog bsil //
NK069(tu)001:10450: zhes chu thams cad yi ge kham las dbyibs legs
NK069(tu)001:10451: pa'i rdzing bu ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa mngar
NK069(tu)001:10452: ba bsil ba nad 'du ba rnam bzhi la byams
NK069(tu)001:10453: par sprul lo // rin chen khang pa sna tshogs dang //
NK069(tu)001:10455: yi ge las rin po che sna tshogs las grub
NK069(tu)001:10456: pa'i gzhal yas khang rgyan sna tshogs kyis rgyan par
NK069(tu)001:10458: rgyan dang dpag bsam ljon pa'i tshal //
NK069(tu)001:10459: zhes khang pa la rin po che'i rgyan dang /
NK069(tu)001:10460: shing thams cad yi ge swa las /
NK069(tu)001:10461: dpag bsam gyi ljon shing gi tshal du gyur par byin gyis brlab bo //
NK069(tu)001:10462: glu dbyangs tshigs su gcad pa'i sgra //
NK069(tu)001:10463: zhes 'jig rten gyi glu bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:10464: bka' bo che gdung 'byam sngags glu dang /
NK069(tu)001:10465: lha mo lugs kyi glu nyan thos kyi glu dbyangs dang /
NK069(tu)001:10466: srid pa bde sbyor bstan chos kyi glu dang /
NK069(tu)001:10467: mos pa tha dad rang dag'i glu dang rnams sam /
NK069(tu)001:10468: sgra sgrag pa thams cad hri las byin rlab bo //
NK069(tu)001:10469: bla re rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs //
NK069(tu)001:10470: zhes gos thams cad +amo las steng bla re /
NK069(tu)001:10476: ba dan du byin brlabs so //
NK069(tu)001:10477: do shal dpung rgyan se mo do //
NK069(tu)001:10478: zhes rgyan thams cad rin po che'i do shal dang /
NK069(tu)001:10482: phyag dub zhabs dub du byin brlab par bya /
NK069(tu)001:10483: bza' dang btung ba'i mchog rnams dang //
NK069(tu)001:10484: zhes bza' ba thams cad yi ge +amo la ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa'i kha zas dang /
NK069(tu)001:10485: bdud rtsi chen po zos pa dang 'thungs pa tsam gyis bde ba skye bar byin rlab bo //
NK069(tu)001:10486: rang la mdzes par rgyan pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:10487: zhes rnal 'byor pa rang nyid la chas dang rgyan gyis mdzes par rgyan pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:10488: rang lhar bsgoms pa'i lha dang lha mo las spros pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:10489: lha dang lha mo rdul rnyed kyi //
NK069(tu)001:10490: zhes lha dang lha mo rdul phra rab snyed dang grangs mnyam pa sprul /
NK069(tu)001:10491: yang na rang lus der sprul lo //
NK069(tu)001:10492: bro gar la sogs bsam yas kyis //
NK069(tu)001:10493: zhes de yang rkang pas bro byed /
NK069(tu)001:10495: zhal du sgra sgrogs pa bsam yas pa /
NK069(tu)001:10496: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bskang nas //
NK069(tu)001:10497: zhes phyogs bcu'i nam mkha'i khams sam /
NK069(tu)001:10498: khams gsum thams cad mchod pas bskang nas /
NK069(tu)001:10500: zhes sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa yod tshad kun la dbul lo //
NK069(tu)001:10501: bskal ldan gsal ba'i khyad par gyis //
NK069(tu)001:10502: zhes mchod pa de rnams gang gis 'bul na /
NK069(tu)001:10503: shes rab rnam par gsum gyis blo'i rgyud spyangs shing /
NK069(tu)001:10504: las dang skal bar ldan pa /
NK069(tu)001:10505: gnyis su myed pa'i byang chub sems rtogs pa'i shes rab gsal ba /
NK069(tu)001:10506: sngon gyi rgyal ba la lhag pa'i bya ba byas pa /
NK069(tu)001:10507: las 'phro dang skal bar ldan pa de'i ting nge 'dzin gyi khyad par gyis zhe'o //
NK069(tu)001:10508: rims kyis yang na cig char du //
NK069(tu)001:10509: zhes gong gi mchod pa'i khyad par de rnams ni /
NK069(tu)001:10510: ting nge 'dzin gsal na dus gcig la cig char du dbul /
NK069(tu)001:10514: dal bus bstan par byas shing dbul lo //
NK069(tu)001:10515: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK069(tu)001:10516: zhes tshad kyi dngos nas ni /
NK069(tu)001:10517: chos kyi dbyings kyis gar khyab par mchod pas khyab par sbyor ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:10519: dang po yang chos kyi dbyings nas byung la /
NK069(tu)001:10520: tha ma yang chos kyi dbyings su thim par sbyor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:10522: mchod pa dngos por bzung ba ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:10523: chos kyi dbyings mtshan ma myed par rtogs par mnyam par sbyor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:10524: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen por bsgom //
NK069(tu)001:10525: zhes mchod gnas kyi yul lha dang /
NK069(tu)001:10527: mchod pa 'bul mkhan gyi rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid dang gsum /
NK069(tu)001:10528: dbyer myed pa lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya chen por bsgom par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:10529: gsal ldan ma'am byin brlabs la //
NK069(tu)001:10530: zhes yum ni sngon gyi rgyal ba la lhag pa'i bya ba byas pa /
NK069(tu)001:10531: las 'phro dang skal bar ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:10532: shes rab rnam pa gsum gyis rig pa'i blo sbyangs nas /
NK069(tu)001:10533: mnyam nyid gnyis su myed pa'i byang chub sems rtogs pa gsal na byin gyis rlab mi dgos /
NK069(tu)001:10534: de lta bu ma yin na /
NK069(tu)001:10535: gang yang rung ba'i rigs kyi yum lngar byin rlabs la /
NK069(tu)001:10536: stong gsum nyungs 'brur bzhugs tshul du //
NK069(tu)001:10537: zhes sbyor ba'i mchod pa'i drod tshad dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:10538: stong gsum tsam gyi chen po nyungs 'bru tsam gyi chung du bzhugs pa /
NK069(tu)001:10539: stong gsum tsam gyi chen po 'gengs pa'i ting nge dang ldan pas bya ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:10541: dper na stong gsum gyi chen po nyungs 'bru tsam gyi chung ngu ru bzhugs pa'i tshul du /
NK069(tu)001:10542: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas rnams rnal 'byor gyi sems bzhugs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10543: dbyings nas dkyil 'khor spyan drangs mchod //
NK069(tu)001:10544: ces chos kyi dbyings kyis gar khyab par /
NK069(tu)001:10545: bde bar gshegs pa sangs rgyas kyi dal gyis khyab la /
NK069(tu)001:10546: dal de dag yum gyi gsang ba'i mkha' la spyan drangs shing mchod de /
NK069(tu)001:10547: yum gyi mkha' chos kyi dbyings su /
NK069(tu)001:10548: yab kyi byang chub sems thugs ye shes kyi dal spros la /
NK069(tu)001:10549: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba mchod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10550: mnyes nas grub pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK069(tu)001:10552: phyogs bcu'i rgyal ba thams cad mnyes nas /
NK069(tu)001:10553: byin gyis rlob cing mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub ter /
NK069(tu)001:10554: dngos grub rtsal ba las mi 'da' bas na dam
NK069(tu)001:10555: tshig de las thams cad 'grub pas na mchog yin
NK069(tu)001:10556: no // bdag nyid chen po mchod pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:10557: zhes chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid gnyis su myed
NK069(tu)001:10558: par rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor gyi bdag nyid chen pos
NK069(tu)001:10559: sbyor ba'i mchod pa phul ba yis /
NK069(tu)001:10560: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus mnyes //
NK069(tu)001:10561: zhes phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dal ma lus pa thams cad yang mnyes la /
NK069(tu)001:10562: srid gsum 'gro ba thams cad la //
NK069(tu)001:10563: srida pa gsuma gyi 'gro ba ma lus pa thams cada la yang /
NK069(tu)001:10564: dga' ba chen pos khyab par 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:10565: zhes rang gi ngo bo la ltos pa'am lhan skyes
NK069(tu)001:10566: chen pos dga' ba bcu drug gis thams cad la
NK069(tu)001:10567: khyab pa'o // dga' bas khyab tu btub pa'i dpe ni /
NK069(tu)001:10568: ji ltar bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pa la /
NK069(tu)001:10569: spre'u gyi rgyal po ha lu ma d+has /
NK069(tu)001:10571: bcom ldan 'das kyis gsol ba'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:10573: sems can thams cad kyis kyang sbrang rtsi'i ro dus cig tu myong bar 'gyur la /
NK069(tu)001:10574: de ltar myong bar 'gyur ba'i gzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:10575: de bzhin gshegs pas chos thams cad kyi mnyam pa
NK069(tu)001:10576: nyid thugs su chud pas de ltar grub pa yin
NK069(tu)001:10577: no // de bzhin du rnal 'byor pas sgyu 'phrul
NK069(tu)001:10578: dra ba'i don gnyis myed du rtogs shing bstan pa
NK069(tu)001:10579: no // thob pa yis / sbyor ba byang chub sems kyi mchod pa byas na /
NK069(tu)001:10580: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa ni mnyes la /
NK069(tu)001:10581: srid pa gsum gyi sems can thams cad la /
NK069(tu)001:10582: dga' bas dus cig du khyab par 'gyur ba yang mi 'gal bar bstan pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:10586: bsam gtan gyi +amo la gzugs khams tshang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:10587: shes rab kyi a la gzugs myed tshang /
NK069(tu)001:10588: zung 'jug gi h+aum la thugs tshang /
NK069(tu)001:10589: 'gro ba drug gi sa bon la 'dod khams tshang /
NK069(tu)001:10590: rigs lnga'i sa bon la mya ngan las 'das pa tshang bas /
NK069(tu)001:10591: der dga' ba nyams su myong bas /
NK069(tu)001:10593: sems can la dga' bas khyab par 'gyur ba de
NK069(tu)001:10594: ba ga'i yi ge'i pho brang du gnas pas so
NK069(tu)001:10595: // thabs shes rab gnyis su myed pa'i dga' bas khyab par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:10596: spyir dga' ba la bcu drug ste /
NK069(tu)001:10597: go rims la ltos pa'i dga' bzhi dang /
NK069(tu)001:10598: gnas la ltos pa'i dga' ba bzhi dang /
NK069(tu)001:10599: spang bya la ltos pa'i dga' ba bzhi dang /
NK069(tu)001:10600: rang gi ngo bo la ltos pa'i dga' ba bzhi'o //
NK069(tu)001:10601: go rims la ltos pa'i dga' ba bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:10602: skad cig ma dang po la dga' ba /
NK069(tu)001:10605: bzhi pa la lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:10606: gnas la ltos pa'i dga' ba la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:10609: phyi'i gnas la ltos pa'i dga' ba bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:10610: lus khol bur bde ba skye ba dga' ba /
NK069(tu)001:10611: lus phal cher skye ba mchog dga' /
NK069(tu)001:10612: lus phyed tshal du skye ba dga' bral /
NK069(tu)001:10613: lus yongs la khyab par skye ba lhan skyes so //
NK069(tu)001:10614: nang gi gnas la ltos pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:10618: lte bar lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:10619: spang bya la ltos pa'i dga' ba bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:10620: rang gi rnam rtog rags rims 'gog pa dga' ba /
NK069(tu)001:10621: yum gyi rnam tog rags rims 'gog pa mchog dga' /
NK069(tu)001:10622: gnyis ka'i rnam tog shes cher 'gag pa dga' bral /
NK069(tu)001:10623: rnam par rtog pa thams cad 'gag pa lhan skyes so //
NK069(tu)001:10624: rang gi ngo bo la ltos pa'i dga' ba bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:10628: stong pa lhan cig skyes pa'i dga' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:10629: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba bstan pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:10630: zhes thabs shes rab 'bral ba'i don /
NK069(tu)001:10636: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus dang //
NK069(tu)001:10637: zhes bdag gi rdul snyed du sprul nas /
NK069(tu)001:10638: zhal mthong gsung thos chos kyi sgra bo byed /
NK069(tu)001:10639: mchod pa'i khyad par mang pos phar mchod tshur mchod byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10641: zhes der yang ma zad de khams gsum gyi 'gro ba rnams sngar gar skyes /
NK069(tu)001:10644: las ci byed pa kun yang mngon sum du mthong bar 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:10645: bshad rgyud thal ba dang sbyar na gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:10646: sbyor ba'i mchod pa bya thabs ni /
NK069(tu)001:10649: yab yum thabs dang shes rab kyi rtsa sa ya phrag sogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:10651: khams bdud rtsi'i thig le dang /
NK069(tu)001:10652: snying po rlung rnams lhar byin gyis brlabs so //
NK069(tu)001:10653: b+ha ga'i nang du 'gro ba drug gi yi ge nyungs 'bru tsam du bsdus te /
NK069(tu)001:10654: byang sems drangs la bde bas mchod na /
NK069(tu)001:10656: gnyis pa mchod pa'i yon tan ni /
NK069(tu)001:10657: bdag nyid chen po mi mchod pa yis /
NK069(tu)001:10658: ces pa la sogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:10659: sbyor ba'i sgra ha pa'i rlung skul nas /
NK069(tu)001:10660: khams thig le sangs rgyas kyi bdag nyid kyi rgyun /
NK069(tu)001:10661: steng sgo spyi bo nas byung bas /
NK069(tu)001:10662: lus kyi rtog tshogs lhar gnas pa de bde bas mnyes so //
NK069(tu)001:10663: rtsa sum cu rtsa drug nas yab yum gnyis kyi bum par thim pas /
NK069(tu)001:10664: bde ba thub drug lta bus b+ha ga'i sa bon drug 'od zer gyis sbyangs so //
NK069(tu)001:10665: des dbang bskur bde ba thob pa dga' bas khyab pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10666: gsum pa mchod pa'i 'bras bu ni //
NK069(tu)001:10667: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba bstan pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:10670: sems can gyi las shes par 'gyur ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:10672: shes rab thabs gsal ltan ma'am /
NK069(tu)001:10674: dra ba'i thig le yi ge nyid //
NK069(tu)001:10678: khams gsum 'gro rnams bsdus bya ste //
NK069(tu)001:10679: rtog tshogs dkyil 'khor mngon du bya //
NK069(tu)001:10680: phyogs bcu dus bzhi spyan drangs te //
NK069(tu)001:10681: rig pa so so'i gnas su stim //
NK069(tu)001:10682: skyod pa ha si'i sgra bskul ba'i //
NK069(tu)001:10683: bdag nyid bdag nyid chen po mchod pa yis /
NK069(tu)001:10685: steng sgo nas byung bde ba'i bcud //
NK069(tu)001:10686: so so'i bzhi bcu gnyis la thim //
NK069(tu)001:10687: kun nas bde ba'i ye shes che //
NK069(tu)001:10692: drug gnyis zer gyis sbyangs nas ni //
NK069(tu)001:10693: dbang bskur byin brlabs bde thob pa //
NK069(tu)001:10694: theg pa chen por dbugs phyung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:10696: lus ngag sems dang chos thams cad //
NK069(tu)001:10698: rnam par smin pa'i lus dang /
