NK069(tu)001:10699: rlung gis skyod pa'i ngag dang /
NK069(tu)001:10700: bag chags gos pa'i ngag dang /
NK069(tu)001:10701: mya ngan las 'das pa'i sangs rgyas kyi chos dang /
NK069(tu)001:10702: khams gsum 'khrul pa las 'khor ba'i chos thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:10703: gang na'ang mi gnas mi dmigs pa //
NK069(tu)001:10704: zhes don dam par ni gnas gang la yang mi gnas /
NK069(tu)001:10705: dngos po gang du yang myi dmigs so //
NK069(tu)001:10706: dmig yor tshul du sbyor ba yis //
NK069(tu)001:10710: snang la rang bzhin myed par /
NK069(tu)001:10711: ting nge 'dzin gyis rtse gcig tu sbyor ba yis /
NK069(tu)001:10712: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK069(tu)001:10713: zhes chos nyid nam mkha' lta bu la /
NK069(tu)001:10714: rig pa nam mkha' lta bus /
NK069(tu)001:10715: snang ba'i chos thams cad nam mkha' lta bur sgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:10716: des ni bdag gi rang bzhin spyir shes shing sgom par bya bar bstan no //
NK069(tu)001:10718: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK069(tu)001:10719: ces slob dpon gyi las su bya ba kun byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:10720: slob dpon de ni dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang dbyer myed par rtogs pa'i rig pas 'jug pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:10723: de nas slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK069(tu)001:10726: de yang dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga la bco brgyad de /
NK069(tu)001:10727: dang po slob dpon 'jug cing bzod par gsol ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:10728: shar sgor dbang gos dang ldan pas mchod pa phul ba rigs pa'i me tog dor /
NK069(tu)001:10729: slob ma bzhugs du gsol zhes lha la bzod gsol bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:10730: gnyis pa slob ma rnams dri zhim po'i chus khrus bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:10731: gsum pa dar dmar pos gdong pa dgab /
NK069(tu)001:10732: snyim par rin po che thog pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10733: bzhi pa bu khyod ci la dga' dri /
NK069(tu)001:10734: bskal ba bzang la dga' zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:10736: slob dpon gyi sras su byed /
NK069(tu)001:10738: sangs rgyas kyi 'bras bu 'dod par lus 'bul lo //
NK069(tu)001:10739: drug pa smin brag du as tshe srung /
NK069(tu)001:10740: khro bos bgegs bskrad pa bya /
NK069(tu)001:10741: bdun pa sgrib pa sbyangs la rnam shes lhar bskyed /
NK069(tu)001:10742: brgyad pa bdud rtsi lnga'i chus dam tshig sbyin /
NK069(tu)001:10743: dgu pa snying khar rdo rje bzhag la dam tshig dbog /
NK069(tu)001:10744: bcu pa tsan dan dkar dmar gyi chus chu nan bya /
NK069(tu)001:10745: bcu gcig pa dam tshig sgrag /
NK069(tu)001:10746: bcu gnyis pa me tog dor la 'brel ba brtag /
NK069(tu)001:10747: bcu gsum pa yi ge h+aum gis dam tshig phab la lha stim /
NK069(tu)001:10748: bcu gzhi pa yi dam zung cig pa'i nan tan bya /
NK069(tu)001:10750: bcu drug pa dkyil 'khor bstan pa don bshad /
NK069(tu)001:10751: bcu bdun pa tshogs bsags pa'i phyir yon 'bul /
NK069(tu)001:10752: bco brgyad pa yon phul ba'i yon tan bshad par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:10753: de rnams dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i cho ga rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:10755: de nas rigs kyi bu mchog des //
NK069(tu)001:10757: lha gang la me tog phog pa'i rigs kyi bu'am /
NK069(tu)001:10758: sngon gyi las mchog dang ldan pa'i gang zag des /
NK069(tu)001:10759: tshogs bsags pa'i rten du bla ma la yon dbul ste /
NK069(tu)001:10760: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK069(tu)001:10761: zhes rnam snang gi dkyil 'khor du zhugs na /
NK069(tu)001:10762: rang gi rgyal srid ci yod pa phul zhing rnams dbul lo //
NK069(tu)001:10763: rdo rje sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor du zhugs na /
NK069(tu)001:10764: rang gi lus phul la nor gyis slu'o //
NK069(tu)001:10765: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK069(tu)001:10766: ces pad ma rigs kyi dal du zhugs na /
NK069(tu)001:10767: rang gi bu dang chung ma dbul /
NK069(tu)001:10769: rin po che'i rigs kyi dal du zhugs na /
NK069(tu)001:10772: 'bru la sogs pa ci yod dbul lo //
NK069(tu)001:10773: rab tu ces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NK069(tu)001:10774: zhes las kyi rigs kyi dal du zhugs na /
NK069(tu)001:10775: rang la rab tu ces pa'i snying nor ram /
NK069(tu)001:10776: bla ma'i yid la 'byung zhing thugs dang 'thad ba rig pas gcad la dbul lo //
NK069(tu)001:10778: rigs lnga'i dal du zhugs pas so //
NK069(tu)001:10780: dbang phyug longs spyod lngas mchod na //
NK069(tu)001:10781: zhes thams cad la mnga' snyes pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:10782: slob dpon rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po de
NK069(tu)001:10783: 'dod pa'i yon tan lngas mchod cing mnyes par byas
NK069(tu)001:10784: na / yon tan ci yod zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:10785: sangs rgyas kyi dal thams cad mchod cing /
NK069(tu)001:10787: dkyil 'khor thams cad mchod pa yin //
NK069(tu)001:10788: zhes sangs rgyas thams cad mnyes pa ci te zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:10789: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyang rdo rje slob dpon nas 'byung ba yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:10790: slob dpon de dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams cad kyi rang bzhin nam bdag nyid yin par ro //
NK069(tu)001:10791: nye ba'i dkyil 'khor smos ci dgos //
NK069(tu)001:10793: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dkyil 'khor yang mchod pa yin na /
NK069(tu)001:10794: nye ba'i dkyil 'khor rang gi yid dam gyi lha
NK069(tu)001:10795: mnyes par 'gyur ba lta smos kyang ci dgos pa'o
NK069(tu)001:10796: // nyes pa thams cad dag par 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:10797: ces slob dpon mnyes par byas pas /
NK069(tu)001:10798: nyan thos kyi tshul khrims lta bu'am /
NK069(tu)001:10799: byang chub sems dpa'i slab pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:10801: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig nyams pa'i nyes skyon rnams /
NK069(tu)001:10802: bla ma mchod pa des dag cing /
NK069(tu)001:10805: dad brtson btul shugs rab rtogs na //
NK069(tu)001:10806: zhes don gyi mtshan nyid rab du rtogs nas /
NK069(tu)001:10807: snod dang mthun dbang sbyin pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:10809: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang /
NK069(tu)001:10810: dbang bskur ba'i las rim snod dang stun pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:10811: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK069(tu)001:10812: zhes bdag don gyi brtson 'grus can la nyan bsgom gyi dbang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:10813: gzhan don gyi brtson 'grus can la nyan bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:10814: gnyis ka'i brtson 'grus can la slob dpon gyi dbang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:10815: spyod pa'i tul shug can la gsang dbang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:10816: rig pa'i tul shugs can la shes rab ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:10817: mnyam pa'i tul shugs can la bde ba chen po'i dbang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:10819: snying rjes chud ma zos par bzung //
NK069(tu)001:10820: zhes slob dpon gyis snying rjes slob ma'i snod chud ma zos par thugs rjes bzung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:10821: slob ma nyan na blo btul /
NK069(tu)001:10822: slob tu bcug na sgom mi nus /
NK069(tu)001:10823: las kyi bye brag mi shes /
NK069(tu)001:10825: 'du shes lug bzhin rmongs pa la /
NK069(tu)001:10826: slob dpon gyis nor phra mo tsam la ltas nas dbang byin na /
NK069(tu)001:10827: khos bdag la dbang bskur mnyam nas /
NK069(tu)001:10828: spyod pa ci dgar spyad pas /
NK069(tu)001:10829: slob ma ngan song du song na /
NK069(tu)001:10831: slob dpon gyis snying rje de lta bu byar mi rung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:10832: yang slob mnyan du bcug na blo rno /
NK069(tu)001:10833: bsgom du bcug na bsgom sran che /
NK069(tu)001:10834: las kyi bya ba byed na ni gang la yang ma rmongs /
NK069(tu)001:10835: 'chad du bcug na ni don go ston nus pa /
NK069(tu)001:10836: de lta bu'i yon tan tshad dang ldan pa la /
NK069(tu)001:10837: slob dpon gyis dga' 'gu phran tshegs pa ltas nas /
NK069(tu)001:10838: 'chad pa dang slob dpon gyi dbang ma bskur na yang chud zos te /
NK069(tu)001:10840: mdor na slob dpon gyis slob ma'i snod kyi rim pa dang sbyar la /
NK069(tu)001:10841: dbang yang ji ltar rigs pa bzhin du bskur zhing /
NK069(tu)001:10842: slob ma chud ma zos par don bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:10843: dbang bskur ba la brgyad de /
NK069(tu)001:10846: dbang rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK069(tu)001:10851: mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:10854: phan pa'i dbang bcu'i mtshungs ldan ni /
NK069(tu)001:10855: spyi bo bde ba chen po'i 'khor lo gdugs kyi dbang du rang la gnas /
NK069(tu)001:10856: rtsa'i dbang bdud rtsis gang ba bum pa'i dbang /
NK069(tu)001:10857: gsang ba'i dbang po rgyal mtshan gyi dbang /
NK069(tu)001:10858: khams bdud rtsi lnga bza' btung gi dbang /
NK069(tu)001:10859: lus kyi rtsa mkha' 'gro mas lus bsrung ba go cha'i dbang /
NK069(tu)001:10860: rtsa ro ma dang rkyang ma gnyis gcod pan gyi dbang /
NK069(tu)001:10861: kun d+har ma mdud pa bcu drug yod pa 'phreng ba'i dbang /
NK069(tu)001:10862: rtog tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis phyag rgya'i dbang /
NK069(tu)001:10863: rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes lngar gnas dbu rgyan gyi dbang /
NK069(tu)001:10864: khams lnga'i thig le yi ger gnas pa snying po lnga'i dbang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:10865: nus pa'i dbang gi mtshungs ldan ni /
NK069(tu)001:10868: snying ka chos sgom sgrub dbang /
NK069(tu)001:10869: lag pa g.yas g.yon thabs shes rab 'phrin las dbang /
NK069(tu)001:10870: spyi mgrin snying lte ba gsang ba lnga rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:10871: thob byed kyi rkyen bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:10875: mtshungs pa'i rkyen snod du gyur par bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:10876: dbang rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK069(tu)001:10880: de la phan pa'i dbang ni /
NK069(tu)001:10881: shi ba la bskur na ngan song las grol ba la phan /
NK069(tu)001:10882: na ba la bskur na nad sos par 'gyur ba la phan /
NK069(tu)001:10883: rim 'gror bskur na srung bar phan no //
NK069(tu)001:10890: zab mo ni chags lam mo //
NK069(tu)001:10894: zab mos chos sku thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:10895: dbang bskur ba'i las kyi rim pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:10896: dad pa can la phan pa'i dbang bcu bskur /
NK069(tu)001:10897: brtson 'grus can la nus pa'i dbang lnga bskur /
NK069(tu)001:10898: btul zhugs can la zab mo'i dbang gsum bskur ro //
NK069(tu)001:10900: 'khor ba las grol du mi 'dod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10904: yang na thal mo rab snol nas //
NK069(tu)001:10905: zhes yang na ni bsnan pa'i tshig go //
NK069(tu)001:10906: yang na mi 'dra ba bshad pa /
NK069(tu)001:10907: yang na gsang dbang bskur na'o //
NK069(tu)001:10908: slob dpon gyis thal mo bsnol ba la 'dzug gang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:10909: phyag rgya chen po'i dbang du ni //
NK069(tu)001:10910: zhes lus ngag yid gsum lha'i sku phyag rgya chen por bsgom pa'i dbang du ni /
NK069(tu)001:10912: zangs sam shing tsan dan la yab kyi mkha' mtshon pa'i dal /
NK069(tu)001:10913: thal mo bshibs pa'i tshad 'dzug go //
NK069(tu)001:10914: mkhas pas cho ga bzhin du bya //
NK069(tu)001:10916: mdor na gsang dbang gsum po'i dkyiil 'khor mtshon pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10918: thal mo zhes bya ba sdebs pa'i sgra //
NK069(tu)001:10919: dbang po yul dus rab sbyor bas //
NK069(tu)001:10920: phyag rgya chen po nam mkha'i dbyings //
NK069(tu)001:10921: btul zhugs gnyis kyi dbang du blang //
NK069(tu)001:10922: rdo rje mdzub mo'i rtse dag tu //
NK069(tu)001:10923: til 'bru nam mkha'i gzhal yas su //
NK069(tu)001:10924: ri rab tsam gyi phyag rgya bgod //
NK069(tu)001:10925: thabs kyi cho ga rab gnas dang //
NK069(tu)001:10926: gsang ba'i sbyin sreg lugs su dbul //
NK069(tu)001:10929: yab yum rdo rje pad ma sbyor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:10930: phyag rgya chen po ni yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:10931: de nam mkha'i dbyings phyug mar byin gyis brlabs so //
NK069(tu)001:10932: yang na ni yum bla ma'i spang du blang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:10933: 'dzug gang gi gsang ba'i rdo rje'o //
NK069(tu)001:10935: thig le til 'bru tsam pas yum gyi b+ha ga'i gzhal yas su /
NK069(tu)001:10936: lha sku ri rab tsam pa dgod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:10938: shes rab ye shes kyis rab gnas bya /
NK069(tu)001:10939: bde ba chen pos lugs byung lugs zlog /
NK069(tu)001:10940: yang na sa gzhi rab mnyams te //
NK069(tu)001:10941: zhes zhi ba bsdus pa rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi dal byed na /
NK069(tu)001:10942: dkyil 'khor khru gang tshad du bya //
NK069(tu)001:10943: zhes dkyil 'khor gyi phyag len goms shing mkhas pas /
NK069(tu)001:10944: yang na lus gang tshad du ste //
NK069(tu)001:10945: zhes goms pa chung zhing mi mkhas pas khru bzhi pa /
NK069(tu)001:10946: yang na lus ni gsum gyi tshad //
NK069(tu)001:10947: ces 'bring lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor byed na /
NK069(tu)001:10948: 'dom gsum mam khru bcu gnyis par bya /
NK069(tu)001:10949: yang na bcu drug par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:10950: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la don bcu ste /
NK069(tu)001:10952: dkyil 'khor che chung gi tshad dang /
NK069(tu)001:10961: dang po sa gzhi mnyam pa la don brgyad de /
NK069(tu)001:10962: sa spyi'i mtshan nyid rtags pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:10963: sa rang gi mtshan nyid rtags pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:10965: rang gi dbang bya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:10966: sa ngan na sbyang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:10967: nus mthu can du byin brlab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:10968: sa'i bar chad bsrung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:10971: sa phyogs rang bzhin gyis bkra shis pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:10972: bde bar gshegs pa'i zhabs kyis lcags pas bkra shis pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:10973: gang zag grub pa thob pas bkra shis pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:10974: lha mi'i mngags pa brjod pa'i gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:10975: sa rang gi mtshan nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:10978: sa'i ro gyo mgo sreg ma /
NK069(tu)001:10979: shing gi ro 'gal dum dang sol ba /
NK069(tu)001:10980: sha'i ro rus pa dang song dong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:10981: sa blang ba ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:10982: snang ba rgyal po dang yul bdag la blang /
NK069(tu)001:10983: mi snang ba sa'i lha mo dang sa bdag lha
NK069(tu)001:10984: klu la gtor ma byin bden pas bgo la blang
NK069(tu)001:10985: ngo // rang gi dbang du bya ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:10986: zangs sam shing gi phur bu zla kham la /
NK069(tu)001:10987: rta mgrin dmar po zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa /
NK069(tu)001:10988: g.yas g.yon dang po pad ma dang zhags pa /
NK069(tu)001:10989: tha ma gnyis phur pa dril bar bsams la /
NK069(tu)001:10990: sa'i dngos grub rang gi dbang du bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:10991: sa ngan na sbyang ba ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:10992: las dang bya ba ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:10993: sbyin sreg 'bar ba mes sbyang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:10994: sngags dang phyag rgyas sbyang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:10995: nus mthu can du byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:10996: gzhal yas khang du skyed la bzhag go //
NK069(tu)001:10997: sa'i bar chad bsrung ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:10998: sum b+ha ni'i sngags rings kyis me dpung 'bar ba'i gur du bsam /
NK069(tu)001:11000: thams cad lha'i dkyil 'khor du shes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:11002: yang na sa gzhi rab mnyams te /
NK069(tu)001:11004: dkyil 'khor che chung gi tshad ni /
NK069(tu)001:11005: shin du 'phra ba'i tshad sor bzhi 'dzub gang yin /
NK069(tu)001:11008: 'dom gang 'dom gsum ni zhi ba 'bring po /
NK069(tu)001:11009: khru bcu drug pa ni zhi ba rgyas pa /
NK069(tu)001:11010: dpag tshad rgyang grags mthar nye'i lam pas sangs rgyas stong gi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad do //
NK069(tu)001:11012: ye shes kyi thig nam mkha' la gdab /
NK069(tu)001:11013: dam tshig gi thig sa gzhi la gdab bo //
NK069(tu)001:11015: rab rin po che rnam pa lnga /
NK069(tu)001:11017: tha ma rdul tshon rnam pa lnga'o //
NK069(tu)001:11019: rgyas 'bring bsdus pa gang byed bri bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:11023: sku tsaka li bgod par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:11025: ye shes pa spyan drangs la dam tshig pa la stim /
NK069(tu)001:11028: 'khor ba ma stongs kyi bar du bzhugs pa'i gsol ba gdab bo //
NK069(tu)001:11029: sbyin sreg brtags ngan na bya /
NK069(tu)001:11030: der slob ma zhugs la dbang bskur bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:11032: de lta bu'i cho ga cha tshang ba'i dkyil 'khor du zhugs na /
NK069(tu)001:11033: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor du zhugs pa dang 'dra'o //
NK069(tu)001:11034: de rnams ni ngag 'don phyogs du bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11036: phur bu srad bu mtshon che dang /
NK069(tu)001:11038: gos rgyan mdzes pa'i yid 'ong grogs //
NK069(tu)001:11040: thig gdab cho ga phun sum tshogs //
NK069(tu)001:11041: mkhas ldan chen pos sgrims te bya //
NK069(tu)001:11042: zhes thig gdab pa la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:11048: phyi'i 'khor lo skor ba'i rdzas phur bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:11049: dal gyi cha 'god pa'i rdzas thig skud srad bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:11050: ye shes dam tshig gi thig gi rdzas kha dog go //
NK069(tu)001:11051: de la ye shes thig gi skud pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:11052: rgyu pad ma'i rnal ma las skud pa lnga sgril /
NK069(tu)001:11053: ye shes lnga'i kha dog dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11054: dam tshig gi thig skud ni /
NK069(tu)001:11055: ras bal las kha dog gsum ldan sku gsung thugs ldan no //
NK069(tu)001:11056: de gnyis snod gtsang mar bzhag la /
NK069(tu)001:11057: bsangs te ye shes lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:11058: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs so //
NK069(tu)001:11062: sems dngas bas yid du 'ong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:11064: +amo badz+ra su tra sa ma ya ma ti tra ma h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:11065: ye shes kyi thig bar snang la nam mkhar gtab la /
NK069(tu)001:11066: der dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas spyan drangs la bzhugs pa la cung zad mchod la dpang por bcol /
NK069(tu)001:11067: +amo sarba sho da ni h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:11068: zhes pas dam tshig gi thig sa gzhi la gdab bo //
NK069(tu)001:11069: dkyil 'khor bsdus rgyas 'bring sogs gang byed gdab bo //
NK069(tu)001:11071: thig skud chad na slob dpon 'chi /
NK069(tu)001:11072: phyogs 'khrugs na dpon slob gnyis ka dam tshig nyams /
NK069(tu)001:11073: thig rgyun chad na lam la bar chad 'ong /
NK069(tu)001:11074: de bas na lag len mkhas pa /
NK069(tu)001:11076: chang dang gnyid dang le lo spangs la shes pa sgrims te bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:11077: yang na khru ni bcu drug dang //
NK069(tu)001:11078: zhes 'di yang zhi ba 'bring po'i tshad do //
NK069(tu)001:11079: nyi shu'am nyi shu rtsa lngar bya //
NK069(tu)001:11080: zhes zhi ba rgyas pa'i dal tshad gnyis ni /
NK069(tu)001:11083: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor lnga rnams bsgom //
NK069(tu)001:11084: zhes dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring bsdus pa gang byed kyang rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor de /
NK069(tu)001:11085: zhi ba sku'i dal byed na /
NK069(tu)001:11086: rnam par snang mdzad kyis gtso bo byas la /
NK069(tu)001:11087: gzhan 'khor du sgom pas na rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:11089: snang ba mtha' yas gtso bor bya /
NK069(tu)001:11094: yon tan gyi dal du byed na /
NK069(tu)001:11098: don yod grub pa dbus kyi gtso bor bya //
NK069(tu)001:11099: gzhan 'khor du bsgoms pas na rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:11100: de ltar sgom pa'i rten dgod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:11102: cho ga yan lag tshang bar dgod pas na /
NK069(tu)001:11104: rdul tshon byin gyis brlab pa yang gzung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:11105: nges pa ni rigs lnga'i dal gang byed yin no //
NK069(tu)001:11106: sku gsung thugs ldan gzugs kyang dgod //
NK069(tu)001:11110: de gsum gang 'god kyang rung ste /
NK069(tu)001:11111: sku gsung thugs gsum dang ldan par byin gyis rlab pa'i gzugs dgod de /
NK069(tu)001:11114: de las skur byas nas dgod do //
NK069(tu)001:11116: gsung gi dkyil 'khor gsung yig 'bru dang ldan pas yin la /
NK069(tu)001:11117: de bzhin du sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:11118: de bas na lha re re la yang sku gsung thugs gsum gsum tshang bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:11119: yang na rgyang grags dpag tshad dam //
NK069(tu)001:11120: zhes yang na mchog gi tshad ni /
NK069(tu)001:11121: gzhu 'dom lnga rgya la rgyang grags gcig /
NK069(tu)001:11122: de brgyad la dpag tshad gcig de mchog dang /
NK069(tu)001:11125: slob dpon mthar nye'i lam la gnas pas /
NK069(tu)001:11126: thig dor ba tsam gyis dal du ldang bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:11127: nam mkha' dbyings kyi bsam yas par //
NK069(tu)001:11128: zhes yang na tshad la nges pa myed de /
NK069(tu)001:11129: nam mkhas gar khyab sar chos kyi dbyings kyis khyab la /
NK069(tu)001:11130: chos kyi dbyings la mtha' myed de /
NK069(tu)001:11131: dkyil 'khor dang 'dra ba chos kyi dbyings /
NK069(tu)001:11132: lha dang 'dra ba ye shes yin pas na'o //
NK069(tu)001:11133: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor sna tshogs sgom //
NK069(tu)001:11134: zhes sgyu 'phrul rang gi dbang du na /
NK069(tu)001:11136: nyi khri chig stong la sogs pa sgom /
NK069(tu)001:11137: yang na spyi'i dbang du na /
NK069(tu)001:11138: rgyud gzhan las 'byung ba'i lha sgom yang sgom nus pas sgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:11139: de yang bshad rgyud rdo rje las /
NK069(tu)001:11140: slob dpon mthar nye'i lam gnas pas /
NK069(tu)001:11141: rgyang grags dpag tshad la sogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:11142: rdo rje thig tshad dor tsam gyis /
NK069(tu)001:11143: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gsal lhang ba /
NK069(tu)001:11144: dkyil 'khor sna tshogs mchog tu gsungs /
NK069(tu)001:11145: ma mthong rmongs la ston phyir tshon //
NK069(tu)001:11147: 'gro ba'i sems ye shes lngar gnas pa ma mthong bar rmongs pa de la /
NK069(tu)001:11148: ye shes lngar ston par mtshon no //
NK069(tu)001:11149: de yang brgyad bcu pa las /
NK069(tu)001:11150: sems can ma lus thams cad la //
NK069(tu)001:11151: ye shes lnga yis kun khyab kyang //
NK069(tu)001:11152: rang gi rnam rtog sgrib byas nas //
NK069(tu)001:11153: ye shes lnga yi don ma mthong //
NK069(tu)001:11154: de ltar rmongs pa thams cad la //
NK069(tu)001:11155: ye shes mtshan nyid bstan pa'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:11156: dkar dang dmar dang ser ba dang //
NK069(tu)001:11157: ljang khu la sogs nag por bstan //
NK069(tu)001:11159: kha dog nyi shu rtsa lnga 'am //
NK069(tu)001:11162: khro bo la sogs pa'i kha dog bsal ba'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:11167: dkar nag ces pa la sogs pa gzhan la yang 'dre bar shes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:11168: lnga yi tshon gyis bri bar bya //
NK069(tu)001:11169: zhes zhi ba 'bring po dang bsdus pa la /
NK069(tu)001:11170: dkar ser dmar ljang mthing ka dang lnga'o //
NK069(tu)001:11173: gtso bo gang gis 'dul ba'i dal du 'gyed na /
NK069(tu)001:11174: pan tsa re kha'i rtsig pa la bya /
NK069(tu)001:11175: 'gro ba gang gi 'dul ba'i dbang du 'gyed na /
NK069(tu)001:11177: 'khor lo rtsibs re re'i steng du rtsibs bzhi pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:11178: spyir 'khor lo rtsibs drug par bya /
NK069(tu)001:11179: las rnams bzhi gang 'dul gyi steng du 'gyed na /
NK069(tu)001:11180: zhi ba la dkar por shas che bar bya /
NK069(tu)001:11183: drag po la mthing ka shas che bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:11184: 'dir tshon la ngag don du gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:11189: rab rin po che lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11190: sngon po in tra ni la /
NK069(tu)001:11192: ser po spos shel lam gser /
NK069(tu)001:11193: dmar po pad+ma ra ga'am byu ru /
NK069(tu)001:11198: nyi shu rtsa lnga'i snod rna mas ma 'dres par byas la /
NK069(tu)001:11200: lnga las yig 'bru gcig las kha dog nyi shu rtsa lngar bsam /
NK069(tu)001:11201: de yongs su gyur pa las lha yab yum du bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:11202: lnga ni sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las lngar bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:11204: sarba pan tsa rad na sa ma ye h'u /
NK069(tu)001:11206: sor mo lnga la 'bru lnga sgoms la sa tshon spung /
NK069(tu)001:11207: de nas thig dmigs pas steg la /
NK069(tu)001:11208: byang shar du tshon pra brtag de nas lag pa
NK069(tu)001:11209: 'bru lnga dang ldan pa'i rdo rje khu tshur gyis
NK069(tu)001:11210: legs par bzabs la bri bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:11211: ting 'dzin rol mo mtha' yas mchog /
NK069(tu)001:11212: ces rnal 'byor pa ting nge 'dzin la rtse cig pas /
NK069(tu)001:11213: lha'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas bsam gyis mi khyab pa yon tan mchog dang ldan par bsgom pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:11214: ting nge 'dzin snang la rang bzhin myed pa rol mo ltar bsgom pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:11215: dkyil 'khor nyid slang la sgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:11216: yi ge 'am gdan nam snying po 'am /
NK069(tu)001:11217: zhes yi ge ta tha la sogs pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:11219: snying po'i yi ge h'u mum mam /
NK069(tu)001:11220: phyag rgya sku gsung thugs ldan par //
NK069(tu)001:11221: ces phyag rgya sku gzugs las bskyed de /
NK069(tu)001:11223: yi ge gsung phyag mtshan nam nyi zla'i thig le thugs so //
NK069(tu)001:11224: byin rlabs ya mtshan rmad po che //
NK069(tu)001:11225: zhes sku gsung thugs dang ldan par bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:11226: sku gsung thugs las byung ba'i byin rlabs ya mtshan che ba /
NK069(tu)001:11227: rmad du byung ba 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:11230: bka' bzhin sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pa la /
NK069(tu)001:11231: sangs rgyas kyi dngos grub ma stsal na /
NK069(tu)001:11232: de bzhin gshegs pa yang thugs dam nyams par 'gyur bas /
NK069(tu)001:11233: dngos grub rtsol ba las mi 'da' bas na dam tshig zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:11234: spyir rab gnas la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:11238: bum pa skyon myed kha dog dkar po la /
NK069(tu)001:11240: rnam rgyal bum par rang rang gi lha bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:11241: las thams cad pa'i bum par bdud rtsi 'khyil par bsam /
NK069(tu)001:11243: khrus byas la dris byugs te /
NK069(tu)001:11245: brod pa skyed la dbugs dbyung /
NK069(tu)001:11246: lha bskyed la go bgo so shing dor /
NK069(tu)001:11251: ba'i rnam lnga dang shing shun gyi sku phyi /
NK069(tu)001:11252: me long la sku khrus gsol /
NK069(tu)001:11255: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis rlab /
NK069(tu)001:11260: de nas me tog dor ro //
NK069(tu)001:11264: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab bo //
NK069(tu)001:11265: sa la sogs la phyag rgyar byas //
NK069(tu)001:11266: zhes sa la sku byas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11267: rin po che la lugs su blugs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11268: ras la ris su bris pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11269: rdo dang shing la 'bur du bskos pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11270: ras bal la thags su byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:11271: de la rab gnas byas pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:11274: thugs rdo rje dril bu lta bur rab gnas byas pas /
NK069(tu)001:11275: rnam grol rim par thob par 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:11276: ces rgyu bzang ngan gyi rnam pas /
NK069(tu)001:11277: grol lugs kyi rim pa yod /
NK069(tu)001:11279: rgyus byas pas rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:11280: de rang bzhin med par sbyang pas 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs so //
NK069(tu)001:11281: dag pa'i ye shes kyis sbyangs na //
NK069(tu)001:11282: zhes gzung 'dzin dag pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK069(tu)001:11283: bag chags kyis sgrib pa ngan pa thams cad mtshan ma med par sbyangs nas /
NK069(tu)001:11284: ting nge 'dzin gyis lha'i dkyil 'khor du bsgoms na /
NK069(tu)001:11285: 'bras bu thob mi 'thob smos ci dgos /
NK069(tu)001:11286: smos ci dgos te de nyid yin //
NK069(tu)001:11287: ces da lta nyid du 'bras bu thob pa de /
NK069(tu)001:11288: de yang rgyu sngar spyad pas 'bras bu phyis 'byung du re ba ni ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:11289: rang rig pa'i rgyal po lhar shes pa la /
NK069(tu)001:11290: rang dbang bsgyur ba de nyid kho na 'bras bu yin zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:11291: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK069(tu)001:11292: zhes phyogs bcu dus bzhis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:11295: ye nas sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor kun tu
NK069(tu)001:11296: bzang por sangs rgyas pa'i bdag nyid du dbyer med
NK069(tu)001:11297: cing tha mi dad pas na bdag nyid chen po'o
NK069(tu)001:11298: // mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK069(tu)001:11299: zhes bdag nyid chen po de ltar dbyer med pa de yang rtsa ba gar 'dus zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:11300: rtsa ba rang gi sems su 'dus la /
NK069(tu)001:11301: sems kyi rang bzhin gcig dang du ma dang bral ba /
NK069(tu)001:11303: gzhi dang rtsa ba med pa /
NK069(tu)001:11304: ji lta bu yang dmigs su med cing /
NK069(tu)001:11305: mi dmigs pa chos kyi dbyings yin la /
NK069(tu)001:11306: chos kyi dbyings rig pa dang ldan pa kho na thugs ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:11307: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:11308: zhes de ltar chos thams cad kyi rtsa ba /
NK069(tu)001:11309: sems nyid thugs ye shes dkyil 'khor yin phan cad /
NK069(tu)001:11310: sems su snang ba'i chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin yang /
NK069(tu)001:11311: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ma yin pa myed de /
NK069(tu)001:11312: dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin ye nas yin la /
NK069(tu)001:11313: yin pa de yin pa'i sar ma lus par /
NK069(tu)001:11314: de ltar shes rab kyis kyang rtogs par byas la /
NK069(tu)001:11315: ting nge 'dzin gyis kyang gzugs las gzugs su gyur pa /
NK069(tu)001:11316: thabs las thabs su gyur pa /
NK069(tu)001:11317: thabs kyi rgyal po sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyar sgom pa de ni /
NK069(tu)001:11320: dkyil 'khor gyis dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drangs shing
NK069(tu)001:11321: mchod pa yin pas na dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan
NK069(tu)001:11323: rang snang dbyer myed dkyil 'khor la //
NK069(tu)001:11324: zhes 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK069(tu)001:11325: rig pa rang snang ba'i chos thams cad dbyer myed de /
NK069(tu)001:11326: gang du dbyer myed zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:11327: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs
NK069(tu)001:11328: yang dag pa'i ye shes la yang sku gsung thugs
NK069(tu)001:11330: rig pa rang snang ba'i chos 'di kun gyi rang bzhin yin yang /
NK069(tu)001:11331: rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs sku gsung thugs
NK069(tu)001:11332: kyi rang bzhin du gnas dkyil 'khor du gnas la
NK069(tu)001:11334: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa'i gnas skabs na /
NK069(tu)001:11335: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du snang ba yang /
NK069(tu)001:11336: thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes rang snang la /
NK069(tu)001:11337: rig pa rang snang ba'i chos thams cad kyang rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis /
NK069(tu)001:11338: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin yin pa yang sems rang snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:11339: sems dang ye shes rang snang ba dbyer myed pas dbyer med kyi dal lo //
NK069(tu)001:11340: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK069(tu)001:11341: zhes de ltar chos thams cad sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du'am /
NK069(tu)001:11342: thugs ye shes kyi rang bzhin nam /
NK069(tu)001:11343: mtshan nyid yin pa'i don de la /
NK069(tu)001:11344: shes rab kyis kyang rtogs par 'jug la /
NK069(tu)001:11345: ting nge 'dzin gyis kyang rtogs pa'i don la rtse
NK069(tu)001:11346: gcig tu mnyam zhing dbyer myed par sbyor bas so
NK069(tu)001:11347: // phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:11348: zhes yang na gong ma ltar rtogs pa de la /
NK069(tu)001:11349: phyogs bcu dus bzhi kun nas gshegs pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:11350: tshe rabs thog ma myed pa'i dus nas snyen snyen bsgrubs bsgrubs pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:11351: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i bde' bar gshegs pa'i dkyil
NK069(tu)001:11352: 'khor gyi che ba'i yon tan yang de la rab
NK069(tu)001:11353: tu rdzogs na / shin tu nye bar gyur pa'i
NK069(tu)001:11354: yid dam gyi lha'i dngos grub thob pa las mi
NK069(tu)001:11355: 'da' ba dang smos su myed pas dam tshig mchog
NK069(tu)001:11356: tu rdzogs na / ces bya'o // 'bras bu ci 'grub zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:11359: dus bzhi kun nas gshegs pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:11360: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rab tu rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:11361: zhes sangs rgyas snyen cing bsgrub par bya ba'i bde bar gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor kun /
NK069(tu)001:11362: gong ma ltar rtogs shing bsgoms pa'i de /
NK069(tu)001:11363: yon tan mtha' dag pa ma tsal bar shugs kyis rab tu rdzogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11365: nye bar gyur pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK069(tu)001:11366: ces de la phyogs bcu'i bde ba gshegs pa thams cad nye bar sku ston par 'gyur /
NK069(tu)001:11367: nye bar gsung gis chos 'chad par gyur /
NK069(tu)001:11368: nye bar thugs kyis dgongs par 'gyur ba las mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig mchog yin no zhe'am /
NK069(tu)001:11369: dpag bsam shing dang yid bzhin gyi //
NK069(tu)001:11370: rin po che dang 'byung ba dag /
NK069(tu)001:11371: ces lha'i 'jig rten na dpag bsam gyi shing la 'dod pa 'byung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:11372: 'khor lo sgyur ba'i rgyal po la yid bzhin gyi
NK069(tu)001:11373: nor bu rin po che la 'dod pa 'byung ba
NK069(tu)001:11374: dang / gnod sbyin chen po brgyad la bum pa bzang po las 'dod pa 'byung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:11375: 'dzam bu gling gi mi la sogs pa la 'byung ba lnga la spyod pa kun no //
NK069(tu)001:11376: de dag rdzas yod ma yin te //
NK069(tu)001:11377: zhes dpag bsam gyi shing dang /
NK069(tu)001:11378: rin po che de dag rdzas su grub pa zhig
NK069(tu)001:11379: logs na yod pa la spyod pa ni ma yin
NK069(tu)001:11380: te / rang sems bsod nams rtan pa yin //
NK069(tu)001:11381: zhes 'o na gang yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:11382: tshe rabs dpag tu myed pa nas //
NK069(tu)001:11383: rang sems la bsod nams dge' ba'i rtsa ba mang po spyad pa'i bag chags rtan zhing /
NK069(tu)001:11385: sems nyid dpag bsam gyi shing dang yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po cher snang ba yin la /
NK069(tu)001:11386: de la las dang bag chags 'thun pa'i lha rnams spyod pa gcig du bas /
NK069(tu)001:11387: mi 'byung ba lnga la spyod pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:11388: rang gi sems la mir skye ba de tsam gyis bsod nams sam /
NK069(tu)001:11389: dge' ba'i rtsa ba bag chags ltas shing rtan par byas pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:11390: sems nyid 'byung ba chen po lngar snang ba yin la /
NK069(tu)001:11391: de la las dang bag chags mthun pa'i mi rnams spyod pa gcig tu bas /
NK069(tu)001:11393: 'dir 'bras bu gsum byung ba la ma 'dabs sam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:11395: gong nas sgyu 'phrul dra ba bstan pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:11398: thabs lam zab mo'i dbang nyams su blangs pa'i 'bras bu yin la /
NK069(tu)001:11399: dpag bsam shing dang ces pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK069(tu)001:11400: gzugs rnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs shing rab tu gnas pa byas pa'i 'bras bu yin /
NK069(tu)001:11401: cho ga lnga ni rdzogs byas shing ces pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK069(tu)001:11402: tshogs bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu thob tshul bshad pa yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:11403: ngo mtshar cho 'phrul smad kyi chos //
NK069(tu)001:11404: zhes gong ma de dag dpe' don yin yang /
NK069(tu)001:11405: don gyi phyogs cig dper bzhag te don bstan na /
NK069(tu)001:11406: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku dang ye shes dang /
NK069(tu)001:11408: sku gsung thugs kyi cho 'phrul bsam gyis myi khyab pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:11409: ngo mtshar rmad du 'byung ba'i chos yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:11410: gzhan nas yod 'ongs ma yin te //
NK069(tu)001:11411: zhes de ltar ngo mtshar cho 'phrul smad kyi chos de dag kyang /
NK069(tu)001:11412: gzhan ma zhig na dngos por grub pa zhig yod pa ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:11413: 'o na de gang yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:11414: thabs la rten pa'i shes rab nyid //
NK069(tu)001:11415: ces thabs sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya mtshan ma dang bcas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11416: mtshan ma myed pa gnyis dbyer myed pa'i don /
NK069(tu)001:11417: shes rab kyis kyang rtogs la /
NK069(tu)001:11418: ting nge 'dzin gyis kyang myi 'gyur ba'i rtse gcig tu bsgoms shes rab ye shes nyid /
NK069(tu)001:11419: de lta bu yi ngang du 'byung //
NK069(tu)001:11420: zhes de ltar gong ma de lta bu'i /
NK069(tu)001:11421: ngo mtshar ba'i cho 'phrul sna tshogs pa smad du
NK069(tu)001:11422: 'byung ba'i chos kyi ngang dam rang bzhin du 'byung
NK069(tu)001:11423: zhes bya'o // shes rab dbyings kyi de bzhin nyid //
NK069(tu)001:11424: thabs kyi phyag rgyar gyur pa'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:11425: ces shes rab spros pa dang bral ba'i don chos kyi dbyings kyi de bzhin nyid dang /
NK069(tu)001:11426: thabs sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya'i rgyur gyur pa'i phyir zhe'am /
NK069(tu)001:11427: yang na shes rab ye shes la bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:11428: dbyings rig pa dang ldan la /
NK069(tu)001:11429: shes rab ye shes spros pa dang bral bas /
NK069(tu)001:11430: chos kyi dbyings dang ye shes gnyis myed pa'i de bzhin nyid /
NK069(tu)001:11431: thabs sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya'i rgyur gyur pa'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:11432: ye shes la ni ye shes rol //
NK069(tu)001:11433: ye shes rol pa nyid kyang bsog /
NK069(tu)001:11434: ces ye shes phyag rgya rang snang ba la ni ye shes nyid rol la /
NK069(tu)001:11435: ye shes rol pa nyid kyang gsog gsob stong pa nyid de /
NK069(tu)001:11436: mtshan ma myed pa'i ngang las ma g.yos so //
NK069(tu)001:11437: rol pa ni gang yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:11438: rgyal ba 'jig rten du mngon par sangs rgyas shing byung bas /
NK069(tu)001:11439: sems can 'khor ba dang ngan song las skyob pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11440: sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs sam cho 'phrul bsam
NK069(tu)001:11441: gyis mi khyab pa ston pa yang de ltar ston
NK069(tu)001:11442: pa nyid na ye shes rol pa nyid kyang bsog
NK069(tu)001:11444: rgyal ba sngon 'byung skyob pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:11445: zhes 'khor ba las rgyal ba'i sangs rgyas ni /
NK069(tu)001:11446: de bzhin nyid mtshan ma myed pa'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang /
NK069(tu)001:11447: sngon 'byung 'jig rten du sprul pa'i sku byung nas /
NK069(tu)001:11448: 'gro ba drug gi sems can 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las skyob pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11449: byin brlabs ston pa'ang de bzhin te //
NK069(tu)001:11450: zhes sku'i byin rlabs mdzad pa bcu gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:11451: gsung gi byin rlabs chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri bzhi stong /
NK069(tu)001:11452: thugs kyi byin brlabs mngon shes lnga //
NK069(tu)001:11453: yon tan gyi byin rlabs sku dang zhal la sogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa /
NK069(tu)001:11454: 'phrin las kyi byin rlabs theg pa ston pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:11455: ye shes sgyu ma lta bus bya ba byed nus
NK069(tu)001:11456: pa'i gsog bsob lta bu gong ma de bzhin yin
NK069(tu)001:11457: te / bya byed nus pa'i gzi' brjid kyis //
NK069(tu)001:11458: zhes de yang gsog gsob sgyu ma lta bus ci
NK069(tu)001:11459: yang bya ba byed mi nus pa ni ma yin
NK069(tu)001:11460: te / thugs ye shes de nyid 'gro ba'i don
NK069(tu)001:11461: ci yang bya ba byed nus pa'i gzi brjid dang
NK069(tu)001:11462: te / ldan pas so // sgyu ma rdo rje brtsan po mchog /
NK069(tu)001:11463: ces de ltar bya ba byed tsam na dngos por ma grub pa ni sgyu ma dang 'dra la /
NK069(tu)001:11464: phar ni bzung 'dzin dang log lta thams cad 'joms pas ni rdo rje pha lam dang 'dra /
NK069(tu)001:11465: tshur ni cis kyang mi tshugs pas ni rdo rje brtsan po mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:11466: cho ga lnga ni rdzogs byas shing //
NK069(tu)001:11467: zhes 'jug pa'i cho ga lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11468: sgo gsum zol pog myed pas rdo rje slob dpon mchod cing mnyes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11469: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig ma nor zhing ma nyams pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11470: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas lha'i mtshan nyid ngo shes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11471: sngags gsang ba'i dbang thob nas man ngag gi gnang ba thob pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11472: bsgom sgrub kyi gdams ngag phyin ci ma log par thugs su chud pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11473: rang don cho ga lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11474: ston pa mchod pa la brtson pa /
NK069(tu)001:11477: sngags zlos pa las su rung ba /
NK069(tu)001:11478: phyag rgya cing zhing bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11479: theg pa chen po'i cho ga lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11481: phyi bskyed rims kyi cho ga lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11487: nang rdzogs rims kyi cho ga lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11488: gnas pa rtsa la bsgom pa /
NK069(tu)001:11489: grub pa yi ge la bsgom pa /
NK069(tu)001:11490: rten pa thig le la bsgom pa /
NK069(tu)001:11491: g.yo ba rlung la bsgom pa /
NK069(tu)001:11492: gdam ngag sems nyid stong par bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11493: yo byad lnga ni rdzogs par ldan //
NK069(tu)001:11494: zhes gzhi'i yo byad lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11495: gnas bde zhing yid du 'ong ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:11496: sgrub pa'i grogs mchog dang ldan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11497: gzungs ma mtshan dang ldan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11498: rdo rje dril bu la sogs pa'i sngags cha tshang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:11499: phyi nang gi 'tsho' ba'i yo byad dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11500: sgrub po rang gi yon tan gyi yo byad lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11506: thun mong gi yo byad lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11508: spyir rgyun gyi yo byad lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11509: bdud rtsi lnga sman gyi yo byad dang /
NK069(tu)001:11510: sha lnga gtor ma'i yo byad do //
NK069(tu)001:11511: tshogs sgrub pa'i yo byad lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11512: bza' dang btung ba'i yo byad dang /
NK069(tu)001:11513: rgyan dang bgo' ba'i yo byad dang /
NK069(tu)001:11514: glu tshig dbyangs dang sgra'i yo byad dang /
NK069(tu)001:11516: a li ka li thabs dang shes rab kyi yo byad do //
NK069(tu)001:11517: sngags kyi yan lag lnga rdzogs pas //
NK069(tu)001:11518: zhes bskyed pa rgyu'i yan lag lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11519: mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin mtshan ma myed par bsgom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11520: kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin snying rje chen po bsgom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11521: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin zla ba'i dal h'u dang bcas pa bsgom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11522: thugs phyag rgya bsgom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11523: sku yongs su rdzogs pa bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11524: dgug pa sngags kyi yan lag lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11530: bzlas pa bsgrub pa'i yan lag lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11531: snying khar ye shes sems dpa' bsgom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11532: de'i thugs khar nyi zla'i dal bsgom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11533: de la dam tshig gi phyag rgya bzhag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11534: de la yig 'brus skor ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:11535: zlos tshe spro bsdu'i yan lag lnga'o //
NK069(tu)001:11536: lha'i yan lag spro ba lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11537: thabs kyi lha 'bu ta zhi gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:11538: shes rab kyi lha ye shes sems dpa' /
NK069(tu)001:11539: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i lha sku gsung thugs kyi lha /
NK069(tu)001:11540: dbur rgyan gyi lha rigs lnga'i dbang /
NK069(tu)001:11541: de dag las lha stong du rtsi ba la sogs te lnga'o //
NK069(tu)001:11542: 'bras bu lam rim gyi yan lag lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:11543: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK069(tu)001:11548: ma nyams 'jug la rab brtson na //
NK069(tu)001:11549: zhes gong ma de dag las ma nyams shing /
NK069(tu)001:11550: sgrub pa'i thabs la 'jug pa la rab tu brtson 'grus che na /
NK069(tu)001:11551: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK069(tu)001:11552: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK069(tu)001:11553: dbang sgyur rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK069(tu)001:11554: ces tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyi dngos grub dam pa de 'grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:11555: de yang 'bras bu thob pa'i dus ni /
NK069(tu)001:11556: skal ba rab kyis zhag sum cu phrag drug la zla ba drug yod /
NK069(tu)001:11557: bcu gnyis ni zla ba bcu gnyis lo gcig /
NK069(tu)001:11558: bcu bzhi ni lo gcig dang zla ba gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:11559: bcu drug la lo gcig zla ba bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:11560: zla ba bcu drug gis 'grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:11561: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin la drug ste /
NK069(tu)001:11562: dang po tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyi ngo bo ni /
NK069(tu)001:11563: gsang sngags kyi mthong ba'i lam ste /
NK069(tu)001:11564: 'di nyid las ma lus bdag nyid zhal mthong ba /
NK069(tu)001:11565: dbang sgyur mchog gi dam pa yin //
NK069(tu)001:11568: lha mi khyad par can gyi cha lugs te /
NK069(tu)001:11570: mi dang lha dang tshangs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:11571: skye ba rnam dag 'dzin mod kyang //
NK069(tu)001:11572: khyad par sa la gnas 'gyur yin //
NK069(tu)001:11575: bdag don gyi tshe tshad ni /
NK069(tu)001:11577: tshe ni bcu dang drug pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:11578: brgya brgya dag tu snur zhing gnas //
NK069(tu)001:11580: gzhan don gyi tshe tshad ni /
NK069(tu)001:11581: skal pa grangs myed gnas 'gyur yang //
NK069(tu)001:11582: sku ni shin tu gzhon pa'i tshul //
NK069(tu)001:11584: bzhi pa tshe dbang 'grub pa'i tshad ni /
NK069(tu)001:11585: ma nyams 'jug la rab brtson na //
NK069(tu)001:11586: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam //
NK069(tu)001:11588: lnga pa tshe dbang gang dang sbyor na /
NK069(tu)001:11591: drug pa sangs rgyas 'grub pa'i dus ni /
NK069(tu)001:11592: de tshe bcu drug tshun chad kyis //
NK069(tu)001:11593: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni //
NK069(tu)001:11596: lus dang phung por bcas pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:11597: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin grub //
NK069(tu)001:11598: rig pa 'dzin pa'i tshe nyid kyis //
NK069(tu)001:11599: bla med kun tu bzang por 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:11601: de tshe bcu drug tshun chad kyis //
NK069(tu)001:11602: zhes tshe'i dngos grub de'i tshe /
NK069(tu)001:11603: rig 'dzin tshe lo brgya pa zhig yin la /
NK069(tu)001:11606: tshe lo brgya brgyar snar zhing bsgrub ste /
NK069(tu)001:11607: tha mar tshe lo stong drug brgya tshun chod kyis ni 'grub nges la /
NK069(tu)001:11609: grub pa de gang grub na /
NK069(tu)001:11610: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni //
NK069(tu)001:11612: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK069(tu)001:11613: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku dang /
NK069(tu)001:11615: sprul pa'i sku lnga dbyer myed par lhun gyis grub /
NK069(tu)001:11616: de la thugs ye shes lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:11622: 'phrin las zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun grub lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:11623: nyi shu rtsa lngar lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:11625: de lta bu de ni lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin te de la lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:11626: gzhi' gang dang sbyar ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:11627: gzhan gyi 'gro don byed nus pa dang sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:11628: bden pa gang rtogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:11629: slob pa mthar thug pa'i tshul gyis dbyer myed rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11631: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:11635: ma h+aa yo ga'i lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK069(tu)001:11636: pha rol tu phyin pa'i lam gyi thad ka gang dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:11637: sa bcu pa dang sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:11639: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i don po zhal mthong dgos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11640: de ltar grub pa de nyid rang gi ngo bo gang snang zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:11643: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:11646: lhun gyis grub pa'i slob pa po'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK069(tu)001:11647: mi slob pa sangs rgyas so //
NK069(tu)001:11649: mthong nas nye bar mnyes pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:11652: gcig dang du mar bral ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:11654: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin sangs rgyas sar 'gro ba ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:11655: rang don du sangs rgyas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11656: gzhan don du sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11662: rdo rje lta bu'i ye shes shar nas /
NK069(tu)001:11663: shes bya'i sgrib pa rang dag ste /
NK069(tu)001:11664: 'bras bu sku dang ye shes rang shar nas sangs rgya ba de /
NK069(tu)001:11665: ye shes thig le de nyid la /
NK069(tu)001:11666: ye shes thig le nyid snang ba ces so //
NK069(tu)001:11667: gzhan don du sangs rgya ba nas /
NK069(tu)001:11668: de ltar bdag don du sangs rgyas nas 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal por skye ba bzhes te /
NK069(tu)001:11669: mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad nas /
NK069(tu)001:11670: mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11672: de ltar bya ba kun byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:11673: mthar ni skye myed rdo rje'i sa //
NK069(tu)001:11675: ye shes thig le de nyid la /
NK069(tu)001:11676: zhes ye shes spros pa dang bral ba'i thig le /
NK069(tu)001:11677: chos kyi dbyings de nyid la /
NK069(tu)001:11678: ye shes thig le nyid snang ba //
NK069(tu)001:11679: zhes dbyings rig pa dang ldan pa'i ye shes de nyid /
NK069(tu)001:11680: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las mi bzad pa
NK069(tu)001:11681: rgyan gyi 'khor lor rang snang ba nyid snang ba'o
NK069(tu)001:11682: // bsam gyis mi khyab mtha' yas mchog /
NK069(tu)001:11683: ces de ltar snang ba'i yon tan ni /
NK069(tu)001:11684: bsam gyis mi khyab mtha' yas mchog dang ldan no ////
NK069(tu)001:11689: rtsa ye shes kyi thig le dang /
NK069(tu)001:11690: yi ge ye shes kyi thig le dang /
NK069(tu)001:11691: khams bdud rtsi ye shes kyi thig le dang /
NK069(tu)001:11692: snying po rlung ye shes kyi thig le'o //
NK069(tu)001:11694: spyi bo'i rtsa stong pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:11695: mgrin pa'i rtsa so sor rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:11696: snying ka'i rtsa me long lta bu'i ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:11697: lte ba'i rtsa mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:11698: gsang ba'i rtsa bya ba grub pa'i ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:11699: rtsa lnga dbyer myed ye shes thig le'o //
NK069(tu)001:11706: yi ge lnga dbyer myed pa'i thig le'o //
NK069(tu)001:11712: dri chu bya grub lnga dbyer myed thig le'o //
NK069(tu)001:11718: srog 'dzin me long lnga dbyer myed thig le'o //
NK069(tu)001:11719: 'bras bu ni nyi shu tham pa dbyer myed pa'i
NK069(tu)001:11720: thig le chen po chos kyi sku gcig tu gyur
NK069(tu)001:11721: pa'o // phyogs bcu dus bzhir mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:11722: zhes sngar phyogs bcu dus bzhi na mngon par rdzogs
NK069(tu)001:11723: pa sangs rgyas pa'i zhing khams rnam pa dag pa
NK069(tu)001:11724: yod pa dang / zhing khams rnam dag bsam yas dang //
NK069(tu)001:11725: zhes de'i grangs gdul bya'i blos bsam pa las yas pa sngar sangs rgyas par 'gyur ba rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:11726: rgya dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK069(tu)001:11727: de yod pa yang rgya che chung gi tshad dang bral ba /
NK069(tu)001:11728: rgyu ye shes kyi rin po che las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK069(tu)001:11729: 'khor lo rgyan dang rol mo'i tshogs //
NK069(tu)001:11730: zhes dbus 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i pho brang na /
NK069(tu)001:11732: 'dod yon lnga'i rol mo'i tshogs dang bcas pa kun dang /
NK069(tu)001:11733: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsam yas kun //
NK069(tu)001:11734: zhes de la longs spyod pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dang ldan pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:11735: bde bar gshegs pa ma lus pa kun /
NK069(tu)001:11736: mthong nas nye bar mnyes pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:11737: zhes gang zag rnal 'byor pa bdag lta bu zhig phyis sangs rgyas pa des /
NK069(tu)001:11738: sngar sangs rgyas pa kun gyi zhal mthong nas /
NK069(tu)001:11740: bdag gis yang mchod pa'i khyad par phul /
NK069(tu)001:11741: tshur la yang mchod par snang bas mnyes pas mnyes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11742: rgya chen gsung las don byung ba'ang //
NK069(tu)001:11743: zhes bde bar gshegs pa'i gsung gcig la yang gsung
NK069(tu)001:11744: dbyangs yan lag bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan
NK069(tu)001:11745: pa'i / rgya chen po'i gsung de las chos nyid kyi don 'byung ba yang thos pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:11746: mthun pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:11747: zhes ye nas sangs rgyas pa mi bzhugs pa ma yin bzhugs la /
NK069(tu)001:11749: sgrib pa ni gtan nas spangs /
NK069(tu)001:11750: bsod nams ni dpag tu myed pa bsags /
NK069(tu)001:11751: ye shes ni tshad par skyed pa'i sangs rgyas de kun yang /
NK069(tu)001:11752: yul du byas pa'i bdag gi rigs lo pa na dngos por grub pa zhig la /
NK069(tu)001:11753: bdag gis tshur zhal mthong ba ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:11754: sangs rgyas pa de bzhin du bdag gis kyang sgrib pa 'thun par yangs /
NK069(tu)001:11755: bsod nams ma lus par bsags /
NK069(tu)001:11758: 'thun pa'i ye shes rang snang ba nyid gong ma snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:11759: 'dir gtar kas gags gsal ba la /
NK069(tu)001:11760: ye shes rang snang ba yin na /
NK069(tu)001:11761: mthun zhes gdags su mi stub ste /
NK069(tu)001:11762: dper na mthun zhes bya ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:11763: rig pa rang snang ba'i don dang gnyis 'gal te /
NK069(tu)001:11767: glang gnyis gnya' mthun bya ba dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:11768: mthun zhes zer ba'i sgo nas /
NK069(tu)001:11769: ye shes rang snang ba de mi stub ste /
NK069(tu)001:11770: gong ma ltar snang ba yang /
NK069(tu)001:11771: rig pa las ma rtogs par /
NK069(tu)001:11772: yul gyi dngos por grub pa zhig yod zhes rgal ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:11774: sngar mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pa'i zhing khams rnam par dag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11775: de na yod pa'i rgya che chung dang bral ba'i gzhal yas khang dang /
NK069(tu)001:11776: de la longs spyod pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil
NK069(tu)001:11777: 'khor ma lus pa de dag gi rang bzhin du
NK069(tu)001:11778: snang ba ni / bdag gi rig pa sbyangs par snang ba yin la /
NK069(tu)001:11779: bdag gi rig pa'am sems kyi rang bzhin ni ye nas gnas pa dang mthun par snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:11780: dper na me long nang gi byad dang 'dra bar snang ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:11782: gzugs 'char bar snang ba yang ye nas yod /
NK069(tu)001:11783: byad byung ba dang gzugs rang snang du 'thun par snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:11784: de'i lan ni gcig dang du mar bral ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:11785: zhes pa la sogs kyis lan 'debs so //
NK069(tu)001:11786: gcig dang du mar bral ba yi //
NK069(tu)001:11787: bdag gi rig pa'am sems kyi rang bzhin ni /
NK069(tu)001:11788: gcig dang du mar bral ba yi /
NK069(tu)001:11789: mtha' dang dbus myed de bzhin nyid //
NK069(tu)001:11791: gzhi' dang rtsa la myed pa /
NK069(tu)001:11792: de bzhin nyid chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:11793: sangs rgyas nyid kyang mi gzigs te //
NK069(tu)001:11794: zhes sems las ma rtogs pa'i yul logs shig na /
NK069(tu)001:11795: dngos por grub pa zhig ni /
NK069(tu)001:11796: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi spyan
NK069(tu)001:11797: dang ldan pa'i sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs te
NK069(tu)001:11798: / dngos por grub pa myed la /
NK069(tu)001:11799: rang 'byung ye shes gnas myed snang //
NK069(tu)001:11800: zhes gong ma ltar snang ba ni rang gi rang bzhin du rang byung ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:11801: rang gi rig pa sbyangs pa las byung ba'i ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:11802: dngos po'am mtshan ma'i mtha' la gnas pa myed pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:11803: yod myed kyi mtha' la gnas pa myed pa nyid snang la /
NK069(tu)001:11804: log par rtogs rtags rnam dag cing //
NK069(tu)001:11805: ye shes dbyings las mi gzhan phyir //
NK069(tu)001:11806: thugs rje chen pos 'brel pas na //
NK069(tu)001:11807: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK069(tu)001:11808: zhes de yang 'thun pa'am snang ba'i dpe' ni /
NK069(tu)001:11809: las dang bag chags mthun na /
NK069(tu)001:11810: thun mong phan tshun snang ba 'dra la /
NK069(tu)001:11811: myi 'thun pa la myi snang ba'i dpe' ni /
NK069(tu)001:11812: las dang bag chags mi 'thun pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:11813: lhan cig 'dug kyang mi mthong ba dri za'i grong khyer dang 'dra'o zhes smras pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11815: las dang bag chags mthun pa la snang /
NK069(tu)001:11816: mi mthun pa la mi snang med /
NK069(tu)001:11817: sangs rgyas dang sems can las dang bag chags mi 'thun pas /
NK069(tu)001:11818: ji ltar sems can gyis sangs rgyas mi 'thong ba bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:11819: sangs rgyas kyis kyang sems can mi 'thong zhes rgal na /
NK069(tu)001:11820: sems can gyis sangs rgyas mi 'thong ba ni de ltar bden na /
NK069(tu)001:11821: sangs rgyas kyis sems can gzigs te /
NK069(tu)001:11822: gzigs pa'i gtan tshigs ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:11823: log par rtogs pa rtags shing spyad na rnam par dag pa'i phyir na gzigs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:11824: sems can gyis sangs rgyas mi 'thong ba ni dper na me long dang 'dra ste /
NK069(tu)001:11825: me long la gzugs rnyan snang ba'i rgyu yon tan kyang /
NK069(tu)001:11826: blo 'ur gyi g.yas g.yogs na gzugs rnyan snang ba'i bya ba byed mi nus pa dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:11827: sems can gyi sems ye shes yang dag pa'i rgyu yin yang /
NK069(tu)001:11828: thog pa myed pa'i dus nas /
NK069(tu)001:11829: rgyu nyon mongs pa ma rig pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11830: rkyen gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa blo bur bas sgrib pas /
NK069(tu)001:11831: sangs rgyas mi mthong ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:11832: me long g.yas g.yogs pa dang 'dra la /
NK069(tu)001:11833: de bzhin gshegs pa ni sems can gyi log par rtog pa nyid /
NK069(tu)001:11834: thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes su mkhyen pas /
NK069(tu)001:11835: me long g.yas dag pa dang 'dra ste /
NK069(tu)001:11836: gtan tshigs de'i phyir yang gzigs so //
NK069(tu)001:11837: gnyis pa ye shes dbyings las mi zhan pa'i phyir yang gzigs te /
NK069(tu)001:11838: sems can gyi sems las ma rtogs pa logs shig nas sangs rgyas kyi thugs ye shes myed de /
NK069(tu)001:11839: sems can gyi sems gnas su dag par rtogs pa nyid sangs rgyas kyi thugs ye shes nyid de /
NK069(tu)001:11840: chos kyi dbyings las sems can gyi sems mi zhan pa'i phyir yang gzigs so //
NK069(tu)001:11841: gsum pa ni thugs rje chen pos 'brel bas gzigs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:11842: sems can ni snying rje dang bral ba yin pas sangs rgyas mi mthong ba yin la /
NK069(tu)001:11843: sangs rgyas ni thugs rje dang ldan pas sems can dang thugs rje dang 'brel bas na gzigs te /
NK069(tu)001:11844: dper na las mi 'thun zhing ma 'brel na ni /
NK069(tu)001:11845: rang gi drung na 'dug kyang shi chad dang skyid sdug mi mthong la /
NK069(tu)001:11846: rgya la shi ba mthong yang mya ngan myi byed do //
NK069(tu)001:11848: dbus mtha' 'dug kyang de ma phrad yang /
NK069(tu)001:11849: yig 'phrin gyis blugs nas shi ma shi dang bde'i sdug yod pa dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:11850: sangs rgyas ni sems can dang thugs rje chen pos 'brel bas na /
NK069(tu)001:11851: 'gro ba drug po dus bzhi'i gnas skabs ma lus par gzigs shing des 'dul bar snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:11852: bde' ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK069(tu)001:11853: stangs dpyal gnyis sam yang na lnga //
NK069(tu)001:11854: byas te dang ldan rab zhugs na //
NK069(tu)001:11855: zhes lha mang po bsgom par mi lcogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:11856: ma h+aa su ka bde' chen po'i dkyil 'khor ni yab yum kha sbyor te /
NK069(tu)001:11859: yang na yum bzhi gtso bo dang lnga'o //
NK069(tu)001:11860: don dam byang chub sems dang ldan par bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:11861: dad pa dang ldan pas der zhugs sam de'i ting nge 'dzin du zhugs nas bsgom na /
NK069(tu)001:11864: rang yid du 'ong ba'i yon tan ni /
NK069(tu)001:11865: lha mang po bsgom pa'i yon tan dang mnyam par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:11866: lha mang po bsgom par mi nus pa rnams la ni /
NK069(tu)001:11867: zhi ba stus pa bsgom par bstan pa 'di la ngag don ni /
NK069(tu)001:11868: gang zag sngon sbyangs pa'i las 'phro che zhing /
NK069(tu)001:11870: ting nge 'dzin las su rung ba /
NK069(tu)001:11871: de lta bus lha mang po bsgom na /
NK069(tu)001:11872: bsod nams dpag tu myed pa thob nas /
NK069(tu)001:11873: gang zag las dang po pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11876: lha mang po bsgom par mi cogs pa rnams kyis /
NK069(tu)001:11877: lha mang po'i ting nge 'dzin mi lcogs mi gsal ba bsgom pa bas /
NK069(tu)001:11878: lha gcig gam gnyis gsum tsam gyi don byang chub sems bde' bar dang bcas par byas te /
NK069(tu)001:11880: shes rab zhan yang dad pa che bas de'i sgor zhugs nas sgrubs na /
NK069(tu)001:11881: yon tan lha mang po bsgoms pa dang mnyam par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:11883: bskal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes de //
NK069(tu)001:11884: zhes yi dam gyi lha bzung ba ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:11889: slob dpon gyi yan lag dkyil 'khor lngar bsgom pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:11891: slob mas me tog bor ba'i lha gang la babs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11893: sku'i gzugs snyan bris la gang la mos dri ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:11895: rmi lam 'debs su bcug pas zin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11896: gsum pa de gang la babs cing mos pa'i lha de kho na /
NK069(tu)001:11897: las 'phro dang bskal ba 'thun zhing mnyam pas /
NK069(tu)001:11898: bskal ba mnyam pa'i ye shes kyi lha de la /
NK069(tu)001:11900: zhes don du gnyer zhing sgrubs na /
NK069(tu)001:11901: dngos grub kyi 'bras bu nye bar 'byung ba'i mtshan ma'am brtags ni /
NK069(tu)001:11902: ya mtshan chen po 'byung bar nges //
NK069(tu)001:11903: zhes ya mtshan chen por 'byung ba nges so //
NK069(tu)001:11905: rab sangs rgyas sku lnga lhun grub 'thob /
NK069(tu)001:11906: 'bring rig 'dzin rnam pa bzhi po gang rung 'thob /
NK069(tu)001:11907: tha ma thun mong gi dngos grub sna tshogs pa 'byung ba 'thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:11909: ces spyir dkon mchog gsum la ma dad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11910: khyad par du zab mo'i don la dad myed cing yid ma ches par /
NK069(tu)001:11911: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:11912: sgrubs pa'i 'bras bu myed cing pha rol tu yang
NK069(tu)001:11913: rang 'phung ste ngan song du ltung bar 'gyur ro
NK069(tu)001:11915: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i las //
NK069(tu)001:11916: rdo rje bkod pa gsang ba dam tshig gi le'u ste dgu' pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:11918: // phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang dang dal gyi rim par dgod pa ston pas gsungs pas na ///
NK069(tu)001:11919: 'dir gtar ka gags bsal ba la /
NK069(tu)001:11920: 'dir dam tshig ma gsungs par dam tshig gi le'u bya ba 'gal zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:11922: spyir gsang sngags kyi lus kyis /
NK069(tu)001:11923: dkyil 'khor la brten nas dbang yong /
NK069(tu)001:11924: dbang la brten nas dam tshig yong bas /
NK069(tu)001:11925: dbang dang dkyil 'khor gyi don las mi 'da' bas
NK069(tu)001:11926: na dam tshig ma gsungs yang dbang gi khong na
NK069(tu)001:11928: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos //
NK069(tu)001:11929: zhes le'u dgu' pa dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i rjes de nas /
NK069(tu)001:11932: dga' bas nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:11933: mchog dga' phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:11934: dga' bral gyi dga' bas lha'i bu'i bdud bcom mo //
NK069(tu)001:11935: lhan skyes kyi dga' bas bdag gi bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:11937: dga' ba bcu drug dbang gi nyams myong dang ldan /
NK069(tu)001:11938: 'das pa ni 'jig rten pa'i lam las 'das /
NK069(tu)001:11940: thun mong gi dgyes pa 'dod pa'i 'dod chags la dga' ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:11941: 'jig rten pa'i dgyes pa bsam gtan bzhi'i dgyes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11942: lam pa'i dgyes pa dang po'i mthong lam dang /
NK069(tu)001:11943: khyad par gyi dgyes pa bsam gyis myi khyab pa
NK069(tu)001:11944: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dgyes pa ni chen po ste
NK069(tu)001:11945: / ltos pa tsam ma yin pa'i zag pa myed pa'i dgyes chen po /
NK069(tu)001:11946: rgyal po sbyin pa zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas /
NK069(tu)001:11947: zhes rgyal po sbyin pa ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:11948: dbang yod pas thob pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11952: dper na blon po la sogs pa la /
NK069(tu)001:11953: rgyal pos blon dral stod cing yig tshang byin pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:11954: sa bdag gi rgyal po byed pa pos byed pa yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11955: sa bdag gi rgyal po mi bzhugs na ni /
NK069(tu)001:11956: blon po la sogs pas kyang thabs dang yig tshang mi thob la /
NK069(tu)001:11957: sa bdag gi rgyal po bzhugs na yig tshang dang thabs thob pas /
NK069(tu)001:11958: de ni yod pas thob pa zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:11960: de ltar rgyal pos blon por bskos pa de yang /
NK069(tu)001:11961: chu chun dang nor bu la sogs pa la mi sko ste /
NK069(tu)001:11962: shes pa che la 'dzangs shing dran nyan can yo
NK069(tu)001:11963: gal med pa de lta bu ldan pa la skos
NK069(tu)001:11964: na / rgyal po'i rgyal srid bstan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:11965: rgyal 'bangs yongs kyang bde' bar 'gyur bas /
NK069(tu)001:11966: de ni ldan pas thob pa zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:11968: sa bdag gi rgyal po yang bzhugs la /
NK069(tu)001:11969: 'dzangs mi yon tan dang ldan pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:11970: sa bdag rgyal po bka' ma btags /
NK069(tu)001:11972: blon rkyen ma byin bar du /
NK069(tu)001:11973: blon dral du mi chud cing /
NK069(tu)001:11974: rgyal 'bangs yongs la dbang byar myed de /
NK069(tu)001:11975: sa bdag rgyal pos blon gcad tags /
NK069(tu)001:11976: blon rkyen la sogs pa byin na /
NK069(tu)001:11977: stod rgyal 'bangs byin la dbang sgyur du yod pas /
NK069(tu)001:11978: de ni byin pas thob pa zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:11980: slob dpon dbang thams cad rdzogs shing tshang bar yod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:11981: yod pas thob pa zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:11982: des slob ma snod dang mi ldan pa la skur bas ma thob pas /
NK069(tu)001:11983: snod rtags nas snod dang ldan pa la skur bas thob pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:11984: snod ldan yin pas ldan pas thob pa zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:11985: slob ma snod ldan de la /
NK069(tu)001:11986: gsang sngags kyi bya ba la mi dbang de /
NK069(tu)001:11987: slob dpon gyi dbang bar byed pa'i dbang skur bas /
NK069(tu)001:11988: de'i bya ba byed nus pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:11990: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:11991: 'gro ba'i don du spyir rjod pa las khyad par gyis ched du brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:11992: shes rab thabs yab yum bstan kyi phyag rgya las //
NK069(tu)001:11993: shes rab spros pa dang bral ba'i rtags yum dang /
NK069(tu)001:11994: thabs gzung 'dzin yangs pa'i rtags yab bo //
NK069(tu)001:11995: slob dpon yab yum mi skyod pa yab yum gyi phyag rgyar bsgom pa las ///
NK069(tu)001:11996: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:11997: 'dir zab mo'i dbang gsum la tshigs bcad gcig las ma byung bas /
NK069(tu)001:12000: gsum ka ma tshang na gang rung gnyis chad do zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:12002: gsang dbang slob dpon yab yum gyis skur ba yin /
NK069(tu)001:12003: shes rab ye shes rang nyams su len pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:12004: bde ba chen po 'bras bu yin te /
NK069(tu)001:12005: gsum ka tshigs bcad gcig la dgongs pas so sor phye bas tshang ste /
NK069(tu)001:12008: bde' ba'i 'bru tshogs gsal ba'i rgyun //
NK069(tu)001:12009: zhes yab yum sbyor ba byas pa'i dga' ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:12010: bde' ba'i byang chub kyi sems yi ge h'u gi tshogs bde' ba /
NK069(tu)001:12013: rdo rje'i lam nas pad mor 'khyil //
NK069(tu)001:12014: zhes yab kyi rdo rje'i bam nas /
NK069(tu)001:12015: yum gyi pad mo'i gzhal yas khang du 'khyil lo //
NK069(tu)001:12017: rtse nas stim zhing dkyil 'khor bsgyur //
NK069(tu)001:12018: ces yab kyi rdo rje'i rtse'am /
NK069(tu)001:12019: yum gyi pad mo'i sna rtse nas thig le blangs te /
NK069(tu)001:12020: slob ma'i lce la stim zhing khong du lha'i dal
NK069(tu)001:12021: du lha'i dal du bsams la slob ma'i rtog tshogs
NK069(tu)001:12023: 'dir bshad rgyud thal ba'i dbang du bshad na gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:12029: mi bskyod yab yum du bsgom la sbyor ba bya /
NK069(tu)001:12030: rol pa'i bde ba gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:12031: bde' ba mi dmigs pa shes rab bo //
NK069(tu)001:12032: de yi ge h+aum gi tshogs su gsal ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:12034: yab kyi rdo rje nas yum gyi pad mar 'khyil /
NK069(tu)001:12035: yum gyi pad mo'i sna rtse nas /
NK069(tu)001:12036: byang sems rdo rje sems dpa' nyungs 'bru tsam par gyur nas /
NK069(tu)001:12037: slob ma'i lce la byin nas stims pas /
NK069(tu)001:12038: slob ma'i snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo na /
NK069(tu)001:12039: 'gro ba drug gi sa bon la reg pa dang bcas pa la phog pas /
NK069(tu)001:12041: sa bon tshig ste stong pa nyid las /
NK069(tu)001:12042: ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor du sgyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:12044: mi bskyod yab yum rol pa'i bde ba gsal zhing myi dmyigs pa /
NK069(tu)001:12045: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12046: rdo rje ye shes h'u tshogs kyis //
NK069(tu)001:12047: pad mo'i ye shes bsdus 'khyil ba'i //
NK069(tu)001:12048: nyungs dkar tshad tsam rdo rje sems //
NK069(tu)001:12049: rtse nas lce ru byin pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:12050: rang bzhin chos khams dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK069(tu)001:12051: sa bon zung gsum nyid dang bcas //
NK069(tu)001:12052: gnas ngan len pa gsum sbyangs te //
NK069(tu)001:12053: dmyigs myed sems kyi ye shes lnga //
NK069(tu)001:12054: gsal bas sa bon tshig pa bzhin //
NK069(tu)001:12055: myi skye thabs kyi dbugs phyung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:12058: yab yum lha'i phyag rgya gong ma dang rjes su 'thun /
NK069(tu)001:12059: zil pa thig le sngon lam ltar rgyus nas /
NK069(tu)001:12067: mtshungs ldan gyi rgyu ci yin /
NK069(tu)001:12081: sngon 'byung gi lo rgyus ji ltar bu /
NK069(tu)001:12085: dang po snod gang la skur na gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:12086: thun mong gi snod nyon mongs pa chung zhing nus dbang la sems dad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12087: khyad par gyi snod bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i brtson 'grus gsum ldan no //
NK069(tu)001:12088: mchog gi rgyu gcig la bskur thabs tha dad pa'i nus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12090: phyi rol rdul mtshon rgyas 'bring bsdus pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:12091: nang lus kyi rtsa gnas so so'o //
NK069(tu)001:12094: phan pa'i dbang bcu rdzogs par byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:12095: nus dbang skur ba'i dus so //
NK069(tu)001:12096: snod kyi dus ni nus dbang lnga gang la dang ba dang gang dbang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:12098: gnas lngar dbang lnga rang bzhin gyis gnas pa de la /
NK069(tu)001:12099: rkyen gyis klang nas nus pa lnga thib pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12107: las kyi bya ba byed nus pas na /
NK069(tu)001:12110: rang rang gi gnas lngar dkyil 'khor skyed /
NK069(tu)001:12117: rin 'byung gi rab gnas byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12118: sgom pa la 'phreng ba rang gi yi dam lha'i rab gnas byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12119: phrin las la rdo rje rgya gram don grub kyi rab gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:12120: 'chad pa la 'khor lo 'od dpag myed kyi rab gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:12121: rdo rje rgyal bo'i dbang la rdo rje dril bu kun bzang yab yum gyi rab gnas byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12123: rang la lhun grub tu gnas pa mtshungs par ldan pa'i rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:12124: skur thabs shes pa lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu'o //
NK069(tu)001:12125: rkyen gang gis thob pa ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:12126: rgyu'i rkyen slob ma skal ldan /
NK069(tu)001:12127: slob dpon 'thun pa 'jom pa bdag po'i rkyen no //
NK069(tu)001:12128: de ma thag pa'i rkyen sems lnga skyes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12129: dmigs pa'i rkyen slob dpon dbang rdzogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12131: skur gnas rna ba la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12132: gzhan longs spyod pa dang ldan par bya ba'i phyir bzang btung gis dbang skur /
NK069(tu)001:12133: ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i bya ba'i phyir nang gi snying po lngas dbang skur ro //
NK069(tu)001:12134: de ltar phan pa'i dbang bcu skur na /
NK069(tu)001:12136: dus 'di phyin cad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK069(tu)001:12137: zhes dbang skur bas thob pa'i dus 'di phyin chad /
NK069(tu)001:12138: rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob cing rig pa 'dzin pas na rgyal ba'i sras zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:12139: ngan song thams cad med pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:12140: zhes de ni ngan song gsum du nam yang mi skye ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:12141: yang na skyes na ngan song gi sdug bsngal nyams su mi myong bas thams cad myed ces bya /
NK069(tu)001:12142: tshe ring bde ba phun sum 'tshogs //
NK069(tu)001:12143: zhes lha dang mi'i tshe mthar ring ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:12144: longs spyod kyis phun sum 'tshogs pa dang ldan par 'gyur /
NK069(tu)001:12145: mtho ris lha dang mir skyes na yang /
NK069(tu)001:12146: lha dang mi dbang byed pa'i bdag por 'gyur la /
NK069(tu)001:12147: mtho ris thar pa'i bdag por 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:12148: ces yang na mthar mtho ris dang thar pa'i dbang byed pa'i bdag po sangs rgyas su 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:12149: yang na mtho ris thar pa'i bdag po sangs rgyas su 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:12150: yang na mtho ris thar pa'i bdag po sangs rgyas
NK069(tu)001:12151: bcom ldan 'das nyid du 'gyur bar gdon mi za'o
NK069(tu)001:12153: rtogs par bka' bas gsang ba gsang ba bcud 'dus
NK069(tu)001:12154: pas snying po mi slu bas de kho na nyid
NK069(tu)001:12155: ma nor bas nges pa yang dag pa las /
NK069(tu)001:12156: dbang ma thob bar du gsang sngags kyi bya ba
NK069(tu)001:12157: byar mi rung ba de la dbang sbyin pa'i sa
NK069(tu)001:12158: ste dbang thob nas byar rung ba de la dbang
NK069(tu)001:12159: sbyin pa'i le'u ste bcu pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12161: // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa chen po /
NK069(tu)001:12162: zhes le'u bcu drug par dbang thob nas bcu gcig
NK069(tu)001:12163: pa tshogs bston pas na de bzhin gshegs pa ni
NK069(tu)001:12164: ston pa kun tu bzang po'i /
NK069(tu)001:12165: dgyes pa ni yab yum thabs shes rab dbyer med dang ldan pas na dgyes pa chen po'o //
NK069(tu)001:12166: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i rgyal po sgyur ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas /
NK069(tu)001:12168: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:12169: ces tshogs kyi dal du 'dus pa'i rnal 'byor pa thabs dang shes rab 'brel pas d+r+wa ba /
NK069(tu)001:12170: mtha' gnyis las rgyal bas rgyal po /
NK069(tu)001:12171: ston pa da sdod ting nge 'dzin la zhugs mi dgos na /
NK069(tu)001:12172: ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa tshogs kyi mchod pa
NK069(tu)001:12173: byed pa'i dus su ting nge 'dzin rtse cig pa
NK069(tu)001:12174: la snyoms par zhugs shig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12175: rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs sten pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12177: zhes pa gzhung don du bshad na rgyu gcig par rtogs pa la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:12178: don dam pa ma byung ma skyes skye ba myed pa chos kyi dbyings su gcig /
NK069(tu)001:12179: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid du rig pa rang snang bar gcig /
NK069(tu)001:12180: don dam kun rdzob kyang tha mi dad dbyer med par gcig go //
NK069(tu)001:12181: don dam ni rgyur ma grub /
NK069(tu)001:12184: skye ba myed pa chos kyi dbyings so //
NK069(tu)001:12186: dper na rgya gar na sgyu ma'i sbyor sngags mkhan gyis /
NK069(tu)001:12188: skyes pa dang bud myed dang /
NK069(tu)001:12189: srin po 'bar ba'i gzugs gang 'dod bris te /
NK069(tu)001:12190: sgyur sngags chags shing la tab nas de la brtab pas /
NK069(tu)001:12191: gang 'dod pa'i gzugs su 'gyur ba bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:12192: 'khor 'das kyi rgyu sems su gcig ste /
NK069(tu)001:12193: rkyen rtogs ma rtogs kyis 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos su snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:12195: don dam ma skyes pa nyid kun rdzob sgyu mar snang /
NK069(tu)001:12196: kun rdzob ma skyes pa nyid don dam ma skyes par snang ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:12197: gnyis su rnam par gcig gi dung dang dkar po bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:12199: ces pa yig 'bru'i tshul du rtogs pa ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:12200: chos thams cad don dam par skye ba myed par mnyam pa ni yi ge as mtshon te /
NK069(tu)001:12201: a skye ba myed pa chos nyid kyi gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:12202: don skye myed ni don gyi gsung /
NK069(tu)001:12203: ar brjod pa ni tshig gi gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:12204: kun rdzob sgyu mar cig pa ni yi ge os mtshon te /
NK069(tu)001:12205: a ni sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo chos sku la /
NK069(tu)001:12206: o ni ma 'gags pa'i kun rdzob tu shar ba gzugs sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:12207: skye ba myed pa las skye ba'i cho 'phrul byung ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:12209: don dam kun rdzob dbyer myed pa ni thig les mtshon te /
NK069(tu)001:12210: yid bzhin gyi nor bu dgos 'dod 'byung bas na /
NK069(tu)001:12211: thig le mi 'gyur ba'i thugs yang dag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12212: de ltar kun rdzob dang don dam pa dbyer myed par gcig pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:12213: yig 'bru'i tshul du sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du gcig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12214: byin gyis rlab dang zhes pa byin gyis rlabs kyis rtogs pa ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:12218: sgrub byed rnal 'byor pa de byin gyis rlob par byed pa'i mthu' ni /
NK069(tu)001:12219: sgrub thabs man ngag la yod /
NK069(tu)001:12220: sgrub thabs man ngag byin gyis rlob pa'i mthu' ni /
NK069(tu)001:12221: sgrub bya sangs rgyas la yod de /
NK069(tu)001:12222: dper ras dkar po las dmar por sgyur ba'i mthu' ni rtsod la yod pa bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:12223: chos thams cad rnam par dag cing sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas pa'i don ni /
NK069(tu)001:12224: gang gis rtogs par byin gyis rlob na /
NK069(tu)001:12225: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul gyis byin gyis barloba bo //
NK069(tu)001:12227: zhes mngon gsum par rtogs pa ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:12228: rnal 'byor gyi mngon gsum zad par gyi ting nge 'dzin las su rung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:12229: yid kyi mngon gsum yul 'gags na yul gyi rnam pa gsal ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:12230: dbang po'i mngon gsum yul ma 'gags na thug phrad du gcod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:12231: rang rig pa'i mngon gsum lung rigs man ngag dang myi 'gal bar gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12233: bde bar gshegs pa'i zhal nas nges pa'i don du gsungs pa'i lung tshad ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:12234: bla ma blo dang chos su 'dres pa'i nyams phog pa'i man ngag tshad ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:12235: rang gi rig pas lung dang man ngag gi tshig
NK069(tu)001:12236: zin tsam ma yin par don blo la nos par
NK069(tu)001:12237: rtogs pa ni mngon gsum pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12238: rab tu rtogs dang rnam bzhi yis //
NK069(tu)001:12239: zhes de ltar rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:12240: rab sam mchog tu gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:12241: don phyin ci ma log par gyur pas so //
NK069(tu)001:12242: thams cad mngon rdzogs rgyal po che //
NK069(tu)001:12243: zhes dper na rin po'i gling du phyin tsam na /
NK069(tu)001:12244: thams cad rin po cher gyur pa ltar /
NK069(tu)001:12245: rtogs pa bzhi dang ldan na /
NK069(tu)001:12246: 'khor 'das thams cad dbyer myed par mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas pas che'o //
NK069(tu)001:12247: de ltar rtogs pa dang ldan pas tshogs kyi mchod
NK069(tu)001:12248: pa byas na bsod nams 'thob la rtogs pa dang
NK069(tu)001:12249: mi ldan pa phal gyis mchod pa byas pa la
NK069(tu)001:12251: rtogs pa bzhir rtog par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12252: rtogs pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:12253: ngag don man ngag gi rtogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:12254: gzhung don man ngag gi rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12255: ngag don man ngag gi rtogs pa la drug ste /
NK069(tu)001:12256: gnas lugs bzhi'i rtogs pa bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:12257: mtshon tshul grub mtha'i rtogs pa bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:12258: grol lam lta ba'i rtogs pa bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:12259: thabs lam chags bcas kyi rtogs pa bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:12260: longs spyod rdzas kyi rtogs pa bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:12261: 'bras bu don gyi rtogs pa bzhi'o //
NK069(tu)001:12262: gnas lugs bzhi rtogs pa bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:12264: yi ge dpa' bo 'bru lnga phung po lngar gcig /
NK069(tu)001:12265: yi ge gsum lus ngag yid gsum /
NK069(tu)001:12266: sangs rgyas kyi sku gsung thugs su byin barloba /
NK069(tu)001:12268: sku gsung thugs mi bzad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor mngon du gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:12269: mtshon tshul grub mtha'i rtogs pa bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:12270: re re la bzhi bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:12275: de la rgyu gcig pa'i gzhal bya ni /
NK069(tu)001:12276: 'khor 'das phyi nang gi dngos pos bsdus pa'i chos thams cad do //
NK069(tu)001:12278: rgyu skye ba myed pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:12279: stong par rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12281: blo che na gcig char rtogs blo chung na rim gyis rtogs so //
NK069(tu)001:12283: don dam skye myed rtogs so //
NK069(tu)001:12284: yig 'bru'i tshul gyi gzhal bya ni /
NK069(tu)001:12285: gong gi don dam de rang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:12287: yi ge a o am la sogs pa rnams kyis /
NK069(tu)001:12288: lus ngag yid sgyu mar rtogs par byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12290: kun rdzob sgyu ma blo che chung gis rim gyis dang cig char rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12292: kun rdzob don dam du rtogs so //
NK069(tu)001:12293: byin gyis brlabs kyi gzhal bya ni /
NK069(tu)001:12294: gong gi don dam kun rdzob gnyis so //
NK069(tu)001:12296: bden pa gnyis dbyer myed du rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12298: bden pa dbyer med rtogs tshabs che chung du 'dug pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12300: bden pa dbyer myed rtogs pa de rang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:12301: mngon gsum par rtogs pa'i gzhal bya ni /
NK069(tu)001:12302: gong gi bden pa dbyer myed de rang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:12303: gtan tshigs ni snang la rang bzhin myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12305: yul la yul du mi byed pa de la blo che chung du 'dug pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12307: dbyer myed spyod yul dang bral ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:12308: grol lam lta ba'i rtogs pa bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:12309: re re la gsum gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:12310: de la rgyu gcig par rtogs pa'i gzhal bya ni /
NK069(tu)001:12313: go ba'am rtogs pa gang skye ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:12314: 'khor 'das sems nyid du rgyu cig par rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12315: zhen pa gang grol ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:12316: 'khor 'das tha dad du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa las grol lo //
NK069(tu)001:12317: yig 'bru'i tshul du rtogs pa'i go ba'am rtogs pa gang skyed pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12318: yi ge 'bru gsum gyi sgo nas lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs su rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12319: zhen pa gang grol ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:12320: 'bras bu gzhan nas thob pa ma mnyam nas gzhan nas tshol ba'i zhen pa grol ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:12321: byin gyis rlabs kyis rtogs pa'i go ba'am rtogs pa gang skye ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:12322: rgyu cig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul gyis sku gsung
NK069(tu)001:12323: thugs su rtogs pa'i mthu' ngo shes nas bden par
NK069(tu)001:12325: zhen pa ni mi rdan pa'i zhen pa las grol nas rdan par rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12326: mngon gsum par rtogs pa'i zhen pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12327: mthu' ngo shes nas mi bstan pa rdan par rtogs
NK069(tu)001:12328: pa de sgra tsam ma yin par blo'i gting du
NK069(tu)001:12330: zhen pa gang grol ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:12331: sgra bzhin du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa las grol ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:12332: thabs sam chags bcas kyi rtogs pa bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:12334: spyi bo bde' ba chen po'i 'khor lo na /
NK069(tu)001:12335: thams cad byang chub sems bde' ba chen po rgyu gcig /
NK069(tu)001:12337: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo na /
NK069(tu)001:12338: gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cu 'byung ba'i yig 'bru a li bcu drug go //
NK069(tu)001:12340: rang rig pa bde' gshegs kyi thugs su byin gyis rlob pa snying ka chos kyi 'khor lo'o //
NK069(tu)001:12342: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo nas /
NK069(tu)001:12343: me rlung gi sbyor bas byang sems phab pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:12344: bde' ba mngon gsum du 'char ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:12345: longs spyod rdzas kyi rtogs pa bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:12347: dam rdzas lnga rigs lngar rgyu gcig /
NK069(tu)001:12349: dam rdzas lnga dpa' bo 'bru lngas sbyong /
NK069(tu)001:12351: khams bdud rtsi lngas rang lus sangs rgyas lngar byin gyis rlob /
NK069(tu)001:12352: mngon gsum par rtogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12353: bdud rtsi lnga pa nyid rigs lngar sangs rgyas te /
