NK069(tu)001:12354: ye shes lngar mngon gsum du rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12355: 'bras bu don gyi rtogs pa bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:12356: rgyu gcig pa chos kyi sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:12358: yi ge dpa' bo 'bru lnga longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:12360: chos sku longs sku'i byin rlabs sprul pa'i sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:12362: sku gsum dbyer myed pa ngo bo nyid kyi sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:12363: de ltar rtogs pa ni rab tu rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12364: des thams cad mngon par rdzogs pa sangs rgyas bar che ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:12365: spyi don gnyis pa gzhung don man ngag gi rtogs pa bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:12366: rgyu gcig pa dang yig 'bru'i tshul ces pa la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12367: yab tu bsgom pa bstan cig pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12368: yan lag dbang po rnam shes kun //
NK069(tu)001:12369: zhes tshogs bsgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:12373: ye nas rang bzhin ngang gis lhar gnas pas /
NK069(tu)001:12374: lhar bskyed cing bsgom pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12375: rnam smin du shes par bya //
NK069(tu)001:12376: zhes sems can gyi ltar dngos po dang mtshan ma'i rnam par rtog par /
NK069(tu)001:12377: rnam smin gyi lus nyid ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin du shes par bya /
NK069(tu)001:12379: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin ma rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:12380: rnam par smin pa'i bag chags ltas phung por smin pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:12381: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom //
NK069(tu)001:12384: rnam shes brgyad ye shes lnga /
NK069(tu)001:12385: de ltar tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lhar bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:12387: zhes yang na khro bor bsgom pa la mos na /
NK069(tu)001:12388: yan lag lnga rigs lnga'i khro bo /
NK069(tu)001:12389: dbang po lnga sing ha la sogs pa'i ma mo /
NK069(tu)001:12390: rnam shes brgyad ko'u ri la sogs pa brgyad du bsgom pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:12391: yang na khro bo brgyad du bsgom par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12392: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du lus pa'i yab yum byin gyis brlabs pa la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:12398: yan lag dbang po rnam shes kyi don yab du sbyang /
NK069(tu)001:12399: yul gzugs sgra la sogs pa rnams yum du sbyang /
NK069(tu)001:12401: sems kyi rnam smin ye shes lngar shes par bya /
NK069(tu)001:12402: yul gyi rnam smin yum chos kyi dbyings su shes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12404: yi ge yab kyi dkyil 'khor du bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:12405: mum yum gyi dkyil 'khor du bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:12409: yab rnams kyis ye shes kyi cha gzung /
NK069(tu)001:12410: yum rnams kyis dbyings kyi cha gzung la /
NK069(tu)001:12411: dbyings ye shes su shes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12412: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du 'dus pa'i rnal 'byor pho mo byin gyis rlab pa'i rim pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12413: yum du bsgom pa bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12414: gzugs sgra dri ro reg la sogs //
NK069(tu)001:12415: zhes tshogs bsgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK069(tu)001:12420: lus kyi yul reg bya dang /
NK069(tu)001:12421: bsogs pa'i khongs su ni yid kyi yul du chos so //
NK069(tu)001:12422: rnam smin mum du shes par bya //
NK069(tu)001:12423: zhes yum gyi rnam smin rnams sems can ltar /
NK069(tu)001:12424: yul gyi dngos po dang mtshan mar mi lta bar /
NK069(tu)001:12425: yi ge m+aum chos kyi dbyings su shes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12426: yum gyi dkyil 'khor nyid du bsgom //
NK069(tu)001:12427: zhes yul rnams rigs lnga'i yum gyi dkyil 'khor du bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:12428: 'dod pa'i yon tan drug gi lha mor bsgom par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12429: yang na khro mo'i dkyil 'khor bsgom //
NK069(tu)001:12430: zhes yang na khro mor bsgom na /
NK069(tu)001:12431: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri la sogs pa khro mo'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:12432: 'dod yon drug khro mo drug tu yang bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:12433: gos rgyan ces mchod rdzas byin gyis rlab pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12434: rgyan dang bgo' ba'i yo byad ni /
NK069(tu)001:12435: gos chas lngar dgon pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:12436: 'phreng ba la sogs pa'i rgyan rnams gdags pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:12437: yo byed rang gi ngo bo bstan bza' btud bza' dang btung ba'i yo byed ni /
NK069(tu)001:12438: bza' ba bdud rtsi lnga dang sha bsogs /
NK069(tu)001:12442: ces glu tshig sgra'i yo byad ni /
NK069(tu)001:12443: glu de ngag tu glu drug blang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:12444: tshig de mchod pa'i tshig sngags dang /
NK069(tu)001:12445: bstod pa'i tshigs su bcad pa rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:12446: bro gar bro gar 'dra 'phro'i yo byad ni /
NK069(tu)001:12447: sngags tshig dang bcas pas rkang pas bro barngunga /
NK069(tu)001:12450: zhes de dag mang bar sprul ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:12451: tshogs kyi yo byad de dag yang nam mkha'i sprin phung lta bur sprul lo //
NK069(tu)001:12452: h'u du shes pas rab spyad na //
NK069(tu)001:12454: zhes yo byad de dag h'u thugs rnam par mi rtog pa'i yongs su shes par byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:12456: ye shes la ye shes rol ba'i tshul du rab tu spyad na /
NK069(tu)001:12460: mtshan rtags ngo mtshar can 'byung ba'i dngos grub 'thob cing /
NK069(tu)001:12461: bde bar gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor mnyes pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:12462: bdag dang 'gro ba'i don du mchod pas /
NK069(tu)001:12463: 'gro ba'i don la 'byung ba'i bde bar gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor mnyes par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:12465: lha mo a'i shes rab kyi yo byad sbyor ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:12466: lha mo ni yum mtshan bzang po'o //
NK069(tu)001:12467: yang na gzugs byad phun sum 'tshogs pa zhi zhing nges pa ni lha mo'o //
NK069(tu)001:12468: klu mo klu mo ni yum mtshan 'bring po'o //
NK069(tu)001:12469: yang na mtshan dang ldan pa rtsang sbra che ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:12471: zhes rigs ni yum mtshan tha ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:12472: mtshan dang mi ldan pa gang yang myed do //
NK069(tu)001:12473: yang mtshan dang ldan la spyod pa blang dor rtsang rtsog myed pa ni rigs ngan no //
NK069(tu)001:12475: dbye' 'am yang na mi dbye' bar //
NK069(tu)001:12479: spang blang gi dngos nas byas na /
NK069(tu)001:12483: yang na mi dbye' ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:12485: de bla ma'i drod tshad dang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12488: yum rigs kyi yum lngar phye la /
NK069(tu)001:12489: rigs gang yin du byin gyis brlab bo //
NK069(tu)001:12491: gzungs ma de yum gang yang rung bar byin rlab bo //
NK069(tu)001:12492: go don gnas lugs dang sbyar ba'i snyen bsgrub bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:12494: don dam pa byang chub kyi sems ngo shes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12495: de la ci ste bya zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:12497: dngos po dang mtshan mar brtags pas /
NK069(tu)001:12498: mya ngan las 'das pa las ring du song zhing 'khor bar gnas pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:12499: rnal 'byor ba ni don dam pa'i byang chub sems /
NK069(tu)001:12500: stong pa bdag myed par rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:12502: mya ngan las 'das pa la snyen pas na snyen pa zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12504: don dam pa byang chub kyi sems rtogs pa'i steng
NK069(tu)001:12505: du yang bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum lha'i sku
NK069(tu)001:12506: gsung thugs su bsgom pas te /
NK069(tu)001:12507: de la ci'i phyir bya zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:12508: don dam rtogs pa'i steng du lha sku bsgom pas /
NK069(tu)001:12509: 'khor ba las shin tu yang srings nas /
NK069(tu)001:12510: mya ngan las 'das pa la shin snyen pas /
NK069(tu)001:12511: nye ba'i snyen pa zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12512: sgrub pa ni yum mdun du skyed pa de /
NK069(tu)001:12513: de la ci'i phyir bya zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:12514: sgrub pa'i gazhi'am lam du gyur ba yum yin pas sgrub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12516: yum dang gnyis su myed par ldan pa'i byang chub sems las /
NK069(tu)001:12519: las rtsam pa la sogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:12520: bde' bar gshegs pa'i mdzad pa tshang zhing /
NK069(tu)001:12521: mthar phyin par gnas pas sgrub pa chen po zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12522: snyan sgrub bzhi bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12523: snyen pa dang ni zhes chags lam man dang sbyar ba'i snyen bsgrub bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:12524: snyen pa ni yum dag pa rtsal ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:12525: de yang skye bas dag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:12536: thos bsam gyi rgyud sbyangs pas /
NK069(tu)001:12537: dbang gis shes bya smin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:12539: de la ci ste snyen pa zhes gdags zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:12540: sbyor ba byed pa la snyen pas so //
NK069(tu)001:12542: zhes nye ba'i snyen pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12543: bdag nyid yum lus kyi sha rgyas par byas la /
NK069(tu)001:12544: rlung bzung zhing thig le sbyang ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:12548: lte skog nas rlung me dang mnyam pa las /
NK069(tu)001:12549: yi ge ram las me byung bas spyi bo na
NK069(tu)001:12550: thig le hang mthing kya mgo' thur du lta ba
NK069(tu)001:12551: kha ba 'khyags pa lta bu la phog /
NK069(tu)001:12552: zhu bas 'og gi me mar gsos so //
NK069(tu)001:12553: de nas steng gi rlung bag tsam mnan /
NK069(tu)001:12556: de la sbyor ba byed pa la nye bas na nye bar snyen pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12557: sgrub pa dang ni zhes sgrub pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12558: yum mtshan dang ldan pa de rtsar bzhag la /
NK069(tu)001:12563: de la dang po thig le dbab cing spel /
NK069(tu)001:12565: bzung zhing rim gyis zlog go //
NK069(tu)001:12567: skad gcig ma dang po la dga' ba'i ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:12568: de ni thig le ldang ba'i drod do //
NK069(tu)001:12569: skad cig ma gnyis pa mchog dag'i ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:12570: de ni thig le g.yo ba'i drod do //
NK069(tu)001:12571: skad gcig ma gsum pa dga' bral gyi ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:12573: de'i dus su thig le bzung ka bas bzung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:12574: de yang bde' ba 'dzin pa la ma mkhas na bde ba yun thung bas /
NK069(tu)001:12575: bzung ba la mkhas na lus ngag gi 'gyur ba bya /
NK069(tu)001:12576: gling bzhi ri rab la bsdu /
NK069(tu)001:12578: dar po che rlung la phyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:12579: ngag tu yang h'u zhes drang bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12581: zhes bsgrub pa chen po ni /
NK069(tu)001:12582: lhan gcig skyes pa'i ye shes skad gcig ma bzhi pa la thob pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:12583: thig le bstan pa'i drod do //
NK069(tu)001:12585: de yang zlog pa la ma mkhas na /
NK069(tu)001:12587: zlog pa la mkhas na dud 'gro'i 'gyur ba bya /
NK069(tu)001:12588: rnam gril gyi phyag rgyas dgram /
NK069(tu)001:12590: de nas thig le srung ste /
NK069(tu)001:12591: bde ba skyes te gang bas 'dzag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:12592: gdon dang bag chags kyis rmi lam du 'dzag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:12593: nad gzhi chu dang sdong bas 'dzag /
NK069(tu)001:12594: gzungs ma'i rkyen gyis chags pa skyes te 'dzag /
NK069(tu)001:12595: kha zas mi 'thun pas rang nyams te 'dzag /
NK069(tu)001:12596: spyod lam gyis dang stong ste 'dzag pa rnams srung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:12597: yum gyi pad mo'i gzhal yas su //
NK069(tu)001:12598: zhes yum gyi b+ha ga ni /
NK069(tu)001:12599: rtsa'i dbyibs rim pa gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:12604: rtsa kha kha mu ka e'i gzugs gru gsum du gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12606: rtsa kun rtar ma'i nang nas 'babs te /
NK069(tu)001:12607: kun rdar ma de yang pad ma'i gnal ma ltar 'phra /
NK069(tu)001:12608: chu shing gi snying po ltar drang /
NK069(tu)001:12609: til gyi mar me ltar gsal /
NK069(tu)001:12611: bu ram gyi khra ba ltar 'dzin no //
NK069(tu)001:12612: bde' ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor spro //
NK069(tu)001:12613: zhes yab kyi bde' ba ni yum gyi mkhar spro ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:12616: bde' bar gyi bde' ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:12617: lhan gcig skyes pa'i bde' ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:12618: sangs rgyas kyi thugs lta bu ste /
NK069(tu)001:12622: spang bya ma rig pa las log pa /
NK069(tu)001:12623: thob bya ye shes kyi snang ba ni thob /
NK069(tu)001:12624: de dkyil 'khor lha tshogs kyi rang bzhin du gsang ba yum gyi b+ha gar spro ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:12625: sangs rgyas sprin tshogs ma lus la //
NK069(tu)001:12627: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer gyis /
NK069(tu)001:12628: dus gsum sangs rgyas mang po nam mkha'i sprin tshogs tsam pa ma lus pa spyan drangs la /
NK069(tu)001:12629: bdag gi lus la sdus la /
NK069(tu)001:12631: yang na mdun na gnas pa la byang chub sems kyis mchod /
NK069(tu)001:12632: bdag la tshur mchod par bsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:12633: dgyes mnyam mchog gi sbyin pas stim //
NK069(tu)001:12634: zhes yab yum thabs dang shes rab gnyis su myed pa'i bde' bas dgyes pas dgyes la /
NK069(tu)001:12635: yab yum dbang po'i sgo mnyam par sbyar ba las byung bas dgyes pa mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:12636: lhag pa byang chub sems bde' ba'i mchod pa de mchog yin pas mchog /
NK069(tu)001:12637: byang chub sems la sbyin pa la sogs pa pha rol tu phyin pa drug rdzogs pas sbyin pa /
NK069(tu)001:12638: bdag dang sangs rgyas 'od zer snol mar stims pas na sbyin pas stims zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12639: dngos grub blang ba bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12640: sgrub pa nyi zla'i snying po dag /
NK069(tu)001:12645: yab yum gyi bde' bas sgrub pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12646: nyi ma yum gyi pad ma rag ta dang /
NK069(tu)001:12647: zla ba yab kyi byang sems dkar po ni /
NK069(tu)001:12648: yab yum gnyis kyi lus kyi snying po /
NK069(tu)001:12649: bde ba chen por sangs rgya bar byed pa'i rdzas de dag /
NK069(tu)001:12650: dkyil 'khor rdo rje lce yis blang //
NK069(tu)001:12651: zhes yum gyi b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor nas slob ma'i
NK069(tu)001:12652: lce rdo rje khang seng du sgoms pa yis blang
NK069(tu)001:12653: ngo // 'bras bu ba stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12656: nam ka la bya bzhin du 'gro ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:12657: lus kha dog gsal zhing 'bar ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:12661: tshe nyi zla dang mnyam ste /
NK069(tu)001:12662: sgron me rlung gi tshe dbang gis rig 'dzin thob /
NK069(tu)001:12664: lte ba me long gi ngos ltar 'dred /
NK069(tu)001:12665: ro stod seng ge ltar rdzid /
NK069(tu)001:12666: 'gro ba thams cad kyi yid du 'ong /
NK069(tu)001:12668: lus mi snang bar sbed nus so //
NK069(tu)001:12669: yid bzhin sprin gyi bdag por 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:12670: ces yid la ji ltar bsam pa bzhin 'byung ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:12671: dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che
NK069(tu)001:12672: la rtog pa myed bzhin du dgos 'dod thams cad
NK069(tu)001:12673: 'byung ba dang 'dra bar lhag pa'i byang chub sems
NK069(tu)001:12674: rten cing dang du blangs pa'i tshe /
NK069(tu)001:12675: rnam par rtog pa myed bzhin du dngos grub kyi bye brag kun 'byung ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:12676: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che'am /
NK069(tu)001:12677: dbyar ka'i sprin gyi tshogs las char gyi rgyun 'byung ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:12678: yi ge rin po che'i sprin las dngos grub 'byung ba bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:12679: 'khor 'das kun la dbang byed pa'i bdag por 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:12680: zhing 'gyur mchog dang mchog phran rnams //
NK069(tu)001:12681: zhes skye zhing 'byung ba'i phyir na zhing /
NK069(tu)001:12682: gnas shing rten pa'i phyir yang zhing ngo //
NK069(tu)001:12683: dper na sa gzhi' las lo tog skye zhing 'byung /
NK069(tu)001:12685: de bzhin du sangs rgyas thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:12686: 'byung yang sems can gyi sems nyid dag pa las 'byung /
NK069(tu)001:12687: gnas kyang sems kyi chos nyid la gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:12689: mchog phran ni rta dang glang po la sogs pa byol song ngo //
NK069(tu)001:12690: rnams ni sgral ba'i zhing bcur gyur pa thams cad do //
NK069(tu)001:12691: nyi zla'i dkyil du mkhas pas bzhag /
NK069(tu)001:12694: sgrol mkhan rgyud dang don la mkhas pa'i rnal 'byor bas /
NK069(tu)001:12695: sgral bya zhing gi rnam pa rnams dkyil 'khor du bzhag la /
NK069(tu)001:12697: nga rgyal lag gi 'du byed bsgom //
NK069(tu)001:12698: zhes bdag nyid las kyi he ru ka'i sku phyag
NK069(tu)001:12699: brgya'i ting nge 'dzin gyi nga rgyal du gnas la
NK069(tu)001:12700: / lag pa'i sor mo rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su byin gyis rlabs te /
NK069(tu)001:12701: lag pa rigs lnga 'dul byed kyis sgral bya'i rigs drug sa bon 'dul bar bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:12708: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo na /
NK069(tu)001:12709: chos nyid kyi rtsa zlum po la /
NK069(tu)001:12711: de la lha ma yin gyi sa bon su ser po dang /
NK069(tu)001:12712: dud 'gro'i sa bon tri dmar nag dang /
NK069(tu)001:12714: ye shes kyi rtsa gru bzhi la /
NK069(tu)001:12716: lha'i sa bon a dkar po dang /
NK069(tu)001:12718: thugs kyi snying po h'u gnas /
NK069(tu)001:12719: yon tan gyi rtsa zla kham la /
NK069(tu)001:12720: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid gnas /
NK069(tu)001:12721: yid dwags kyi pre dmar po dang /
NK069(tu)001:12722: dmyal ba'i du dud ka dang /
NK069(tu)001:12724: rang rgyud kyi rtsa gru gsum la /
NK069(tu)001:12727: rtsa de rnams kyi mdo' gcig tu 'dus pas na /
NK069(tu)001:12728: sa'i dwangs ma dar dkar gyi skud pa tsam pa /
NK069(tu)001:12729: khrag gi dwangs 'tshal khu tsam pa /
NK069(tu)001:12730: dbugs kyi dwangs ma gser gyi rlangs pa tsam /
NK069(tu)001:12731: drod kyi dwangs me long nyi ma la bzhag pa'i ngad tsam pa gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:12733: snying po chos sku gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:12734: de ni sems can thams cad la gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:12736: gnas lugs de snying kha na gtso' bo'i tshul du gnas /
NK069(tu)001:12737: gsang ba na pad ma 'dab brgyad la phal pa'i tshul du gnas pas /
NK069(tu)001:12738: gsang dbang bskur na gsang bar gnas pa gal che /
NK069(tu)001:12739: sgrol ba la snying khar gnas pa gal che ste /
NK069(tu)001:12746: bag chags rmi lam du 'char ro //
NK069(tu)001:12749: sgral ba'i rgyud sbyong ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:12752: de nas lag pa la rlung 'drongs par gyur pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:12753: rang gi lag pa'i rtse la sgral ba'i shes pa bsdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:12754: gnas yar ba bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12755: h'u du gyur pas rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:12756: ces sgral ba'i sems nyid yi ge h'u du gyur nas /
NK069(tu)001:12757: rang gi 'dzub mo'i rlung gi lcags kyus drangs /
NK069(tu)001:12758: 'gro ba rigs drug gi sa bon dag nas h'u la 'dus so //
NK069(tu)001:12759: h'u gi 'od kyis sgral bya'i sgrib pa thams cad thugs ye shes su rnam par dag nas /
NK069(tu)001:12760: dbyings su thim pas phyag rgyar 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:12761: zhes sgral ba'i sems can gyi sems des chos kyi dbyings rtogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:12762: mtshan ma myed pa'i dbyings su thim nas h'u 'od du zhu ba las /
NK069(tu)001:12763: rang gi ting nge 'dzin skad cig mas thugs phyag mtshan 'od 'bar bar bskyed do //
NK069(tu)001:12765: ces thugs phyag mtshan las sku yongs su rdzogs par gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:12766: 'od zer 'phro ba dang bcas pas sku shin tu brjid pa /
NK069(tu)001:12767: mtshan sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK069(tu)001:12768: dpe' byad brgyad cu dang bcas par bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:12769: gtsug tu rnam par rgyal bar bsgom //
NK069(tu)001:12770: zhes sgral ba'i sems lhar skyed pa de'i spyi bo'i btsug tu /
NK069(tu)001:12771: ngan song thams cad kyi snying po /
NK069(tu)001:12772: ngan song thams cad las rnam par rgyal ba'i ye shes sems dpa' dkar po /
NK069(tu)001:12774: g.yon mnyam bzhag steng na bdud rtsi'i bum pa rnam pa bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12776: ngo mtshar ngan 'gro thar ba'i thabs //
NK069(tu)001:12781: kun nas nyon mongs pa'i chos ma spangs par spyad kyang skyon gyis mi gos la /
NK069(tu)001:12782: skyon gyis ma gos tsam du ma zad de /
NK069(tu)001:12783: sgral bya de nyid ngan song ngam ngan 'gro las thar ba'i thabs su gyur pas /
NK069(tu)001:12784: thabs kyang de las che ba myed pas ngo mtshar thabs che /
NK069(tu)001:12785: ngan song las thar zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12786: ye nas skye myed de bzhin nyid //
NK069(tu)001:12787: ces a li ka li'i yo byad sgrol sbyor /
NK069(tu)001:12789: don dam par ni ye nas ma byung ma skyes skye ba myed pa /
NK069(tu)001:12790: chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag par rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:12791: sgyu mar snang ba'i smig yor tshul //
NK069(tu)001:12792: zhes kun rdzob sgyu mar snang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:12793: dmig yor dang sprul pa la sogs te /
NK069(tu)001:12794: sgyu ma'i dpe' brgyad ltar snang la rang bzhin myed
NK069(tu)001:12795: pa'i don nam tshul du rtogs pas dmyigs yor tshul
NK069(tu)001:12796: du / sgrol sbyor bya ba kun byas kyang //
NK069(tu)001:12797: zhes de ltar rtogs pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:12798: sgrol sbyor gyi bya ba kun byas sam spyad kyang /
NK069(tu)001:12799: kun rdzob tsam du ni chos thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:12800: sgyu ma'i dpe' brgyad ltar snang la rang bzhin myed par gnas pas /
NK069(tu)001:12801: dngos por grub pa gang yang myed la /
NK069(tu)001:12802: rdul cha tsam yang byas pa myed //
NK069(tu)001:12803: ces don dam par ni rdul phra rab tsam du yang dngos por grub pa myed pas /
NK069(tu)001:12804: sgrol sbyor byas pa gang yang myed zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:12805: dag pa gsum bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12806: snod bcud rgyud rnams dag rtogs shing //
NK069(tu)001:12807: zhes phyi snod kyi 'jig rten yum lnga'i dkyil 'khor du dag /
NK069(tu)001:12808: nang bcud kyi 'jig rten phung po lha'i dkyil 'khor du dag /
NK069(tu)001:12809: shes pa'i rgyud tshogs brgyad ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du dag /
NK069(tu)001:12810: de ltar dag pa rnam pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs
NK069(tu)001:12811: kyis lha dang lha mo'i ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK069(tu)001:12812: rnams su dag pa de rnal 'byor pas de ltar
NK069(tu)001:12813: du rang gi sems kyis rtogs shing /
NK069(tu)001:12814: mnyam pa bzhi bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12815: mnyam gnyis lhag pa'i mnyam gnyis kyis //
NK069(tu)001:12816: zhes thun mong gi mnyam pa gnyis ni /
NK069(tu)001:12817: don dam skye 'gag myed par mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:12818: kun rdzob mtshan nyid bzhi ldan du mnyam pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12819: lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis ni /
NK069(tu)001:12820: kun rdzob phyi snod lha mor mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:12822: don dam du snang ba 'di nyid skor bdun ngo bo nyid kyi rgyur gnas pa /
NK069(tu)001:12823: lhag pa chen po chos kyi skur mnyam par gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:12824: de gnyis kyi yon tan bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12825: dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK069(tu)001:12826: zhes de ltar dag pa gsum dang /
NK069(tu)001:12828: chos thams cad lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang por sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:12829: che ba'i yon tan skyed pa'i zhing du rtogs pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:12830: blang dor thams cad dang ngang gis bral ba /
NK069(tu)001:12831: byed pa thams cad yongs kyis 'od gsal ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:12832: byed spyod tshogs chen gnyis 'gyur nas //
NK069(tu)001:12833: zhes lus kyis skyod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:12834: dbang po yul la 'jug pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:12835: sems kyi dran rtog thams cad dang lus ngag yid gsum gyi byed spyod thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:12836: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs su ma gyur ba gang yang myed de /
NK069(tu)001:12837: de gang yang mi 'gog par spyod pa ni bsod nams kyi tshogs la /
NK069(tu)001:12838: gsal tsam na rang bzhin myed par rtogs pa ni ye shes kyi tshogs /
NK069(tu)001:12839: de ltar tshogs rnam pa gnyis su 'byung bar rtogs nas /
NK069(tu)001:12840: stod tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du tshud do //
NK069(tu)001:12841: yan lag ma nyams yo byad ldan //
NK069(tu)001:12842: ston pa po gang gi bya /
NK069(tu)001:12843: ces dam tshig gzhi'i yan lag ma nyams pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12844: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyams pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12845: ting nge 'dzin mchog gi yan lag nyams pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:12860: sbyor sgrol rnams dang ldan par gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12861: cho ga rdzogs par shes pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:12862: zhes skul tshig dbyangs kyi cho ga dang /
NK069(tu)001:12863: yid zlas pa'i snying po dang /
NK069(tu)001:12866: lus rol mo rnga'i rdung thabs la sogs pa rdzogs par shes pa'i sngags pas /
NK069(tu)001:12869: zhes de lta bu'i rnal 'byor pa gcig gis byar mi tub ste /
NK069(tu)001:12870: nyung yang gnyis dang gsum yan cad nas /
NK069(tu)001:12871: mang na brgya yan cad nas /
NK069(tu)001:12873: rang rang gi lha bsgom zhing sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor du bde' bar gnas la zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:12874: dgos pa ci'i phyir bya na /
NK069(tu)001:12875: nges par legs pa'i dgos pa 'grub //
NK069(tu)001:12876: ces de rnams lta ba mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs pa dang mi ldan yang /
NK069(tu)001:12877: dam tshig ma nyams pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:12878: ting nge 'dzin rtse gcig dang ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:12879: tshogs kyi mchod pa byas na /
NK069(tu)001:12880: 'bras bu nges par legs pa lha dang mi'i go 'phang thob pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12885: lnga dang lnga zhing sbyor ba yis //
NK069(tu)001:12888: yab yum bcu sbyor ba yis /
NK069(tu)001:12889: tshom bu lnga'i lha bkod la //
NK069(tu)001:12892: yum rnams yum du bsgom ste /
NK069(tu)001:12893: khro bo bcu dang khro mo bcu //
NK069(tu)001:12894: h'u ka ra la sogs pa'i khro bo yab bcu dang /
NK069(tu)001:12895: sgra 'byin ma la sogs pa'i khro mo bcu ste nyi shu /
NK069(tu)001:12896: 'khor lo'i tshul du rnam par bsgom //
NK069(tu)001:12897: zhes dbus tshom bu lnga'i dkyil 'khor lha lnga bcu tham pa /
NK069(tu)001:12898: de'i phyi rim 'khor lo la khro bo yab yum nyi shus skor bar bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12900: dbus na rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum la /
NK069(tu)001:12901: shar rdo rje sems dpa' dang /
NK069(tu)001:12903: lhor rin chen sems ma dang yum 'bar ma /
NK069(tu)001:12904: nub chos dang yum dge ma /
NK069(tu)001:12905: byang las kyi sems dpa' dang yum stum mo //
NK069(tu)001:12906: lnga sbyor ba ni tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor dang po'o //
NK069(tu)001:12907: shar gyi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la /
NK069(tu)001:12908: dbus rnam snang dang 'bu ta spyan /
NK069(tu)001:12909: shar sems dpa' dang sgeg mo /
NK069(tu)001:12910: lho rgyal po dang spos ma /
NK069(tu)001:12912: byang legs pa dang sgrol ma spyan no //
NK069(tu)001:12913: de ni tshom bu gnyis pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12915: dbus rin chen 'byung dang ma ma ki /
NK069(tu)001:12916: shar rin chen dang 'phreng ba ma /
NK069(tu)001:12917: lhor nyi ma dang me tog /
NK069(tu)001:12918: nub rgyal mtshan dang zhags pa ma /
NK069(tu)001:12919: byang bzhad pa dang bde' ba ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:12921: nub tu 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la /
NK069(tu)001:12922: dbus snang ba mtha' yas dang gos dkar ma /
NK069(tu)001:12923: shar rdo rje chos dang dbyangs ma /
NK069(tu)001:12924: lhor rnon po dang mar me /
NK069(tu)001:12925: nub 'khor lo dang lcags sgrog ma /
NK069(tu)001:12926: byang smra ba dang 'jin rten ma /
NK069(tu)001:12928: byang gi 'khor lo'i rtsibs bzhi la /
NK069(tu)001:12929: dbus su don yod grub pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:12931: shar du rdo rje las dang gar ma /
NK069(tu)001:12932: lhor srung ba dang dri chab ma /
NK069(tu)001:12933: nub tu gnod sbyin dang dril bu ma /
NK069(tu)001:12934: byang du rdo rje khu tshur dang 'bebs ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:12935: tshom bu lnga pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK069(tu)001:12936: de bzhin rigs dang rdo rje'i rigs //
NK069(tu)001:12937: sku rdo rje de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK069(tu)001:12939: pad mo'i rigs te sku gsung thugs //
NK069(tu)001:12940: kyi gsung pad mo'i rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:12942: khro bo'i tshogs dang ldan pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:12943: zhes khro bo khro mo nyi shu'o //
NK069(tu)001:12944: lha tshogs sum cu tham pa gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:12945: tshom bu gsum gyi lha rnams bsgom //
NK069(tu)001:12948: yum rnams yum du bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:12949: tshom bu gsum pa ni 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la /
NK069(tu)001:12951: shar rdo rje sems dpa' dang sgeg mo /
NK069(tu)001:12952: lhor rgyal po dang spos ma /
NK069(tu)001:12960: lho rnon po dang mar me /
NK069(tu)001:12962: byang smra ba dang 'jig rten ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:12966: dbus na rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum la /
NK069(tu)001:12967: shar sems dpa' dang rtan ma /
NK069(tu)001:12972: rigs kyi rigs te rigs kyi gtso' //
NK069(tu)001:12973: zhes rigs thams cad kyi gtso' bo lta bu rdo rje sems dapa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12974: de yang rigs thams cad kyi rigs rdo rje sems dpa' yin /
NK069(tu)001:12975: rdo rje rigs rang gi gtso' bo yang rdo rje sems dapa'o //
NK069(tu)001:12976: thugs kyi thugs te thugs kyi mchog /
NK069(tu)001:12977: ces thugs thams cad kyi thugs yang rdo rje'i rigs yin la /
NK069(tu)001:12978: rdo rje rigs rnams kyi thugs kyi mchog tu gyur
NK069(tu)001:12979: pa ni rdo rje sems dpa' yin pas rdo rje
NK069(tu)001:12980: sems dapa'o // khro bo'i tshogs dang ldan pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:12981: zhes khro bo yab yum nyi shus skor bar bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:12982: rdo rje rigs kyi yab yum cu ste sum cu'o //
NK069(tu)001:12983: tshom bu gcig pa'i lha rnams bsgom //
NK069(tu)001:12985: dbus rdo rje mi bskyod pa yab yum /
NK069(tu)001:12991: khro bo khro mo'i tshogs chen po //
NK069(tu)001:12992: khro bo rigs lnga dang khrag 'thung /
NK069(tu)001:12994: pho nya phyag rnyan bka' nyan tshogs //
NK069(tu)001:12995: pho nya gnas kyi ma mo ko'u ri brgyad /
NK069(tu)001:12996: phyag rnyan yul gyi phra myen mgo brgyad sing ha brgyad /
NK069(tu)001:12997: bka' nyan las kyi sgo ma bzhi re re la nang ris mang bas tshogs so //
NK069(tu)001:12998: ci bgyi' la sogs tshogs rnams kyis //
NK069(tu)001:12999: dpal gyi las ci bgyi la sogs zer zhing dbang mo nyer brgyad kyi tshogs rnams kyis /
NK069(tu)001:13000: dngos grub las rnams grub par byed //
NK069(tu)001:13001: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub dang /
NK069(tu)001:13003: rnal 'byor pa ji ltar 'dod pa ltar grub par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:13006: sngags 'chang bas dngos grub sgrub par byed pa'i rgyu ni /
NK069(tu)001:13007: mnyam rdzogs lhun grub ngang gnas shing //
NK069(tu)001:13008: chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid gnyis su myed par rdzogs pa chen por lhun gyis grub pa'i don /
NK069(tu)001:13009: shes rab kyis rtogs par byas la /
NK069(tu)001:13010: rtogs pa'i ngang la ting nge 'dzin gyis rang rtse gcig tu gnas shing /
NK069(tu)001:13011: spyod pas ci la'ang thogs myed pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:13012: spyod pas kyang bzang ngan dang dbye' gsal dang blang dor myed par /
NK069(tu)001:13013: ci la yang thogs pa myed par spyod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13014: thams cad ye nas dbyer myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13015: de ltar chos thams cad lta bas kyang ye nas sangs rgyas par rtogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:13016: spyod pas 'jug pa dbyer myed par spyod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13017: rdo rje'i ris su thams cad bskyil //
NK069(tu)001:13018: zhes rdo rje rigs su rnal 'byor pa du yod pa thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:13020: yang na sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid der rnal
NK069(tu)001:13021: 'byor pa yab yum du yod pa thams cad ma
NK069(tu)001:13022: lus pa sku gsung thugs kyi lha de bsgom mo
NK069(tu)001:13024: zhes de ltar bsgom pa yang so so'i ting nge 'dzin la bsgom la /
NK069(tu)001:13025: de yang ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i rtags /
NK069(tu)001:13026: sku las yang dag pa'i ye shes kyi 'od 'phro bar bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:13027: 'dir ngag don du tshom bu gcig pa nas 'go'
NK069(tu)001:13028: gzung nas grangs myed par bstan pa la gnyis te
NK069(tu)001:13031: rigs chung ni gtso' bo rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum la /
NK069(tu)001:13033: phyogs kyi khro bo yab yum brgyad de bco' brgyad do //
NK069(tu)001:13035: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum la /
NK069(tu)001:13036: sa'i snying po dang sgeg mo gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:13037: byams pa dang spos ma gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:13038: gshin rje dang lcags kyu gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:13039: kun po yab yum dang dmyal ba'i thub pa ste bcu gcig go //
NK069(tu)001:13040: mdor na rdo rje'i rigs yod tshad rnams bsgom pas na /
NK069(tu)001:13041: rdo rje'i rigs su thams cad dkyil ces pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13042: chags myed tshul gyis stim par bya //
NK069(tu)001:13044: chags pa myed pa'i mthar phyin pa'i tshul gyis /
NK069(tu)001:13045: phyi nang gi ba spu'i bu ga nas /
NK069(tu)001:13046: ye shes kyi 'od zer yang snol mar stim par bya /
NK069(tu)001:13047: de ltar yab yum gnyis su med pa'i 'od zer thim par gyur nas /
NK069(tu)001:13048: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub thob par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:13049: gnyis myed gyur nas phyag rgya che //
NK069(tu)001:13051: phyi nang gi ba spu'i bu ga nas ye shes kyi 'od zer snol mar 'phros pa las /
NK069(tu)001:13052: yab yum gnyis su myed par 'od zer snol mar phan tshun stim pas /
NK069(tu)001:13053: de ltar byas na phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub thob pa'i rig 'dzin thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:13054: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin la lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:13056: gzhan gyi 'gro don byed nus pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13058: spyi las skyed gdon du myed pa'i tshul gyis dbyer myed rtogs /
NK069(tu)001:13059: 'o na tshe dbang dang khyad ci zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13060: bye brag lnga bsal mi gsal gyi khyad yod pas so //
NK069(tu)001:13062: gnyis myed gyur nas phyag rgya che'o //
NK069(tu)001:13063: yang na rang lugs phyag rgya che'o //
NK069(tu)001:13064: sgoms pas mngon du gyur pa'i lha /
NK069(tu)001:13065: mtshan dang dpe' byad mngon shes ldan /
NK069(tu)001:13066: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin grags ces so //
NK069(tu)001:13068: kri ya'i phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK069(tu)001:13072: mtshan nyid kyi lam gyi mo tshod sa brgyad pa mi g.yo' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:13073: yang na sku gsung thugs nyid de //
NK069(tu)001:13074: zhes yang na tshom bu gsum du bsgom na /
NK069(tu)001:13077: mi bskyod pa thugs kyi bdag nyid der /
NK069(tu)001:13078: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK069(tu)001:13079: zhes rnal 'byor pa yab yum du yod pa thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:13083: thugs mi bskyod pa de sku gsung thugs kyi lhar bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:13085: zhes der bsgom pa yang so so'i ting nge 'dzin bsal bar bsgom la /
NK069(tu)001:13086: phyi nang gi ba spu'i bu ga nas ye shes kyi 'od zer 'phro ba yang /
NK069(tu)001:13087: gnyis myed dbyings kyi ngang du thim //
NK069(tu)001:13088: zhes yab yum gnyis su myed pa'i 'od zer snol mar phan tshun du stim par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:13089: tshom bu gsum pa bsgom pa la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:13096: rnam snang yab yum rigs chung dang bcas pa yab yum bcu /
NK069(tu)001:13097: snang ba mtha' yas yab yum rigs chung dang bcas pa yab yum bcu /
NK069(tu)001:13098: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs chung yab yum dang bcas pa bcu /
NK069(tu)001:13099: steng 'og gi khro bo yab yum bor ba'i bcu drug ste bzhi bcu zhe drug go //
NK069(tu)001:13103: lha dang dud 'gro'i thub pa gnyis so //
NK069(tu)001:13110: mi bskyod pa yab yum la /
NK069(tu)001:13112: byams pa dang ngu pe ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:13113: gshin rje yab yum rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:13115: sku gsung thugs su rtogs tshad kyi lha bsgom pas na /
NK069(tu)001:13116: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs /
NK069(tu)001:13119: gong nas yang tshom bu bsgom pa bstan /
NK069(tu)001:13121: le'u gcig la lan gnyis 'dabs so zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13123: gong du gsungs pa rnams ni /
NK069(tu)001:13124: tshom bu bsgom pa'i dmyigs bstan pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:13125: 'og ma 'di rnams ni bsgom pa'i thabs dngos bstan pa yin pas 'gal ba myed do //
NK069(tu)001:13128: dngos grub kyi mchog rig 'dzin gyi dngos grub yang thob par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:13130: dkyil 'khor ma lus pa 'od 'bar ba yang 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:13131: nyon mongs sdug bsngal sel bar mdzad //
NK069(tu)001:13132: las dang nyon mongs pa'i sdug bsngal sel bar byed /
NK069(tu)001:13133: rdo rje'i rigs su skye ba'i gnas //
NK069(tu)001:13134: sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i rigs su gdung tshob pas na /
NK069(tu)001:13135: lha'i sku gsung thugs dang dbyer myed pas na rdo rje'o //
NK069(tu)001:13136: lha dang dbyer myed du skye'o //
NK069(tu)001:13137: sngags 'chang dngos grub yang dag ni //
NK069(tu)001:13138: rnal 'byor pa sngags 'chang ba rnams kyi /
NK069(tu)001:13139: dngos grub sgrub pa'i thabs yang dag pa ma nor ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:13140: thabs dang shes rab thams cad kyis //
NK069(tu)001:13141: zhes rnal 'byor pa yab thams cad kyi thabs yab rnams bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:13142: yum thams cad kyis shes rab yum rnams bsgom ste /
NK069(tu)001:13144: zhes rnal 'byor pas rigs lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:13149: khro mo rnams rigs lnga'i tshom bu lnga bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:13150: chags pa myed pa'i tshul gyis ni //
NK069(tu)001:13151: de yang chags tsam na chags pa myed pa'i mthar phyin pa'i tshul gyis ni /
NK069(tu)001:13152: tshom bu lnga pa la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:13153: rigs chung du bsgom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13154: rigs bye brag pa bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13156: rigs lnga yab yum la rigs chung gis skor bas lnga bcu /
NK069(tu)001:13157: khro bo yab yum nyi shu ste bdun cu'o //
NK069(tu)001:13158: rigs bye brag par bsgom na /
NK069(tu)001:13160: shar du rdo rje sems dpa' la /
NK069(tu)001:13161: rdo rje rigs kyi sems dpa' /
NK069(tu)001:13164: lhor rin 'byung la rin chen rigs kyi sems dpa' /
NK069(tu)001:13165: nam mkha'i snying po dang 'phreng ba /
NK069(tu)001:13166: sgrib sel dang me tog ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:13167: nub tu snang ba mtha' yas la /
NK069(tu)001:13168: spyan ras gzigs dang glu ma /
NK069(tu)001:13169: kun bzang dang a lo ka'o //
NK069(tu)001:13170: byang du don yod grub pa yab yum la /
NK069(tu)001:13171: phyag na rdo rje dang nir ti ma /
NK069(tu)001:13173: thub drug kun bzang bar khyams /
NK069(tu)001:13174: sgo bzhi khro bo yab yum brgyad do //
NK069(tu)001:13175: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis tshom bu lngar bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13176: me ri la khro bo bcu bsgom pa yang mi 'gal lo //
NK069(tu)001:13177: 'od gzer rnam pa mang po spro //
NK069(tu)001:13178: phyi nang gi ba spu'i bu ga nas ye shes kyi 'od zer rnam pa mang po spros pas /
NK069(tu)001:13179: gnyis su myed par stim par bya //
NK069(tu)001:13180: yab yum gnyis su myed par 'od zer gyis bstim par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:13181: dngos grub mchog gi snying po 'grub //
NK069(tu)001:13182: ces de ltar byas pas dngos grub kyi mchog tu gyur pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:13184: mchog lhun grub kyi rig 'dzin la /
NK069(tu)001:13185: snying po chos skur sbyor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:13186: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin la lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:13187: dang po gzhi' gang dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:13188: gzhan don byed nus pa dang sbyar /
NK069(tu)001:13190: slob pa mthar thug pa'i tshul gyis dbyer myed rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13196: dngos grub mchog gi snying po 'grub /
NK069(tu)001:13198: sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:13203: rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa yo ga'i lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK069(tu)001:13204: pha rol tu phyin pa'i lam gyi thad ka gang tsam dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:13205: sa bcu pa chos kyi sprin dang lam gyi mo tshod sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:13206: 'dir gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:13207: tshom bu gcig pa bsgom pas phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin thob ste /
NK069(tu)001:13208: gnyis med gyur nas phyag rgya che zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:13209: tshom bu gsum pa bsgom pas lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin thob ste /
NK069(tu)001:13212: tshom bu lnga pa sgoms pas yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'grub ste /
NK069(tu)001:13213: dngos grub mchog gi snying po 'grub /
NK069(tu)001:13215: dang po nas tshom bu lnga pa bsgom par rigs zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13217: blo rim gyis dang po tshom bu gcig pa /
NK069(tu)001:13219: de nas lnga pa bsgom po'o //
NK069(tu)001:13220: 'o na tshom bu gcig sgoms pas /
NK069(tu)001:13221: lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK069(tu)001:13222: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas mi 'thob sam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13223: des na blo rims su khyad yod pa las /
NK069(tu)001:13224: mthar phyin na tshom bu gcig la mthar phyin pas kyang chog ste /
NK069(tu)001:13225: ye shes rgyal po stangs dpyal bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:13226: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kun /
NK069(tu)001:13227: ma lus par ni bsgom par 'gyur /
NK069(tu)001:13229: rnal 'byor thabs dang shes rab kyis //
NK069(tu)001:13230: tshogs sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:13232: yum shes rab kyi rang bzhin gyis /
NK069(tu)001:13233: yab thabs kyis rigs lnga'i de bzhin gshegs pa bsgom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13234: de bzhin gshegs dang yum du bsgom //
NK069(tu)001:13235: yum gyis de bzhin gshegs pa'i yum du bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:13236: sems dpa' sems ma nyid du bsgom //
NK069(tu)001:13238: 'khor mo rnams sems ma nyid du bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:13239: so so'i sngags dang phyag rgya dang /
NK069(tu)001:13240: rigs lnga dang sems dpa' gang bsgom yang rung ste /
NK069(tu)001:13241: so so lha gang bsgom pa'i sngags dang phyag rgya dang /
NK069(tu)001:13242: ting 'dzin yang dag so sor gsal //
NK069(tu)001:13244: yang dag pa ma nor ba /
NK069(tu)001:13245: so sor gang bsgom pa de'i ting nge 'dzin gsal bar bya /
NK069(tu)001:13246: mdor na mi res lha re bsgrub par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:13247: gnas dang longs spyod ci bde dang //
NK069(tu)001:13248: de ltar bsgrub pa'i dus ni /
NK069(tu)001:13249: ji ltar dga' zhing yid du 'ong ba'i gnas dang /
NK069(tu)001:13250: 'dod pa'i longs spyod yo byad ci bder spyod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13251: ma nyams blo ni rab ldan pas //
NK069(tu)001:13252: zhes rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig mnos pa las mi 'da' ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:13253: gnyis su med par rtogs pas shes rab kyi blo dang ldan par /
NK069(tu)001:13254: dang po dam mnos bzhin du bya //
NK069(tu)001:13255: zhes sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor ni dang po tshom bu gcig pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13257: lnga pa gang yang rung bar dam bcas pa bzhin du sgrub par bya /
NK069(tu)001:13258: slob dpon la rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nos pa las mi 'da' bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:13259: ngag don du phun sum tshogs pa la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:13260: dang po gnas phun sum 'tshogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:13262: bde bar gshegs pa'i zhabs kyis bcags pas bkra shis pa'i gnas dang /
NK069(tu)001:13263: sngon grub ba thob pas byin rlabs che ba'i gnas dang /
NK069(tu)001:13264: sa phyogs rang bzhin gyis bkra shis pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13265: lha dang mi mang pos basngagasa pa brjod pa'i gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:13266: gnyis pa yo byad phun sum 'tshogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:13268: bsgrub pa rdzas kyi yo byad dang /
NK069(tu)001:13269: sgral ba zhing gi yo byad dang /
NK069(tu)001:13270: sbyor ba yum gyi yo byad dang /
NK069(tu)001:13271: rkyen bzlog rdzas kyi yo byad dang /
NK069(tu)001:13272: dam rdzas mchod pa'i yo byad do //
NK069(tu)001:13275: bgegs bzlog pa'i gu gul phur bu /
NK069(tu)001:13276: nad khams bzlog pa'i sman no //
NK069(tu)001:13279: gsum pa sgrub pa po phun sum 'tshogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:13280: ma nyams blo ni rab ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:13284: yum lha grangs dang mnyam pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13285: de rnams yang dam tshig ma nyams pa /
NK069(tu)001:13286: lta ba'i blo rab tu ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13287: bzhi pa bsgrub thabs phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:13289: gang bsgrub mthar phyin par byed pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:13290: dang po dam mnos bzhin du bya ces so //
NK069(tu)001:13291: le lo bsgyid snyoms myed pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:13292: zhes de ltar bsgrub pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:13293: spang bya ni le lo dang /
NK069(tu)001:13294: bsgyid snyoms myed par byas la bsgrub /
NK069(tu)001:13295: blang bya ni lus ngag yid kyi brtson 'grus drag po byas pa yis /
NK069(tu)001:13296: the rtsom myed par sgrub byas na //
NK069(tu)001:13297: zhes de yang sgrub pa'i thabs de ltar yin nam /
NK069(tu)001:13299: sgrub pa ni grub bam mi grub mnyam pa'i the rtsom can ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:13300: sgrub pa'i thabs bya 'di kho na ltar yin /
NK069(tu)001:13301: 'di ltar sgrubs na gang bsgrub grub par nges la /
NK069(tu)001:13302: de ltar yid ches shing the rtsom myed par bsgrub par byas na /
NK069(tu)001:13304: ces 'bras bu bde' bar gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad 'od 'bar bar 'grub par gyur /
NK069(tu)001:13305: de yang tshom bu gcig pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13308: gsum po gang bsgrub pa de grub par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:13309: rdo rje gsang mchog dam pa 'thob //
NK069(tu)001:13310: ces sku gsung thugs rdo rje dbyer myed par de rang bzhin gyis rtogs par bka' bas gsang /
NK069(tu)001:13311: dngos grub mchog gi yon tan dam pa dang ldan pa 'thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:13312: de yang sku lnga lhun grub kyi sangs rgyas thob par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:13313: sgrub pa'i zhag dang tshes grangs ni //
NK069(tu)001:13314: rgyud las smos pa bzhin du bshad //
NK069(tu)001:13315: ces sgrub pa du byed pa'i zhag grangs ni /
NK069(tu)001:13317: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam /
NK069(tu)001:13319: bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis /
NK069(tu)001:13322: dang po dam mnos bzhin du bya /
NK069(tu)001:13324: dang po tshes grangs de la zhugs nas /
NK069(tu)001:13325: tha ma tshes grangs gang la 'don pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:13326: rgyud 'di nyid bshad pa bzhin du thob par bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:13327: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:13328: rgyud las smos pa bzhin du bshad /
NK069(tu)001:13329: ces pa 'di rgyud ma yin nam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13332: zhag ni sum cu phrag drug gam /
NK069(tu)001:13335: dang po dam mnos bzhin du bya /
NK069(tu)001:13337: rdo rje gsang ba'i tshig tu'o //
NK069(tu)001:13338: zhes gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pas gsang ba'i tshig tu bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:13339: ces de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la ched du kleng ngo //
NK069(tu)001:13340: tshogs sgrub ba'i thabs de 'gro ba'i don ched du /
NK069(tu)001:13341: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:13342: rtogs par ka bas gsang ba /
NK069(tu)001:13344: mi slu bas de kho na nyid /
NK069(tu)001:13346: de lta bu'i rgyud zab mo las so //
NK069(tu)001:13347: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyi le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13350: 'byor ldan yo byad kyi tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:13352: tshogs gnyis rjogs pa'i tshogs so //
NK069(tu)001:13353: de yang bshad rgyud rdo rje las /
NK069(tu)001:13356: 'byor pa'i longs spyod ldan pa ni //
NK069(tu)001:13357: bde' ba'i longs spyod tshogs su bshad //
NK069(tu)001:13358: lha dang dam can kun 'dus pa //
NK069(tu)001:13359: 'dus pa chen po'i tshogs su bshad //
NK069(tu)001:13360: thams cad spyod la mi 'dzin pa //
NK069(tu)001:13361: tshogs gnyis rgyun du rdzogs byed pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:13362: tshogs chen po ru nges par bshad //
NK069(tu)001:13364: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa dgyes pa chen po /
NK069(tu)001:13365: zhes le'u bcu gcig par tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bstan nas /
NK069(tu)001:13366: le'u bcu gnyis par tshogs bsgrub pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:13367: nyan thos ltar bka' thub dang /
NK069(tu)001:13368: sdug bsngal gyis sgrub pa ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:13369: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la dgyes pa chen pos spyod cing sgrub pas na /
NK069(tu)001:13370: rol pa'i sprin rnam par spros te //
NK069(tu)001:13371: zhes sgrub pa'i thabs yang snang la rang bzhin myed pas rol mo dang 'dra /
NK069(tu)001:13372: sgrub pa'i 'bras bu yang dngos po gcig tu ma
NK069(tu)001:13373: grub cing cir yang sgyur du stub pas rol mo
NK069(tu)001:13374: dang 'dra / de lta bu'i dngos grub bsgrub pa'i thabs dang 'bras bu mang po sprin dang 'dra'o //
NK069(tu)001:13375: rgyan bkod pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas //
NK069(tu)001:13376: zhes kun tu bzang po'i thugs ye shes nyid thabs shes rab tu ldan la /
NK069(tu)001:13377: thabs dang shes rab gcig gi rgyan du gcig 'gyur bas rgyan bkod pa'i ting nge 'dzin to //
NK069(tu)001:13378: 'gro ba'i don la ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:13379: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:13381: zhi ba'i lha sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su bsgom kyang rung /
NK069(tu)001:13382: rigs lnga'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom kyang bsgom kyang rung /
NK069(tu)001:13383: zhi khro gang bsgom yang rung ste /
NK069(tu)001:13384: sgyu 'phrul dra ba thabs shes rab gnyis su 'brel ba'i don /
NK069(tu)001:13385: shes rab kyis kyang rtogs par byas la /
NK069(tu)001:13386: ting nge 'dzin gyis kyang mngon gsum dang 'dra bar rdzogs par bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13388: zhes de ltar lha'i dkyil 'khor rtse gcig tu bstan
NK069(tu)001:13389: zhing mi 'gyur ba'i ting nge 'dzin du bsgom pa
NK069(tu)001:13390: yang rang gi blo sems las su rung na /
NK069(tu)001:13391: rig pa skad cig ma cig la dus gcig tu rdzogs par bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13398: zhes bdag lha'i skur bsgom nas /
NK069(tu)001:13399: rkang pas bro brdung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:13400: lag pas gar bya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:13403: sems can gyi don byed par bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:13404: de yang lus kyi yan lag lnga la tshom bu lnga'i lha bsgom par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:13406: ces de'i rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK069(tu)001:13407: bdag gi lus ri brag la thogs pa myed par 'dzul ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:13408: gar gyis nam ka la bya bzhin du 'gro ba'i dngos grub thob par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:13410: de nas thams dang shes rab gnyis //
NK069(tu)001:13411: lta spyod ya char ma gyur na //
NK069(tu)001:13412: dkyil 'khor bdag la gsal bsgom nas //
NK069(tu)001:13413: dbus nas shar du kha ltas nas //
NK069(tu)001:13414: rkang pa'i stabs chen skyod byas shing //
NK069(tu)001:13415: lag gi 'du byed kun skyod nas //
NK069(tu)001:13416: bro dang gar gyi phyag rgya bya //
NK069(tu)001:13418: glu tshig sgra'i yo byad ni /
NK069(tu)001:13419: glu tshig sgra'i phyag rgyas ni //
NK069(tu)001:13422: mi rtogs pa rgyud la skyed pa'i tshig dang bstod pa bya /
NK069(tu)001:13423: des 'phags pa'i thugs dam gyi rgyud skul /
NK069(tu)001:13424: 'gro ba la theg pa sna tshogs kyi chos ston pa'i sgra bsam yas pa sgrags pa yis /
NK069(tu)001:13425: chos kyi dngos grub mchog thob 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:13428: 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa'i skad kyi bye brag rnams la rda sprad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13429: bdag gi skad kyis stong gsum du go zhing thos pa'i dngos grub yong /
NK069(tu)001:13431: glu dbyangs tshig gi sgra sgrags pas //
NK069(tu)001:13432: phyogs bcu'i skye gnas ma lus kun //
NK069(tu)001:13433: rdo rje lhun grub skur mthong zhing //
NK069(tu)001:13434: chos kyi dung chen sgra yang thos //
NK069(tu)001:13436: rgyan bgo' ba'i yo byad ni /
NK069(tu)001:13437: brgyan dang bgo' ba'i phyag rgya yis //
NK069(tu)001:13439: lus la do shal dang phyag dub la sogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:13444: yon tan gyi chos gos dang /
NK069(tu)001:13445: mdzad pa las kyi phu rung dang /
NK069(tu)001:13446: yang khro bo'i chas brgyad kyi gos yang gon la /
NK069(tu)001:13448: ces 'od kyis lha'i dkyil 'khor du byin gyis brlabs pa'i phyag rgya yis dgos na /
NK069(tu)001:13449: lus la 'od 'bar ba'i lha dang mi'i rgyal po /
NK069(tu)001:13450: dpung bzhi'i tshogs kyis thub pa myed pa grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:13452: bzang mdzes legs pa'i gos bgos nas //
NK069(tu)001:13454: de nas mthar thug myed kyi bar //
NK069(tu)001:13455: ye shes lnga yis rgyan par 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:13457: bza' dang btung ba'i yo byad /
NK069(tu)001:13458: bza' dang btung ba'i phyag rgyas ni //
NK069(tu)001:13460: bza' ba tshogs kyi zhal zas bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13461: btung ba mdza' gad dpa' bo la sogs pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:13462: lha'i sku phyag rgyar byin gyis brlabs la /
NK069(tu)001:13463: lha la lha thim pa'i tshul gyis mchod pas ni /
NK069(tu)001:13464: yid bzhin sku dang bdud rtsi 'grub //
NK069(tu)001:13466: yid la ji ltar bsams pa bzhin du 'grub /
NK069(tu)001:13467: bdag gi ngag gis bdud rtsi chu 'byung bar 'grub /
NK069(tu)001:13469: lus me long g.ya' dag pa ltar gnas /
NK069(tu)001:13470: snod bcud dang bcas pa'i 'gro ba 'jig rten thams cad sa ler snang bar 'grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:13472: spyan gyis gzigs dang snyan gyis bsan //
NK069(tu)001:13473: dri dang ro dang reg pa rnams //
NK069(tu)001:13474: thabs dang shes rab nyid gnas shing //
NK069(tu)001:13475: bde' mchog ro la myong bar byed //
NK069(tu)001:13477: a li ka li thabs shes rab kyi yo byad /
NK069(tu)001:13478: a li ka li'i phyag rgya yis //
NK069(tu)001:13479: zhes dgongs te bshad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:13480: a li ni shes rab ste /
NK069(tu)001:13481: kun tu bzang mor shes pas /
NK069(tu)001:13482: yum la sbyor ba'i man ngag go //
NK069(tu)001:13484: kun tu bzang por shes pas /
NK069(tu)001:13485: yab kyis sgrol ba'i man ngag go //
NK069(tu)001:13486: thabs shes rab gnyis myed do //
NK069(tu)001:13488: ces des sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rnam gsum thams cad dang /
NK069(tu)001:13489: las rnam bzhi'i dngos grub thams cad dang /
NK069(tu)001:13490: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thabs dang shes rab gnyis su myed bar 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:13491: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:13492: yo byad lnga las 'bras bu la khyad che chung byung bas /
NK069(tu)001:13493: dang po nas a li ka li'i phyag rgya mi spyod zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13496: gcig la gcig rten pa yin te /
NK069(tu)001:13497: snga ma snga ma rgyu yin la /
NK069(tu)001:13498: phyi ma phyi ma 'bras bu yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:13499: de bas na gzhan 'byongs nas sdod a li ka li'i spyod dgos par bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13500: mtshan nyid gsum gyis lam gyi gzhung srang ba bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:13502: zhes rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:13503: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa sdus pa'i chos thams cad dam /
NK069(tu)001:13504: rtsa ba sems dang sems su snang bas sdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:13505: da bzod lam gyis ma bsgrubs /
NK069(tu)001:13507: ye sdod ma nas mnyam pa nyid /
NK069(tu)001:13508: rdzogs pa chen po sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK069(tu)001:13509: du sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du dbyer myed par
NK069(tu)001:13510: / ye nas cig par gnas pa'i don /
NK069(tu)001:13511: shes rab kyis tshig tsam ma yin par rtogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:13512: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid de /
NK069(tu)001:13513: dper na dpyid rmo kol byas pas /
NK069(tu)001:13514: ston lo thog rtsa ba shes pa lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:13515: de ni rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:13517: bsgom ba dang spyod pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:13518: de ltar shes rab kyis rtogs pa'i don la /
NK069(tu)001:13519: ting nge 'dzin gyis kyang yang nas yang du goms par 'jug pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:13520: yang na shes rab kyis rtogs pa'i rtags /
NK069(tu)001:13521: spyod pas kyang blang dor dang bzang ngan dang dbye' bsal myed pas spyod cing 'jug pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:13522: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid bsgom spyod de /
NK069(tu)001:13523: dper ston lo thog brtsa' bar shes pas /
NK069(tu)001:13524: dpyid rmo bsko' la lhag par 'jug pa lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:13525: de ni shes pa la 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid bsgom spyod do //
NK069(tu)001:13526: mngon du gyur pa 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:13527: de ltar shes pa'i mtshan nyid dam /
NK069(tu)001:13528: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid 'go' 'byor cing phan tshun spras dam /
NK069(tu)001:13529: lta spyod ldan par gzungs su gyur tshun cad ni /
NK069(tu)001:13531: sar tshud pa'i rig 'dzin zhes bya la /
NK069(tu)001:13532: des ngan song dang 'khor bar mi gtong ba'i gzungs su gyur pas /
NK069(tu)001:13534: de ni dper na sa bon sa la btab pa lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:13535: 'bras bu smin byed rgyu dang rkyen //
NK069(tu)001:13536: zhes des 'bras bu bla na myed pa'i byang chub
NK069(tu)001:13537: kyi 'bras bu'i go 'phang thob cing smin par byed
NK069(tu)001:13538: pa'i rgyu ni / lta ba shes ba la rkyen ni bsgom spyod 'jug pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:13539: de yang ci'i phyir de gnyis rgyu rkyen du bzhag zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13540: rgyu shes pa dang sdod rkyen 'jug pas spyod pa yin te /
NK069(tu)001:13543: de ltar rgyu shes pa lta ba'i don la /
NK069(tu)001:13544: rkyen 'jug pa ting nge 'dzin dang spyod pas /
NK069(tu)001:13545: yang nas yang du goms par 'jug pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:13546: dper na sa bon sa la btab pas /
NK069(tu)001:13550: sa bon ba sa shing rlan pa lta bu de ni /
NK069(tu)001:13551: sa la gnas pa'i rig 'dzin dang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:13552: nus mthu' can du gar 'gyur ba //
NK069(tu)001:13553: zhes de ltar sa bon ba sa pa'i mthus /
NK069(tu)001:13554: skad cig ma snga ma la bya rtsang rdol nas /
NK069(tu)001:13555: skad cig ma phyi ma la bar cis kyang ma
NK069(tu)001:13556: chod par myu gu sngon po 'byung ba la rag
NK069(tu)001:13558: rgyu shes pas rtogs pa'i don la /
NK069(tu)001:13559: rkyen 'jug pa'i ting nge 'dzin dang spyod pas /
NK069(tu)001:13560: yang nas yang du goms par byas pa'i bag chags mthu can du gyur pa des /
NK069(tu)001:13561: skad cig ma snga ma la sgrib pa'i bag chags yang nas /
NK069(tu)001:13562: skad cig ma phyi ma la sku gsung thugs kyi
NK069(tu)001:13563: dngos grub thob pa la rag ma lus par rtogs
NK069(tu)001:13564: pa de gnas pa de la ni sar smin pa'i
NK069(tu)001:13566: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:13567: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:13568: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid bsgom pa gnyis ka 'bras bu skyed bar 'dug pa la /
NK069(tu)001:13569: lta ba rgyur 'gro ba'i 'thad pa ci yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13570: lta ba de 'bras bur 'gro ba'i gtso' bo lta bu ste /
NK069(tu)001:13571: dper na myu gu sngon po skyed pa la sa bon grung po de rgyu'i gtso bo lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:13572: bsgom pa ni rkyen chu lud lta bu yin la /
NK069(tu)001:13573: lta bsgom gnyis kyi stobs kyis 'bras bu smin cing grub par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:13574: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK069(tu)001:13575: zhes de ltar sar tshud pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK069(tu)001:13576: sa la gnas pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK069(tu)001:13578: rig 'dzin de gsum rgyal ba sangs rgyas thams cad bskyed pa'i zhing du grags zhe'am /
NK069(tu)001:13579: yang na rig 'dzin gsum po de las ma rtogs pa myed pas /
NK069(tu)001:13580: rgyal ba'i zhing khams su rig 'dzin de gsum du thams cad 'dus par grags so //
NK069(tu)001:13582: rgyu shes pa'i mtshan nyid lta ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:13583: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid bsgom spyod dang /
NK069(tu)001:13584: mngon du gyur pa 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:13585: rgyu shes ba'i mtshan nyid lta ba la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:13592: gzhal byar stub mi stub kyi mtshan nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:13596: log rtog gi bag chags ngan pa la blo zhen pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13598: bsgrub byed kyi gtan tshigs tshad mas gzhal ba'i yul du gyur pas gzhal bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:13599: gzhal du stub mi stub kyi mtshan nyid la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:13602: mi stub pa ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:13604: de yang 'das pa la gzhal du mi stub ste /
NK069(tu)001:13605: mya ngan las 'das pa'i snang ba la 'jol na /
NK069(tu)001:13606: 'das pa'i snang ba las dang po pa'i spyod yul ma yin /
NK069(tu)001:13607: mya ngan las 'das pa'i zhen pa la 'jol na /
NK069(tu)001:13609: de bas na 'das pa la gzhal du mi stub bo //
NK069(tu)001:13610: 'khor ba la yang 'jal du mi stub ste /
NK069(tu)001:13612: rang rig pa snang ba yin yang gzhal bya myen no //
NK069(tu)001:13614: zhen pa kun rtags yin no //
NK069(tu)001:13615: 'o na so sor rtog pa'i shes rab kyis rang la rang 'jel lo zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13616: 'dzug mo rang gis 'dzug mo rang la reg du mi stub pa bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:13618: lta bas yid so sor rtog pa'i shes rab tu gnas 'gyur kyang /
NK069(tu)001:13619: zhen pa'i gnyan po bsgom pa'i shes rab yin te /
NK069(tu)001:13620: ma bsgom pa'i zhen pa 'dag du mi stub pas /
NK069(tu)001:13623: dbang po rab rtags kyis rtogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13624: 'bring gtan tshigs kyis gtan la phab nas rtogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13625: tha ma ting nge 'dzin rgyud pas rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13626: dbang po rab la lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:13627: mthing ka mthong na chos nyid mi 'gyur bar rtogs /
NK069(tu)001:13628: dkar bo mthong na nyes pa'i skyon gyis ma gos par rtogs /
NK069(tu)001:13629: ser po mthong na che ba'i yon tan rgyas par rtogs /
NK069(tu)001:13630: dmar por mthong na 'gro ba'i don la chag par rtogs /
NK069(tu)001:13631: ljang khu mthong na 'phrin las mthar phyin par rtogs so //
NK069(tu)001:13639: gtan la 'bebs par byed pa'i phyir gtan tshigs so //
NK069(tu)001:13644: ston pa sku lnga dngos kyis gsungs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13645: ston pa rig 'dzin dngos lnga dang tshul 'thun pas /
NK069(tu)001:13647: 'gro ba la tshul mthun gyi tshig lngas brda' 'jal bar byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13649: sku bzhi'i dngos tshul tshig gsum la spyad du myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13650: sprul sku'i tshig tu spyad du yod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13652: bsgrub bya mtha' bral la gtan tshigs mtha' can gyis gtan la phab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13653: bsgrub bya dang gtan tshigs 'thun par gtan la phab pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13655: sgra mthun don dpags dang tshad ma bka' gzhung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:13656: sgra 'thun don dpags la drug ste /
NK069(tu)001:13657: dag pa gsum gyi gtan tshigs kyis /
NK069(tu)001:13658: snang ba mi spang bar 'bras bur gtan la dbab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13659: mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis bdag nyid chen por lhun gyis grub pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13660: rtogs pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis sku gsung thugs mi bzad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor bya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:13661: bden pa gnyis kyi gtan tshigs kyis bden pa dbyer myed zung du 'jug pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13662: ldem dgongs man ngag gi gtan tshigs kyis gnas kyi don gnyis mthong bar bya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:13663: dngos po lo rgyus kyi gtan tshigs kyis bdag nyid chen por gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13664: tshad ma bka' bzhung la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:13667: grub mtha' ni lta ba bden pa dbyer myed rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13669: dbyer myed de nyid mngon gsum du gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13670: rkyen 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid bsgom spyod la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:13671: nyams su len pa'i bsgom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13673: bsgom pa la rim gyis pa blo chung ba'i dbang du byas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13674: gcig char ba blo che ba'i dbang du byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13675: spyod pa yang de gnyis dang tshul mthun par spyod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13676: mngon du gyur pa 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:13679: lam du gyur pa ni rig 'dzin de /
NK069(tu)001:13680: de la rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin la lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:13681: dang po gzhi' gang dang sbyar ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:13683: gnyis pa bden pa gang rtogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:13687: dper na khyung dang seng ge bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:13689: bzhi pa rnam grangs ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:13690: rgyus bsdus pa'i rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin dang /
NK069(tu)001:13691: 'bras bus sdus pa'i rnam par smin pa'i rig 'dzin no //
NK069(tu)001:13695: lnga pa lam gyi mo tshod gang dang sbyar ba ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:13696: rgyus sdus pa'i rnam smin ni sbyor lam dang sbyar /
NK069(tu)001:13697: 'bras bus sdus pa'i rnam smin ni bsgom lam dang sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:13698: rig 'dzin gsum po'i khyad par rnam par bzhag pa ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:13699: dang po chos nyan lugs nas khyad par bzhag na /
NK069(tu)001:13700: tshe dbang sprul sku la nyan /
NK069(tu)001:13701: phyag rgya chen po longs sku la nyan /
NK069(tu)001:13702: lhun grub chos sku la nyan no //
NK069(tu)001:13703: gnyis pa sgrib pa yong lugs nas bzhag na /
NK069(tu)001:13704: tshe dbang gis kun tu 'gro ba lta ba'i sgrib pa yong /
NK069(tu)001:13705: phyag rgyas lhan cig gnas pa shes bya'i sgrib pa yong /
NK069(tu)001:13706: lhun grub kyis bag la nyal gyi sgrib pa ma lus pa yong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:13707: gsum pa sa'i sgo nas bzhag na /
NK069(tu)001:13708: tshe dbang gis sa dang po /
NK069(tu)001:13710: lhun grub kyis sa bcu pa mngon du byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13711: bzhi pa cho 'phrul 'gyed lugs nas khyad bzhag na /
NK069(tu)001:13714: lhun grub cho 'phrul tsol ba khyed par 'gyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13715: lnga pa cha byad kyi khyad bzhag na /
NK069(tu)001:13716: tshe dbang ni mi dang lha'i cha byad do //
NK069(tu)001:13717: phyag rgya ye shes lha'i cha lugs so //
NK069(tu)001:13718: lhun grub sangs rgyas nyid kyi cha lugs so //
NK069(tu)001:13723: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku dang /
NK069(tu)001:13724: rdo rje'i sku lngar lhun gyis grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:13725: des na rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags ces so //
NK069(tu)001:13726: rig 'dzin gyi cha lugs bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:13727: mi dang lha dang tshangs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:13728: zhes rig 'dzin de'i skye gnas ni /
NK069(tu)001:13730: mi dang sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha'o //
NK069(tu)001:13731: gzugs khams su skye na tshangs pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:13732: skye ba rnam dag 'dzin mod kyang //
NK069(tu)001:13733: zhes skye ba der len kyang /
NK069(tu)001:13734: skye ba rnam par dag ste /
NK069(tu)001:13735: phyi ma 'khor bar mi skye ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:13736: de ltar skye ba mi dang lha'i lus kyi skye ba 'dzin mod kyi /
NK069(tu)001:13737: khyad par sa las gnas 'gyur yin //
NK069(tu)001:13738: zhes rtogs pa'i khyad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:13739: sa dang po nas sa bcu pa'i byang chub sems
NK069(tu)001:13740: dpa' rnams dang rtogs pa mnyam pas khyad par gyi
NK069(tu)001:13741: sa la gnas pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:13742: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin la lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:13743: dang po gzhi' gang dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:13744: gzhan gyi 'gro don byed nus pa dang sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:13745: gnyis pa bden pa gang rtogs na /
NK069(tu)001:13746: bden pa dbyer myed de spyi las skyed gdon du myed pa'i tshul gyis rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13747: gsum pa khungs gang dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:13748: 'di nyid kyi bcu gsum pa las /
NK069(tu)001:13749: dbang sgyur mchog nyid dam pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:13750: bzhi pa rnam grangs ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:13751: bdud rtsi sman las grub pa'i rig 'dzin tshe dbang dang /
NK069(tu)001:13752: sgron ma rlung las grub pa'i tshe dbang dang /
NK069(tu)001:13753: thabs lam rtsa rlung thig le las grub pa'i tshe dbang dang /
NK069(tu)001:13754: grol lam bskyed rdzogs las grub pa'i tshe dbang dang bzhi'o //
NK069(tu)001:13755: lnga pa lam gyi mo tshod ni /
NK069(tu)001:13756: sa dang po dang sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:13757: pha rol phyin pa kun tu rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:13758: zhes sa bcu thob pa'i rgyu ni pha rol tu phyin pa bcu ste /
NK069(tu)001:13759: de yang rig 'dzin gyis mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa'i rig pa skad cig la /
NK069(tu)001:13760: theg pa 'og ma bas sa bcu 'grub pa'i rgyu
NK069(tu)001:13761: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu yin pas rdzogs so
NK069(tu)001:13762: // 'o na de spyad pas rdzogs sam /
NK069(tu)001:13763: ma spyad par rdzogs zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13766: bzod pa ma bsgom shing ma spyad bzhin du rdzogs so //
NK069(tu)001:13767: thabs dang shes rab sa'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:13768: shes rab mchog gi mchog gyur pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:13769: zhes de ltar byang chub sems dpa'i sa bcu thob
NK069(tu)001:13770: pa'i rgyu pha rol tu phyin pa bcu rdzogs pa
NK069(tu)001:13771: ma zad / sangs rgyas kun tu 'od kyi sa thob pa'i rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:13772: thabs shes rab dbyer myed par rdzogs so //
NK069(tu)001:13773: 'o na sangs rgyas kun tu 'od kyi sa thob pa'i rgyu thabs dang shes rab ni rdzogs na /
NK069(tu)001:13774: sangs rgyas kun tu 'od kyi mtshan nyid ji lta bu zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13776: mos pa spyod pa nas sa dgu'i bar du sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK069(tu)001:13777: sa bcu pa chos kyi sprin gyi gnas skabs su /
NK069(tu)001:13778: rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin gnyen po ye shes chen po'i yang chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:13779: shes bya'i sgrib ba chung ngu'i yang chung ngu bag la nyal ba'i cha 'phra mo yan cad /
NK069(tu)001:13780: skad cig ma snga ma la spangs na /
NK069(tu)001:13781: skad cig ma phyi ma la mtshan ma myed pa rtogs pa'i mthar phyin pas /
NK069(tu)001:13782: dbyings dang rig pa gnyis myed par gyur pa'i chos
NK069(tu)001:13783: kyi sku mngon du gyur pa la kun tu 'od
NK069(tu)001:13784: ces zhes bya'o // de la ci'i phyir kun tu 'od kyis zhes bya zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13785: chos thams cad ni chos nyid mtshan ma myed pa'i dbyings kyis khyab la /
NK069(tu)001:13786: chos kyi dbyings kyis gar khyab pa der rtogs pa'i
NK069(tu)001:13787: ye shes kyis khyab pas kun tu 'od kyi sa
NK069(tu)001:13788: zhes bya'o // de la thabs dang shes rab dbyer med pa kun tu 'od kyi sa /
NK069(tu)001:13789: thabs dang shes rab mchog tu gyur pa pad+ma can gyi sa /
NK069(tu)001:13790: thabs dang shes rab mchog tu gyur pa yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13791: sa'i khyad par bcu dang gsum /
NK069(tu)001:13795: rgyu 'bras khyad par lhun gyis rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:13796: zhes rgyu'i sa bcu rang la yang rgyu 'bras kyi khyad par yod de /
NK069(tu)001:13797: rgyu pha rol tu phyin pa bcu /
NK069(tu)001:13799: 'bras bu'i sa gsum rang la yang rgyu 'bras yod de /
NK069(tu)001:13800: rgyu thabs dang shes rab mchog /
NK069(tu)001:13803: rgyu'i sa bcu pha rol tu phyin pa dang bcas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13804: 'bras bu'i sa gsum sku gsum dang bcas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13806: sa dang po rab tu dga' ba'i sa /
NK069(tu)001:13807: rten sbyin pa'i pha rol tu phyin pa /
NK069(tu)001:13808: dpe' mi bzad pa'i gter dang 'dra /
NK069(tu)001:13809: rtsal ma rig pa zil gyis gnon pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13810: sa gnyis pa dri ma myed pa la /
NK069(tu)001:13811: rten tshul khrims kyi phar rol tu phyin pa /
NK069(tu)001:13813: rtsal ma rig pa ye shes su gsal /
NK069(tu)001:13815: rten bzod pa'i pha rol tu /
NK069(tu)001:13817: rtsal nyon mongs pa rtsad nas rlag /
NK069(tu)001:13818: sa bzhi pa 'od byed pa la /
NK069(tu)001:13822: sa lnga pa sbyangs dka' ba la /
NK069(tu)001:13826: sa drug pa mngon du gyur pa la /
NK069(tu)001:13827: rten shes rab kyi dpe' sman ma ki ta /
NK069(tu)001:13829: sa bdun pa ring du song ba la /
NK069(tu)001:13830: rten thabs kyi pha rol tu /
NK069(tu)001:13832: rtsal dug lnga sman du sgyur /
NK069(tu)001:13833: sa brgyad pa mi g.yo' ba la /
NK069(tu)001:13835: dpe' yid bzhin gyi nor bu /
NK069(tu)001:13837: sa dgu pa legs pa'i blo gros la /
NK069(tu)001:13840: rtsal log lta dbyings su sgrol /
NK069(tu)001:13841: sa bcu pa chos kyi sprin la /
NK069(tu)001:13842: rten ye shes kyi pha rol tu /
NK069(tu)001:13844: rtsal sgrib pa dag nas thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:13845: 'bras bu'i sa gsum sku gsung thugs dang bcas pa la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:13849: bcu gcig kun tu 'od la sprul sku thob /
NK069(tu)001:13850: bcu gnyis ma chags pad ma spyan la longs sku thob /
NK069(tu)001:13851: bcu gsum yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen la chos sku thob /
NK069(tu)001:13852: ye shes rgyun chad du 'dod pa'i lugs so //
NK069(tu)001:13854: bcu gcig kun tu 'od la thabs shes rab dbyings ye shes dbyer myed chos sku thob /
NK069(tu)001:13855: bcu gnyis ma chags pad ma spyan thabs shes rab
NK069(tu)001:13856: mchog tu gyur pa la longs skur byon nas sa
NK069(tu)001:13858: bcu gsum yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen thabs shes
NK069(tu)001:13859: rab mchog gi mchog tu gyur pa thob nas longs
NK069(tu)001:13860: skur byon nas sa bcu'i sgrib pa sel /
NK069(tu)001:13861: bcu gsum yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen thabs shes
NK069(tu)001:13862: rab mchog gi mchog tu gyur pa thob nas longs
NK069(tu)001:13863: sku las sprul skur phrung nas 'gro ba drug gi
NK069(tu)001:13864: don mdzad pa'o // de lta bu'i rgyu 'bras kyi
NK069(tu)001:13865: khyad par yang dbyer myed du lhun gyis grub nas
NK069(tu)001:13868: // gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:13869: pha rol tu phyin pa bcu dus kun tu rdzogs na spyad rgyu myed /
NK069(tu)001:13870: thabs shes rab kyi mchog yin na /
NK069(tu)001:13871: shes rab myed pa'i thabs gcig pur song /
NK069(tu)001:13872: shes rab kyi mchog las kyang mchog tu gyur pa cig yod na /
NK069(tu)001:13873: shes rab thugs myed du song /
NK069(tu)001:13874: sa'i khyad par dang rgyu 'bras kyi khyad par lhun gyis rdzogs na /
NK069(tu)001:13875: 'bad pa myed par grol mnyam pa la /
NK069(tu)001:13877: 'dir lam rim gyis pa dang gcig char ba'i gnyis yod pa las /
NK069(tu)001:13878: lam gcig char ba la dgongs pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:13881: gzhi' rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa la /
NK069(tu)001:13882: rgyu 'bras kyi pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13883: rgyu 'bras kyi thabs shes rab dang /
NK069(tu)001:13885: theg pa gong 'og gi rgyu 'bras kyi khyad par thams cad rdzogs so //
NK069(tu)001:13886: de ma rdzogs na lam ma 'byongs /
NK069(tu)001:13887: lam ma 'byongs na lam gcig char ba myed pas 'gal ba myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13888: mkha' dkyil dang ba'i dbyings nyi zla //
NK069(tu)001:13889: zhes rnal 'byor pas lha gcig bsgom pas ye shes
NK069(tu)001:13890: kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad bsgom par bstan pa ni
NK069(tu)001:13891: / nam mkha' nyid dngos por dang mtshan ma'i mtha' dang bral bas dkyil /
NK069(tu)001:13892: ngo bo nyid kyis dang bas chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa'i rang bzhin yin la /
NK069(tu)001:13893: der gdan nyi ma thabs dang /
NK069(tu)001:13894: zla ba shes rab gnyis rtsegs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du /
NK069(tu)001:13895: ye shes rgyal po stangs dpyal bsgom //
NK069(tu)001:13896: zhes lha ye nas gnas cing yin pa'i don shes pas na ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:13897: mtshan ma'i mtha' gnyis las rgyal bas na rgyal po /
NK069(tu)001:13900: lha gang yang rung ba yab yum don byang chub sems dang ldan par bsgom shing bsgrubs na /
NK069(tu)001:13901: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kun //
NK069(tu)001:13902: zhes de bsgoms pa'i yon tan ni /
NK069(tu)001:13903: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad bsgoms par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:13904: lha thams cad lha gcig gi ngang du tha mi dad de /
NK069(tu)001:13905: lha thams cad kyang don byang chub sems su gcig pas /
NK069(tu)001:13906: don byang chub sems kyi rtogs pa dang ldan la /
NK069(tu)001:13907: yi dam gyi lha'i sku thams cad dus gcig tu bsgoms pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:13908: ma lus par ni bsgom par 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:13909: ces lha gcig bsgom pas kun bsgom par 'gyur ba ci ste zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13910: lha gcig gi rang bzhin las lha thams cad 'byung la /
NK069(tu)001:13911: dus bzhi phyogs bcu gang nas kyang //
NK069(tu)001:13918: steng 'og gnyis dang bcu nas kyang /
NK069(tu)001:13919: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnyed mi 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:13921: yang dag pa'i rgyal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:13925: nam zhig snyed du re nas rtsal yang /
NK069(tu)001:13926: rnyed pa lam phrad par myi 'gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:13927: sems nyid rtogs na sangs rgyas pas //
NK069(tu)001:13928: zhes 'o na gang nas snyed zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13929: rang gi sems nyid rtogs pa kho na /
NK069(tu)001:13930: tshogs gnyis rjogs pa'i sangs rgyas yin zhe'am /
NK069(tu)001:13931: rang gi sems nyid rtogs pa sangs rgyas yin par bshad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13932: sangs rgyas gzhan du ma tshol cig /
NK069(tu)001:13933: ces 'on kyang sangs rgyas rang gi sems nyid las ma rtogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:13934: sems las gzhan pa'i logs su sangs rgyas ma tshol cig /
NK069(tu)001:13935: de skad du yang gsang ba'i sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las kyang /
NK069(tu)001:13936: rang bzhin gnas phyir gzhan nas 'ongs pa myed /
NK069(tu)001:13937: zhen pa log pas bdag zhal bdag gis mthong /
NK069(tu)001:13939: dkyil 'khor kun tu mnyam sbyor bas //
NK069(tu)001:13940: zhes dkyil 'khor kun yi dam lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyar sbyar nas /
NK069(tu)001:13941: lha tshogs mang po rnams yang gsal bar rang gi lus ngag yid gsum dang mnyam par sbyar bas /
NK069(tu)001:13943: ces bde' bar gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs 'grub par 'gyur /
NK069(tu)001:13944: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub rnam gnyis 'grub par 'gyur /
NK069(tu)001:13946: gtar ka gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:13947: cho ga lhag chad byung na legs par snang ngo zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:13949: rang sems sangs rgyas su shes na /
NK069(tu)001:13950: lha mang po bsgom yang mtsho' la gza' skar shar ba ltar bsgom shes la /
NK069(tu)001:13952: rig pa rlung du phab nas lhag par 'jog nus te /
NK069(tu)001:13953: der rang sems nyid lhar shes pas /
NK069(tu)001:13954: ma rig pa'i skyon nyid dag nas /
NK069(tu)001:13955: lhag chad thams cad chos nyid du rang grol bas nyes pa myed par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:13956: cho ga lhag gam ma tshang yang //
NK069(tu)001:13957: skyon nyid dag ste nyes pa myed //
NK069(tu)001:13959: ces de ltar sangs rgyas gcig bsgoms pas /
NK069(tu)001:13960: rgyal ba kun bsgoms par shes sam /
NK069(tu)001:13961: rang sems las ma rtogs pa gzhan na sangs rgyas myed par shes sam /
NK069(tu)001:13962: dkyil 'khor kun dang rang gi lus ngag yid gsum dang mnyam par sbyar bas /
NK069(tu)001:13963: dngos grub thams cad grub par 'gyur ba ci'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:13964: de ltar rtogs pa'i gnas skabs na /
NK069(tu)001:13965: cho ga'i rim pa lhag gam /
NK069(tu)001:13967: skyon nyid rnam par dag ste /
NK069(tu)001:13968: nyes pa rdul tsam yang myed do //
NK069(tu)001:13970: thams cad sems su rtogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:13971: rol mo'i sprin gyis mnyes par gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:13972: zhes rol mo ni gzhi' ma nges pa las sna
NK069(tu)001:13973: tshogs su snang bas thams cad tshim par byed pa'o
NK069(tu)001:13974: // 'dir yo byad lnga la sogs pa thams cad rig pa rang snang bar shes nas /
NK069(tu)001:13975: de la sna tshogs su spyod pa nyid ye shes kyi rol pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13976: de dag 'khor 'das gnyis su myed pas sprin /
NK069(tu)001:13977: mchod pas tshogs gnyis rdzogs mnyes par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:13979: gsang pa'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las //
NK069(tu)001:13980: gsang ba ni snod ngan pa la /
NK069(tu)001:13981: snying po ni gsang sngags kyi nying khu /
NK069(tu)001:13982: de kho na nyid ni chos thams cad kyi de kho na'o //
NK069(tu)001:13984: mtshan nyid ltar drang ba'i don ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:13985: 'bras bu gsang sngags nges pa'i don kho nar ston po'o //
NK069(tu)001:13986: de lta bu'i rgyu chen po 'di las /
NK069(tu)001:13987: tshogs bsgrub pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:13992: dbang po'i spyod yul du snang ba'i chos thams cad dang /
NK069(tu)001:13993: bdag dang 'khor dang phyi nang gi yo byad thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:13994: lha'i dkyil 'khor du byin gyis rlob nus pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13997: dgongs pa khyad myed par mnyam pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13998: las kyi skar ma 'phrin las kyi bye brag thams cad la ma rmongs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:13999: 'khor phal pa rang lhar byin gyis rlob nus pa dang bzhi ldan na tshogs zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:14000: 'byor ldan yo byad kyi tshogs ni /
NK069(tu)001:14001: tshogs kyi mchod pa byed pa'i dus su /
NK069(tu)001:14002: 'jig rten 'dod pa'i longs spyod lnga la yod do
NK069(tu)001:14003: cig ma tshang ba myed par mtshogs pa'i tshogs so
NK069(tu)001:14004: // gsal ba dgongs pa'i tshogs ni /
NK069(tu)001:14009: des bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs pas tshogs so //
NK069(tu)001:14013: bka' bzhin du sgrub pa la sangs rgyas dngos grub gter bar dgongs /
NK069(tu)001:14014: de gnyis mthun zhing mdza' bas na mdza' ba 'dus pa'i tshogs te /
NK069(tu)001:14015: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i
NK069(tu)001:14016: sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor thams cad gcig
NK069(tu)001:14017: tu gyur te / zhes le'u bcu gnyis par tshogs bsgrubs nas /
NK069(tu)001:14018: bcu gsum par rdzogs rim bsgom pas de nas so //
NK069(tu)001:14022: sku gsung thugs rdo rje ltar dbyer myed par ni ldan /
NK069(tu)001:14023: de lta bu'i bde' bar gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor thams
NK069(tu)001:14024: cad gsang ba'i man ngag 'di bstan zhing bshad pa
NK069(tu)001:14025: phyir / gnas gcig tu 'dus par gyur te zhe'am /
NK069(tu)001:14026: yang na phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor dang ldan pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:14027: bde' bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi rang bzhin ston pa kun tu bzang po des /
NK069(tu)001:14028: gsang ba'i man ngag 'di bstan pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:14029: thugs kyi dgongs pa rtse gcig tu gyur nas zhes pa'i don yang yin no //
NK069(tu)001:14030: dgyes pa chen pos chos thams cad ye nas rdzogs pa chen por lhun gyis grub pa'i dam tshig /
NK069(tu)001:14031: ces ston pa kun tu bzang po de /
NK069(tu)001:14032: 'jig rten gyi longs spyod la dgyes /
NK069(tu)001:14033: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i zag myed la yang dgyes /
NK069(tu)001:14034: de gnyis dbyer myed par mkhyen pas chen po /
NK069(tu)001:14035: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad 'phral du lam gyis ma sgrubs /
NK069(tu)001:14037: ye nas sku gsung thugs ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rdzogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:14039: dbyer myed 'bad rtsol dang bral ba'i rang bzhin du lhun gyis grub la /
NK069(tu)001:14040: de'i rang bzhin las mi 'da' bas sam /
NK069(tu)001:14041: de ltar rtogs par bya ba las mi 'da' bas na dam tshig go //
NK069(tu)001:14042: shin tu gsang ba snying po'i sprin bkod pa'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas /
NK069(tu)001:14043: zhes rdzogs pa chen por lhun gyis grub pa'i don ni /
NK069(tu)001:14044: shin tu khyad par du rang bzhin gyis rtogs par bka' bas ni rang bzhin gyi gsang ba /
NK069(tu)001:14049: snod ngan pa la bstan du ci rung bas na /
NK069(tu)001:14050: gzhan la mi bstan pa'i gsang ba /
NK069(tu)001:14051: yon tan thams cad kyi rtsa ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:14052: rgyur gyur pas na rgyu'i snying po /
NK069(tu)001:14056: rlung ngo bo nyid kyi sku gnas pas na 'bras bu'i snying po'o //
NK069(tu)001:14057: chos thams cad kyi gnas lugs mang por bston pas sprin dang 'dra /
NK069(tu)001:14059: de las grub pa'i yi ge dang /
NK069(tu)001:14060: de la sten pa'i khams bdud rtsi'i thig le dang /
NK069(tu)001:14061: de dag grub pa'i snying po rlung rnams ma 'dres par bkod pa'i ting 'dzin la zhugs nas so //
NK069(tu)001:14062: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:14063: zhes 'gro ba rnams sangs rgya bar bya ba'i ched du /
NK069(tu)001:14064: shin tu gsang ba'i man ngag 'di /
NK069(tu)001:14065: dgos ched dang bcas nas brjod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14066: ma rtogs pa dang chos nyid ye ma rtogs pa dang zhes phyal ba pas ni /
NK069(tu)001:14067: las dge sdig yod par ma shes /
NK069(tu)001:14068: shing kun tu rmongs shing gti mug pas ma rtogs pa'o //
