NK069(tu)001:14070: chos nyid las log par rtogs pa rgyang phan pa tshe gcig tu lta ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:14071: mu stegs pa bdag brtag par mi 'gyur bar lta ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:14072: mur thugs pa mtha' chad par lta ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:14073: de rnams ni 'jig rten pa'i lta ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:14074: de gsum log par rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14075: phyogs rtogs zhes nyan thos kyis chos la bdag myed par rtogs yang /
NK069(tu)001:14076: gang zag la bdag myed par ma rtogs so //
NK069(tu)001:14077: rang sangs rgyas kyis gang zag la bdag myed par rtogs pa'i steng du /
NK069(tu)001:14078: chos kyi phyogs gcig gzung ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:14079: gzugs kyi phung po la bdag myed par rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:14080: chos kyi don cha gcig gam phyogs gcig rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:14083: zhes byang chub sems dpas chos thams cad don dam
NK069(tu)001:14084: par stong pa bdag myed par rtogs kyang yang dag
NK069(tu)001:14085: pa mnyam pa nyid gnyis su myed par ma rtogs
NK069(tu)001:14086: pas / yang dag nyid ma rtogs so //
NK069(tu)001:14087: 'dul ba dgongs pa gsal ba dang //
NK069(tu)001:14088: zhes 'gro ba 'dul ba'i dbang du gsungs pa khrus dang gtsang sbras 'dul ba kri ya dang /
NK069(tu)001:14089: ldem dgongs kyis bstan pa'i u pa ya cha gnyis 'dzin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14090: gsang ba'i don mtshon cing ston pa yo ga /
NK069(tu)001:14091: rang bzhin gsang ba'i don rnams ni //
NK069(tu)001:14092: chos nyid kyi don rang bzhin gyis rtogs par dka' bas /
NK069(tu)001:14094: de'i don phyin ci ma log par ston pa'i rgyud lung man dag gsum gyi don rnams sam /
NK069(tu)001:14095: rnal 'byor chen po ma h+aa yo ga'i don rnams ni /
NK069(tu)001:14096: yi ge sgras brtags ming tshogs las //
NK069(tu)001:14097: zhes don zab mo rnams gang gis 'chad cing ston zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:14098: yi ges mtshon par byed de /
NK069(tu)001:14101: yi ge'i sgra mang por rtogs pa las /
NK069(tu)001:14102: yi ge'i tshogs rnams byung la /
NK069(tu)001:14103: rten pa'i tshig gis rab mtshon te //
NK069(tu)001:14104: zhes ming gi tshogs la rten pa'i tshig gis ni /
NK069(tu)001:14105: rang bzhin gyis gsang ba'i don rnams mtshon cing ston pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:14106: yi ge dang ming dang tshig gi tshogs la rten nas /
NK069(tu)001:14107: rang bzhin gsang ba'i don rnams mtshon par byed la /
NK069(tu)001:14108: yi ge ming dang tshig gi khongs nas rang bzhin
NK069(tu)001:14109: gsang ba'i don rnams gnas par rab tu mtshon pa'o
NK069(tu)001:14110: // gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:14111: so so'i skye bo tha mal pa la ni don 'di bstan du mi stub /
NK069(tu)001:14113: mtshan nyid pa la gsang bshad 'di dgos pa myed par /
NK069(tu)001:14114: thams cad kyi don man ngag 'dis ston pa 'gal zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:14116: a li ka li'i sgras ming gis tshig mtshon par byed pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:14117: sems can thams cad la 'khor lo bzhi rang la rang gnas su yod pa de ma shes pas /
NK069(tu)001:14118: de shes pas thams cad rang gnas su shes pa'i phyir smos pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:14119: khong nas gab sbas don 'byin pa //
NK069(tu)001:14120: zhes slob dpon gyi dgongs pa'i gong na gab /
NK069(tu)001:14121: yi ge kyus kyi khong na gab pas na gab pa'i gsang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:14123: gsang ba'i don 'di yang phal gyi spyod yul /
NK069(tu)001:14124: de'i phyir bde gshegs kyis kyang sgra rang thad du ma gsungs te /
NK069(tu)001:14125: rda dang man ngag gi sgo nas bstan pas sbas pa'i gsang ba /
NK069(tu)001:14126: de yang yi ge kyus la gab pa slob dpon gyi dgongs pas 'byin /
NK069(tu)001:14127: slob dpon gyi dgongs pa la gab pa yi ge kyus la rten nas 'byin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:14128: ston pa rdo rje'i thugs la gnas //
NK069(tu)001:14129: zhes rang bzhin gyi gsang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:14131: sbas pa'i gsang ba'i don 'byin cing ston pas na
NK069(tu)001:14132: ston pa sku mi 'gyur bas na rdo rje lta
NK069(tu)001:14133: bu'o // de'i thugs la gnas te /
NK069(tu)001:14136: rjes 'jug tu man ngag gi khungs sam /
NK069(tu)001:14138: rjes 'jug tu man ngag gi khungs sam thugs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:14139: ston pa'i zhal kyin rdo rje slob dpon gyi thugs la gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14140: 'di man chad la ngag don du bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:14141: phyi dbyibs kyi bdag nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:14143: nang sngags kyi bdag nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:14144: a li ka li yi ge'i gzugs su grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14145: gsang ba chos kyi bdag nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:14146: snying po ye shes kyi rlung du gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14147: de la phyi'i dbyibs gzhal yas khang du gtan la babs ste /
NK069(tu)001:14148: spyi bo bde' ba chen po'i 'khor lo rnam par snang mdzad kyi gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14149: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo ni snang ba mtha' yas kyi gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14150: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo ni rdo rje sems dpa'i gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14151: lte ba' sprul pa'i 'khor lo ni rin chen 'byung ldan gyi gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14152: gsang ba me rlung gi 'khor lo ni don yod grub pa'i gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14153: nang sngags ni sku gsum du gtan la dbab ste /
NK069(tu)001:14155: gsang ba'i k+sha ye shes te /
NK069(tu)001:14156: kun bzang yab yum chos sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:14157: rtsa gsum gyi ka li rnams longs sku rigs lnga sems dpa' dang bcas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14158: a li dang spyi bo'i ham ni sprul sku thub drug go //
NK069(tu)001:14159: gsang ba chos ni dam rdzas lngar gtan la dbab ste /
NK069(tu)001:14160: dri chen rnam par snang mdzad /
NK069(tu)001:14161: byang sems rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK069(tu)001:14162: sha chen rin chen 'byung ldan du /
NK069(tu)001:14163: rag ta snang ba mtha' yas /
NK069(tu)001:14165: de kho na nyid rlung ni lhar gtan la dbab ste /
NK069(tu)001:14166: srog 'dzin pa'i rlung rnam par snang mdzad /
NK069(tu)001:14167: sa'i rlung rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK069(tu)001:14169: me'i rlung snang ba mtha' yas /
NK069(tu)001:14170: rlung gi rlung don yod grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14171: yang na nam mkha'i rlung mi bskyod pa /
NK069(tu)001:14175: rlung gi rlung don grub zhes bzhed do //
NK069(tu)001:14176: de la phyi'i dbyibs rtsa'i 'khor lo ni gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:14177: nang sngags ni gsung mi bzad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'o //
NK069(tu)001:14178: gsang ba chos ni sku mi bzad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'o //
NK069(tu)001:14179: de kho na nyid rlung ni thugs mi bzad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'o //
NK069(tu)001:14180: de yang rtsa re re'i nang na sngags re re grub /
NK069(tu)001:14181: sngags re re la rten nas khams bdud rtsi gnas /
NK069(tu)001:14182: bdud rtsi'i thig le la rten nas rlung gi tshogs rnams rtog pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:14183: rtog tshogs lha yin par shes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:14184: de la dbyibs la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:14189: nyam rtsa mkhal ma'i nang na gnas /
NK069(tu)001:14190: mya ngan gyi lag pa'i the 'od dang bol gong na gtso' bor gnas /
NK069(tu)001:14191: rkang pa'i the 'ong la phal bar gnas /
NK069(tu)001:14192: 'dre'i rtsa lag pa'i srin lag la gtso' bor gnas /
NK069(tu)001:14193: rkang pa la phal par gnas /
NK069(tu)001:14194: klad pa dang phyi ma'i rtsa /
NK069(tu)001:14195: 'og tu mkhal ma'i phyi rol na gnas /
NK069(tu)001:14196: steng du dmig rtsa la 'khyil bar gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14197: rtsa chung ba ni nang lus stong phrag brgya bcu'o //
NK069(tu)001:14198: rtsa chen po ni 'khor lo bzhi dang srog shing gsum mo //
NK069(tu)001:14199: de la sngags la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:14201: shes rab kyi sngags a li /
NK069(tu)001:14202: mya ngan las 'das pa'i dpa' bo 'bru lnga /
NK069(tu)001:14204: de la bdud rtsi la lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:14207: dbus kun rdar ma byang sems /
NK069(tu)001:14208: long ka sdom byed dri chen /
NK069(tu)001:14209: mkhal rtsa 'khor ba sha chen no //
NK069(tu)001:14213: gyen du gyu ba'i rlung dang /
NK069(tu)001:14214: me dang mnyam pa'i rlung dang /
NK069(tu)001:14215: thur du sel ba'i rlung dang de lta rlung la lnga /
NK069(tu)001:14217: rab tu rgyu ba'i rlung dang /
NK069(tu)001:14218: shin tu rgyu ba'i rlung dang /
NK069(tu)001:14219: mngon par rgyu ba'i rlung dang /
NK069(tu)001:14220: yang dag par rgyu ba ni yan lag gi rlung lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:14221: yo log pas bcu tham pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14222: dkyil 'khor ldan pa'i zhes phyi dbyibs kyi bdag nyid du bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:14223: spyi bo bde' ba chen po'i 'khor lo ni /
NK069(tu)001:14225: klad pa bde ba dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14226: de yang spyi bo na bde ba yod pa'i rtags ltas pas tshim par 'dod chags ldang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:14227: nang sngags kyi bdag nyid du bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:14228: dbus ham mgo' thur du lta ba gnas /
NK069(tu)001:14229: 'dab ma la ka li rim pa gnyis gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14231: mi 'gyur bstan pa'i thig le nyid //
NK069(tu)001:14232: ham yig snying po byang chub sems //
NK069(tu)001:14233: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la gnas shing //
NK069(tu)001:14234: kun d+ha dung gi mdog mdangs gsal //
NK069(tu)001:14235: sum cu rtsa gnyis yi ge'i tshogs //
NK069(tu)001:14237: rang gi dkyil 'khor rten byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14239: zhes phyi ltar na mgrin pa longs spyod kyi dkyil
NK069(tu)001:14240: 'khor rtsa 'dab ma bcu drug gis sgad pa'i tshim
NK069(tu)001:14244: rtsa 'dab ma la a li bcu drug gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14246: sgra gnas brjod pa'i rgyun ldan pa //
NK069(tu)001:14247: gsang gsum dam tshig sngags kyi gnas //
NK069(tu)001:14248: bcu drug bdud rtsi 'dzag pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:14250: yig dbyangs kyi yi ges brgyan //
NK069(tu)001:14251: kun 'byung brjod pa'i yi ge ste //
NK069(tu)001:14252: spro dang sdu ba dga' ba'i tshul //
NK069(tu)001:14254: dkyil 'khor la ni zhes phyi dbyibs ltar na /
NK069(tu)001:14255: snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo ni rtsa 'dab ma brgyad do //
NK069(tu)001:14256: de na bde' ba yod pas lag pas bcangs pas tshim pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14259: 'dab ma la a ka tsa ta ta pa ya sha dang /
NK069(tu)001:14260: dpa' bo 'bru lnga 'gro dug yi ge gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14262: chos kyi dkyil 'khor h'u yig rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:14263: dkar ser 'od zer lnga yi mdangs //
NK069(tu)001:14264: gnas brgyad yi ge'i 'phreng bas mdzes //
NK069(tu)001:14265: shes pa brgyad gnas ye shes rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:14266: bya ba chen po'i don kun ston //
NK069(tu)001:14267: de dag skye dang 'gag pa las //
NK069(tu)001:14268: yang dag sbyang pas kun grol zhing //
NK069(tu)001:14269: gnyis myed ye shes bstan pa'i tshul //
NK069(tu)001:14273: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo ni /
NK069(tu)001:14275: dbang po sgo sprod pas tshim pa'i 'dod chags so //
NK069(tu)001:14278: a li dang ka lis skor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:14280: sprul pa'i 'khor lo cha rgyas pa //
NK069(tu)001:14281: 'od dmar chags pa'i ri mo can //
NK069(tu)001:14282: am yig sngags kyi phreng bas mdzes //
NK069(tu)001:14283: bcu drug rtsa bzhi gnas rnams su //
NK069(tu)001:14284: bde chen thig le'i ngang tshul cin //
NK069(tu)001:14285: de ming 'bod pa'i sgra dang bcas //
NK069(tu)001:14286: thabs kyi tshul gyis rnam par 'phags //
NK069(tu)001:14288: de ltar dkyil 'khor bzhi srog shing gsum bsgom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14289: ngag don nyams su blang ba la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:14293: dang po gcig la rten pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:14298: lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo'i lam dmar po'i shin tu cha 'phra ba la phog /
NK069(tu)001:14299: am las me dmar zhing tsha ba lte ba na sor bzhi tsam 'bar bar bsam /
NK069(tu)001:14300: 'og rlung gnyis mar rtse sprad la /
NK069(tu)001:14301: rlung rim gyis kha sbyar la /
NK069(tu)001:14302: thun la drangs tshad myed par bya /
NK069(tu)001:14306: nyams dang drod byung rgyal du gtang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:14312: rtsa dbu' ma na yang song /
NK069(tu)001:14313: snying ka'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus na /
NK069(tu)001:14314: h'u sngo skya mgo' thur du lta ba la phog /
NK069(tu)001:14315: h'u gi byang chub sems cha 'phra ba lte ba'i lam gyi bar du 'dzag ste /
NK069(tu)001:14316: dkar dmar gyi rnam pa la blo gtad de /
NK069(tu)001:14317: rlung rim gyis kha sbyar ba gong dang 'dra'o //
NK069(tu)001:14319: sum mdo'i rlung me ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:14320: nyi ma gnyis rtse sprad pas /
NK069(tu)001:14321: g.yas ro ma 'dzag pa'i lam na yar la me song /
NK069(tu)001:14322: snying khar chos kyi dkyil 'khor gyi /
NK069(tu)001:14325: mgrin pa longs spyod dal gyi yig 'bru' rnams sregs /
NK069(tu)001:14326: mes spyi bo bde' chen gyi ham kha dkar po mgo 'thur du lta ba bsregs pas /
NK069(tu)001:14328: g.yon rkyang ma 'bab pa'i lam na mar la byung bas /
NK069(tu)001:14329: mgrin pa'i yig 'bru rnams kha dog dmar po 'go' gyen la lta bar gsal gdab /
NK069(tu)001:14330: yang rkyang ma nas snying kha'i yig 'bru rnams gsos /
NK069(tu)001:14331: rkyang ma nas lte ba'i a la phog pas /
NK069(tu)001:14332: a 'khros pa'i tshul du cher 'bar bas /
NK069(tu)001:14333: des dbus kun d+ha' ma kha cung zhig bye /
NK069(tu)001:14334: de'i nang na yar la nyi zer tsam song bas /
NK069(tu)001:14335: snying kha'i h'u sngon po dang /
NK069(tu)001:14336: mgrin pa'i am dmar po bcom /
NK069(tu)001:14337: spyi bo ham la reg pas /
NK069(tu)001:14338: bdud rtsi'i rgyun lte bar babs par bsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:14339: rlu nga rim gyis kha sbyar ba la sogs pa 'dra'o //
NK069(tu)001:14345: me rlung srin bu me khyer /
NK069(tu)001:14346: rlung gi rlung mar me 'bar ba lta bu /
NK069(tu)001:14348: nam mkha' sprin myed lta bu skye'o //
NK069(tu)001:14359: me rlung sbyor bas skul byas te /
NK069(tu)001:14361: smin byed khyab pa bde' ba'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:14362: rang gi gnas su rnam par 'khyil /
NK069(tu)001:14364: dkyil 'khor ces sum mdo' rlung gi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK069(tu)001:14370: rtsa'i yal ga sbrul lce lta bur gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14371: rkang pas 'gro ba yang rlung des byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14372: dkyil 'khor ces lte skog me'i dkyil 'khor na /
NK069(tu)001:14373: dbyibs ni rtsa gru gsum du gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14374: sngags ni yi ge k+sha dmar nag gnas pa /
NK069(tu)001:14375: zas dang btung ba 'ju bar byed pa /
NK069(tu)001:14376: rtsa sbom 'phra gro sog gi bu ga tsam pa'i
NK069(tu)001:14377: nang na ram dmar skya dang k+sha gnyis gnas so
NK069(tu)001:14379: zhes gong ltar rtsa rkyang pa nyams su blangs pas /
NK069(tu)001:14380: dkyil 'khor gcig la rten nas bsgom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14381: gnyis la rten nas bsgom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14382: bzhi la rten nas bsgom pas /
NK069(tu)001:14384: dmyigs rgyu la sogs pa byung ba'i dus de na /
NK069(tu)001:14385: thugs rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes chos sku rtogs par 'gyur ba'i snga ltas 'byung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:14386: dus de tsam na thugs ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor sbyang zhing bsgom pas na /
NK069(tu)001:14387: thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dkyil 'khor mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:14389: ces khyad par du thugs kyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:14390: rang gnas kyi rim pas mchog tu gyur pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14391: bsgom pa'i nyams kyi mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14392: dang po rang gnas kyi rim pas mchog tu gyur pa ni rtsa brgyad yang bzhir bsdus te /
NK069(tu)001:14394: gnyis pa ye shes kyi rtsa /
NK069(tu)001:14397: de la chos kyi rtsa la dgu' ste /
NK069(tu)001:14400: tshul ni dngul chu zhun ma la ra gan gyi sil pa song ba 'dra'o //
NK069(tu)001:14402: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14406: yi dwags dang lha ma yin gyi sa bon pre dmar po dang su ser po gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14407: 'od ser po rtsa'i dwangs ma dar dkar skud pa la rgyu'o //
NK069(tu)001:14409: gyi 'og na pre su gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14411: yi dwags dang lha ma yin du skye ba'i kha
NK069(tu)001:14412: zin kun gzhi'i rnam shes kyis byas nas sa bon
NK069(tu)001:14413: pri dang du la phog go //
NK069(tu)001:14414: ye shes kyi rtsa la dgu ste /
NK069(tu)001:14416: dbyibs ni gru bzhi zhags pa sdoms pa'am sbrul 'khyil ba bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:14417: tshul ni dar le'u rgan la shel sgor rgyus pa bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:14419: yid kyi rnam par shes pa gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14421: thugs kyi snying po h'u mthing ka'o //
NK069(tu)001:14427: dbugs kyi dwangs ma gser sa 'og na gnas pa'i rlangs pa tsam rgyu'o //
NK069(tu)001:14428: a n+ri gnyis dbugs kyi snyigs ma la rgyu'o //
NK069(tu)001:14430: h'u gi 'og nas a n+ri gnyis gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14432: lha mir skye ba'i kha zin yid kyi rnam par shes pas byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:14433: sa bon a dang n+ri la sog go //
NK069(tu)001:14434: rang rgyud kyi rtsa la yang dgu' ste /
NK069(tu)001:14438: sos ka'i chu la dmyigs rgyu byung ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:14439: yang ni rtsi skya'i kha la zil pa chags pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:14440: zangs zhun ma la ra gan gyi rtsi song ba 'dra'o //
NK069(tu)001:14442: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14446: byol song gi du dud ka dang /
NK069(tu)001:14449: 'od dmar po la khrag gi dwangs 'tshal lcog la ba'i khu ba tsam rgyu'o //
NK069(tu)001:14450: khrag gi snyigs ma la du tri gnyis rgyu'o //
NK069(tu)001:14452: 'od dmar po'i 'og na du tri gnyis gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14454: byol song dang dmyal bar skye ba'i kha zin nyon
NK069(tu)001:14455: mongs pa can gyi yid kyis byas nas sa bon
NK069(tu)001:14456: tri dang du la sog go //
NK069(tu)001:14457: yon tan gyi rtsa la lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:14459: dbyibs bya gag gi ze ba 'dra'o //
NK069(tu)001:14460: tshul ni ba thag ma'i rgya ltar 'aphra'o //
NK069(tu)001:14463: las rtogs na yon tan du 'char te /
NK069(tu)001:14464: la sogs pas sku gsung thugs mi bzad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor 'gyur la /
NK069(tu)001:14465: ma rtogs na a n+ri su tri pre du drug gis 'khor ba rigs drug tu 'khyam /
NK069(tu)001:14466: de gnyis 'dres nas byang sems la 'khor 'das tshang bar gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14467: de ltar gnas pas na thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ces bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:14468: gnyis pa bsgom pa'i nyams kyi mchog tu gyur pa ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:14473: de ltar gnas de'i rtsa rnams mdo' gcig tu 'dus pas na /
NK069(tu)001:14475: sa'i dwangs ma dar dkar gyi skud pa 'dra ba ni sangs rgyas spyan /
NK069(tu)001:14476: rtsa de la chu'i dwangs ma mtshal lcog la ba'i
NK069(tu)001:14477: khu ba 'dra ba gnas pa ni ma ma ki
NK069(tu)001:14478: / de la drod kyi dwangs ma me long nyi
NK069(tu)001:14479: ma la bzhag pa'i ngad tsam gnas pa ni gos
NK069(tu)001:14480: / dkar mo / de la dbugs kyi dwangs ma
NK069(tu)001:14481: gser sa 'og tu bcug pa'i rlangs pa tsam gnas
NK069(tu)001:14482: pa ni dam tshig sgrol ma /
NK069(tu)001:14483: de'i nang na thig le stong pa ni yum dbyings phyug ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:14484: de la yab lnga'i dbang du /
NK069(tu)001:14486: dbus stong pa nyid ni chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:14488: de ltar rtsa chos skur bstan na /
NK069(tu)001:14489: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang na /
NK069(tu)001:14490: thig le byang chub sems stong zhing bdag myed pa /
NK069(tu)001:14491: gser zhun ma'i bu gar nor bu rin po che
NK069(tu)001:14492: ze'u ka bcug pa 'dra bar mi sgrib par gsal
NK069(tu)001:14493: ba / nyi ma shar ba'i dkyil ltar bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:14494: de ni sgo bya rang gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14496: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas yab yum longs sku /
NK069(tu)001:14497: sku gsung thugs kyi yi ge sprul sku /
NK069(tu)001:14498: 'gro ba drug gi yi ge sbyang bya /
NK069(tu)001:14499: thig le byang chub sems thob bya de ltas te /
NK069(tu)001:14500: rlung bzung nas thig les 'gro drug gi sa bon gzhu' /
NK069(tu)001:14501: yab yum thabs dang shes rab dbyer myed du thim par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:14503: de ltar thig le byang chub sems su rung na /
NK069(tu)001:14504: sku gsung thugs kyi yi ge'i 'og na /
NK069(tu)001:14505: 'gro drug sa bon yod pa zhu 'od du 'bar te /
NK069(tu)001:14506: thig le rang bzhin myed par gyur /
NK069(tu)001:14507: de la 'gro ba drug rang dag ces bya /
NK069(tu)001:14508: des rtsa dar dkar gyi skud pa rta'i rnga ma bcu tshal tsam pa thim /
NK069(tu)001:14509: de khrag gi dwangs ma la thim pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:14510: sa chu la thim zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:14511: de drod kyi dwangs ma la thim /
NK069(tu)001:14512: chu me la thim zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:14513: de dbugs kyi dwangs ma la thim /
NK069(tu)001:14514: de'i dus na me rlung la thim zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:14515: des bde' ba chen po g.yon nas 'od 'bar te /
NK069(tu)001:14517: rlung rnam par shes pa la thim zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:14518: dwangs ma nyid kyang rang bzhin myed par sor ste /
NK069(tu)001:14519: nam mkha'i gzugs su skyes tsam na /
NK069(tu)001:14520: khams gsum thams cad so so ma yin /
NK069(tu)001:14521: ye shes su lhun gyis grub ste /
NK069(tu)001:14522: chos kyi skur gnas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:14525: des ni thugs kha chos kyi dkyil 'khor du /
NK069(tu)001:14526: kun tu bzang po thig le chos kyi skur bsgom pa bstan pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:14527: gsang ba'i thig le'i dkyil 'khor dbyings //
NK069(tu)001:14528: zhes phyi dbyings ltar bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:14530: lte ba sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor te /
NK069(tu)001:14531: gsang ba b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor dang 'brel ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:14532: 'khor lo'i rang bzhin du yod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14533: nang gsang sngags kyi bdag nyid du bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:14534: phyi dbyibs yi ge ar snang /
NK069(tu)001:14535: nang na bsam gtan gyi dkar po /
NK069(tu)001:14536: shes rab kyi a dmar po /
NK069(tu)001:14538: 'gro drug gi lha'i a dkar po /
NK069(tu)001:14540: lha ma yin gyi su ser po /
NK069(tu)001:14542: yi dwags kyi pri dmar po /
NK069(tu)001:14544: dbus na snying po'i a dkar po dang /
NK069(tu)001:14545: lha srin gyi k+sha dmar nag dang /
NK069(tu)001:14546: stobs kyi h'u mthing ka rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:14548: lte ba na kun gzhi' kun tu bzang mo'i sa
NK069(tu)001:14549: bon thig le nyungs dkar 'bring po tsam gnas de
NK069(tu)001:14550: / des ma lte dang bu lter 'brel /
NK069(tu)001:14551: mas zos pa'i bcud bu'i lte ba nas gso' /
NK069(tu)001:14552: rtogs na lhan gcig skyes pa'i ye shes 'char /
NK069(tu)001:14553: de ltar 'khor 'das tshang bas dkyil 'khor ro //
NK069(tu)001:14554: rtogs na kun tu bzang mo /
NK069(tu)001:14555: shes rab chos dbyings su 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:14557: bde' ba 'char ba'i rlung me dang mnyam pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14558: 'byung ba shes rab rigs kyi yum //
NK069(tu)001:14559: zhes gong ltar kun tu bzang po thugs kar 'byongs nas /
NK069(tu)001:14560: thig le lte bar phab pas /
NK069(tu)001:14562: sa'i dar ma dar dkar gyi skud pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:14563: 'byung ba sa lta bur snang nas /
NK069(tu)001:14564: sdod ma nas phung po'i rten byed pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:14567: stong pa chen po'i ye shes te /
NK069(tu)001:14568: thams cad dbyings rnam par dag pa'i thig le'i ngang
NK069(tu)001:14569: du 'gyur ba myed pa'i rten byed pa'i las can
NK069(tu)001:14570: no // chu'i dwangs ma mtshal lcog la ba'i khu ba lta bu ni /
NK069(tu)001:14571: gdod ma nas phung po'i long 'dogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:14574: de rtogs na mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes te /
NK069(tu)001:14575: ye shes des thams cad dbri skol myed par dbyings su sdud pa'i las can no //
NK069(tu)001:14576: drod kyi dwangs ma me long nyi ma la bzhag pa'i ngad tsam ni /
NK069(tu)001:14577: sdod ma nas lus smin par byed pa'i rang bzhin 'byung ba me ltar snang ste /
NK069(tu)001:14579: de rtogs na so sor rtog pa'i ye shes te /
NK069(tu)001:14580: ye shes des thams cad bde ba chen po'i dbyings su rtogs pa'i sgron me'o //
NK069(tu)001:14581: dbugs kyi dwangs ma gser sa 'og tu mnan pa'i rlangs pa tsam pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:14582: gdod ma nas phung po yang zhing g.yo' bar byed pa'i las can te /
NK069(tu)001:14583: 'byung ba rlung ltar snang bas yum dam tshig sgrol ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:14584: de rtogs na bya ba grub pa'i ye shes te /
NK069(tu)001:14585: bde' ba chen po'i dbyings su skyod pa'i las can no //
NK069(tu)001:14586: de dag 'od kha dog sna tshogs su snang zhing stong ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:14588: sdod ma nas phung po stong pa'i las can te /
NK069(tu)001:14589: 'byung ba nam mkha' ltar snang bas /
NK069(tu)001:14591: de rtogs na me long lta bu'o ye shes te /
NK069(tu)001:14593: de bas na rgyu 'byung ba lnga /
NK069(tu)001:14594: rkyen shes rab kyis stong par rtogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:14596: 'bras bu ye shes lnga dang dbyer myed par gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14597: gsang ba'i thig ler bshad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14598: chen po rigs kyi de bzhin te //
NK069(tu)001:14599: zhes de kho na nyid snying po ye shes kyi rlung du bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:14600: 'byung ba chen po ni rigs kyi yab lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:14601: nam mkha' ltar khyab pa'i rlung dang /
NK069(tu)001:14602: sa ltar bstan pa'i rlung dang /
NK069(tu)001:14604: me dang drod mnyam pa'i rlung dang /
NK069(tu)001:14605: rlung ltar yang ba'i rlung lnga'o //
NK069(tu)001:14606: de la nam mkha' ltar khyab pa'i rlung ni bdun te /
NK069(tu)001:14609: zin na rtags shes pa gsal la yang /
NK069(tu)001:14612: rgyu tshul ni 'chi ba'i tshe na rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:14614: lha rnam par snang mdzad do //
NK069(tu)001:14615: sa ltar brtan pa'i rlung ni bdun te /
NK069(tu)001:14616: gnas ni tshigs dang mdangs thams cad la gnas /
NK069(tu)001:14617: las ni tshigs rnams skyed par byed /
NK069(tu)001:14618: zin na rtags lus bde' la yang /
NK069(tu)001:14619: ma chun nas log na tshigs khengs nas na /
NK069(tu)001:14620: rgyu tshul ni dal zhing rgyu ba myed pa ltar bstan /
NK069(tu)001:14622: lha rdo rje sems dpa' yin /
NK069(tu)001:14623: chu dang 'grogs pa'i rlung bdun te /
NK069(tu)001:14624: gnas lkog ma'am snying kha na gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:14625: las ni gyen du rgyu zhing ldang bar byed do //
NK069(tu)001:14626: zin na rtags shes pa gsal zhing /
NK069(tu)001:14632: sna bug gnyis ka nas dal bar rgyu'o //
NK069(tu)001:14635: me dang drod mnyam pa'i rlung la bdun te /
NK069(tu)001:14638: zin na rtags shes pa gsal zhing pho ba 'de' /
NK069(tu)001:14639: ma chun nas log na rmu chur 'gro /
NK069(tu)001:14643: lha snang ba mtha' yas so //
NK069(tu)001:14644: rlung ltar yang ba'i rlung ni bdun te /
NK069(tu)001:14646: las dri chu thur du sel /
NK069(tu)001:14647: zin na rtags shes pa gsal zhing 'og rlung bde' /
NK069(tu)001:14648: ma chun nas log na dri chu sdom mo //
NK069(tu)001:14652: lha ni don yod grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14653: rlung lnga po de log nas mnon na /
NK069(tu)001:14654: rgyud tshig zab mo'i lta bas log mnan /
NK069(tu)001:14655: byin brlabs can gyi bla ma spyii bor bsgom la log mnan /
NK069(tu)001:14656: bsod nams cad kyi tshogs 'khor byas /
NK069(tu)001:14657: la log mnan lus kyi 'khrul 'khor byas pa log mnan no //
NK069(tu)001:14658: de la rlung lnga la chen por 'jog pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:14659: tha ma pa'i lus kyi bya ba byed pas che /
NK069(tu)001:14660: rnal 'byor pa'i dngos grub sgrub pas che /
NK069(tu)001:14661: 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob par byed pas che'o //
NK069(tu)001:14662: de yang bshad rgyud khro bo chen po stobs kyi rnal 'byor dbang phyug sgrub pa'i rgyud las /
NK069(tu)001:14663: sa yi rlung dang chu dang me //
NK069(tu)001:14664: rlung dang rim bzhin 'byung byed pa //
NK069(tu)001:14665: gyen dang thur du 'byung bar byed //
NK069(tu)001:14666: gyen du g.yas g.yon gnyis ka nas //
NK069(tu)001:14667: dal drag rim par rgyu ba ni //
NK069(tu)001:14669: gsang ba thig le dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:14670: dri chen gyi dwangs ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:14672: byang chub sems kyi dwangs ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:14673: sha chen gyi dwangs ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:14674: dri chu'i dwangs ma dang rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:14675: de yang rtsa'i mdud pa re re'i nang na /
NK069(tu)001:14676: thig le re re rlung re re gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14677: rtsa 'khor lo bzhi dang bcas pa la khyab par gnas pa kha na'o //
NK069(tu)001:14681: de kho na ltar bde' ba dang sbyar nas bshad pas rang la gnas tshul shes la /
NK069(tu)001:14682: 'byung ba 'byongs tshul nas bshad pas rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi khyad par ni /
NK069(tu)001:14683: 'byung ba chen po lngar bshad pas sangs rgyas rigs lnga'i dgongs pa rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14685: byang chub sems ni rdo rje'i tshogs //
NK069(tu)001:14687: dbang po yul sems ma dus sems ma rig khro bo rnams pa'i rnams //
NK069(tu)001:14688: zhes de kho na nyid rlung dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:14689: byang chub sems dpa' yab yum rnams ni /
NK069(tu)001:14690: skye 'jig med pa'i rdo rje ste /
NK069(tu)001:14691: rgyu ba'i rlung dmyigs la gnas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14692: rab tu rgyu ba rna ba la gnas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14693: shin tu rgyu ba sna la gnas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14694: mngon par rgyu ba lce la gnas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14695: yang dag par rgyu ba lus la gnas pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:14696: de la rgyu ba'i rlung ni /
NK069(tu)001:14699: zin na dmig gi mngon shes thob /
NK069(tu)001:14700: ma chun na dmig skyon yong /
NK069(tu)001:14701: rang bzhin ni dmig gi rnam shes sa'i snying po dang /
NK069(tu)001:14702: de'i yul sgeg mor rig pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14703: dmig gi dbang po byams pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14704: dpyid kyi dus spos ma rnams su rlung des rig par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:14705: rab tu rgyu ba'i rlung ni /
NK069(tu)001:14706: gnas rna ba gnyis la gnas /
NK069(tu)001:14708: zin pa'i yon tan snyan gyi mngon shes 'char /
NK069(tu)001:14709: ma chun na rna ba'i sgra skyon yong /
NK069(tu)001:14711: rna ba'i rnam par shes pa phyag na rdo rje dang /
NK069(tu)001:14713: rna ba'i dbang po 'jam dpal dang /
NK069(tu)001:14714: rgyun gyi dus su dri chab ma rnams rlung des 'byed rig par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:14718: zin na rdzu 'phrul gyi mngon shes 'char /
NK069(tu)001:14719: ma chun na sna la skyon yongs /
NK069(tu)001:14721: sna'i rnam shes nam mkha'i snying po dang /
NK069(tu)001:14723: sna'i dbang po sgrib sel dang /
NK069(tu)001:14724: dbyar gyi dus su me tog ma rnams su rig par byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14728: zin na yon tan ni sngon gyi gnas dran pa'i mngon shes 'thob /
NK069(tu)001:14729: ma chun na lce la skyon yong /
NK069(tu)001:14730: rang bzhin lce'i rnam par shes pa spyan ras gzigs dang /
NK069(tu)001:14732: lce'i dbang po kun bzang dang /
NK069(tu)001:14733: ston gyi dus mar me ma rnams su rig par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:14734: yang dag par rgyu ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:14737: zin na gzhan gyi sems shes pa'i mngon shes 'char /
NK069(tu)001:14738: ma chun na lus la skyon yong /
NK069(tu)001:14740: lus kyi rnam par shes pa bzhi khro bo bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:14741: de'i yul bzhi khro mor rig go //
NK069(tu)001:14742: de yang khro bo stobs kyi rgyud las /
NK069(tu)001:14743: rgyu ba'i gnas ni spyan yin te //
NK069(tu)001:14744: rnam par rgyu ba rna ba la //
NK069(tu)001:14745: yang dag rgyu ba sna dang ni //
NK069(tu)001:14746: rab tu rgyu ba lce la g.yas //
NK069(tu)001:14747: nges par rgyu ba lus nyid de //
NK069(tu)001:14748: dmyig dang rna ba sna dang lce //
NK069(tu)001:14749: sa snying la sogs sems dpa' brgyad //
NK069(tu)001:14750: rnam shes dbang pos phyi nang phye //
NK069(tu)001:14751: yul brgyad 'dzin pas rnam bzung ba //
NK069(tu)001:14752: phyi nang sems ma brgyad du shar //
NK069(tu)001:14753: ces pa la sogs pa gsungs pas gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:14754: kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK069(tu)001:14755: zhes rang bzhin kun tu bzang po ni /
NK069(tu)001:14756: rtsa rlung thig le yi ge rnams kyi rang bzhin lhar dag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14757: dus kun tu bzang po ni /
NK069(tu)001:14758: ye sdod ma nas rtogs rung ma rtogs rung sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14759: de ltar yid kyi rnam par shes pas rig cing rtogs pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:14760: chos thams cad yid rang 'byung gi ye shes su 'dus /
NK069(tu)001:14761: yid rang 'byung gi ye shes de kho na kun tu bzang po yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:14762: de ltar bas na spyod yul thams cad kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor yin pa de la /
NK069(tu)001:14763: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po bdag nyid chen po'i lta zhing bsgom par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:14764: bdag nyid chen po lhag pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:14765: zhes kun tu bzang po'i thugs ye shes rtogs pas bdag nyid /
NK069(tu)001:14766: dgos pa rang la tshang bas chen po /
NK069(tu)001:14767: sems can gyi sems las lhag par gyur pas /
NK069(tu)001:14768: rgyal ba rang la gnas par rnyed pas yid ces bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:14769: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen por gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14770: thugs kyi ye shes lnga lta zhing //
NK069(tu)001:14771: zhes rang gi sems nyid stong pa chos dbyings ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:14772: gsal ba me long ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:14773: mkhyen pa so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:14774: thams cad gcig par shes pa mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:14775: sangs rgyas thams cad rang la gnas pa bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:14776: 'dir rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen pos rang gi thugs kyi ye shes la lta zhing bsgom ste /
NK069(tu)001:14777: dang po bsgom pa'i gnad ni /
NK069(tu)001:14779: rang gi rkang mthil gnyis su ram dmar nag bsam /
NK069(tu)001:14780: rkang mthil skyod rlung kha sbyar bas /
NK069(tu)001:14781: me 'bar nas long bu'i rtsa nang na yar song bas /
NK069(tu)001:14782: barla'i rtsa bo che'i nang na yar la zhugs /
NK069(tu)001:14784: me de yang 'phra zhing rno ba /
NK069(tu)001:14789: zas dang spyod kham gyis lcag gis skul /
NK069(tu)001:14791: de la nyams ma skyes pa skyed pa'i don du rab zhag gsum bya /
NK069(tu)001:14792: skyes pa thogs dbyung ba'i don du 'bring zhag lnga /
NK069(tu)001:14793: nyams bstan pa'i phyir tha ma zhag dagu'o //
NK069(tu)001:14794: lte ba man chad du thig le 'thab mo bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:14795: me'i rtse mo thig le dkar po sran ma tsam /
NK069(tu)001:14796: de'i steng du thig le dkar po de bas che bas de la rgyab bas /
NK069(tu)001:14797: 'od zer gyis nang thams cad gang bar bsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:14798: de nas yang dmigs pa 'phos te /
NK069(tu)001:14799: snying kha man chad du thig le'i rtse mo la
NK069(tu)001:14800: me sko ru ltar 'khor bas thams cad mes gang
NK069(tu)001:14801: / de nas yang dmigs pa 'phos te /
NK069(tu)001:14802: mgrin pa man chad du me 'khor ro la 'khor bar bsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:14803: de nas yang dmigs pa 'phos te /
NK069(tu)001:14804: spyi bo man chad me dmar chi li li khengs par bsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:14805: de nas yang dmigs pa 'phos te /
NK069(tu)001:14806: spyi bo'i thig le zhu nas sam /
NK069(tu)001:14807: yang na snying kha'i gnas lugs rnams zhu nas lte bar bsam /
NK069(tu)001:14808: lte ba nas gyen du 'phros pas /
NK069(tu)001:14809: thugs ka nas ye shes lnga'i 'od du 'bar ba la /
NK069(tu)001:14811: lte bar kun tu bzang mo bsgom pa'i man ngag go //
NK069(tu)001:14813: gzhung tshod rtsi na snying ka man chad bde gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:14814: snying po'i thig le mnyam sbyor bas //
NK069(tu)001:14815: zhes snying po ni lte ba sprul pa'i 'khor lo chos kyi dbyings kyi snying po'o //
NK069(tu)001:14816: snying po chos kyi 'khor lo ye shes kyi snying po'o //
NK069(tu)001:14817: dbyings kyi thig le stong pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14818: ye shes kyi thig le gsal ba gnyis 'dres nas /
NK069(tu)001:14819: mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo dang mnyam par sbyor bas /
NK069(tu)001:14820: bde ba'i ye shes rol mo yis //
NK069(tu)001:14821: zhes dbyings ye shes 'dres pa'i thig le de /
NK069(tu)001:14828: ye shes kyi ro bde gsal mi rtog par gyur pa de /
NK069(tu)001:14829: cir yang snang bas rol mo lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:14830: de lta bu de mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo la bde' ba chen por gnas pa yis /
NK069(tu)001:14831: ye shes dgyes la mchod par 'bul //
NK069(tu)001:14832: zhes ye shes ni rang gnas kyi don shes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14833: dgyes pa ni rang gnas rtogs par 'dod cing dga' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:14835: snang ba thams cad bde ba chen por lhun gyis grub par 'dod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14836: des kyang mi g.yo bar gnas par 'dod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14837: 'dir mgrin pa longs spyod kyi 'khor lo sbyor ba dag pa'i man ngag la /
NK069(tu)001:14838: bdag nyid lus lcog bur sdad nas /
NK069(tu)001:14839: rang gi dbugs phyir ldang ba'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:14840: g.yas rtsa ro ma nyi ma me'i rang bzhin kha dog dmar por sal gyis gyur /
NK069(tu)001:14841: dbugs nang du 'jug pa'i dus su g.yon rkyang ma
NK069(tu)001:14842: zla ba chu'i rang bzhin kha dog dkar sal gyis
NK069(tu)001:14843: gyur / dbugs gnas pa'i dus su dbus kyi kun d+har ma de ni /
NK069(tu)001:14844: pad ma'i rnal ma ltar ni 'phra /
NK069(tu)001:14845: chu shing gi snying po ltar ni drang /
NK069(tu)001:14846: til gyi mar me ltar ni gsal /
NK069(tu)001:14847: rgya skyegs kyi me tog ltar dmar krug gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:14848: bsus pa'i spu ne gu'i thad ka na /
NK069(tu)001:14849: khrag gi thig le'i nang na rtsa gsum 'dzom nas /
NK069(tu)001:14850: lte ba dang snying kha'i thig le gnyis mgrin par 'khyil lo //
NK069(tu)001:14851: der thig le mnyam par sbyor bas /
NK069(tu)001:14852: thig le bde ba'i ye shes des /
NK069(tu)001:14853: mgrin pa'i zas la dgyes pa la bdud rtsi lngas mchod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14854: zag pa myed pa'i bsod nams kyis //
NK069(tu)001:14855: zhes mgrin pa'i thig le de /
NK069(tu)001:14858: dbyings ye shes gnyis myed de rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:14859: des bag chags thams cad dag pas na zag myed /
NK069(tu)001:14860: ris drug rang dag pas bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14861: ye shes sgyu mar rang snang ba //
NK069(tu)001:14862: zhes bde ba'i thig le de ye shes yin la /
NK069(tu)001:14863: ye shes de dngos por ma grub pas sgyu ma dang 'dra la /
NK069(tu)001:14864: ye shes sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid rang gis rtogs nas rig pa rang snang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:14865: rol mo'i dkyil 'khor mtha' yas mchog /
NK069(tu)001:14866: ces rang las byung nas rang snyes pas rol mo /
NK069(tu)001:14867: rtog tshogs kyi lha thams cad dbyer myed gcig tu gyur pas /
NK069(tu)001:14868: dkyil 'khor mtha' yas pa rnams yang /
NK069(tu)001:14869: bde ba chen po'i thig le mchog tu gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14870: gsang ba'i thig le nyid kyi dbyings //
NK069(tu)001:14871: zhes de rtogs par ka bas na gsang /
NK069(tu)001:14872: thams cad bde' ba chen po gcig tu gyur pas na thig le /
NK069(tu)001:14873: thig le de nyid spros pa dang bral bas /
NK069(tu)001:14875: de ni sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK069(tu)001:14876: zhes dbyings ye shes 'du 'bral myed pa de ni /
NK069(tu)001:14877: sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos gzhir bzhugs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14878: 'dir spyi bo bde' ba chen po brdal khyab chen po'i man ngag ni /
NK069(tu)001:14879: mgrin pa'i thig le rtsa kun d+har ma'i nang na yar song ste /
NK069(tu)001:14880: me long gi ngos ltar 'jam la gsal ba /
NK069(tu)001:14881: ral gri'i so ltar gcod pa /
NK069(tu)001:14882: mdung gi rtse ltar rno ba /
NK069(tu)001:14883: nyi ma'i 'od ltar mtsher bar song nas /
NK069(tu)001:14886: zla ba'i thig le zhu nas /
NK069(tu)001:14887: thur du babs pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:14888: glo ba rgyangs ba ltar ni ltar ltar byung /
NK069(tu)001:14889: nyi ma shar ba ltar ni gsal gsal gyur /
NK069(tu)001:14890: nam langs pa ltar ni sangs sangs gyur /
NK069(tu)001:14891: nyi ma'i snying po ltar gsal la mi rtog pas lus mer gyis gang nas /
NK069(tu)001:14892: spang bya ma rigs pa'i snang ba las log pa chos can /
NK069(tu)001:14893: yid kun tags dang bral bas chos nyid /
NK069(tu)001:14894: chos can chos nyid dbyer myed du gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:14895: spang bya ma rig pa'i zhen pa thams cad dag cing spang nas /
NK069(tu)001:14896: thob bya sku dang ye shes kyi snang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:14897: chos sku bde' ba chen po thob pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:14898: de'i dus su nyams sems la shar bas chos su nyams su myong /
NK069(tu)001:14899: bag chags rmi lam du shar bas /
NK069(tu)001:14900: chos nyid kyi snang bar rmi /
NK069(tu)001:14902: spyod pa ma bcos lhug par 'gyur /
NK069(tu)001:14903: mthong snang yul la shar ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:14904: snang ba 'di nyid chos kyi sku'i zhing khams su mthong bar gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14905: rang zhal rang gis mthong ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:14906: phyogs bcu dus bzhir mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:14907: zhes phyogs bcu na ni bzhugs /
NK069(tu)001:14909: mngon par rdzogs par ni sangs rgyas /
NK069(tu)001:14910: sku dang ye shes ni mthar phyin pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams /
NK069(tu)001:14911: sku gsung yon tan 'phrin las thugs //
NK069(tu)001:14912: zhes sku rnam snang gi rigs dang /
NK069(tu)001:14914: yon tan rin 'byung gi rigs dang /
NK069(tu)001:14915: 'phrin las don grub kyi rigs dang /
NK069(tu)001:14916: thugs mi bskyod pa'i rigs dang /
NK069(tu)001:14917: yang na sku lnga lhun grub kyi rgyal po'o //
NK069(tu)001:14918: ma lus bdag nyid zhal mthong ba //
NK069(tu)001:14919: zhes sangs rgyas ma lus pa zhal mthong ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:14920: rtsa rlung thig le sngags kyi don rtogs pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:14921: dbang sgyur mchog gi dam pa yin //
NK069(tu)001:14922: ces de ltar rtogs pa'i dus na chos thams cad la ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du dbang sgyur /
NK069(tu)001:14923: yon tan gyi mchog dang ldan pa'i bdag nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:14924: yang na sgron ma rlung ngam rtsa rlung gi tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin thob ste /
NK069(tu)001:14925: lus gzhon sha chags nas skra dkar myed pas 'gro ba gzhan gyi yid du 'ong ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:14926: rnam par smin pas lus stobs 'phel bas rdzu 'phrul ston nus pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14927: mtshan dpe' 'phel bas lces longs spyod bdud rtsi'i ro myong ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:14928: sgrib pa myed pa'i tshe nyi zla dang mnyam zhing mngon shes 'char ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:14929: mchog gi yon tan dam pa 'thob pa'i phyir tshe la dbang bsgyur ba thob pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14931: chos sku dri ma myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14932: longs sku 'dod pa la longs spyod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14933: sprul sku mdzad pa bcu gnyis mthar phyin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14934: rdo rje'i sku dbyer mi phyed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:14935: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku ye shes sgyu ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:14937: chos sku brjod myed don gyi gsung /
NK069(tu)001:14938: longs sku dgongs pa brda' yi gsung /
NK069(tu)001:14939: sprul sku sna tshogs tshig gi gsung /
NK069(tu)001:14940: rdo rje grags stong dbyer myed gsung /
NK069(tu)001:14941: mngon byang rig pa sgyu ma'i gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:14949: zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:14951: 'bras bu dang tshe dbang dus gcig pa 'gal zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:14953: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las smos pa ni 'bras bu dngos yin la /
NK069(tu)001:14954: dbang sgyur mchog ni tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin te /
NK069(tu)001:14955: 'bras bu mthar phyin pa de nyid /
NK069(tu)001:14956: tshe la dbang ba'i rig 'dzin gyis /
NK069(tu)001:14957: zag pa myed pa'i mthong lam du zhal mthong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:14958: dkyil 'khor thams cad rang la shar ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:14960: ces 'bras bu rdzogs shing mthar phyin pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor la gnas pas /
NK069(tu)001:14961: bdag gi rig pa rang snang ba'i chos thams cad dang dbyer myed pa nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:14963: 'bras bu rdzogs shing mthar phyin pa'i bde' bar gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK069(tu)001:14964: rig pa rang snang ba'i chos la gnas shing /
NK069(tu)001:14965: dbyer myed pas dkyil 'khor la gnas /
NK069(tu)001:14966: de ltar snang ba yang rang gi rig pa rang snang la /
NK069(tu)001:14967: rig pa rang gi gnas su dag par rtogs pa de kho na /
NK069(tu)001:14968: thugs ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gyi bdag nyid yin pas dkyil 'khor nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:14969: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub //
NK069(tu)001:14971: rang gi rig par rang snang la /
NK069(tu)001:14972: rig pa rang gi ngo bo stong zhing gnas su
NK069(tu)001:14973: dag par rtogs pa de kho na rang la yang
NK069(tu)001:14974: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor rnams
NK069(tu)001:14975: ma lus par lhun grub tu rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14977: bdag gi rig pa thugs ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gyi bdag nyid du rtogs pa de la ni /
NK069(tu)001:14978: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dang ldan pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:14979: rtsal ba myed par lhun gyis grub par gnas pas lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14980: rgyan du dkyil 'khor ma lus thogs //
NK069(tu)001:14981: zhes thugs ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor gyi bdag nyid la /
NK069(tu)001:14982: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pas mdzes par rgyan pas na /
NK069(tu)001:14983: de bas na dkyil 'khor ma lus rgyan du thogs so //
NK069(tu)001:14984: de ltar bdag gi rig pa bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK069(tu)001:14985: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dang dbyer myed par
NK069(tu)001:14986: gnas pas / bdag gi rig pa'i rgyan du sku
NK069(tu)001:14987: gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa mdzes par
NK069(tu)001:14989: rtog tshogs rang la rang chas su rgyan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:14990: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor mnyam sbyor bas //
NK069(tu)001:14991: zhes rang gi rig pa thugs ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rtogs pa de la ni /
NK069(tu)001:14992: tshogs rdzogs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dang ldan pas sangs rgyas dang mnyam par sbyor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:14993: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:14994: rdzogs pa chen por lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:14995: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas su
NK069(tu)001:14996: ma gyur ba gcig kyang myed pas rdzogs pa'i dkyil
NK069(tu)001:14997: 'khor / de lta bur rang gi blos mnyam par sbyor bas so //
NK069(tu)001:15000: zhes de la the tshom zhig rgal te /
NK069(tu)001:15001: 'o na chos thams cad sangs rgyas pa yin na /
NK069(tu)001:15002: chos thams cad kyi khongs su ni sems can yang rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:15003: sems can yang sangs rgyas yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:15004: sangs rgyas kyis sems can gyi don mi byed pa zhig yin nam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15006: de bzhin gshegs pas ni 'khor ba dang mya ngan
NK069(tu)001:15007: las 'das pa'i chos thams cad rdzogs par chen por
NK069(tu)001:15008: lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:15009: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du dbyer myed par sangs rgyas pa yang shes rab kyis rtogs la /
NK069(tu)001:15010: ting nge 'dzin gyis kyang sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du mnyam pa rtse gcig tu 'byor ba las /
NK069(tu)001:15011: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas kyi rang bzhin mkhyen la /
NK069(tu)001:15012: sems can gyis de ltar ma rtogs shing khams gsum du 'khor ba mkhyen cing /
NK069(tu)001:15015: thugs rje'i sar ma lus par /
NK069(tu)001:15017: ngang ngam yongs kyis yang don mdzad pas /
NK069(tu)001:15021: zhes de ltar phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis sdus pa'i
NK069(tu)001:15022: chos thams cad sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK069(tu)001:15024: sangs rgyas pa yin phan cad /
NK069(tu)001:15025: bde' bar gshegs pa'i thugs rjes don mdzad pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:15027: dkyil 'khor gyis dkyil 'khor sgrol bar mdzad pas dkyil 'khor 'dul ba'i mgon /
NK069(tu)001:15029: sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor bsgom pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:15030: zhes de yang ji ltar don mdzad zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15031: sgyu ma mkhan gyis rde'u dang shing bu la sgyu ma'i mtsho' da kyil nas /
NK069(tu)001:15032: sgyu ma'i mi dang rdzas sgyu ma'i rdzings la bzhag nas /
NK069(tu)001:15033: sgyu ma'i gru pas sgrol tsam na /
NK069(tu)001:15036: sgral bar bya ba'i mi dang /
NK069(tu)001:15037: rdzas gang yang dngos por grub pa myed pa de dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:15038: 'khor lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor nas /
NK069(tu)001:15039: sems can nyon mongs pa lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor /
NK069(tu)001:15040: thugs rje lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor gyis /
NK069(tu)001:15041: mya ngan las 'das pa lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du sgrol bar mdzad de /
NK069(tu)001:15042: sgrol tsam nyid na dngos por ni sgyu ma dang
NK069(tu)001:15043: dra bas sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor sgrol ba zhes bya'o
NK069(tu)001:15044: // bya byed myed par dkyil 'khor spyod //
NK069(tu)001:15045: ces don dam par don bya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:15046: don byed pa'i dngos por grub pa myed par /
NK069(tu)001:15047: kun rdzob du gong ma lta bu'i dkyil 'khor gyis 'gro ba'i don spyod do //
NK069(tu)001:15048: yang na don bya ba dang byed pa tsam nyid na /
NK069(tu)001:15049: bya ba myed pa'i mthar phyin par rtogs pa'i sgo nas /
NK069(tu)001:15050: gong ma lta bu'i dal gyis 'gro ba'i don spyod do //
NK069(tu)001:15051: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK069(tu)001:15052: zhes lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du /
NK069(tu)001:15053: rig pa'i me tog gang gis skye zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15054: chos thams cad bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i ngo bo /
NK069(tu)001:15055: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du /
NK069(tu)001:15056: sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du gnas pa la /
NK069(tu)001:15057: gang gis de la don rtogs shing rig pa'i me tog skye zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15058: ye gdod ma nyid nas sbyangs pa'i las 'phro myed pa phal la mi skye ste /
NK069(tu)001:15059: thos bsam bsgom pa'i mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK069(tu)001:15060: zhes 'o na gang gis rtogs zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15061: thos pa nyan pa'i shes rab dang /
NK069(tu)001:15064: shes rab rnam pa gsum gyis rig pa'i rgyud sbyangs shing /
NK069(tu)001:15065: yang dag pa'i shes rab zab cing rgya che ba /
NK069(tu)001:15066: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis rtogs shing /
NK069(tu)001:15067: de'i don la rtogs pa rda 'byal gyis mnyam par sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:15068: rang 'byung kun ngam lhun gyis grub //
NK069(tu)001:15069: ces chos thams cad lhun gyis grub par rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa de la ni /
NK069(tu)001:15070: rang gi rang bzhin du rang 'byung ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:15071: rang gi rig pa sbyangs pa las byung ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:15072: rang 'byung gi sangs rgyas kun yang ngam zhing ngo mtshar skyes nas /
NK069(tu)001:15073: lhun gyis grub pa'i dngos grub brtsol zhing byin gyis brlab par mdzad pas /
NK069(tu)001:15074: lhun gyis grub pa zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:15075: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:15076: zhes rdzogs pa chen por lhun gyis grub pa gsang ba'i man ngag gi don 'di las ni /
NK069(tu)001:15077: sangs rgyas thams cad kyis kyang mda' bar mi mdzad pa'i dam tshig mchog ni /
NK069(tu)001:15078: rtsa dang rlung dang thig le'i man ngag dam pa
NK069(tu)001:15079: shin tu yang gsang ba 'di yin no zhe 'am
NK069(tu)001:15080: / mda' bar mi mdzad dam tshig mchog /
NK069(tu)001:15081: ces yang ni gong ma ltar /
NK069(tu)001:15082: chos thams cad lhun gyis grub pa'i don /
NK069(tu)001:15083: gsang ba'i man ngag gi don rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa de ni /
NK069(tu)001:15084: sangs rgyas thams cad kyis kyang dngos grub brtsol zhing
NK069(tu)001:15085: byin gyis barloba pa las myi 'da' bas 'da' bar
NK069(tu)001:15086: mi mdzad de / ci ste zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15087: gzhung bzhin du bsgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pa la /
NK069(tu)001:15088: bde' bar gshegs pas dngos grub ma rtsol na /
NK069(tu)001:15089: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sngon gyi thugs dam nyams pas /
NK069(tu)001:15090: 'o tang de bzhin gshegs pa'i yang nyams pas snyems nas /
NK069(tu)001:15091: dngos grub rtsol ba las mi 'da' bas dam tshig mchog ces so //
NK069(tu)001:15092: gang zhig 'di la mos gyur pa //
NK069(tu)001:15093: zhes rnal 'byor pa gang zhig gam /
NK069(tu)001:15095: gsang ba'i man ngag 'di'i don nam /
NK069(tu)001:15101: dad pas ja 'chi ma 'khrug pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15102: ba spu ldang ba tsam du mos shing /
NK069(tu)001:15103: 'di la yid ches par gyur pa'i rnal 'byor pa la /
NK069(tu)001:15104: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor thams cad kyis //
NK069(tu)001:15105: ces dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas sam /
NK069(tu)001:15106: skal pa bye ma snyed kyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyis /
NK069(tu)001:15107: phyogs dus kun nas thams cad du //
NK069(tu)001:15110: rnam pa thams cad nas dus thams cad kun tu /
NK069(tu)001:15111: dkyil 'khor ma lus snyen pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:15112: zhes sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa /
NK069(tu)001:15113: snyen snyen sgrubs sgrubs pa'i dngos grub thams cad ma
NK069(tu)001:15114: nor bar snyen cing thob pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK069(tu)001:15115: 'khor gyis / nye ba'i sras su dgongs par 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:15116: ces sangs rgyas kyi sras dang nyan thos yang yin na /
NK069(tu)001:15117: de las khyad par du nye ba'i sras /
NK069(tu)001:15118: sa thob pa'i byang chub sems dpa' lta bur thugs kyi sras su dgongs par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:15119: sngon sbyangs pa'i 'bras bu yin par bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15120: skal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du //
NK069(tu)001:15121: zhes rnyed par dka' zhing dkon pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15122: da ltar gnas cig tu 'dus nas /
NK069(tu)001:15123: rgyud 'di gsang ba'i man ngag gi don 'chad cing nyan pa de yang /
NK069(tu)001:15124: da lta 'phral du blo 'ur gyi rgyu rkyen gyis sgrubs pa ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:15125: skal pa gcig la yang yun bsam gyis mi khyab pa gcig yod la /
NK069(tu)001:15126: skal pa yun ring po de lta bu'i drangs rdul snyed dang mnyam pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:15127: shin tu sbyangs la rab gnas pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:15128: zhes shin tu khyad par du /
NK069(tu)001:15132: blo mi ldog pa la rab tu gnas shing /
NK069(tu)001:15133: dkyil 'khor ma lus snyen pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:15134: zhes sangs rgyas kyi sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:15135: sngon nas snyen snyen sgrubs sgrubs pa'i 'bras bu gang yin pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15137: zhes gsang chen ni rgyud 'adi'am gsang ba'i man ngag gi le'u 'di thos sam /
NK069(tu)001:15138: 'di'i don tshig tsam ma yin par blo'i ting du ni go //
NK069(tu)001:15139: shes rab kyis phyin ci ma log par rtogs par byed dgos so //
NK069(tu)001:15141: skal pa nas sbyangs pa'i 'bras bu rgyud 'di dang phrad pa yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:15143: sngon du skal par sbyangs pa ma yin pa 'dir 'jug tu mi stub sam /
NK069(tu)001:15147: 'bras bu sangs rgyas thob pa gnyis dus nye ring 'dra bar 'dug ste /
NK069(tu)001:15148: 'bras bu'i ring thag nyan thos yin pas kyang skal pa rgyar tshogs sog dgos pa yin pa la /
NK069(tu)001:15149: 'di de bas kyang ring ngo mnyam pa la /
NK069(tu)001:15151: skal par sbyangs nas rang rang gi 'bras bu thob kar sdong 'dir 'jug dgos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15152: dus gsum na gnas pas kyang 'di rtogs nas sangs rgya bar bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15153: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na //
NK069(tu)001:15154: 'gro ba rigs drug gi 'jig rten na /
NK069(tu)001:15155: phan tshun nam yang man drug gi phyogs bcu na /
NK069(tu)001:15157: zhes sngar rgyu 'bras spyad zin de 'das pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15160: da ltar bgrod pa'i lam yin /
NK069(tu)001:15161: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus la //
NK069(tu)001:15162: dus gsum 'khor ba'i g.yul las rgyal ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:15163: gtso' 'khor dang bcas pa ma lus pa thams cad kyis kyang /
NK069(tu)001:15164: mnyes nas sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:15165: zhes 'das dang da ltar gyi sangs rgyas pas kyang
NK069(tu)001:15166: gsang ba'i man ngag 'di'i don rtogs shing snyes nas
NK069(tu)001:15167: sdod sku lnga lhun grub kyi sangs rgyas thob pa
NK069(tu)001:15168: yin no // yang na 'jig rten phan tshun yan man drug gi phyogs bcu na /
NK069(tu)001:15170: da ltar byung ba'i rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pas kyang /
NK069(tu)001:15171: gsang ba'i man ngag gi don 'di rtogs shing mnyes nas /
NK069(tu)001:15172: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i dngos grub rdzogs la /
NK069(tu)001:15174: ma 'ongs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad kun yang /
NK069(tu)001:15175: gsang ba'i man ngag gi don 'di rtogs pa yis /
NK069(tu)001:15176: sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa'i dngos grub thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:15178: zhes rgyu 'bras ma 'tshogs pas 'byung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:15179: rgyu 'bras yul du ma gyur bas na ma 'ongs pa thams cad kun /
NK069(tu)001:15180: 'di gsang ba'i snying po yis 'bras bu sku lnga lhun gyis grub par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:15181: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:15182: 'bras bu la lam du byed na /
NK069(tu)001:15183: 'bras bu nyan pa la byed dam /
NK069(tu)001:15184: 'bras bu smin cing grol ba la byed dam /
NK069(tu)001:15186: nyan pa la byas na 'bras bur mi 'gro /
NK069(tu)001:15188: smin pa la bya mi dgos /
NK069(tu)001:15189: 'bras bu la lam du bya rgyu phan cad 'bras bu men /
NK069(tu)001:15190: yin yang lam du byed zer na /
NK069(tu)001:15191: thug pa myed par 'gro zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15193: 'bras bu shes nas 'bras bu lam du byed de /
NK069(tu)001:15194: da rung 'bras bur shes yang 'bras bu'i rtsal ma rdzogs te /
NK069(tu)001:15195: dper na lu gu lug yin yang lug ni rtsal
NK069(tu)001:15196: rdzogs te lug gi bya ba byed mi nus pa
NK069(tu)001:15197: dang 'dra'o // 'bras bu lam du bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15198: 'di ni gsang chen nges pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:15199: zhes rgyud dam man ngag gi le'u 'di ni /
NK069(tu)001:15200: rang bzhin gyis rtogs par bka' bas /
NK069(tu)001:15201: rang bzhin gyis gsang ba yang yin la /
NK069(tu)001:15202: snod du ma gyur ba la mi brtan pa'i gsang ba yang yin pas gsang chen /
NK069(tu)001:15203: nges pa'i don mthar thug pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:15204: mthar phyin par gsungs pa yin pas nges pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15205: 'bras bu lam du gyur pa yin //
NK069(tu)001:15206: ces rgyu'i dus nyid nas 'bras bu tshang bar gnas pas na /
NK069(tu)001:15207: 'bras bu nyid lam du gyur pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:15208: de la grol lam gyi dbang du na /
NK069(tu)001:15209: rtog tshogs nyid 'bras bu sku dang ye shes su gyur pa de lam du byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15214: rlung ngo bo nyid kyi skur shes nas lam du
NK069(tu)001:15215: byed pas na 'bras bu nyid lam du gyur pa
NK069(tu)001:15216: yin no // man ngag 'di las ma rtogs gzhan myed par bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15217: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus la //
NK069(tu)001:15218: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhi'i rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa thams cad la /
NK069(tu)001:15219: 'di las gsang ba'i nges don myed //
NK069(tu)001:15220: gsang ba'i man ngag gi don 'di las ma rtogs pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:15221: chos gsang ba'i nges don gzhan myed de /
NK069(tu)001:15222: brtsal kyang rgyal bas mi snyems so //
NK069(tu)001:15225: rgyal ba sangs rgyas kyis yang mi rnyed na /
NK069(tu)001:15226: gzhan gyis lta ci smos so //
NK069(tu)001:15227: kun gyi phyag rgya chen po mchog /
NK069(tu)001:15228: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba kun gyi sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya dang dbyer myed pas chen po /
NK069(tu)001:15229: yon tan mchog dang ldan pa 'adi'o //
NK069(tu)001:15230: snod ldan gyis rnyed par bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15231: thos bsam bsgoms la rab sbyangs pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:15232: zhes man ngag 'di su yi spyod yul yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15233: thos pa'i shes rab sgra la sbyangs pa /
NK069(tu)001:15234: bsam pa'i shes rab sgra don spel mar sbyangs ba /
NK069(tu)001:15235: bsgom pa'i shes rab don b+ha zhig la sbyangs pa /
NK069(tu)001:15236: shes rab rnam pa gsum gyis rang rgyud legs par
NK069(tu)001:15237: smin pa de ni sbyangs pas snod du gyur ba'o
NK069(tu)001:15238: // shes rab myig ldan rnams kyis zung //
NK069(tu)001:15239: zhes yang dag pa'i lta ba rtogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15241: lta ba dang ldan pa rnams kyis /
NK069(tu)001:15242: go zhing rtogs pas na de la bstan /
NK069(tu)001:15243: des 'di'i don bsgom zhing bsgrub par gzung bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:15244: snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la bstan //
NK069(tu)001:15245: ces rang bzhin gyi snod dang ldan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15246: blo rno zhing shes rab che ba /
NK069(tu)001:15247: gsang thub cing dad pas len pa /
NK069(tu)001:15248: ngang bzang zhing blo thub pa /
NK069(tu)001:15250: tshul shes pa bag ma dang 'dra /
NK069(tu)001:15252: lus dang longs spyod gtong la sbyin //
NK069(tu)001:15253: zhes rang gi lus yang chos phyogs su gtong ba /
NK069(tu)001:15254: longs spyod dkon mchog la mchod par gtong nus pa /
NK069(tu)001:15255: sems can la sbyin pa gtong nus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15257: bzang bar blang bar bya ba'i rten gyi gang zag dang /
NK069(tu)001:15258: ngan pa dor bar bya ba'i rten gyi gang zag go //
NK069(tu)001:15260: skal sman rgyud pa'i gdul bya sbyangs pas snod du rung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:15261: nges pa don gyi gdul bya rang bzhin gyi snod du rung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:15262: de la sbyangs pas snod du rung ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:15263: tshe snga ma'am 'di la ci rigs par sbyangs pas gsang ba'i snod du gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15264: rang bzhin gyis snod du gyur pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15265: tshe snga ma'am 'di la ye ma sbyangs par nas pha'i snod du gyur ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:15266: de la sbyangs pa'i snod du gyur pa la yang gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:15269: de gnyis kyi khyad par ni /
NK069(tu)001:15271: lha mi'i thig pa nas 'jug pa ni rim gyis pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15272: nyan thos nas 'jug pa ni cig char ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:15273: sbyangs lugs nas khyad bzhag na /
NK069(tu)001:15274: tshe snga ma dang 'di gnyis char la sbyangs nas
NK069(tu)001:15275: sngags nang par sems skyed pa ni rim gyis pa'o
NK069(tu)001:15276: // tshe snga ma la sbyangs nas tshe 'di la sngags nang par 'jug pa ni cig char ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:15277: rang bzhin gyis snod du gyur pa la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:15282: chos can chos nyid kyis grub pa dang chos nyid rang bzhin gyis grub pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15283: nus pa byin rlabs kyis grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:15285: tshe snga ma la ma sbyangs par /
NK069(tu)001:15286: tshe 'di la rgyu rkyen dang ldan pas ma nges pa nas 'jug pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:15289: gnyis ka rgyud nas yo gar 'jug /
NK069(tu)001:15292: tshe snga ma la ma sbyangs par tshe 'di la
NK069(tu)001:15293: sngags gang rung gcig nas ma h+aa yo gar 'jug
NK069(tu)001:15294: pa'o // 'o na spyir gzhi' la dbang po rno rtul yod dam myed zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15295: rno rtul yod par 'dod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15296: dper na lcags la rno rtul yod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15299: de ltar bzhi la rno rtul yod na 'bad pa myed par grol bar 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:15300: gzhi' la rtul po yod na 'bad pa byas kyang mi 'grol lo //
NK069(tu)001:15301: rno rtul yod myed 'dra bar 'dod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15303: rigs med pa mi srid la /
NK069(tu)001:15304: theg chen pa'i lugs kyis rkyen gyis rigs chad pa mi srid de /
NK069(tu)001:15305: dper na 'tshams myed pa lnga la sogs pa byas
NK069(tu)001:15306: pa'i rkyen gyis 'khor ba ngan par ltung ba lta
NK069(tu)001:15307: bu'o // rkyen gtso' bor 'dod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15308: las dang nyon mongs pa'i rkyen gyis brtul bor 'byung la /
NK069(tu)001:15309: shes rab rnam pa gsum gyis rkyen gyis rnon po 'byung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:15310: de ltar na rno rtul rkyen b+ha zhig byas na /
NK069(tu)001:15311: rgyu bas rkyen gtso' bar 'dug pas mi 'thad do //
NK069(tu)001:15312: 'o na rang gi 'dod pa gang yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15314: gzhi' la rno ru rung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:15315: brtul du rung ba'i chos khas len no //
NK069(tu)001:15316: de gzhi' yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:15317: rno rtul dngos 'byung ba rkyen la rag lus te /
NK069(tu)001:15318: shes rab rnam pa gsum gyi rkyen dang phrad na dbang po rnon par 'byung la /
NK069(tu)001:15319: las dang nyon mongs pa'i rkyen dang phrad na btul bor 'byung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:15320: gzhi' la rno rtul 'byung sgo ma 'gags la /
NK069(tu)001:15321: rno rtul dngos su myed yang rkyen gyis snang bar 'dod pa yang yod do //
NK069(tu)001:15322: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi tshig go //
NK069(tu)001:15323: gzhan du nams kyang sbyin mi bya //
NK069(tu)001:15324: zhes snod ngan pa spang bar bya ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:15331: ngos dga' byed pa de la /
NK069(tu)001:15332: nams kyang sbyin par mi bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:15333: la gcod pa'i tshig yin no //
NK069(tu)001:15334: rmongs la 'phyar bas gal te byin //
NK069(tu)001:15335: ces rmongs pa ste slob dpon blun pa /
NK069(tu)001:15336: 'phyar ba ste slob dpon srab mo bcam bu nor dang can gyis /
NK069(tu)001:15337: nor phran tshegs la ltas nas /
NK069(tu)001:15338: gal te'am rgya lam na snod ngan la byin na /
NK069(tu)001:15339: dus min par ni srog zad nas //
NK069(tu)001:15342: slob dpon nyid 'chi ba'i dus ma yin blo bur du srog zad nas 'chi ste /
NK069(tu)001:15343: bka' srungs kyi mkha' 'gro ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:15344: dam nyams pa'i nad kas so //
NK069(tu)001:15345: bsregs dang sbrems la yun ring gnas //
NK069(tu)001:15347: sregs pa tsha ba'i dmyal bar skal pa gsum du gnas /
NK069(tu)001:15348: de nas kyang sbrems pa ste yi dwags kyi yul du skal pa gnyis gnas /
NK069(tu)001:15349: de nas thon nas kyang skal par sangs rgyas kyi sgra yang mi thos par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:15350: yang na sbrems pa ni grang ba'i dmyal bar skye ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:15351: zhes de bzhin gshegs pa ston pa kun tu bzang po nyid //
NK069(tu)001:15352: 'khor rigs lnga'i de bzhin gshegs pa sangs rgyas nyid
NK069(tu)001:15353: sangs rgyas nyid la nyid la ched du brjod do
NK069(tu)001:15354: // rtogs par dka' bas gsang ba bcud 'dus pas
NK069(tu)001:15355: snying po ma nor bas de kho na nyid mi
NK069(tu)001:15357: snod ngan gyis rtogs par dka' zhing ma rtogs nyes
NK069(tu)001:15358: pa che bas shin tu gsang ba'i rtogs na tshegs
NK069(tu)001:15359: chung dus grub pa'i man ngag gi rtsa rlung thig
NK069(tu)001:15360: le sngags kyis rang lus sangs rgyas par byed pas
NK069(tu)001:15361: na / snying po'i le'u ste bcu gsum pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15362: man ngag gi snying po ni /
NK069(tu)001:15363: snying ka chos kyi dal du kun tu bzang po
NK069(tu)001:15364: bsgom pa la mthar phyin na sgrol ba gnas spor
NK069(tu)001:15365: nus pas na sgrol ba'i man ngag snying po'o //
NK069(tu)001:15366: de nas lte bar phab ste gsang ba'i dal kun
NK069(tu)001:15367: tu bzang mo bsgom pa mthar phyin na sbyor ba
NK069(tu)001:15368: rtsom nus pas na sbyor ba'i man ngag gi snying
NK069(tu)001:15369: po'o // de gnyis dbyer myed pas mgrin pa longs
NK069(tu)001:15370: spyod kyi dal du thig le ro myong na rig
NK069(tu)001:15371: po'o // 'dzin 'grub / des spyi bo'i bde' ba
NK069(tu)001:15372: lus la khyab par 'bebs nus na sangs rgyas 'grub
NK069(tu)001:15373: po'o // 'dzin 'grub / pa'o // de yang rtsa gnas kyi man ngag snying po /
NK069(tu)001:15374: khams bdud rtsi'i thig le sku'i snying po /
NK069(tu)001:15376: rlung thugs kyi man ngag gi snying po'o //
NK069(tu)001:15377: bstod pa la ngag don du gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:15378: rigs lnga la bstod par 'dod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15379: sku lnga lhun grub la bstod par 'dod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15380: rigs lnga la bstod par 'dod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15381: sku la bstod pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:15382: gsung ni snang ba mtha' yas la bstod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15383: thugs ni mi bskyod pa'i rigs la bstod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15384: yon tan ni rin chen 'byung ldan gyi rigs la bstod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15385: 'phrin las ni las kyi rigs don yod grub pa la bstod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15386: spyir bstod pa ni rigs lnga thams cad la bstod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15387: sku lnga lhun grub la bstod na /
NK069(tu)001:15388: sku lnga la bstod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15389: gsung lnga la bstod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15390: thugs lnga la bstod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15391: yon tan lnga la bstod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15392: 'phrin las lnga la bstod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15393: spyir sku lnga lhun grub dbyer myed par bstod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15394: de las rigs lnga la bstod pa na 'thad pa yin te /
NK069(tu)001:15396: gdul bya lam pa'i snang ba yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15397: rnal 'byor pas rigs lnga bsgoms pa la bstod par 'thad do //
NK069(tu)001:15398: sku lnga ni che ba tsam du sbyar ba las /
NK069(tu)001:15399: dngos su bstod par na mi 'thad de /
NK069(tu)001:15400: da lta sku lnga lhun grub bsgom pa ma yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:15401: spyir sku lnga lhun grub 'di yang dmyigs pa'i yul
NK069(tu)001:15402: du mos pa byas pa la ni 'gal ba myed
NK069(tu)001:15403: de / yi dam lha bsgom du yod pa la
NK069(tu)001:15404: bstod pa ni rigs lnga la bstod par 'thad do
NK069(tu)001:15405: de / // don la rigs lnga yang sku lnga yin pas tha dad myed do //
NK069(tu)001:15406: le'u bcu gsum pa rdzogs rim gyi man ngag bstan nas /
NK069(tu)001:15408: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:15409: ston pa kun tu bzang por dbyer myed pa'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK069(tu)001:15410: yang na bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi dal lo //
NK069(tu)001:15411: ston pa nyid thugs ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du snang bar byed pa la /
NK069(tu)001:15413: dgyes pa chen po'i bstod pa ngag tu dbyangs su len pas na rdo rje'i glu blangs so //
NK069(tu)001:15415: zhes de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la sku'i sgo nas bstod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15418: glu len pa'i mkhan po yang yin /
NK069(tu)001:15422: dper na 'jig rten pa glu dag len pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:15430: sku gsung thugs gsum dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15432: 'jig rten dag na yang kye dang es 'go' drangs na klu gnyan la /
NK069(tu)001:15433: de dang mi ldan na ma snyan pa dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:15436: ye shes kyi phyag rgya zhes bya la /
NK069(tu)001:15437: glu gyis rgyan pa la ni /
NK069(tu)001:15438: glu ye shes kyi phyag rgya zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:15440: ye shes kyis glu rgyan pas /
NK069(tu)001:15441: glu 'chal ba'am rkyang par ma song bas /
NK069(tu)001:15444: tshig gi 'go 'tha' dag gyis drangs pas /
NK069(tu)001:15445: klu ye shes kyi tshig dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15446: phyogs bcu dus bzhir rdzogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:15447: zhes sku la spyir bstod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15448: phyogs bcu dus bzhis sdus pa'i chos thams cad ye
NK069(tu)001:15449: nas rdzogs pa chen po'i sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin
NK069(tu)001:15450: yang yin zhe'am / yang na phyogs bcu na bzhugs shing /
NK069(tu)001:15451: dus bzhir gshegs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad ni /
NK069(tu)001:15452: tshogs rnam pa gnyis rdzogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:15453: mtshan dang dpe' byad du ldan pa yin no zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:15454: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le che //
NK069(tu)001:15455: zhes sku'i thugs la bstod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15456: sku de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs stong pa nyid kyi ye shes de la ni /
NK069(tu)001:15457: sku gsung thugs gsum gyi dkyil 'khor dang ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:15459: thig le dang ye shes sbag mar byung ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:15460: chos kyi dbyings dang sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:15461: thig le spros pa myed pa chos kyi dbyings dang tha mi dad pas thig le che'o //
NK069(tu)001:15463: zhes sku'i sku la bstod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15464: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes de la ni bsod
NK069(tu)001:15465: nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis dang ldan la
NK069(tu)001:15466: / de'i rtags su mtshan dang dpe' byad du ldan pa /
NK069(tu)001:15467: sku de nyid sku gsung thugs gsum dang ldan pas na sku'i tshogs so //
NK069(tu)001:15468: yang na sku de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi tshogs zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:15469: snang stong thig le kun tu rdzogs ho //
NK069(tu)001:15470: zhes sku'i gsung la bstod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15471: stong pa ni don gyi gsung spros pa myed pa las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:15472: tshig gi gsung cir yang ston cing cir yang sgrogs bas snang /
NK069(tu)001:15473: gsung de nyid sku gsung thugs gsum dang ldan pa'i thig le /
NK069(tu)001:15474: sku gsung thugs de rnams dus kun yang sku gsung thugs gsum dang ldan par rdzogs so //
NK069(tu)001:15475: ho ni de la dgyes pa skyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15476: sku lnga la bstod pa'i dbang du na /
NK069(tu)001:15478: dus bzhir ni gshegs pa'i sangs rgyas thams cad ni /
NK069(tu)001:15479: sku lnga lhun grub du rdzogs la /
NK069(tu)001:15480: rdzogs pa ci'i phyir zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15481: ye shes rig pa rang snang gi dkyil 'khor du
NK069(tu)001:15482: dbyer myed pa'i thig le chen po gcig tu gyur
NK069(tu)001:15483: pa'o // dbyer myed pa'i 'thad pa gang zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15484: rgyu bsod nams kyi dang 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:15489: mngon par byang chub pa'i sku lnga'i dkyil 'khor tshogs su snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:15490: sku lnga po de nyid gdul bya la snang /
NK069(tu)001:15493: snang stong dbyer myed pas thig le /
NK069(tu)001:15494: dus kun tu ni sku lnga lhun grub tu rdzogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15495: de ltar de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la sku'i sgo
NK069(tu)001:15496: nas bstod pa ni gdul bya la dal du snang
NK069(tu)001:15497: ba'o // sku lnga la bstod pa ni rtogs ldan la 'bras bu snang ba'i sgo nas so //
NK069(tu)001:15499: yang na phyogs bcu dus bzhis ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:15500: thams cad gcig sku lnga lhun grub du rdzogs mngon par byang chub pa'i sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:15502: ye shes lnga yang rnam par mi rtogs pa'i ye shes su gsal /
NK069(tu)001:15503: de nyid khyab rdal chen por gnas pas chos sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:15505: gang yang ma yang par zag myed kyi bsod nams rang snang ba ni longs spyod rdzogs sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:15507: thams cad kyi ngo bo la thams cad du cir snang bas sprul sku'o /
NK069(tu)001:15509: snang stong gnyis su myed pa'i phyir rdo rje sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:15510: rdo rje bsod nams thig le che //
NK069(tu)001:15511: zhes rdo rje'i rigs la thugs kyi sgo nas bstod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15512: dang po thugs kyi sku la bstod pa la /
NK069(tu)001:15513: me long lta bu'i ye shes de nyid bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis dang ldan la /
NK069(tu)001:15514: de dbyer myed pas thig le che'o //
NK069(tu)001:15515: de yang thugs rdo rje'i rigs yin pas rdo rje zhes brjod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15516: rdo rje ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK069(tu)001:15517: zhes de'i rtags su sku mtshan dang dpe' byad du ldan pa'i sku de la yang /
NK069(tu)001:15518: sku gsung thugs gsum dang ldan pa'i ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan no //
NK069(tu)001:15519: rdo rje sgra chen mtha' yas pa //
NK069(tu)001:15520: thugs kyi gsung la bstod pa /
NK069(tu)001:15521: don gyi gsung spros pa myed pa las ma g.yos bzhin tu /
NK069(tu)001:15522: tshig gi gsung mtha' yas par ston pas mtha' yas so //
NK069(tu)001:15523: rdo rje rgyal po thig le che ho //
NK069(tu)001:15524: zhes thugs kyi thugs la bstod pa /
NK069(tu)001:15525: de ltar sku gsung thugs gsum ka yang /
NK069(tu)001:15526: sku gsung thugs rdo rje ltar dbyer myed par gsum dang ldan zhing /
NK069(tu)001:15527: mtha' rnam pa gnyis las rgyal ba'i rgyal po /
NK069(tu)001:15528: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du dbyer myed pas na thig le che zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:15529: thugs lnga la bstod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15531: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:15532: thig le che ni mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:15533: rdo rje ye shes ni me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:15534: rdo rje sgra chen ni so sor rtog pa'i ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:15535: rdo rje rgyal po ni bya ba grub pa'i ye shes so //
NK069(tu)001:15536: slob dpon sgeg pa rdo rje'i bzhed pa 'grel pa rin po che spar khab las /
NK069(tu)001:15537: rdo rje bsod nams thig le che la sogs pa
NK069(tu)001:15538: gsung lnga la bstod par bshad sku gsung thugs kyi
NK069(tu)001:15539: rdzogs pa che la sogs pa thugs la bstod par
NK069(tu)001:15540: bshad / myi dmyigs sgyu 'phrul la sogs pa yon tan la bstod par bshad pas /
NK069(tu)001:15542: de ni sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lnga'i go rims dang sbyar ba yin la /
NK069(tu)001:15543: 'dir ni dkyil 'khor lha dang sbyar bas /
NK069(tu)001:15545: de nas rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK069(tu)001:15547: de nas snang ba mtha' yas /
NK069(tu)001:15548: de nas don yod grub pa la bstod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15550: thugs rdo rje'i rigs yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15551: yon tan las thams cad rdzogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15552: gsung dbang gi rigs yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15553: de'i phyir dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs la rim pa ma nor bar bstod pas mngon no //
NK069(tu)001:15554: zhes gsungs pa de ni bla ma rnams kyi man ngag zhal gdams yin no //
NK069(tu)001:15555: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK069(tu)001:15556: zhes rin po che'i rigs la yon tan gyi sgo nas bstod de /
NK069(tu)001:15557: yon tan mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes de la yang /
NK069(tu)001:15558: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor rdzogs par mnga' bas rdzogs pa che'o //
NK069(tu)001:15562: dang po ni yon tan gyi sku rdzogs pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:15563: bar pa ni yon tan 'phrin las rdzogs pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:15564: tha ma ni blos 'phral la byas pa ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:15566: yon tan 'phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:15567: zhes sku gsung thugs rdzogs par ma zad de /
NK069(tu)001:15569: 'phrin las rnam bzhi kun yang rdzogs so //
NK069(tu)001:15570: de yang yon tan rgyas pa'i rang bzhin yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:15571: kun tu yon tan che ba rdzogs so //
NK069(tu)001:15572: 'dir yon tan lnga dang sbyar na sku gzhal yas khang du snang /
NK069(tu)001:15576: 'di bsgeg pa rdo rje'i bzhed pas thugs la bstod par byas te /
NK069(tu)001:15577: yon tan la thams cad rdzogs pas yon tan du 'thad do //
NK069(tu)001:15578: spyir sku lnga lhun grub la dbyer myed pas gang ltar byas yang 'gal ba myed la /
NK069(tu)001:15579: lam pa la dmigs so sor bzung na bade'o //
NK069(tu)001:15580: ye nas lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang //
NK069(tu)001:15581: zhes de ltar sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lnga rdzogs pa de yang /
NK069(tu)001:15582: ye nas che ba'i yon tan lhun grub du rdzogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:15583: kun tu bzang por sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin can no //
NK069(tu)001:15584: 'dus pa'i tshogs chen thig le che ho //
NK069(tu)001:15585: zhes de yang kun tu bzang por sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du gcig cing 'dus pas na /
NK069(tu)001:15586: de la che ba'i yon tan kun rdzogs /
NK069(tu)001:15587: de yang dbyer myed par gcig pas thig le chen
NK069(tu)001:15588: por sangs rgyas pa la dgyes pas ho zhes gsungs
NK069(tu)001:15589: pa yin no // 'dir thams cad thig ler bstod pas mtshon tshul 'dres so zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15593: bsal ba mi sgrib pas thugs /
NK069(tu)001:15596: myi dmyigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK069(tu)001:15597: zhes pad mi'i rigs la gsung gi sgo nas bstod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15599: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes kyis chos kyi dbyings rtogs nas /
NK069(tu)001:15600: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis myed mthar phyin pa la /
NK069(tu)001:15601: dngos po dang mtshan ma'i ngo bor ma dmigs pa la /
NK069(tu)001:15606: dra ba dbyer myed par bstan pas /
NK069(tu)001:15607: thabs shes rab la mnga' snyems pas longs sku dang sbyar /
NK069(tu)001:15609: sprul skus sems can 'ga' tsam gyi don spyod ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:15610: sems can kun la mnyam zhing snyoms su don mdzad pas sprul sku dang sbyar /
NK069(tu)001:15611: dbyings ni de ltar rtogs na sku gsum 'byung ba'i dbyings /
NK069(tu)001:15612: thams cad dbang du sdud pa'i dbyings so //
NK069(tu)001:15613: mtha' yas kun tu sna tshogs 'phro //
NK069(tu)001:15617: de nas dbang du bsdud de /
NK069(tu)001:15619: phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams kun nas /
NK069(tu)001:15620: sprul pa'i sku sna tshogs pa 'phro ba /
NK069(tu)001:15621: don yang so sor mdzad pas sna tshogs pa 'aphro'o //
NK069(tu)001:15622: mtha' yas kun nas lhun gyis thim //
NK069(tu)001:15623: zhes sprul pa bsdu ba yang gnas gcig tu nges pa myed de /
NK069(tu)001:15624: phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa kun nas 'phro zhing snang ba'i sprul pa'i chos kun snang tsam na /
NK069(tu)001:15625: rang gi ngo bos stong zhing mtshan ma myed pa'i ngang du lhun gyis thim pas /
NK069(tu)001:15626: bsdu ba yang so so nyid du 'dus pas lhun gyis thim mo //
NK069(tu)001:15627: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen po ho //
NK069(tu)001:15628: zhes sprul pa'i sku sna tshogs par snang ba thams cad kyang /
NK069(tu)001:15629: 'gro ba dbang du sdud pa'i las byed la /
NK069(tu)001:15630: las de yang sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor dang dbyer med par ldan te /
NK069(tu)001:15631: de kho na gsung gi mdzad pa yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:15633: de la dgyes pas na ho zhes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15636: chos sku skyed myed don gyi gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:15640: sprul sku tshig gi gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:15642: mngon byang rig pa'i sgyu ma'i gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:15643: sna tshogs sku gsung ni rdo rje grag stong dbyer myed kyi gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:15644: 'di 'grel pa spar khab kyi yon tan du bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:15645: gsung snang ba mtha' yas la bstod par bade'o //
NK069(tu)001:15646: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK069(tu)001:15647: zhes las kyi rigs la 'phrin las kyi sgo nas bstod de /
NK069(tu)001:15648: phyogs bcu snod bcud kyi 'jig rten yang /
NK069(tu)001:15649: phan tshun du ni za 'og dar khyim kram pa 'dra la /
NK069(tu)001:15650: yan man ni rgya shog 'dab ma rtsegs pa 'dra ba de /
NK069(tu)001:15652: de na gnas pa'i bcud kyi sems can yang grangs rdul snyed gcig yod la /
NK069(tu)001:15653: rgyal ba'i don rnams rdul phran rnyen //
NK069(tu)001:15654: zhes gdul bya de dag la /
NK069(tu)001:15655: 'dul byed rgyal ba sangs rgyas kyis /
NK069(tu)001:15656: 'phrin las kyis don mdzad pa'i rnam pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:15657: rdul phra rab snyed kyis kyang /
NK069(tu)001:15659: bdag gcig bu byang gi tsha blan gyi bar du /
NK069(tu)001:15660: lho'i btson shor bya ba lta bu ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:15661: sprul pa rdul phran bsam yas kyis //
NK069(tu)001:15662: zhes don mdzad pa yang sprul pa rdul phra rab dang grangs mnyam pa /
NK069(tu)001:15663: blos bsam yas pa rnams kyis /
NK069(tu)001:15665: skad cig yud la lhun gyis grub ho //
NK069(tu)001:15666: zhes sems can ltar rim gyis sam khad kyis don mdzad pa ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:15667: skad cig tsam de se gol tog pa'i yun tsam mam /
NK069(tu)001:15668: yud tsam mam thang gcig tsam la /
