NK069(tu)001:15669: zhi rgyas dbang drag gi ngang du don rnams mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15670: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:15671: skad cig yud la lhun gyis grub ces pa /
NK069(tu)001:15672: sangs rgyas kyis sems can gyi don mdzad pa de /
NK069(tu)001:15673: skad cig gam yud tsam las don mi mdzad na /
NK069(tu)001:15674: bcom ldan 'das kyis 'jig rten du lo mang po bzhugs pa dang 'gal zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15676: rgyal bas skad cig tsam la don byas kyang /
NK069(tu)001:15677: sems can gyis yun du gnas par mthong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:15678: yang na 'phrin las gyur pa'i chag tshad kyang yin no //
NK069(tu)001:15681: gdul bya yin pas dbang du sdud pas dbang gi las so //
NK069(tu)001:15683: gdul byed yin pas bstan pa rgyas pa dang sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:15685: don mdzad pas nyon mongs pa 'jil bas zhi ba dang sbyar /
NK069(tu)001:15687: myur bas drag po dang sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:15689: rtsal ba myed par lhun gyis grub pas thod rgal gyi 'phrin las so //
NK069(tu)001:15690: thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK069(tu)001:15691: zhes spyir sku gsung thugs la bstod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15692: chos ma lus pa thams cad sna tshogs par snang ba ni sku /
NK069(tu)001:15693: rang bzhin myed par don 'jal ba ni gsung /
NK069(tu)001:15694: gnyis su myed par rig pa ni thugs so //
NK069(tu)001:15695: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK069(tu)001:15696: zhes de ltar chos thams cad sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin nam /
NK069(tu)001:15697: bdag nyid du ma gyur ba myed cig /
NK069(tu)001:15698: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du dbyer myed pas na chen po /
NK069(tu)001:15699: sku gsung thugs kyis kun tu khyab //
NK069(tu)001:15700: ces chos thams cad sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du dbyer myed par gnas pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:15701: chos thams cad logs zhig nas sku gsung thugs kyi
NK069(tu)001:15702: dkyil 'khor du byas pa lta bu ma yin te
NK069(tu)001:15703: / chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin gang yin pa sku gsung thugs yin la /
NK069(tu)001:15704: sku gsung thugs nyid dang tha mi dad par ye nas gnas pas /
NK069(tu)001:15705: dpe' dung dang dkar po 'dra bar khyab bo //
NK069(tu)001:15706: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che ho //
NK069(tu)001:15707: zhes de ltar chos thams cad sku gsung thugs kyi
NK069(tu)001:15708: dkyil 'khor du ma gyur ba myed pas thig le
NK069(tu)001:15709: / sku gsung thugs kyang dbyer myed pas chen po /
NK069(tu)001:15710: de lta bu'i don la mnyes pas ho zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:15711: des ni gong gi rigs lnga re re la yang
NK069(tu)001:15712: sku gsung thugs gsum dang ldan pa la bstod pa'o
NK069(tu)001:15713: // gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:15714: thams cad sku gsung thugs su byas pas /
NK069(tu)001:15716: de la dang po ni 'khor 'das kyis sdus pa'i
NK069(tu)001:15717: chos thams cad sku gsung thugs su ngo bo yin
NK069(tu)001:15718: par bstod / bar pa ni sku gsung thugs kyis khyab pa'i rang bzhin du bstod /
NK069(tu)001:15719: tha ma ni sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan nyid du thig le chos skur bstod pas /
NK069(tu)001:15720: mtshon tshul 'dres pa'i 'gal ba myed do //
NK069(tu)001:15722: zhes sku gsung thugs la bstod pas /
NK069(tu)001:15723: bstod pa byed pa'i rnal 'byor pa la /
NK069(tu)001:15727: bstod pa de sgrags thos par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:15728: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las //
NK069(tu)001:15731: de kho na nyid ma nor ba /
NK069(tu)001:15732: nges pa mi slu ba'i rgyud las /
NK069(tu)001:15733: mnyes pa'i le'u ste bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15735: // bstod pa byas pas rgyal ba'i thugs mnyes /
NK069(tu)001:15736: sems can gyi yid tshim pa ste bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15738: dang po shes rab chen po'i khro bo ni /
NK069(tu)001:15740: yang dag shes rab chen po ni /
NK069(tu)001:15741: mtshan ma 'joms phyir khro bo'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:15743: gnyis pa ye shes chen po'i khro bo ni /
NK069(tu)001:15745: rang rig ye shes rgyal po yis //
NK069(tu)001:15746: phyogs bcu'i khams rnams dbang sdus nas //
NK069(tu)001:15747: kun kyang mi dmigs dbyings su thim //
NK069(tu)001:15748: thams cad khro bo'i tshogs su 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:15750: gsum pa phyag rgya chen po khro bo ni 'di nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:15751: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag po //
NK069(tu)001:15752: zhes de gong ma'i mjug sdud pas te /
NK069(tu)001:15754: phal che ba'i dbang du dgongs nas /
NK069(tu)001:15755: de yan chad du zhi ba bstan pas so //
NK069(tu)001:15758: phal che ba'i dbang du dgongs nas /
NK069(tu)001:15759: 'di man chad du khro bo ston pas so //
NK069(tu)001:15760: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rang bzhin yang kun tu bzang po de yin la /
NK069(tu)001:15761: sangs rgyas thams cad ma lus kun la mnga' snyems
NK069(tu)001:15762: pa'i bdag po yang ston pa kun tu bzang po
NK069(tu)001:15763: yin pas na / rgyal ba rigs lnga la sogs thams cad kyi mnga' bdag go //
NK069(tu)001:15764: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid kyis //
NK069(tu)001:15765: zhes dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ngo
NK069(tu)001:15766: bo nyid dam rang bzhin du gyur pa'i ston pa
NK069(tu)001:15767: kun tu bzang po thams cad mkhyen pa des /
NK069(tu)001:15768: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du mngon par 'du mdzad de //
NK069(tu)001:15769: zhes zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis las /
NK069(tu)001:15770: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du mngon sum du 'dus pa'i mdzad pa bstan te /
NK069(tu)001:15771: don chos nyid dang bcas nas 'khros /
NK069(tu)001:15773: rigs lnga khrag 'thung gi dal du mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15774: khro bo rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la ngag don du gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:15778: ci'i phyir khro bos 'dul bar mdzad pa ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:15782: rgyu ni ma rigs cing rmongs pas log par rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15783: rkyen ni srid pa'i sa bon rtsub mo bsags pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15786: yi dwangs su skye ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:15787: las kyi srin por skye ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:15788: ji ltar btul ba ni drug ste /
NK069(tu)001:15795: dang po che mchog khro bo'i dal ni /
NK069(tu)001:15796: sku khro bor sgyur nas yum phyung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:15798: yab yum gyi mkha' las khro bo 'chol pa spros nas /
NK069(tu)001:15799: phyogs bcu'i dregs pa rnams 'dul ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:15800: zhe sdang rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK069(tu)001:15801: phyogs bcu'i khro bo chol pa rnams tshur rigs bzhi
NK069(tu)001:15802: he ru kar 'dus nas 'dregs pa rnams zhabs kyis
NK069(tu)001:15803: mnan pa'o // rdo rje srin po'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK069(tu)001:15804: dregs pa'i nga rgyal 'dul ba'i phyir dbu dgu' phyag bco' brgyad par sgyur nas /
NK069(tu)001:15805: dregs pa pho rnams sgral nas zhal du gsal /
NK069(tu)001:15806: mo rnams sngags kyis dbang du sdus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15807: rdo rje khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du /
NK069(tu)001:15808: yang rigs lnga'i he ru kar snang bar byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:15809: dbang mo rnams la so sor sbyor ba byas /
NK069(tu)001:15811: dbang mo rang gi gnas su krad nas /
NK069(tu)001:15812: dregs pa rnams lto ba nas zhabs su mi rtsang ba'i tshul du phyung nas slar gsos /
NK069(tu)001:15816: phyag steng brgyad brgyar sprul nas /
NK069(tu)001:15817: 'jig rten khams kyi gdul byar gyur chad rnams dus gcig la stul lo //
NK069(tu)001:15818: las skos la btab pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15822: rang rang gi lus dpal gyi gdan su phul /
NK069(tu)001:15823: 'khor rnams tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bsrung bar phul /
NK069(tu)001:15824: de rnams kyis dpal la dngos grub nos /
NK069(tu)001:15825: dbang rtags su lag tu rdo rje byin /
NK069(tu)001:15826: gsang ba'i ming rtags nas bstan pa bsrung bar dam bcas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15828: ste sku zhi ba las khro bor sgyur pa de dgos ched ci zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:15830: sngon gyi dus na gsang sngags kyi sgor zhugs pa las /
NK069(tu)001:15831: gsang sngags kyi spyod pa spyad nyes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15832: lhan cig skyes pa'i sgyu ni /
NK069(tu)001:15833: bdag tu rmongs pa'i rtog pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:15834: zhes chos nyid zhi ba bdag myed pa las /
NK069(tu)001:15835: nga dang bdag tu bzung ba de kho na /
NK069(tu)001:15836: rmongs shing gti mug pa yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:15837: rmongs pa'i rtag pa ngan pa rang dga' ma des so //
NK069(tu)001:15838: brtags pa la mngon par zhen pas //
NK069(tu)001:15839: zhes bzung ba'i yul la rtogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15840: 'dzin pa'i sems su rtags pa las /
NK069(tu)001:15841: de ltar bzung 'dzin gyi rtog pas mngon par chags shing zhen pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15843: yang dag pa'i lam dang bral ba dag /
NK069(tu)001:15844: ces yang dag pa ni bla na myed pa'i byang chub yin la /
NK069(tu)001:15845: de'i lam ni thos bsam bsgom pa'i shes rab rnam pa gsum yin pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:15846: shes rab rnam pa gsum dang bral ba dag zhe'o //
NK069(tu)001:15847: de la spyod pa spyad nyes pa ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:15848: sgrol ba ni snying rje chen pos zin par byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:15849: thabs dang shes rab gnyis myed du sgrol ba yin pa la /
NK069(tu)001:15850: de ltar ma rtogs te dngos por gzung nas zhe sdang rang dka' mas bsad /
NK069(tu)001:15851: sbyor ba yang yum ye shes kyi lha mor byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK069(tu)001:15852: bde' ba lhan cig skyes pa'i ye shes lam du len par ma shes pas /
NK069(tu)001:15853: dngos por bzung nas chags pa rang ka mas spyed do //
NK069(tu)001:15854: ma byin par len pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15855: ser sna can dang sgral ba zhing gi nor blangs
NK069(tu)001:15856: nas bla ma dang chos la stong pa yin la
NK069(tu)001:15857: / de ltar ma shes par slob dpon dang mched la skus /
NK069(tu)001:15858: khro bo bsgom pa yang gdul bya 'dul ba'i phyir bsgom pas don chos nyid yin pa la /
NK069(tu)001:15859: de ltar ma rtogs te zhe sdang gis khro bo rang rgyud du bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:15863: de 'dul ba'i phyir khro bor sgyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:15864: gab pa'i gsang ba ma rtogs par //
NK069(tu)001:15865: zhes gab pa ni dag pa rnam pa gsum dang
NK069(tu)001:15866: mnyam pa gnyis kyis don ston pa'i dgongs pa la
NK069(tu)001:15867: gab / yi ge kyus la gab pa de gsang bas ma rtogs par /
NK069(tu)001:15868: sbas pa'i gsang ba la mngon par 'chal nas //
NK069(tu)001:15869: zhes theg pa 'og ma la sbas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:15870: gsang ba sgrol sbyor la sogs pa la mngon par 'chal lam /
NK069(tu)001:15871: lam mngon par bzung nas so //
NK069(tu)001:15873: rgyu dang 'bras bu la smongs pas //
NK069(tu)001:15874: rgyu las ngan pa spyad pas /
NK069(tu)001:15875: 'bras bu gnas ngan pa len pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15878: de ltar rgyu 'thun pa'i 'bras bu mi slu bar
NK069(tu)001:15879: smin par ma shes pas kho na rmongs pa ste
NK069(tu)001:15880: ma rig pas dbang byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15881: rgyu mthun gyi rgyu nyes rab len pa'i rgyu ni /
NK069(tu)001:15882: srid pa'i sa bon rtsub mos 'phangs nas //
NK069(tu)001:15883: sngon gsang sngags spyod pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:15884: zhe sdang rang ka mas gsad pas /
NK069(tu)001:15885: tsha ba'i dmyal ba'i sa bon byas /
NK069(tu)001:15886: 'dod chags rang ka mas spyad pas /
NK069(tu)001:15887: grang ba'i dmyal ba'i sa bon byas /
NK069(tu)001:15889: yi dwags su skye ba'i sa bon byas /
NK069(tu)001:15890: khro bo rang rgyud du bsgoms pas /
NK069(tu)001:15891: las kyi srin por skye ba'i sa bon byas /
NK069(tu)001:15892: sngon gyi las kyi srid pas ngan song du 'phangs so //
NK069(tu)001:15893: dmyal bar skye ba'i sngon gsang sngags spyod pa'i dus su sgrol ba spyad nyes pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:15895: sgrol ba la yang snying rje chen pos bla na
NK069(tu)001:15896: myed pa'i byang chub kyi gnas su sgral bar dam
NK069(tu)001:15897: bcas pa dang / shes rab kyis mnyam pa nyid
NK069(tu)001:15898: kyi don tshig tsam ma yin par rtogs par byas
NK069(tu)001:15899: bcas pa dang / nas / shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin du ldan par bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:15900: ye shes kyi lha dang gnyis su myed par sgral rgyu yin pa las /
NK069(tu)001:15901: de ltar ma rtogs te dngos por bzung nas zhe
NK069(tu)001:15902: sdang gi dbang gis gsod pas tsha ba'i dmyal bar
NK069(tu)001:15904: dmyal bar skye ba'i tshul lam dus na /
NK069(tu)001:15905: 'tshams myed pa'i zhes las ngan pa'i bar dge' bas ma chod pas 'tshams myed pa /
NK069(tu)001:15906: sdug bsngal gyi ngo bo la bde' ba'i bar 'tshams myed na yang 'tshams myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15907: rab tu tsha ba'i dmyal bar skyes so //
NK069(tu)001:15908: zhes rab tu tsha ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:15910: khro chu khol ma'i nang na 'dug pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15911: las dang sdug bsngal gyis lus ngag nyams thag pas na dmyal ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:15913: de rab tu tsha ba'i sdug bsngal drag po'i bsdungs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15914: zhes dmyal ba der skyes pa'i tshe na yang /
NK069(tu)001:15915: lus ngag rab tu tsha ba'i sdug bsngal gyis /
NK069(tu)001:15916: sems la drag pos bstungs ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:15917: 'di bas shin tu grang na yang ci ma rung mnyam pa'i mod la /
NK069(tu)001:15918: zhes yid la dge ba ma dran par /
NK069(tu)001:15920: 'di bas bag na grang na mnyam pa mnyam pa dran pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15921: grang ba'i las ngan pa byang bas /
NK069(tu)001:15922: rab tu sbrebs pa dang pad ma ltar gas pa'i
NK069(tu)001:15923: sdug bsngal drag po dag gis zhes grang ba'i dmyal
NK069(tu)001:15925: lus rab tu grang ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:15926: dper na pad ma 'dab ma stong du gas pa ltar /
NK069(tu)001:15927: lus grang bas tshal par gas pa'i sdug bsngal lo //
NK069(tu)001:15928: grang ba'i dmyal bar skye ba'i rgyu yang /
NK069(tu)001:15930: yum ye shes kyi lha mor bskyed cing byin gyis brlabs la /
NK069(tu)001:15931: yum de yang don dam par ni /
NK069(tu)001:15932: chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin du rtogs par byas la /
NK069(tu)001:15933: kun rdzob du chu zla'am 'ja' tshon ltar snang la rang bzhin myed par rtogs par bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:15934: 'dod chags tsam na 'dod chags myed pa'i mthar phyin pa /
NK069(tu)001:15936: gnyis myed par rtogs par byas la sbyor ba bya rgyu yin pa la /
NK069(tu)001:15938: dngos por gzung nas 'dod chags rang ka mar spyad pas /
NK069(tu)001:15939: grang ba'i dmyal bar skyes so //
NK069(tu)001:15940: de lta bu'i sdug bsngal rab tu tsha ba la sogs pa brgyad dang /
NK069(tu)001:15941: zhes tsha ba'i nad kyis yang shi yang sos yang sos byed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15942: lus la lcags sregs kyi thig thig nag gtab nas sog les bshag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15943: lcags bsdus 'jom kyi rtun du lus rdul phra rab ltar gdung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:15944: lus la mtshon zug nang du zhing ngu 'bod 'bod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15945: shal ma ri shul mas ngus ngu 'bod chen po pas 'bod pa chen po byed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15946: lus mes tshig pa ltar tsha ba tsha ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:15947: khro chu khol ma'i nang du rab tu tsha ba rab tu tsha ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:15948: sdug bsngal gyis mnar nas mnar med do bde' ba myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:15949: shin tu grang ba la sogs pa brgyad po dag tu /
NK069(tu)001:15950: zhes dang po grang bas a chu zer ba de /
NK069(tu)001:15951: de bas kyang grang bas kyi hud zhes smre sngags 'don pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15952: de bas grang bas so tham tham 'dar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:15953: de bas grang bas lus la chu bur 'byung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:15954: de bas grangs bas chu bur rdol ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:15955: de bas grang bas lus pad+ma ltar tshal pa bzhir gas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15956: de bas grang bas lus pad+ma chen po ltar pad+ma
NK069(tu)001:15957: ltar cher gas pa tshal pa brgyad du gas pa
NK069(tu)001:15958: dang / de bas kyang grang bas lus ud dpal
NK069(tu)001:15959: ltar ud pa ltar cher gas pa tshal pa bcu
NK069(tu)001:15962: zhes 'jig rten gcig 'jig cing stong na /
NK069(tu)001:15963: 'jig rten chags zin pa de'i gnas skad cig gis slebs par 'phos te /
NK069(tu)001:15964: stong gsum gyi stong chen po 'jig rten gyi khams brgyud de /
NK069(tu)001:15965: las ngan pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa de ma zad kyi bar du thon mi srid do //
NK069(tu)001:15967: skal pa chen po stong phrag bcu gnyis su myong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:15968: zhes skal ba'i bsgrang lugs ni /
NK069(tu)001:15969: dang po tshe lo brgyad khri thub pa'i dus nas bsod nams mar la 'grib pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15970: tshe lo bcu pa la thug /
NK069(tu)001:15971: de nas yang yar la 'phel bas brgyad khri la thug pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15972: de ltar zung nyi shu ni chags /
NK069(tu)001:15975: nyi shur ni stong par gyur pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15978: skal pa chen po gcig ces bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:15979: de lta bu'i skal pa stong phrag bcu gnyis su
NK069(tu)001:15980: dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal tsha grang nyams su myong ngo
NK069(tu)001:15982: dpag tshad brgyad kyis 'khor ba'i lcags kyi sdong po gcig la /
NK069(tu)001:15983: phug ron gyi gshog pas byugs pas sked par tshad do //
NK069(tu)001:15984: yi dwags su skye ba'i dus ni /
NK069(tu)001:15985: de nas rnam par smin pa de zad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15986: zhes sgrol ba ma rtogs par srog bcod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:15987: sbyor ba ma rtogs par 'dod chags rang dgar spyad pas /
NK069(tu)001:15989: grang ba'i dmyal bar skyes pa sngon gyi las rnam par smin pa'i lan chags 'khor bas zad do //
NK069(tu)001:15990: yi dwags rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK069(tu)001:15992: zhes ma byin pa len pa spyad nyes pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK069(tu)001:15993: bkres pa yid la dwags nas /
NK069(tu)001:15995: yi dwags su skye ba'i rgyu dang /
NK069(tu)001:15996: ma byin pa blang ba yang /
NK069(tu)001:15997: ser sna can dang bsgral ba zhing bcu'i nor /
NK069(tu)001:15998: thabs mkhas pa'i ye shes kyi 'od zer gyis blangs nas /
NK069(tu)001:15999: dkon mchog gsum la mchod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16000: tshogs kyi yo byad du tang rgyu yin pa las /
NK069(tu)001:16003: mched lcam dral gyi nor la thugs thub du spyad
NK069(tu)001:16004: pas yi dwags bkres pa skom pa lus rid par
NK069(tu)001:16005: skyes pa'o // gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:16006: ru tra gnyen po ye shes rgyud la sten par rnam par smin pa zad na /
NK069(tu)001:16007: khams gsum 'khor ba yang rang bzhin gyis sangs rgya bar rigs /
NK069(tu)001:16008: ru tras gnyen po ye shes gcig rten nas sangs na /
NK069(tu)001:16009: ru tra phyis dpal gyis grol bar mi rigs zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:16010: rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu myong ba yin te /
NK069(tu)001:16011: sngon gyi las re re zad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16012: yang sngon gyi bag chags re re sad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16013: des na 'gal ba can myed do //
NK069(tu)001:16014: skom pa'i sdug bsngal gyis nyes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16015: zhes skom pa yid la btags te /
NK069(tu)001:16016: tha na sor mo'i rtse mo la klan tsam yang ltar myed pas /
NK069(tu)001:16017: skad kyang mi thon par gyur pa de /
NK069(tu)001:16018: bza' btung myed pa de ni yi dwags spyi thun gyi sgrib pa can zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:16019: 'dod pa'i dngos po rnams yid du mi 'ong ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16020: zhes phyi'i sgrib pa can ni /
NK069(tu)001:16021: mdun na rang gi 'dod pa'i dngos po rnams mthong yang /
NK069(tu)001:16024: rang gi yid du mi 'ong ba'i bza' btung mi 'dod par mthong nas /
NK069(tu)001:16025: bkres skom yang bza' btung byar ma stub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16026: stug cing rtsub pa'i dngos po sna tshogs su 'gyur ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16027: zhes nang gi sgrib pa can ni /
NK069(tu)001:16029: khong du nad sbyar dug ltar sdug cing /
NK069(tu)001:16031: nang du khro chu khol ma ltar song nas /
NK069(tu)001:16032: nad kyi dngos po sna tshogs kyis zug cing gzer nas na bar gyur pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16034: zhes phyi'i sgrib pa can gyi rigs gcig ni /
NK069(tu)001:16036: de zar phyin tsam na myed par song bas /
NK069(tu)001:16038: dper na myigs rgyu chur mthong ba dang 'dra'o //
NK069(tu)001:16039: shin tu rid cing skams pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16040: zhes de'i lus kyang shin tu rid cing /
NK069(tu)001:16041: rus mgo' spags kyis thum tsam pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16042: chu rgyus dang rtsa res 'dra ba /
NK069(tu)001:16043: spags pa skam nas thal kyar bun gyis song ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16044: lus dang yan lag dang dbang po mi 'tsham par 'gyur pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:16045: zhes yi dwags sgo khur gyi sgrib pa can ni /
NK069(tu)001:16046: lus ri rab tsam yod pa /
NK069(tu)001:16047: rkang lag 'jag ma tsam yod pas /
NK069(tu)001:16052: yang 'go rdza ma tsam la lus 'jag ma tsam du gyur nas /
NK069(tu)001:16053: lus kyis 'go' mi theg pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16055: kha'i dbang po khab dmyig tsam du zas mi tshud pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16057: skal pa chen po drug tu skyes so //
NK069(tu)001:16059: yar skye mar 'grib zung nyi shur ni chags /
NK069(tu)001:16060: de ltar zung nyi shur ni gnas shing 'khor /
NK069(tu)001:16063: de lta bu'i 'jig chags stong gnas /
NK069(tu)001:16066: de la skal pa chen po gcig go //
NK069(tu)001:16068: dmyal ba nas skal pa phyed kyis sdug bsngal yun thung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:16069: 'dir spyir ru tra la 'dod lugs gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:16070: gsang sngags sgra ji bzhin du spyad pas rgyu 'bras
NK069(tu)001:16071: mi bslu ba la dog pa ste rang rgyud pa'am
NK069(tu)001:16072: phyi'i ru tra dang sbyar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16073: bdag tu 'dzin pa la dgongs te /
NK069(tu)001:16074: sprul pa'am nang gi ru tra dang sbyar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:16075: gal te tshul de gnyis su mi bden de /
NK069(tu)001:16077: sprul pa lta bu gcig bden na /
NK069(tu)001:16078: sems can dmyal ba rang yang drang don nam sdigs mo yin te /
NK069(tu)001:16079: don la ma rtogs pa la yang myed par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:16080: rang rgyud pa gcig pu ltar bden na yang /
NK069(tu)001:16083: bdud lha sbyin ni gzhan yin mnyam du ma ston cig /
NK069(tu)001:16085: sangs rgyas kyi che bar dbyung ba'i phyir sprul pa de yang mi bden par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:16087: thong thong rje'i bdag po cis te ltar byed dam zhes 'dzer cing ces so //
NK069(tu)001:16088: de bas na gnyis ka ltar 'dod de /
NK069(tu)001:16089: ma rtogs na rang rgyud pa /
NK069(tu)001:16092: gsang ba'i lam nor ba las byung /
NK069(tu)001:16093: nang gi ru tra ni ma rig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16094: de yi dwags nas thon pa nas las kyi sbyor
NK069(tu)001:16095: ba dang ma byin par len pa'i rnam par smin
NK069(tu)001:16096: pa rtsub mo de rim gyis sam dal bus khad
NK069(tu)001:16097: kyis de'i bag chags ngan pa srabs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16098: las kyi srin por skye ba'i dus ni /
NK069(tu)001:16099: sngon gyi nyes pa'i srid pas bag chags ngan pa'i 'tshams sbyar nas /
NK069(tu)001:16100: zhes srin por skye ba'i rgyu ni /
NK069(tu)001:16102: bcas bcos gnyis dang ldan pa'i sku phyag rgya chen po /
NK069(tu)001:16103: snang la rang bzhin myed pa'i don byang chub sems dang ldan par bsgom rgyu yin pa la /
NK069(tu)001:16105: zhe sdang gis khro bo rang rgyud par bsgom pas /
NK069(tu)001:16108: yi dwags kyi srin po chen po rab tu gdug pa gtum po /
NK069(tu)001:16109: zhes cha byad yi dwags 'dra bar rid pa /
NK069(tu)001:16110: ngo bo las kyi srin po chen por gyur pa /
NK069(tu)001:16113: rigs 'byung po'i rigs su rtogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:16114: sde tshan na byol song khongs su sdeb bo //
NK069(tu)001:16116: lus gcig la 'go' brgya pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16117: zhes lus gcig la mgo' brgya yod pa /
NK069(tu)001:16120: lus gcig gi khong du ma shong bas /
NK069(tu)001:16123: zhes mgo' de dag yang stag dang seng ge la sogs pa bza' ba la dgyes pa'i dabu'o //
NK069(tu)001:16124: lus brgya' la mgo' gcig pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16125: zhes lus brgya yod pa la /
NK069(tu)001:16126: mgo gcig gis zos pas mi bgrangs shing rtogs pa'i sdug bsngal dang /
NK069(tu)001:16128: zhes lus de dag yang sbrul dang dred la sogs
NK069(tu)001:16129: pa lto che ba'i lus rnams su sha ra yod
NK069(tu)001:16130: pa dang / ru tra nyid bstan /
NK069(tu)001:16132: zhes byol song rkang bzhi ba glang lta bu'i yan lag dang /
NK069(tu)001:16133: rkang gnyis bya lta bu'i dang /
NK069(tu)001:16134: rkang mang rta bla lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:16135: rkang myed sbrul lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:16136: yan lag sna tshogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16139: la la sbar mo can dang /
NK069(tu)001:16140: la la sems can phal pa'i yan lag 'dra ba rmig sder myed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16141: gdug pa'i lag cha sna tshogs pa thogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:16159: thog skyogs la sogs pa gdug pa'i lag cha dang /
NK069(tu)001:16160: 'khor rab tu bstan 'khor rab tu bstum po mang po dang /
NK069(tu)001:16163: las mthun pa'i phyogs gcig tu skyes pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16164: dper na bcom ldan 'das la bdud kyi tshogs kyis 'jigs gzugs bstan pa lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:16165: 'jigs pa'i nga ro'i sgra sna tshogs sgrog pa /
NK069(tu)001:16166: zhes 'dre'i skad kyis sems dpa' zhum par byed /
NK069(tu)001:16169: las kyi sbyor bas gzhan la gnod tshul bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16170: gzugs dang nga ro dang dri dang kha rlangs kyis thams cad skyi bung zhes byed pa /
NK069(tu)001:16171: gzugs mi sdug pa'i ni drang srong 'dra /
NK069(tu)001:16172: nga ro mi snyan pa ni 'dre skad smra /
NK069(tu)001:16173: dri mi zhim pa ni bse shing gi sdong po 'dra /
NK069(tu)001:16174: kha rlangs ni nad kyi sprin du chags pas sems can thams cad lus ba spu ldang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:16175: rab tu 'jigs pa'i rlung nag dang /
NK069(tu)001:16176: zhes sna bug nas sems can rab tu 'jigs pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:16177: rlung nag ldang bas dbyar gyis char sprin ltar 'thibs so //
NK069(tu)001:16178: grang ba dang tsha ba'i dbugs kyis phyogs bcu kun tu khams 'khrug par byed pa /
NK069(tu)001:16179: zhes rlung dang bad kan grang ba'i nad dang /
NK069(tu)001:16180: khrag dang mkhris pa tsha ba'i nad ni /
NK069(tu)001:16182: sems can phyogs bcu na yod pa'i nad kham des 'khrugs cing klong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:16183: nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhis 'debs par byed pa /
NK069(tu)001:16184: zhes nad rtsa ba bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:16191: bad kan las gyur pa brgya /
NK069(tu)001:16192: mkhris pa las gyur pa brgya /
NK069(tu)001:16194: sems can rnams la 'debs par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:16195: myos shing nyams par byed pa'i mthus /
NK069(tu)001:16196: zhes gang la gtab pa de ni /
NK069(tu)001:16197: lus kyi dbang po ni myos /
NK069(tu)001:16198: sems kyi dran pa ni nyams /
NK069(tu)001:16200: gang rnams dbang du sdus zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:16202: zhes rgyal rigs sa la dbang /
NK069(tu)001:16206: rdol pa dug la dbang ba rnams dang phyi'i rol mtsho la gnas pa dang gling la gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16207: lha ma yin gyi ris dang /
NK069(tu)001:16208: zhes ri rab kyi khong seng na lha ma yin
NK069(tu)001:16209: gyi rgyal po shud ke na mchu rings la sogs
NK069(tu)001:16210: pa rnams so // lha'i ris dang /
NK069(tu)001:16218: gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi lha dang /
NK069(tu)001:16219: sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lha'i ded dpon ka ru na btul lo //
NK069(tu)001:16221: zhes spyir gzugs khams gnas ris bcu bdun las /
NK069(tu)001:16222: bsam gtan dang po'i gnas gsum ni /
NK069(tu)001:16226: de yang 'khor ba'i nyon mongs pa gyod dang khrin las tshangs pas na tshangs so //
NK069(tu)001:16228: zhes bsam gtan gnyis pa'i gnas gsum ni /
NK069(tu)001:16232: de yang rang gi lus la 'od gsal zhing /
NK069(tu)001:16233: nyi zla'i bya ba dang bral bas so //
NK069(tu)001:16235: zhes bsam gtan gsum pa'i gnas gsum ni /
NK069(tu)001:16239: de yang bsod nams kyi dge rtsa rgyas pas na dge rgyas so //
NK069(tu)001:16240: 'bras bu che ba man chad dbang du bsdus so //
NK069(tu)001:16241: zhes bsam gtan bzhi pa'i gnas gsum ni /
NK069(tu)001:16245: de yang gzhan las dge ba'i 'bras bu che bas na 'bras bu che ba zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:16250: 'dod pa'i khams la gnas ris nyi shu ste /
NK069(tu)001:16251: de yang ngan song gnas bcu ni /
NK069(tu)001:16252: tsha ba'i dmyal ba brgyad dang /
NK069(tu)001:16253: grang ba'i dmyal ba brgyad dang /
NK069(tu)001:16255: yi dwags dang dud 'gro gnyis te bcu'o //
NK069(tu)001:16258: rgyal chen rigs bzhi dang lnga /
NK069(tu)001:16259: sum cu rtsa gsum dang drug /
NK069(tu)001:16264: gzugs khams gnas ris bcu bdun ni /
NK069(tu)001:16287: gzugs myed khams na skye mched mu bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:16288: nam mkha' mtha' yas skye mched dang /
NK069(tu)001:16289: yod min myed min skye mched dang /
NK069(tu)001:16290: ci yang myed pa'i skye mched do //
NK069(tu)001:16292: ru tras 'bras bu che ba man chad dbang du sdus so //
NK069(tu)001:16293: yang na steng lha'i srid pa /
NK069(tu)001:16295: 'og klu'i srid pa gsum dbang du sdus so //
NK069(tu)001:16296: mi che ba la sogs pa'i rtsang ma'i ris kyi
NK069(tu)001:16297: lha lnga pa ni 'phags pa'i gnas gzhan yin pas
NK069(tu)001:16298: dbang du sdu' rgyu ma rnyed do //
NK069(tu)001:16301: sngon rten pa'i stobs zhes pa /
NK069(tu)001:16302: de yang sngon skal pa kun bkod bya ba la /
NK069(tu)001:16303: zhing khams mngon par dga' ba zhes bya bar /
NK069(tu)001:16304: slob dpon dge slong thub ka gzhon nu zhes bya ba la /
NK069(tu)001:16305: gsang sngags theg pa chen po'i chos la mkhas par gyur pa la /
NK069(tu)001:16306: der yul phyogs de na khyim bdag ko'u ka ya zhes bya ba la /
NK069(tu)001:16307: bu thar pa nag po nag zhes bya ba yod de /
NK069(tu)001:16308: bu thar pa nag po zhes bya ba yod de /
NK069(tu)001:16309: des g.yog dan phag zhes bya ba khrid nas /
NK069(tu)001:16310: dge slong thub ka gzhon nu la chos zhus pas /
NK069(tu)001:16312: da lta rang ci dgar spyad nas /
NK069(tu)001:16313: tshe phyi ma la sangs rgyas ba'i chos yod na zhu zhes byas pas /
NK069(tu)001:16314: dge slong gis don dam pa la dgongs nas yod gsung nas bshad pa /
NK069(tu)001:16315: ji bzhin nyid de ma bcos na //
NK069(tu)001:16316: dngos po bzhi la gnas bcas kyang //
NK069(tu)001:16317: nam mkha' la ni sprin dengs bzhin //
NK069(tu)001:16318: rnal 'byor de nyid dam pa'i lam //
NK069(tu)001:16324: thabs che'o gsung nas der thar pas dge slong byas /
NK069(tu)001:16325: g.yog dan phag gis dge tshul byas nas //
NK069(tu)001:16327: der thar pa nag pos sgra ji bzhin du rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:16328: dngos po bzhi rang dga' spyad de /
NK069(tu)001:16331: mi tshangs pa rang dgar spyad /
NK069(tu)001:16332: khro bo rang rgyud par bsgoms so //
NK069(tu)001:16333: g.yog gis don ji bzhin par go ste /
NK069(tu)001:16334: de lta ma yin zhes byas pas /
NK069(tu)001:16337: dge slong g.yo' rgyu myed par drang por smra ste /
NK069(tu)001:16338: de'i thar pa ltar ni myin /
NK069(tu)001:16339: dan phag bzhin yin no byas pas /
NK069(tu)001:16341: slob dpon yang dan phag la dga' ba 'dir ma gnas cig zhes byas pas /
NK069(tu)001:16342: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dam tshig nyams /
NK069(tu)001:16343: dan phag yang nga'i g.yog yin pa la /
NK069(tu)001:16344: khyod nga la 'gran pa 'dir ma 'dug ces byas pas /
NK069(tu)001:16345: rdo rje mched kyi dam tshig nyams /
NK069(tu)001:16346: snying rje myed pas byang chub sems kyi dam tshig nyams /
NK069(tu)001:16348: ma byin pa len pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16349: rdzun dang phra ma byas pas yan lag gi dam tshig nyams /
NK069(tu)001:16351: kun tu nyams par cen por 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:16354: de nas thon nas las kyi srin por skyes pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16356: slob dpon dang dan phag dge ba rten pa'i stobs kyis sangs rgyas so //
NK069(tu)001:16357: thams cad mkhyen pas gzigs nas /
NK069(tu)001:16358: dge slong thub ka gzhon nu ni dpal rdo rje sems dpar sangs rgyas la /
NK069(tu)001:16359: g.yog dan phag ni dpal phyag na rdo rjer sangs rgyas pas /
NK069(tu)001:16361: shes bya ji ltar bar mkhyen pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16362: sems can thams cad kyi sems sangs rgyas su mkhyen pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16363: shes bya ji snyed par mkhyen ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:16364: sems can thams cad kyi las dang sdug bsngal tha dad pa rnams ma 'dres par mkhyen no //
NK069(tu)001:16365: ji lta ba dang ji snyed pa dbyer myed par mkhyen pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16366: rig ma rig me long gi lto rgyab ltar dbyer myed du mkhyen no //
NK069(tu)001:16367: des dge slong thar pa nag po ru trar skyes te /
NK069(tu)001:16368: gdul byar gyur pa de gzigs nas 'dul ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:16369: 'dir gtar kas gags bsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:16370: ru tra sngon thugs khar gzhon nus rten nas /
NK069(tu)001:16373: de sngon nas gzigs la thang /
NK069(tu)001:16374: yang ru tra 'khor bar 'khyams pa ma gzigs na /
NK069(tu)001:16376: gzigs na dmyal bar skyes tsam na 'don la thang zer na /
NK069(tu)001:16378: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyan gyis gzigs yang /
NK069(tu)001:16379: gdul bya'i snang ba log par song ste /
NK069(tu)001:16380: dper na brag phug kha byang du lta bar nyi ma mi 'char ba 'dra'o //
NK069(tu)001:16382: yul can du gzigs na yul yul can gyi rtog pa dang bcas par 'gro /
NK069(tu)001:16383: yul myed par gzigs su myi stub /
NK069(tu)001:16384: yul lus can dbyer myed du gzigs na /
NK069(tu)001:16385: dbyer myed mnyam po la gang gis gang la thugs rje skye zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:16386: yul du byas la rtog pa myed pa'i tshul gyis gzigs te /
NK069(tu)001:16387: de yang rnam rtog mi mnga' cir yang sa le mkhyen /
NK069(tu)001:16390: zhes spyir thugs rje la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:16391: rtag pa rgyun du skye ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16392: rang bzhin shugs kyis skye ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16393: skul zhing gsol ba btab pas skye ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16394: yul dang phrad na skye ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:16395: 'dir yul dang brad nas skye ba'i thugs rjes 'dul bar gyur to zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:16397: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa che ba'i rdo rje bkod pa'i sgyu 'phrul dra bas /
NK069(tu)001:16398: zhes thugs rje'i gzigs nas pa de nas /
NK069(tu)001:16399: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dang dbyer myed pa de ni che ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:16400: sku gsung thugs dbyer myed rdo rje'o //
NK069(tu)001:16401: tha dad myed bzhin tha dad pa'i rnam par bkod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16403: thabs shes rab gnyis su myed par bkod pas na dra ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:16404: che mchog longs spyod kyi dal dang /
NK069(tu)001:16405: ting nge'i cho 'phrul 'di man chad do //
NK069(tu)001:16410: cho 'phrul rmad du 'byung ba la drug ste /
NK069(tu)001:16413: sprul pa rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK069(tu)001:16414: byin gyis rlabs kyis cho 'phrul dang /
NK069(tu)001:16417: dkyil 'khor rmad du byung ba ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:16418: che mchog longs spyod chen po'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK069(tu)001:16419: sprul pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK069(tu)001:16420: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK069(tu)001:16421: ngo mtshar tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK069(tu)001:16422: 'phrin las rmad du 'byung ba ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:16423: 'phrin las kyi ngo bo rmad du 'byung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16424: 'phrin las kyi 'bras bu rmad du 'byung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:16428: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i srid pa'i gsum gyi bdag po /
NK069(tu)001:16429: zhes gdul bya ni spyir rigs drug gi /
NK069(tu)001:16434: bar mi'i srid pa gsum gyis bdag po ni log par 'dren pa'i ru tras byas pas so //
NK069(tu)001:16435: 'dul ba'i ngar rgyal chen po'i gzi' brjid ston pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:16436: zhes nga myed pa'i nga rgyal gyis /
NK069(tu)001:16437: log pa'i nga rgyal can gyi ru tra de dag
NK069(tu)001:16438: gi lus ngag yid kyi sbyor ba zil gyis mnon
NK069(tu)001:16439: pa'i gzi' brjid bstan pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:16440: che mchog longs spyod chen po ni /
NK069(tu)001:16444: dbu' smug nag sku dang mthun no //
NK069(tu)001:16452: dbus dkar po zhi ba'i zhal lo //
NK069(tu)001:16454: g.yas ni rdo rje rtse dgu' dang /
NK069(tu)001:16461: dbang phyug chen po dbyug pa phyar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:16463: thod pa bdud rtsis bkang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16470: u ma de ba'i ba ga dang /
NK069(tu)001:16472: 'di kun bzang he ru ka ste /
NK069(tu)001:16473: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i bdag po zhes bya ba yin no //
NK069(tu)001:16474: las kyi bdag po bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16475: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i bdag po /
NK069(tu)001:16476: zhes de ma nor ba chos kyi dbyings /
NK069(tu)001:16478: de'i ngang du rtogs pas gshegs pa /
NK069(tu)001:16479: thams cad ni sangs rgyas so //
NK069(tu)001:16483: dbyer myed du gshegs pa'i bdag po /
NK069(tu)001:16484: rigs kyi kun tu bzang po'o //
NK069(tu)001:16485: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po /
NK069(tu)001:16487: sku dang ye shes su ldan /
NK069(tu)001:16489: longs spyod rnam gnyis la dgyes pas chen po /
NK069(tu)001:16491: khro bo'i rgyal po'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin chen po rnam par 'phro ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:16492: zhes rigs lnga he ru ka'i bdag po /
NK069(tu)001:16493: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi rtsa ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:16494: sprin dang 'dra ba'i khro bo mang po rnams 'phro ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:16495: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i rgyal po'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs te /
NK069(tu)001:16499: rgyal po ni mtha' gnyis las so //
NK069(tu)001:16500: che mchog khro bo'i ting nge 'dzin du snyoms par zhugs nas so //
NK069(tu)001:16501: sprul pa 'byung ba'i gzhi yum bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16502: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nas /
NK069(tu)001:16503: zhes de bzhin nyid chos kyi dbyings las sam /
NK069(tu)001:16504: de bzhin nyid kho na yum yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:16505: de yum gyi 'byung gnas su gyur pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:16506: khro mo dbang phyug chen mo mngon phyung ste /
NK069(tu)001:16507: zhes de bzhin nyid chos kyi dbyings kyi rtags /
NK069(tu)001:16509: 'khor 'das kyi dbang phyug chen mo ste /
NK069(tu)001:16510: sku mngon du phyung nas thon pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16511: dper na nam ka'i char ltar 'byung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:16512: de yang zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK069(tu)001:16514: g.yas rdo rje g.yon b+han d+ha snams pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16516: hi hi dgyes pa'i gzi' mdangs kyis pad ma rgyas par mdzad nas /
NK069(tu)001:16517: zhes chos nyid kyi dgyel pa ldan pa'i rtags sam /
NK069(tu)001:16520: rang gi ba ga pad ma'i dkyil 'khor rgyas par mdzad nas /
NK069(tu)001:16522: ba gar phyi dbyibs kyi a /
NK069(tu)001:16528: rigs lnga yab yum gyi yi ge bkod nas so //
NK069(tu)001:16529: gnyis su myed par 'khril ba'i dgyes pas thim pas /
NK069(tu)001:16531: gsang ba'i rdo rje'i dgyes par mdzad nas sam /
NK069(tu)001:16532: don dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su myed pa'i rtags /
NK069(tu)001:16533: yab yum thabs shes rab gnyis su myed par 'khril ba'i dgyes pa /
NK069(tu)001:16535: yab yum 'od zer snol mar thim nas /
NK069(tu)001:16536: sprul pa'i rgyu bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16537: byang chub sems kyi sprin las /
NK069(tu)001:16538: zhes lhag pa'i byang chub sems mkha' la sprin tshogs ltar 'phros pas /
NK069(tu)001:16539: gsung gi dkyil 'khor sngags kyi sgra dang bcas par spro'o //
NK069(tu)001:16540: sprul pa'i rkyen bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16542: zhes lhag pa'i byang chub de nyid thugs ye shes kyi rang bzhin yin pas h'u du snang /
NK069(tu)001:16543: thugs de yang sku gsung thugs gsum dang ldan pa'i rtags su yi ge gsum du snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:16552: phata ni sod la sregs shig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16553: ha la ni chom shig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16554: ha la ha la ha la /
NK069(tu)001:16556: h'u ni thugs ye shes te /
NK069(tu)001:16557: sku gsung thugs gsum dang ldan pas sna tshogs pa'i khro bo'o //
NK069(tu)001:16560: byang chub sems las gsung gi dkyil 'khor sngags kyi yi ge'i sgra dang bcas par spro ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:16562: sku gsung thugs sna tshogs pa'i rdo rje khro bos /
NK069(tu)001:16563: 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi gdug pa can thams cad sod la sregs /
NK069(tu)001:16564: chom la thugs ye shes su bsdus cig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16565: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas par khyab pas /
NK069(tu)001:16566: zhes 'di man chad ni sprul pa rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul dang /
NK069(tu)001:16567: khro bo 'chol ba'i dkyil 'khor ston te /
NK069(tu)001:16568: byang chub sems kyis kun la khyab pas /
NK069(tu)001:16569: stong gsum kun sngags kyi sgras gang /
NK069(tu)001:16575: zhes de'i ngo bo khro bo'i dal lo //
NK069(tu)001:16577: badz+ra he ru ka g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing /
NK069(tu)001:16578: rdo rje kha tong ti ra'i g.yug pa g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:16579: dung dmar rgyu zhags khyung khra g.yon /
NK069(tu)001:16580: 'bu ta he ka g.yas ljang g.yon sngo dbus ser zhal /
NK069(tu)001:16581: 'khor lo dgra' s+t+wa zhags pa g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:16582: ban d+ha rnge'u chung kha tong g.yon /
NK069(tu)001:16586: rin chen bshol dang stun shing g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:16587: ban d+ha dgra s+t+wa rnge'u chung g.yon /
NK069(tu)001:16588: pad ma he ru ka g.yas sngo g.yon ljang dbus dmar zhal /
NK069(tu)001:16589: pad ma'i rnge'u chung spu gri g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:16590: b+han d+ha kha tong sor 'phreng g.yon /
NK069(tu)001:16591: kar ma he ru ka g.yas dmar g.yon ser dbus ljang zhal /
NK069(tu)001:16592: ral gri rgyu zhags rnge'u chung g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:16593: ban d+ha thog dbyug kha tong g.yon /
NK069(tu)001:16598: de bas na khro bo 'chol ba'i dkyil 'khor zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:16600: sprul pa rang gi ngo bo ba stan tshad /
NK069(tu)001:16602: phyogs bcu'i rdul grangs ni phra mo rnyed rdul phra rab dang mnyam pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16604: zhes che chung gi tshad ni /
NK069(tu)001:16606: de yang stong chung rgyun dang /
NK069(tu)001:16608: stong gsum gyi stong chen po las so //
NK069(tu)001:16613: grangs rdul snyed mi shong zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:16615: de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba'i dbang du /
NK069(tu)001:16616: stong gsum yang nyungs 'bru gcig tu tshud ma la smos la /
NK069(tu)001:16617: gdul bya'i snang ba'i dbang du ru tra la zag bcas kyi mngon shes yod pas /
NK069(tu)001:16618: des mthong tshad du khro bo spros pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16620: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad g.yos /
NK069(tu)001:16622: zhes 'di man chad ni byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul te /
NK069(tu)001:16623: shar mtho' na nub dma' ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16624: nub dma' na shar mtho ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16625: lho mtho' na byang dma' ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16626: byang mtho na lho dma' ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16628: mtha' mtho' na dbus dma' de rnams sa drug tu g.yos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16629: rab tu g.yos ngag kun tu g.yos yid so //
NK069(tu)001:16630: zhes g.yo' ba byang chub sems kyis /
NK069(tu)001:16631: lus ngag yid gsum thams cad la /
NK069(tu)001:16632: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyi cho 'phrul ston /
NK069(tu)001:16633: 'ur lus 'ur rab tu 'ur ngag 'ur kun tu 'ur yid 'ur ro //
NK069(tu)001:16634: zhes smon pa byang chub sems kyi lus ngag yid gsum la /
NK069(tu)001:16635: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi cho 'phrul ston /
NK069(tu)001:16636: chem lus chem rab tu chem ngag chem kun tu chem yid chem mo //
NK069(tu)001:16637: zhes ldang ba byang chub sems kyis lus ngag yid gsum la /
NK069(tu)001:16638: mnyam pa nyid kyis ye shes kyi cho 'phrul ston /
NK069(tu)001:16639: shig lus shig rab tu shig ngag shig kun tu yid shig shig go //
NK069(tu)001:16640: zhes 'jug pa byang chub sems kyis /
NK069(tu)001:16642: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi byin brlabs kyi cho 'phrul ston /
NK069(tu)001:16643: gtor lus gtor rab tu gtor ngag gtor kun tu gtor yid gtor ro //
NK069(tu)001:16644: zhes gnas pa byang chub sems kyis lus ngag yid
NK069(tu)001:16645: gsum la bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyi byin
NK069(tu)001:16647: sprul pas 'dul bar bya ba'i ngo bo bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16648: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i stong khams thams cad na gnas pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:16649: zhes chos snang ba'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK069(tu)001:16650: dug gsum la gnad du snun par byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16652: ma h+aa de ba rgyal rigs kyi lha yin pas dbang che /
NK069(tu)001:16653: yang na 'dod chags kyi lha yin pas dbang che ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16655: tshangs pa rje'u rigs kyi lha yin pas gzi brjid che /
NK069(tu)001:16656: yang na gti mug gi lha yin bas gzi brjid che ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16658: khyab 'jug bram ze rigs kyi lha yin pas mthu' che ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:16659: yang na zhe sdang gi lha yin pas mthu' che'o //
NK069(tu)001:16660: dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:16661: dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa thams cad rmong rigs kyi lha yin pas 'dod chags che /
NK069(tu)001:16662: nga rgyal gyi lha yin pas kun la dbang bsgyur ba yin no //
NK069(tu)001:16663: zil gyis mnan pa bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16664: rgyal rab tu rgyal kun tu brgyal bar gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:16668: dran pa'i dbang po nyams par gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:16670: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po nyid /
NK069(tu)001:16671: ces de yan chad khro bo 'chol pa'i dkyil 'khor bstan nas /
NK069(tu)001:16672: 'di man cad sprul pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor ram /
NK069(tu)001:16673: zhe sdang rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor ston pas na de nas so //
NK069(tu)001:16674: dbus kyi gtso' bo 'bu ta he ru ka ni /
NK069(tu)001:16675: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po zhes bya ba de nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:16676: bdud dang log 'dren rnams 'jigs byed gzhan las khyad
NK069(tu)001:16677: 'phags pas chen po gdug pa can la ni shin
NK069(tu)001:16678: tu rngam pa'i dbu' dgu phyag bco' brgyad par gnas
NK069(tu)001:16679: pas na / thams cad kyi bung zhes byed /
NK069(tu)001:16680: skyi bung zhes byed pa'i 'bar ba chen po'i /
NK069(tu)001:16681: khrag 'thung sku smug nag cir yang gyur ba /
NK069(tu)001:16682: zhes che mchog longs spyod kyi dkyil 'khor gyi dus
NK069(tu)001:16683: kyi kun bzang he ru ka de nyid ni sku
NK069(tu)001:16684: smug nag go // de las khro bo 'chol pa 'byung ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:16685: rang yang dbu' gsum phyag drug tu sgyur bas na /
NK069(tu)001:16687: dbu' dang phyag dang zhabs stong khams kyi rdul rnyed mtshon cha 'dzin pa de /
NK069(tu)001:16688: ces khro bo 'chol ba'i dus na yang /
NK069(tu)001:16694: mtshon cha sna tshogs pa 'dzin par spros nas /
NK069(tu)001:16696: dbu' gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhir 'dus so //
NK069(tu)001:16698: dbu' gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhir gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:16699: zhes 'bu ta he ru ka sku smug nag /
NK069(tu)001:16703: phyag drug 'khor lo kha t+w+aam ta ri g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:16704: dril bu ban d+ha rgyu zhags g.yon /
NK069(tu)001:16706: dbus kyi he ru ka'i phyag rgya ni /
NK069(tu)001:16707: ti ra'i dbyug to chen po dang /
NK069(tu)001:16709: dung chen dmar gyis rkang ba la /
NK069(tu)001:16710: rdo rjes dkrug cing rab tu gsol /
NK069(tu)001:16713: dur khrod chen por dgyes nas /
NK069(tu)001:16714: zhes he ru de bzhugs pa'i gnas ni /
NK069(tu)001:16717: gsang ba tshogs brgyad kyi dur khrod /
NK069(tu)001:16718: de kho na nyid chos nyid kyi dur khrod las /
NK069(tu)001:16719: phyi rdzas kyi dur khrod la dga' zhing dgyes pas na /
NK069(tu)001:16722: 'byung po mi sha can gnas la /
NK069(tu)001:16723: de dag 'dul bar mdzad pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:16724: dur khrod chen por dgyes nas so //
NK069(tu)001:16725: khrag gi rgya mtsho'i dkyil na /
NK069(tu)001:16726: zhes 'dod chags khrag gi rgya mtsho' la /
NK069(tu)001:16727: 'khor ba 'dod pa'i khams kyi zhen pa sbyang ba'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:16728: phyi ltar khrag gi rgya mtsho' la /
NK069(tu)001:16729: nang ltar 'dod khams kyi zhen pa sbyong ba /
NK069(tu)001:16730: gsang ba ltar bde ba'i ye shes su gsal ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:16731: khrag mtsho' 'de'i dkyil na gang yod zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:16733: rag ta zhes bya ba'i sgras drangs na /
NK069(tu)001:16735: thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don la chags pas na khrag /
NK069(tu)001:16736: thugs rje zab cing ting dpag dka' ba'am rgya che bas rgya matsho'o //
NK069(tu)001:16737: keng rus chen po'i ri rab kyi steng /
NK069(tu)001:16738: zhes zhe sdang keng rus kyi ri rab la /
NK069(tu)001:16739: 'khor ba gzugs kyi khams kyi zhen ba sbyong ba'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:16740: phyi ltar keng rus dkar po'i ri rab la /
NK069(tu)001:16741: nang ltar gzugs khams kyi zhen pa sbyong ba /
NK069(tu)001:16742: gsang ba ltar gsal ba'i ye shes su gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:16743: ri rab de'i steng na gang yang yod zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:16745: khrag dang chu ser gyi rlan dang bral ba yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:16746: yang dag pa'i shes rab kyang nyon mongs pa'i rlan dang bral ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:16747: yang dag pa'i shes rab de ye shes kyi tshogs
NK069(tu)001:16748: mang po dang ldan pa'i rtags su keng rus kyi
NK069(tu)001:16749: ri rab bungs che la mtho' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:16750: 'bar ba chen po'i klong gi 'khor lo'i dkyil na /
NK069(tu)001:16751: zhes gti mug gi mun pa sel ba'i me dbung 'bar ba la /
NK069(tu)001:16752: 'khor ba gzugs myed khams kyi zhen pa sbyong ba'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:16754: nang ltar gzugs myed khams kyi zhen pa sbyong ba /
NK069(tu)001:16755: gsang ba ltar mi rtog pa gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:16756: de'i dbus na pho brang gzhal yas khang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi' pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:16757: dbus kyi lte ba la gdan ni /
NK069(tu)001:16759: rtog pa dang thugs rje 'bar ba rnam gnyis dang ldan pa'i rtags /
NK069(tu)001:16760: me dpung 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang /
NK069(tu)001:16761: 'du 'phro klong gi dkyil na 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi
NK069(tu)001:16762: mu khyud dang bcas pa'i dbus kyi lte ba la
NK069(tu)001:16765: zhes 'bu ta he ru ka'i gdan ni khams gsum
NK069(tu)001:16766: dbang du sdud pa'i ru tra ni dbang phyug chen
NK069(tu)001:16767: po'o // dur khrod kyi bdag po khyo shugs kyi gdan la /
NK069(tu)001:16768: zhes dur khrod na gnas pas na dur khrod bdag
NK069(tu)001:16769: po pho mo byi chings snol mar yod pas na
NK069(tu)001:16771: yang na phyi bzung ba'i yul bdag myed par ma rtogs pa yum /
NK069(tu)001:16772: nang 'dzin pa'i sems bdag myed par ma rtogs pa yab /
NK069(tu)001:16773: bzung 'dzin gyis dregs shing bdag 'dzin la dbang ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:16774: de gnyis myed du sgrol ba'i phyir byi chings su snol ba'i tshul yin no //
NK069(tu)001:16777: thugs rje chen po thabs mkhas pa'i mdzad spyod kyis /
NK069(tu)001:16778: 'gro ba'i don la lag rkyang nas mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16780: 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa nyid na /
NK069(tu)001:16781: shes rab kyis chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos par rtogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16782: de bas na thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral myed par bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:16783: rigs lngar 'du' tshul bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16784: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor sprin phung de dag kyang /
NK069(tu)001:16785: zhes sku khro tshul dang bcas /
NK069(tu)001:16786: 'bar ba'i gar dgus khyab pas khro bo /
NK069(tu)001:16787: gtso' dang 'khor du ldan pas dkyil 'khor /
NK069(tu)001:16788: grangs mang la bungs 'thug pas na sprin phung /
NK069(tu)001:16789: de ltar gnas pa de dag kyang /
NK069(tu)001:16790: ji ltar gnas pa yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:16791: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po rdo rjer gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:16792: zhes rdo rje rigs kyi khro bo thams cad 'dus nas badz+ra he ru kar gyur pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16797: g.yas rdo rje kha t+w+aam zhing dbyug /
NK069(tu)001:16798: g.yon dril bu dung dmar rgyu zhags so //
NK069(tu)001:16799: rgya bcu pa'i le'u so gcig pa las /
NK069(tu)001:16800: shar gyi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni /
NK069(tu)001:16801: ti ra chen po'i dbyugs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16802: rdo rje chen por rab tu 'bar /
NK069(tu)001:16803: mi mgo' dmar gyis bskang ba gsol /
NK069(tu)001:16806: zhes de ni me long lta bu'i ye shes kyi
NK069(tu)001:16807: khyad par las byung ba'i badz+ra he ru ka grub
NK069(tu)001:16809: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po cher gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:16811: zhes rin po che'i rigs kyi khro bo thams cad 'dus nas /
NK069(tu)001:16812: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyi khyad par las gyur pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:16813: rat+na he ru kar grub nas /
NK069(tu)001:16814: lho phyogs na bzhugs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16819: g.yas rin chen kha tong ti ra /
NK069(tu)001:16820: g.yon dril bu dung dmar rgyu zhags so //
NK069(tu)001:16822: lho phyogs phyag rgya chen po ni /
NK069(tu)001:16823: ti ra chen po'i dbyug pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16824: yid bzhin nor bu rin po che dang /
NK069(tu)001:16825: yid bzhin nor bu'i gzhal yas su /
NK069(tu)001:16826: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rab tu gsol /
NK069(tu)001:16828: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po pad ma chen por gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:16830: zhes pad ma rigs kyi khro bo thams cad 'dus nas /
NK069(tu)001:16831: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyi khyad par las byung ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:16832: pad ma he ru kar grub nas /
NK069(tu)001:16834: g.yas ser g.yon ljang dbus dmar /
NK069(tu)001:16836: pad ma kha tam ti ra g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:16837: dril bu dung dmar rgyu zhags g.yon /
NK069(tu)001:16839: nub kyi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni /
NK069(tu)001:16840: ti ra chen po'i dbyug pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16841: rdo rje pad ma chags myed 'bar /
NK069(tu)001:16842: dung chen dmar gyis skang ba gsol /
NK069(tu)001:16844: la la ni dpal khrag 'thung chen po kun tu las su gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:16846: zhes las kyi rigs kyi khro bo thams cad gcig tu 'dus nas /
NK069(tu)001:16847: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyi khyad par las byung ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:16848: kar ma he ru kar gyur te byang na bzhugs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16850: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal /
NK069(tu)001:16852: ral gri kha tam zhing dbyug g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:16853: dril bu dung dmar rgyu zhags g.yon no //
NK069(tu)001:16855: byang gi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni /
NK069(tu)001:16856: ti ra chen po'i dbyug pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:16857: rdo rje rgya gram rab tu 'bar /
NK069(tu)001:16858: dung chen dmar gyis skang ba gsol /
NK069(tu)001:16859: khro mo rnams kyang khro dang 'thun /
NK069(tu)001:16861: rigs lnga'i cha lugs bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16862: de dag kun kyang 'jig byed chen po'i cha lugs dang /
NK069(tu)001:16863: zhes rigs lnga de dag gi chas la dgu ste /
NK069(tu)001:16865: gti mug dag pa'i ban glang gi kor rlon /
NK069(tu)001:16866: 'dod chags dag pa'i zhing lpags kyi g.yang gzhi' /
NK069(tu)001:16867: zhe sdang dag pa'i stag lpags kyi sham thabs so //
NK069(tu)001:16868: gdab pa'i tshom bu gsum ni /
NK069(tu)001:16869: mkha' 'gro dbang du bsdud pa'i raka ta'i thig le /
NK069(tu)001:16870: don dam bcud dang ldan pa'i zhag gi zo ris /
NK069(tu)001:16871: 'dul byed 'phrin las thal chen gyi tshom bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:16873: sku gsum mtshon pa'i thod pa'i rgyan /
NK069(tu)001:16874: thabs chen mtshon pa'i nyi zla'i rgyan /
NK069(tu)001:16875: dug lnga dag pa sbrul gyis rgyan no //
NK069(tu)001:16877: gsung rngam pa'i nga ro ni /
NK069(tu)001:16880: ha la ha la sgrogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16882: skal pa 'jig pa'i dus kyi me dpung lta bur 'bar ba'i klong na /
NK069(tu)001:16883: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhis /
NK069(tu)001:16885: ye shes drug dang ldan pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:16886: tshad myed pa bzhi dang ldan pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:16888: zas su dri za bas na dri za dang /
NK069(tu)001:16889: de ni shar gyi khro bo'i gdan no //
NK069(tu)001:16891: rang gi gnod pa gzhan la gter bas na /
NK069(tu)001:16893: de ni byang gi khro bo'i gdan no //
NK069(tu)001:16895: sha khrag gi srog la dga' bas srin po dang /
NK069(tu)001:16896: nub kyi khro bo'i gdan no //
NK069(tu)001:16898: sems can gshin gyi rje byed pas na gshin rje /
NK069(tu)001:16900: khyo shugs kyi gdan byas pa la /
NK069(tu)001:16902: pho mo byi chings su snol ba'i gdan byas pa /
NK069(tu)001:16904: zhes lha'i bu'i bdud bzhom pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:16906: 'jig rten gyi lha chen 'dar rgyel zhabs kyis rdzis pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16907: khyad par bya bas btsun mo btsun mo nyon mongs
NK069(tu)001:16908: pa 'thung bas khrag 'thung thugs rje che bas chen
NK069(tu)001:16910: so so'i sku la 'khril ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:16911: zhes rigs lnga'i yum so so'i sku la 'khril nas 'khod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16912: dang po gtso' bo bkod nas phyir khro mo 'god pa lta bu ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:16913: dang po dkyil 'khor spro ba'i dus na yang /
NK069(tu)001:16914: yab yum gnyis su myed par ldan par spros la /
NK069(tu)001:16915: slar bsdu ba'i dus na yang yab yum 'khril mar sdud pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16916: yang rigs lnga gcig tu 'du ba bstan /
NK069(tu)001:16917: rigs lnga'i he ru ka las gcig tu thim ste /
NK069(tu)001:16918: zhes de nas rigs gcig tu 'dus nas thim pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:16919: rtags so so ma yin tha mi dad /
NK069(tu)001:16920: don ye shes lnga yang dbyer myed par thim pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16921: bsdus nas gcig gis mang po 'dul ba ngo mtshar cher bstan to //
NK069(tu)001:16922: zhes de ltar he ru ka gcig tu bsdus pa'i rgyu mtshan ni he ru ka gcig gis /
NK069(tu)001:16923: dregs pa mang po 'dul ba de /
NK069(tu)001:16924: shin tu ngo mtshar bas na /
NK069(tu)001:16925: sprul pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor ram /
NK069(tu)001:16926: zhe sdang rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor du bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:16927: de nas dregs pa chen po la sogs pa btum pa'i sems kyis /
NK069(tu)001:16928: zhes 'di man chad 'phrin las rmad du 'byung ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:16929: rdo rje srin po'i dkyil 'khor ston te /
NK069(tu)001:16930: ru tra la sogs pa'i nyon mongs pa lnga rang rgyud du shar bas stub pa'i sems kyis /
NK069(tu)001:16931: gdug pa'i rdzu 'phrul chen po sna tshogs bstan nas /
NK069(tu)001:16934: sems kyis log par rtog pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:16935: 'grin gcig tu gdug pa'i nga ros /
NK069(tu)001:16939: barlanga po'i btum tshig gis smras pa /
NK069(tu)001:16940: zhes tshig barlanga po zhes bya ba ni zhes dang snyan sngags myed par /
NK069(tu)001:16941: rngan can nam zhe gcod pa'i tshig go //
NK069(tu)001:16942: smra ba stum po gyong khengs can no //
NK069(tu)001:16943: thong thong snying rje'i bdag po cis de ltar byed dam zhes 'dzer zhing /
NK069(tu)001:16944: zhes khyed sangs rgyas bya ba /
NK069(tu)001:16945: gnyen skyong thugs rje che zer tsam na /
NK069(tu)001:16946: de ltar byed dam thong thong /
NK069(tu)001:16947: snying rje'i mnga' bdag po ma yin nam /
NK069(tu)001:16948: sdug bsngal du ma bzhug ces so //
NK069(tu)001:16949: sems kyis bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rdo rje srin po
NK069(tu)001:16950: 'khros nas ngag gi dbang po dpal la rngam mo
NK069(tu)001:16951: // dregs pa nga rgyal 'don pa 'dul ba'i de
NK069(tu)001:16952: nas bcom ldan 'das rdo rje srin po ni don
NK069(tu)001:16954: dbu' dgu phyag bco' brgyad zhabs 'bar ba brgyad du gnas nas /
NK069(tu)001:16955: zhes rdo rje srin po dbu' dgu' ni /
NK069(tu)001:16956: sgyu 'phrul bla ma'i le'u dgu nas /
NK069(tu)001:16957: dbu' gsum dang la byung ba ni //
NK069(tu)001:16958: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK069(tu)001:16959: rnam par thar pa'i dbu' gsum la //
NK069(tu)001:16960: khams gsum mya ngan zlo ba'i zhal //
NK069(tu)001:16961: dbu' gsum bar ma rngam pa ni //
NK069(tu)001:16962: g.yas sngo g.yon ljang dbus mthing nag /
NK069(tu)001:16963: thabs dang shes rab sems kyi dbu' //
NK069(tu)001:16964: srid gsum dbyings su rdzogs pa'i zhal //
NK069(tu)001:16965: dbu' gsum tha mar rngam pa ni //
NK069(tu)001:16966: g.yas mthing g.yon mthing dbus mthing zhal //
NK069(tu)001:16967: khams gsum re ba skong ba yi //
NK069(tu)001:16968: lung dang man ngag sems kyi dbu' //
NK069(tu)001:16969: 'gyur ba myed pas mthing nag zhal //
NK069(tu)001:16971: dang po rtsa ba'i zhal ni g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal /
NK069(tu)001:16972: bar ma ni g.yas sngo g.yon ljang dbus mthing zhal /
NK069(tu)001:16973: steng ma gsum ka mthing ka'o //
NK069(tu)001:16974: de ni he ru ka dgu' klong gi zhal lo //
NK069(tu)001:16977: bco' brgyad phyag na snams pa ni //
NK069(tu)001:16978: rdo rje glo snying zhing chung g.yas //
NK069(tu)001:16979: ban d+ha zhing chen tir chung g.yon //
NK069(tu)001:16980: nang zhags nyi ma khyung chen g.yas //
NK069(tu)001:16981: zhing chen zla ba 'ug pa g.yon //
NK069(tu)001:16982: me dang rgya mtsho' ga'u g.yas //
NK069(tu)001:16983: rlung dang rin chen ri rab g.yon //
NK069(tu)001:16984: yon tan bco' brgyad dbyings su rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:16986: phyag bco' brgyad kyi g.yas dang po gsum na /
NK069(tu)001:16998: g.yon gyi dang po gsum ni /
NK069(tu)001:17010: stong pa bco' brgyad kyi don thugs la gsal ba'i rtags sam /
NK069(tu)001:17011: brdar bstan pa'i phyag bco' brgyad bstan no //
NK069(tu)001:17012: zhabs brgyad ni yang bla ma nas /
NK069(tu)001:17013: zhabs brgyad nga rgyal dregs pa gnon //
NK069(tu)001:17014: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:17015: rdo rje mthing ka'i gshog pa rkyang //
NK069(tu)001:17017: zhabs 'bar ba brgyad kyis dregs pa'i lha brgyad yab yum mgo' byi chings su /
NK069(tu)001:17018: bsgal tshigs bcom nas gnan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:17019: ngo bo thabs dang shes rab dbyer myed pa'i don no //
NK069(tu)001:17020: mtha' gnyis zil gyis mnon pa'i rtags rdo rje gshog pa rkyang ba'i tshul lo //
NK069(tu)001:17021: rngam pa'i skad kyis thugs rjes 'dul ba'i thabs kyis shin tu 'khros nas /
NK069(tu)001:17023: dbu' dgu' rol pa'i byin brlabs las //
NK069(tu)001:17024: g.yas gsum glog stong lce 'byin cing //
NK069(tu)001:17025: g.yon gsum 'brug stong sgra sgrogs pa //
NK069(tu)001:17026: dbus gsum rdo rje ser chen 'bebs //
NK069(tu)001:17028: 'khor bar 'khyams pa la thugs rje skyes /
NK069(tu)001:17030: thabs khyad par can la 'dzud pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17032: ni gdug pa can de dag gi sems thugs ye shes kyi rang bzhin du sdud par byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17035: de lta bu'i don la dgyes shing rngam pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:17036: kha hi kha hi kha hi /
NK069(tu)001:17037: gsum ni dug gsum zhal du zad par gsol zhing zos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17040: ma rig pa la ni rngams /
NK069(tu)001:17041: thugs rje chen pos ni 'dul lo //
NK069(tu)001:17042: de yang nyams sems la shar bas mkhyen /
NK069(tu)001:17044: mthong snang yul la shar bas gzigs so //
NK069(tu)001:17045: dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:17046: zhes 'dod chags kyi lha dbang phyug chen po /
NK069(tu)001:17048: gti' mug gi lha tshangs pa /
NK069(tu)001:17051: gdug pa chen po'i tshogs de dag gi //
NK069(tu)001:17052: zhes lhor gshin rje dang grul bum /
NK069(tu)001:17053: shar rgya sbyin dang dri za /
NK069(tu)001:17055: byang gnod sbyin dang stobs bzangs /
NK069(tu)001:17056: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi khyo rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:17057: rdos bcas kyi phung po bshig pas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:17058: snying dang dbang po kun phyung /
NK069(tu)001:17059: zhes sems can gyi nyon mongs pa rtsad nas gcad pa'i phyir snying kun phyung /
NK069(tu)001:17060: dbang po lngas log pa'i sgo dgag pa'i phyir dbang po phyung /
NK069(tu)001:17064: zhes bzung 'dzin 'brel pa'i mngon par zhen pa dgag pa'i phyir nang rol drangs so //
NK069(tu)001:17065: yan lag kun bcad stubs nas /
NK069(tu)001:17066: zhes las ngan pa'i yan lag mang po yod pa kun rgyun bcad pa'i phyir na //
NK069(tu)001:17068: yan lag bcad pa ni las ngan pa gcad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17072: gti' mug ye shes su sbyangs pas sha kun zosa /
NK069(tu)001:17073: 'dod chags zad par byas pas khrag kun 'thungsa /
NK069(tu)001:17074: zhe sdang dag par byas nas rus pa kun 'chos so //
NK069(tu)001:17077: gis de yang dug lnga gnas 'gyur ye shes lngar sbyangs /
NK069(tu)001:17078: lto ba chos kyi dbyings su sgrib pa sbyangs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17079: b+h+yo e a ra li dz+dza dz+dza /
NK069(tu)001:17080: zhes pho sgral ba de nas /
NK069(tu)001:17081: dbang phyug ma rnams bsdu ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:17082: h'u ni thugs ye shes nyid sku gsung thugs gsum dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17083: b+h+yo ni dbang phyug mi snying po'o //
NK069(tu)001:17084: a ra li ni nam mkhar mgro' ma /
NK069(tu)001:17085: dz+dza ni dbang du bsdul ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:17086: chung ma kun dbang du bsdu ba'i sngags de brjod pas /
NK069(tu)001:17087: 'khor dbang du bsdud pa'i sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:17089: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams nam mkha' dang bcas pa /
NK069(tu)001:17090: zhes phyogs bcu snod kyi 'jiig rten gyi khams na /
NK069(tu)001:17091: stong gsum gyi stong chen po nam mkha' dang bcas pa /
NK069(tu)001:17092: nyungs 'bru tsam gcig gi nang du chud par dbang du stus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17093: nyungs 'bru gcig tsam du tshud par bstus so //
NK069(tu)001:17095: snod kyi 'jig rten yang nyungs 'bru gcig tsam gyi
NK069(tu)001:17096: nang du tshud par dbang du sdus nas de na
NK069(tu)001:17097: gnas na / bcud kyi 'jig rten dbang du sdud
NK069(tu)001:17098: pa lta smos kyang ci dgos zhes pa'i don no
NK069(tu)001:17099: gnas na / // de nas 'byung po ma lus pa'i rgyal po'i yang rgyal po /
NK069(tu)001:17100: zhes dus dang gnas skabs myed par kun tu 'byung bas na /
NK069(tu)001:17102: gdon chen bco brgyad de'i yang rgyal po ni /
NK069(tu)001:17103: dregs pa chen po la sogs pa'i chung ma /
NK069(tu)001:17104: zhes srin po'i rgyal po dang /
NK069(tu)001:17111: 'byung mo thams cad kyi rje mo'i yang rje mo /
NK069(tu)001:17112: zhes 'byung po rnam par rgyal ba'i bu mo 'byung mo yid 'khrug ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:17113: shar gyi rgyal mo drug ni /
NK069(tu)001:17114: srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang /
NK069(tu)001:17115: zhes spyir dbang phyug ma la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:17119: 'dir spyir mgo' snyan du bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:17122: mgo' ni g.yag gi mgo' can no //
NK069(tu)001:17125: mi srin dmar ser tri shul zhing chen g.yag /
NK069(tu)001:17130: mgo' sbrul mgo' can lag na rdo rje rtse lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:17132: tshangs ma dmar skya rtse lnga ba ban dmar sprul /
NK069(tu)001:17135: zhes ming ni 'khrug mo'am yang na khro mo /
NK069(tu)001:17140: khro mo ser nag 'jug zor spu gri gzig /
NK069(tu)001:17148: dbang mo dmar ser ban byi khog chen dred /
NK069(tu)001:17154: lag na rgyu zhags dang dung dmar /
NK069(tu)001:17155: khyab 'jug dkar dmar rgyu zhags dung dmar sre /
NK069(tu)001:17160: mgo' pha wang mgo' lag na 'khor lo 'dril lo //
NK069(tu)001:17161: gzhon nu ser nag pha wang 'khor lo 'dril /
NK069(tu)001:17163: de rnams ni shar gyi drug go //
NK069(tu)001:17172: dmar mo zhing chen rgyu zhags sdom /
NK069(tu)001:17178: lag na rin po che dang bum pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17179: bdud rtsi sngo nag chu srin rin chen bum /
NK069(tu)001:17182: zhes ming ni zhi ba mo /
NK069(tu)001:17187: zhi ba sngo skya glo snying bum pa sdigs /
NK069(tu)001:17195: be con nag mo bam chen gri 'debs khra /
NK069(tu)001:17199: sku mdog ser nag dbu' wa mo'i mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17202: srin mo ser nag rgyu 'dren rnge'u chung wa /
NK069(tu)001:17208: lag na bam chen gyi snying 'byin /
NK069(tu)001:17209: za byed mthing nag bam chen snying 'byin stag /
NK069(tu)001:17210: nub kyi dbang mo drug ni /
NK069(tu)001:17217: dga' byed dmar nag lcags kyu bgegs 'dren rgod /
NK069(tu)001:17219: ra ro khrag 'thung myos ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:17223: lag na rdo rje rtse lnga dang mdung dmar ro //
NK069(tu)001:17224: khrag 'thung dmar mo rtse lnga mdung dmar rta /
NK069(tu)001:17230: lag na rdo rje dang ban dmar /
NK069(tu)001:17231: gcig pur dkar dmar rdo rje ban dmar byi /
NK069(tu)001:17237: lag na zhing dbyug dang dung dmar ro //
NK069(tu)001:17238: yid 'phrog dmar nag tir chung dung dmar byi'o //
NK069(tu)001:17244: lag na pad ma zhags pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17245: grub ba dkar dmar pad zhags pu shud mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17252: rlung mo ljang ser ro za sha pho'i mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17254: byang gi srin mo drug ni /
NK069(tu)001:17260: lag na rnge'u chung dang ral gri /
NK069(tu)001:17261: gsod byed dmar nag rnge'u chung ral gri phag /
NK069(tu)001:17266: lag na rgyu ma dang kha tang /
NK069(tu)001:17267: me mo ljang nag rgyu 'dren kha tam kyin /
NK069(tu)001:17272: lag na rdo rje rtse lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:17274: phag mo nag mo rtse lnga zhing za phag /
NK069(tu)001:17282: rgan byed dmar mo dung dmar rgyu 'dren skrag /
NK069(tu)001:17290: sna chen ljang nag zangs gri zhags pa rnga /
NK069(tu)001:17293: zhes ming chu lha ste klu mo /
NK069(tu)001:17298: klu mo sngo skya bya rog dung dmar gri /
NK069(tu)001:17300: phyogs kyi sgo ma bzhi ni /
NK069(tu)001:17302: zhes shar gyi sgo ma ni /
NK069(tu)001:17307: nag mo lcags kyu pu tra khu byug mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17309: ra mgo' dmar ser chen mo dang /
NK069(tu)001:17310: zhes ming ni ra ni mo /
NK069(tu)001:17311: sku mdog dmar ser ram sngo mo /
NK069(tu)001:17313: lag na rgyu zhags dang gri /
NK069(tu)001:17314: ra ni sngon mo rgyu zhags 'debs pa'i ra /
NK069(tu)001:17317: bum sna sngo nag chen mo dang /
NK069(tu)001:17318: zhes nub kyi sgo ma ni /
NK069(tu)001:17323: bum sna sngo nag lcags sgrog kun sdom spre'u /
NK069(tu)001:17325: gsus 'dzin ser nag chen mo la sogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:17326: zhes byang gi sgo ma ni /
NK069(tu)001:17332: gsus 'dzin ser nag dril chen dung dmar spyang /
NK069(tu)001:17335: zhes las byed pa'i bran 'byung mo rnams dang /
NK069(tu)001:17336: de'i yang bran 'byung po phal pa rnams dang /
NK069(tu)001:17338: zhes bkur bsti byed pa'i g.yog mo rnams dang /
NK069(tu)001:17339: de'i yang g.yog mo rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:17340: 'khor zhing gi rdul snyed kyang bsdus so //
NK069(tu)001:17341: zhes rje mo lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:17344: dbang sdud mo lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:17347: zhing khams kyi rdul dang grangs mnyam pa rnams dbang du sdus so //
NK069(tu)001:17348: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po /
NK069(tu)001:17349: zhes de nas rdo rje khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bstan te /
NK069(tu)001:17350: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor zhes kyang bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:17351: yang na 'khor sdud pa'i cho 'phrul zhes kyang bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:17352: de yang rtog pa dbang du bcom /
NK069(tu)001:17354: bde' ba la dgyes pa longs spyod du gyur pas na chen po zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:17356: dpal khrag 'thung chen pos 'dul ba'i thabs kyis /
NK069(tu)001:17357: zhes bdag gzhan la dga' bas /
NK069(tu)001:17358: chags pa rang sar grol bas /
NK069(tu)001:17359: thabs shes rab gnyis su myed par sbyor ba'i thabs kyis so //
NK069(tu)001:17360: yang rigs lnga'i 'jigs byed chen por snang bar byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:17361: zhes yang ni mnan pa'am skyar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:17362: rigs lnga yang gcig las cig lngar 'byed par snang bas na'o //
NK069(tu)001:17363: de dag kun kyang dgyes pas rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin 'byung zhes bya ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:17364: zhes rigs lnga'i 'khor de dag kun kyang /
NK069(tu)001:17365: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su myed pa'i dgyes pas /
NK069(tu)001:17366: rol pa'i dkyil 'khor mang po sprin dang 'dra ba dbyung ba'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK069(tu)001:17368: dang po che mchog longs spyod rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor kun bzang he ru ka'i ting nger zhugs /
NK069(tu)001:17369: de las khro bo 'chol pa'i dkyil 'khor mang por spros /
NK069(tu)001:17370: de las zhe sdang rdo rje rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor du bstan te tshur sdus /
NK069(tu)001:17371: de nas yang rdo rje srin po'i dkyil 'khor dbu' dgu' pa gcig tu bstan /
NK069(tu)001:17372: de nas yang 'dir rdo rje khro bo'i dkyil 'khor rigs lngar ston pa de /
NK069(tu)001:17373: don ci la dgongs pa yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:17374: dang po lha yab yum gcig gi ting nge 'dzin zhugs pa de ni /
NK069(tu)001:17375: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bdag po kun bzang he ru ka yin par shes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:17376: de nas khro bo 'chol pa spro ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:17377: ru tra'i tshogs thams cad dpa' skong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:17378: de nas sngar sdud pa de ni /
NK069(tu)001:17379: spros pa thams cad dang yang rigs lngar 'dus shing gdul bya'i gtso' bo lngar 'dul ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:17380: lnga las sku gcig tu byas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:17382: zhal theg pa chen po'i lam du bcug /
NK069(tu)001:17383: lto ba chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang gcig tu sgrib pa sbyang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:17384: de las lngar snang bar byed pa 'di ni /
NK069(tu)001:17385: dbang mo mang bas so sor chags pas tshim par byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17387: sku mang pos 'dul ba'i dus su ni sku mang por bstan la /
NK069(tu)001:17388: sku lngas 'dul ba'i dus su ni /
NK069(tu)001:17390: sku gcig gis 'dul ba'i dus na ni sku gcig tu yang bstan te /
NK069(tu)001:17391: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i zhal phyag gis 'dul bar dgongs pa'i dus su ni dbu dgu brgya /
NK069(tu)001:17392: phyag stong brgyad brgya yang ston no //
NK069(tu)001:17394: des ni rim pa mang nyung ngam /
NK069(tu)001:17395: bye brag mi 'dra ba'i gags gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:17396: ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas /
NK069(tu)001:17397: zhes ston pas ting nge 'dzin la ma zhugs par gsung mi spyod par ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:17398: phyi rabs kyis 'di ltar rtogs par dgongs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17400: sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las 'di phyung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:17401: zhes spyir snang ba ni sku /
NK069(tu)001:17403: rigs gcig gsal ba ni thugs yin pa la /
NK069(tu)001:17404: 'dir sku gsung thugs tha dad du dbyer myed par stong pa nyid du gcig pas na rdo rje /
NK069(tu)001:17405: thugs rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin las so //
NK069(tu)001:17407: h'u am badz+ra pra be sha a la la ho /
NK069(tu)001:17410: sku gsung thugs gsum gyi rang bzhin te /
NK069(tu)001:17411: dngos ye shes gsang ba'i rdo rje'o //
NK069(tu)001:17412: brda des ni yab kyi mkha' thabs kyi mnga' bdag chen por mtshon pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17413: pra be sha ni yum gyi bdag pad ma'i 'dab ma lta bu sgoo 'byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17414: ni yab yum 'brel ba'i byang sems yid bzhin gyi nor bu lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:17416: dga' ba bzhis lus thams cad la bde' /
NK069(tu)001:17419: rtog las 'das pa'i nyams gsal zhing bstan pa thob par byed pas dgyes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17420: 'byung po'i rgyal mo rnams shin tu yang chags pa'i yid g.yos nas /
NK069(tu)001:17421: zhes gzhi' rang la rgyu mthun pa'i 'bras bu yod pas chags pa'i yid g.yos so //
NK069(tu)001:17422: rkyen gsang sngags kyis mthu' yod pas chags pa'i yid g.yos so //
NK069(tu)001:17423: yon tan bstan pa'i byin brlabs zhugs pas chags pa'i yid g.yos so //
NK069(tu)001:17424: ngo bo bde ba'i ye shes sdang bas chags pa'i yid g.yos so //
NK069(tu)001:17425: de bas na shin tu chags pa'i yid g.yos nas zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:17426: pad ma'i dkyil 'khor sdud cing rgyas par gyur nas /
NK069(tu)001:17427: zhes dpal he ru ka'i byin rlabs spyir khyab pas
NK069(tu)001:17428: dbang mo rnams ba ga pad ma'i dkyil 'khor bsdud
NK069(tu)001:17429: / des rang gi bde' ba rang babs su gyur pas rgyas te /
NK069(tu)001:17430: lus kyi sna rtse bya rog stong pa las /
NK069(tu)001:17433: nyi ma ltar gsal bar gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:17434: dper na khab len la lcags 'du ba'i tshul du /
NK069(tu)001:17436: rdo khab len rengs pa'i dus na lcags rang dbang myed par 'gul zhing ldeg /
NK069(tu)001:17438: dpal gyi sku mthor ba'i dus na dbang mo rnams
NK069(tu)001:17439: lus sems rang dbang med par dpal gyi sku la
NK069(tu)001:17441: rigs las mi btags pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:17442: rang gi mtshan nyid las btags pa las /
NK069(tu)001:17443: rigs las btags pa las ni /
NK069(tu)001:17444: khyo chen po la chung ma chen mo zer ba ltar /
NK069(tu)001:17445: ming rang rang gi khyo las drangs shing btags pa la bya /
NK069(tu)001:17446: rang gi mtshan nyid las btags pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:17447: rang gi las ci byas pa de las blangs nas mtshan btags pa la bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:17448: de ltar dbang mo rnams la spyir sbyar bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:17449: badz+ra he ru ka la gtso mo brgyad 'khril bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:17450: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal khrag 'thung chen po rdo rje'i sku la /
NK069(tu)001:17451: zhes 'dir badz+ra he ru kas gtso' byes pas na /
NK069(tu)001:17452: rdo rje khro bo'i dkyil 'khor zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:17453: badz+ra he ru ka dbu' gsum /
NK069(tu)001:17454: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing sku /
NK069(tu)001:17455: rdo rje kha tang rnge'u chung g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:17456: dung dmar rgyu zhags khyung khra g.yon /
NK069(tu)001:17460: srin mo chen mo mi'i srin mo dang /
NK069(tu)001:17461: zhes srin mo ni srin mo la bu lnga brgya skyes pa las /
NK069(tu)001:17462: na ma re la bu zos pas srin mo /
NK069(tu)001:17464: snod kyi 'jig rten gos su gon /
NK069(tu)001:17465: bcud kyi 'jig rten zas su za /
NK069(tu)001:17466: nyi zla gza' skar lan char byed pas na mi srin mo'o //
NK069(tu)001:17467: 'dir dbang mo la nang du khro mor sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:17468: srin mo smug nag rdo rje thod rlon 'chang /
NK069(tu)001:17470: gsang ba mkha' 'gro mar sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:17471: mi srin dmar ser g.yag mgo can /
NK069(tu)001:17472: ban d+ha zhing za lcags kyu g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:17473: tri shul su dri sgyu ma 'dren pa g.yon na'o //
NK069(tu)001:17477: rdo rje dmar mo tsan dan 'thung zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:17479: zhing chen dmar mo dom gyi mgo' can /
NK069(tu)001:17480: g.yas zhing chen dril 'khrol lcags kyu g.yon dung dmar rgyu zhags dbyug pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17481: lha kring shi ka'i chung ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:17482: snod yangs pa ban d+ha'i nang du /
NK069(tu)001:17485: lha dmar po kri shi ka'i chung ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:17489: sems can thams cad nor gyis dga' bar byed pas dga' ba mo dang zhes /
NK069(tu)001:17491: dga' ba dmar mo rdo rje dka' dar 'phyag /
NK069(tu)001:17494: dga' byed dmar nag bya rgod mgo' can /
NK069(tu)001:17495: g.yas lcags kyu dung dmar zhing dbyug /
NK069(tu)001:17496: g.yon bgegs dang kha tong rag ta'o //
NK069(tu)001:17499: zhes dus lnga brgya'i tha ma la sems can ces kyang mi thul te /
NK069(tu)001:17500: gsod pa nyi tshes thul bas /
NK069(tu)001:17501: sdug bsngal thams cad chos kyi dbyings su sgrol zhing gsod pas na gsod byed mo dang /
NK069(tu)001:17503: gsod byed dmar mo rdo rje ral gri so /
NK069(tu)001:17505: gsod byed dmar nag phag gi mgo' can /
NK069(tu)001:17506: g.yas na tir chen rdo rje ral gri /
NK069(tu)001:17507: g.yon glo snying rnge'u chung zhing za ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:17511: lha 'char ka chen po'i chung ma yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:17512: nag mo chen mo dang zhes /
NK069(tu)001:17515: rdo rje nag mo rdo rje lcags kyu 'dzin /
NK069(tu)001:17518: nag mo sngo nag khu byug mgo' can no //
NK069(tu)001:17519: phyag dang po gnyis zhing chung za zhing stob pa /
NK069(tu)001:17520: bar ma gnyis lcags kyu kha tang /
NK069(tu)001:17521: tha ma gnyis dung dmar ral gri snams pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17524: rang gi mtshan nyid las btags te /
NK069(tu)001:17525: mdog dmar ser chen mo dang /
NK069(tu)001:17527: bdud ra thod can gyi bu mo ra mgo' can zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:17529: rdo rje ser nag rdo rje ra mgo' zhags /
NK069(tu)001:17532: ra ni sngon mo ra'i mgo' can /
NK069(tu)001:17533: g.yas na zhing chen dung dmar kha tang /
NK069(tu)001:17534: g.yon rgyu zhags dril chen zhags pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17535: srin po d+ha sha khro bo'i chung ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:17539: srin po bum sna'i chung ma yin la /
NK069(tu)001:17540: srin po de sngo nag tu yod pas /
NK069(tu)001:17541: chung ma yang sngo nag chen mo dang /
NK069(tu)001:17544: rdo rje dmar nag rdo rje la lcags sgrog sdom /
NK069(tu)001:17546: bum sna dmar mo spre'u mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17547: dang po gnyis ban d+ha khrag chen stob /
NK069(tu)001:17548: bar ma gnyis zhing chen lcags sgrog 'dzin /
NK069(tu)001:17549: tha ma gnyis kha tang zang gri'o //
NK069(tu)001:17550: ser nag chen mo rnams 'khril lo //
NK069(tu)001:17551: zhes rang gi mtshan nyid las te /
NK069(tu)001:17552: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams chos kyi dbyings na bzhugs nas /
NK069(tu)001:17553: sku gsum che ba'i yon tan gyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad par shes pas /
NK069(tu)001:17554: lha mo 'dis dril bu stong pa'i sgras /
NK069(tu)001:17555: sku drin che ba'i yon rnams 'gro ba'i rgyud la 'bebs par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:17556: de bas na bsus 'dzin ser nag go //
NK069(tu)001:17557: ser ba ni che ba'i yon tan no //
NK069(tu)001:17558: nag pa ni ljang nag go //
NK069(tu)001:17559: mdog dang las las ming tags so //
NK069(tu)001:17561: rdo rje ljang nag rdo rje dril 'khrol dgyes so //
NK069(tu)001:17563: gsus 'dzin ser nag spyang khu'i mgo' can /
NK069(tu)001:17564: g.yas zhing chen dril bu dung dmar /
NK069(tu)001:17565: g.yon snying kha tang rnge'u chung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:17566: phyag drug pa gsang ba khro mor bshad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:17567: cha 'thun pa'i rgyud lha mo sgyu 'phrul dra ba nas bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:17569: dpal chen po'i sku gcig tu 'khril bar stum bam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:17572: dper na mi gcig la chung ma brgyad yod pa lta bu ste /
NK069(tu)001:17573: dus gcig la thams cad dang sbyor bar myi bzhed do //
NK069(tu)001:17574: gnyis pa ye shes snang tshul ni /
NK069(tu)001:17575: dper na bzhin gcig mdun du me long brgyad dam /
NK069(tu)001:17577: de re re'i nang na bzhin gyi gzugs brnyan re re 'char ba dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:17578: dpal chen po'i sku yang gcig las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:17583: yang na gcig dang bzhugs na sku gcig tu snang la /
NK069(tu)001:17584: brgyad dang bzhugs na sku brgyad du yang snang /
NK069(tu)001:17585: lnga dang bzhugs na sku lngar yang snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:17586: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po'i sku la /
NK069(tu)001:17587: b+hu ta he ru ka zhal gsum g.yas mthing g.yon dkar dbus smug go //
NK069(tu)001:17588: phyag drug g.yas na dang po ti ra'i dbyug pa /
NK069(tu)001:17593: tha ma ti ri ba su ta'o //
NK069(tu)001:17594: b+hud d+ha he ru ka la shar gyi lngas 'khril te /
NK069(tu)001:17596: zhes tshangs ris kyi lha'i lta ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:17597: 'dod khams kyi lha 'dod pa'i yon tan ni /
NK069(tu)001:17598: spyod pa ni sdug bsngal du lta'o //
NK069(tu)001:17599: khong rang gi lus kyi bsam gtan gyi dga' ste spyod bzhi la /
NK069(tu)001:17601: zhi ba mya ngan las 'das par lta /
NK069(tu)001:17602: de ltar ltas pas 'og ma'i sdug bsngal las tshangs par rtogs so //
NK069(tu)001:17604: de'i chung ma tshangs ma dbu' bzhi'o //
NK069(tu)001:17606: tshangs ma dmar ser rdo rje pad ma snams /
NK069(tu)001:17609: tshangs ma dmar ser sbrul gyi mgo' can /
NK069(tu)001:17610: g.yas ban d+ha zhing za lcags kyu /
NK069(tu)001:17611: g.yon rtse lnga kha tam zhags so //
NK069(tu)001:17613: zhes dug gsum gyis sems 'khrugs pas /
