NK069(tu)001:17615: lag na tri shul rtse gsum can no //
NK069(tu)001:17616: lha ma h+aa de ba'i chung ma /
NK069(tu)001:17618: lha chen dkar ljang rdo rje tri shul la'o //
NK069(tu)001:17620: khro mo ser nag gzig gi mgo' can /
NK069(tu)001:17621: g.yas dril bu dbyug to tir /
NK069(tu)001:17622: g.yon b+han d+ha lcags kyu spu gri'o //
NK069(tu)001:17625: mdun sa chen po bzhi la /
NK069(tu)001:17626: tshal chen po lnga la dbang mdzad pa de'i chung ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:17628: rgya byin dkar mo rdo rje i dra gdengs /
NK069(tu)001:17630: zhing chen dmar mo dom gyi mgo can /
NK069(tu)001:17631: g.yas zhing chen dril 'khrol lcags kyu /
NK069(tu)001:17632: g.yon rgyu zhags dung dmar dbyug pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17635: thams cad du 'jug cing sha khrag la sred pa de'i chung ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:17637: stong 'dod sngon mo rdo rje 'khor lo 'chang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:17639: khyab 'jug dkar dmar sre mo'i mgo can /
NK069(tu)001:17640: g.yas rdo rje ti ra zhags pa /
NK069(tu)001:17641: g.yon ban d+ha kha tang rnge'u chung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:17643: zhes ma h+aa de ba la bu mang po yod pa kun rgan che nas /
NK069(tu)001:17644: gzhon pa bzhir byin gyis rlabs te /
NK069(tu)001:17648: gu lang dang bzhi yod do //
NK069(tu)001:17649: de las 'di gzhon nu smin drug zhes bya ba byad bzhin la smin ma drug yod pa /
NK069(tu)001:17650: de'i chung ma yin pas gzhon pa zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:17652: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'phen no //
NK069(tu)001:17654: gzhon nu ser nag pha wang mgo /
NK069(tu)001:17655: g.yas zhing chen ban d+ha kha tang /
NK069(tu)001:17657: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po rin po che'i sku la /
NK069(tu)001:17658: rad na he ru ka ni /
NK069(tu)001:17659: dbu' gsum g.yas mthing g.yon dkar dbus ser /
NK069(tu)001:17660: phyag drug la g.yas dang po byi byug /
NK069(tu)001:17663: g.yon dang po stong gi 'jig rten /
NK069(tu)001:17670: nyi ma'i chung ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:17671: nyi ma'i rna cha bdud rtsi zhags pas /
NK069(tu)001:17672: sems can thams cad gso' bar mdzad pas so //
NK069(tu)001:17674: bdud rtsi dmar mo rdo rje pad ma 'dzin no //
NK069(tu)001:17677: bdud rtsi sngo nag chu srin mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17678: phyag dang po ban d+ha khrag chen stob /
NK069(tu)001:17680: tha ma rin chen bum pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17682: zhes zla ba tshes pa ltar yon tan thams cad
NK069(tu)001:17683: shas kyis sems can zhi ba'i las byed pas so
NK069(tu)001:17684: // de yang tsha zhing gdung ba zhi'o //
NK069(tu)001:17686: zla ba dkar mo rdo rje pun d+ha ri /
NK069(tu)001:17688: zhi ba sngo skya sdig pa'i mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17689: g.yas glo ba dril 'khril rtse lnga /
NK069(tu)001:17690: g.yon snying 'dren dung dmar rin chen bum /
NK069(tu)001:17692: zhes mtshan nyid las tags te /
NK069(tu)001:17693: phyag na be con thogs pa mo dang /
NK069(tu)001:17695: be con ljang nag rdo rje dbyug to phyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:17697: be con nag mo khra'i mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17698: g.yas tir chen dung dmar kha tam /
NK069(tu)001:17699: g.yon glo snying ral gri rgyu zhags so //
NK069(tu)001:17701: zhes ming mtshan nyid las btags te /
NK069(tu)001:17702: zhing za zhing ba su 'dren pas /
NK069(tu)001:17704: za byed ljang nag rdo rje ba su 'dren no //
NK069(tu)001:17706: za byed mthing nag stag gi mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17707: g.yas ti ra dung dmar dril bu /
NK069(tu)001:17708: g.yon snying 'dren kha tang ral gri'o //
NK069(tu)001:17712: srin mo dmar mo rdo rje thod khrag 'thung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:17714: khro mo ser nag wa'i mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17715: g.yas ban d+ha rgyu 'dren ti ra /
NK069(tu)001:17716: g.yon khra dang rnge'u chung kha tang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:17717: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po pad+ma chen po'i sku la /
NK069(tu)001:17718: zhes pad ma he ru ka g.yas dkar g.yon ljang dbus dmar /
NK069(tu)001:17721: tha ma rdo rje dgra s+t+wa /
NK069(tu)001:17722: g.yon dang po stong gi 'jig rten /
NK069(tu)001:17725: pad ma he ru ka la lho'i lnga 'khril ba bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:17727: stobs bzang bcom ldan 'das kyi rtags len pa yin pa las /
NK069(tu)001:17728: bcom ldan 'das kyis mya ngan las 'da' kar /
NK069(tu)001:17729: chung ma rgun chang 'dur du bcug pas blud pas ra ro //
NK069(tu)001:17730: der ra ro ba sangs nas khos chos thams cad kyang ra ro ba dang 'dra bar mkhyen pas /
NK069(tu)001:17731: de'i chung ma yang dus rtag tu khrag gis ra ro zhing myos pa yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:17733: stobs chen dkar mo rdo rje bshol mda' 'dzin no //
NK069(tu)001:17735: khrag 'thung dmar mo rta'i mgo can no //
NK069(tu)001:17736: g.yas ban d+ha dril bu rtse lnga /
NK069(tu)001:17737: g.yon dbyug pa kha tang zhing chen no //
NK069(tu)001:17739: 'di na ma h+aa de wa'i chung ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:17740: ma h+aa de ba dang yab yum gnyis dmyig mngas byed pa la /
NK069(tu)001:17741: khos ma la rten pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:17742: pha ma gnyis ka'i bur 'dra na /
NK069(tu)001:17743: mnyam por rten na ces nyes byas bras /
NK069(tu)001:17744: bu 'khros nas sha rnags nas ma'i bka' drin 'di las ma 'chis zer nas ma la kyur /
NK069(tu)001:17745: rus pa gcig pus chung ma spyod pas so //
NK069(tu)001:17746: de'i chung ma yin pas gcig pur spyod ma dang zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:17748: rdo rje ser mo spu gris gcod do //
NK069(tu)001:17750: cig pu dkar dmar byi ba'i mgo /
NK069(tu)001:17751: g.yas b+han d+ha rdo rje tri shul /
NK069(tu)001:17752: g.yon dril bu dbyug pa zhing chung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:17754: lha me tog gi 'da' can gyis /
NK069(tu)001:17755: lha mo gang yin pa la mda' 'phangs pas /
NK069(tu)001:17756: phog pa dang kho'i dbang du 'adu'o //
NK069(tu)001:17757: de'i chung mas kyang mo rang gang yid du 'ong ba de'i yid 'phrog pas na /
NK069(tu)001:17759: 'dod pa dmar mo rdo rje mda' gzhu' 'gengs so //
NK069(tu)001:17761: yid 'phrog dmar nag spyang khu'i mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17762: phyag dang po gnyis tir chung za zhing stobs /
NK069(tu)001:17763: bar ma gnyis kha tang lcags kyu /
NK069(tu)001:17764: tha ma gnyis dung dmar ral gri'o //
NK069(tu)001:17766: bden bral nor la dbang bas /
NK069(tu)001:17767: de'i chung ma yang nor zad mi shes pa'i gter
NK069(tu)001:17768: gyi bum pa snams nas nor lha las grub pa
NK069(tu)001:17769: mo dang / nang khro mo ni /
NK069(tu)001:17770: nor srung dkar mo bum pa 'dzin no //
NK069(tu)001:17772: grub pa dkar dmar pud shud mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17773: g.yas tir chen pad+ma kha tang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:17774: g.yon glo snying dung dmar zhags pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17776: sems can thams cad kyi khong pa na /
NK069(tu)001:17777: u da na bya ta ka zhes bya ba /
NK069(tu)001:17779: rlung des srog gi dbang po la reg pas ni srog 'tshol bar byed /
NK069(tu)001:17780: yid kyis rnam par shes pa la reg pas ni /
NK069(tu)001:17782: bsgo' lnga'i rnam shes la reg pas ni yul la 'dzin par byed /
NK069(tu)001:17783: rung de la dbang byeed pas na rlung mo rnams 'khril lo zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:17785: rlung lha sngon mo rdo rje ba dan 'phyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:17787: rlung mo dmar ser sha pho'i mgo' g.yas ban d+ha rnge'u chung kha tam /
NK069(tu)001:17788: g.yon gri 'debs ro za khrag 'thung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:17789: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung chen po kun tu las kyi sku la /
NK069(tu)001:17790: zhes kar ma he ru ka g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ljang /
NK069(tu)001:17791: phyag drug g.yas dang po ral gri /
NK069(tu)001:17794: g.yon dang po stong gi 'jig rten /
NK069(tu)001:17797: kar ma he ru ka la byang gi lnga 'khril ba bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:17799: bsam gtan dang po tshad kyang mes 'jigs par byed /
NK069(tu)001:17800: lus la khong na gzi mdangs mes gsal bar byed /
NK069(tu)001:17801: de la dbang pa'i me lha'i chung ma med dpung nang na bzhugs pa'i me mo dang /
NK069(tu)001:17803: me mo dmar mo bsal shing 'chang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:17805: me mo ljang nag skyin po'i mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17806: g.yas ban d+ha kha tang rnge'u chung /
NK069(tu)001:17807: g.yon ro za gri 'debs khrag 'thung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:17809: sa bdag phag mo'i chung ma yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:17810: dbu' phag 'go' can gyi phag mo dang /
NK069(tu)001:17812: phag mo nag mo rdo rje mchel zhags ston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17814: phag mo ljang ser phag gi mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17815: g.yas ban d+ha rtse lnga zhing za /
NK069(tu)001:17816: g.yon khra chen kha tang ral gri'o //
NK069(tu)001:17818: zhes gshin rje'i chung ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:17819: ma h+aa de wa'i chung ma yin pa la a
NK069(tu)001:17820: ma gcig pu la bltas pas rmo khros te rgan
NK069(tu)001:17821: mor sprul pas rgan byed mo dang /
NK069(tu)001:17823: rgan byed dmar mo rdo rje zhing chung za'o //
NK069(tu)001:17825: rgan byed dmar skya skag pa'i mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17826: g.yas bdud rtsi dbyug pa dril bu /
NK069(tu)001:17827: g.yon dung dmar kha tam rgyu ma 'dren no //
NK069(tu)001:17829: zhes 'di ma h+aa de wa'i spar mo yin te /
NK069(tu)001:17830: ma spor mo ltas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:17831: glang po che'i klad pa'i nang na sman g+hi ha
NK069(tu)001:17832: yod pa brus nas 'thungs pa de'i rkyen gyis smod
NK069(tu)001:17833: pa dor bas / mo rang gi snang yang glang po che'i sna lta bur gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17834: yang na sna chen tshogs kyi bdag mo'i yum yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:17836: sna chen dkar mo rdo rje dung khrag 'thung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:17838: sna chen ljang nag rnga mo'i mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17839: g.yas bdud rtsi kha tang ral gri /
NK069(tu)001:17844: zhes zas thams cad yang chu la byed /
NK069(tu)001:17845: chu la gnas pa'i klu'i nor bu rin po che 'phrog /
NK069(tu)001:17850: chu lha sngon mo rdo rje sbrul zhags 'dzin no //
NK069(tu)001:17852: chu lha sngo skya bya rog mgo' /
NK069(tu)001:17853: zhing chen dung dmar dril bu g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:17854: glo snying kha tang ral gri g.yon no //
NK069(tu)001:17855: de rnams la dkyil 'khor skyong ba'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:17857: pho nya mdzad pa'i dus na mgo' snyan de /
NK069(tu)001:17859: lhag ma stud pa'i dus na mkha' la 'gro ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:17860: mdor na don gyi ngo bo gcig las sprul pa
NK069(tu)001:17861: yin pa yin pas dbyer myed pa'i bdag nyid do
NK069(tu)001:17863: zhes rigs lnga'i dkyil 'khor gyi khro bo de dag gis h'u zhes brjod pas /
NK069(tu)001:17864: gnyis su myed pa'i byang chub sems bde' ba de /
NK069(tu)001:17865: thugs ye shes kyi rang bzhin yin pas h'u /
NK069(tu)001:17866: de gsung ngam thugs la brjod pas /
NK069(tu)001:17867: pad ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs bstus nas /
NK069(tu)001:17868: shin tu yang bcum par gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:17869: zhes dbang phyug ma rnams kyi pad ma'i dkyil 'khor du thim pa las /
NK069(tu)001:17870: h'u ye shes kyi bde' ba dang ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:17871: so sor yum gyi ba ga /
NK069(tu)001:17872: yab kyi rdo rje la gras pas shin tu bcum gyis sdom par gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:17873: de yang dbang mo rnams kyi ba gar /
NK069(tu)001:17874: h'u re re bzhag pa de ni /
NK069(tu)001:17875: dngos 'dod 'byung bas rin po che dang 'dra /
NK069(tu)001:17876: rgyu gyur pas sa bon dang 'dra /
NK069(tu)001:17877: cir yang snang bas sprul pa'am sgyu ma 'dra'o //
NK069(tu)001:17878: de nas dgyes te ha ha zhes brjod pas /
NK069(tu)001:17879: zhes de nas byang chub sems snol mar stims pas dgyes te /
NK069(tu)001:17880: so so'i mkha' nas lhag pa'i byang chub sems 'phros pa las /
NK069(tu)001:17881: dgyes pa chen po'i sgra ha zhes pa /
NK069(tu)001:17884: byang chub sems kyi sprin las /
NK069(tu)001:17885: zhes so so'i mkha' nas byang chub sems kyi 'phro
NK069(tu)001:17886: 'du mang po sprin dang 'dra bar 'dul nas ha
NK069(tu)001:17890: zhes ko'u ri ma 'di ni thugs kyi lha mo yin te /
NK069(tu)001:17891: dpal he ru ka'i thugs rnam par dag pa mkhyen
NK069(tu)001:17892: pa'i ye shes las mtshan ma'i skyon gyis ma gos
NK069(tu)001:17893: pa'i rtags su bstan pas dkar mo /
NK069(tu)001:17894: mdog mthing ka thugs kyi rang bzhin mi 'gyur ba yin /
NK069(tu)001:17895: mi 'gyur ba nyid mtshan skyon gyis mi mnga' bas dkar mo'o //
NK069(tu)001:17899: thugs sna tshogs kyi ye shes rtogs par byed pas tshogs so //
NK069(tu)001:17901: zhes lha mo 'di ni yon tan gyi lha mo ste /
NK069(tu)001:17902: dpal he ru kas 'byed pa myed pa'i shes rab kyis /
NK069(tu)001:17903: gti mug gi mun nag sel ba'i rtags su bstan /
NK069(tu)001:17904: 'byed pa myed pa'i shes rab kyis yang dag pa'i don rtogs /
NK069(tu)001:17905: de ltar rtogs pa'i ngang nas ye shes kyis sbos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17906: pu ka si dmar ser chen mo rgyu ma'i zhags pa thogs nas /
NK069(tu)001:17907: sems can thams cad bla na myed pa yang dag pa'i gnas su 'dren pas /
NK069(tu)001:17908: sems can thams cad kyi tshogs 'dren ma zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:17910: zhes lha mo 'di ni gsung gi lha mo yin te /
NK069(tu)001:17911: he ru kas gsung rabs rgya mtsho' 'gro ba la sgrogs pa'i rtags su 'di bstan te /
NK069(tu)001:17912: pra mo has gsung rab rgya mtsho' 'brug ltar sgrags pas /
NK069(tu)001:17913: bdud dang dregs byed zil gyis mnan nas /
NK069(tu)001:17914: nyon mongs pa mgo' rmongs par byed pas rmongs mo //
NK069(tu)001:17915: 'gro ba dbang du byed pas sku dmar mo /
NK069(tu)001:17916: 'khor ba las rgyal zhing thugs rjes 'dzin pas chu srin rgyal mtshan thogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17917: thams cad las rgyal bas na tshogs so //
NK069(tu)001:17919: zhes 'di ni he ru ka'i yon tan dang 'phrin las gnyis ka'i lha mo yin te /
NK069(tu)001:17920: he ru ka'i che ba'i yon tan gyi 'phrin las kyis /
NK069(tu)001:17921: 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:17922: sems can gyi nyon mongs pa thams cad thal bar klog pas thal byed ma /
NK069(tu)001:17923: g.yas rdo rje sa dgu'i shi ba glong /
NK069(tu)001:17924: g.yon rnge'u chung gis bla byed gnas su sdud par byed pa'i tshogs so //
NK069(tu)001:17927: zhes lha mo 'di ni sku'i lha mo yin te /
NK069(tu)001:17928: dpal he ru kas 'byed pa myed pa'i shes rab kyis /
NK069(tu)001:17929: gti' mug gi mun nag sel ba'i rtags su bstan /
NK069(tu)001:17930: 'byed pa myed pa'i shes rab kyis yang dag pa'i don rtogs /
NK069(tu)001:17931: de ltar rtogs pa'i ngang las ye shes kyis sbos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17932: pu ka si dmar ser chen mo rgyu ma'i zhags pa thogs nas /
NK069(tu)001:17933: sems can thams cad bla na myed pa'i gnas su 'dren pas /
NK069(tu)001:17934: sems can thams cad kyi tshogs 'dren ma zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:17936: zhes lha mo 'di ni thugs rje'i lha mo ste /
NK069(tu)001:17937: dpal he ru ka'i thugs rje zhe sdang chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:17938: sems can bla na myed pa'i gnas su 'dren par mdzad pas bstan te /
NK069(tu)001:17940: dper na mi stum po la /
NK069(tu)001:17941: mi thub yang brdeg pa ltar /
NK069(tu)001:17943: 'khor ba na gnas pa'i sems can sgrol ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:17944: de'i rtags su sku mdog ser skya mgo' lus 'brel lo //
NK069(tu)001:17945: sme sha can gyi tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:17946: zhes lha mo 'di ni mi 'byed pa'i lha mo ste /
NK069(tu)001:17947: dpal he ru kas 'dod pa chos nyid dang /
NK069(tu)001:17948: chags pa ye shes chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:17949: sems can log pa'i 'dod chags las sgrol ba'i rtags su bstan te /
NK069(tu)001:17950: dper na mi sme sha can ni /
NK069(tu)001:17951: zas bzang ngan mi 'byed par kun za ba ltar /
NK069(tu)001:17952: lha mo 'dis sems can la 'dod chags bzang ngan du mi 'byed par /
NK069(tu)001:17953: kun bla na myed pa'i gnas su 'dren pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17954: ka ma ri ljang khu dung khrag krung cing /
NK069(tu)001:17955: sems can thams cad kyi 'phrin las byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:17957: zhes he ru ka dang ma mo bdun gyi sku dang ye shes thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:17958: ma mo 'dis sdud pas na ma tshogs ma zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:17959: de yan chad kyi he ru ka dang /
NK069(tu)001:17960: ma mo bdun gyi sku dang /
NK069(tu)001:17961: ye shes che ba'i gnas thams cad 'di las 'byung bas ma tshogs ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:17962: sme sha ni mthing nag mi 'gyur ba /
NK069(tu)001:17963: gzung 'dzin can gyi snying za bas /
NK069(tu)001:17964: sems can gyi gzung 'dzin thams cad dag par byed pa'i tshogs so //
NK069(tu)001:17965: rang rang gi lag cha dang ngo mtshar dang bcas nas ston to //
NK069(tu)001:17967: ston nas kyang 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi shar phyogs nas /
NK069(tu)001:17969: rang rang gi lag cha dang bcas 'khod do //
NK069(tu)001:17970: zhes rgyud bshad rgyud bla ma nas /
NK069(tu)001:17971: shar gyi phyogs su bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:17972: sa bdag sgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:17973: kun gzhi'i gnas 'gyur phra men ma //
NK069(tu)001:17974: rnal 'byor sngo nag ko'u ra ste //
NK069(tu)001:17975: ral pa kham nag gyen du 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:17976: mche gtsigs rkan brdab sa gzhi g.yo //
NK069(tu)001:17977: bshugs pas glu dbyangs ha har bzhad //
NK069(tu)001:17978: ti ra'i g.yug pa g.yas pa na //
NK069(tu)001:17979: ban d+ha rag ta g.yon pa 'dzin //
NK069(tu)001:17980: skye shi ma la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:17981: lho'i phyogs su bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:17982: gsong byed bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:17983: rnam shes gnas 'gyur phra men ma //
NK069(tu)001:17984: rnal 'byor ser nag gatso'u ri ste //
NK069(tu)001:17985: ral pa kham nag gyen du 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:17986: mche gtsigs rkan brdab sa gzhi g.yo //
NK069(tu)001:17987: bshugs pas glu dbyangs ha har bzhad //
NK069(tu)001:17988: thabs kyi mnga' 'dren g.yas pa na //
NK069(tu)001:17989: shes rab mda' gzhu mdung g.yon na //
NK069(tu)001:17990: ya ma ye la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:17991: nub kyi phyogs su bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:17992: nyi ma bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:17993: nyon mongs gnas 'gyur phra men ma //
NK069(tu)001:17994: rnal 'byor dmar nag pra mo ha //
NK069(tu)001:17995: ral pa kham nag gyen du 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:17996: mche gtsigs rkan brdab sa gzhi g.yo //
NK069(tu)001:17997: bshugs pas glu dbyangs ha ha bzhad //
NK069(tu)001:17998: chu srin rgyal mtshan g.yas pa na //
NK069(tu)001:17999: ban d+ha rag ta g.yon pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18000: su rgya ye la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:18001: byang gi phyogs su bsrung bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18002: zla ba bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18003: reg bya gnas 'gyur phra myen ma //
NK069(tu)001:18004: rnal 'byor mthing nag pe ta li //
NK069(tu)001:18005: ral pa kham nag gyen du 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:18006: mtshe gtsigs rkan brdab sa gzhi' g.yo' //
NK069(tu)001:18007: bshugs pas glu dbyangs ha ha bzhad //
NK069(tu)001:18008: rdo rje rtse lnga g.yas pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18009: gter chung mgo' gcad g.yon pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18010: tsan tra ye la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:18011: shar lho mtshams su bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18012: me lha bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18013: lta byed gnas 'gyur phra myen ma //
NK069(tu)001:18014: rnal 'byor dmar nag pu ka si //
NK069(tu)001:18015: skra 'bar mche' gtsigs rkan brdab shing //
NK069(tu)001:18016: dur khrod g.yang gzhi'i klag pa gyon //
NK069(tu)001:18017: bshugs pas glu dbyangs ha ha bzhad //
NK069(tu)001:18018: ti ra chen po g.yon pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18019: tshems par rgyu 'dren g.yas pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18020: ag ne ye ma brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:18021: lho nub mtshams su bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18022: bden bral bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18023: nyan byed gnas 'gyur phra myen ma //
NK069(tu)001:18024: rnal 'byor mthing nag sma sha ni //
NK069(tu)001:18025: skra 'bar mche' gtsigs rkang brdab shing //
NK069(tu)001:18026: srog bdag chen mo'i g.yang gzhi' gyon //
NK069(tu)001:18027: bshugs pas glu dbyangs ha ha bzhad //
NK069(tu)001:18028: ti ra chu rgyun g.yon pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18029: bi ta phyung ba g.yas pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18030: ni ri ti la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:18031: nub byang mtshams su bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18032: glung lha bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18033: snom byed gnas 'gyur phra myen ma //
NK069(tu)001:18034: rnal 'byor ser nag tsan d+ha li //
NK069(tu)001:18035: skra 'bar mche' gtsigs rkan brdab shing //
NK069(tu)001:18036: ti ra chen po shun pa gyon //
NK069(tu)001:18037: bshugs pas glu dbyangs ha ha bzhad //
NK069(tu)001:18038: ti ra chu rgyun g.yon pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18039: ban d+ha bcas pa g.yas pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18040: ba ya be la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:18041: byang shar mtshams su bsam bya bar //
NK069(tu)001:18042: dbang ldan bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18043: myos byed gnas 'gyur phra myen ma //
NK069(tu)001:18044: rnal 'byor ljang nag kas ma hri //
NK069(tu)001:18045: skra 'bar mche' gtsigs rkan brdab shing //
NK069(tu)001:18046: ti ra chen po'i shun pa gnong //
NK069(tu)001:18047: bshugs pas glu dbyangs ha ha bzhad //
NK069(tu)001:18048: ban d+ha rag ta g.yon pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18049: rtse gsum 'khrug pa g.yas pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18050: pa ta ye ma brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:18051: zhes gsungs pas zhal phyag dang sku mdog dang na
NK069(tu)001:18052: bza' rgyan chas la sogs pa kun legs pa gsal
NK069(tu)001:18054: de nas shin tu dgyes nas he zhes brjod pas /
NK069(tu)001:18055: zhes byang chub sems dgyes pa'i sprin phyir 'phros /
NK069(tu)001:18056: don byas nas slar 'dus pa las he he zhes pa'i skur gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:18057: seng gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:18059: dper seng ge gangs kyi steng nas skad phyung bas /
NK069(tu)001:18060: nags kha bzhin gnas pa'i gcan zan phal pa thams cad rgyal nas /
NK069(tu)001:18061: rtsal che bas 'brug gi sgra grags pa dang sprin gseb tu mchong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:18063: dpal he ru kas kyang bdud dang dregs pa thams cad bad rgyal bar mdzad /
NK069(tu)001:18064: nyon mongs pa thams cad rtsal gyis mnon /
NK069(tu)001:18065: de'i rtags su seng ge'i 'go can ser mo /
NK069(tu)001:18066: phyag snol nas khro tshul gyis kun la lta ba'i ya bdud kyi tshogs thams cad 'dul lo //
NK069(tu)001:18067: phyag rdor rtse gsum gyen du bsnol ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:18068: de ni sku gsum gyis chos nyid mtshon pa'o /
NK069(tu)001:18070: wa gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:18071: zhes dper na wa ni 'dzem bag che bas grong bar du mi 'grim par dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:18072: he ru kas 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i dus su /
NK069(tu)001:18073: chos kyi dbyings la gnas nas /
NK069(tu)001:18075: de'i rtags su tri la ma nag mo /
NK069(tu)001:18076: zhing ni khog pa kha phye nas 'dag par bstan to //
NK069(tu)001:18077: zhing 'dag pa med pa'i chos nyid /
NK069(tu)001:18078: khrag 'dag pa myed pa'i chos nyid /
NK069(tu)001:18080: des sems can sna tshogs pa'i don byed pa'o /
NK069(tu)001:18082: stag gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:18084: dper na stag ni dpa' tul che ste /
NK069(tu)001:18088: de bzhin du he ru ka ni /
NK069(tu)001:18089: ye shes kyis dba' la brtson /
NK069(tu)001:18091: 'phrin las kyis za bar byed pas /
NK069(tu)001:18092: stag gdong ser mo phyag rgya khu tshur 'dzug mo
NK069(tu)001:18093: sgreng nas thur du bsnol bas sems can la thugs
NK069(tu)001:18096: khyi gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:18097: zhes dper na khyi bzang pos grong khyer gcig kyang mi 'byed par bsrung ba dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:18098: he ru kas 'khor ba sdug bsngal gyi grong khyer las /
NK069(tu)001:18099: gang yang mi 'byed par bla myed gnas su sgrol lo //
NK069(tu)001:18100: de'i rtags sho na ma zhing dral nas gnas lta ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:18102: lta ba ye shes kyi spyan te /
NK069(tu)001:18103: sems can thams cad chos nyid kyi ngang du 'dren pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18104: bzhad gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:18106: dang po god yod par lding /
NK069(tu)001:18107: de bya gzhan bran nas god ma /
NK069(tu)001:18108: de nas bya gzhan song ba dang bya rgod za ba ltar /
NK069(tu)001:18109: dang po kun tu tshol ba'i yid kyis mthong /
NK069(tu)001:18110: de'i ting la rnam shes byung /
NK069(tu)001:18111: de nas 'du shes kyis kun brtags su 'dzin /
NK069(tu)001:18112: de 'phags pa'i dus su gnas 'gyur ba'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:18113: thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don byed do //
NK069(tu)001:18114: de'i rtags su bya rgod mgo' dkar mo lus po
NK069(tu)001:18115: ser ba gri dang ban d+ha snams par ba stan
NK069(tu)001:18116: nas / sems can sna tshogs pa'i don byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18117: rkang ka'i gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:18118: zhes dper na bya rkang ka dang bya gzhan 'grogs nas /
NK069(tu)001:18119: ro'i dong gi khar phyin nas /
NK069(tu)001:18120: rkang kas rkan rdabs pas ro sa 'og nas steng du 'byung /
NK069(tu)001:18121: de sked par bcad nas za /
NK069(tu)001:18122: de'i ting la bya gzhan za ba dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:18123: 'du byed yid dang 'grogs nas phyir yul la 'byung /
NK069(tu)001:18124: rnam par shes pas yul ma spyad bar du /
NK069(tu)001:18125: yid kyis nges par gcod mi nus /
NK069(tu)001:18126: rnam par shes par spyad tsam na /
NK069(tu)001:18128: de gnas 'gyur nas sangs rgya ste don mdzad pa ltar /
NK069(tu)001:18129: kang ka'i mgo' can zhing 'phrag la skal nas /
NK069(tu)001:18130: sems can rnams la brdar ston pas so //
NK069(tu)001:18131: dur bya'i gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:18132: zhes dper na bya rog gi lus kyi spu dog la mtshon gzhan gyis sgyur du myed pa ltar /
NK069(tu)001:18133: kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa me long lta bu'i ye shes su gnas 'gyur ba'i dus na yang /
NK069(tu)001:18134: nyon mongs pas slad pas mi 'gyur /
NK069(tu)001:18135: bdud dang dregs pas mi shigs /
NK069(tu)001:18136: de'i rtags su bya rog mgo' can nag mo gri
NK069(tu)001:18137: dang ban d+ha thogs pa kha na ro khyer ba
NK069(tu)001:18138: brdar bstan pa'o // 'ug pa'i gdong chen mo'i rnams /
NK069(tu)001:18139: zhes 'ug pa ni nyin mo nyal /
NK069(tu)001:18140: nub mo langs nas chu nang gi nya la dmigs pas bsam gyis skyel ba dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:18141: sangs rgyas chos kyi dbyings su nyal nas /
NK069(tu)001:18142: gdul bya skabs la bab pa dang 'dul te /
NK069(tu)001:18144: de'i rtags su 'ug gdong sna tshogs mdog phyag na lcags kyu dang ban d+ha snams pa bstan no //
NK069(tu)001:18145: rang rang gi lag cha dang bcas nas ston par gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:18146: ston nas kyang 'bar ba chen po'i 'khor lo'i phyi rol /
NK069(tu)001:18147: zhes de yang sgyu 'phrul gyi bshad brgyud bla ma nas /
NK069(tu)001:18149: smug nag 'bar ba'i bar khyams la //
NK069(tu)001:18150: gsang ba'i mkha' las skur bskyed pa //
NK069(tu)001:18151: shar gyi phyogs su bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18152: dri za bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18153: kun gzhi yul las gnas 'gyur ba //
NK069(tu)001:18154: phra myen thogs myed seng ge'i mgo' //
NK069(tu)001:18155: rnal 'byor ser nag sing nga ma //
NK069(tu)001:18156: mche' gtsigs rkan brdabs g.yang gzhi' gyon //
NK069(tu)001:18157: phyag gnyis bsnol nas shin tu 'gying //
NK069(tu)001:18158: ti ra chen po sprug cig gsol //
NK069(tu)001:18159: dri za'i gdan la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:18160: lho yi phyogs su bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18161: grul bum bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18162: rnam shes yul las gnas 'gyur ba //
NK069(tu)001:18163: phra myen dpa' bo stag gi mgo' //
NK069(tu)001:18164: rnal 'byor dmar nag byang kri ma //
NK069(tu)001:18165: mche' gtsigs rkan rdabs g.yang gzhi' gsol //
NK069(tu)001:18166: phyag gnyis gyad kyi dor thabs kyis //
NK069(tu)001:18167: ti ra sgyur nas 'bri tshugs lta //
NK069(tu)001:18168: grul bum gdan la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:18169: nub kyi phyogs su bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18170: yi dwags bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18171: nyon mongs yul las gnas 'gyur ba //
NK069(tu)001:18172: phra myen stangs snyoms wa mo'i mgo' //
NK069(tu)001:18173: rnal 'byor dmar nag kri la ma //
NK069(tu)001:18174: mche' gtsigs rkan brdabs g.yang gzhi gyon //
NK069(tu)001:18175: lag gnyis tir chung nang rol 'bru //
NK069(tu)001:18176: yi dwags gdan la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:18177: byang gi phyogs su bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18178: gnod sbyin bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18179: reg bya yul las gnas 'gyur ba //
NK069(tu)001:18180: phra men stangs snyoms spyang mo'i mgo' //
NK069(tu)001:18181: rnal 'byor mthing nag sho na ma //
NK069(tu)001:18182: mche' gtsigs rkan brdabs g.yang gzhi' gon //
NK069(tu)001:18183: phyag gnyis rol pa chen po yi //
NK069(tu)001:18184: ti ra phyed mar gcad nas gsol //
NK069(tu)001:18185: gnod sbyin gdan la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:18186: shar lho mtshams su bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18187: drang srong bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18188: lta byed yul las gnas 'gyur ba //
NK069(tu)001:18189: phra myen gzi' ldan bya rgod mgo' //
NK069(tu)001:18190: rnal 'byor mthar nag kri ta ma //
NK069(tu)001:18191: mchu' sdengs rkan brdabs g.yang gzhi' gyon //
NK069(tu)001:18192: zangs gri dmar po g.yas pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18193: rgyu zhags drangs pa g.yon na sdob //
NK069(tu)001:18194: drang srong gdan la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:18195: lho nub mtshams su bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18196: srin po bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18197: nyan byed yul las gnas 'gyur ba //
NK069(tu)001:18198: phra myen gsal byed dur bya'i mgo' //
NK069(tu)001:18199: rnal 'byor snar mgo' kang ka ma //
NK069(tu)001:18200: mchu' dang rkan sdebs g.yang gzhi' gyon //
NK069(tu)001:18201: tir chung stod smad g.yas g.yon na //
NK069(tu)001:18202: rngam pa'i tshul gyis 'phrag la skal //
NK069(tu)001:18203: srin po'i gdan la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:18204: nub byang mtshams su bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18205: rlung rta bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18206: snom byed yul las gnas 'gyur ba //
NK069(tu)001:18207: phra myen sa le bya rog gdong //
NK069(tu)001:18208: rnal 'byor dmar nag kha kha ma //
NK069(tu)001:18209: mchu dang rkan brdab g.yang gzhi' gon //
NK069(tu)001:18210: zangs gri dmar po g.yas pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18211: ban d+ha rag ta g.yon na 'dzin //
NK069(tu)001:18212: rlung lha'i gdan la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:18213: byang shar 'tshams su bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18214: byi na bsgyel ba'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18215: myong byed yul las gnas 'gyur ba //
NK069(tu)001:18216: phra myen rdzogs byed 'ug pa'i gdong //
NK069(tu)001:18217: rnal 'byor ser nag hu lu ma //
NK069(tu)001:18218: mchu dang rkan brdab g.yang gzhi' gon //
NK069(tu)001:18219: rdo rje lcags kyu g.yas pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18220: ti chung ci bcum g.yon pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18221: byi na ya la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NK069(tu)001:18223: shar phyogs nas 'khor bar rngam pa'i mdangs kyis 'khod do //
NK069(tu)001:18227: de nas yab yum thabs dang shes rab shin tu
NK069(tu)001:18228: dgyes pa'i byang chub sems kyis phyogs bcu'i rgyu bstan
NK069(tu)001:18229: / zhing khams ma lus par bde bas khyab nas /
NK069(tu)001:18231: skyen bstan phata ces brjod pas /
NK069(tu)001:18232: thig le las lha'i skur gyur pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:18233: rang gi ngo bo bstan rdo rje srings 'gro ma'i tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:18235: rdo rje lta bu'i thugs las /
NK069(tu)001:18236: yid myur brda'i dbur bstan nas /
NK069(tu)001:18237: 'gro ba las khad srings nas mya ngan las 'das pa'i sar 'gro zhing /
NK069(tu)001:18238: sems can ma lus pa'i tshogs kyi don byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18239: 'di bsdu' ba'i dngos po bzhi las /
NK069(tu)001:18241: snying rje la sbyin pa yun srings nas gtong bas na /
NK069(tu)001:18243: brda yid srings nas 'gro ba ltar /
NK069(tu)001:18244: 'khor ba las yid rings nas 'gro ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:18245: tshad myed pa bzhi las ni /
NK069(tu)001:18247: snying rjes sems can 'khor ba las sgrol bas na /
NK069(tu)001:18248: phyag na lcags kyu snams pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18250: dpa' bar 'gro ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:18251: lha mo 'di thugs rdo rje'i rigs yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:18252: dpa' bo'i spyod pas sems can 'dren pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18253: shar du 'god pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:18255: thugs rje ye shes kyi nyi ma 'char bar byed pas na shar du bkod do //
NK069(tu)001:18256: rdo rje gdong mo'i tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:18257: zhes rang mi 'gyur zhing gzhan 'joms pa'i rdo rje pha lam lta bu las /
NK069(tu)001:18258: gzhan 'joms pa phag gdong du bstan nas /
NK069(tu)001:18259: sems can ma lus pa'i tshogs rnams kyi don byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18260: lha mo 'di bsdu' ba'i dngos po bzhi las /
NK069(tu)001:18261: don mthun pa dang sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:18262: sbyin pa gtong ba'i tshe na gang 'dod pa dang mthun par stong bas so //
NK069(tu)001:18263: tshad myed pa bzhi las ni /
NK069(tu)001:18264: byams pa dang sbyar te byams pa'i zhags pas 'dzin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18266: rin chen phyag rgya'i ting nge 'dzin te /
NK069(tu)001:18268: de yang rdo rje pha lam gyis gzhan 'bigs pa ltar /
NK069(tu)001:18269: phag gdong gis gzhan 'bigs shing dgos 'dod 'byung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:18270: lhor dgod pa'i dgos pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:18271: che ba'i yon tan ma lus pa thams cad rgyas shing rdzogs pas lhor 'god pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18272: rdo rje 'jig rten ma'i tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:18273: rdo rje lta bu'i thugs nas /
NK069(tu)001:18275: nyi zla'i spyan gnyis kyis 'jig rten pa'i mun pa sel zhing /
NK069(tu)001:18276: sems can ma lus pa'i tshogs kyi don byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18277: 'di bsdu' ba'i dngos po bzhi las ni don spyod pa dang sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:18278: sbyin pa gtong ba'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:18279: sbyin pa che bas sems can gyi dgos 'dod skongs te /
NK069(tu)001:18280: bdag kyang bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs pas so //
NK069(tu)001:18281: tshad myed pa bzhi las ni /
NK069(tu)001:18282: dga' ba tshad myed pa dang sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:18284: bdag gzhan gyi don rdzogs par dga' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:18286: shes rab sgron me'i ting nge 'dzin te /
NK069(tu)001:18288: 'jig rten gyi ma rig pa'i mun pa sel lo //
NK069(tu)001:18290: nyi zla'i spyan gyis 'jig rten mun pa sel lo //
NK069(tu)001:18291: rdo rje ro langs ma'i tshogs rnams /
NK069(tu)001:18292: zhes thugs stong pa nyid kyi rdo rje las /
NK069(tu)001:18293: sangs rgyas thams cad mchod pa'i nus mthus /
NK069(tu)001:18294: shi ba'i ro yang slang bar nus pas na /
NK069(tu)001:18295: sems can ma lus pa'i tshogs kyi don byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18296: 'di na bsdu ba bzhi las ni /
NK069(tu)001:18297: snyan par smra ba dang sbyang ste /
NK069(tu)001:18298: lha mo 'dis dril bu'i sgra snyan sgrogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18299: tshad myed pa bzhi las ni stangs snyoms dang sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:18300: spyang ku'i mgos nyon mongs pa lnga stangs snyoms su spyod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18302: slar mtsho' ba'i ting nge 'dzin te /
NK069(tu)001:18304: sangs rgyas thams cad spyan 'dren no //
NK069(tu)001:18305: lha mo 'di mchod cing rten na /
NK069(tu)001:18306: rnam par shes pa shi nas ro lta bu yang langs par 'gyur /
NK069(tu)001:18307: lus thal bar song yang slangs par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:18309: dril bus 'gro ba la chos ston cing las dang nyon mongs pa'i bag chags byang bar byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18310: rang rang gi lag cha dang /
NK069(tu)001:18311: ngo mtshar dang chas nas bstan par gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:18313: ston nas kyang 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgor /
NK069(tu)001:18314: rngam pa'i gzugs kyis gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:18315: zhes gsang ba sgyu 'phrul gyi rgyud bla ma nas /
NK069(tu)001:18316: 'bar ba'i bar khyams sgo bzhi ru //
NK069(tu)001:18317: phyin ci log bzhi gnas 'gyur ba //
NK069(tu)001:18318: phag chen mo'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18319: rta gdong nag mo g.yang gzhi' gyon //
NK069(tu)001:18320: rdo rje lcags kyu g.yas ba na //
NK069(tu)001:18321: ban d+ha rag ta g.yon ba na //
NK069(tu)001:18323: yang lho'i sgor ni bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18324: ra gdong chen mo'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18325: phag gdong chen mo'i g.yang gzhi' gon //
NK069(tu)001:18326: lcags kyi dril zhags g.yas pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18327: ban d+ha rag ta g.yon pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18330: nub kyi sgor ni bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18331: bum sna chen mo'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18332: dred gdong chen mo'i g.yang gzhi' gon //
NK069(tu)001:18333: lcags sgrog me 'bar g.yas pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18334: ban d+ha rlon pa g.yon ba na //
NK069(tu)001:18336: byang gi sgor ni bsam bya ba //
NK069(tu)001:18337: bsus po che'i gdan stengs su //
NK069(tu)001:18338: spyang gdong chen mo g.yang gzhi' gon //
NK069(tu)001:18339: thal rkyen dril bu g.yas pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18340: ban d+ha rlon pa g.yon pa na //
NK069(tu)001:18341: de nas dgyes pa'i sprin las phyogs bcu nas phata zhes bsgrags pas thams cad 'khrol nas /
NK069(tu)001:18342: zhes de ltar rigs lnga'i he ru kas /
NK069(tu)001:18343: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad la /
NK069(tu)001:18344: sras mo nyi shu ston nas /
NK069(tu)001:18346: dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i rjes de nas /
NK069(tu)001:18347: dbang mo rang gi gnas su 'byed pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:18348: yab yum thabs dang shes rab la /
NK069(tu)001:18349: dgyes pa'i byang chub sems kyi sprin las /
NK069(tu)001:18350: phyogs bcu nas phata zhes pa'i sgra byung nas /
NK069(tu)001:18352: dper na ri dwags ngang gis yang 'grogs snying 'dod pa la /
NK069(tu)001:18353: mi rnams kyis khus btab pas /
NK069(tu)001:18354: skad cig kyang mi bzod cing rgyugs pa dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:18355: lha'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbang phyug ma de dag kyang /
NK069(tu)001:18356: ye nas kyang dpal chen po ye shes kyi sku la /
NK069(tu)001:18358: dpal chen po rigs lnga yang ngang gis yang 'khro tshul dang ldan pa la /
NK069(tu)001:18359: thugs rje chen pos khra bor bcos nas kyang /
NK069(tu)001:18360: khyad par du khro tshul lam /
NK069(tu)001:18361: khro bo'i gdang ngar gyis sgra chen po phata zhes sgrags pas /
NK069(tu)001:18362: thams cad khyad par yang khro khro rngam rngam bzhin du gnas par gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:18363: dgyes pa rang gi ngo bo bstan /
NK069(tu)001:18364: ma mo thams cad kyang rang rang gi gnas ga la ba der yud tsam gyis phyin par baskye'o //
NK069(tu)001:18365: zhes ma mo dbang phyug ma rnams /
NK069(tu)001:18366: ri dwags la khus btab pas 'grogs pa ltar /
NK069(tu)001:18367: rang rang gi gnas ri rab kyi khong seng ngam /
NK069(tu)001:18369: ri rab kyi steng du so sor gyes te /
NK069(tu)001:18370: shar gyi rgyal mo bdun dang /
NK069(tu)001:18372: nub kyi dbang mo bdun dang /
NK069(tu)001:18373: byang gi bran mo bdun du bye nas /
NK069(tu)001:18374: sems kyi bsam pa yud tsam pa gcig la /
NK069(tu)001:18375: so so'i gnas su phyin par skye bas /
NK069(tu)001:18376: rang gi gnas su khyim du song ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:18378: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po dpal khrag 'thung chen po de dag kun /
NK069(tu)001:18379: zhes gong du ru tra dang bdud dang srin po la sogs pa bsgral /
NK069(tu)001:18380: yum rnams la sbyor ba byas /
NK069(tu)001:18382: rigs lnga thabs dang shes rab gnyis myed du dgyes
NK069(tu)001:18383: nas thugs rje chen pos khrag 'thung ba de dag
NK069(tu)001:18384: kun / dregs pa can rnams gnas stobs par ston pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:18385: bdud rtsi chen pos lus kyi rgyun gsol ba zhes kyang bya /
NK069(tu)001:18386: sgro skur gyi ya ga bral ba'i phyir gsad pa gso' ba zhes kyang bya /
NK069(tu)001:18387: sngon gyi gnas dran byed zhes kyang bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:18388: dpal gyi lhums nas sngon gyi las dran pas na'o //
NK069(tu)001:18389: thugs rje chen po'i bdud rtsi gang phyung na 'byung
NK069(tu)001:18390: ba zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par
NK069(tu)001:18391: zhugs nas / zhes gas da pa gso' ba zhes bya ba'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:18392: thugs rje chen pos slar sos par byed pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:18394: ra hu las bdud rtsis skus nas 'thungs par byed pas /
NK069(tu)001:18395: phyag na rdo rjes 'khor lo rgyab nas lus dum bu brgyad du stubs yang /
NK069(tu)001:18396: bdud rtsis ma shi bar lus dum bu rgyu ba ltar shi ba sos so //
NK069(tu)001:18397: sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje las 'di phyung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:18398: zhes rigs lnga khrag 'thung de dag gi sku dang
NK069(tu)001:18399: gsung dang thugs gsum dbyer myi phyed pas rdo rje'o
NK069(tu)001:18400: // +amo badz+ra ma h+aa a smri ta ma h+aa kro d+he am am am /
NK069(tu)001:18403: ni ye shes lngas byin gyis brlab pas /
NK069(tu)001:18404: badz+ra ni rdo rje ste thugs kyi ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:18405: ma h+aa a smri te ni bdud rtsi chen pos te /
NK069(tu)001:18406: lus dum bur stubs kyang 'byor bar byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18407: ma h+aa kro d+he ni chos kyi dbyings kyi rtags khro bo khro mo /
NK069(tu)001:18408: ni chos kyi dbyings de nyid sku gsung thugs gsum dang ldan pa'i don de /
NK069(tu)001:18409: ru tra'i tshogs kyi lus ngag yid gsum shi ba slong ba'i bdud rtsi'i theg pa gsum mo //
NK069(tu)001:18410: mdor na chos kyi dbyings rtogs pa'i ye shes kyi bdud rtsi chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:18411: mtha' gnyis su shi ba las slong bar byed pas bdud rtsi chen po zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:18413: dbang phyug chen po la sogs pa thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:18414: ces rmangs rigs 'dod chags can gyi dbang phyug chen po dang /
NK069(tu)001:18415: rgyal rigs kyi lha dbang chen ma h+aa de ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:18416: rje'u rigs kyi lha gzi' brjid che ba tshangs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:18417: bram ze'i rigs 'thu' che ba khyab 'jug dang /
NK069(tu)001:18420: dregs pa can thams cad do //
NK069(tu)001:18422: bcom ldan 'das khro bo chen po /
NK069(tu)001:18423: de dag gis snam nas ston te /
NK069(tu)001:18424: zhes badz+ra he ru ka'i 'phongs nas ru tra ston /
NK069(tu)001:18425: 'bu ta he ru ka'i 'phongs nas brgya sbyin gton /
NK069(tu)001:18426: rad na he ru ka las bshen rje grul bum la sogs pa ston /
NK069(tu)001:18427: pad ma he ru ka'i 'phongs nas klu chu bdag gi rigs rnams ston /
NK069(tu)001:18428: kar ma he ru ka'i zhabs nas gnod sbyin stobs bzangs la sogs pa rnams ston /
NK069(tu)001:18429: mdor na dbang phyug ma rnams kyi khyo la sogs
NK069(tu)001:18430: pa rnams rigs lnga khrag 'thung so so'i zhabs na
NK069(tu)001:18431: mar la dri chen du gtang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:18432: ci'i phyir ston na mi gtsang ba'i 'dam gyi rgya mtshor tshud pa las /
NK069(tu)001:18433: zhes dper na gtsang ba'i nang na dri chen la srog chags srin bu gnas pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:18434: 'dam nang gi rbal pa dmig phyi ba lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:18436: snam nas u tsus ma kro ta phyung nas /
NK069(tu)001:18437: zhes rnam zhes bya ste 'phongs nas u tsus ma kro ta zhes kyang bya /
NK069(tu)001:18439: rtsang rme med pa zhes kyang bya ba phyung nas /
NK069(tu)001:18440: yang dag pa la gtsang rme myed de /
NK069(tu)001:18441: mi gtsang ba nyid bdud rtsi yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:18442: de ston par byed pa'i gnyen po khro bo rme rtsegs phyung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:18443: khro bo rme rtsegs zhal cig phyag bcu drug pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:18449: bkra shis shin tu kra ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:18461: zhags pa rnams rim pa bzhin du thogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18463: phyi bdud rtsi lnga mi gtsang ba'i 'dam khur 'thungs /
NK069(tu)001:18464: nang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa lnga ye shes lngar mthong /
NK069(tu)001:18465: gsang ba khams bdud rtsi lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas lngar 'thungs te /
NK069(tu)001:18466: de kho na nyid ma rig pa /
NK069(tu)001:18467: rig pa'i ye shes su 'thungs pas /
NK069(tu)001:18468: gtsang rme myed par rim pas rtsegs pas na rme rtsegs zhes bya ba yin no //
NK069(tu)001:18469: rnam shes slar 'tsho' bas 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:18470: 'dam khur kun 'thungs nas dran pa slar rnyed de
NK069(tu)001:18471: rnam shes slar 'tsho bas 'chi bdag gi bdud bcom
NK069(tu)001:18472: / zhes mi gtsang ba'i 'dam dang 'dra ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:18473: shes pa'i rgyud la yod pa'i las dang bag chags kyi sgrib kun 'a thungs nas /
NK069(tu)001:18474: shi ba'i las slar sos pa la yang dran pa snyed nas ces bya /
NK069(tu)001:18475: yang na sgrib pa byang nas sngar gyi skye ba dran pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18476: yang na shes pa'i rgyud la yod pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:18477: las dang nyon mongs pa'i bag chags kyi sgrib pa sbyangs nas /
NK069(tu)001:18478: rang gi sems kyi chos nyid byang chub sems sngar ma rtogs pa de /
NK069(tu)001:18479: rtogs par gyur pa la yang dran pa slar snyed nas zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:18480: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs de dag kyang /
NK069(tu)001:18481: zhes 'jigs byed khro bo'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK069(tu)001:18489: 'jigs byed khro bor snang bar mdzad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:18491: zhes dbu' dgu' ni sa dgu /
NK069(tu)001:18492: sa re re la che ba 'i yon tan mang bas na /
NK069(tu)001:18494: de yang rgya mtsho' dgur snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:18496: zhes phyag stong ni stong pa bco' brgyad de /
NK069(tu)001:18497: rtsa ba stong pa bco' brgyad du 'dus /
NK069(tu)001:18498: de re re la yang yon tan du ma yod pas na brgya brgya /
NK069(tu)001:18499: de yang stong dang brgyad brgyar snang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:18501: zhes stong gsum gyi dregs pa gnan po'i phyir zhabs brgya' tsho brgyad do //
NK069(tu)001:18502: sku 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor na bzhugs pa 'thong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:18503: zhes de lta bu'i sku me dpung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor na bzhugs par ru tras 'thong ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:18504: sgrib pa byang bas bsam pa lhun gyis grub pa'i rig 'dzin zhal 'thong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:18505: de'i dus su 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i srid
NK069(tu)001:18506: pa'i kun tu dregs pa'i dbang phyug thams cad 'dul
NK069(tu)001:18507: ba'i thabs sna tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab par /
NK069(tu)001:18509: rigs drug gi 'jig rten na gnas pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:18533: za byed la sogs pa phyogs bcu'i na gnas pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:18534: srid pa gsum gyi bdag po /
NK069(tu)001:18537: de dag thams cad gang la gang shis su 'dul thabs kyis stul te /
NK069(tu)001:18538: mdor na bsam gyis myi khyab pa btul lo //
NK069(tu)001:18539: so sor snang bas dus cig tu btul lo //
NK069(tu)001:18540: zhes sprul pa rdul phran grangs med kyis /
NK069(tu)001:18541: skad cig yud la don grub par bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:18542: tha dad par snang bas don grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:18543: de nas de dag shin tu 'dar zhing bred pa rab tu zhum pa'i nga ros /
NK069(tu)001:18544: zhes de nas las skos la stab pa bstan te /
NK069(tu)001:18545: slar drag pa snyed pa'i dregs pa de dag /
NK069(tu)001:18548: ngag gi nga ro 'khyal par sgra /
NK069(tu)001:18550: zhes 'phral gyi bkur sti dang rim 'gro byed pa'i
NK069(tu)001:18551: 'bangs su 'chi yun gyi don srid du byid pa'i
NK069(tu)001:18552: 'bangs su 'chi' / 'bangs su nan tan ma bgyis na //
NK069(tu)001:18553: zhes 'bangs su nan tan byas pa de ltar /
NK069(tu)001:18554: bya ba dang bkur sti ma byas na /
NK069(tu)001:18555: mgo' dang lus ni brgya' gshegs shing //
NK069(tu)001:18556: zhes tshe 'di la bdag cag gi mgo' 'gas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:18557: lus dum bur bshag par gyis shig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18559: ces snying yang 'gas shing stubs 'gyur shing /
NK069(tu)001:18560: yang na snying la khro bo yag sha me dbal gyis stubs shig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18561: rul myags tshig nas brlag pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:18567: dmyal bar lhung nas 'bod par shog /
NK069(tu)001:18568: ces rdo rje dmyal bar lhung nas /
NK069(tu)001:18569: sdug bsngal gyis 'o dod chen po gnam du 'bod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18570: zhes 'bangs mching bar mna' bor nas /
NK069(tu)001:18571: dkyil 'khor gyi gdan du gzhag go //
NK069(tu)001:18573: rang skal nyi zla pad ma las kyi gdan /
NK069(tu)001:18574: rtags kyi che ba rin po che ston pa'i gdan /
NK069(tu)001:18575: yon tan kun la sa rnams rdzogs pa'i gdan /
NK069(tu)001:18576: gus pas sgrib pa dregs pa rnams sbyong ba'i gdan pas /
NK069(tu)001:18577: 'di ni gus pas skur ti'am sgrib pa sbyong ba'i gdan no //
NK069(tu)001:18579: thams cad kyis 'grin cig tu yang smras pa /
NK069(tu)001:18580: zhes dregs pa chen po thams cad kyis yid kyi bsam pa gcig /
NK069(tu)001:18582: bdag cag rnams kyi mchis bred dang //
NK069(tu)001:18583: ma dang sring mo bu mo rnams //
NK069(tu)001:18584: zhes rtse ga cig yid la byams pas ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:18585: lus ngag sems kyis gdung bas sreng mo /
NK069(tu)001:18586: sha khrag lus las chad pas bu mo rnams /
NK069(tu)001:18587: dkyil 'khor chen por bzhes su gsol //
NK069(tu)001:18588: zhes khro bo dkyil 'khor chen por 'bul bas dang du bzhes su gsol /
NK069(tu)001:18589: dpa' bo lha rje bzhes su gsol //
NK069(tu)001:18590: 'khor ba'i g.yul ngo zlog pa'i dpa' bo /
NK069(tu)001:18591: 'khor 'das kyi lha thams cad rje bo khyod kyis /
NK069(tu)001:18592: de phyi rabs kyi las bya ba /
NK069(tu)001:18593: bdag cag so so'i 'khor bcas kyis //
NK069(tu)001:18594: bdag cag ni dregs pa chen po'o //
NK069(tu)001:18595: dregs pa so so'i 'khor bcas kyis //
NK069(tu)001:18597: khro bo chen po tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor //
NK069(tu)001:18598: ming tsam 'dzin par byed pa yang //
NK069(tu)001:18599: 'di la mos pa byed pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:18600: gtsug gi nor bu 'bar ba ltar //
NK069(tu)001:18601: dper na klu'i rgyal po dga' bo'i spyi bo'i gtsug
NK069(tu)001:18602: gi yid bzhin gyi nor bu 'od 'bar ba yod
NK069(tu)001:18603: pas / de la lus ngag yid kyis rtag tu mchod pa byed pa ltar /
NK069(tu)001:18604: spyi bor skur bar bstan pa /
NK069(tu)001:18605: g.yo' rgyu myed cing gus ldan pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:18606: lus ngag yid gsum g.yo' rgyu dang zol sogs myed cing /
NK069(tu)001:18607: lus gus sems mos ngag dang ba dang ldan pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:18608: sems kyis blangs te spyi bo yi //
NK069(tu)001:18612: gtsug tu zhabs bzhag par bsams la /
NK069(tu)001:18613: gtsug tu bzhag te bskur bar bagyi'o //
NK069(tu)001:18615: nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du mchod cing bskur /
NK069(tu)001:18616: de'i dgos pa ci yang rung //
NK069(tu)001:18617: ming tsam 'dzin pa'i rnam 'byor pa de yi /
NK069(tu)001:18619: ma lus rdzogs par bdag cag bsgrub //
NK069(tu)001:18622: bdag cag dregs pa 'khor bcas rnams kyis sgrub bo //
NK069(tu)001:18623: ma sgrubs na rang la sdig par mnas bor ba /
NK069(tu)001:18624: gal te dpa' bo'i spyan mnga' 'dir //
NK069(tu)001:18626: dpa' bo he ru ka'i spyan mnga' 'dir /
NK069(tu)001:18627: smras pa bzhin du ma bsgrubs na //
NK069(tu)001:18628: bdag gis da lta smras pa bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:18629: phyis sngon 'byung gi rjes su ma sgrubs na /
NK069(tu)001:18630: bdag cag rnams kyi mgo' lus snying //
NK069(tu)001:18631: dregs pa can 'khor dang bcas pa /
NK069(tu)001:18632: yan lag gi dang po mgo' dang /
NK069(tu)001:18635: bskas stubs dum bur rul bar 'chi' //
NK069(tu)001:18637: gzer zug drag pos lus sdug bsngal nas /
NK069(tu)001:18638: lus kyi dbang po'i rgyun nyams nas 'chi' /
NK069(tu)001:18639: rang gi gnas nas dal du yongs pa /
NK069(tu)001:18640: de nas de dag gi chung ma'i tshogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:18641: zhes 'di man chad 'khor dam la btags te bstan pa yun du gnas par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:18642: gsang ba'i dbang po 'jug pa'i yul bdag du byas pa chung ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:18644: lus ngag yid gsum gdung bas ni sring mo dang /
NK069(tu)001:18645: blo sems rtse cig tu byams pas ni ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:18646: bu mo'i tshogs thams cad dkyil 'khor du yud tsam gyis 'ongs nas /
NK069(tu)001:18647: sha khrag lus las chad pas sam /
NK069(tu)001:18648: skyed pa'i pha mar gyur pas skyed pas bu mo'i /
NK069(tu)001:18649: gong du phata zhes sgrags pas gnas su skye ba de rnams /
NK069(tu)001:18650: bya nag thang la babs pa ltar 'ongs nas /
NK069(tu)001:18651: rtogs pa chos sku don gyis dpa' ba /
NK069(tu)001:18652: 'dul bya longs sku khro bo gnyen pos dpa' ba /
NK069(tu)001:18653: 'dul thabs gsad gso' spyod pas dpa' ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:18654: las kyi dngos grub zhu ba /
NK069(tu)001:18655: thams cad kyis 'grin cig tu smras pa /
NK069(tu)001:18656: dregs pa dang ma dang chung ma dang bu mo thams cad kyis /
NK069(tu)001:18658: bdag cag 'khor tshogs thams cad kun //
NK069(tu)001:18660: dpa' bo chen po'i 'bangs su mchi' //
NK069(tu)001:18661: dpa' bo he ru ka chen pos bdag cag rnams dregs pa can rnams /
NK069(tu)001:18662: las kyi dngos grub rtsal du gsol //
NK069(tu)001:18671: phyi la dgra bgegs zhi ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:18673: nang la nyon mongs pa zhi ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:18674: rtog pa ngan pa zhi ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:18675: rgyas pa la yang gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:18690: phyi rol pa gzungs ma dgug pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:18691: mi 'thun pa'i dgra bgegs rnam gnyis kyi dbang po sgyur te dgug pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18703: de rnams kyis las bzhi yongs su rdzogs pa'i dngos grub yin te /
NK069(tu)001:18704: de lta bu de gsal du gsol /
NK069(tu)001:18706: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:18707: dregs pas zhus pa de nas /
NK069(tu)001:18708: ston pa bcom ldan 'das thabs dang shes rab la
NK069(tu)001:18709: dgyes pa chen pos zhes pa spyod yul dag par
NK069(tu)001:18710: shes pa'o // lag tu rdo rje byin nas ming gi dbang bskur nas /
NK069(tu)001:18711: zhes las kyi lag tu rdo rje lag g.yas su ming gi dbang bskur nas /
NK069(tu)001:18712: srin mo smug nag rdo rje thod rlon 'chang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:18713: dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rim du bkod do //
NK069(tu)001:18714: dkyil 'khor bar 'byams kyi phyi rim du bkod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:18718: byang du bdun rnams bkod do //
NK069(tu)001:18719: gsang pa snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:18720: rtogs par bka' bas na gsang ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:18722: ma nor bas na de kho na nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:18723: drang don ma yin te nges don 'thar thug pa las /
NK069(tu)001:18724: khro bo rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor /
NK069(tu)001:18725: sku khro tshul dang bcas nas 'bar ba'i gar dgus khyab pas na /
NK069(tu)001:18726: sprin rnam par spros pa'i le'u ste bco lnga pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18727: mang zhing dpangs 'thugs pas na sprin /
NK069(tu)001:18728: gdul bya la zhal mi 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:18729: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:18730: khro bo rang bzhin gyi dal 'og min na yod pa myin nam /
NK069(tu)001:18731: 'di ru 'dul ba la sprul pa la /
NK069(tu)001:18732: rang bzhin gyi dal bya ba 'gal lo zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:18734: 'og min na 'di zhi bar bzhugs pa la /
NK069(tu)001:18735: 'dir ru tra 'dul ba la zhi ba rang bzhin gyis khro bor gyur pa la dgongs nas /
NK069(tu)001:18736: khro bo rang bzhin gyi dal lo //
NK069(tu)001:18739: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:18740: zhes le'u bco' lnga pa khro bo rang bzhin gyi dal bstan pa'i barjesa de nas /
NK069(tu)001:18741: ston pa bdud bzhi bcom pa de /
NK069(tu)001:18742: khro bo'i 'tsham rngam drag pos lha chen po 'dar zhing sgyel nas rdzis pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:18744: btul shugs rol pas phung po sdos bcas bshig pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:18746: dug gsum yangs par sha rus khrag la za ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:18747: nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:18748: rnam par shes pa 'chi ba myed par sangs rgyas
NK069(tu)001:18749: kyi sras su stabs pa ni 'chi bdag gi bdud
NK069(tu)001:18756: yab yum thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral myed par dgyes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18757: dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs chen po 'di dag dam tshig gis bsgrub par bya ba'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:18758: zhes khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs mang po 'di dag /
NK069(tu)001:18759: gsung gi dam tshigs sngags kyis /
NK069(tu)001:18760: rnal 'byor pa'i lus nyid khro bo bsgrub par bya ba'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:18761: de bzhin gshegs pa'i khro bo khrag 'thung chen po /
NK069(tu)001:18762: zhes 'jig rten gyi khro bo ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:18763: de ma nor ba'i chos kyi dbyings so //
NK069(tu)001:18764: bzhin ma bcos pa rig pa'i ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:18765: de'i ngang du rtogs pas gshegs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18768: gzhan las khyad par du gyur pas che ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:18769: 'di rnams la go rims stob na gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:18772: zhi khro sbag mar byed na /
NK069(tu)001:18774: zhi ba'i sku las khro bo'i skur gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:18775: yang na skad cig ma'i ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK069(tu)001:18776: gzhal yas khang skyed pa'i nang du /
NK069(tu)001:18777: bdag cho ga gsum gyis yab yum gyi skur skyed /
NK069(tu)001:18778: de nas lhag pa'i byang chub sems las /
NK069(tu)001:18779: yum gyi gsang ba'i gnas su yig 'bru h'u ha he phata bgod /
NK069(tu)001:18781: sarba ta th+aa ga ta la sogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:18782: skur skyed phyogs bcur spros nas 'dus pas /
NK069(tu)001:18784: 'khor rnams 'don pa'i sngags kyis ton la /
NK069(tu)001:18785: dkyil 'khor du so sor dgod do //
NK069(tu)001:18790: ye shes kyi ngal bsgrub pa la sogs pa ma nor bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:18791: btsun mo dang bcas pa'i tshogs de dag gi //
NK069(tu)001:18792: zhes spyad par bya ba'i yul du gyur pas na btsun mo /
NK069(tu)001:18793: yab yum thabs dang shes rab dang bcas pa /
NK069(tu)001:18794: sku dang gsung dang thugs rdo rje'i ye shes rngam pa las /
NK069(tu)001:18795: zhes ye nas sku gsung 'du 'bral myed par gnas pa la /
NK069(tu)001:18796: 'du 'bral myed par shes pas na ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:18797: de ltar rtogs pa'i don la rngam pa'i nga ro dang bcas pa las /
NK069(tu)001:18798: gsung gyi dkyil 'khor 'di dag phyung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:18799: zhes brjod pa'i sgra go brdar sprod pas na gsung /
NK069(tu)001:18800: brjod bya dang rjod byed 'drel bar go brda' spros pas na yang gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:18801: tshig dang don du smra bas na yang gsung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:18802: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru
NK069(tu)001:18803: ka ma h+aa tsan d+ha sarba dush+tana ta ka ha
NK069(tu)001:18804: na da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:18805: +amo ni thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes sam ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:18806: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ni /
NK069(tu)001:18807: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:18808: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ni /
NK069(tu)001:18809: dpal he ru ka khrag 'thung chen po /
NK069(tu)001:18810: ma h+aa tsan+da tsa ni stum po chen po /
NK069(tu)001:18811: sarba dush+tana ni sdig can thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:18816: h+aum h+aum h+aum ni sku gsung thugs kyi ngang du sdus shig /
NK069(tu)001:18817: phata ni sod la sregs shig /
NK069(tu)001:18818: sangs rgyas he ru ka'i sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:18819: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:18821: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rjes /
NK069(tu)001:18824: sdig pa byed pa'i gdug pa can thams cad la rgyob cig /
NK069(tu)001:18827: de nas thams cad thugs rjes sam /
NK069(tu)001:18828: sku gsung thugs su sdus shig /
NK069(tu)001:18829: don de kun yang thugs ye shes su byin gyis barlobasa shig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18830: ye shes lnga badz+ra rdo rje ma h+aa chen po
NK069(tu)001:18831: sh+r+ai dpal he ru ka khrag 'thung ma h+aa chen
NK069(tu)001:18832: po tsan d+ha stum po sarba thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:18833: dush+tana sdang ba ta ka rgyob cig ha na rtogs
NK069(tu)001:18834: shig da ha sregs shig pa tsa chom shig h+aum
NK069(tu)001:18835: h+aum h+aum sku gsung thugs su bsdus shig /
NK069(tu)001:18836: phata ni sod la sregs shig /
NK069(tu)001:18837: rdo rje rigs kyi dpal chen po thugs rdo rje'i rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:18838: he ru ka sku gsung thugs dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:18839: he ni dgyes pa chos sku /
NK069(tu)001:18840: ru ni chags pa longs sku /
NK069(tu)001:18841: ka ni mdzad pa te sprul sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:18842: rat+na ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan
NK069(tu)001:18843: d+ha sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa
NK069(tu)001:18845: ces rin chen he ru ka yon tan gyi rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:18846: he ru ka dgyes chags dang sbyang na /
NK069(tu)001:18847: he ni dgyes pa ste bde' ba /
NK069(tu)001:18848: ru ra ga na chags pa /
NK069(tu)001:18850: ka ni ka pa la na thod pa de /
NK069(tu)001:18851: dgyes chags kyis thod khrag 'thung ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:18852: +amo pad ma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma
NK069(tu)001:18853: h+aa tsa na d+ha sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na
NK069(tu)001:18854: da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:18855: ces pad ma he ru ka gsung pad ma'i rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:18856: he ru ka sku gsung thugs dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:18860: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa'i he ru ka'o //
NK069(tu)001:18861: +amo karma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa
NK069(tu)001:18862: tsan d+ha sarba da dush+tana ta ka ha na da
NK069(tu)001:18863: ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:18864: ces las kyi rigs he ru ka 'phrin las kyi bdag po /
NK069(tu)001:18865: he ru ka sgra brgyad dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:18866: he he ka na dgyes pa ste chos sku /
NK069(tu)001:18867: he he du na rgyu ste snying rje'i gtan tshigs /
NK069(tu)001:18868: ru ra ga na chags pa /
NK069(tu)001:18870: ka ka ru na thugs rje /
NK069(tu)001:18872: b+h+ya ka ra na sgra bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:18873: +amo sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri sarba dush+tana h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:18874: ces 'di ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:18875: kro ti shwa ri ni khro mo dbyings phyug ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:18876: +amo ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:18877: ces rdo rje rigs kyi yum badz+ra kro ti /
NK069(tu)001:18880: +amo ma h+aa sur+ya rat+na ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri bi da ma h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:18881: ces rin chen rigs kyi yum rat+na kro ti /
NK069(tu)001:18884: hri shod ta sa man ta pad ma ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri kha'i h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:18885: ces pad ma rigs kyi yum /
NK069(tu)001:18889: +amo sarba a mo ka ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri b+hi shwa h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:18890: ces las kyi rigs kyi yum /
NK069(tu)001:18894: rdo rje dkar mo'i rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18895: badz+ra tso'u ri ha rdo rje chom kun rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18900: rdo rje ro longs ma rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18902: rdo rje gtum mo'i rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18904: rdo rje spos ma'i rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18906: rdo rje rme sha can gyi rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18908: rdo rje dur khrod ma'i rtsa sngags ma tshogs ma /
NK069(tu)001:18909: zhes ma mo brgyad kyi sngags la /
NK069(tu)001:18910: badz+ra ni thugs rdo rje ltar mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:18911: ko'u ri la sogs pa ni mi sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:18912: ha brgyad ni skyed yig sa bon no //
NK069(tu)001:18916: las sna tshogs 'grub pa'i sngags su 'gro /
NK069(tu)001:18917: +amo badz+ra ko'u ri ha h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:18918: +amo badz+ra tso'u ri ha h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:18919: ces gzhan la yang sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:18920: dal gyi rtsibs 'chan bzhi dang gru chad bzhi la skyed do //
NK069(tu)001:18921: badz+ra si ngang mu ka he /
NK069(tu)001:18922: rdo rje seng ge'i gdong gi rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18923: badz+ra byang gri mu ka he /
NK069(tu)001:18924: rdo rje stag gi gdong gi rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18925: badz+ra kri la mu ka he /
NK069(tu)001:18926: rdo rje wa'i gdong ba can gyi rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18927: badz+ra sho na mu ka he /
NK069(tu)001:18928: rdo rje spyang gdong ma'am khyi'i gdong gi rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18929: badz+ra kri ta mu ka he /
NK069(tu)001:18930: rdo rje bya rgod gdong can gyi rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18931: badz+ra rkang ka mu ka he /
NK069(tu)001:18932: rdo rje dur bya gdong gi rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18933: badz+ra kha kha mu ka he /
NK069(tu)001:18934: rdo rje bya rog gdong gi rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18935: badz+ra hu lu ka mu ka he /
NK069(tu)001:18936: rdo rje 'ug pa'i gdong can gyi rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18937: zhes he ni rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:18938: skyed pa rkyen gyi sngags ni badz+ra sing nga mu ka la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18939: skul ba las kyi sngags ni /
NK069(tu)001:18940: +amo badz+ra sing nga mu ka he h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:18941: ces pa las sna tshogs pa grub pa'i sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:18942: dkyil 'khor bar khyams dang po la /
NK069(tu)001:18943: gcan gzan gyi mgo' can bzhi phyogs bzhir /
NK069(tu)001:18944: 'dab chags kyi mgo' can 'tshams bzhir bgod /
NK069(tu)001:18945: badz+ra ar+ya te tsa te nga dza /
NK069(tu)001:18946: rdo rje 'phags ma sring 'gro ma'i rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18948: rdo rje don yod ma'i rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18950: rdo rje 'jig rten ma'i rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18951: badz+ra pa smi pa la ya ba to ho /
NK069(tu)001:18952: rdo rje thal byed slar mtsho' ma'i rtsa sngags /
NK069(tu)001:18953: zhes pas sgo bzhi'i nang du bskyed cing dgod par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:18954: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:18955: 'dir dbang phyug ma la sngags ma gsungs ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:18956: b+h+yo las ma bstan pa ci zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:18958: dbang mo las las grub pa yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:18959: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags b+h+yo ba rjod
NK069(tu)001:18960: pa tsam gyis chog pas ma gsungs pa'ang yin la
NK069(tu)001:18961: / gzhan yang rgyud 'di rtsar rgyud yin pas rtsa sngags las ma gsungs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:18962: sngags rdzogs par ni bshad rgyud rnams na bzhugs yod /
NK069(tu)001:18963: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK069(tu)001:18964: shar gyi rgyal mo bdun zhi ba'i las byed ma'i sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:18965: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK069(tu)001:18966: lha'i blon mo bdun rgyas pa'i las byed /
NK069(tu)001:18967: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK069(tu)001:18969: dbang mo bdun dbang gi las byed ma /
NK069(tu)001:18970: b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK069(tu)001:18971: byang gi bran mo bdun drag po'i las byed ma /
NK069(tu)001:18972: b+h+yo 'di dag ni dbang mo'i sngags te /
NK069(tu)001:18973: shes rab che zhing ting nge 'dzin las su rung ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:18974: b+h+yo 'di dag brjod pa tsam gyis dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK069(tu)001:18975: sdom tshig srin mo smug nag rdo rje thod rlon 'chang /
NK069(tu)001:18977: sku mdog dang phyag mtshan la sogs pa gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:18978: de las ting nge 'dzin a cang las su mi rung na /
NK069(tu)001:18979: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad po 'di dag kyang /
NK069(tu)001:18980: ril sku mdog dmar mo la /
NK069(tu)001:18981: phyag g.yas rdo rje snams pa /
NK069(tu)001:18983: de las kyang las su mi rung na /
NK069(tu)001:18984: b+h+yo nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi yig 'bru 'di rnams /
NK069(tu)001:18985: sku mdog le'u rgan dmar po ltar sa le bar
NK069(tu)001:18986: khyams phyi ma na phar la gsal bar bsgom par
NK069(tu)001:18987: bya'o // ru lu ru lu ru lu h+aum /
NK069(tu)001:18989: thugs ye shes nyid sku gsung thugs dang ldan zhing /
NK069(tu)001:18990: sku gsung thugs gsum yang thugs ye shes su dbyer med pas h+aum ngo /
NK069(tu)001:18992: zlas pa'i sngags gnyis ka 'dis grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:18993: snyan gsan dbab pa'i sngags yin no //
NK069(tu)001:19003: sngags 'di dag phyag rgya bzhi dang /
NK069(tu)001:19004: ting nge 'dzin gyis mdun gyi nam ka la spyan drangs shing bzhugs su gsol /
NK069(tu)001:19006: ram ni spyan drangs pa'o bzhugs gnas /
NK069(tu)001:19010: rang bskyed pa dang me ri 'dab 'byor tsam du mdun gyi nam kar byon nas bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:19011: +amo badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya h+aum /
NK069(tu)001:19012: zhes rdo rje khro bo'i dam tshig ni thugs zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:19013: ting nge 'dzin gyis skyed pa'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK069(tu)001:19014: spyan drangs ba'i khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gnyis thams cad
NK069(tu)001:19015: nas thams cad du thugs ye shes su dbyer myed
NK069(tu)001:19016: pa kho na / dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:19017: rig pa'i me tog dor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:19018: khro la 'khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK069(tu)001:19019: zhes tshig bshad 'dis bod skad du dngos grub skul ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:19021: khro la ni gong gi bdud dang srin po zhe sdang gis khro la /
NK069(tu)001:19022: de la chen po bcas bcos rnam pa gnyis dang ldan pa'i 'khros bas /
NK069(tu)001:19023: gdug pa can zhe sdang gis 'khor ba de /
NK069(tu)001:19024: zhi bas 'dul bar mdzad pa de ni zhi mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19025: thugs rjes 'khros dpal rngam pa'i tshogs //
NK069(tu)001:19026: zhes de ltar thugs rjes 'khor ba de ni /
NK069(tu)001:19027: sems can thams cad kyi 'gon dang dpal du gyur pas na 'khro dpal /
NK069(tu)001:19028: don thugs ye shes yod myed dang brtag chad gzung 'dzin las /
NK069(tu)001:19030: sku yang khro zhing rngam pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:19031: sku che la yan lag rags pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:19032: zhal gdangs shing mche' ba rtsigs pa rngam pa'i dal gyi tshogs su bzhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:19033: 'bar ba'i byin brlabs smad po che //
NK069(tu)001:19034: zhes don rtogs pa dang thugs rje 'bar ba rnam gnyis dang ldan pa'i rtags /
NK069(tu)001:19035: sku las ye shes kyi me 'bar ba /
NK069(tu)001:19036: sku gsung thugs kyi byin brlabs sam /
NK069(tu)001:19038: gzhan gyis smad yang rang la dngos grub du 'byung bas /
NK069(tu)001:19039: cho 'phrul dang ngo mtshar smad du 'byung ba dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19040: da nyid du ni bdag la gsol //
NK069(tu)001:19041: zhes de dus myur du ltungs la da ltar nyid
NK069(tu)001:19042: du khyed kyi sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bdag
NK069(tu)001:19045: dngos grub skul ba 'di gsung gi dal du 'agro'am mi 'gro /
NK069(tu)001:19047: mi 'gro na yong du ma thang zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:19049: sngags kyis yang dngos grub skul ba las myed la /
NK069(tu)001:19050: 'dir tshig bshad 'dis yang dngos grub bskul ba kho na'i las byed pas na /
NK069(tu)001:19051: dngos grub bskul ba dang sngags la don la khyad par gang yang myed do //
NK069(tu)001:19052: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya stom /
NK069(tu)001:19053: zhes rgya skad kyi dngos grub gsol ba na /
NK069(tu)001:19054: rdo rje khro bo dam tshig dus la bab po zhe'o //
NK069(tu)001:19055: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya phata /
NK069(tu)001:19056: ces rdo rje khro bo'i dam tshig gis gdug pa can srod la sregs cig sreg pa /
NK069(tu)001:19057: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya ho /
NK069(tu)001:19058: zhes rdo rje khro bo'i dam tshig gis mnyes par mdzod cig /
NK069(tu)001:19060: a li bza' ba u li btung ba ta li 'bras bu sna tshogs /
NK069(tu)001:19064: gnyis myed byang chub sems kyis bstan par byas pa'i brdar yang bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:19065: tram tram go na ro'u tri /
NK069(tu)001:19066: tang tam ni mche' ba can te /
NK069(tu)001:19068: go'u na ro tri ni yon tan drag mo ste khro mo rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:19069: kha ram yo gi kha hi ho /
NK069(tu)001:19070: zhal 'bar ba'i rnal 'byor ma rnam ste khro mo nyi shu'o //
NK069(tu)001:19075: h+aum zhes pas ting nge 'dzin las skyed pa'i khro bo yab yum bcu dang /
NK069(tu)001:19076: spyan drangs pa gnyis su myed par sgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:19077: has dkar mo la sogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:19078: hes gdong mo la sogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:19079: phata kyis sgo ma la sogs stims la /
NK069(tu)001:19081: yang na yum gyi mkha' las 'don pa'i snying po yang bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:19084: 'gro ba rigs drug gi gnas na sdug pa can yod pa rnams la /
NK069(tu)001:19085: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad tshig /
NK069(tu)001:19086: las sngags ma h+aa can rda la sogs pas ru tra'i lus tshig /
NK069(tu)001:19087: rab tu ngag tshig tshig kun tu tshig go //
NK069(tu)001:19088: yid tshig nas sgrib pa dag pa ni las sngags kyi mathu'o //
NK069(tu)001:19092: zhes skyed pa'i sngags kyis skur gyur /
NK069(tu)001:19093: sku rab tu gsal bar gyur /
NK069(tu)001:19094: kun tu skur gyur pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:19095: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka la sogs pa'i nus mthus khro bo'i skur gsal bar gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:19096: thams cad du 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gyis gang /
NK069(tu)001:19098: kun tu gang bar gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:19099: zhes bstim pa'i h+aum ha he dang /
NK069(tu)001:19101: 'das pa ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:19102: skyed pa dam tshig khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs la /
NK069(tu)001:19103: gnyis su myed par stims pas gang /
NK069(tu)001:19104: gnyis myed kyi yon tan rgyas pas kun tu gang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:19105: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:19106: rtogs par bka' bas gsang ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:19108: ma nor bas de kho na nyid ma bcos pas nges pa /
NK069(tu)001:19109: khro bo'i tshogs chen po'i gsung gi dkyil 'khor spros pa'i le'u ste bcu drug pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19111: // sku khro tshul dang bcas pas khro bo'i /
NK069(tu)001:19112: gtso' 'khor du ma yod pas tshogs /
NK069(tu)001:19114: gsang sngags kyi snying po ni gsung gi sngags mang
NK069(tu)001:19115: por bshad pas na dkyil 'khor spros pas le'u ni
NK069(tu)001:19117: bcu drug pa 'o ni drangs kyi rnam grangs so //
NK069(tu)001:19118: 'dir ma nor bar rtogs pa'i go rims sdeb na gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:19119: zhi bzhag khro bzhengs su byed na dang /
NK069(tu)001:19120: zhi khro gnas 'gyur du byed na'o //
NK069(tu)001:19121: zhi khro gnas 'gyur du byed na /
NK069(tu)001:19122: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor la dmyigs nas /
NK069(tu)001:19123: brum zhes bya ba brjod pas /
NK069(tu)001:19124: zhi ba'i dal de nyid khro bo'i dal du rgyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:19125: zhi bzhag khro bzhengs su byed na /
NK069(tu)001:19127: de las dur khrod la gzhi' /
NK069(tu)001:19129: de'i dbus su keng rus kyi ri rab /
NK069(tu)001:19130: de steng du brum smug nag las /
NK069(tu)001:19131: gzhal yas khang me 'od 'bar bar skyed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19132: de'i dbus 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi ser po'am /
NK069(tu)001:19133: mdog mthun pa he ru ka yab yum bcu'i gnas /
NK069(tu)001:19134: rtsibs 'chan dmar po la ke'u ri bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:19135: mu khyud thod pas rtsig pa /
NK069(tu)001:19136: gru chad bzhi ser po la pu ka si la sogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:19137: bar khyams nang ma smug nag la phra mya na ma /
NK069(tu)001:19138: sgo la sgo ma bzhi bar khyams la dbang mo /
NK069(tu)001:19140: sku la ye shes kyi me skal pa 'jig pa'i dus kyi me lta bu 'bar bas so //
NK069(tu)001:19141: dkyil 'khor dbus kyi pho brang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud dang bcas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19142: de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po /
NK069(tu)001:19144: skur skyed pa ston pas de nas so //
NK069(tu)001:19145: khro bos gzhan gyi rgyud la yod pa'i bdud bzhi bcom pas bcom /
NK069(tu)001:19148: yab yum thabs dang shes rab kyi bde ba la dgyes pa /
NK069(tu)001:19149: mchog tu gyur pas chen po'o //
NK069(tu)001:19150: de dag gi dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:19151: rigs lnga'i khro bo de dag gi dkyil 'khor dgod pa'i rim pa /
NK069(tu)001:19152: ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa la bstan pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:19153: gdul bya'i don chen du ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:19155: gru chen bzhi sa ni rnam par rgyan //
NK069(tu)001:19156: zhes 'khor lo de'i phyi rim la /
NK069(tu)001:19157: thun mong gi bden pa gnyis dang /
NK069(tu)001:19158: lhag pa'i bden pa gnyis mtshon pa'i gru chad bzhis mdzes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19159: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis kyis mdzes //
NK069(tu)001:19160: zhes khro bo'i bar khyams nang ma smug nag la seng gdong ma la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19161: phyi ma phyogs mthun la dbang mo nyer brgyad do //
NK069(tu)001:19162: bar khyams kyis 'khor lo de rab tu mdzes par gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19163: gru bzhi sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan //
NK069(tu)001:19164: zhes phyi'i dbyibs gru bzhi sgo bzhi phyogs dang 'thun /
NK069(tu)001:19166: rta babs bzhi dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19167: rta babs ni mi ro khog skam la /
NK069(tu)001:19170: zhing chen gyi lpags pa'i gdugs dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19171: thod sbrul sna tshogs nyi zlas brjid //
NK069(tu)001:19172: ces yang na thod pa skam rlon gsum ni /
NK069(tu)001:19174: thod pa skam pos dbus kyi lte ba la rgyan /
NK069(tu)001:19175: sha ra ris phyi'i mu khyud la rgyan /
NK069(tu)001:19176: rlon pas mtshon sna lnga'i rtsig pa byas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:19177: thod pa'i dbang po lnga ye shes lnga yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:19178: dug lnga dag pa'i rdar sbrul lnga'i chun pos za rang tshags so //
NK069(tu)001:19179: ma rig pa'i mun pa sel ba'i phyir nyi ma
NK069(tu)001:19180: dang zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyis brjid par rgyan pa'o
NK069(tu)001:19182: thod pa skam po'i rtsig pa /
NK069(tu)001:19184: sbrul rigs bzhi'i za rang tshags /
NK069(tu)001:19185: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyis 'od gsal bar 'thong khung
NK069(tu)001:19186: lta bu byas pa ni shin tu yang brjid che
NK069(tu)001:19187: bar gnas pa'o // 'bar ba'i 'phro ba mang po 'khrug /
NK069(tu)001:19188: ces gzhal yas khang gi phyi rol na /
NK069(tu)001:19189: rdo rje 'bar ba'i rtsig pa byas pa /
NK069(tu)001:19190: me dpung 'bar ba'i tsha tsha skar ltar 'phro ba /
NK069(tu)001:19192: rtogs pa 'bar bas bag chags ngan pa thams cad sregs /
NK069(tu)001:19193: thugs rje 'bar bas gdug pa can gnas su sgrol
NK069(tu)001:19194: bas ye shes kyi me dpung rab tu 'bar ba'o
NK069(tu)001:19196: khyu mchog ma he stag dang gzig /
NK069(tu)001:19197: stobs kyi khyu mchog zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:19199: glang khyu ba ni 'bu ta he ru'i gdan no //
NK069(tu)001:19200: mi 'jigs ma he zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:19202: zhe sdang badz+ra he ru ka'i gdan no //
NK069(tu)001:19203: dpa' stul za byed stag zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:19204: nga rgyal che bas rat+na he ru ka'i gdan no //
NK069(tu)001:19205: klong yangs theg le gzig ni /
NK069(tu)001:19207: pad ma he ru ka'i gdan du 'os pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19208: gtum pa'i dom gyi spar bas na //
NK069(tu)001:19210: 'phrag dog che bas kar ma he ru ka'i gdan du byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19212: khyu mchog dang ma he la spar ba myed par /
NK069(tu)001:19213: spar bas gzung zhes pa dang 'gal zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:19215: spar ba myed yang ma shor bar mnan pa kho na gzung ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:19217: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK069(tu)001:19218: gtum pa dom gyi spar bas ni /
NK069(tu)001:19219: dregs pa chen po gtum tshogs gzhan /
NK069(tu)001:19222: dregs pa'i gdan ni dbang phyug lha chen la sogs gzung //
NK069(tu)001:19223: zhes sems can gdug pa can de dag gi 'og du dbus dbang phyug chen po pho mo /
NK069(tu)001:19224: shar lha chen po pho mo /
NK069(tu)001:19227: byang gnod sbyin pho mo ste /
NK069(tu)001:19228: dregs pa can rma phab nas /
NK069(tu)001:19229: rang rang gi zhon pas rang rang mnan /
NK069(tu)001:19230: de'i steng du he ru ka rnams bzhugs pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:19231: dbang phyug yang ches mnan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19232: mi gtong zhing thugs rjes 'khor bar 'khyams pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:19233: thabs mkhas pa'i ye shes kyi gzung ba'i brdar bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19234: sa'i khyad par sgrod pa'i gdan dang /
NK069(tu)001:19235: yon tan gyis che ba bcom pa'i gdan dang /
NK069(tu)001:19236: drag shul 'phrin las mdzad pa'i gnad las 'phrin las gdan no //
NK069(tu)001:19237: smug nag sngo nag ser nag dang //
NK069(tu)001:19238: 'bu ta he ru ka sku mdog ni smug nag go sku'i rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:19239: badz+ra he ru ka ni sngo nag go //
NK069(tu)001:19241: rad na he ru ka ni sku mdog ser nag go //
NK069(tu)001:19243: dmar nag ljang nag 'jig pa'i sku //
NK069(tu)001:19244: pad ma he ru ka ni dmar nag go //
NK069(tu)001:19245: gsung ngam dbang gi rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:19246: kar ma he ru ka ni sku mdog ljang nag go //
NK069(tu)001:19248: 'dir sku mdog nag po d+ha zhing tu ba stan pa ci zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:19249: drag po'i shas che ba la dgongs nas sku mdog yang nag po shas che bar bstan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19251: mi thung bis pa'i gzugs 'dra la /
NK069(tu)001:19252: ka ko la'i rkang lag rags pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19253: bdud dang gnod sbyin 'jigs pa'i tshul sku zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:19255: dang po ye shes bzhi dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:19257: sngo nag me long ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:19259: dmar nag so sor rtog pa /
NK069(tu)001:19260: ljang nag bya ba grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19261: gnyis pa nyon mongs pa lnga dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:19262: smug nag gti mug sngo nag zhe sdang /
NK069(tu)001:19266: gsum pa rigs dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:19272: bzhi pa thabs shes rab dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:19279: nag po ni mi 'gyur bas stong pa shes rab bo //
NK069(tu)001:19285: 'bras bu ni ye shes lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:19286: nyi shu rtsa gnyis su 'dus par ston pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19287: dbu' gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhir bsgrad //
NK069(tu)001:19288: ces dbu' gsum la yang gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:19293: sku gsum thugs su lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19297: dam tshig gis bzhi gzung bas /
NK069(tu)001:19299: spyod pas thabs kyis zhe sdang dag /
NK069(tu)001:19300: srung ba'i dam tshig gis 'dod chags dag go //
NK069(tu)001:19302: stong pa nyid kyi sgo sgoms pas zhal g.yas mi rtog pa chos sku /
NK069(tu)001:19303: grub pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis g.yon sprul sku /
NK069(tu)001:19304: thabs la mkhas pa'i sgos longs sku'o //
NK069(tu)001:19306: rgyud drug gi sa bon dag pa ni phyag drug du snang ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:19308: pha rol du phyin pa drug te /
NK069(tu)001:19309: pha rol du phyin pa drug gis rgyud drug du
NK069(tu)001:19310: 'khyams pa'i sems can rnams 'don pa'i brdar bstan no
NK069(tu)001:19311: // rgyu tshad med pa bzhi bsgoms pas /
NK069(tu)001:19312: lam du byas pas zhabs bzhir shar te /
NK069(tu)001:19314: don sgrod du med pa'i gnas su sgrod par byed par byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19315: de yang byams pa ni yid dang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:19316: snying rjes ni yid dga' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:19317: dga' bas ni yid chags pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19318: btang snyoms kyis ni yid mi 'byed pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:19319: des ru tra la sogs pa gdul ba'i sems can
NK069(tu)001:19320: dregs pa can 'khor ba nas sgrol ba'i brda' zhabs
