NK069(tu)001:19321: so // kor rlon gos ni sna tshogs glang chen gyi ko ba rlon pa gyon //
NK069(tu)001:19324: bdud bzhi las rgyal ba'i rtags su dpa' rtags stag spags 'gong gi sham thabs so //
NK069(tu)001:19325: gsung gi sgra rngam pa'i sgra chen 'jigs par sgrogs //
NK069(tu)001:19326: zhes thugs ye shes yod med rtag chad kyi mtha' la rngam pa'i rtags /
NK069(tu)001:19327: h'u h'u dang phata phata dang ha la ha la'i sgra 'jigs pa sgrogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19328: thugs kyi don sbrul dang thod 'phreng nyi zlas chas //
NK069(tu)001:19329: zhes rgyal rigs dbu la rgyan /
NK069(tu)001:19334: thod pa skam po dbu' la /
NK069(tu)001:19336: phyed mas snyan la rgyan no //
NK069(tu)001:19340: chas dgu don rtags dang sbyar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:19341: 'bras bu sku lnga dang sbyar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:19342: chas dgu' don rtags dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:19343: dang po gon pa'i gos gsum ni /
NK069(tu)001:19344: gti mug bdud 'dul glang po'i ko rlon dang /
NK069(tu)001:19345: zhing pags g.yang gzhi' tshul khrims kyi gos dang /
NK069(tu)001:19346: dpa' za byed stag gi sham thabs gsum ni /
NK069(tu)001:19347: glang po'i ko ba ni thang ba lta bu /
NK069(tu)001:19348: zhing dpags kyi chos gos lta bu /
NK069(tu)001:19349: stag pags kyi sham thabs te sprul sku nyan thos kyi chos dang sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:19351: dpa' rjed gnyen gcug sbrul gyi rgyan ni /
NK069(tu)001:19352: sbrul rigs lnga dbu' dang phyag zhabs lhu tshigs rgyan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19353: dbang 'chad sgrol ba thod pa'i rgyan ni /
NK069(tu)001:19354: sku gsung thob pa la dbang /
NK069(tu)001:19355: theg gsum 'chad pa thod pa tshar gsum gyi rgyan no //
NK069(tu)001:19356: thabs dang shes rab nyi zla'i chas so //
NK069(tu)001:19357: gdab pa'i tshom bu gsum ni /
NK069(tu)001:19358: rag ta thugs rje chags pa'i rgyan /
NK069(tu)001:19359: gzi' chen don dam bcud kyi rgyan /
NK069(tu)001:19360: thal ba 'dul byed 'phrin las kyi rgyan no //
NK069(tu)001:19361: 'bras bu sku lnga dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:19363: dur khrod rgyan gyis rgyan pa ni //
NK069(tu)001:19365: zhi ba phyogs gcig mya ngan zlo //
NK069(tu)001:19366: mngon par rdzogs pa'i sku snyems so //
NK069(tu)001:19368: khams gsum dbang du sdus nas ni //
NK069(tu)001:19369: sprul pa'i sku la mnga' snyems so //
NK069(tu)001:19370: thod pa phyed tshal 'phreng bas ni //
NK069(tu)001:19371: dug gsum bdud rtsir sbyor ba'i rde //
NK069(tu)001:19372: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku snyems pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19373: zhing chen rlon pa'i na bza' ni /
NK069(tu)001:19374: chos dbyings mnyam pa chen po ste //
NK069(tu)001:19375: chos kyi sku la mnga' snyems so //
NK069(tu)001:19376: stag pags g.yang gzhi'i sham thabs ni //
NK069(tu)001:19377: 'phrin las rnam bzhi'i rang bzhin te /
NK069(tu)001:19378: rdo rje sku la mnga' snyems so //
NK069(tu)001:19379: sbrul nag chun 'chang mang po ni //
NK069(tu)001:19380: ye shes thams cad 'byung ba'i rtags //
NK069(tu)001:19381: rtag chen sku la mnga' snyems so //
NK069(tu)001:19384: zhes b+hu ta he ru ka'i phyag gi /
NK069(tu)001:19385: stong gi 'jig rten gling bzhi'i ri rab lcags ris 'khor yug dang bcas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:19387: bsam gtan gyi pha rol du phyin pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:19388: stong gi 'jig rten gling bzhi ri rab dang bcas pa de'i don mdzad pa'i rtags su /
NK069(tu)001:19389: chos kyi 'khor lo skor zhing 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:19390: stong gi 'jig rten las kyi rigs dang sbyar /
NK069(tu)001:19391: 'khor lo ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:19392: b+hu ta he ru ka'i phyag mtshan no //
NK069(tu)001:19393: rdo rje dung chen bkang ba dang //
NK069(tu)001:19394: zhes rdo rje ni ye shes kyi pha rol du phyin pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:19395: rdo rje'i rang bzhin ni mi 'gyur ba'i don stong pa nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:19396: las ni 'bigs shing 'joms par byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19397: de yang ye shes rdo rje lta bus /
NK069(tu)001:19400: rang bzhin stong pa nyid du gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19401: badz+ra he ru ka'i phyag mtshan no //
NK069(tu)001:19402: yab yum kun gyi g.yon na /
NK069(tu)001:19403: ban ta ni bzod pa'i pha rol du phyin pa dang sbyar te /
NK069(tu)001:19404: ban d+ha zlum po na chos nyid spros pa dang bral ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:19406: dbang po lnga ni ye shes rnam pa lnga yin te /
NK069(tu)001:19407: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19408: de bas na dung chen zhes pa ni ban d+ha mtshan ldan no //
NK069(tu)001:19409: bkang ba ni khrag gis skang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:19410: khrag ni thugs rje chags pa'i rtags te /
NK069(tu)001:19411: dbyings ye shes kyis 'khor ba la thugs rjes chags pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19412: lha thams cad kyi phyag g.yon na snams so ////
NK069(tu)001:19413: 'bu ta he ru kas gtso' byas nas gnas 'phrog rtses na /
NK069(tu)001:19414: 'bu ta he ru ka'i g.yas dang po 'khor yug /
NK069(tu)001:19427: rang na he ru ka ni /
NK069(tu)001:19447: tha ma stong gi 'jig rten 'khor yug dang bcas pa snams pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:19448: rtsa ba'i rgyud nyid kyi gnas 'phrog rtsis pa'o ////
NK069(tu)001:19449: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:19450: 'dir zhal gsum phyag drug du bshad nas /
NK069(tu)001:19452: de rtsa ba'i rgyud yin pas rgyas par ma bshad de /
NK069(tu)001:19453: bsogs zhes pa'i khongs su tshang bar yod pa'i shes pas te /
NK069(tu)001:19455: sgyu 'phrul bla ma dang bshad pa'i rgyud yin pas rgyas par bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:19456: ral gri dgra sta bshol la sogs //
NK069(tu)001:19458: ral gri ni brtson 'grus kyi pha rol du phyin pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:19459: ral gri'i so gnyis yod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:19460: ye shes kyi sos ni chos nyid kyi don rtogs nas mya ngan las 'das pa'i mtha' cod la /
NK069(tu)001:19461: thugs rje'i sos ni sems can gyi don mdzad cing 'khor ba'i 'tha' cod do //
NK069(tu)001:19462: karma he ru ka'i phyag mtshan no //
NK069(tu)001:19464: dgra sta ni stobs kyi pha rol du phyin pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:19465: nyon mongs pa'i dgra la thugs rje chen pos cod pas te /
NK069(tu)001:19466: pad+ma'i rigs pad+ma he ru ka'o //
NK069(tu)001:19468: thong bshol thabs kyi pha rol du phyin pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:19469: chos kyi dbyings kyi zhing sa la /
NK069(tu)001:19470: ye shes kyi bshol kyis rmos /
NK069(tu)001:19471: yod med kyi mthar rol cing zlog pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:19472: 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan gyi sprul pa phyogs bcur 'phro ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:19475: kha t+wam stobs kyi pha rol du phyin pa /
NK069(tu)001:19476: zhing dbyug sbyin pa'i pha rol du phyin pa /
NK069(tu)001:19477: rda shes rab kyi pha rol du phyin pa /
NK069(tu)001:19478: pad+ma tshul khrims kyi pha rol du phyin pa /
NK069(tu)001:19479: rin po che sbyin pa'i pha rol du phyin pa'o ////
NK069(tu)001:19480: badz+ra he ru kas gtso bo byas nas gnas 'phrog rtses na /
NK069(tu)001:19481: badz+ra he ru ka'i g.yas dang po rdo rje /
NK069(tu)001:19487: b+hu ta he ru ka'i g.yas dang po 'khor yug /
NK069(tu)001:19507: karma he ru ka'i g.yas dang po ral gri /
NK069(tu)001:19516: lhor skor nas gnas 'phrogs pa des shes so //
NK069(tu)001:19517: rtsa rgyud du 'di rang du tshang bar gnas 'phrog par brtsi /
NK069(tu)001:19518: bshad rgyud du bsogs khongs su don bgrol lo //
NK069(tu)001:19519: rang gi las cha sna tshogs dang //
NK069(tu)001:19522: rdo rje rdo rje dril bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:19525: badz+ra he ru ka la g.yas g.yon dang po rdo rje dril bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:19526: bar ma rdo rje dung dmar /
NK069(tu)001:19528: de bzhin 'khor lo dgra sta dang /
NK069(tu)001:19531: 'bu ta'i g.yas g.yon dang po 'khor lo dgra sta /
NK069(tu)001:19532: bar ma rdo rje dung dmar /
NK069(tu)001:19533: tha ma sti ra kha tang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:19534: nor bu rin chen rgyu zhags dang //
NK069(tu)001:19535: rdo rje dgra sta rab du stobs //
NK069(tu)001:19537: ran+ta g.yas g.yon dang po rin chen rgyu zhags /
NK069(tu)001:19538: bar ma rdo rje dung dmar /
NK069(tu)001:19539: tha ma bra ta re dang dgra sta'o //
NK069(tu)001:19540: chags mchog pad+ma che po dang //
NK069(tu)001:19541: dril bu rnga yi sgra sgrogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19543: pad+ma he ru ka'i g.yas g.yon dang po pad+ma dril bu /
NK069(tu)001:19544: bar ma rdo rje ban d+ha /
NK069(tu)001:19545: tha ma ti ra rnge'u chung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:19546: las ni ral gri bshol chen dang //
NK069(tu)001:19549: karma he ru ka g.yas g.yon dang po ral gri bshol /
NK069(tu)001:19550: bar ma rdo rje dung dmar /
NK069(tu)001:19551: tha ma ti ra 'jig rten no //
NK069(tu)001:19552: bar la ni rdo rje dung dmar 'khrug /
NK069(tu)001:19553: ti ra chen po rab tu stobs /
NK069(tu)001:19554: zhes pas khro bo kun gyi /
NK069(tu)001:19555: bar ma gnyis rdo rje dung dmar /
NK069(tu)001:19556: g.yas kyi tha ma na ti ra'i dbyug pa snams pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19560: spyad par bya ba'i don gyis na btsun mo //
NK069(tu)001:19561: khro mo'i skur snang bas na 'jigs pa'i tshogs ni /
NK069(tu)001:19573: sems can gyi gnas na rnam par shes pa bzhi
NK069(tu)001:19574: gnas su dag pa ko'u re la sogs pa bzhi
NK069(tu)001:19575: dang / dbang po bzhi gnas su dag pa /
NK069(tu)001:19577: yul ni de'i yul gzugs sgra la sogs pa bzhi
NK069(tu)001:19578: gnas su dag pa seng nga la sogs bzhi dang
NK069(tu)001:19579: / dus bzhi gnas su dag pa kri ta la sogs pa bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:19580: ma mo brgyad kyi sku dang /
NK069(tu)001:19581: 'phra men ma brgyad kyi sku ni phyag rgya'o ////
NK069(tu)001:19584: ko'u ri ban dmar byi dbyug sngo //
NK069(tu)001:19585: gatso'u ri mda' gzhu' 'gengs ma ser //
NK069(tu)001:19586: pra mo chu srin rgyal mtshan dmar //
NK069(tu)001:19587: pe ta byi za rdor 'phyar nag /
NK069(tu)001:19588: pu ka dmar ser byi rgyu 'dren //
NK069(tu)001:19590: sman sha 'thing nag byi snying za //
NK069(tu)001:19591: tsan d+ha ser skya mchog lus 'brel //
NK069(tu)001:19592: ces pa gnas kyi ma mo la'o //
NK069(tu)001:19594: seng nga kha ro snol ser po //
NK069(tu)001:19595: byang kri gnas lha snol mar rngag /
NK069(tu)001:19596: kri la nag mo byi rngag wa //
NK069(tu)001:19597: sho na dral ta mthing ka kyi //
NK069(tu)001:19598: kri ta dkar ser rgyur mgo' rgod //
NK069(tu)001:19599: rkang ka zhing phrag snar 'go' ring //
NK069(tu)001:19600: kha kha kha ro bon gri nag /
NK069(tu)001:19601: hu lu lcags kyu dung tshogs 'ug /
NK069(tu)001:19602: ces pa yul gyi 'phra men brgyad la'o //
NK069(tu)001:19603: he ru ka'i gal po'i sdom tshig go //
NK069(tu)001:19604: bshad rgyud bla ma nas bshad pa de le'u bco lnga par bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:19605: sgo bzhi'i phyag rgya rab mdzes shing //
NK069(tu)001:19608: phyin ci log bzhi gnas su dag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:19611: stag gdong dkar mo lcags kyu 'dren //
NK069(tu)001:19612: phag gdong nag mo mche' zhags can //
NK069(tu)001:19613: lcags sgrog dmar mo nyi zla'i spyan //
NK069(tu)001:19614: thal byed dril bu sna tshogs mdog /
NK069(tu)001:19615: ces gal po nas gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:19616: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK069(tu)001:19620: slas ni chun mar byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19621: byi mo ni dregs pa can ma tshor bar dpal gyis bkog du dbang du byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19622: bran mo ni dkyil 'khor gyi phyi rim du bkod nas lhag ma za zhing /
NK069(tu)001:19623: ci bgyi' zhes bran du khas blangs so //
NK069(tu)001:19624: de rnams kyi nang nas gtso' mo ni /
NK069(tu)001:19625: bcu gnyis dang ni brgyad kyis mdzes //
NK069(tu)001:19627: bcu tshan gnyis la nyi shu tham pa /
NK069(tu)001:19628: brgyad ni de'i steng du brgyad de /
NK069(tu)001:19631: dkyil 'khor bar khyams phyi ma la bkod pas /
NK069(tu)001:19632: dkyil 'khor gyi brgyan du bsnang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:19633: rang gi bstan dang lag cha dang //
NK069(tu)001:19636: za 'ug gi steng na zhing skyang pa re re'o //
NK069(tu)001:19640: srin mo smug nag rdo rje thod rlon 'chang /
NK069(tu)001:19641: ces pa la sogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:19643: mkha' 'gro zhal cig phyag drug du bshad pa la
NK069(tu)001:19644: sogs pa le'u bco' lnga par bshad pa' gsal lo
NK069(tu)001:19645: // ci bgyi' zhes ni chas te gnas //
NK069(tu)001:19648: dpal chen po dang dbyer med par gnas pa'i rnal
NK069(tu)001:19649: 'byor pa'i las thams cad la brtson zhing dang du
NK069(tu)001:19650: len pa'i phyir na ci bgyi' zhes byon de dal
NK069(tu)001:19651: du gnas pa'o // zhes brjod pas /
NK069(tu)001:19652: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad du /
NK069(tu)001:19653: 'gro ba rigs drug gi 'jig rten drug gi re re'i phyogs bcu thams cad du /
NK069(tu)001:19654: 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad kun tu gsal bar 'gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:19656: 'bar ba ni thugs la ye shes yes stong pa 'bar /
NK069(tu)001:19658: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gdul bya'i snang ba la gsal bar gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:19659: gsang pa snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:19660: rtog par ka bas gsang ba bcu 'dus pas snying po /
NK069(tu)001:19661: ma nor bas de kho na nyid /
NK069(tu)001:19663: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu bdun pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19665: // sku khro tshul dang babs shing 'bar ba'i gar dgu
NK069(tu)001:19666: dang ldan pas na khro bo de'i sku'i dkyil dakhora
NK069(tu)001:19667: gdul bya la bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu bdun pa'o
NK069(tu)001:19668: // de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:19671: mchod pas mnyes par byed pas de nas so //
NK069(tu)001:19674: mchong mkhan bdag dang gsum dbyer med par gnas pa'i dgyes pa chen po te /
NK069(tu)001:19675: ston pa bcom ldan 'das nyid dgyes pa dang ldan pas na chen po'o //
NK069(tu)001:19676: mnyes pa'i mchod pa chen po 'di ched du brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:19679: rmad du byung ba'i mchod pa bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:19684: theg pa 'og ma ba las khyad par du gyur pas na chen po /
NK069(tu)001:19685: de lta bu rtogs par bka' ba 'di rtogs par bya ba'i phyir brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:19686: de la mchod sbyin dam pa 'di //
NK069(tu)001:19688: de lta bu'i mchod pa byed de la /
NK069(tu)001:19689: de bzhin gshegs pa la mchod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:19690: sems can la sbyin pa gtang ba'i thabs dam pa 'di zhe 'am /
NK069(tu)001:19691: yang na sangs rgyas rnams la mchod /
NK069(tu)001:19693: 'khor gsum yongs su dag pas dam pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19694: thog mar bdag nyid rtog bsgoms bsgral //
NK069(tu)001:19696: rtogs pas bdag sgral ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:19697: dang po'am thog mar bdag nyid kyis /
NK069(tu)001:19698: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:19699: rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyi chos thams
NK069(tu)001:19700: cad sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas
NK069(tu)001:19701: pa'i rang bzhin du dbyer med par gcig pa'i don
NK069(tu)001:19702: / shes rab kyis kyang tshig tsam ma yin par rtogs la /
NK069(tu)001:19703: rtogs pa de'i don la ting nges kyang rtse gcig du bsgoms pas /
NK069(tu)001:19704: rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:19705: ci spyad kyang skyon gyis mi gos pa de la ni rtogs pas bdag sgral lo //
NK069(tu)001:19706: de nas gnyes med blo yis ni //
NK069(tu)001:19708: de nas thugs rjes gzhan sgral ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:19709: gong gi gnyis su med par rtogs pa'i shes rab kyi blo dang ldan pa de yis ni /
NK069(tu)001:19710: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK069(tu)001:19712: gnyis su med pa'i don ma rtogs pa'i blo 'khor ba 'am 'jig rten na gnas pa la /
NK069(tu)001:19713: snying rje chen pos de bla na med pa'i byang chub du sgral bar dam bcas pa la /
NK069(tu)001:19714: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK069(tu)001:19717: ye shes kyi lha dang gnyis su med par sgral bar bya /
NK069(tu)001:19718: de yang rdo rje 'dzin pa yab yum thabs shes
NK069(tu)001:19719: rab gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems kyis dbang
NK069(tu)001:19720: bskur nas / rgyal ba'i rigs nges pa'i sras su sgral zhing gnas spar bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:19721: sgrol ba zhes bya ba'i dpe' ni /
NK069(tu)001:19722: dper na chu chen po la /
NK069(tu)001:19725: yang na gru gtong ba'i skya thabs la mkhas pa zhig gis /
NK069(tu)001:19727: rdzas kyang pha rol du thon la /
NK069(tu)001:19728: rang yang chur mi 'chi' ba yin no //
NK069(tu)001:19729: yang skyal yang mi shes la /
NK069(tu)001:19730: gru gtong ba'i skya thabs la yang mi mkhas na /
NK069(tu)001:19731: rdzas kyang pha rol du mi sgrol la /
NK069(tu)001:19734: bdag shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin du mi ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:19736: sgral ba bya ba'i yul de yang gnas mi stobs la /
NK069(tu)001:19737: bdag kyang sgrib pas gos nas rtag chad kyi mthar 'chi ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:19738: de bas mchos thams cad mnyam pa nyid kyi don
NK069(tu)001:19739: shes rab kyis kyang tshig tsam ma yin par rtogs
NK069(tu)001:19740: la / rtogs pa'i don la ting nge 'dzin gyis kyang rtse gcig du sgoms nas /
NK069(tu)001:19741: rtogs pa'i don mngon du gyur pa'i shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin du ldan pas sgral na ni /
NK069(tu)001:19742: gang sgral ba yang gnas stobs la /
NK069(tu)001:19743: bdag nyid kyang sgrib pas mi gos kyi steng du yang thar pa'i grogs chen por 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:19744: 'khril pa'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK069(tu)001:19746: sbyor ba'i mchod pa'i don ni /
NK069(tu)001:19747: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med par 'khril /
NK069(tu)001:19748: rtags yab yum thabs shes rab gnyis su med par 'khril /
NK069(tu)001:19749: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med par mnyam pa'i
NK069(tu)001:19750: lhag pa'i byang chub sems sbyor ba'i mchod pas mchod
NK069(tu)001:19751: pa de ni / mchod pa thams cad kyi nang
NK069(tu)001:19752: na nan tan gyi mchod pa yin pas mchod chen
NK069(tu)001:19753: pa de ni / no // de gang las byung na /
NK069(tu)001:19754: yab yum dgongs pa thams cad tshang ba'i dbang po mnyam par sbyor ba las byung bas na /
NK069(tu)001:19756: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya //
NK069(tu)001:19758: de ltar byang chub sems bde' ba chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:19759: bdag nyid mchod cing mnyes pas /
NK069(tu)001:19760: ye shes kyi lha la yang mchod cing mnyes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:19761: mnyam pa'i grub rdzas chen po dag /
NK069(tu)001:19764: bsgrub par bya ba'i rgyal ba rigs lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:19765: rten par bya ba'i dam rdzas lnga dbyer med pa mnyam pa'i rdzas /
NK069(tu)001:19766: lnga po de la ni grub pa bzhi'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pas na grub pa'i rdzas zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:19767: rdzas de nyid sangs rgyas rigs lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:19768: dbyer med par lus la khams bdud rtsir gnas pas na chen po'o //
NK069(tu)001:19769: ye nas rigs lngar sangs rgyas pas dag ces bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:19770: mnyam sbyor ni mnyam pa bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:19771: dang po lus mnyam pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:19772: yab yum gnyis ka lus skyes pa'i rim pa bsgom nus par mnyam pas /
NK069(tu)001:19773: dbang po snol mar byin gyis rlob nus sam /
NK069(tu)001:19774: gnyis pa dag mnyam pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:19775: yab yum gnyis ka zlas brjod snying po 'dra ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:19776: gsum pa 'dod pa mnyam pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:19777: yab ni yum la rten nas sangs rgyas thob par 'dod /
NK069(tu)001:19778: yum yab la rten nas sangs rgyas thob par 'dod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19779: bzhi pa gnas dang man ngag mnyam pa ni gnyis ste /
NK069(tu)001:19782: gnas dag pa ni gnyis ste /
NK069(tu)001:19786: lta spyod dam tshig gis rang rgyud la gos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19787: yum dag pa ni gnyis ste /
NK069(tu)001:19788: skye bas dag pa dang sbyangs pas dag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19794: lcug phran ma ste mtshan dang ldan pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19796: thos bsam gyis rgyud sbyangs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:19797: sdom pas rgyud dag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:19798: dbang gis smin par byas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:19799: sbyong ba'i man ngag gis dag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19800: man ngag gis zin pa ni lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:19805: mthar mi nyams par srung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:19811: bde bral gyi bde' ba la theg le bzung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:19813: lhan gcig skyes pa pa'i bde ba las gyen du spyi bor log go //
NK069(tu)001:19814: de nyid khyab par bya ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:19815: lus yongs la khyab par dgram pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19816: mthar zag med kyi bde' ba de mi nyams par bsrung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:19817: de lta bur mnyam par sbyar nas /
NK069(tu)001:19818: bdag nyid yab yum gnyis longs spyod bdag mnyes /
NK069(tu)001:19819: sangs rgyas yum gyi mkha' la spyan drangs nas mchod pas sangs rgyas kyang mnyes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19820: grub pa ni grub pa bzhi'i mtshan nyid de /
NK069(tu)001:19821: dang po chos nyid ngo bo nyid kyis grub pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:19822: kun gyis sgrub cing don du gnyer bar bya ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:19824: chos nyid ma skyes pa gang yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:19825: kun gyis smad cing bsrung bar bya ba'i dam rdzas lnga'i chos nyid ma skyes pa gang yin pa /
NK069(tu)001:19826: ma skyes pa'i ngang du dbyer med cing tha mi dad pas ni /
NK069(tu)001:19827: chos nyid ngo bo nyid kyis grub pa zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:19828: gnyis pa chos can rang gi mtshan nyid kyis grub pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:19829: rang gi mtshan nyid kyis grub pa'i chos nyid med pas /
NK069(tu)001:19832: a ru ra dang dur byid kyis ci ste 'khru ba med ces pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19833: me rang gi mtshan nyid kyis sreg la /
NK069(tu)001:19834: chus rang gi mtshan nyid kyis 'dag /
NK069(tu)001:19835: a ru ra dang dur byid rang gi mtshan nyid kyis 'khru' /
NK069(tu)001:19836: de bas na rang gi mtshan nyid kyis grub pa'i chos med do //
NK069(tu)001:19837: 'on tang dam rdzas lnga po 'di rten pas ci te 'grub bya ba med de /
NK069(tu)001:19838: dam rdzas 'di rten pas rang gi mtshan nyid kyis 'grub cing /
NK069(tu)001:19840: chos can rang gi mtshan nyid kyis grub pa zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:19841: gsum pa ting nge 'dzin gyis grub pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:19842: 'das pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyis kyang dam rdzas rnam
NK069(tu)001:19843: pa lnga pa 'di'i rang bzhin mkhyen cing thugs su
NK069(tu)001:19844: chud nas / sngags dang phyag rgya dang /
NK069(tu)001:19845: ting nge 'dzin gyis byin gyis rlabs nas /
NK069(tu)001:19846: rten cing dang du blangs pa'i mthu' mnyes la /
NK069(tu)001:19847: da lta dang ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pas kyang /
NK069(tu)001:19848: dam rdzas lnga po 'di'i rang bzhin rtogs par byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:19849: sngags dang phyag rgya dang ting nge 'dzin gyis byin gyis rlabs pa'i 'thus /
NK069(tu)001:19851: byin gyis rlabs kyis kyang grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19853: dam rdzas 'di dag la so so'i grub pa re re yod de /
NK069(tu)001:19854: de yang sha chen rten pas 'thu' che /
NK069(tu)001:19857: byang chub sems kyis tshe ring /
NK069(tu)001:19858: dri chen gyis mdze' thub pas so //
NK069(tu)001:19859: de bas na nus 'thus grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19860: de yang thal ba'i rgyud las /
NK069(tu)001:19861: dngos po ma lus sems nyid phyir //
NK069(tu)001:19862: mtshan nyid bral ba chos kyi dbyings //
NK069(tu)001:19863: rang bzhin bde ba'i ye shes lnga //
NK069(tu)001:19864: byed pa med rang snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:19865: shes rab ting 'dzin thabs dag gi //
NK069(tu)001:19867: 'di lta'i lam la gang gnas pa //
NK069(tu)001:19868: phyogs dus kun nas byin gyis barloba //
NK069(tu)001:19869: zhes gsungs pas legs par gsal lo ////
NK069(tu)001:19870: gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:19871: rdzas gzhan la grub pa med par /
NK069(tu)001:19872: dam rdzas lnga la grub pa yong ba ci zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:19874: rdzas gzhan la grub yod yang ma smos ste /
NK069(tu)001:19875: rdzas gzhan la mi rtsang ba'i rtog pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:19876: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga la rtsang rme'i rtog pa
NK069(tu)001:19877: bsal ba'i phyir grub pa bzhi smos pa yin no
NK069(tu)001:19878: // bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK069(tu)001:19880: de ltar bsgrub pa chen po bdud rtsi lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:19881: bdag kyang rten cing spyad la /
NK069(tu)001:19882: bdag dang bde bar gshegs pa don dam par ma bskyes par mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:19883: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid du mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:19884: don dam pa dang kun rdzob kyang dbyings med par mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:19885: de ltar bdag dang lha thams cad nas thams cad
NK069(tu)001:19886: du dbyer med par mnyam pa'i bde bar gshegs pa
NK069(tu)001:19887: la 'bul lo // bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo' //
NK069(tu)001:19889: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga chos nyid kyi rkyen du rig pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:19891: chos nyid ma skyes pa'i rgyan du gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19892: bza' ba ni bshos dang krums la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19894: yos kyi rnam pa mang sa la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19895: btung ba ni chang gi rnam pa mang po la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19898: khro bo'i dur khrod chas brgyad la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19899: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni //
NK069(tu)001:19901: mdor na 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:19902: gzugs ni lha mo dkar mo me long thogs par byin gyis brlab /
NK069(tu)001:19903: de bzhin du sgra ni sngon mo pi wang thogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:19904: dri ni ser mo spos khang thogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:19905: ro ni dmar mo zhal zas thogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:19906: rig ni ljang khu lha'i na bza' thogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:19907: chos ni mthing ka gru gsum thogs par byin rlab te /
NK069(tu)001:19908: mdor na 'dod pa'i longs spyod lnga dang ldan pa thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:19909: lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor rang rang thim par dbul bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:19911: zhes bdag kyang lha'i dkyil 'khor du bsgoms la /
NK069(tu)001:19912: zas dang longs spyod kyang lha'i dkyil 'khor du byin gyis brlabs la /
NK069(tu)001:19914: chos nyid la chos nyid thim pa'i tshul du mchod do //
NK069(tu)001:19915: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:19916: de ltar mchod pa'i yon tan ni /
NK069(tu)001:19919: bde' gshegs yon tan smad po che //
NK069(tu)001:19920: bde bar gshegs pa'i yon tan sku dang ye shes ni /
NK069(tu)001:19921: ngo mtshar rmad du byung bas na smad po che yin la /
NK069(tu)001:19922: gzhan nas yod pa ma yin te //
NK069(tu)001:19923: de yang gzhan na yod pa ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:19924: rang la rang chas su yod pas /
NK069(tu)001:19925: gong ma ltar mchod pa byas pas /
NK069(tu)001:19926: sangs rgyas kyi che ba'i yon tan yang 'grub par 'gyur na /
NK069(tu)001:19927: lha srin la sogs smos ci dgos //
NK069(tu)001:19930: mi'i rgyal srid lta bu dang /
NK069(tu)001:19936: lha dang mi'i rgyal srid la sogs pa 'grub par lta smos kyang ci dgos zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:19937: 'grub pa the tshom mi za ba'i tshig go //
NK069(tu)001:19938: rnal 'byor las su rung rnams kyis //
NK069(tu)001:19940: de grub pa'i rgyu bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:19942: lha'i rnal 'byor gyis ting nge 'dzin las su rung ba rnams kyi ni /
NK069(tu)001:19943: sgrub pa'i thabs kyang 'di kho na lta bu yin la /
NK069(tu)001:19945: grub pa'i 'bras bu yang 'grub nges bya ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:19946: yid gnyis med pa dang ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:19947: 'grub nges pa'i gdong gis gcad de sgrub bo ////
NK069(tu)001:19949: mtshan nyid kyi lugs ltar na /
NK069(tu)001:19950: chos nyid kyi mtshan ma thams cad ni zhi ba /
NK069(tu)001:19951: sus kyang ma bcos pa'i don gyi rnal ma la /
NK069(tu)001:19952: de rtogs pa'i ye shes lhag 'thong rig pa'i blos 'byor bas rnal 'byor /
NK069(tu)001:19954: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa /
NK069(tu)001:19955: mtshan ma med pa'i ngang las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:19956: sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan ma'i rnam par yang gsal la /
NK069(tu)001:19957: mtshan ma gsal btsam na mtshan ma med pa'i ngang las ma g.yos ste /
NK069(tu)001:19958: mtshan ma dang mtshan ma med pa gnyis med pa'i don ni /
NK069(tu)001:19959: ma bcos rnal ma yin la /
NK069(tu)001:19960: de ni sangs rgyas dang sku gsung thugs kyi chos thams cad kyi ngang du 'byor ba 'am /
NK069(tu)001:19961: yangs sangs rgyas dang chos thams cad de'i rang bzhin du 'byor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:19962: ma h+aa yo ga ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:19963: yab yum thabs dang shes rab dbyer med pa'i don gyi rnal ma la /
NK069(tu)001:19964: che ba'i yon tan gyi dngos grub phun sum tshogs par 'byor pas na rnal 'byor ro //
NK069(tu)001:19966: sems dang sems snang ba'i chos thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:19969: ye nas sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:19971: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin du 'byor ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:19972: chos thams cad sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du 'byor ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:19973: de lta bu'i rnal 'byor gyi don rtogs shing zhes bya ba'i don no //
NK069(tu)001:19974: phyag rgya chen por rdzogs gyur cing //
NK069(tu)001:19976: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyar bsgoms pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:19977: yo byad rdzogs par ma lus par gyur cing /
NK069(tu)001:19978: gsal ba'i yid gnyis med pa na //
NK069(tu)001:19980: mnyam pa nyid kyi shes rab gsal ba'i sgrub pa'i thabs ni /
NK069(tu)001:19981: de ltar yin nam ma yin nam /
NK069(tu)001:19982: grub bam mi grub bam gyi yid rtse gnyis med pas sgrubs na /
NK069(tu)001:19985: dkyil 'khor chen po 'od 'bar ba yang 'grub par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:19986: de nas bzod sbyor sgrol la sogs pa'i gzhan don bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:19988: mnyes pa chen pos 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu thams cad du khyab par gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:19989: gsang pa snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:19990: mchod sbyin bde bar gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor la mchod cing /
NK069(tu)001:19991: sems can la sbyin pa'i thabs dam pa bstan pa'i le'u ste bac+wo'a brgyad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:19993: // de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:19995: bsgrub pa bya ba'i dam tshig rigs lngas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:19996: mi spang ba'i dam tshig nyon mongs pa lnga ye shes su gsal bas nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:19997: shes par bya ba'i dam tshig phung po dang khams
NK069(tu)001:19998: dang skye mched lha dang lha mo'i rang bzhin 'dis
NK069(tu)001:20000: dang du blang ba'i dam tshig dam rdzas lha'i bu'i bdud bcom mo //
NK069(tu)001:20001: mchod pa byed pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis srung ba'i dam tshig ston pas na de nas /
NK069(tu)001:20003: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyams pa la dgyes /
NK069(tu)001:20004: don yod par bya ba'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:20005: dam tshig dag cing rtsang na sgrubs pa'i 'bras bu chud mi za bar bsgrubs pas na /
NK069(tu)001:20006: lam dang 'bras bu la don yod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20007: dam tshig chen po 'di ched du brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:20008: zhes don yod pa ni dam tshig gi dgos chad de /
NK069(tu)001:20009: gong du byang chub sems skyed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20011: spyan drangs shing mchod pa dbul ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:20013: 'og nas 'byung ba'i las rnam bzhi rtsam pa la sogs pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:20014: dam la mi gnas shing dam nyams pa gyur na byas pa chud zos te /
NK069(tu)001:20016: dam tshig gi ngang la gnas shing ma nyams par bsrungs na /
NK069(tu)001:20017: gong ma rnams yang byas pa don yod cing chud mi za bar 'byung ste /
NK069(tu)001:20018: mtshan nyid kyi thig pa las kyang /
NK069(tu)001:20019: ji ltar sa gzhi'i skye 'khrungs kun gyi gzhi /
NK069(tu)001:20020: sa la rten nas dge ba'i lo thog skyed /
NK069(tu)001:20021: de bzhin 'dul ba'i sdom pa sogs kun gyi gzhi' /
NK069(tu)001:20022: 'di la rten nas dge ba'i lo thog skyed /
NK069(tu)001:20024: mtshan nyid kyi thig pa'i gzhung gis kyang /
NK069(tu)001:20025: tshul khrims sdom pa ma nyams par srungs na /
NK069(tu)001:20026: dge ba'i rtsa ba ci spyad pa kun kyang chud mi za zhing 'bras bu yod pa bstan la /
NK069(tu)001:20027: sngags kyi theg pa la zhugs pa rnams kyis kyang /
NK069(tu)001:20028: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyams par bsrungs na /
NK069(tu)001:20029: dge ba'i rtsa ba chud mi za zhing 'bras bu yod par 'gyur bas /
NK069(tu)001:20030: don yod par bya ba'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:20031: sgrub par bya ba'i sangs rgyas dang /
NK069(tu)001:20032: srung bar bya ba'i dam tshig gnyis gnyis su med pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:20033: de bas na don yod par zhes smos pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:20034: bla med theg par rab nges na //
NK069(tu)001:20036: theg pa chen po'i yang chen por gyur pa /
NK069(tu)001:20037: gsang sngags kyi theg pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20038: theg pa bla na med pa yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:20040: bla na med pa'i tshad ni /
NK069(tu)001:20041: rtogs pa rnam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis /
NK069(tu)001:20042: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos sam /
NK069(tu)001:20043: sems dang sems snang ba'i chos thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:20046: chos thams cad sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK069(tu)001:20047: kun tu bzang por sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du gnas pa'i don /
NK069(tu)001:20048: shes rab kyis kyang tshig tsam yin par rtogs nas /
NK069(tu)001:20049: rtogs pa'i don la ting nge 'dzin gyis kyang rtse gcig par bsgoms pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20050: theg pa der nges pa'i tshad do //
NK069(tu)001:20051: nyon mongs las rnams kun spyod kyang //
NK069(tu)001:20053: bsgoms pas rtogs pa mngon du gyur pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:20054: nyon mongs lnga'i las ci spyad kyang skyon gyis mi gos la /
NK069(tu)001:20055: de yang gsog gcod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20056: ma byin par len pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20061: log par lta ba la sogs pa ci spyad kyang /
NK069(tu)001:20062: de'i skyon gyi mi gos ste /
NK069(tu)001:20063: slar bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs rnam pa gnyis su 'gyur bas na /
NK069(tu)001:20064: bla na med pa'i theg pa der nges pa'i tshad yin no ////
NK069(tu)001:20065: dam tshig zhes bya ba'i nges tshig yang /
NK069(tu)001:20067: 'og nas 'byung ba'i rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig 'di dag /
NK069(tu)001:20068: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin yin pa las mi 'da' ba 'am /
NK069(tu)001:20069: de ltar rnal 'byor pas shes shing rtogs par bya ba las mi 'da' ba'i phyir yang dam tshig /
NK069(tu)001:20070: de ltar rtogs shing ma nyams par srungs na /
NK069(tu)001:20071: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i dngos grub thob pa las mi 'da' ba'i phyir yang dam tshig /
NK069(tu)001:20072: de ltar rtogs shing ma nyams par srungs na /
NK069(tu)001:20073: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i dngos grub thob par 'gyur ba las mi 'da' ba'i phyir yang dam tshig /
NK069(tu)001:20074: dam tshig de dag lus dang srog la bab kyang ma nyams par srung rgyu yin pa las /
NK069(tu)001:20076: shes pa'i rgyud thal ba bzhin du 'tshig pas kyang dam tshig /
NK069(tu)001:20077: yang na rtsa ba dang yan lag gi don ston pa'i tshig la yang tshig ces bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:20078: yang na dam tshig gi mtshan gyi khyad par kun
NK069(tu)001:20079: thob cing 'gro ba'i phyir yang dam tshig ces bya
NK069(tu)001:20080: ste / dam tshig gi ngang la gnas shing ma nyams par srungs na /
NK069(tu)001:20081: lha dang mi'i bde' ba'i go 'phang thob nas /
NK069(tu)001:20082: bla na med pa'i byang chub mi gnas pa'i ye
NK069(tu)001:20083: shes chen por 'gro bas kun thob cing 'gro ba'i
NK069(tu)001:20085: yang na rtogs shing khong du chud pa'i phyir yang dam tshig ste /
NK069(tu)001:20086: dam tshig gi sdongs la gnas shing ma nyams par srungs na /
NK069(tu)001:20087: thun mong ma yin pa'i shes rab rang ting 'dzin rtogs shing khong du chud par 'gyur ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:20088: yang na 'jig rten las 'das pa'i sku dang ye shes man chad dang /
NK069(tu)001:20089: 'jig rten pa'i nya dang khra dang spyang khu yan
NK069(tu)001:20090: chad rtogs shing khong du chud par 'gyur bas so
NK069(tu)001:20091: // yang na gzung ba zhes kyang bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:20092: dam tshig ma nyams par srung pas 'khor ba dang
NK069(tu)001:20093: ngan song du mi ltung zhing bla na med pa'i
NK069(tu)001:20094: byang chub 'grub par 'gyur ba'i gzungs su 'gyur bas
NK069(tu)001:20096: nyes pa dag las zlog pa'i phyir 'dzin par byed pa la yang gzungs zhes bya'o ////
NK069(tu)001:20097: 'dir nyon mongs pa lam du byed pa la bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:20098: nyon mongs pa gsang ba yin nam sgrag pa yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:20099: blo chung ba la gsang ba yin /
NK069(tu)001:20100: blo che ba la sgrag pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:20101: nyon mongs pa drang don yin nam nges don yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:20102: mtshan nyid pa la drang don yin /
NK069(tu)001:20103: gsang sngags pa la nges don yin /
NK069(tu)001:20104: nyon mongs pa mi yong ba'i gtan tshigs ci yin zhe na gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:20105: nyon mongs pa la spang bya ma grub pas mi spong ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:20106: dper na dmigs rgyu la chu rags mi dgos pa lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:20107: nyon mongs pa thabs la mkhas pa'i lam yin pas mi spong ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:20108: me tog gur gum gyi nags tshal lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:20109: nyon mongs pa chen po yin pas mi spong ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:20110: rgyal ba'i dgongs pa'i zhe phugs yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:20111: nyon mong pa ma yangs pa'i dgos pa ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:20112: nyon mongs pa ma spangs par grol tsam na /
NK069(tu)001:20113: nyon mongs pa 'chi ba'i rgyu 'ba' zhig yin mnyam
NK069(tu)001:20114: pa'i dngos po phyogs can du 'dzin pa'i zhen pa
NK069(tu)001:20116: de tsam na chos nyid kyi bden pa'i don rtogs pa'i blo myur ba dang gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:20117: de tsam na nyon mongs pa ma spangs par grol pas /
NK069(tu)001:20118: gsang sngags ma nor ba'i don yin mnyam pas bka'
NK069(tu)001:20119: zab mo la gus pa'i stobs skye ba dang gsum
NK069(tu)001:20120: mo // de bas na nyon mongs las rnams kun zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:20121: byas la mi sog tshogs 'gyur te //
NK069(tu)001:20123: de lta bu'i shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin du ldan pas ni /
NK069(tu)001:20125: lha'i zhal zas rtsang ma rten pas 'grub pa lta ci smos ste /
NK069(tu)001:20126: mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pa'i shes rab dang /
NK069(tu)001:20127: ting nge 'dzin du ldan pas ni /
NK069(tu)001:20128: kun nas nyon mongs pa'i chos mi dge ba rnams dang /
NK069(tu)001:20129: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la 'jol nyag du spyad kyang /
NK069(tu)001:20130: skyon gyi mi gos pa'i phyir byas la mi sog ces so //
NK069(tu)001:20131: mtshan nyid kyi thig pa'i nang nas kyang /
NK069(tu)001:20132: byas la mi sogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20133: ma byas pa la sogs pa yod de /
NK069(tu)001:20134: byas la mi sog pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20135: thog ma nas zhe sdang gis bsad par ma bsams bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:20138: mi 'am sems can lag du shi na /
NK069(tu)001:20139: phyis 'gyod pa drag pos bar bcad nas dge' ba'i las bshags nas /
NK069(tu)001:20140: de'i sgrib pas mi gos par 'gyur ba ni byas la mi sog pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20141: ma byas la sog pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20143: gzhan srog gcod pa dang sdig pa rlabs po che byed pa la /
NK069(tu)001:20144: dga' zhing smon pa dang rjes su yid rang byed na /
NK069(tu)001:20145: ma byas kyang bag chags kun gzhi' la 'jog par byed pas /
NK069(tu)001:20146: rnam par smin pa'i 'bras bu ngan song du skye bar 'gyur ro zhes ston to //
NK069(tu)001:20147: gong ma lta bu'i shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin du ldan pa la /
NK069(tu)001:20148: ci spyad kyang skyon gyis mi gos sam mi sog par ma zad de /
NK069(tu)001:20149: de nyid bdag dang gzhan gyi don tshogs rnam pa gnyis su 'gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:20150: mtshan ma gang yang mi 'gog par spyod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20152: de nyid rang bzhin med par rtogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20153: ye shes kyi tshogs su 'gyur te /
NK069(tu)001:20154: tshul khrims sdom pa phun gsum 'tshogs //
NK069(tu)001:20155: zhes de'i gnas skabs na nyan thos kyi tshul khrims dang /
NK069(tu)001:20156: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:20157: ma bsrungs ma spyad bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:20158: nyes byas 'ga' yang mi gnas par /
NK069(tu)001:20159: phun sum 'tshogs pa nyid du rnam par dag par 'gyur ba bstan no //
NK069(tu)001:20160: 'o na de mi 'gal lam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:20162: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig gi nang du'o //
NK069(tu)001:20163: 'og ma'i sdom pa rnams ma srungs par tshang zhing rdzogs pa mi 'gal lam bya ba'i lan du /
NK069(tu)001:20164: bla med mchog gi dam tshig du /
NK069(tu)001:20165: zhes pa'i tshig bzhi tshigs su bcad pa gcig gsungs pa yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:20166: des mi 'gal ba'i 'thad pa bsgrub bo ////
NK069(tu)001:20167: 'dir gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:20168: tshul khrims sdom pa phun sum 'tshogs zhes pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20169: de la the tshom zhig rgal te /
NK069(tu)001:20170: mnyam pa nyid rtogs pa'i shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin du ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:20171: ci spyad kyang skyon gyi mi gos la /
NK069(tu)001:20172: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs su 'gyur ba ni rung na /
NK069(tu)001:20173: de'i gnas skabs na nyan thos kyis tshul khrims dang /
NK069(tu)001:20174: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa'i sdom pa kun yang
NK069(tu)001:20175: nyes byas 'ga' yang med par slar phun sum 'tshogs
NK069(tu)001:20176: pa nyid du rnam par dag pa de stubs sam
NK069(tu)001:20179: dper na phul gyi nang du bri mi shong la /
NK069(tu)001:20180: bre'i nang du na phul shong ba dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:20181: theg pa chung ngu'i nang du ni theg pa chen po'i don mi shong la /
NK069(tu)001:20182: theg pa chen po'i nang du ni theg pa chung ngu don thams cad shong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:20183: de bas na che chung zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:20184: bla med mchog gi dam tshig du /
NK069(tu)001:20186: gong ma de'i lan du ni /
NK069(tu)001:20187: gsang sngags kyi thig pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20188: theg pa chen po'i yang chen po /
NK069(tu)001:20189: theg pa bla na med pa'i mchog yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20190: de'i dam tshig kyang tshul khrims dang sdom pa thams cad nang na /
NK069(tu)001:20191: sdom pa bla na med pa'i mchog yin pas bla med mchog gi dam tshig go //
NK069(tu)001:20192: 'dul ba'i dbang gi tshul khrims dang /
NK069(tu)001:20195: dam pa'i chos 'dul ba'i dbang gis gsungs pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:20196: nyan thos kyi tshul khrims sde pa bco' brgyad bstan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20197: nges pa ni nyon mongs pa rta rgod dang 'dra ba la /
NK069(tu)001:20198: gnyen po khrims nyis brgya lnga bcus 'dul bas na 'dul ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:20199: de'i dbang gi srung bya rnams dang ///
NK069(tu)001:20201: rang bzhin gyi sbyor sgrol 'khor 'das sems su shes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20202: dbang po yul gyi sbyor sgrol gzung 'dzin gnyis med du shes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20203: ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyor sgrol dmigs pa dag pa sbyang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:20204: thabs chen po'i sbyor sgrol man ngag bsgoms pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20205: mngon du phyung ba'i sbyor bsad gso' nus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20207: dang po gang zag gis sgral na /
NK069(tu)001:20208: lta spyod ting nge 'dzin 'brel pa la goms pas sgral /
NK069(tu)001:20209: gnyis pa yul gang sgral na /
NK069(tu)001:20211: dkon mchog gi spyi dgra dang /
NK069(tu)001:20212: slob dpon gyi sku dgra dang /
NK069(tu)001:20216: sgrub pa 'dus par bar chad la 'ongs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20217: sems can yongs la gnod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20218: dam tshig can gyi dgrar gyur pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20219: rang rgyud ngan pa'i ngang tshul can dang /
NK069(tu)001:20221: gsum pa tshul lam thabs ji ltar sgral na /
NK069(tu)001:20225: byang chub sems dpa'i zhing du sgral lo //
NK069(tu)001:20226: bzhi pa gang ltar sgral na /
NK069(tu)001:20227: phung po tshogs la dngos pos rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs par sgral /
NK069(tu)001:20228: bag chags sbyangs nas rnam shes lhar byas te 'og min du 'phangs pas /
NK069(tu)001:20229: ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs par sgral lo //
NK069(tu)001:20230: dgos ched ci'i phyir sgral na /
NK069(tu)001:20231: sems can thams cad bde ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:20233: bdag gi dam skongs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20234: byang chub kyi spyod pa 'phel ba'i phyir sgral lo //
NK069(tu)001:20237: yod med dbus ma la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20238: ji snyed sdom pa bsam yas pa /
NK069(tu)001:20240: ji snyed ni mang po ste /
NK069(tu)001:20241: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa rgya mtsho' lta bu bsam yas pa /
NK069(tu)001:20244: mtshan nyid kyi thig pa chen po'i byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa nyi shu pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20245: gsang sngags phyi pa kri yog la sogs pa'i dam tshig dang sdom pa rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:20246: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /
NK069(tu)001:20248: tshul khrims dang sdom pa ma lus pa kun /
NK069(tu)001:20249: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig gi nang du 'dus la /
NK069(tu)001:20250: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig gi ngang la gnas shing ma nyams par srungs nas /
NK069(tu)001:20251: nyan thos kyi tshul khrims dang /
NK069(tu)001:20252: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa bsam yas pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:20253: re re nas srungs mi dgos te /
NK069(tu)001:20254: ma srungs bzhin du nyes byas gang yang med par /
NK069(tu)001:20255: phun sum 'tshogs pa nyid du rnam par dag par gnas pas rnam par dag ces bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:20256: yod med dbu' ma mi dmigs shing //
NK069(tu)001:20258: don dam pa'i chos thams cad ma byung ma skyes skye ba med la /
NK069(tu)001:20259: skye ba med pa'i chos kyi dbyings de la /
NK069(tu)001:20261: dbu' ma bya bar mi dmigs shing /
NK069(tu)001:20263: yang na chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin mnyam pa nyid gnyis su med pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:20264: gnyis su med pa de'i don de ni /
NK069(tu)001:20265: mtshan ma sna tshogs par snang bas ni /
NK069(tu)001:20267: snang tsam na mtshan ma med pa'i ngang las ma g.yos pas ni /
NK069(tu)001:20269: sna tshogs par snang bas ni /
NK069(tu)001:20271: snang tsam na rang bzhin med pa'i ngang las ma g.yos pas ni /
NK069(tu)001:20273: yod med gnyis ka mthar phyin pas /
NK069(tu)001:20274: dbu' ma bya ba yang mi dmigs pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:20275: gnyis su med pa'i don de la ni /
NK069(tu)001:20276: sgyu ma dmigs yor lta bu'i tshul //
NK069(tu)001:20278: kun rdzob tu chos thams cad sgyu ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:20281: rmi lam la sogs pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:20282: sgyu ma'i dpe' brgyad lta bu'i tshul du snang tsam
NK069(tu)001:20283: na dngos por ma grub ste rang bzhin gang yang
NK069(tu)001:20284: med zhes bya'o //// yang na sgyu ma'i dpe brgyad
NK069(tu)001:20285: dmig yor la sogs pa med bzhin du snang tsam
NK069(tu)001:20286: med zhes bya'o //// na / rang gi ngo bos stong ste /
NK069(tu)001:20287: yod med gnyis kyi ngo bor ma grub /
NK069(tu)001:20288: de lta chos thams cad dam par cir yang dmigs su med la /
NK069(tu)001:20289: kun rdzob tu ni sgru ma'i dpe' brgyad lta bu'i tshul du snang bas /
NK069(tu)001:20290: dngos po ma grub ste rang bzhin med zhe'am /
NK069(tu)001:20291: ngag don du 'di man chad la gnyis su med pa'i dam tshig 'jug par bstan te /
NK069(tu)001:20292: chos thams cad kyi gzhi' mnyam pa nyid yin pa /
NK069(tu)001:20293: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med par mnyam pa /
NK069(tu)001:20294: mtshan ma dang mtshan ma med par yang gnyis su med par mnyam par mnyam pa /
NK069(tu)001:20295: de shes rab kyis kyang rtogs par byas la /
NK069(tu)001:20296: ting nge 'dzin gyis kyang de la goms par 'jug pas /
NK069(tu)001:20297: gnyis su med par dam tshig la 'jug pa zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:20298: de las spyir 'di na mar la khog don du /
NK069(tu)001:20299: nyan thos kyi gnas skabs na /
NK069(tu)001:20300: srog gcod pa la sogs pa'i nyes pa rtsa ba bzhir byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:20301: de ma spyad par yangs pas dag par yin la /
NK069(tu)001:20303: srog gcod pa la sogs pa yan lag du byas ste /
NK069(tu)001:20304: mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:20305: ma spangs par spyang pa nyid kyis dag pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:20306: de gnyis yang dag pa'i tshabs 'di che bar bstan pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:20307: srog med srog bcad du med //
NK069(tu)001:20309: de ltar snang chas na rang gi ngo bos ste /
NK069(tu)001:20310: gnyis med pa'i don de la /
NK069(tu)001:20311: srog gi dngos por grub pa med /
NK069(tu)001:20312: de bas na srog dang skyes bu log par rtogs pa tsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:20313: srog gi dngos po grub pa med pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20315: srog cad du med srog cad pa yang med do //
NK069(tu)001:20316: srog dang skyes bu log rtog tsam //
NK069(tu)001:20318: 'o na skyes bu zhig gis srog cad pa'i rnam
NK069(tu)001:20319: par smin pas ngan song skyes so zhes 'byung bas
NK069(tu)001:20322: srog dang srog cod pa'i skyes bu ni /
NK069(tu)001:20323: log par rtogs pa tsam ste /
NK069(tu)001:20324: snang ba las ma rtogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:20326: kun rdzob du yang chos thams cad sgyu ma'i dpe'
NK069(tu)001:20327: brgyad ltar snang la rang bzhin med par gnas ste
NK069(tu)001:20329: de ltar rtogs pa dang ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:20330: sgrol ba byas na ni sgrib pas mi gos kyi /
NK069(tu)001:20331: de lta bu'i rtogs pa'i don dang mi ldan pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:20332: 'di la khung byung nas so so gar sgrar gsog cad na /
NK069(tu)001:20333: dpal chen po'i thugs khral du 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:20334: dper na sgyu ma'i ting nge mi shes na rdzas shing tas kyang srog gcad do ////
NK069(tu)001:20335: zhe sdang lam du byed pa la dgu ste /
NK069(tu)001:20336: dang po zhe sdang yangs nas lam du byed na /
NK069(tu)001:20337: nyon mongs pa lam du byed pa yang bud /
NK069(tu)001:20338: nyon mongs pa lam du byed pa yang bud /
NK069(tu)001:20339: nyan thos dang khyad med par yang 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:20340: gnyis pa zhe sdang 'gags pa'i go shul lam du byed na /
NK069(tu)001:20341: de zhe sdang lam du byed pa ma yin no //
NK069(tu)001:20342: gsum pa ye shes zhe sdang dus mnyam yin zer na /
NK069(tu)001:20344: bzhi pa zhe sdang skyes pa'i gnyen po ye shes skyes pa lam du byed na /
NK069(tu)001:20345: ye shes gsar skyes su song ste /
NK069(tu)001:20346: ye shes ma yin par thal lo //
NK069(tu)001:20347: lnga pa zhe sdang gi rgyun khad kyis sgyur ba ye shes yin zer na /
NK069(tu)001:20348: zhe sdang dang ye shes gnyis rgyun skad gcig ma snga phyir 'dug ste /
NK069(tu)001:20349: de yang ye shes gsar skyes su thal /
NK069(tu)001:20350: drug pa zhe sdang dang ye shes de nyid dang gzhan du rjod du med pa yin zer na /
NK069(tu)001:20351: zhe sdang kho na yang ye shes ma yin la /
NK069(tu)001:20352: de las logs pa'i ye shes yang med pa yin ste /
NK069(tu)001:20353: gzhan la mtshon pa'i dbang du stub te /
NK069(tu)001:20354: rang nyams su blang du mi stub bo //
NK069(tu)001:20355: bdun pa zhe sdang skabs kyis skyes pa de dus na ye shes yin zer na /
NK069(tu)001:20356: pha gsad kyi bu yang ye shes skye bar thal /
NK069(tu)001:20357: brgyad pa nyon mongs pa'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pa gcig la lam du byed na /
NK069(tu)001:20358: pha gsad kyi bu yang grol thal bar rigs so //
NK069(tu)001:20359: dgu pa mi ldan pa la lam du byed na /
NK069(tu)001:20360: nyon mongs pa lam du byed pa'i dam bca' bud do //
NK069(tu)001:20366: dper na mi gar yang sa ma song bar sgo na mi 'dug na /
NK069(tu)001:20367: khyim na 'dug pa las 'os med pa bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:20368: gong ma rnams gang yang med tsam na /
NK069(tu)001:20369: blan cha gsal cha las 'os med do //
NK069(tu)001:20370: tshad ma bka' gzhung gi tshig go //
NK069(tu)001:20371: bden pa gnyis gar dbyer med pas /
NK069(tu)001:20374: ma byin pa len pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:20375: chos thams cad don dam pa'i bden par ni ma skyes par gcig /
NK069(tu)001:20377: so so'i rig pa rang snang bar cig /
NK069(tu)001:20378: de ltar kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i bden pa gnyis kar yang /
NK069(tu)001:20379: bdag dang gzhan du dbyer med pas ///
NK069(tu)001:20380: ma byin pa len pa la ngag don du bcu bdun ste /
NK069(tu)001:20381: sgral ba'i zhing bcu'i nor blang ba la bcu /
NK069(tu)001:20382: nag po'i phyogs nas bzungs ma mtshan ldan blang ba dang bcu gcig /
NK069(tu)001:20383: bkra shis dag pa'i rdzas blang ba dang bcu gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:20384: ka nges don ter du thas pa blang ba dang cu gsum /
NK069(tu)001:20385: skye bo phal pa'i lag nas rjes byin rlabs can blang ba dang cu bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:20386: bdag po srung ba yod pa'i gter dang bac+wo lnga /
NK069(tu)001:20387: srung ba med pa'i gter dang bcu drug /
NK069(tu)001:20388: phyug po ser sna can gyi nor ming gis blang ba dang bcu bdun no //
NK069(tu)001:20389: 'phrul dag'i tshul de tha dad min //
NK069(tu)001:20392: longs spyod thams cad rang las 'phrul zhing rang gis
NK069(tu)001:20393: longs spyod kyang dar bzhin ma rtogs pas 'khor ro
NK069(tu)001:20394: // de yang lha dang longs spyod tha dad pa ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:20395: bdag dang gzhan du snang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:20396: dpe' lha 'phrul dag'i longs spyod kyi tshul dang mthun te /
NK069(tu)001:20397: don dam par ma skyes par gcig pas kyang bdag dang gzhan tha dad pa med do //
NK069(tu)001:20398: gzhan dang ma byin med pa'i phyir //
NK069(tu)001:20400: kun rdzob rgyu ma'i dpe' brgyad kyi tshul du yang /
NK069(tu)001:20402: gzhan gyi dngos por grub pa med pas /
NK069(tu)001:20403: de ltar don dam pa dang kun rdzob gnyis kar /
NK069(tu)001:20404: bdag dang gzhan gyi dngos por ma grub phyin cad /
NK069(tu)001:20405: chos thams cad rang gi rig pa la mi zhan pas na gzhan ma grub /
NK069(tu)001:20407: gzhan ma byin pa blang pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:20408: blang med thams cad nyid kyi dbyings //
NK069(tu)001:20410: de ltar gzhan ma grub pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20411: gzhan gyis byin pa yang med pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20413: rang gis blang pa yang med pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20414: bdag gzhan tha mi dad par rtogs pas na /
NK069(tu)001:20415: blangs pa med pa'i bdag gzhan thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:20416: chos nyid kyi dbyings su tha mi dad pa'o ////
NK069(tu)001:20417: ngag don du bdag dang gzhan du snang ba'i chos thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:20418: don dam par ni chos nyid kyi dbyings las ma g.yos par cig la /
NK069(tu)001:20420: rang gi rig pa rang snang ba'i mtshan nyid du cig de ltar rtogs pa dang ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:20423: thabs mkhas pa'i 'od gzer gyis blangs nas /
NK069(tu)001:20425: tshogs kyi mchod par gtang rgyu yin pa las /
NK069(tu)001:20428: mched dang slob dpon gyi nor la gang rung rung du spyad na yang /
NK069(tu)001:20430: de yang dpal chen po'i thugs khral du 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:20431: dper na 'phrul dag'i ting nge 'dzin mi shes na /
NK069(tu)001:20432: rang nor spyad yang kus pa dang 'dra'o //
NK069(tu)001:20433: de ni yang dag par shes na /
NK069(tu)001:20434: gzhan nor gyis yang mi 'ching la /
NK069(tu)001:20435: mi shes na rang nor spyod yang 'ching bar 'gyur
NK069(tu)001:20436: bas na 'phrul dag'i ting nge 'dzin gal che ba
NK069(tu)001:20437: yin no // chos rnams sgyu ma lta bu dang //
NK069(tu)001:20439: rdzun du smra ba yang 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos rnams /
NK069(tu)001:20440: snang tsam na dngos por ma grub pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20441: sgyu ma lta bu bdag gis drangs ste /
NK069(tu)001:20442: sprul pa dang mig yor la sogs ste dpe' brgyad ltar snang la rang bzhin med pas /
NK069(tu)001:20443: rdzun gyi ngo bor gnas pa yin la ///
NK069(tu)001:20444: rdzun du smra ba la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:20449: snang ba 'di kun mi bden ste rdzun /
NK069(tu)001:20450: thams cad rang rig tu snang ba ni bden de /
NK069(tu)001:20451: de ltar rtogs na rdzun no //
NK069(tu)001:20453: sems can thams cad kyi don du gyur pa la bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:20454: rdzun gyi rnam grangs ni bcu bdun te /
NK069(tu)001:20455: gsang ba bcu 'dri na rdzun smra ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:20461: mi dang tshig tu rtags pa rdzun //
NK069(tu)001:20463: 'o na de ltar ston pa'i ming dang tshig tu btags pa de ci yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:20464: de yang dngos po dang mtshan ma gang yang grub pa med pas rdzun zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:20465: rdzun nyid la ni rdzun spyod pas //
NK069(tu)001:20468: lan rde pa gang gi byas te /
NK069(tu)001:20469: de lta chos thams cad sgyu ma'i dpe' brgyad ltar snang la rang bzhin med pas /
NK069(tu)001:20471: rdzun nyid sprul pa lta bu la /
NK069(tu)001:20473: rdzun la rdzun phyogs par bas te /
NK069(tu)001:20475: rdzun zhes btags tsam yod ma yin //
NK069(tu)001:20477: 'o na rdzun zhes rtags pa'i tshig de tsam du dngos por grub pa zhig yin nam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:20478: rdzun zhes btags pa'i tshig de tsam rang du yang
NK069(tu)001:20479: dngos por ma grub pas yod pa ma yin no
NK069(tu)001:20480: //// ngag don du 'di ltar rtogs par byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:20481: rdzun du smra bar byed pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:20482: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod par gyur pa'i gzhan la phan pa'i rdzun te /
NK069(tu)001:20483: dper na mi bshed ma'i brdas pa 'dir byung ngam zhes 'dri na /
NK069(tu)001:20484: ma byung zhes rdzun byas pas /
NK069(tu)001:20486: gcig kyang sgrib pas ma gos par gyur pa lta bu'i rdzun spyad rgyu yin pa las /
NK069(tu)001:20488: gsang ba'i rgyud 'di nyid la khungs phyung ste /
NK069(tu)001:20489: gang rung rung gi rdzun nam /
NK069(tu)001:20491: gzhan gyi shes pa sgyur pa'i rdzun byas na /
NK069(tu)001:20492: rnam par smin pas ngan song du skye'o //
NK069(tu)001:20493: dper na 'khor 'das kyi chos sgyu ma lta bu'i rdzun du ma shes na /
NK069(tu)001:20494: drang por sgras kyang rdzun du 'agro'o //
NK069(tu)001:20495: shes na thams cad dngos med yin pa la /
NK069(tu)001:20496: ma shes na drang po nyid ther zug ngu bzung
NK069(tu)001:20497: bas rang la rang gis rdzun byas par 'gyur ba
NK069(tu)001:20498: yin pas so // sbyor ba'i dam tshig la lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:20499: dang po gang gis sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:20500: log pa'i 'dod chags rang gi yid la yangs pas sbyar /
NK069(tu)001:20501: gnyis pa gang gi don du sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:20502: bdag gzhan gyi don du sbyar /
NK069(tu)001:20503: gsum pa gang la sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:20505: pad can dung can la sogs dang /
NK069(tu)001:20506: spyir lus kyi mtshan nyid lus gnyen la drang ba /
NK069(tu)001:20507: skad pa stod smad phyed pa /
NK069(tu)001:20509: tshigs dmig thams cad zlum pa /
NK069(tu)001:20511: mig gi kyus ring la mig 'bras nag pa /
NK069(tu)001:20512: mchu' zheng gnyis ka mnyam pa /
NK069(tu)001:20514: gsang thub cing spyod pa dal ba /
NK069(tu)001:20515: shes rab che zhing 'grogs na dad pa che ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:20520: phyi nang gsang ba'i chos bshad /
NK069(tu)001:20522: sbyor thabs rtsa rlung gi man ngag la mkhas pas sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:20523: lnga pa sbyar ba'i yon tan ni /
NK069(tu)001:20525: tshig don ni ma chags pa la zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:20526: ma chags pa la chags pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:20529: la la yul mkhar la chags /
NK069(tu)001:20530: la la nor rdzas la chags /
NK069(tu)001:20531: la la pho mo'i bde' ba la chags na /
NK069(tu)001:20532: spyir chags pa de dag gi gzhi' pho mo yin te /
NK069(tu)001:20533: pho mo chags pa'i rang bzhin ni /
NK069(tu)001:20534: don dam par ni ma skyes pa chos kyi dbyings yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:20535: de la yang chags su med par ma chags la /
NK069(tu)001:20536: kun rdzob tu ye shes kyi lha mo /
NK069(tu)001:20537: mtshan nyid nam mkha'i 'ja' tshon nam /
NK069(tu)001:20538: chu zla'i dkyil 'khor ltar snang la rang bzhin med par gnas pas /
NK069(tu)001:20539: de la yang chags su med de /
NK069(tu)001:20540: chags par bya ba'i gzhi med pas ma chags zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:20541: nyan thos ltar chags pa la rgyab kyi phyogs shing /
NK069(tu)001:20542: chags pa spangs pa zhig yin nam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:20543: de ltar chags pa spangs pa yang ma yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:20545: chags pa nyid na chags med pa //
NK069(tu)001:20548: ye shes lha la chags yang rtog par 'gyur zhes 'byung na /
NK069(tu)001:20549: chags na mi 'gal lam zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:20550: gong ma ltar don dam par chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag par rtogs par byas la /
NK069(tu)001:20551: kun rdzob tu ye shes kyi lha mo chu zla'i gzugs brnyan nam /
NK069(tu)001:20553: snang la rang bzhin med par rtogs nas chags na chags su zad de /
NK069(tu)001:20554: chags pa nyid na chags pa med pa'i 'thar phyin te /
NK069(tu)001:20555: chags pa nyid na chags pa med pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20556: 'di ni tshangs mchog rgyal po ste //
NK069(tu)001:20558: 'dod chags dang 'dod chags med pa gnyis med par rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:20559: 'dod chags spyad kyang skyon gyis mi gos ste /
NK069(tu)001:20560: 'dod chags ma spyad par spangs pas nyan thos kyang tshangs na /
NK069(tu)001:20562: gong ma ltar 'dod chags dang 'dod chags med pa gnyis med par rtogs nas /
NK069(tu)001:20563: 'dod chags ma spangs sa nyid kyis /
NK069(tu)001:20564: 'dod chags las tshangs pa de ni /
NK069(tu)001:20565: tshangs pa rnams kyi nang na mchog gam rgyal po lta bu yin no //
NK069(tu)001:20566: shin tu chags pa chen po yin //
NK069(tu)001:20567: zhes shin tu 'am khyad par du /
NK069(tu)001:20568: 'dod chags dang 'dod chags gnyis med par rtogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20569: chags pa chags pa chen po yin no ////
NK069(tu)001:20570: 'di lta bu'i rtogs pa dang ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:20575: gang rung rung du spyad par gyur na /
NK069(tu)001:20577: mngal gyi srin 'bu a kro ka bya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:20578: byol song chags pa can du skye ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:20580: de yi dam lha mi spang ba'i dam tshig bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20581: bla na med pa la gnyis ste /
NK069(tu)001:20582: kun rdzob tu rang lus lha skur shes pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20583: don dam gnyis med du ye shes kyi skur gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:20584: bla na med pa'i ye dam gyi lha mi spang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:20585: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gnas skabs dang /
NK069(tu)001:20586: thugs ye shes nyid mtshan ma med pa'i chos kyi dbyings kyi ngang las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:20587: nye bar brtags pa'i lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya'i mtshan ma'i rnam par yang gsal la /
NK069(tu)001:20589: mtshan ma med pa'i dbyings las ma g.yos ste /
NK069(tu)001:20590: mtshan ma dang mtshan ma med pa gnyis med par gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:20591: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gnas skabs na de ltar yin pa ma zad de /
NK069(tu)001:20592: rnal 'byor pa'i gnas skabs na yang /
NK069(tu)001:20594: bdag gi sems kyi chos nyid /
NK069(tu)001:20595: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i rang bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:20596: mtshan ma med pa'i ngang las ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:20597: bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum nye bar rtags pa'i yi dam gyi lha'i /
NK069(tu)001:20598: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya mtshan ma'i rnam par yang gsal la /
NK069(tu)001:20599: gsal tsam na mtshan ma med pa'i ngang las ma g.yos ste /
NK069(tu)001:20600: mtshan ma dang mtshan ma med pa gnyis med par bsgom mo //
NK069(tu)001:20601: de skad du yang sgyu 'phrul le'u lag nas /
NK069(tu)001:20602: yi dam lha'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK069(tu)001:20603: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis //
NK069(tu)001:20604: lha spangs dge spyad don med 'gyur zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:20605: bla na med pa'i byang chub sems zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:20606: rtsa ba lnga'i yang rtsa bar gyur pas na yang bla med /
NK069(tu)001:20607: yi dam rtogs pas byang chub sems dang dbyer med /
NK069(tu)001:20608: de nam du yang spangs mi stub pas spang ngo ////
NK069(tu)001:20609: bla ma skur ba'i dam tshig bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20612: rdo rje slob dpon sgo gsum zol sog med pas mchod cing mnyes par bya ba'i rim pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20613: spyir slob dpon la drug ste /
NK069(tu)001:20615: chos la 'jug pa 'dren pa'i bla ma /
NK069(tu)001:20616: dam tshig dbang bskur ba'i bla ma /
NK069(tu)001:20617: dam tshig nyams chag skong ba'i bla ma /
NK069(tu)001:20618: rang gi shes rgyud 'grol ba'i bla ma /
NK069(tu)001:20619: man ngag lung gi bla ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:20621: spyi'i bla ma yul la dbang ba'i rgyal po ltar bskur /
NK069(tu)001:20622: de bzhin du 'dren pa'i bla ma khu'o //
NK069(tu)001:20623: dam tshig dbang skur pha bu lta bu /
NK069(tu)001:20624: nyams chag skong ba ma lta bu /
NK069(tu)001:20625: shes rgyud 'grol ba dmig lta bu /
NK069(tu)001:20626: man ngag lung gi bla ma rang gi snying bas kyang lhag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20627: de yang lus kyis bran lta bur byas la zas nor gyis mnyes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:20628: ngag gis bla ma'i skyon sba zhing yon tan nas sgrog /
NK069(tu)001:20629: yid kyis g.yo' rgyu ngan sems 'phrag dog thams cad spangs la skur ba bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:20630: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad //
NK069(tu)001:20632: gsung gi dam tshig stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20634: rgyu ma nor ba rtsa ba'i sngags ni /
NK069(tu)001:20635: zhi ba'i +amo la sogs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20637: skyed pa rkyen gyi sngags kyis sku skyed la /
NK069(tu)001:20638: skul ba las kyi sngags kyis bzlas pa bya ba yin no //
NK069(tu)001:20640: sku phyag rgya chen po bdag lha skur bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:20641: dam tshig phyag rgyas yum skyed /
NK069(tu)001:20642: las kyi phyag rgyas zlas pa'i 'phro 'du bya /
NK069(tu)001:20643: chos kyi phyag rgya ni zhi ba phyag rgya las ma g.yos par /
NK069(tu)001:20644: sgo gsum yi dam du bsgoms nas rtag tu zlas pa byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20646: gzung dang 'dzin pa rnam gnyis po //
NK069(tu)001:20647: dag pa dor ba phyag rgya yin //
NK069(tu)001:20649: gzung 'dzin lhar dag par dor ba yin no //
NK069(tu)001:20654: slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba lta bu /
NK069(tu)001:20655: skad gcig tsam yang mi yengs par gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20658: mtshan lan gsum du bsgom pa ni rtson pa rab /
NK069(tu)001:20659: zla ba gcig la nya gnyis stong gnyis nyi shu gnyis ste dus drug tu bsgoms pa 'bring /
NK069(tu)001:20660: ra ba bzhi la nya gnyis stong gnyis nyi shu
NK069(tu)001:20661: gnyis brgyad gnyis dus brgyad du bsgom pa tha ma
NK069(tu)001:20662: ste / de ltar lus ngag yid 'bad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20663: yang dag lam du zhugs la byams //
NK069(tu)001:20665: mched rogs sku'i dam tshig stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20666: yang dag pa ni bla na med pa'i byang chub sgrub pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:20667: de'i lam ni sngags kyi theg pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:20669: spyi'i mched ni sems can thams cad bde gshegs snying po'i spun no //
NK069(tu)001:20671: sangs rgyas kyi chos sgor zhugs pa rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:20672: 'dres pa'i mched ni slob dpon cig la dam tshig nang 'dres pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20673: nye ba'i mched ni lta spyod nang 'thun pa rnams so //
NK069(tu)001:20674: de la spyi'i mched ni pha tshan lta bur srung /
NK069(tu)001:20675: ring ba'i mched nang tshan la /
NK069(tu)001:20676: nye ba'i mched pha spun lta bur /
NK069(tu)001:20677: dam tshig nang 'dres pa'i mched spun pas kyang lhag par lta'o //
NK069(tu)001:20678: gsang ba'i theg pa la zhugs pa'i mched lcam dral la zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:20679: gsang ba'i theg pa la zhugs pa'i mched lcam dral la byams par byed pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:20681: zas nor la sbur ma ltar phangs pa med pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20682: zhabs tog bran bzhin du bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:20685: 'dug tshul mi legs pa ji ltar yin pa bzhin du rjod par mi bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:20686: yid kyis phrag dog la sogs pa'i tshul ngan pa
NK069(tu)001:20687: thams cad spang bar bya ba ni lhag par gal
NK069(tu)001:20688: che'o // thugs kyi dam tshig bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20689: gsang ba'i don phyir smra mi bya //
NK069(tu)001:20695: yi dam gyi ming dang gzungs ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:20705: sgog rtsong la sogs tshogs zas dang /
NK069(tu)001:20708: tshil chen mar me la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20709: gsang ba gnyer gtad pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20711: de yang gsang ba'i theg pa 'di'i don ni /
NK069(tu)001:20714: dam nyams pa dang gsum la mi stan pa ni gsang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:20715: de ci'i phyir gsang zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:20716: gsang ba'i theg pa 'di yang ngan te dbyung mi bzod pa 'am /
NK069(tu)001:20717: skyon che bas gsang ba ma yin na /
NK069(tu)001:20718: 'di'i don gzhan la stan pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20721: des pha rol du ngan song du 'gro /
NK069(tu)001:20722: de'i nyes pas bdag kyang sgrib pa sogs /
NK069(tu)001:20723: de bas bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don phyir gsang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:20724: 'di ni rtsa ba lnga rnams te //
NK069(tu)001:20726: 'jug bsdus pa'i dam tshig stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20733: sngags dang phyag rgya gsung dang /
NK069(tu)001:20734: gsang ba thugs kyi dam tshig lnga'o ////
NK069(tu)001:20735: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po 'di'i rtsa ba bla
NK069(tu)001:20736: med mi spang ba yi dam lha bsgom pa de
NK069(tu)001:20737: / yi dam gyi lha bsgom na /
NK069(tu)001:20738: bla ma skur ba yang yin te /
NK069(tu)001:20739: yi dam lha dang bla ma dbyer med pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20740: yi dam gsal na mched lcam dral la byams par byas pa yang yin te /
NK069(tu)001:20741: mched dral du gyur pa yang yi dam lhas byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20742: yi dam lha gsal na sngags dang phyag rgya yin te /
NK069(tu)001:20743: sngags dang phyag rgya yang yi dam lha sgrub pa'i thabs yin pas so //
NK069(tu)001:20744: yi dam lha gsal na gsang ba yang gzhan du ma spel ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:20745: gsang ba bcu yang don yi dam lha sgrub pa'i rdzas dang man ngag yin no //
NK069(tu)001:20746: de bas na bla na med pa'i byang chub sems zhes bya ba yin no //
NK069(tu)001:20747: bsgrub dang bsrung ba'i dam tshig mchog /
NK069(tu)001:20748: ces bsgrub pa'i dam tshig ni /
NK069(tu)001:20749: bla med mi spang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:20750: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi gcad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20753: yang dag lam du zhugs pa la byams pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20754: gsang ba mi sgrag pa dang gsum mo //
NK069(tu)001:20755: de rnams ni gzhan las mchog tu gyur pa'i dam tshig go ////
NK069(tu)001:20756: mi spang ba'i dam tshig stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20757: gti' mug chags dang zhe sdang dang //
NK069(tu)001:20758: nga rgyal 'phrag dog mi spang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:20760: gti mug mi spang ba yang /
NK069(tu)001:20761: phyin ci log gi gti' mug spang ba ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:20762: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis chos thams cad stong zhing bdag med par rtogs pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:20763: dngos po dang mtshan ma'i rnam par thar pa dbyer
NK069(tu)001:20764: med pa'i gti mug stong pa nyid kyi ye shes
NK069(tu)001:20766: 'dod chags yang phyin ci log gi 'dod chags 'di ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:20767: so so kun tu rtog pa'i ye shes kyi /
NK069(tu)001:20768: chos spyi'i mtshan nyid stong zhing bdag med par rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:20769: chos kyi dbyings la 'dod chags pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20770: rang gi mtshan nyid ma 'chol bar mkhyen pas /
NK069(tu)001:20771: de ltar ma rtogs pa rnams la /
NK069(tu)001:20772: thugs rje'i don mdzad pa'i 'gro ba'i don la chags pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:20773: so so kun tu rtog pa'i ye shes mi spang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:20774: zhe sdang yang phyin ci log gi zhe sdang 'di ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:20775: zhe sdang gi mtshan nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:20776: zhe sdang skyes par byed pa'i yul 'joms par byed pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:20777: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis /
NK069(tu)001:20778: chos kyi dbyings stong pa bdag med rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:20779: gzung 'dzin dang log rtog thams cad 'joms pa'i me
NK069(tu)001:20780: long lta bu'i ye shes kyi ngo bo de mi
NK069(tu)001:20781: spang ba dang / nga rgyal mi spang ba yang
NK069(tu)001:20782: phyin ci log gi nga rgyal mi spang ba ma
NK069(tu)001:20783: spang ba dang / yin te / nga rgyal gyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK069(tu)001:20784: log pa'i phyogs la sran tshugs /
NK069(tu)001:20785: pha rol ni zil gyis mnon /
NK069(tu)001:20786: bdag ni mtho' bas gnas pa yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20787: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis kyang chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du mkhyen pas /
NK069(tu)001:20788: mnyam pa nyid kyi don la ni sran tshugs la /
NK069(tu)001:20789: nga dang bdag tu 'dzin pa'i rtogs pa zil gyis mnon /
NK069(tu)001:20790: stobs dang mi 'jigs pa dang gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin la sogs pa'i yon tan gyis ni /
NK069(tu)001:20791: bdag 'thong bar gnas pa de mi spang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:20793: sems can gyi phyin ci log gi 'phrag dog ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:20794: 'phrag dog gi mtshan nyid 'chab cing mi ston pa yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20795: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyis kyang /
NK069(tu)001:20796: mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs pa dang mi ldan pa rnams la /
NK069(tu)001:20797: mnyam pa nyid kyi don mi ston par /
NK069(tu)001:20798: las dge sdig rgyu 'bras kyi don ston pas /
NK069(tu)001:20799: 'phrag dog bya ba grub pa'i ye shes mi spang ngo ////
NK069(tu)001:20800: mi spang ba'i dam tshig la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:20805: gzungs ma la spyad pa'i thabs man ngag rtsa rlung la mkhas pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20806: 'dod yon lnga sems kyi rgyan du shes pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20807: yang dag pa la ni shin tu zhin pa'i lam mo //
NK069(tu)001:20809: sgral ba'i zhing bcu rlag par byed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20810: mu stegs la sogs pa'i ltas ngan 'joms pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20811: zhe sdang de ni thabs mkhas pa'i spyod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20813: lta ba mngon par mtho' ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:20814: ting nge 'dzin la nges par sran tshugs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20815: de ni shin tu nga rgyal ba ste mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:20817: lta ba phyogs ris med pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20818: spyod pa blang dor med pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20819: de ni mi 'byed pa'i gti' mug go //
NK069(tu)001:20821: lta spyod sman pa la 'phrag dog pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:20824: nyams pa spong ba ni 'phrag dog go //
NK069(tu)001:20826: sems can kun la yod pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:20827: de ni 'di ltar shes par bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:20828: dug lngar snang ba ni rang rig rang snang yin la /
NK069(tu)001:20830: dran pa thams cad kyi rtsa ba shes pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:20832: rtsol ba sems yin pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:20833: thabs mkhas pas dug lnga rang rig ye shes su shes par bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:20834: rang rig ye shes ni nyi ma la mun pa med pa ltar /
NK069(tu)001:20835: ye shes rang snang la nyon mongs pa ngang gis med de /
NK069(tu)001:20836: de ltar shes na nyon mongs pa spang du med pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20837: de ni dgongs ste bshad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20838: yang na zab mo ltar sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:20839: gti' mug gi spang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:20840: gti' mug gsal cing spangs ba'i pha rol na /
NK069(tu)001:20841: ye shes mi rtog pa bsgrub tu med de /
NK069(tu)001:20843: ma ri pa nyid ye shes gsal //
NK069(tu)001:20845: gti' mug tsam na gti mug pa'i mthar phyin te /
NK069(tu)001:20846: gti' mug dang gti mug pa gnyis med par rtogs pa de kha /
NK069(tu)001:20847: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes yi pas mi spang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:20849: 'dod chags 'di gsal cing spangs ba'i pha rol na /
NK069(tu)001:20850: 'dod chags med pa bya ba zhig logs zhig nas sgrub tu med de /
NK069(tu)001:20852: chags pa nyid na chags med pa zhes 'byung ste /
NK069(tu)001:20853: 'dod chags tsam 'dod chags med pa'i mthar phyin ste /
NK069(tu)001:20854: 'dod chags dang 'dod chags med pa gnyis med par rtogs pa de'i mi spang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:20855: zhe sdang mi spang ba yang /
NK069(tu)001:20857: zhe sdang thugs rje chen po'i ngang //
NK069(tu)001:20858: dmyal ba'i gnas rnams tshar gcod pa //
NK069(tu)001:20860: zhe sdang 'di gsal cing spangs pa'i pha rol na /
NK069(tu)001:20861: zhe sdang med pa zhes bya ba logs zhig nas sgrub tu med de /
NK069(tu)001:20862: zhe sdang tsam na zhe sdang med pa'i mthar phyin te /
NK069(tu)001:20863: zhe sdang dang zhe sdang ba gnyis med pa de mi spang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:20864: nga rgyal mi spang ba yang /
NK069(tu)001:20866: nga rgyal spangs pa'i pha rol na //
NK069(tu)001:20867: nga rgyal med pa bsgrub tu med //
NK069(tu)001:20869: nga rgyal 'di gsal zhing spangs pa'i pha rol na /
NK069(tu)001:20870: nga rgyal med pa'i zhi ba sgrub tu med de /
NK069(tu)001:20871: nga rgyal tsam na nga rgyal med pa'i mthar phyin pas /
NK069(tu)001:20872: nga rgyal dang nga rgyal ba med pa'i gnyis med par rtogs pa de mi spang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:20875: 'phrag dog mi spang don sbyor ba //
NK069(tu)001:20877: 'phrag dog gsal cing spangs ba'i pha rol na /
NK069(tu)001:20878: 'phrag dog med pa yang sgrub tu med de /
NK069(tu)001:20879: 'phrag dog tsam na 'phrag dog med pa'i mthar phyin pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:20880: 'phrag dog dang 'phrag dog pa gnyis med pa de mi spang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:20881: de ni dgongs min du bshad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20883: gti mug nyid rnam par snang mdzad yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:20884: de spangs na rnam par snang mdzad spangs par 'gro /
NK069(tu)001:20885: 'dod chags nyid snang ba mtha' yas yin /
NK069(tu)001:20886: zhe sdang nyid rdo rje sems dpa' yin /
NK069(tu)001:20887: nga rgyal nyid rin chen 'byung ldan yin /
NK069(tu)001:20888: 'phrag dog nyid don yod grub pa yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:20889: de dag spangs na rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas spangs bar 'gro bas yang mi spang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:20890: de ltar yin pa ma shis pas dug lngar snang la /
NK069(tu)001:20891: shes na rigs lngar grol lo //
NK069(tu)001:20892: de ni nges don du bshad do ////
NK069(tu)001:20893: mi dor ba'i dam tshig stan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20894: dkar rtsi dmar rtsi dri sha chen //
NK069(tu)001:20895: dang du blang ba ni dkar rtsi ni badz+ra tsi ta te /
NK069(tu)001:20896: yab kyi rdo rje las byung ba'i byang chub sems so //
NK069(tu)001:20897: ga pur zhes bya bar yang bshad la /
NK069(tu)001:20898: byang chub sems dkar po bya ba yang bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:20899: dmar rtsi ni ka ma la tsi ta ste yum gyi pad+ma las byung ba'i byang chub sems so //
NK069(tu)001:20900: pad+ma rag ta zhes bya bar yang bshad /
NK069(tu)001:20901: byang sems dmar po zhes bya bar yang bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:20902: dri ni yab yum kun las 'byung ba'i dri chen no //
NK069(tu)001:20903: ci zhes yang bya bar bshad do //
NK069(tu)001:20905: de'i sde tshan sha rnam pa lnga ru'o //
NK069(tu)001:20906: dag pa'i snod chu mi dor ro //
NK069(tu)001:20908: 'di rnams ni rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pas na /
NK069(tu)001:20910: sgrub pa rnam pa bzhis rgyan nas dag pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:20911: snod ni rtsa skyang ma nas sgang dpag nang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:20912: chu ni rdo rje dang pad+ma'i lam nas 'byung ba'i gur gum ste /
NK069(tu)001:20914: bshang ba zhes bya bar yang bshad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20915: 'di lnga rten cing mi ngor ro //
NK069(tu)001:20916: mi dor ba'i phyir dang du len pas na /
NK069(tu)001:20917: dang du blang ba'i dam tshig zhes bya ba yin no ////
NK069(tu)001:20918: dam rdzas lnga po dang du blang ba la dgos pa brgyad de /
NK069(tu)001:20919: dang po grub pa bzhis rgyan pa'i phyir dang du blang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:20920: chos nyid rang bzhin gyis grub pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20921: dam rdzas lnga nyid chos nyid du gcig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20922: chos can mtshan mar snang bas grub pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20923: dam rdzas lnga sangs rgyas lnga 'grub pa ci te bya ba med de /
NK069(tu)001:20924: rang gi mtshan nyid kyis grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20926: dam rdzas lnga nyid rigs lnga yin pa'i mthus so //
NK069(tu)001:20927: byin brlabs ting nges grub pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20928: sangs rgyas kyis sngags dang phyag rgya ting nges byin rlob par rnal 'byor pas shes so //
NK069(tu)001:20929: gnyis nad lnga bsal ba'i phyir dang du blang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:20930: byang chub sems kyi tshad nad sel /
NK069(tu)001:20931: rag tas thor bu dang gag pa sel /
NK069(tu)001:20934: dri chus blang nad thub bo //
NK069(tu)001:20935: gsum pa rtsang rme'i rtogs pa sbyang ba'i phyir blang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:20936: dkar gsum mngar gsum rtsang ba'i zas men la /
NK069(tu)001:20937: dam rdzas lnga rme ba'i zas men de /
NK069(tu)001:20938: rtsang rme'i rtog pa chos nyid du sbyong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:20939: bzhi pa thun mong gi dgos pa lnga grub pa'i phyir blang ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:20940: byang chub sems kyis tshe ring /
NK069(tu)001:20942: dri chen gyis phyug por byed /
NK069(tu)001:20945: lnga pa rigs lnga 'grub pa'i phyir yang dang du blang ste /
NK069(tu)001:20946: byang sems kyis rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK069(tu)001:20947: rag tas snang ba mtha' yas /
NK069(tu)001:20948: dri chen rnam par snang mdzad /
NK069(tu)001:20950: dri chu don yod grub pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20951: drug pa mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thob pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:20952: tshe 'dir sdug bsngal las grol nas thun mong gi dngos grub 'thob la /
NK069(tu)001:20954: bdun pa bcud lnga 'thung ba ni lam gyi mchog yin pa'i phyir dang du blang ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:20955: byang sems rtsa kun d+har ma ste /
NK069(tu)001:20963: lus kyi bcud lnga po nyid khams bdud rtsi ste /
NK069(tu)001:20964: rigs lngar gnas par shes pa ni lam gyi mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:20965: brgyad pa thabs kyi lung sten shes na yon tan rjod las 'das pa thob pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20967: khams bdud rtsi dang snying po rlung yi ge'i gzugs su gnas pa de dam tshig sems dapa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20968: de la rang gis rlung bcug nas der thim pa ni ye shes sems dpa' stims pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20973: bag chags rmi lam du 'char te /
NK069(tu)001:20974: thams cad du rigs lnga'i snang ba shes rtan du gyur pas na yon tan rjod las 'das pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:20976: yan lag bcu'i dam tshig ste //
NK069(tu)001:20977: zhes de ltar mi spang ba dug lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:20978: mi dor ba dam rdzas lta ste /
NK069(tu)001:20979: bcu ni yan lag gi dam tshig ste /
NK069(tu)001:20980: ye nas dag pa ni bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:20981: dang po rgyud dag pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20982: phung po khams dang skye mched rgyu 'byung ba lnga yang /
NK069(tu)001:20983: rang gi sems su snang bas 'byung ba lnga rang rgyud pa dag ste /
NK069(tu)001:20985: rgyu'i mtshan nyid dag pa ni //
NK069(tu)001:20986: phyi rol chen po lnga rnams te //
NK069(tu)001:20987: sems nyid gzung 'dzin gnyis snang ba //
NK069(tu)001:20988: bzung ba'i yul ni 'byung ba ste //
NK069(tu)001:20989: rgyu nyid rang gi sems yin pas //
NK069(tu)001:20992: gnyis pa 'bras bu dag pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20993: rgyu 'byung ba lngas skyed pa'i phung po lnga /
NK069(tu)001:20994: dam rdzas rigs lngar dag ste /
NK069(tu)001:20995: dper na 'tshal dmar na khu ba yang dmar ba lta bu'o //
NK069(tu)001:20997: 'bras bu yongs su dag pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:20998: sems can kun gyi rus pa ste /
