NK069(tu)001:20999: rdo rje byang chub sems yin la //
NK069(tu)001:21000: sha ni pad ma rag ta yin //
NK069(tu)001:21001: dri chen dri chu gur gum chu //
NK069(tu)001:21002: so so'i lus la gnas pas dag /
NK069(tu)001:21004: ye nas dag mnyam rtogs pas spyad //
NK069(tu)001:21005: ces de yang rtogs pa ji lta bu dang ldan pas spyan zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:21006: chos thams cad stong pa bdag myed pa /
NK069(tu)001:21007: dngos po dang mtshan ma'i skyon dag pa /
NK069(tu)001:21008: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs pa dang ldan pas spyan zhe'am /
NK069(tu)001:21009: yang na chos thams cad dag pa bzhi'am /
NK069(tu)001:21010: mnyam pa bzhi'i gtan tshigs kyis /
NK069(tu)001:21011: lha dang lho mo dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rtogs pas spyan zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:21012: bsrung zhing sgrub pa'i dam tshig lnga //
NK069(tu)001:21015: yang dag lam du zhugs pa la byams pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21016: bsang ba bzhung bzhin du mi bsgrag pa gsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:21018: bla myed mi yang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21019: sngags phyag rgya rgyu ma cad pa gnyis so //
NK069(tu)001:21020: rtsa ba yin te rigs myed 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:21021: zhes de lnga ni rtsa ba yin te /
NK069(tu)001:21022: nyams na bla na myed pa'i sangs rgyas 'grub pa'i rigs rlag pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:21024: gsum pa don dam dag pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:21025: phyi nang gi chos thams cad gang ltar yang ma grub pas /
NK069(tu)001:21029: don dam dmigs myed dag pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:21030: phyi nang chos rnams thams yang /
NK069(tu)001:21031: rang gi ngo bo ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:21032: skye 'gag myed pa ye nas dag /
NK069(tu)001:21034: bzhi pa kun rdzob dag pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:21035: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad chu zla ltar snang la rang bzhin myed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21037: kun rdzob ye nas dag pa ni //
NK069(tu)001:21038: sgru ma'i rang bzhin thams cad snang //
NK069(tu)001:21039: chu zla'i tshul du mi dmyigs na //
NK069(tu)001:21040: mi dmyigs pa nyid sna tshogs snang //
NK069(tu)001:21041: de bzhin gshegs dang ye nas mnyam //
NK069(tu)001:21044: dang po thun mong gi mnyam pa gnyis ni /
NK069(tu)001:21045: don dam skye ba myed par kun mnyam pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21046: kun rdzob rkyen bzhis lus par mnyam ste /
NK069(tu)001:21051: lhag pa'i mnyam pa gnyis ni /
NK069(tu)001:21052: don dam pa'i ngo bo skor bdun lhun gyis grub pa de /
NK069(tu)001:21053: bsam brjod las 'das pa'i phyir dang /
NK069(tu)001:21054: shes bya dang sgrub bya'i don gnyis ka yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21055: shes rab dam pa'i yul yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21056: rtog ge ba'i yul ma yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21057: rtogs na mi slu bar yon tan thams cad zad pa myed par 'byung bas na lhag go //
NK069(tu)001:21061: rgyu rkyen bzhi la 'dus nas snang ba tsam las /
NK069(tu)001:21062: 'dir ni ye shes 'gag pa myed par thams cad du snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:21064: ye shes 'gog pa myed pa des gdul bya sangs rgya ba'i don byed nus pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21066: rnam rtog dang 'thun pa'i las snang ba ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:21067: gnas lugs dang 'thun pa'i ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:21069: rig pas brtags pa'i stong pa ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:21070: ngo bo nyid dag pas yul las 'das pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21071: mi spang mi dor lnga gnyis ni //
NK069(tu)001:21072: zhes myi spang ba nang gi nyon mongs pa chen po lnga'i mtshan nyid rtogs par bya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21073: mi dor ba bdud rtsi lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:21076: zhes yan lag gi dam tshig yin te /
NK069(tu)001:21077: de las 'das na dngos grub thob par dkar bo zhes pas te /
NK069(tu)001:21078: sting mi thob pa lta bu ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:21079: nye bar mi thob ste 'gyang bar gyur pa la rka zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:21080: mnyam la mnyam par sbyor ba'i //
NK069(tu)001:21081: zhes chos thams cad kyi gzhi' mnyam pa nyid de /
NK069(tu)001:21082: dbyings dang rig pa yang dbyer myed par mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:21083: mtshan ma dang mtshan ma myed pa yang dbyer myed par mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:21084: kun nas nyon mongs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21085: rnam par byang ba yang dbyer myed par mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:21086: 'khor dang mya ngan las 'das pa yang dbyer myed par mnyam la /
NK069(tu)001:21087: de la shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin gyis mnyam par sbyar ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:21088: mnyam pa'i dam tshig la gnas na //
NK069(tu)001:21089: zhes chos thams cad mnyam pa'i rang bzhin las mi 'da' bas na mnyam pa'i dam tshig /
NK069(tu)001:21090: de'i don shes rab kyis kyang rtogs par byas la /
NK069(tu)001:21091: rtogs pa'i don la ting nge 'dzin gyis mnyam par sbyar ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:21092: mnyam rdzogs chen po thob par 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:21093: zhes de ltar shes rab kyis rtogs nas ting nge 'dzin la rtse gcig tu gnas na /
NK069(tu)001:21094: mnyam pa nyid rdzogs pa chen por sangs rgyas pa'i 'bras bu thob pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:21096: mnyam pa'i ngang las 'da' bar myi bya /
NK069(tu)001:21097: 'das na sangs rgyas ma yin no //
NK069(tu)001:21099: 'das na sangs rgyas ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:21101: dang po yang mnyam pa nyid kyi don thugs su chud pas grub pa mnyems pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:21102: grub pa snyems nas kyang mnyam pa nyid kyi ngang las mi 'da' bar zhugs pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:21103: rnal 'byor pas kyang mnyam pa nyid kyi don rtogs par byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:21104: rtogs pa'i don la ting nge 'dzin gyis myi 'da' bar gnas na /
NK069(tu)001:21106: mnyam pa las 'das na rnam par thams cad mkhyen pa'i sangs rgyas su 'grub mi ni 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:21107: nyams pa ma skangs pa'i skyon /
NK069(tu)001:21108: rtsa ba nyams pa'i phyal ba dag /
NK069(tu)001:21109: ces gso' la nye bar mi rtson na //
NK069(tu)001:21110: zhes slar gso' ba la nye bar mi rtson pa de /
NK069(tu)001:21111: rdo rje dmyal bar ltung ste /
NK069(tu)001:21112: dmyal ba phal pa thams cad kyi sdug bsngal sdoms pas de'i 'bum gyi char yang mi phod la /
NK069(tu)001:21113: de la sangs rgyas stong gi 'od zer dang /
NK069(tu)001:21114: byang chub sems dpa'i 'phrin las rgyun du mdzad yang mi phan te /
NK069(tu)001:21115: skal pa chen po ther 'bum du dmyal bar ltung /
NK069(tu)001:21116: dmyal ba'i gnas de'i 'jig rten zhig na /
NK069(tu)001:21117: dmyal ba ma zhig pa'i sa gzhan du 'phos nas /
NK069(tu)001:21119: skad cig yud kyang smra ma byed //
NK069(tu)001:21120: ces mi chos kyi gtam yang skad cig yud tsam smrar mi byed na /
NK069(tu)001:21121: lha chos kyi gtam lta ci smos /
NK069(tu)001:21122: nyams 'gyur nyes pa brjod mi lang //
NK069(tu)001:21123: zhes nyams par gyur pa de dang 'dres par gyur na ni /
NK069(tu)001:21124: nyes pa brjod kyis mi lang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:21125: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams 'gyur na //
NK069(tu)001:21126: zhes rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po ni /
NK069(tu)001:21130: spyi khyab byang chub sems nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:21131: bsgrub pa thams cad log par 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:21132: na mchog dang thun mong gi sgrub pa thams cad log par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:21134: dam tshig nyams par gyur pa'i rgyu dang /
NK069(tu)001:21135: nyams na snga ltas sngon du yong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:21136: nyams par gyur pa'i rgyu ni nyi shu ste /
NK069(tu)001:21137: mi chos kyi sa bzung nas blon po'i las byed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21141: khe dang dregs gnyis 'dod pas 'du bsten pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21142: rdzas la chags sems che ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21146: rang gi lta spyod mnyems pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21157: nyams pa'i rtags ni gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:21162: dgra' dang bgegs la bden pa ma 'jug /
NK069(tu)001:21163: 'khor dang longs spyod yid du 'ong ba dang 'bral /
NK069(tu)001:21167: tsams pa'i las la 'bras bu mi 'ong /
NK069(tu)001:21168: mdor na yid du mi 'ong sna tshogs 'byung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:21170: gal te dam nyams pa la nyams rtags myed na mi rung ste /
NK069(tu)001:21171: tshe phyi ma'i bde bar tshe 'dir zad nas /
NK069(tu)001:21172: de nas rtag tu sdug bsngal lo //
NK069(tu)001:21173: gal te dam ma nyams pa la nyams rtags byung na /
NK069(tu)001:21175: sngon gyi rnam smin zad pa yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:21177: de nas phyi mar ngan song gi sdug bsngal dang bral lo //
NK069(tu)001:21178: yid du mi 'ongs sna tshogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:21184: zhes 'bras bu sdug bsngal mang po'i mtshan ma ngan pa sna tshogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:21185: yid du mi 'ong ba thams cad mi 'dod bzhin du 'du ste /
NK069(tu)001:21186: dper na rdo khab len la lcags 'du ba bzhin du 'adu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21187: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams pa'i skyon la lnga ste /
NK069(tu)001:21188: dang po byang chub sems kyi dam tshig nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:21189: skal par dge ba ci bsags kyang gzhi' rten myed par gyur nas /
NK069(tu)001:21191: gnyis pa sku'i dam tshig nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:21192: ya nga ba'i nad kyis sdug bsngal yong /
NK069(tu)001:21193: dus ma yin par 'chi ba'i dus byed /
NK069(tu)001:21194: skal pa gcig tu rdo rje dmyal bar ltung /
NK069(tu)001:21195: thon nas kyang bde' ba dang mi phrad do //
NK069(tu)001:21196: gsum pa gsung gi dam tshig nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:21197: bgegs rnams thogs pa myed par yong /
NK069(tu)001:21200: chos la byin brlabs mi yong /
NK069(tu)001:21201: skal pa gnyis su dmyal bar ltung /
NK069(tu)001:21202: bzhi pa thugs kyi dam tshig nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:21203: sgrub pa la rtags mi yong /
NK069(tu)001:21204: lus myos shing khas skur pa 'debs /
NK069(tu)001:21205: mnyo' 'bog dang dbang po 'chal ba'i nad yong /
NK069(tu)001:21206: bskal pa gsum du dmyal bar ltung /
NK069(tu)001:21207: lnga pa rtsa ba kun nyams na ni /
NK069(tu)001:21208: gong du rtsa ba kun nyams zhes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21210: yan lag dam tshig nyams 'gyur na //
NK069(tu)001:21211: yan lag gi dam tshig nyams par 'gyur na /
NK069(tu)001:21212: 'bras bu myed cing ngan song ltung //
NK069(tu)001:21213: tshe 'dir bsgrub pa'i 'bras bu myed cing /
NK069(tu)001:21214: slar tshe phyi mar ngan song gsum du ltung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:21215: yan lag gi dam tshig nyams par gyur na ni nyes pa gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:21220: theg pa chen po la gzhan gyis bcas 'dogs te chos snub pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21221: thun mong gi dngos grub sgrub thag ring ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21222: gdul bya'i don rnams yal bar dor ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21223: lta ba gnyis myed yin pa skad zer zhing /
NK069(tu)001:21224: spyod pa blang dor du spyod pas /
NK069(tu)001:21227: theg pa phyi nang 'dres pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21228: bka'i byin brlabs nyams pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21229: ci bsgrubs pa thams cad grub par bka'o //
NK069(tu)001:21230: bsrung ba'i lha thams cad g.yel /
NK069(tu)001:21231: zab mo'i chos thams cad ring du song ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:21233: ngan song gsum gyi gnas ngan pa len par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:21234: dam tshig rnams ni rdo rje che //
NK069(tu)001:21235: gong du stan pa'i rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig rnams ni /
NK069(tu)001:21236: sku gsung thugs rdo rje dang dbyer myed pas rdo rje che'o //
NK069(tu)001:21237: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid yin //
NK069(tu)001:21238: dam tshig ni sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin nam /
NK069(tu)001:21240: sgrub pa'i rgyu yang yin pas bdag nyid yin no //
NK069(tu)001:21241: dam tshig che ba'i dpe' ni bcu gcig ste /
NK069(tu)001:21242: dam tshig sa gzhi' dang 'dra ste lam dang 'bras bu'i chos 'byung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21243: dam tshig so 'tshams kyi 'khar dang 'dra ste ma
NK069(tu)001:21244: srungs na nyes pa che la bsrung na legs pa
NK069(tu)001:21245: dang / dam tshig yid bzhin du 'byung ba'i nor
NK069(tu)001:21246: bu rin po che dbang gi rgyal po dang 'dra
NK069(tu)001:21247: ste dgos 'dod kyi dngos grub 'byung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21248: dam tshig nam mkha' dang 'dra ste kun shong ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21249: dam tshig pha ma dang 'dra ste dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas skyed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21250: dam tshig rgya mtsho' dang 'dra ste yon tan gyi rlabs 'byung ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21251: dam tshig me dpung dang 'dra ste 'gas kyang 'tshig pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21252: dam tshig sman dang 'dra ste 'khor ba'i nad lcong snying sbyong ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21253: dam tshig rgyal po dang 'dra ste /
NK069(tu)001:21254: rtsang mar thub na dge' ba gzhan gyi sna 'gas kyang mtsho' ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21255: dam tshig rgya mtshor nor len pa'i tshong dpon ded
NK069(tu)001:21256: dpon chen po dang 'dra ste dang po nas tha
NK069(tu)001:21257: ma'i bar du mthar phyin par byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21258: de bas na dam tshig rnams ni sku gsung thugs dbyer myed pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:21259: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid yin pas thams cad kun tshang ba yin no zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:21260: rtsa ba'i dam tshig sum brgya drug cur dbye' ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:21261: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga la ni //
NK069(tu)001:21269: zhes de gang yang rung ba gcig la yang gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:21270: lus ngag yid gsum gyi bsrung bya ma 'gags pas /
NK069(tu)001:21272: nang rig pas srung bya stong par shes pas shes rab tu rtogs /
NK069(tu)001:21273: de lnga po re re la yang thabs shes rab gnyis gnyis te bcu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21275: zhes rtsa ba lnga po re re la lus ngag yid gsum la bcu bcu ste /
NK069(tu)001:21276: sum cu sum cur dbye' ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:21278: gong ma'i bcu ste brgya drug cur rtsa ba las dbye' ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:21279: dang po byang chub sems kyi sum cu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21280: zhi ba la yan lag lhag pa'i lha dgu' zhi ba nyid dang bcu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21281: khro bo la yan lag lhag pa'i lha dgu' khro bo nyid dang bcu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21282: thun mong gi byams snying rje dga' stangs snyoms bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:21283: khyad par gyi khro stum byams pa /
NK069(tu)001:21285: bsgral zhing stabs pa dga' ba /
NK069(tu)001:21286: yal bar mi dor stangs snyoms bzhi ste brgyad /
NK069(tu)001:21287: don dam pa dang kun rdzob gnyis te bcu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21288: gnyis pa bla ma sum cu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21289: de la lus kyi bcu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21290: sor rde'u tsam yang mi rteg pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21293: g.yas g.yon mdun rgyab drang por mi 'gro ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21294: gdan bsogs mi rlom pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21295: spyan mngar 'greng 'a dug gi ngan spyod spang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21296: rgyan 'dogs sgeg chos spang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21297: ma rabs kyi spyod pa kun spang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21298: spyod lam zon chag bzab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21300: de la ngag gi bcu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21311: de la sems kyi bcu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21321: dus rtag tu gdung sems rgyun mi gcad do //
NK069(tu)001:21322: gsum pa sngags dang phyag rgya la sum cu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21333: stan par bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21340: zhi ba la dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK069(tu)001:21347: zhi khro gnyis gcig tu rtsis pa dang bco' lnga'o //
NK069(tu)001:21348: bzhi pa mched kyi sum cu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21353: lta spyod mtho' ba'i gong mi gcad /
NK069(tu)001:21355: dus kun tu bag zin bya /
NK069(tu)001:21359: lus la snun cing sreg pa spang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:21370: srid zhu'i sgra dang bcas par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:21381: mi gdung bar spang bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:21382: lnga pa gsang ba mi spel ba'i bcu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21385: gsang bar gnyer gtad pa dang bcu' /
NK069(tu)001:21386: sems kyis rtan par mi bsam pas bcu /
NK069(tu)001:21387: ngag gis brjod par mi bya ba bcu /
NK069(tu)001:21388: lus rdas mi stan pa bcu ste sum cu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21391: rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga gang yang rung ba gcig la /
NK069(tu)001:21392: thabs dang shes rab tu dbye' /
NK069(tu)001:21393: thabs la yang sku gsung thugs gsum du dbye' /
NK069(tu)001:21394: sku gsung thugs gsum la yang /
NK069(tu)001:21395: sku gsung thugs yon tan 'phrin las lnga lngar dabye'o //
NK069(tu)001:21396: de ltar bco' lnga yod pa la /
NK069(tu)001:21397: thabs zang ma nan te bcu drug go //
NK069(tu)001:21398: shes rab la yang de ltar sgres pas bcu drug tu dabye'o //
NK069(tu)001:21399: bcu drug phrag gnyis la sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK069(tu)001:21400: de ltar sum cu rtsa gnyis phrag lnga la /
NK069(tu)001:21402: zer te sngon ma ltar dbye' ba 'thad do //
NK069(tu)001:21403: phyi ma yang bla ma'i bzhed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21404: yan lag gi dam tshig las nyis brgya dbye' ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:21405: yan lag dam tshig lnga gnyis la //
NK069(tu)001:21406: ste mi spang ba'i nyon mongs pa lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:21407: dang du blang ba'i dam rdzas lnga'o //
NK069(tu)001:21408: gcig la'ang bcu phrag gnyis su dbye' //
NK069(tu)001:21409: zhes nyon mongs pa lnga po re re la nyi shu nyi ste brgya /
NK069(tu)001:21410: dam rdzas lnga po re re la nyi shu nyi shu ste brgya /
NK069(tu)001:21412: mi spang ba'i nyon mongs pa lnga la re re la nyi shu nyi shu ste /
NK069(tu)001:21413: dang po gti' mug gi nyi shu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21414: gzhi' sgral ba'i zhing bcu las dbye' ste /
NK069(tu)001:21415: dkon mchog gsum gyi spyi dgra dang /
NK069(tu)001:21416: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dgos dgra dang /
NK069(tu)001:21419: slob dpon mched las 'khrus pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21424: ngan song gsum gcig tu rtsis pa dang bcu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21425: de la thabs kyi mdzad pas zhing bzang ngan dbye' gsal myed par sgrol thabs bcu /
NK069(tu)001:21426: shes rab kyis stong pa dang gnyis myed du myi dbyed pa dang bcu dang nyi shu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21427: zhe sdang gi nyi shu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21428: zhing bcu thabs kyi mdzad pas bcom nas shes rab rang bzhin myed par sgrol ba bcu /
NK069(tu)001:21429: thabs dang shes rab kyi zhe sdang gis bdag gzhan
NK069(tu)001:21430: gyi don rdzogs par byed pa bcu ste nyi shu'o
NK069(tu)001:21442: de la thugs rjes zhi rgyas dbang drag lhun grub
NK069(tu)001:21443: te rigs lnga'i yum du byin gyis brlab pa lnga
NK069(tu)001:21444: ste / ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21447: rang bzhin gyis sbyar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:21448: shes rab chen pos don la chags pa dang bcu ste nyi shu ste /
NK069(tu)001:21449: nga rgyal gyi nyi shu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21450: thabs kyi man ngag steng du gyur pa ni zhing bcu la sgrol ba'i nga rgyal bcu /
NK069(tu)001:21451: shes rab kyis stong par rtogs pa'i nga rgyal bcu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21463: bcu po de la thabs kyi mdzad pa'i sgor mi tshud pa'i 'phrag dog bcu /
NK069(tu)001:21464: shes rab kyis sta ngan mi tshugs pa'i bcu ste nyi shu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21465: dang du blang ba'i dam rdzas lnga ni /
NK069(tu)001:21466: re re la nyi shu nyi shu ste /
NK069(tu)001:21467: byang chub sems kyis nyi shu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21478: zhing bcu'i byang sems bcu ste nyi shu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21479: pad ma rag ta'i nyi shu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21480: yab kyi sna bug gi rag ta /
NK069(tu)001:21484: shing gi rag ta sh+ri shing dang /
NK069(tu)001:21485: me tog gi rag ta ram bu'i spu nyog pa /
NK069(tu)001:21486: 'bras bu'i rag ta ram bu'i 'phru gu dang /
NK069(tu)001:21489: zhing bcu'i rag ta dang nyi shu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21490: dri chen gyi nyi shu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21501: sgral ba'i zhing gi dri chen bcu ste nyi shu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21502: sha chen gyi nyi shu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21507: rkang lag gi nya sha dang /
NK069(tu)001:21508: bla dpung gi bem sha dang /
NK069(tu)001:21509: rtsos gong gi glen sha dang /
NK069(tu)001:21511: de rnams kyi dwangs ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:21513: zhing bcu'i sha bcu ste nyi shu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21525: sgral ba'i zhing bcu'i dri chu ste nyi shu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21526: de ltar dam rdzas lnga la brgya /
NK069(tu)001:21527: nyon mongs pa lnga la brgya ste nyis bargya'o //
NK069(tu)001:21528: yang na yan lag dam tshig lnga gnyis bcu ni /
NK069(tu)001:21529: gang yang rung ba gcig la /
NK069(tu)001:21530: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su dbye /
NK069(tu)001:21533: sku gsung thugs gsum gsum dgu' /
NK069(tu)001:21534: thabs zang mas mnan te bcu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21535: shes rab la yang de'i zlas sgres te bcu'o //
NK069(tu)001:21536: gcig la yang bcu phrag gnyis te nyi shu /
NK069(tu)001:21537: de ltar bcu phrag gnyis gnyis te nyis bargya'o //
NK069(tu)001:21538: gong gi rtsa ba'i brgya drug cu bzhag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21540: dam tshig 'di ni smad po che //
NK069(tu)001:21542: dam tshig 'di'i yon tan ni ngo mtshar rmad du 'byung bas rmada po che'o //
NK069(tu)001:21543: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na //
NK069(tu)001:21544: snod kyi 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na /
NK069(tu)001:21545: srid gsum 'gro ba ji snyed pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:21546: bcud kyi sems can srid pa gasum gyis sdus pa'i
NK069(tu)001:21547: 'gro ba ji snyed pa'i mang po zhig yod la
NK069(tu)001:21548: / 'gro ba so so'i rtogs pa yang ji snyed mang po zhig yod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21549: rtog 'dul dam tshig de snyed spro //
NK069(tu)001:21550: de dag rtog pa 'dul ba'i gnyen po /
NK069(tu)001:21551: dam tshig yang de snyed spro ste /
NK069(tu)001:21552: le'u lag gi dam tshig dang /
NK069(tu)001:21553: dpal gsang ba 'dus pa'i yul la 'jug pa'i dam tshig kun no //
NK069(tu)001:21554: gzhan yang rgyal mchog kun bzang gi //
NK069(tu)001:21555: zhes dam tshig gi sa la gnas shing ma nyams par bsrungs na /
NK069(tu)001:21557: mnyam rdzogs chen po thob par 'gyur /
NK069(tu)001:21560: nyon mongs pa rnams spangs nas nyon mongs pa las rgyal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:21562: nyon mongs pa nyid gnas su dag par rtogs nas /
NK069(tu)001:21563: nyon mongs pa nyid ma spangs par spyad pas rgyal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:21565: rgyal ba'i mchog tu gyur pas na rgyal mchog go //
NK069(tu)001:21566: de'i dus na kun tu bzang po gzhi' dang ldan te /
NK069(tu)001:21567: rang bzhin kun tu bzang po ni /
NK069(tu)001:21568: nyon mongs pa nyid sangs rgyas par gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21569: spyod pa kun tu bzang po ni /
NK069(tu)001:21570: de ltar rtogs pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:21571: ci spyod skyon gyis ma gos shing /
NK069(tu)001:21572: bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogs par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:21573: dus kun tu bzang po ni /
NK069(tu)001:21574: de'i dus na 'das pa'i dus kyang bzang /
NK069(tu)001:21577: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid du'am /
NK069(tu)001:21578: dus gsum 'gyur ba myed par lhun gyis grub pas /
NK069(tu)001:21579: dus kun tu bzang po zhes bya ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:21580: thams cad ma lus phyag rgya'i //
NK069(tu)001:21581: zhes kun tu bzang po gzhi dang ldan pa'i dus na /
NK069(tu)001:21582: nyon mongs pa lngas sdus pa'i chos thams cad ma
NK069(tu)001:21583: lus par sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgyar sangs pa'i
NK069(tu)001:21584: rang bzhin du ye nas gnas pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:21585: bsgrub myed dam pa ma lus 'grub //
NK069(tu)001:21586: ces ye nas gnas pa'i don ni /
NK069(tu)001:21588: rtogs pa'i ngang la ma yengs par gnas na /
NK069(tu)001:21589: kun nas nyon mongs pa'i chos ni skyon du 'gyur nas yang du yang myed la /
NK069(tu)001:21590: rnam par byang ba'i chos ni yon tan du ltas nas sgrub tu yang myed pas sgrub myed /
NK069(tu)001:21591: de ltar kun nas nyon mongs pa'i chos ma spangs par spyod pa nyid kyis /
NK069(tu)001:21592: yon tan du dam pa dang ldan pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub ma lus par 'grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:21593: de la sogs pa mtha' yas mchog /
NK069(tu)001:21594: ces gong du smos pa de dag yon tan mdo' tsam ste /
NK069(tu)001:21595: yon tan mtha' yas pa mchog dang ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:21597: de yang thun mong gi yon tan mtha' yas te brjod las 'das /
NK069(tu)001:21598: mchog gi yon tan mtha' yas pas sku gsum ye shes lnga ldan nam /
NK069(tu)001:21599: sku lnga lhun grub thob bo //
NK069(tu)001:21600: 'dir ngag don du dam tshig ma nyams pa'i yon tan ni /
NK069(tu)001:21601: sku'i dam tshig ma nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:21605: thun mong gi nyes byas 'dag par 'gyur /
NK069(tu)001:21606: srid pa gsum la dbang skur /
NK069(tu)001:21607: theg chen zab mo'i don thob par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:21608: gsung gi dam tshig nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:21611: mthu' dang byin rlabs bsam gyis mi khyab /
NK069(tu)001:21613: bsam pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs so //
NK069(tu)001:21614: thugs kyi dam tshig ma nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:21620: lha rnams kyis dbang skur ro //
NK069(tu)001:21625: yan lag gi yon tan ni /
NK069(tu)001:21626: theg chen gyi lta spyod gzhung srongs pas /
NK069(tu)001:21632: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig ma nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:21634: dam tshig kun 'dir ma srungs par rdzogs pas na /
NK069(tu)001:21635: dge slong byang chub sems dpa' yin /
NK069(tu)001:21636: rnal 'byor rnal 'byor chen po yin no //
NK069(tu)001:21637: rgyal ba'i rigs mchog 'dzin pa de //
NK069(tu)001:21638: zhes thun mong ma yin yin pa'i yon tan bdun dang ldan te /
NK069(tu)001:21639: dam tshig gi ngang la gnas shing ma nyams par srungs na /
NK069(tu)001:21640: 'bras bu nyan thos dang rang rgyal bar mi skye zhing /
NK069(tu)001:21641: rgyal ba sangs rgyas kyi gdung tshob cing rig 'dzin par nges pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21643: zhes dam tshig gi ngang la gnas shing ma nyams par srungs na /
NK069(tu)001:21644: 'jig rten gyi gtso' bo lha dbang phyug chen po dang /
NK069(tu)001:21646: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis /
NK069(tu)001:21647: spyi bo gtsug gi no bu ltar skur zhing /
NK069(tu)001:21648: ci dgos pa'i las grub par byed pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21649: dam pa'i mchog dang dam pa yis //
NK069(tu)001:21650: zhes dam tshig gi ngang la gnas shing ma nyams par srungs na /
NK069(tu)001:21651: dam pa'i mchog sangs rgyas dang /
NK069(tu)001:21652: dam pa byang chub sems dpa' yis /
NK069(tu)001:21653: sras dang spun dgongs byin gyis rlob //
NK069(tu)001:21655: sangs rgyas kyis ni sus su dgongs shing byin gyis rlob pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21657: yun du dgongs nas byin gyis rlob bo //
NK069(tu)001:21658: bde gshegs nyid kyi yul la zhugs //
NK069(tu)001:21659: zhes dam tshig gi ngang la gnas shing ma nyams par srungs na /
NK069(tu)001:21660: da lta nyid nas bde' bar gshegs pa'i thugs gsang
NK069(tu)001:21661: ba'i ye shes mchog gi spyod yul la zhugs te
NK069(tu)001:21662: / nyan thos kyi sdom pa mnos pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:21663: bdag nam 'tsho'i bar du zhes mnos nas /
NK069(tu)001:21664: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa mnos pa ni bdag
NK069(tu)001:21665: byang chub snying po la gnas kyi bar du zhes
NK069(tu)001:21666: mnos la / sngags kyi dam tshig mnos pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:21667: da lta nyid nas bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum dang /
NK069(tu)001:21668: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs dang dbyer myed par khas blangs te /
NK069(tu)001:21669: da lta nyid nas bde' ba'i sku gsung thugs ye
NK069(tu)001:21670: shes gsang ba mchog gi spyod yul la zhugs pa
NK069(tu)001:21671: yin no // 'jig myed kun tu bzang por sbyor //
NK069(tu)001:21672: zhes dam tshig gi ngang la gnas shing srungs na
NK069(tu)001:21673: 'khor ba dang ngan song gi 'jigs pa myed de
NK069(tu)001:21674: / chos thams cad kun tu bzang por sangs rgyas
NK069(tu)001:21675: pa'i rang bzhin du shes rab dang nges sbyor ro
NK069(tu)001:21676: / // ji bzhin nyid dang 'dul ba'i thabs //
NK069(tu)001:21677: dam tshig gi ngang la gnas shing ma nyams par srungs na /
NK069(tu)001:21678: ye ji bzhin pa'i ma nyams pa nyid du ston pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21679: 'dul ba'i thabs ji snyed pa'i tshul khrims dang /
NK069(tu)001:21680: ji snyed sdom pa bsam yas pa //
NK069(tu)001:21681: ma lus rnam dag lhun gyis grub //
NK069(tu)001:21682: ces byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa bsam yas pa kun yang 'dus te /
NK069(tu)001:21683: mtshan nyid thig pa chen po'i chub sems dpa' de /
NK069(tu)001:21684: gsang sngags kri yo ga la sogs gsum yang /
NK069(tu)001:21685: dam tshig gi ngang la gnas shing ma nyams par srungs na /
NK069(tu)001:21686: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig ma nyams par srungs pa'i nang du ni /
NK069(tu)001:21693: yo ga la sogs pa yang re re nas srung mi dgos par /
NK069(tu)001:21694: lhun gyis grub pa nyid du rnam par dag pas na /
NK069(tu)001:21695: dam tshig ma lus pa'i nyes pa rnam par dag nas /
NK069(tu)001:21696: yon tan rnams lhun gyis grub par gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:21697: nyams na bskang pas rdzogs pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:21698: zhes nyan thos kyi tshul khrims ni /
NK069(tu)001:21701: dge slong ni rtsa ba bzhi las gang yang rung ba gcig nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:21702: de phan cad sh+aakya'i sras ma yin /
NK069(tu)001:21705: sman kus pa dang 'dra ste slar gso' ba'i mi rung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:21706: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:21708: gser skyogs zhom pa ni slar srang du yang rung ste /
NK069(tu)001:21709: de ma yin pa'i chag tshabs chen mgar ba mkhas pas slar brdung du yang rung ste /
NK069(tu)001:21711: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa nyams pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:21712: sdom pa chags pa'i dge slong las slar nod du yang rung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:21713: gsang sngags kyi dam tshig ni /
NK069(tu)001:21714: nyan thos kyi tshul khrims nyams pa rdza chag pa bzhin slar blang du myed pa yang ma yin /
NK069(tu)001:21715: byang chub sems pa'i gser skyogs bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:21716: gzhi' nas nod dgos pa yang ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:21717: gang nyams pa de sor chud par byas pas skongs te /
NK069(tu)001:21718: de la yang skang bas rdzogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:21719: mi skongs pa gnyis yod do //
NK069(tu)001:21722: mched lcam dral gang yang rung ba gcig la /
NK069(tu)001:21724: de la bzod par gsol nas thugs rangs par ma byas par /
NK069(tu)001:21728: phyi na gnas 'gal bar byed pa de ni /
NK069(tu)001:21729: rdo rje sems dpa' dang 'dra bas yong mi skongs /
NK069(tu)001:21730: skongs par mi 'gyur zhes gsungs te /
NK069(tu)001:21733: byang chub sems kyi dam nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:21734: bla ma mkhas pa la blangs te gnas par bya /
NK069(tu)001:21736: gang la nyams pa'i bla ma dang mched kun la /
NK069(tu)001:21737: yon gyis mnyes par byas la /
NK069(tu)001:21739: phyin cad sdom pa legs par bzung /
NK069(tu)001:21740: gal te grongs chad du gyur na /
NK069(tu)001:21741: de'i slob dpon bzhugs na de la bshags /
NK069(tu)001:21742: de yang myed na de dang yon tan mnyam brgya la bshags /
NK069(tu)001:21743: de yang ma snyed na de dang mnyam pa gsum la /
NK069(tu)001:21746: nang du dkyil 'khor gyi lha me lha'i lto bar bzhugs la mchod /
NK069(tu)001:21747: de'i rjes su bla ma la mchod la bshags /
NK069(tu)001:21748: nor rdzas yang dbang po gsum la dbul lo //
NK069(tu)001:21749: gal te slob dpon dang mched bshags pa de mi len na /
NK069(tu)001:21750: dam nyams pa dang mi nyams pa gcig ka rdo rje dmyal bar skye'o //
NK069(tu)001:21751: de bas na bshags pa byed pa de blang bar bya gal che'o //
NK069(tu)001:21752: gsung gi dam tshig nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:21753: rang gi lus ngag yid gsum /
NK069(tu)001:21754: yi dam lha'i sku gsung thugs su bsgoms la /
NK069(tu)001:21756: sgrub pa chen po lan gsum bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:21757: thugs kyi dam tshig nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:21758: 'gro drug rang sems su bsal bar rtogs par byas la /
NK069(tu)001:21760: bdag gis bdag la gsang du myed /
NK069(tu)001:21761: bdag mi rtog pa'i ting nge 'dzin du zhugs la /
NK069(tu)001:21762: don ma yengs par blo la 'dris par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:21763: yan lag gi dam tshig nyams na /
NK069(tu)001:21764: gang nyams pa de sor bcug la /
NK069(tu)001:21765: tshogs brgya rtsa brgyad gtong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:21766: de ltar gang nyams pa de skongs na sor chud cing /
NK069(tu)001:21768: de la sogs te mtha' yas mchog /
NK069(tu)001:21769: ces nyams pa skangs ma thag tu sor chud cing rdzogs pa'i yon tan de dag /
NK069(tu)001:21771: de la sogs te yon tan mtha' yas bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i mchog dang ldan no //
NK069(tu)001:21773: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la 'dul bar gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:21774: zhes 'dul ta sems can phyin ci log gi rtog pa 'dul na /
NK069(tu)001:21775: sems can gyi rang bzhin nyid de bzhin gshegs pa las mi zhan pas /
NK069(tu)001:21776: nyid la nyid 'dul bar gyur to zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:21777: rtogs pa dka' bas gsang ba bcud 'dus bas snying
NK069(tu)001:21778: po ma nor bas na de kho na nyid ma
NK069(tu)001:21779: bcos pas na nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:21780: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa gshegs pa der phyin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21781: bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po /
NK069(tu)001:21782: zhes bcu dgu' pa'i rjes de nas /
NK069(tu)001:21783: nyi shu pa'i 'phrin las bston pas so //
NK069(tu)001:21785: zhi bas nyon mongs pa'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:21786: rgyas pas phung po'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:21787: dbang gis lha'i bu'i bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:21788: drag pos 'chi' bdag gi bdud bcom /
NK069(tu)001:21789: de rnams thams cad yang lhun grub tu bcom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21790: lhun gyis grub pa'i dam tshig byin gyis rlob pa
NK069(tu)001:21791: zhes bya ba'i ting nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs
NK069(tu)001:21792: nas / zhes byang chub sems nyid la 'phrin las
NK069(tu)001:21793: rnam pa bzhi rang bzhin gyis lhun gyis grub par
NK069(tu)001:21794: nas / gnas ste / sems dang ba ni zhi ba /
NK069(tu)001:21795: sems dga' ba ni rgyas pa /
NK069(tu)001:21797: sems 'khros pa ni drag po te /
NK069(tu)001:21798: de bas na byang chub sems nyid la 'phrin las rnam pa bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:21799: rang bzhin gyis lhun gyis grub par gnas te /
NK069(tu)001:21800: 'phrin las bzhi'i cho gas bskul bas /
NK069(tu)001:21801: de'i don mngon du snang bar byed pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:21802: byin gyis barloba pa zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:21803: las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub par byin gyis barloba pa las mi 'da' bas na dam tshig /
NK069(tu)001:21805: da bzod de bzhin gshegs pa ting nge 'dzin la 'jug dgos pa ni ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:21806: ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pas las bsgrub na /
NK069(tu)001:21807: ting nge 'dzin la zhugs la sgrubs shig par gdam pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:21808: spyir ngag don du sbyin sreg la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:21809: phyi sku gsum gyi mdzad spyod dang /
NK069(tu)001:21810: nang ting nge 'dzin gyi rtogs tshul dang /
NK069(tu)001:21811: gsang ba rlung gi bde ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:21812: phyi sku gsum gyi mdzad spyod la gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:21815: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi hmo mo /
NK069(tu)001:21816: de la rang bzhin yi hmo ni /
NK069(tu)001:21817: rang rig pa ye shes kyi rgyal po'o //
NK069(tu)001:21818: phyogs bcu ma lus pa thams cad la /
NK069(tu)001:21819: rang rig tu rgyas gtab pas /
NK069(tu)001:21822: rnam shes la dmigs su med de /
NK069(tu)001:21823: rang rig pas ltang na 'joms pas khro bor snang ste /
NK069(tu)001:21824: lus dmyigs myed la mtshan ma'i spros pa med pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21826: chos sku nam mkha' lta bu las /
NK069(tu)001:21827: sku dang ye shes sprin phung lta bu byung nas /
NK069(tu)001:21829: lhag pa'i gzugs rnyan gyi hmo ni dkyil 'khor byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:21830: sbyin sreg byed pa la zer ba yin te cho ga'i gzhung nas ji ltar bshad pa bzhin no //
NK069(tu)001:21831: nang ting nge 'dzin gyi rtogs tshul ni gsum ste /
NK069(tu)001:21832: ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyin sreg dang /
NK069(tu)001:21833: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyin sreg dang /
NK069(tu)001:21834: longs spyod kyi sbyin sreg go //
NK069(tu)001:21835: ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyin sreg la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:21836: rang rig pa'i sbyin sreg dang /
NK069(tu)001:21838: rang rig pa'i sbyin sreg ni /
NK069(tu)001:21839: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:21841: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis bdag myed par rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:21842: phyi nang gi chos thams cad dngos myed du rtogs nas rdzas dang sems kyi bag chags sregs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21845: thugs ka nas ye shes kyi me spros nas /
NK069(tu)001:21846: phyi snod gling bzhi ri rab dang bcas pa thams cad sbyangs /
NK069(tu)001:21847: nang bcud khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad sbyangs /
NK069(tu)001:21849: ngan song gi gnas rnams sbyong /
NK069(tu)001:21850: rang gi sgrib pa dag nas /
NK069(tu)001:21852: lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi sbyin sreg ni /
NK069(tu)001:21853: shes rab kyi spyod yul rdzas su bya /
NK069(tu)001:21854: rang rig stong pa las lhar gyur /
NK069(tu)001:21856: phyi rol yul ni sbyin sreg gi mchod pa'i rdzas su gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21857: longs spyod kyi sbyin sreg ni /
NK069(tu)001:21861: lag pa g.yas g.yon bgang bzar dang bgang blugs /
NK069(tu)001:21862: rgyu dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis rdzogs par dbul lo //
NK069(tu)001:21863: gsang ba rtsa rlung gi bde' ba la gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:21873: mos byang sems kyi bde'i ba drangs nas lus ye shes lha la dbul lo //
NK069(tu)001:21875: khams chags pa la rton pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:21876: yum gyi pad ma thab zhu /
NK069(tu)001:21877: yab kyi rdo rje gzar bu /
NK069(tu)001:21879: khu ba rdzas kyis gnyis pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:21882: rnam shes gsum las byung ba'i gsang ba'i sbyin sreg go //
NK069(tu)001:21883: ched du brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:21884: zhes ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis kyang /
NK069(tu)001:21885: zhi rgyas dbang drag gi las rnam bzhi sgrub par 'dod na /
NK069(tu)001:21886: sangs rgyas kyi bka' dang 'thun par sgrub dgos na /
NK069(tu)001:21887: sangs rgyas kyis 'gro ba'i don ched du /
NK069(tu)001:21888: sbyin sreg gi rim pa 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:21891: ces rgya gar gyi yi ge e ni gru gsum yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:21892: drag po'i thab khung gru gsum du byas la /
NK069(tu)001:21893: dkyil 'khor gyi lha badz+ra he ru ka dang /
NK069(tu)001:21894: sngags mkhan gyi chas gos rnam pa lnga yang kha
NK069(tu)001:21895: dog nag por byas pa ni dkyil 'khor mchog go
NK069(tu)001:21896: // yang na drag po'i dkyil 'khor mchog ni gru gsum mo //
NK069(tu)001:21897: ye shes rngam pa klog gi le'u bcu' lnga pa las /
NK069(tu)001:21898: ya ni zhi ba'i mtshan nyid yin //
NK069(tu)001:21899: ma zhes bya ba rgyas pa ste //
NK069(tu)001:21900: dbang du sdud pa bam du bshad //
NK069(tu)001:21901: e ni drag po'i mtshan nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:21902: 'bar ba'i stum chen rngam pa la //
NK069(tu)001:21903: zhes lha sku ni me dpung 'bar ba'i nang na bzhugs pa /
NK069(tu)001:21907: 'khros pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK069(tu)001:21908: zhes sngags 'khan bdag nyid kyang shin tu 'khros pa'i yid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK069(tu)001:21909: bde bar gshegs pa la mchod /
NK069(tu)001:21911: dgra' bgegs sreg par bya na /
NK069(tu)001:21912: 'og nas bdud rtsi lnga 'am zhes par sbyor /
NK069(tu)001:21913: sangs rgyas bsod nams sku yang 'jig /
NK069(tu)001:21914: ces de ltar byas na sangs rgyas kyi dge ba mang po'i bsod nams las grub pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:21916: de yang rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs las grub pa'i gzugs sku 'jig par nus so //
NK069(tu)001:21917: drag po'i sbyin sreg la ngag don du bcu gcig ste /
NK069(tu)001:21932: yam shing ni rtsa ba la bya /
NK069(tu)001:21933: bur shing ni dug shing ngam tsher ma can no //
NK069(tu)001:21934: lang ki ni rang rdzas dang /
NK069(tu)001:21936: gtor ma ni dug khrag dur sa sol sran can rdo phye la cogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21938: dug tshil khrag sna sran can /
NK069(tu)001:21942: dbung na rdo rje h'u dang bcas pa /
NK069(tu)001:21946: lcags kyu bri kha dog nag por bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:21947: thab ni khro zhal gyi khar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:21949: bud myed nag mo 'khro stum can la bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:21951: thams cad rang bzhin dngos med du 'dzin pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:21952: log rtog la 'khros pa'i sems kyis lha las la bskul lo //
NK069(tu)001:21954: sgral ba'i zhing bcu dgug pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21957: nag so'i shing la zur gsum pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:21959: sbyin pa me lha tri shul 'dzin no //
NK069(tu)001:21960: sreg pa'i lha badz+ra he ru ka'o //
NK069(tu)001:21962: spyid thams cad 'jig pas drag po'i dus so //
NK069(tu)001:21966: bar du lha bsgom zhing sgrub /
NK069(tu)001:21967: tha mar sreg cing las la sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:21969: dbang phyug ma rnams la sbyin par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:21971: zhi rgyas dbang drag bzhi las /
NK069(tu)001:21972: dang po drag po'i sbyin sreg stan pas go log go zhe na dam log ste /
NK069(tu)001:21973: khro bo gdug pa can 'dul ba la shes la de'i phyir snang la drag po'i las smos so //
NK069(tu)001:21974: bdud rtsi lnga 'am zas lnga la //
NK069(tu)001:21987: mtshan ma ming du bcas pa bya //
NK069(tu)001:21988: zhes drag po'i las gang la bya ba'i yul dgra bgegs kyi gzugs byas la /
NK069(tu)001:21990: ming rus dang snying po bris la snying khar bzhug /
NK069(tu)001:21991: gzugs dang byis sa gnyis ltan pas na bcas par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:21992: bkug nas rdo rje phur pas gdab //
NK069(tu)001:21993: ces bdag lta'i thugs nas sprul pa tang nas /
NK069(tu)001:21994: dgra'i rnam par shes pa bkug ste gzugs dang dbyer myed par byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:21995: bdag rdo rje he ru kar bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:21996: drag po'i phur pa yang rdo rje he ru kar bsgom pas gdab bo //
NK069(tu)001:21997: rdul du byas la tshogs la dbul //
NK069(tu)001:21998: zhes de nas ur mo mtshon gyis dum bu brgya stong la sogs par stubs /
NK069(tu)001:21999: rdul du byas na khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshogs
NK069(tu)001:22000: kyi zhal du sbyin sreg bya zhing dbul bar bya'o
NK069(tu)001:22002: dkyil 'khor e yi steng dbyibs gru gsum gyi lha tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du rnal 'byor pa bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:22003: lu gu rgyud du sbrel bstams nas //
NK069(tu)001:22004: rnal 'byor pa pho mo rnams 'dzug mo lu gu rgyud du sbrel nas stams nas /
NK069(tu)001:22005: bcings 'gyur bskyod nas phyogs bcur g.yo' //
NK069(tu)001:22006: yid kyis dgra bgegs bcings par bsams na bcings par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:22007: sred cing skyod par bsams na skyod cing sred par 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:22008: gang srad par bya ba de phyogs bcur g.yo' zhing srad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22009: myos nas gas te tshig par 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:22012: yid tshig par bsams na yad de ltar 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:22013: yang na lus tshig nas thal ba ltar 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:22014: bam gyi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK069(tu)001:22015: ces rgya gar gyi yi ge bam ni zla kham du gnas pas /
NK069(tu)001:22016: thab khung du bzla kham du byas la /
NK069(tu)001:22017: lha yang pad ma he ru ka /
NK069(tu)001:22018: bdag gi chas gos yang dmar por bya /
NK069(tu)001:22019: dbang gi dkyil 'khor ni de ltar byas na mchog yin no //
NK069(tu)001:22020: 'bar ba'i gzi' brjid lhun che ba //
NK069(tu)001:22021: zhes lha 'bar ba'i khro bo'i sku ni /
NK069(tu)001:22023: thams cad dbang du sdud cing zil gyis gnon pa'i gzi' brjid can /
NK069(tu)001:22024: lhun chen po chags pa dang ldan par bdag kyang sgoms la /
NK069(tu)001:22025: chags pa'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK069(tu)001:22026: zhes rnal 'byor pa'i ting nge 'dzin yang /
NK069(tu)001:22027: lha la chags pa'i yid kyis /
NK069(tu)001:22030: dgra' bgegs thams cad dbang du 'dus par bsams la rdzas bsreg go //
NK069(tu)001:22031: rdo rje gsung yang dbang du 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:22033: rdo rje lta bu'i gsung drag stong dbyer myed de yang /
NK069(tu)001:22035: yang na rdo rje'i gsung la mnga' snyoms pa'i pad ma gar dbang yang dbang du 'gyur ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:22036: dbang gi sbyin sreg la ngag don du bcu cig ste /
NK069(tu)001:22053: bud shing ni sdong po la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22054: yam shing ni dmar la dri zhim pa la bya
NK069(tu)001:22055: ling ka ni rang rdzas dang tsha ba gsum la
NK069(tu)001:22057: zangs phye bu ram rag ta ram bu la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22059: skye tshe shang rtse r+ts+wa shing dmar po la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22061: dkyil 'khor zla kham bang rim gsum la /
NK069(tu)001:22063: rim pa la rdo rje pad ma lcags sgrog bya /
NK069(tu)001:22064: thab pad ma 'dab brgyad de la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22066: bud med dmar mo brtson 'grus can la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22068: snang srid thams cad bdag nyid yin pa'i phyir tha mi dad de /
NK069(tu)001:22069: shin du yang de la zhen cing chags par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22071: sems can sngon las kyis chos la mi mos pa /
NK069(tu)001:22072: sangs rgyas la 'dun pa med pa de /
NK069(tu)001:22075: zangs sam shing dmar po la /
NK069(tu)001:22076: rtse mo zla kham par bya /
NK069(tu)001:22078: sbyin pa'i me lha ni dmar por zhags pa thogs pa bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:22079: bsreg pa'i ye shes lha ni /
NK069(tu)001:22080: pad ma he ru ka dmar po bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:22083: dgongs ka dbang gi dus so //
NK069(tu)001:22085: dang po rdzas bsag pa ni byin gyis rlab /
NK069(tu)001:22086: gnyis pa lha bsgom zhing bsgrub /
NK069(tu)001:22087: tha mar las la sbyar zhing smon lam yan chad rdzogs par bya /
NK069(tu)001:22094: lhag ma'i lha gshegs su gsol /
NK069(tu)001:22096: las rjes mi dmyigs par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22097: 'di spyi ya lo de ltar shes par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22098: bdud rtsi lnga 'am zas lnga la //
NK069(tu)001:22099: dri chen la sogs pa bdud rtsi lnga 'am /
NK069(tu)001:22100: yang na d+ha sha la sogs pa rnal 'byor chen po'i zas lnga la /
NK069(tu)001:22101: mtshan ma ming du bcas pa bya //
NK069(tu)001:22102: dgra bo'i mtshan ma bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:22103: gzugs ming rus dang cas pa bya /
NK069(tu)001:22104: rdo rje chags pa'i phur pas gdab //
NK069(tu)001:22105: ces sprul pas gang la bya ba de dbang du byas la gzugs la stim /
NK069(tu)001:22107: bdag pad ma he ru kar bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:22108: phur pa yang pad ma he ru ka chags pa chen por sgoms pas gdab /
NK069(tu)001:22109: chags pa'i tshogs la thim par dbul //
NK069(tu)001:22110: zhes de pho yin na g.yas /
NK069(tu)001:22111: mo yin na g.yon nas phur pas tab pas dbang du 'dus par byas la /
NK069(tu)001:22112: chags pa'i lha tshogs pad ma hi ru ka'i zhal du thim par dbul lo //
NK069(tu)001:22113: bam gyi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK069(tu)001:22114: zhes dkyil 'khor zla kham gyi lha tshogs dang rnal 'byor pa dbyer myed pas /
NK069(tu)001:22115: lu gu rgyud du sbrel nas bsdams //
NK069(tu)001:22116: lag pa srin lag lu gu rgyud du sbrel nas bsdams pas /
NK069(tu)001:22119: phyag na rdo rje yang khugs ste /
NK069(tu)001:22120: rang gi phyi la khyi bzhin du 'breng bar 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:22123: zhes rang ci yong bar 'dod pa /
NK069(tu)001:22129: gang dbang du bya ba de zhugs so //
NK069(tu)001:22130: ma yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK069(tu)001:22131: ces rgya gar gyi yi ge ma ni /
NK069(tu)001:22133: rgyas pa'i thab gru bzhi pa ser por bya /
NK069(tu)001:22134: lha rin chen he ru ka dang rnal 'byor pa'i
NK069(tu)001:22135: chas gos yang ser por bya dgu bzhi ni rgyas
NK069(tu)001:22140: yon tan gyi 'od zer 'du zhing 'phro bas /
NK069(tu)001:22141: gzi' mdangs che bas che ba'i yon tan rgyas par bsams la /
NK069(tu)001:22142: dga' ba'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK069(tu)001:22143: zhes rnal 'byor pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis sems dga' ba'i yid kyis lha la mchod /
NK069(tu)001:22145: rgyas pa'i las su sreg go //
NK069(tu)001:22146: dga' ba'i gad mo dang bcas pas sngags bzlas par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22147: yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK069(tu)001:22148: che ba'i yon tan nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam ste /
NK069(tu)001:22149: bsod nams nam mkha' ltar rgyas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22150: rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg la ngag don bcu cig ste /
NK069(tu)001:22163: me tog sman dang nags tshal yod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22166: bud shing yal ga la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22167: yam shing u du ma b+ha ba 'am 'o ma can gyi shing la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22168: ling ka gang byed kyi rdzas dang /
NK069(tu)001:22176: mar snying dri zhim pa ser po la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22178: dkyil 'khor gru bzhi phyi rim gsum /
NK069(tu)001:22179: dbus rin po che la trom /
NK069(tu)001:22180: rim pa la rdo rje rin chen zhags pa bri /
NK069(tu)001:22181: thab rin chen zur brgyad de dang 'dra bar bya /
NK069(tu)001:22183: bud med ser mo dal zhing blo gros ltan pa la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22185: sems nyid yid bzhin gyi nor bu'i gter dang 'dra ba las /
NK069(tu)001:22186: yon tan thams cad rgyas shing 'phel bar bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:22188: yon tan chung zhing mi 'phel ba de la /
NK069(tu)001:22189: lus ngag yid gsum gyi tshe dang yon tan 'phel ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:22191: gser ram ser po'i shing la rtse mo gru bzhi par bya /
NK069(tu)001:22192: lha ni sbyin pa'i me lha ser po rin chen sgrom bu thogs par bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:22193: sreg pa'i lha rin chen he ru ser por bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:22194: dus ni ston 'bras bu rgyas pa'i dus dang /
NK069(tu)001:22199: tha mar sreg lhag ma ni /
NK069(tu)001:22200: mkha' 'gro ma rnams la dbul lo //
NK069(tu)001:22201: bdud rtsi lnga 'am zas lnga la //
NK069(tu)001:22202: zhes dri chen dri chu mang sa rag ta byang sems lnga 'am /
NK069(tu)001:22203: glang po bya khyi rta ma'i sha lnga 'am /
NK069(tu)001:22204: yon tan yid bzhin gter du rtag /
NK069(tu)001:22205: gang rgyas par bya ba de la /
NK069(tu)001:22206: che ba'i yon tan yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin
NK069(tu)001:22207: po che ltar zad mi shes pa'i gter du rtag
NK069(tu)001:22208: go // nga rgyal dga' 'phro'i phur pas gdab //
NK069(tu)001:22209: ces bdag nga rgyal rin chen he ru ka las /
NK069(tu)001:22210: rgod cing 'od 'phro bas phur pa yang nga rgyal he ru kar sgoms la gdab bo //
NK069(tu)001:22211: de nas dum bur gtubs te /
NK069(tu)001:22213: zhes gang rgyas par bya ba de'i dpal dang /
NK069(tu)001:22215: tshe dang gzi brjid rgyas par bya ba de'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:22216: sku gsung thugs rdo rje ltar 'byor myed pa'i gzi' ba rjid dang ldan pa la /
NK069(tu)001:22217: dpal dang gzi' byin 'phel bar bsams te phul ni /
NK069(tu)001:22218: 'bras bu yang sku gsung rdo rje gzi brjid 'phel zhing rgyas par thob par 'gyur bar yin no //
NK069(tu)001:22220: zhes rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor gru bzhi pa'i nang gi lha tshogs dang bdag dbyer myed pas /
NK069(tu)001:22221: lu gu rgyud du sbrel stams skyod //
NK069(tu)001:22222: ces rnal 'byor pa pho mo rnams lag pa the 'ong lu gu rgyud du stams nas /
NK069(tu)001:22225: dpal dang gzi' brjid 'bar ba'i 'phrul chen po yang spro'o //
NK069(tu)001:22226: de yang 'od gzer ser pos dpal dang gzi' brjid dang /
NK069(tu)001:22228: longs spyod bsam gyi mi khyab pa 'phel lo //
NK069(tu)001:22229: yid bzhin nam mkha' gang bar 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:22230: zhes de ltar mang po spros na /
NK069(tu)001:22231: 'bras bu che ba'i yon tan yid la bsams pa bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:22232: dpal dang gzi' brjid 'byor pa dang longs spyod kyis nam mkha'i khams gang zhing rgyas par gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:22234: ces rgya gar gyi yi ge ya ni dbyibs bzlum po la /
NK069(tu)001:22235: thab khung yang zlum la dkar /
NK069(tu)001:22236: lha yang 'bu ta he ru ka /
NK069(tu)001:22237: rnal 'byor pa'i chas gos yang dkar po'o //
NK069(tu)001:22238: gsal ba'i gzi' brjid mtsher ba la //
NK069(tu)001:22239: lha'i sku mdog yang dkar la gsal ba'i gzi' byin 'tsher bar bsgoms la /
NK069(tu)001:22240: dang ba'i yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK069(tu)001:22241: las kyi ting nge yang sems zhi zhing dang ba'i yid kyis /
NK069(tu)001:22245: bstum chen rngam pa 'ang lhan ner 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:22247: khro bo bstum chen ngang rngam pa de la dmyigs na yang /
NK069(tu)001:22248: lus ngag yid zhi nas dul bar 'gyur ro //
NK069(tu)001:22249: zhi ba'i spyin sreg la ngag don du bcu gcig ste /
NK069(tu)001:22266: bud shing ni rtse mo la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22267: yam shing ni tsan dan dkar po la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22268: gtor ma 'o ma 'bras chen rdul phye me tog dkar po la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22269: mchod rdzas mngar gsum mar til nas /
NK069(tu)001:22270: dkar gsum tsan dan dkar po la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22271: ling ka rang rdzas dang dam rdzas la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22273: dkyil 'khor zlum po rim pa gsum pa /
NK069(tu)001:22275: rim pa gsum la rdo rje 'khor lo me ri bya /
NK069(tu)001:22277: zlum po brtsibs bzhi'i rigs kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK069(tu)001:22278: seng ge'i mgos mu khyud la rgyan par bya /
NK069(tu)001:22280: bud med 'khro sems myed pa'i bong chung ba'i sha rtsa dkar ba la bya /
NK069(tu)001:22282: sems can thams cad kyi sems mtha' bral rnam dag tu bsam /
NK069(tu)001:22284: bdag gzhan la gnod sems dang sbyor ba ngan pa byed pa de'i sems zhi bar bya /
NK069(tu)001:22286: rdul lam dkar po'i shing la /
NK069(tu)001:22288: phur pa gzhan dang de myin rnams mthun /
NK069(tu)001:22290: sbyin pa'i lha mo lha dkar po 'gyu ste thogs pa sgom /
NK069(tu)001:22291: sreg pa'i lha 'bu ta he ru kar bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:22292: sbyin sreg byed pa'i dus ni /
NK069(tu)001:22293: dbyar zhi ba'i dus su bya /
NK069(tu)001:22294: zhag ni snga dro zhi ba'i dus su bya /
NK069(tu)001:22300: dbang mo la dbul bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22301: bdud rtsi lnga 'am zas lnga la //
NK069(tu)001:22302: zhes dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga 'am /
NK069(tu)001:22303: rnal 'byor chen po'i zas sha la ling ka bya /
NK069(tu)001:22304: bstum rngam 'khrug pa'i ngo bor brtag /
NK069(tu)001:22305: ling ka de sgrub pa stum rngam 'khrug pa gang yin pa de'i ngo bor bsams shing brtags /
NK069(tu)001:22306: lha ni gsal ba'i phur pas gdab //
NK069(tu)001:22307: ces lha ne ni zhi ba /
NK069(tu)001:22308: gsal ba ni sku mdog dkar po /
NK069(tu)001:22309: bdag kyang 'bu ta he ru ka der sgom /
NK069(tu)001:22310: phur ba yang der byin gyis brlab bo //
NK069(tu)001:22311: 'bar ba lha ne'i tshogs la dbul //
NK069(tu)001:22312: zhes 'bu ta he ru ka 'od dkar po 'bar ba /
NK069(tu)001:22313: sku zhi ba lha ne'i sgoms pa'i tshogs la /
NK069(tu)001:22314: bdud rtsi lnga 'am zas lnga'i ling ka de dbul lo //
NK069(tu)001:22316: zhes ya zlum po'i zhi ba'i lha tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor dang bdag dbyer med du sgoms /
NK069(tu)001:22317: lu gu rgyud du sbrel nas bstams //
NK069(tu)001:22318: gung mo lu gu rgyud du sbrel stams nas /
NK069(tu)001:22319: 'bar bar ni khro bo la 'od dkar po 'bar /
NK069(tu)001:22321: 'bar ba lha ni 'i byin gyis khyab //
NK069(tu)001:22322: ces 'od dkar po 'bar ba'i sku zhi bar sgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis khyab nas /
NK069(tu)001:22323: thams cad g.yo' ba med par byed //
NK069(tu)001:22324: ces bdag gi dmyigs par bya ba'i yul gang yin pa de thams cad kyang /
NK069(tu)001:22325: lus ngag yid gsum zhi zhing dul bas g.yo' ba
NK069(tu)001:22326: med par lhan gyis 'gyur ba de kho na la
NK069(tu)001:22328: sgrub bya gang yin pa de'i lus ngag yid kyi rgyud zhi bar bya ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:22329: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK069(tu)001:22330: zhes slas ni zhun mar byas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22331: byi mo ni dregs pas ma tshor bar spyad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22332: bran mo ni las mkhan no //
NK069(tu)001:22333: tshogs ni nyi shu rtsa brgyad do //
NK069(tu)001:22334: lha ma'i mchod sbyin 'dod pa sbyin //
NK069(tu)001:22335: zhes mchod pa'i zhal zas thams cad lha'i zhal zas bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK069(tu)001:22336: phud he ru ka yab yum bcu dang /
NK069(tu)001:22337: 'phra myen ma nyi shu la mchod /
NK069(tu)001:22338: de'i 'go ma rnal 'byor pa longs spyad /
NK069(tu)001:22339: de'i 'go ma rang gi lhag ma la /
NK069(tu)001:22340: dbang mo la mchod sbyin byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22341: rang gi dam tshig rab sgrags nas //
NK069(tu)001:22342: zhes thod pa'i phyag rgya ni /
NK069(tu)001:22343: so so'i snying po sngon khas blangs pa'i dam tshig rnams sgrags so //
NK069(tu)001:22344: gang 'dod las de byed par bsgo' //
NK069(tu)001:22345: zhes shar gyi las su zhi bar 'dod dam /
NK069(tu)001:22346: lho'i las su rgyas par 'dod dam /
NK069(tu)001:22347: nub kyi las su dbang du 'dod dam /
NK069(tu)001:22348: dbyang gi las su drag par 'dod pa de dag phyed rigs kyis 'go' drang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:22352: kha chus gdab cing mchod pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:22355: zil gyis mnan cing las bcol ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:22357: lha ga ma sdu ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:22360: de nas phyag tshang ba rol /
NK069(tu)001:22361: de nas lhag ma sdus la las mkhan la dbul lo //
NK069(tu)001:22363: bdag ting nge 'dzin gyis lhar bsgom /
NK069(tu)001:22364: thugs ka nas ram yang khang gsum las sregs sbyangs byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:22365: snod nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor steng du /
NK069(tu)001:22366: lhag ma yi ge hri dmar po las /
NK069(tu)001:22368: lhag ma srin thob sbyar ba'i bar du hri gzung la gtor ma la phyag rgya gtad la /
NK069(tu)001:22369: a h+aum u tsi sh+ta badz+ra a ti ti sh+ta swa mam h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:22370: brgya rtsa brgyad kyis gtor ma la rta 'grin yab
NK069(tu)001:22371: yum gyi byang chub sems su dkar mer gyis bsam
NK069(tu)001:22372: mo // kha chus gdab pa ni gdab yi dam gyi lha'i lce'i stengs su hri dkar po las /
NK069(tu)001:22373: rta 'grin yab yum gyi byang chub sems su bsam pa la /
NK069(tu)001:22374: 'dus ma byas mkha' dbyings kyi phyag rgya'i nang na mar la gdab bo //
NK069(tu)001:22375: badz+ra a smri ta a ti ti sh+ta swa mam h+aum hri tha zhes pas gdab bo //
NK069(tu)001:22377: khro bo rta ki ra tsa sngon po lcags kyu
NK069(tu)001:22378: thogs pa spros la ta ki ni a gad dza
NK069(tu)001:22387: badz+ra ta ki ni h+aum dza dza /
NK069(tu)001:22389: ma mo rnams grub pa'i gnas dang /
NK069(tu)001:22390: so so'i pho brang nas spyan drangs te /
NK069(tu)001:22391: bsgrub pa po'i gnas su bya nag thang la babs pa ltar 'dus pa ra bsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:22393: bdag rta 'grin gyi ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK069(tu)001:22394: rta gdong zhal gyi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK069(tu)001:22395: hri pad ma ba mu ka /
NK069(tu)001:22396: a kar sha ya a kar sha ya /
NK069(tu)001:22397: pra be sha ya pra be sha ya /
NK069(tu)001:22398: ban d+ha ya ban d+ha ya /
NK069(tu)001:22399: to sha ya to sha ya /
NK069(tu)001:22400: mo ha ya mo ha ya /
NK069(tu)001:22401: ha ya gri ba he he hring hring /
NK069(tu)001:22403: ma mo rnams 'dar 'phril gyis dbang du sdu'o //
NK069(tu)001:22404: de nas zil gyis mnan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:22406: thod rlon gyi phyag rgya smin 'tshams su gtad la /
NK069(tu)001:22407: dza h+aum bam ho sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dus stan /
NK069(tu)001:22409: pra ban tsag tra h+aum phata /
NK069(tu)001:22410: ci sgo ba thams cad nyan par bsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:22412: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru ka'i ces pa la sogs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22413: de nas gshegs su gsol ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:22414: ya ya hi 'ag+ha tsa zhes brjod nas /
NK069(tu)001:22415: rang gi gnas gang yin pa rnams dgyes nas gshegs par bsam mo //
NK069(tu)001:22417: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru ka /
NK069(tu)001:22418: zhes sngon gyi dus kyi tshe na /
NK069(tu)001:22419: bdag gzhan gyi dpal du gyur pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:22420: he ru ka sku gsum gyi bdag nyid can de /
NK069(tu)001:22424: pad ma b+hir ba'i sgra las drangs na rtogs pa bdag gi dpal /
NK069(tu)001:22425: pa ra ma tri'i sgra las drangs na thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal /
NK069(tu)001:22426: he he ka na dgyes pa ste chos sku /
NK069(tu)001:22427: he he du rgyu ste snying rje /
NK069(tu)001:22428: ru ra ga na thugs rje /
NK069(tu)001:22429: ru rag ta na khrag ka ka ru na thugs rje /
NK069(tu)001:22430: ka kar ma na 'phrin las so //
NK069(tu)001:22431: de ltar sgra brgyad dang lhag pa'i he ru ka'o //
NK069(tu)001:22432: shin tu gdug cing bstum bag can //
NK069(tu)001:22433: zhes sku shin tu stum pa khro ba stum can du bzhugs pas /
NK069(tu)001:22435: mdzad pa'i mthu' stobs gdug pa /
NK069(tu)001:22437: drag shul gyi ngang stum bag dang bcas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:22438: gdug cing stum pa dang bcas pa de gdul bya
NK069(tu)001:22439: la stan pas na can zhes bya' ldan tshig go
NK069(tu)001:22440: // thams cad ma lus 'dul mdzad pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:22441: zhes gdug pa can thams cad ma lus par 'dul bar mdzad pa'i dbang dang /
NK069(tu)001:22442: yang na shin tu gdug cing stum bag can de gang la dgongs zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:22443: ru tra sogs pa'i gdug pa can /
NK069(tu)001:22446: thugs stum bag can du stan pas 'dul bar mdzad pa la dgongs so //
NK069(tu)001:22447: dbang dang byin brlabs smad po che //
NK069(tu)001:22448: zhes sku gsung thugs kyi byin brlabs smad du byung ba dang stan pas /
NK069(tu)001:22452: mthu' rtsal smad du byung ba de /
NK069(tu)001:22453: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i dbang rang la rdzogs pas dbang che /
NK069(tu)001:22454: sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin du ye nas gnas pas byin brlabs che /
NK069(tu)001:22455: des mthu' rtsal smad du 'byung bas che ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:22456: 'dir gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:22457: le'u 'di kun tu bzang pos gsungs par 'dra ba la /
NK069(tu)001:22458: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru ka'i /
NK069(tu)001:22459: zhes pa la sogs pa ltar na /
NK069(tu)001:22460: kun tu bzang pos ma gsungs par mngon no zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:22462: kun tu bzang pos gsungs kyang /
NK069(tu)001:22463: phyi rabs kyi rnal 'byor pa dbang phyug ma la
NK069(tu)001:22464: las bcol ba'i tshig lung du stan par gsungs pa
NK069(tu)001:22465: ste / rgyud 'di nyid kyang phyi rabs la dgongs nas gsungs pa'i nad kas 'gal ba myed do //
NK069(tu)001:22466: lha chen la sogs dbang bsdus nas //
NK069(tu)001:22467: zhes lha chen ma h+aa de ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:22476: dpal chen pos lus ngag yid gsum gyi mthu' 'phrogs
NK069(tu)001:22477: nas dbang du bsdus pas na dbang du bsdus zhes
NK069(tu)001:22478: bya'o // 'khor rnams dbang phyug slas su byas //
NK069(tu)001:22479: zhes de dag gi 'khor chung ma thams cad la mnga' snyems pa'i dbang phyug ma rnams /
NK069(tu)001:22480: dbang phyug dpal chen po'i slas su byas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:22482: so so'i las rnams bskos pa de //
NK069(tu)001:22483: zhes shar gyi rgyal mo bdun gyis zhi ba'i las grub /
NK069(tu)001:22484: lho'i blon mo bdun gyis rgyas pa'i las grub /
NK069(tu)001:22485: nub kyi dbang mo bdun gyis dbang gi las grub /
NK069(tu)001:22486: byang gi bran mo bdun gyis drag po'i las grub bo //
NK069(tu)001:22487: ji ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:22488: zhes le'u bac+wo lnga pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:22490: ming tsam 'dzin par byed pa yang /
NK069(tu)001:22491: tsug gi nor bu 'bar ba ltar /
NK069(tu)001:22492: g.yo' rgyu med cing gus ltan pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:22493: tsug tu bzhag ste bskur bar bgyi' /
NK069(tu)001:22494: zhes pa la sogs pas gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:22495: ma thogs myur du mngon par phyung //
NK069(tu)001:22496: zhes dus ring por ma thogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:22498: stags mngon gsum phyung zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:22499: dam bcas bzhin du ma byas na //
NK069(tu)001:22500: zhes le'u bco' lnga pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:22501: de'i dgos pa ci yang rung //
NK069(tu)001:22502: ma lus rdzogs par bdag cag sgrub //
NK069(tu)001:22504: ji ltar rang gi mna' bor ba'i //
NK069(tu)001:22505: zhes le'u bco lnga pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:22507: 'bangs su nan tan ma bgyis na /
NK069(tu)001:22508: mgo' dang lus ni rgyar gshegs shing /
NK069(tu)001:22510: rul myags tshig nas rlab pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:22511: dmyal bar lhung nas 'bod par shog /
NK069(tu)001:22513: sdom bcas de las 'das ma byed //
NK069(tu)001:22514: ces rang gi khas blangs ni /
NK069(tu)001:22515: rang dam rang gis bcas pa'i sdom pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22516: de las 'das shing 'gal bar ma byed cig /
NK069(tu)001:22519: zhes khas blangs nas rang dam rang gis bcas pa'i dam tshig de las 'das shing /
NK069(tu)001:22521: spyir las dge sdig gi 'bras bu rgyu'i rjes su 'brang ba yin la /
NK069(tu)001:22522: khyad par du rang gi smon lam gtab pa de smin pa yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:22523: mgo' lus snying yang tshal pa bdun //
NK069(tu)001:22524: zhes spyir mgo' dang lus tshal pa bdun du 'gas so //
NK069(tu)001:22527: gal te dpa' bo'i spyan mnga' 'dir //
NK069(tu)001:22528: smras pa bzhin nu ma sgrubs na //
NK069(tu)001:22529: bdag cag rnams kyi mgo' lus snying //
NK069(tu)001:22530: bkas stubs dum bur rul bar 'chi' //
NK069(tu)001:22532: rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu mi blu bar yong bas so //
NK069(tu)001:22533: yag sha khro bos stub par 'gyur //
NK069(tu)001:22534: zhes khyad par du dam tshig nyams pa rnams la /
NK069(tu)001:22535: chad pas gcod pa'i lha ni /
NK069(tu)001:22536: khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin zhes bya ba /
NK069(tu)001:22537: rang gi dbang skur ba'i dus kyi ye shes dpa' nyid rdo rje gnod sbyin du gnas 'gyur bas /
NK069(tu)001:22538: rang gshed rang la phab nas 'go lus stub bo //
NK069(tu)001:22540: zhes dam tshig nyams pa las kyi sgru mthun ngan pa myi slu bar yong ba de bas /
NK069(tu)001:22541: rnal 'byor ni blo rnal ma ma bcos pa de la /
NK069(tu)001:22544: gsang basngagasa gsang ba'i don du byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22545: de yis bcol ba thams cad ma lus par bya dgos ste /
NK069(tu)001:22546: ji ltar bcos ba bzhin du byos //
NK069(tu)001:22547: zhes zhi rgyas dbang drag gi las bzhi bcol /
NK069(tu)001:22548: gdon pho mo klu dang gsum 'dul bar bcol lam /
NK069(tu)001:22549: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub bskul bar col ba gang yin pa de'o //
NK069(tu)001:22550: las de mngon du ma byas na //
NK069(tu)001:22551: zhes bcol ba'i las de la /
NK069(tu)001:22552: rtags dang mtshan ma mngon sum du /
NK069(tu)001:22553: thog par ma byas na zhe'o //
NK069(tu)001:22554: rang gis mna' bor khas blangs bzhin //
NK069(tu)001:22555: zhes dbang phyug ma rang gis mna' bor ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:22556: gal te dpa' bo'i spyan mnga' 'dir //
NK069(tu)001:22557: smras pa bzhin du ma sgrubs na //
NK069(tu)001:22558: bdag cag rnams kyi mgo' lus snying //
NK069(tu)001:22559: bkas stubs dum bur rul bar mchi' //
NK069(tu)001:22562: de'i dgos pa ci yang rung //
NK069(tu)001:22563: ma lus rdzogs par bdag cag sgrub //
NK069(tu)001:22564: rul myags tshig nas dmyal bar 'gro //
NK069(tu)001:22565: zhes dam tshig gi rnam smin gyis lus rul myags su 'gro /
NK069(tu)001:22566: byang chub kyi rgyun tshig nas /
NK069(tu)001:22568: rdo rje dmyal ba'i tshe tshad ni /
NK069(tu)001:22570: skra nyag mas gtor na chu zad nus la /
NK069(tu)001:22571: rdo rje dmyal ba'i tshad de bas kyang yun ring ngo //
NK069(tu)001:22572: lcags kyi ri rab thor 'bum la /
NK069(tu)001:22573: bya'i gshogs pas byabs na zad nus la /
NK069(tu)001:22574: rdo rje dmyal ba'i tshad de bas yun ring ngo //
NK069(tu)001:22576: zhes las bya ba yang phal gyis ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:22577: rnal 'byor pa bka' bzhin dam tshig la gnas pa'i las ci bcol ba bya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:22578: 'khor rnams bu gcig bzhin du skyongs //
NK069(tu)001:22579: zhes rnal 'byor pa de'i 'khor ram bcom ldan 'das
NK069(tu)001:22580: kyi rjes su 'brang ba'i 'khor rnam bzhi yang bu
NK069(tu)001:22581: gcig po la ma byams pa bzhin du skyongs gcig
NK069(tu)001:22582: / 'phra myen ma yang dngos grub thob //
NK069(tu)001:22585: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub 'thob pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22586: bcol ba'i las rnams mngon du byos //
NK069(tu)001:22587: de bas na ji ltar bcol ba'i las rnam bzhi la sogs pa mngon gsum du byos shig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22588: 'dir gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:22591: rnal 'byor pas dgra' gsod par bskul na las byed dam mi byed /
NK069(tu)001:22592: byed na dngos grub thob na /
NK069(tu)001:22593: mi gsod ldan pas kyang sngags kyi dngos grub 'thob par thal /
NK069(tu)001:22595: gsad pa 'phrin las bzhi las drag po myin par 'gro /
NK069(tu)001:22597: rnal 'byor pas gsod par bskul ba de yang /
NK069(tu)001:22599: bka' bzhin du sgrub pas skul ba de ni /
NK069(tu)001:22600: zhing bcu sgrol ba yin la /
NK069(tu)001:22601: zhing bcu sgral bas dngos grub thob par rgyud las gsungs /
NK069(tu)001:22602: de ma yin par rang dgar gsar par ma gsungs pas /
NK069(tu)001:22603: 'gal ba gang yang yod par ma mthong ngo //
NK069(tu)001:22604: 'phra myen ma yang dngos grub 'thob zhes pas gnyis te /
NK069(tu)001:22605: ko'u ri la sogs pa khro mo nyi shu la 'phra myen du bzhag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:22606: dbang phyug ma la 'phra myen du gzhag pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22607: ko'u ri la sogs khro mo nyi shu la 'phra myen du bzhag pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:22608: dper na dngul la gser chus byugs pa la 'phra myen zor ba dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:22609: 'og nas khro mo 'di rnams kyang pha ni 'jig
NK069(tu)001:22610: rten las 'das pa'i ye shes kyi lha dpal chen
NK069(tu)001:22611: po yin / ma ni 'jig rten pa'i srin mo yin te /
NK069(tu)001:22612: de gnyis las skyid pa'i sku yin pas 'phra myen /
NK069(tu)001:22613: yang na 'phra myen ma 'di dag dpal chen po'i
NK069(tu)001:22614: thugs ye shes kyi khyad par las sprul ba yin
NK069(tu)001:22615: kyang / sku 'jig rten pa'i srin mo'i cha lugs 'dzin pa'i kyang 'phra myen /
NK069(tu)001:22616: de ltar sku 'jig rten pa'i srin mo'i cha lug sa 'dzin yang /
NK069(tu)001:22617: rang bzhin thugs ye shes las sprul pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:22618: ke'u ri la sogs pa brgyad /
NK069(tu)001:22619: seng ha la sogs pa brgyad /
NK069(tu)001:22620: sgo ma bzhi dang nyi shu la ni /
NK069(tu)001:22621: nang gi 'phra myen ma zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:22622: nang gi rnal 'byor ma zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22623: dbang phyug ma zhes bya ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:22624: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni /
NK069(tu)001:22625: dper na dam tshig can la sngags 'chang zer bar dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:22626: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad po 'di dag kyang /
NK069(tu)001:22627: dpa' chen po'i bka' dam tshig la gnas pa yin pas 'phra myen ces bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22628: yang na dbang phyug ma 'di dag kyang /
NK069(tu)001:22629: lus 'jig rten pa'i srin mo'i cha lugs 'dzin kyang /
NK069(tu)001:22630: sems mya ngan las 'das pa yin pas kyang 'phra myen no //
NK069(tu)001:22631: yang na khro mo nyi shu skyed pa'i mar gyur pas kyang ma mo zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22632: 'di rnams ni phyi'i 'phra myen ma zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:22634: 'dir ni dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad yin par ngos bzung bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22636: zhes ston pas gsungs pa de /
NK069(tu)001:22638: dbang phyug ma la bka' de skad du bgo' bar bya ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:22639: khro bo sgrub pa'i las kyi gtso' bo ni 'di yin no //
NK069(tu)001:22640: zhes khro bo'i dngos grub bsgrub pa la /
NK069(tu)001:22641: las kyi gtso' bo ni bro gar 'di yin zhe 'am /
NK069(tu)001:22642: yang na he ru ka yab yum bcu dang /
NK069(tu)001:22644: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad du bsgoms nas /
NK069(tu)001:22645: drag po'i las sgrub pa'i gtso' bo ni /
NK069(tu)001:22647: khrag 'thung chen po la sogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:22648: zhes nyon mongs pa khrag zhag dang 'dra ba 'thung bas khrag 'thung /
NK069(tu)001:22649: chen po ni badz+ra he ru ka la sogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:22651: bro gar klu tshig chen pos ni //
NK069(tu)001:22652: zhes bdag khro bo'i skur bsgoms nas rkang pas bro brdung /
NK069(tu)001:22655: chen po ni theg pa 'og ma ba las khyad par du gyur pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22656: bro gar ni sgyu 'phrul rgya bcu pa'i le'u lnga bcu bdun pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:22657: h'u zhe rdo rje 'khor bcas pas /
NK069(tu)001:22659: skad cig yud la klag mdzad de //
NK069(tu)001:22660: brlag par ma gyur gang yang myed //
NK069(tu)001:22662: bro ni drag po'i dbyibs gru gsum du brdung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:22663: hri 'dod chags rdo rje 'khor bcas pas //
NK069(tu)001:22665: skad cig yud la dbang du bsdus //
NK069(tu)001:22666: dbang du ma gyur gang yang med //
NK069(tu)001:22668: bro ni dbang dbyibs zla kham mo //
NK069(tu)001:22669: tram nga rgyal rdo rje 'khor bcas pas /
NK069(tu)001:22671: skad cig yud la rgyas mdzad de //
NK069(tu)001:22672: rgyas par ma gyur gang yang med //
NK069(tu)001:22674: bro ni rgyas pa'i dbyibs gru bzhir gdung bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22675: gti mug rdo rje 'khor bcas pas /
NK069(tu)001:22677: skad cig yud la zhi mdzad de //
NK069(tu)001:22678: zhi bar ma gyur gang yang med //
NK069(tu)001:22680: bro ni zhi ba'i dbyibs zlum por gdung bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22681: ye shes rngam pa glog gi 'khor lo'i le'u bco lnga pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:22686: khrag 'thung chen pos thim par byed //
NK069(tu)001:22688: rad na kro tis sbyor bar byed //
NK069(tu)001:22689: pad ma kro tis sbyor bar byed //
NK069(tu)001:22690: kar ma kro tis 'bebs par byed //
NK069(tu)001:22692: thams cad thams cad ci 'dod par //
NK069(tu)001:22693: rnal 'byor pa 'khor bcas thams cad kyis las zhi rgyas dbang drag thams cad ci 'dod pa de /
NK069(tu)001:22694: thams cad thams cad byed pa yin //
NK069(tu)001:22695: zhi rgyas dbang drag gi las thams cad dang mchog
NK069(tu)001:22696: thun mong gi las thams cad byed pa yin no
NK069(tu)001:22697: // mdzod ldan chen mo la sogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:22698: zhes ko'u ri ma ni kun gzhi' las gnas 'gyur ba na /
NK069(tu)001:22699: kun gzhi' la las dkar nag sog pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:22703: rnal 'byor sngo nag ko'u ri ma zhes so //
NK069(tu)001:22704: yid kyi rnam shes tso'u ri /
NK069(tu)001:22705: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid spra mo ha /
NK069(tu)001:22706: lus kyi rnam shes rig bya las pe ta li yin pas na la sogs so //
NK069(tu)001:22707: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni //
NK069(tu)001:22708: zhes rnal 'byor pa rnams mkha' 'gro ma de bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin du zhugs la /
NK069(tu)001:22710: lag pas phyag rgya'i gar bya /
NK069(tu)001:22711: ngag tu bstod pa'i glu blang /
NK069(tu)001:22714: ces dbang du sdud par 'dod na /
NK069(tu)001:22716: pra ma hos gang dbang du 'du bar 'dod pa de /
NK069(tu)001:22717: dbang du bsdud par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:22718: de yang yul khams dbang du bya ba /
NK069(tu)001:22722: gatso'u ri dang dpe ta lis tshe dang dbang thang
NK069(tu)001:22723: dang 'byor pa dang longs spyod 'phel bar 'dod na
NK069(tu)001:22724: gang yin pa ni 'phel bar byed do //
NK069(tu)001:22725: bro gar ni ye shes rngam pa klog gi le'u nyi shu pa nas /
NK069(tu)001:22726: g.yas pa khu tshur bcangs nas sgreng /
NK069(tu)001:22727: g.yon pa 'dzin ltar byas pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:22728: g.yas dang g.yon du lta zhing sgyur /
NK069(tu)001:22729: ko'u ri'u tshogs kyi phyag rgya yin /
NK069(tu)001:22731: mda' gzhu' 'gengs pa'i tshul du ni //
NK069(tu)001:22733: g.yas kyi gu mo'i rtse mo sgreng //
NK069(tu)001:22734: kun mo tshogs kyi phyag rgyar bshad //
NK069(tu)001:22735: g.yas pa'i khu tshur phyar nas ni //
NK069(tu)001:22736: the 'ong the'u chung rkyang par bya //
NK069(tu)001:22737: g.yon pas 'dzin pa khro tshul lta //
NK069(tu)001:22738: pra mo'i phyag rgyar dpa' bos bshad //
NK069(tu)001:22739: g.yas kyi gung mo'i rtse mo sgreng //
NK069(tu)001:22740: sor bzhi'i rtse'u bsdus rdo rje phyar //
NK069(tu)001:22741: g.yas pa kun tu rten pa ni //
NK069(tu)001:22742: 'bri tshugs lta ba se ta'i rgya //
NK069(tu)001:22745: lta tshul gyi stangs thabs kyis bro rdung zhing ngag du yang glu de skad du blang par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22746: spos mo chen mo la sogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:22749: che ba'i yon tan gyis spos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22750: myig ni rnam shes las gnas 'gyur ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:22752: rnam shes las gnas las gnas 'gyur ba rnam shes ni dang /
NK069(tu)001:22753: sna'i rnam shes las gnas 'gyur ba tsan d+ha li dang /
NK069(tu)001:22754: lce'i rnam shes las gnas 'gyur ba karma ri'o //
NK069(tu)001:22755: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni //
NK069(tu)001:22759: chen mo ni mkha' 'gro ma'i dar rgyal du zhugs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22760: lhan ner 'dod na lha nor byed //
NK069(tu)001:22764: gnyis kyis zhi bar byed de /
NK069(tu)001:22768: mugs par 'dod na mugs par byed //
NK069(tu)001:22770: lus sems dran pa myed par byed na /
NK069(tu)001:22771: gang yin pa'i lus ngag yid gsum mugs par byed de /
NK069(tu)001:22772: gti' mug gi yon tan cher 'phel bas mugs par byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22774: g.yon pas nyon mongs mnan tshul la //
NK069(tu)001:22775: g.yas pa rgyu 'dren za ba'i tshul //
NK069(tu)001:22776: pu ka si'i phyag rgyar bshad //
NK069(tu)001:22777: g.yon pas dung khrag 'dzin pa la //
NK069(tu)001:22778: g.yas pas krug cing rngam tshul ston //
NK069(tu)001:22779: kas ma'i phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK069(tu)001:22780: g.yas pas snying 'dren za tshul du //
NK069(tu)001:22781: sgrol tshul lta bas sman sha'i rgya //
NK069(tu)001:22782: g.yas pas mgo' can phyar nas kyang //
NK069(tu)001:22783: g.yon pas lus 'dzin stobs par lta //
NK069(tu)001:22784: tsan d+ha'i phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK069(tu)001:22786: lag pas phyag rgya'i gar bya /
NK069(tu)001:22787: lus lta tshul gyis stabs bya /
NK069(tu)001:22788: de nas yang srin lag lu gu rgyud du sgrel ba las /
NK069(tu)001:22789: las rnam bzhi'i bro brdung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:22791: 'phrin las rnam bzhi spel bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22792: ser gdong chen mo la sogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:22793: zhes kun gzhi'i yul kun tog las gnas 'gyur ba seng gdong ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:22794: yid kyi rnam shes kyi yul chos las gnas 'gyur ba rtag gdong ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:22795: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid kyi yul 'dzin pa las gnas 'gyur ba wa gdong ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:22796: reg bya las gnas 'gyur ba 'jam tsub las bya gdong ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:22797: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni //
NK069(tu)001:22802: sogs pa ni ting nge 'dzin dang sngags so //
NK069(tu)001:22803: thams cad kun la za bar byed //
NK069(tu)001:22804: ces 'di ni 'phra myen ma spyan zan gyi mgo' can no //
NK069(tu)001:22805: seng stag wa spyang bzhi dang chos 'thun te /
NK069(tu)001:22806: srid pa gsum la dbang byed pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:22807: srid gsum rlag par byed pas na za ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:22809: rdul cha tsam yang med par byed //
NK069(tu)001:22810: ces dgra bgegs kun rlag par byas nas /
NK069(tu)001:22811: rul phra rab kyi cha tsam yang med par byed de /
NK069(tu)001:22813: dug gsum du zos nas myed par byas pa kho na'o //
NK069(tu)001:22815: lag gnyis dral la snol nas ni //
NK069(tu)001:22816: kha na ro thogs ral sig pa //
NK069(tu)001:22817: seng gdong tshogs kyi phyag rgya yin //
NK069(tu)001:22818: lag gnyis thur du snol nas ni //
NK069(tu)001:22819: zhing la 'bri tshugs mche gnyer ba //
NK069(tu)001:22820: stag gdong tshogs kyi phyag rgya yin //
NK069(tu)001:22821: lag gnyis kha 'gram g.yas g.yon du //
NK069(tu)001:22822: za ba'i tshul du ston pa ni //
NK069(tu)001:22823: 'di ni wa gdong tshogs kyi rgya //
NK069(tu)001:22824: lag gnyis khog pa kha phye nas //
NK069(tu)001:22825: sha dri tshugs lta ba sho ni'i rgya //
NK069(tu)001:22829: lag pa lu gu rgyud du sgrel la /
NK069(tu)001:22830: las 'phrin las rnam bzhi'i bro re gdung bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22831: gzhan gdong chen mo la sogs pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:22832: zhes dmyig gi yul gzugs las gnas 'gyur ba ni bya rgod kyi mgo' ni gzhad gdang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:22833: rna ba'i yul sgra las gnas 'gyur ba ni dur bya'i rkang ka'i mgo' can no //
NK069(tu)001:22834: sna'i yul dri las gnas 'gyur ba kha kha ma bya rog gi mgo' dang /
NK069(tu)001:22835: lca'i yul ro las gnas 'gyur ba hu lu mu ka 'ug pa'i mgo' can no //
NK069(tu)001:22836: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni //
NK069(tu)001:22837: zhes stangs stabs kyi bro dang /
NK069(tu)001:22838: lag pa'i phyag rgya'i gar dang /
NK069(tu)001:22839: ting nge 'dzin gyis 'phra myen mar bsgoms pa yis ni /
NK069(tu)001:22840: thams cad kun la 'byin par byed //
NK069(tu)001:22841: ces 'di bzhi 'dab chags kyi 'go can de /
NK069(tu)001:22842: bya rgod kyis gang na yod tshol zhing 'byin /
NK069(tu)001:22843: rkang kas dong nas 'byin pa ltar gnas 'byin /
NK069(tu)001:22844: kha khas dbang po 'byin cing za /
NK069(tu)001:22846: dmyig sgyu ma 'byin cing za ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:22847: dngos su na drag po'i las byed pa nyi tshe'o //
NK069(tu)001:22848: kun la rab tu nyams par byed //
NK069(tu)001:22849: ces dbang po sgo lnga'i nus pa nyams par byed /
NK069(tu)001:22850: de kho na la 'byin pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22852: lag na spu gri thogs nas su //
NK069(tu)001:22853: g.yon gyis rgyu ma 'dren cing za //
NK069(tu)001:22854: 'di ni gzhan gdong tshogs kyi rgya //
NK069(tu)001:22855: zhing chen 'phrag pa la skal nas ni //
NK069(tu)001:22856: keng ru thogs la ltar byed pa //
NK069(tu)001:22857: dur bya'i gdong gi phyag rgya yin //
NK069(tu)001:22858: g.yon pas ban d+ha g.yas pas gri //
NK069(tu)001:22859: glo snying 'dren pa ltar byed pa //
NK069(tu)001:22860: kha kha'i phyag rgya yin par bshad //
NK069(tu)001:22861: g.yas pa rdo rje 'dzin tshul du //
NK069(tu)001:22862: g.yon pas 'dzin pa hu lu'i rgya //
NK069(tu)001:22864: yid kyis ting nge 'dzin gsal ba /
NK069(tu)001:22865: rkang pas bro stabs ma nor ba /
NK069(tu)001:22866: lag pas phyag rgya rgyur ba /
NK069(tu)001:22867: ngag tu glu tshig gi dbyangs dang sngags su bcas pas /
NK069(tu)001:22868: lu gu rgyud dang spel la dkyil 'khor chen po'i mtha' na phar la skor ba bya /
NK069(tu)001:22869: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK069(tu)001:22870: zhes dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni /
NK069(tu)001:22871: dpal chen po'i chun mar byas pas na slas so //
NK069(tu)001:22872: dregs pas ma tshor bar spyad pas na byi mo' /
NK069(tu)001:22873: tha mar dkyil 'khor du bkod nas /
NK069(tu)001:22874: las kyi pho nyar khas blangs pas na bran zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22875: bro gar glu tshig chen mos ni //
NK069(tu)001:22876: zhes 'di dag gi ting nge 'dzin du zhugs nas le'u bco lnga pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:22877: 'di nyid kyi lhag ma'i sbyin pa la sogs pa byas pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:22878: rbad cing gtang bar bya ba ste //
NK069(tu)001:22879: zhes dgra bgegs la dbang mo rnams rbad cing /
NK069(tu)001:22880: rnal 'byor pa'i las la tang bar bya ba yin te /
NK069(tu)001:22881: thams cad thams cad byed pa yin //
NK069(tu)001:22882: zhes zhi rgyas gnyis kyi las thams cad dang /
NK069(tu)001:22883: dbang drag gnyis kyi las thams cad dam /
NK069(tu)001:22884: bdag gi las thams cad dang /
NK069(tu)001:22885: gzhan gyi las thams cad byed pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:22887: 'dir sgo ma bzhi'i bren mo byung bas /
NK069(tu)001:22889: ma dgos pa yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:22890: sgo ma bzhis kyang zhi rgyas dbang drag gi las bzhi 'grub la /
NK069(tu)001:22891: lha gzhan ma rnams la yang zhi rgyas dbang drag gi las bzhi tshang bas ma smos pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22892: le'u 'dir dbang mo lan gnyis 'dabs so zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:22893: ma 'dabs te dgong dang slas dang byi mo /
NK069(tu)001:22895: lhag ma gtor ba yin la /
