NK069(tu)001:22896: 'di nas slas dang byi mo bran mo zhes pa ni bro gdung ba yin no //
NK069(tu)001:22897: ljon pa dang ni dgongs te bshad pa'i yum ni /
NK069(tu)001:22899: dper na shing ljon pa lta bu ste /
NK069(tu)001:22901: rgyud dul bas zhi ba'i yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:22904: srid du ring la 'phra la ltem //
NK069(tu)001:22906: ljon shing ma zhes bshad pa yin //
NK069(tu)001:22910: dbus kun rdar ma gsum la rlung snyoms par gzhon pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22911: gsang ba'i gzungs ma 'di ni 'bu ta kro ti shwa rir byin rlob /
NK069(tu)001:22914: ljon shing 'bras bu skye ba'i shing lcug ma dngos la bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:22915: de dang 'dra ba'i bud myed na so tshad du phyin pa /
NK069(tu)001:22917: de rgyas pa'i yum du shes so //
NK069(tu)001:22918: rngam klog gi bcu gcig pa las 'phra zhing bshan la bzang po ring /
NK069(tu)001:22919: bcu gnyis nyi shu rtsa lnga'i bar //
NK069(tu)001:22920: lus la rag ta 'dzag pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:22921: rdo rje'i mtshon gyis ma phog pa //
NK069(tu)001:22922: lcug phrad ma'i rigs su bshad //
NK069(tu)001:22924: nang rtsa gsum po de spu na gu'i na khrag gi thig ler 'dus pa la /
NK069(tu)001:22925: khu ba 'bab sla bas skye rgyu mang ngo //
NK069(tu)001:22926: gsang ba gzung 'di ni rad na kro ti shwa rir byin barloba /
NK069(tu)001:22927: sdong cig dang ni sdong gcig ma ni /
NK069(tu)001:22928: shing sdong po gcig lta bu ste /
NK069(tu)001:22929: bud myed skye rgyun ma chad pa /
NK069(tu)001:22930: gnyen bshes med pa'i cig pu ma la /
NK069(tu)001:22933: skye rgyun med cing kra mi shis //
NK069(tu)001:22934: gcig pur 'dug pa sdong gcig ma //
NK069(tu)001:22936: dbang gi yul du de mngags pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22937: nang rtsa gsum po de khrag gi thig ler 'brel thag ring bas des bkra mi shis pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22938: gsang gzungs 'di pad ma kro ti shwa rir byin gyis rlob /
NK069(tu)001:22940: zhes me reg ni shing mes tshig pa lta bu ste /
NK069(tu)001:22942: de ni drag po'i yum mo //
NK069(tu)001:22944: yan lag thams cad mes tshig bzhin //
NK069(tu)001:22945: tan du 'phel ba'i rgyu med pa //
NK069(tu)001:22946: me rig ma'i rigs su bshad //
NK069(tu)001:22948: yugs sa mo'i rigs la bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22950: g.yas su rlung rnams zhugs pas /
NK069(tu)001:22951: rlung gis rtsa tshig nas skye rgyu med pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22952: gsang gzung 'di badz+ra kro ti shwa rir 'am /
NK069(tu)001:22953: kar ma kro tir byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22954: dang bas dga' ba chags pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:22955: zhi ba la dang ba'i sems kyis phur pa gdab pa sogs bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22956: rgyas pa la dga' zhing spro ba dang chags pa'i sems kyis las sbyar bar bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22957: drag po la 'khros shing 'khrugs pa'i sems kyis las la sbyar ro //
NK069(tu)001:22958: 'khros pas ki li rab tu bya //
NK069(tu)001:22959: zhes ki li ni phur pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:22960: sems de bzhi dang ldan pas las bzhi'i phur pa gdab par rab tu bya ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:22961: yang na thabs shes rab dang ldan pas bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:22963: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid de bzhin gshegs pa nyid sbyong bar gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:22964: zhes ston pa de bzhin gshegs pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:22966: 'dul bya 'dul ba'i don du sbyong bar gyur to //
NK069(tu)001:22967: de bzhin gshegs pa da bzod las rnam bzhi sbyong dgos pa lta bu ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:22968: sems can de bzhin gshegs pa'i rang bzhin las ma zhan pa'i bdag nyid las /
NK069(tu)001:22969: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs ye shes kyi bdag nyid /
NK069(tu)001:22970: 'phrin las rnams kyis sems can gyi sgrib pa sbyong bar 'gyur ro'am /
NK069(tu)001:22971: yang na rnal 'byor pa'i shes rab dang ting nge
NK069(tu)001:22972: 'dzin gyi rtsal rang gi rig pa la sbyong bar
NK069(tu)001:22974: gsang ba rtogs par dka' bas snying po cud 'dus
NK069(tu)001:22975: pas ma nor bas de kho na nyid mi slu
NK069(tu)001:22977: lhun gyis grub pa'i 'phrin las 'phrin las rnam pa
NK069(tu)001:22978: bzhi lhun gyis grub par bdag gzhan la byin gyis
NK069(tu)001:22979: rlab pa'i 'phrin las rnam bzhi byin gyis barloba pa
NK069(tu)001:22980: zhes bya ba'i le'u ste nyi shu pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:22982: // de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen po'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyis /
NK069(tu)001:22983: zhes 'phrin las ston pa de nas /
NK069(tu)001:22990: rigs lnga'i khro bo'i tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gyis kun tu bzang po nyid kyis nyid la /
NK069(tu)001:22991: shin tu rngam pa'i gdangs kyis //
NK069(tu)001:22992: shin tu khro tshul gyis don 'dzum la dngos rngam pa'i glu 'di blangs so //
NK069(tu)001:22993: zhes ma mo'i bshugs glu dang /
NK069(tu)001:22997: h'u tum chen dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar //
NK069(tu)001:22998: zhes de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi khro bo la sku'i sgo nas stod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:22999: h'u ye shes lnga dang ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:23000: klu nyid ye shes rgyan gyi klu yin pas phyin 'go drangs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23002: rtag chad dang gzung 'dzin gyi mtha' las khro zhing tum pa'i rtags /
NK069(tu)001:23003: sku yang 'khro tum ltar bzhugs pas na tum chen zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:23006: 'phrin las drag shul mdzad pa'i phyag stum /
NK069(tu)001:23007: de lta bu'i sku la ye shes kyi me /
NK069(tu)001:23008: skal pa 'jig pa'i dus mtha'i me lta bu 'bar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:23010: zhes sku las ye shes kyi 'od zer 'phro ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:23011: mun pa sel ba'i 'od zer gsal /
NK069(tu)001:23012: thabs mkhas pa'i 'od zer mang ba /
NK069(tu)001:23013: thugs rje chen po'i 'od zer gyis khyab pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:23014: dper na nyi ma 'bum gyi 'od zer bas che ba 'am /
NK069(tu)001:23015: de dag nyi ma 'bum dus gcig tu shar ba'i 'od lta bus thams cad zil gyis mnon no //
NK069(tu)001:23016: khro gnyer klog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK069(tu)001:23017: zhes dbang du sdud pa'i khro gnyer sna gong du sdud pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:23018: zil gnod pa'i khro gnyer mig dang rna mchog bar du sgreng ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:23019: thabs la mkhas pa'i khro gnyer spra ba /
NK069(tu)001:23020: sna tshogs su g.yo' ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:23021: de yang dper na nam ka la klog stod dus cig tu 'khyugs pa lta'o //
NK069(tu)001:23022: mche' ba zang yag za byed che ho //
NK069(tu)001:23023: zhes skye shi rtsad nas gcod pa'i mche' ba dkar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:23024: gdug pa za byed kyi mche' ba rtsa dmar ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:23025: rngam pa'i mche' ba rab tu rno ba ste /
NK069(tu)001:23026: don ye shes kyis skye shi dang gzung 'dzin rtsad
NK069(tu)001:23027: nas cad pa'i rtags mche' ba ran tsam nyug ge
NK069(tu)001:23028: rtsegs pa dang / mche' ba dkar ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:23029: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes la dngos po dang mtshan mas ma gos pa /
NK069(tu)001:23030: rno ba skye shi rtsad nas gcod pa /
NK069(tu)001:23031: rtse mo zlum pa spros pa dang bral ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:23032: h'u rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug stong 'dir //
NK069(tu)001:23033: zhes pad ma rigs kyi khro bo la gsung gi sgo nas stod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:23035: drag po'i nga ro 'jigs par drag pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:23036: stong pa'i gsung chos skur rngam /
NK069(tu)001:23037: bde' ba'i gsung long skur rngam /
NK069(tu)001:23038: mdzad pa'i gsung sprul skur rngam mo //
NK069(tu)001:23039: de yang thugs don ye shes yod myed dang rtag
NK069(tu)001:23040: chad kyi mtha' la rngam pa'i rtags rngam pa'i nga
NK069(tu)001:23041: ro de yang 'brug stong dus cig la 'dir ba'i
NK069(tu)001:23042: sgra'o // stug chem ri rab 'bum rnyil skad //
NK069(tu)001:23043: ces lha gshegs pa'i stug chem che ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:23044: 'phrin las mdzad pa'i stug chem drag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:23045: sprul pa 'khrug pa'i stug chem mang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:23046: stug chem gyi skad de yang /
NK069(tu)001:23047: dper na ri rab 'bum dus gcig la nyel ba bas kyang sgra skad che la 'jigs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23048: a a ha la'i gad rgyangs che //
NK069(tu)001:23049: zhes rngam pa'i gad mo a a dang /
NK069(tu)001:23050: stum pa'i gad mo ha la ha la dang /
NK069(tu)001:23051: dgyes pa'i gad mo ha ha ste /
NK069(tu)001:23052: a a ha la chos nyid rtogs pa'i dgyes pa dang ldan pa'i rtags /
NK069(tu)001:23053: rta bgad drag po chen po byung bas gad rgyangs che zhes bya ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:23056: ma skyes pa chos kyi dbyings rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:23057: dngos po dang mtshan ma'i mtha' thams cad 'joms pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23058: dpyugs pas mthor rlung g.yeng ba che ho //
NK069(tu)001:23059: zhes 'khor sdud pa'i bshugs pa stang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:23060: bdug pa 'dul ba'i bshugs pa drag pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:23063: de yang chos thams cad chos nyid las mi zhan par thugs su chud pas /
NK069(tu)001:23064: zhal nas bshugs pa'i rgyun brengs pas /
NK069(tu)001:23065: 'jig rten thams cad gtor zhing 'jig pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:23066: ras bal rlung gis gtor ba bzhin du 'gyur bas na g.yeng ba che zhes gsungs pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:23067: h'u khro bo shes rab 'od po che //
NK069(tu)001:23068: zhes rdo rje rigs kyi khro bo la thugs kyi sgo nas stod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:23069: shes rab chen po sngon du gtang bas ni /
NK069(tu)001:23070: khro bor bcas pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:23071: snying rje chen po sngon du gtang bas ni khro bo bcos pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:23072: sdug bsngal sel ba'i shes rab gsal /
NK069(tu)001:23073: nyon mongs pa sel ba'i shes rab gdang ba /
NK069(tu)001:23074: sgrib pa sel ba'i shes rab 'phro ba de /
NK069(tu)001:23075: khro bo nyid shes rab kyi ngo bo la /
NK069(tu)001:23076: ldang na mi dmigs shing mi sgrib par gsal ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:23077: bcas bcos gnyis dang ldan pa'i khro bos /
NK069(tu)001:23078: thugs mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:23079: yang dag pa'i shes rab des /
NK069(tu)001:23080: ma rig pa'i man pa sel zhing /
NK069(tu)001:23081: ye shes chen po'i snang bskyed cing mchod par byed pas na /
NK069(tu)001:23082: 'od po che zhes bya ste 'od gzhan las 'phags so //
NK069(tu)001:23083: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal //
NK069(tu)001:23084: zhes thugs ye shes dkyil lta bu la /
NK069(tu)001:23085: ye shes bzhi'i 'khor dang ldan pa de la /
NK069(tu)001:23086: dus dang gnas skabs kun tu gzung 'dzin gyis ma sgribs pas gsal ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:23087: yang na gnas pa ye shes lnga dang /
NK069(tu)001:23088: rtogs pa'i ye shes lnga yang /
NK069(tu)001:23089: ye shes rnam pa lnga'i bya ba thams cad ma
NK069(tu)001:23090: lus par mkhyen pas na dus kun tu gsal ba'i
NK069(tu)001:23091: rang bzhin no // 'bar ba'i ye shes kun tu 'joms //
NK069(tu)001:23092: zhes thugs ye shes de la /
NK069(tu)001:23094: snying rje 'bar pa rnam gnyis dang ldan pas /
NK069(tu)001:23095: phyi dngos po dang mtshan ma dang /
NK069(tu)001:23096: nang shes pa'i rgyud la yod pa'i gzung 'dzin gyi bag chags sreg par byed pas 'joms pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23097: yang na thugs rdo rje lta bu'i ye shes kyis /
NK069(tu)001:23098: snang ba dang dngos po thams cad yang rang nyid
NK069(tu)001:23099: las mi zhan par sbyong zhing 'joms pas 'joms zhes
NK069(tu)001:23100: bya'o // sna tshogs ye shes thig le che ho //
NK069(tu)001:23101: zhes thugs ye shes nyid sna tshogs pa'i chos su snang ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:23102: sna tshogs pa'i chos thams cad thugs ye shes de'i
NK069(tu)001:23103: dkyil 'khor las mi zhan pas thig le che ho
NK069(tu)001:23104: zhes pa'o // yang na snang ba'i ye shes lnga /
NK069(tu)001:23105: kri yog gi ye shes lnga mtshan nyid theg pa'i ye shes bzhi /
NK069(tu)001:23108: de bzhin nyid kyi ye shes /
NK069(tu)001:23109: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes de /
NK069(tu)001:23110: ye shes bco' brgyad thugs la dbyer med du gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:23111: 'dir gtar kas gags gsal ba ni /
NK069(tu)001:23112: thams cad thig ler stod pas mtshon tshul 'dres zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:23115: go brda' sprod pa'i dngos nas gsung /
NK069(tu)001:23116: mi tog pa'i dngos nas thugs /
NK069(tu)001:23117: ma 'gags pas yon tan mdzad pa'i dngos nas 'phrin las yin te /
NK069(tu)001:23118: mtshon tshul gcig la tha dad pas ma 'dres pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23119: h'u khro bo'i rgyal po sprin chen po //
NK069(tu)001:23120: zhes rin po che'i rigs kyi khro bo la yon tan gyi sgo nas stod de /
NK069(tu)001:23121: rin po che'i rigs kyi khro bo ni /
NK069(tu)001:23122: khro bo thams cad kyi yon tan mchog gam rgyal
NK069(tu)001:23123: por gyur pa rad na he ru ka yin te
NK069(tu)001:23124: / sku'i yon tan ni gti' mug la 'khro gsung 'dod chags la /
NK069(tu)001:23127: 'phrin las 'phrag dog la 'khros pas rgyal po /
NK069(tu)001:23128: khro bo de mas yon tan mang po sprin dang 'dra bar 'byung ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:23129: yon tan gyi tshogs mang bas na sprin chen no //
NK069(tu)001:23131: zhes rin po che'i rigs kyi khro bo la /
NK069(tu)001:23132: sprin gyi tshogs las char gyi rgyur 'byung ba ltar /
NK069(tu)001:23133: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi char chen po'i 'bebs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23134: de yang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor so so'i sprul pa dang bcas pa /
NK069(tu)001:23135: bsam yas pa gdul bya tha dad la snang bar mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23136: de dag mi bzad pa'i phyir na /
NK069(tu)001:23137: dkyil 'khor yid bzhin du 'byung ba'i ter dang char chen no //
NK069(tu)001:23139: zhes yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che la rtog pa myed bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:23140: dgos 'dod yid bzhin du 'byung ba dang 'dra bar /
NK069(tu)001:23141: rin po che'i rigs kyi khro bo de las kyang /
NK069(tu)001:23142: rtog pa myed bzhin du khro bo'i dkyil 'khor yid bzhin du 'byung zhing /
NK069(tu)001:23143: zad mi shes pa'i gter chen por gyur pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:23144: sna tshogs 'khros pa'i thig le che ho //
NK069(tu)001:23145: zhes sna tshogs khro bo'i dkyil 'khor 'byung ba yang /
NK069(tu)001:23147: yon tan ni rin po che'i rigs kyi khro bo ste /
NK069(tu)001:23148: yon tan sna tshogs dang bcas pa'i khro bo de rnams /
NK069(tu)001:23149: rin po che'i rigs su ro gcig pa'i phyir thig le /
NK069(tu)001:23150: 'di dang dbyer myed par dgyes pas na ho zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:23151: h'u bdud kun kyi ni bdud chen po //
NK069(tu)001:23152: zhes las kyi rigs kyi khro bo la 'phrin las kyi sgo nas stod pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:23153: bdud ni dbye' na bzhi ste /
NK069(tu)001:23158: de yang bsdu na gnyis ste /
NK069(tu)001:23167: bdud bzhi po kun gyi rang bzhin nam bdag nyid yang yin la /
NK069(tu)001:23168: de dag kun la mnga' snyems pa yang yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:23171: ma spangs dbang du byed pa'i phyir na bdud kun gyi bdud chen po'o //
NK069(tu)001:23172: bdud kyi bdud te bdun rnams 'joms //
NK069(tu)001:23173: zhes bdud de dag gi yang bar du gcod pa'i bdud du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK069(tu)001:23175: bdud de 'joms par byed pas na bdud rnams 'joms so //
NK069(tu)001:23177: ru tra 'khor dang bcas pa bcom zhing sbyangs /
NK069(tu)001:23179: phyir ltas na ru tra 'pham par snang ba ni 'joms pa chen po yin no //
NK069(tu)001:23181: zhes las kyi rigs kyi khro bo de ni /
NK069(tu)001:23182: srin po chen po ru tra la sogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:23184: las kyi he ru kas 'jig par byed de /
NK069(tu)001:23185: thams cad bsdigs par snang bar mdzad pa'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:23186: 'jigs byed chen po thig le che ho //
NK069(tu)001:23187: zhes las kyi rigs kyi khro bos sems can 'jigs par byed pa la /
NK069(tu)001:23188: des 'jigs par byed pa'i nang nas /
NK069(tu)001:23190: sangs rgyas rnams khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du sgrur ba
NK069(tu)001:23191: de las che la 'jigs pa myed pas 'jigs byed
NK069(tu)001:23192: chen po ste / ye shes kyi mdzad pa thams
NK069(tu)001:23193: cad chos nyid las ma g.yos par sgang bas na
NK069(tu)001:23194: thig le che ho zhes dgyes pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23196: 'phrin las la stod pa lan gnyis byung bas 'dabs so zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:23198: gong ma na las kyi rigs kyi khro bo la stong pa yin la /
NK069(tu)001:23199: 'di khro bo lnga ka'i skal pa'i 'phrin las la stod pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23200: de yang snod kyi 'jig rten 'jig pa yang sangs rgyas kyi 'phrin las te /
NK069(tu)001:23201: las ngan pa rgyun bcas nas /
NK069(tu)001:23202: gnas ngan pa blangs pa rnams sgrol ba'i phyir ro //
NK069(tu)001:23203: h'u rdo rje brag chen sra ba po //
NK069(tu)001:23204: zhes 'byung ba bzhi dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:23205: thugs ye shes ni 'byung ba chen po brag gi rnam par yang snang la /
NK069(tu)001:23206: brag tha mal pa 'joms par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:23207: ye shes bzhi dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:23208: brag ni sra zhing rtan pa yin te /
NK069(tu)001:23209: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis chos thams cad stong zhing bdag myed par rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:23210: dngos po dang mtshan ma'i mthar myi dmyigs myi 'gyur ba ni brag dang 'dra ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:23211: de ni gdan rdo rje brag la tshang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:23212: rdo rje chu bo sdud chen po //
NK069(tu)001:23213: zhes 'byung ba bzhi dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:23215: 'byung ba chen po chu'i rnam par yang snang la /
NK069(tu)001:23216: des chu tha mal pa yang sdud par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:23217: ye shes bzhi dang sbyar na /
NK069(tu)001:23218: chu ni sdud par byed pa yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:23220: chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rtogs cing mnyam
NK069(tu)001:23221: pa nyid du bsdud par byed pas bsdud chen po
NK069(tu)001:23222: / de ni zhal nas rag ta'i chu 'bab pa'am /
NK069(tu)001:23224: rdo rje me te kun 'bar che //
NK069(tu)001:23227: 'byung ba chen po me'i rnam par yang snang la /
NK069(tu)001:23228: des me tha mal pa yang sreg par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:23230: me ni sreg bar byed pa yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:23231: so so kun tu rtog pa'i ye shes kyis kyang /
NK069(tu)001:23232: spyi'i mtshan nyid ni stong zhing bdag myed par rtogs pas /
NK069(tu)001:23233: 'khor ba'i mtha' sreg par byed la /
NK069(tu)001:23234: rang gi mtshan nyid ni ma 'chol bar mkhyen pas /
NK069(tu)001:23235: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i don byed pas /
NK069(tu)001:23236: nyan thos zhi ba phyogs gcig pa'i mtha' sreg par byed do //
NK069(tu)001:23237: de ni sku la skal pa'i me 'bar ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:23239: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che ho //
NK069(tu)001:23241: thugs ye shes de 'byung ba chen po rlung gi rnam par snang la /
NK069(tu)001:23242: des rlung tha mal pa yang 'thor zhing g.yeng bar byed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23244: rlung gi skyod par byed pa yin pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:23245: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyis kyang /
NK069(tu)001:23247: mya ngan las 'das pa'i gnas su skyod par byed pas 'thor rlung che ho /
NK069(tu)001:23249: de ni shangs nas ye shes kyi rlung lngas /
NK069(tu)001:23250: nyon mongs pa lnga 'thor bar byed do //
NK069(tu)001:23251: 'di rnams la ngag don du drug ste /
NK069(tu)001:23254: nyon mongs pa'i gnyen po dang /
NK069(tu)001:23259: 'bu ta he ru ka de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs te /
NK069(tu)001:23260: 'gro ba'i 'jig rten du thugs rjes don la gshegs pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23261: rdo rje he ru ka ni rdo rje'i rigs te /
NK069(tu)001:23262: sems can log pa'i zhe sdang thams cad chos su sgrol ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:23263: rad na he ru ka ni /
NK069(tu)001:23265: che ba'i yon tan rin po che ltar sems can gyi dgos 'dod skong ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:23266: pad ma he ru ka ni 'dod chags pad ma'i rigs te /
NK069(tu)001:23267: 'gro ba chags pa'i tshul gyis 'dul ba'i don mdzad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23268: kar ma he ru ka 'phrin las kyi rigs te /
NK069(tu)001:23269: sems can 'phrag dog gis phyin ci log tu lta ba yang dag pa la 'dzud pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23271: gti' mug 'bu ta he ru ka /
NK069(tu)001:23272: zhe sdang badz+ra he ru ka /
NK069(tu)001:23273: nga rgyal rad na he ru ka /
NK069(tu)001:23274: 'dod chags pad ma he ru ka /
NK069(tu)001:23275: 'phrag don kar ma he ru ka'o //
NK069(tu)001:23276: gti' mug 'joms pas sangs rgyas he ru ka /
NK069(tu)001:23277: zhe sdang 'joms pas rdo rje he ru ka /
NK069(tu)001:23278: nga rgyal 'joms pas rin chen he ru ka /
NK069(tu)001:23279: 'dod chags 'joms pas pad ma he ru ka /
NK069(tu)001:23280: 'phrag dog 'joms pas las kyi he ru ka'o //
NK069(tu)001:23281: yum ni sra ba'i brag rdo rje dbyings phyug ma /
NK069(tu)001:23282: bsher zhing rlan pa'i chu rin chen dbyings phyug ma /
NK069(tu)001:23283: sreg cing smin pa'i me pad ma dbyings phyug ma /
NK069(tu)001:23284: mthor zhing skyod pa'i rlung las kyi dbyings phyug ma'o //
NK069(tu)001:23285: nam mkha' ni spyir yongs na gnas pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23288: ye shes rdo rje zhe sdang 'joms //
NK069(tu)001:23291: las kyi ral gris phrag dog 'joms so //
NK069(tu)001:23293: bde' gshegs he ru ka'i 'phrin las te /
NK069(tu)001:23294: shes rab kyis lta ba rtogs na /
NK069(tu)001:23295: phyi'i skal pa nam mkha' stongs /
NK069(tu)001:23296: nang gi skal pa phung po'i rgas rgud 'joms pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23297: mtshon cha'i skal pas 'jig pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:23298: badz+ra he ru ka'i 'phrin las te /
NK069(tu)001:23301: rad na he ru ka'i 'phrin las te /
NK069(tu)001:23302: zhi gnas kyi chus bdag 'dzin gyi bag chags 'khru ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:23303: me'i skal pas sreg pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:23304: lhag mthong gi mes ma rig pa sreg pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23305: rlung gis 'thor ba ni kar ma he ru ka'i 'phrin las te /
NK069(tu)001:23306: shes rab thogs pa med pas phyin ci log gi
NK069(tu)001:23307: 'phrag dog thams cad ye shes kyi rlung gis 'thor
NK069(tu)001:23308: bar byed pa'o // de yang 'phrin las rnams yum dang dbyer myed pas na /
NK069(tu)001:23309: 'byung ba bzhi yum dang bcas pa la sogs pa la stod pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:23311: gsang pa snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:23312: khro bo la stod pa'i le'u ste nyi shu gcig pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23314: // de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:23315: zhes rgyud don rdzogs pa'i rjes de nas /
NK069(tu)001:23316: rgyud gtad pa ston pas so //
NK069(tu)001:23317: ston pa bcom ldan 'das don la dgyes pa chen pos /
NK069(tu)001:23318: bdud bzhi ni rtogs pas bcom /
NK069(tu)001:23319: legs pa ni yon tan du ldan /
NK069(tu)001:23320: mtha' thams cad ni skyog las 'das /
NK069(tu)001:23321: 'gro ba sems can gyi don mdzad par ni dgyes /
NK069(tu)001:23322: gzhan las khyad 'phags pas chen po'o //
NK069(tu)001:23323: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la sngags kyi rgyal po stan par bzung ba 'di ched du brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:23324: zhes de yang mdo sde thams cad ni 'jam dpal la gtad /
NK069(tu)001:23325: 'dul ba thams cad ni 'phags pa kun dga' bo la gtad /
NK069(tu)001:23326: mngon pa thams cad ni 'phags pa byams pa la gtad /
NK069(tu)001:23327: yo ga phyir rgyud ni phyag na rdo rje la gtad /
NK069(tu)001:23328: nang pa gsang ba'i rgyud kha gcig ni rdo rje chos la gtad /
NK069(tu)001:23329: gsang ba'i snying po'i rgyud 'di' don ni /
NK069(tu)001:23330: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la gtad do //
NK069(tu)001:23332: gtad da ma 'ongs pa'i rnal 'byor pa las 'phro
NK069(tu)001:23333: dang skal bar ldan pa rnams kyi don du stan
NK069(tu)001:23334: na / rnal 'byor pa nyid de bzhin gshegs par sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin yin pas na /
NK069(tu)001:23335: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid la zhes bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:23336: rgyud gsang pa snying po 'di las /
NK069(tu)001:23337: rgyud dang mtshan nyid thams cad dang po yang 'di las byung /
NK069(tu)001:23340: gtan la yang 'dir nges par 'bebs pas /
NK069(tu)001:23341: rgyud 'di ni mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi 'byung gnas /
NK069(tu)001:23342: rgyud kyi mtshan por gyur pas /
NK069(tu)001:23344: rgyud gsang ba snying po 'di ni ma 'ongs pa'i
NK069(tu)001:23345: rnal 'byor pa las 'phro dang skal bar ldan pa
NK069(tu)001:23346: rnams kyis / shes rab rnam pa gsum gyis stan zhing mi 'gyur ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:23347: myi nub par gzung ba'i thabs 'di rjod do //
NK069(tu)001:23349: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rang bzhin 'di //
NK069(tu)001:23350: zhes kye kye ni bod pa'i ngam pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:23354: dus bzhi snga phyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:23355: ji lta bu yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:23356: phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin ni /
NK069(tu)001:23357: da bzod lam gyis ma sgrubs /
NK069(tu)001:23358: gnyen pos ma bcos pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:23359: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo nyid //
NK069(tu)001:23360: ces ye nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:23361: gsangs nyid yin pas ngo bo nyid do //
NK069(tu)001:23362: 'o na phyogs bcu dang dus bzhis bsdus pa'i chos 'di dag thams cad kyi rang bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:23363: ye nas sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas pa /
NK069(tu)001:23364: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ngo bo yin na /
NK069(tu)001:23365: 'o na chos thams cad kyi khongs su sems can yang rtogs na /
NK069(tu)001:23366: sems can khams gsum du 'khor ba ci ste na /
NK069(tu)001:23368: zhes rang gi gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pas cings te /
NK069(tu)001:23369: phyi bzung ba'i yul med pa la ni /
NK069(tu)001:23370: bzung ba'i yul du btags la /
NK069(tu)001:23371: nang 'dzin pa'i sems myed pa la ni 'dzin pa'i sems su bzung ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:23372: gzung 'dzin gnyis su spros pa la zhen nam /
NK069(tu)001:23375: rnam rtog zhags pas so sor zin //
NK069(tu)001:23376: zhes phyin ci log gi rnam par rtog pa zhags pa dang 'dra bas /
NK069(tu)001:23377: so so rang rang gis rang rang zin /
NK069(tu)001:23378: rang rang gis rang rang sngams pas 'khor ba yin /
NK069(tu)001:23379: de yang rang rang gi rnam par rtog pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:23381: des rang gi rgyud cings pa ni zhags pas zin pa dang 'dra /
NK069(tu)001:23382: de yang tha dad so sor snang bar zin pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23383: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK069(tu)001:23384: zhes byang chub sems pa'i sa dang po rab tu dga' ba /
NK069(tu)001:23385: gnyis pa dri ma myed pa /
NK069(tu)001:23389: drug pa mngon du gyur pa /
NK069(tu)001:23390: bdun pa ring du song ba /
NK069(tu)001:23392: dgu pa legs pa'i blo gros /
NK069(tu)001:23393: bcu pa chos kyi sprin nas /
NK069(tu)001:23394: sangs rgyas kyi sa kun tu 'od nas /
NK069(tu)001:23395: pad ma spyan la sogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:23396: rim pa skas kyi ldang bu ltar bkod de gnas pa de yang zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:23397: gsang ba'i snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK069(tu)001:23398: zhes rgyud gsang po dang yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa dbyer myed de /
NK069(tu)001:23399: gsang ba snying po yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen
NK069(tu)001:23400: du 'gro ba'i lam stigs su theg pa gzhan gyur
NK069(tu)001:23402: ye shes ngo mtshar rab 'byam gyis //
NK069(tu)001:23403: zhes 'bras bu byang chub sems pa'i rnams kyi rim pa khyad par bkod pa kun /
NK069(tu)001:23404: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen du 'gro ba'i lam stegs yin phan cad /
NK069(tu)001:23405: sa'i khyad par rim par gnas pa de dag 'grub pa'i rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:23406: sangs rgyas kyi chos kyi sa ka ngo mtshan can rab 'byam gsungs so //
NK069(tu)001:23407: don du mi 'gyur yong ma gsungs //
NK069(tu)001:23408: zhes theg pa'i bye brag mtha' yas bsam gyis mi khyab pa cig gsung ba yang /
NK069(tu)001:23409: sems can gyi don du mi 'gyur ba'i chos ni 'ga' yang ma gsungs te /
NK069(tu)001:23410: la la lam stegs su gsungs /
NK069(tu)001:23411: la la lam la 'jug par gsungs /
NK069(tu)001:23412: la la 'bras bu'i chos su gsungs so //
NK069(tu)001:23413: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa ni ye shes gnyis su 'dus te /
NK069(tu)001:23414: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK069(tu)001:23415: ci yang sa le mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK069(tu)001:23416: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK069(tu)001:23417: ci yang sa le mkhyen pa'i ye shes de yang /
NK069(tu)001:23418: rnam par mi rtog ye shes kyi ngang la ma g.yos bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:23419: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK069(tu)001:23420: chos thams cad kyu ru ra lag thil du blangs pa bzhin du /
NK069(tu)001:23421: sa le mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis gsal bar yang mkhyen la /
NK069(tu)001:23422: mkhyen bzhin rnam par mi rtog /
NK069(tu)001:23423: de lta bu'i thugs ye shes ngo mtshar ba /
NK069(tu)001:23424: thugs rje chen po rab 'byams bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:23425: bde' bar gshegs pa rnams kyis /
NK069(tu)001:23426: 'dul ba'i dbang du sems can gyi blo'i rim pa dang sbyar nas /
NK069(tu)001:23427: theg pa'i bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab pa gcig gsungs yang /
NK069(tu)001:23428: sems can so so'i don du 'gyur bar gsungs shing /
NK069(tu)001:23429: don du mi 'gyur ba'i chos ni gang yang ma gsungs pas /
NK069(tu)001:23430: 'on te theg pa mtho dman so so'i blo la 'tsham zhing bzang bas /
NK069(tu)001:23431: 'gro ba'i don du yang yang du myed de /
NK069(tu)001:23433: theg pa mtha' dag thams cad bzung bar stan pa zhes kyang gsungs pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:23435: rgyud zab mo 'di stan pa'i sngon du nyan dbang thob dgos pa yang bshad nas /
NK069(tu)001:23436: 'dir rtogs nas sgra na dbang thob pa bshad pa dang 'gal zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:23438: sngon la nyan dbang thob nas de nas rtogs nas bshad na /
NK069(tu)001:23440: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang thams cad ma lus par rdzogs par bshad pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23441: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK069(tu)001:23442: phyag rgya gsang chen snying po 'di //
NK069(tu)001:23443: zhes rgyud 'di 'chad pa'i yon tan bstan pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:23444: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK069(tu)001:23445: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya rang bzhin 'di rtogs par ka bas rang bzhin gyis gsang ba /
NK069(tu)001:23446: de snod du ma gyur ba la mi rtogs pas mi stan pa'i gsang ba /
NK069(tu)001:23447: de lta bu'i rgyud gsang ba snying po 'di'i don rtogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:23448: rtogs pa thams cad kyi nang nas mchog gi snying po /
NK069(tu)001:23449: yon tan thams cad 'byung ba'i rgyur gyur pas rgyu'i snying po'am /
NK069(tu)001:23450: yang na mtshan nyid kyi chos thams cad 'byung ba'i rgyur gyur pa'i phyir yang /
NK069(tu)001:23451: snying po zhes bya ba 'di ni /
NK069(tu)001:23452: rtogs nas smra bar gang byed pa //
NK069(tu)001:23453: zhes 'di'i don bdag gis yang phyin ci ma log par rtogs pa /
NK069(tu)001:23454: rtogs nas gzhan la yang 'di chad cing sgra bar byed pa'i gang zag de ni /
NK069(tu)001:23455: de nyid nga yi dbang yang rdzogs //
NK069(tu)001:23456: zhes de nyid kun tu bzang po nga yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:23457: de la ni sdod dbang skur mi dgos te /
NK069(tu)001:23458: dbang yang rang chas su rdzogs par gnas pa yin zhe'am /
NK069(tu)001:23459: yang na de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi phyag
NK069(tu)001:23460: rgya gsang chen snying po 'di'i don bdag gis tshig
NK069(tu)001:23461: tsam ma yin par shes rab kyis kyang rtogs shing
NK069(tu)001:23462: rtogs pa'i don yang 'chad cing smra bar gang byed
NK069(tu)001:23464: de nyid dpal kun tu bzang po nga yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:23465: de lta bu la dbang skur na /
NK069(tu)001:23466: dbang yang rang bzhin gyis gnas par 'gyur ro zhes pa'i don to //
NK069(tu)001:23467: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la //
NK069(tu)001:23469: phyogs bcu'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs la /
NK069(tu)001:23470: gsang ba 'di la gzhan mi mnga' //
NK069(tu)001:23471: rgyud gsang ba snying po'i don 'di las ches gsang ba'i nges don gzhan mi mnga' bas /
NK069(tu)001:23472: sgro dang skur pa zhi ba yi //
NK069(tu)001:23475: phri te chad pa'i skur pa ma gtab /
NK069(tu)001:23476: sgro dang skur thams cad zhi ba yi don /
NK069(tu)001:23477: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK069(tu)001:23478: rang bzhin rtogs pa ka ba'i gsang ba'i /
NK069(tu)001:23479: ma mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad 'byung ba'i rgyur gyur pa'i snying po /
NK069(tu)001:23480: de kho na nyid yang dag pa /
NK069(tu)001:23481: nyid de nges pa'i dbyings nas phyung //
NK069(tu)001:23482: zhes ma nor ba kri ya ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:23483: drang ba'i don ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:23484: 'di ni nges pa'i don mthar phyin pa /
NK069(tu)001:23485: bde bar gshegs pa thugs kyi dbyings rum nas phyung ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:23486: thugs ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor nas phyung bas /
NK069(tu)001:23487: de nas nges par lung stan te //
NK069(tu)001:23488: rgyud 'di' don rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pa de ni /
NK069(tu)001:23489: da ltar nyid nas nges par sangs rgyas 'thob par lung stan pa ste /
NK069(tu)001:23490: sras ni thugs las skyes pa yin //
NK069(tu)001:23491: sras ni nyan thos rang rgyal yang yin na /
NK069(tu)001:23492: 'di'i don rtogs pa ni thugs las skyes pa'i sras yin no //
NK069(tu)001:23493: sa rab rig pa 'dzin la gnas //
NK069(tu)001:23494: sa rab ni rig pa 'dzin pa'i sa zhes kyang bya /
NK069(tu)001:23495: rdo rje 'dzin gyis la gnas zhes kyang bya /
NK069(tu)001:23496: kun tu bzang po dbye' ba myed pa'i sa zhes kyang bya /
NK069(tu)001:23497: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa zhes kyang bya /
NK069(tu)001:23498: sangs rgyas kyi sa 'thar phyin pa zhes kyang bya /
NK069(tu)001:23499: sangs rgyas kyi sa gnas so //
NK069(tu)001:23501: zhes ston pa kun tu bzang pos brjod pas /
NK069(tu)001:23502: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dbyer myed par dgyes nas /
NK069(tu)001:23503: de bzhin gshegs pa la la ni dgyes la /
NK069(tu)001:23504: la la ni mi dgyes pa lta bu ma yin te /
NK069(tu)001:23505: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad dgongs pa 'thun par dbyer myed par dgyes par gyur nas zhes bya /
NK069(tu)001:23506: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings //
NK069(tu)001:23507: phyogs bcu dus bzhis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:23508: don dam par skye ba myed par mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:23509: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i mtshan nyid du mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:23510: don dam pa dang kun rdzob dbyer myed par mnyam pa nyid kyi /
NK069(tu)001:23511: de lta bu'i rang bzhin yin pas dbyings so //
NK069(tu)001:23512: sku gsung thugs kyi lhun btug po' bkod pa'i //
NK069(tu)001:23513: zhes de ltar mnyam pa yang gzhan du mi mnyam /
NK069(tu)001:23514: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du mnyam ste /
NK069(tu)001:23515: phyogs bcu dus bzhis sdus pa'i chos thams cad /
NK069(tu)001:23516: kun rdzob sgyu ma mnyam zhing /
NK069(tu)001:23518: don dam par ma skyes par mnyam pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:23520: don dam pa dang kun rdzob dbyer myed pa ni thugs te /
NK069(tu)001:23521: de ltar chos thams cad sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil
NK069(tu)001:23522: 'khor du sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du ye nas
NK069(tu)001:23523: gnas pa la / 'thug po ni mang ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:23525: thugs kyi dgongs pa rtogs par dkar ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:23527: chos thams cad sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du sangs rgyas par lhun gyis grub par gnas pas /
NK069(tu)001:23528: sangs rgyas kyang bsam gyis mi khyab pa mang po rdzas rlabs pa ltar 'dug pas sdug po'am /
NK069(tu)001:23529: yang na go cha 'thug po la mtshon gyis phigs par dka' ba'am /
NK069(tu)001:23530: ko ba 'thug po la khab bam snyung bus phigs par ka ba ltar /
NK069(tu)001:23531: chos thams cad sku gsung thugs mi bzad pa rgyan
NK069(tu)001:23532: gyi 'khor lor sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin du gnas
NK069(tu)001:23533: pa'i don de rtogs par ka bas kyang 'thugs so
NK069(tu)001:23534: // tha dad pa myed bzhin du yang tha dad pa'i rnam par bkod pa'i /
NK069(tu)001:23535: de lta bu'i rgyan nyid du ston pa kun tu bzang po gnas so zhe 'am /
NK069(tu)001:23536: yang na ston pa kun tu bzang po'i thugs ye shes la ni /
NK069(tu)001:23537: thabs dang shes rab tu ldan pa la /
NK069(tu)001:23538: thabs shes rab kyi rgyan du cig gi rgyan du cig bzhugs pa yin no //
NK069(tu)001:23540: zhes rgyud 'di'i don rtogs pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:23541: rtogs pa thams cad kyi mchog gam rgyal po yin pas /
NK069(tu)001:23543: yang na rgyud la rtogs pa zhes bya ste /
NK069(tu)001:23544: rgyud 'di rgyud thams cad kyi mchog gam /
NK069(tu)001:23545: rgyal po zhes bya ba yin no //
NK069(tu)001:23546: sgyu 'phrul dra ba'i le'u stong phrag rgya pa la /
NK069(tu)001:23548: shes rab stong pa ni rgyu /
NK069(tu)001:23550: thabs shes rab dbyer myed pa ni dra ba /
NK069(tu)001:23554: de gnyis dbyer myed pa d+r+wa ba /
NK069(tu)001:23558: ba ga rdo rjer 'drel ba d+r+wa ba /
NK069(tu)001:23563: le'u stong phrag rgya pa ni /
NK069(tu)001:23564: sgyu 'phrul gyi rgyud sangs rgyas kyis gsung pa thams
NK069(tu)001:23565: cad kyi le'u grangs gcig tu grangs pa la stong
NK069(tu)001:23567: rgyud mi gcig yang chos sde tshoms su sgrangs ba yin no zhes bzhed pa'o //
NK069(tu)001:23568: mtshan nyid dang lung gi spyi dang /
NK069(tu)001:23569: zhes spyir chos thams cad kyi mtshan nyid zhib mor ston cing 'chad pas na mtshan nyid /
NK069(tu)001:23570: yon tan rdzod pas na mdo' sde che ba ston pas gsang sngags kyi lung yin pa las /
NK069(tu)001:23571: rgyu gsang ba snying po 'di nas /
NK069(tu)001:23573: mdul ba mdo' sde mngon pa la sogs pa yang 'dir 'dus pas na /
NK069(tu)001:23574: lung thams cad kyi ye yin no //
NK069(tu)001:23575: rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi /
NK069(tu)001:23576: zhes phyi pa thub pa'i rgyud /
NK069(tu)001:23577: kri ya dang yo ga dang u pa ya gsum yang 'dir 'dus par rton la /
NK069(tu)001:23578: nang pa thabs kyi rgyud ma h+aa yo ga dang /
NK069(tu)001:23579: lung a nu yo ga dang /
NK069(tu)001:23580: man ngag a ti yo ga ste /
NK069(tu)001:23583: rjes su rnal 'byor la sogs pa'i lung thams cad kyi spyi'o //
NK069(tu)001:23584: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba /
NK069(tu)001:23585: zhes dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas ni /
NK069(tu)001:23589: ma nor bar gshegs pas na de bzhin gshegs pa /
NK069(tu)001:23590: ma lus pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi gsang ba rmad du 'byung ba /
NK069(tu)001:23591: thugs yang dag pa'i ye shes phyin ci ma log par gnas pa ni gsang ba /
NK069(tu)001:23592: rol pa chen po ye shes kyi spyod yul rtogs par dka' bas gsang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:23593: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa'i lung las /
NK069(tu)001:23594: rtogs par dka' bas gsang ba /
NK069(tu)001:23596: ma nor pa de kho na nyid /
NK069(tu)001:23597: ma bcos pas nges pa'i kun 'dus pas lung ngo //
NK069(tu)001:23598: thams cad ma lus par spros te /
NK069(tu)001:23599: zhes mtshan nyid rgyu'i chos thams cad dang /
NK069(tu)001:23600: thub pa phyi pa'i sngags thams cad dang /
NK069(tu)001:23601: nang pa thabs kyi sngags thams cad de /
NK069(tu)001:23602: 'khor lo skor ba de dag gi 'bras bu'i mchog /
NK069(tu)001:23604: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi chos kyi 'khor lo //
NK069(tu)001:23605: ston pas skor zhing bshad pa de dag gi nang nas /
NK069(tu)001:23607: mdo' sde'i lugs kyis yon tan brjod pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:23608: sngags kyi lugs kyi che brjod pa yin /
NK069(tu)001:23610: chos kyi mtshan nyid zhib tu bshad pa yin pa la /
NK069(tu)001:23611: rgyud dang mtshan nyid thams cad ma lus par 'dir 'dus /
NK069(tu)001:23613: de skad du yang nyid kyi le'u gsum pa las /
NK069(tu)001:23614: 'dul ba mdo' sde chos mngon dang /
NK069(tu)001:23615: dam tshig sgrub dang grub pa dang /
NK069(tu)001:23616: sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud /
NK069(tu)001:23617: gsang ba snying po las 'phros te zhes gsungs pas gsal lo //
NK069(tu)001:23619: gsang ba snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las /
NK069(tu)001:23621: 'khor rnams rgyud kyi chos don zab mos /
NK069(tu)001:23622: mnyes pa dang yongs su ston pas 'khor la rgyud
NK069(tu)001:23623: yongs su gzung bar gtad pa'i gzung ba'i le'u nyi
NK069(tu)001:23627: // de las yongs su gtad pa'i don /
NK069(tu)001:23628: ched du nas brjod pa 'di brjod do //
NK069(tu)001:23629: gang na gsang chen 'di yod par /
NK069(tu)001:23630: me ma dper na rang gi mtha' la /
NK069(tu)001:23632: spu gri'i so ni mtha' ma skor kyang /
NK069(tu)001:23634: 'dzegs nas rgyud 'di shes pa de dag las /
NK069(tu)001:23635: bu dag 'gro bar sangs rgyas par bya'o //
NK069(tu)001:23636: kho ngan rang gi gnas pa'i yang khong snying gi nang du /
NK069(tu)001:23638: lcags dam pa 'am rub pa'i nges kyi sgrom bu kha bsdams so //
NK069(tu)001:23639: pa ltar sbas la mi smra'o //
NK069(tu)001:23640: thams cad la yang me long bzhin /
NK069(tu)001:23642: bltas kyang ye shes kyi gzugs snyan yongs su mi snang so //
NK069(tu)001:23643: rgyud 'di la man ngag ye shes 'phrul gyi lde dmig gis //
NK069(tu)001:23644: rdo rje'i tha tshigs rgyud 'di' sgo phye nas //
NK069(tu)001:23645: yid rgyud don bzhin rin chen gter gyur la /
NK069(tu)001:23646: skal ldan tshogs kyis rang rig pa'i shes rab kyis spyad du gsol //
NK069(tu)001:23650: // rgyud rgyal sgyu 'phrul gsang ba snying po 'di //
NK069(tu)001:23651: kun ston pa bzang phyag rdor sdud pa po rgyal
NK069(tu)001:23652: po las 'phro can la byin brlabs dza la bshad
NK069(tu)001:23653: // ku ku ra dza an+t+ra b+ho d+hi dang //
NK069(tu)001:23654: sras mo go ma sangs rgyas gsang la rgyud //
NK069(tu)001:23655: de'i slob ma bran bod kyi lo ts+aa ba ka mu re dang //
NK069(tu)001:23656: man+dzu sh+ri gnyis lo ts+aa sgra sgyur mkhan //
NK069(tu)001:23657: sangs rgyas gsang bas rgya gar gyi slob ma bi ma mi tra la //
NK069(tu)001:23658: bran ka 'jam dpal bi ma rnam gsum la //
NK069(tu)001:23659: rin chen mchog gis zhus nas slob ma ni //
NK069(tu)001:23660: bzhi ste gang yin zhe na /
NK069(tu)001:23661: gye re mchog skyongs gtsug ru gzhon nu dang //
NK069(tu)001:23662: dar rje dpal grags zhang rgyal yon tan bshad //
NK069(tu)001:23663: zhang gis sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che //
NK069(tu)001:23664: ye shes dbang phyug byang chub rgyal mtshan dang //
NK069(tu)001:23665: skor thung shes rab ra thung tshul khrims dang //
NK069(tu)001:23666: myang chen shes rab mchog dang ye shes 'byung gnas dang //
NK069(tu)001:23667: zur chen sh+aag 'byung shes rab grags pa dang //
NK069(tu)001:23668: skyo ston sh+aaka yes g.yung drung rdo rje dang //
NK069(tu)001:23669: skyi nag 'od dpal mkhas pa dbus grur rgyud //
NK069(tu)001:23670: dbus gru'i mkhas pa smon lam seng ge yis //
NK069(tu)001:23671: man ngag bshad srol 'chad la yi ger bris //
NK069(tu)001:23672: gsang ba sgrogs pa'i nyes pa rdo rjer bshags //
NK069(tu)001:23673: bdag kyang khong rang che bar 'byin pa yi //
NK069(tu)001:23674: dam med lag tu dpe 'di ma phrad cig /
NK069(tu)001:23675: mos gus dam tshig ldan pa'i gang zag la //
NK069(tu)001:23676: yig cha 'di yis 'gro don byed par shog /
NK069(tu)001:23677: rgya gar gyi pan tri ta sangs rgyas gsang ba dang /
NK069(tu)001:23678: bod kyi lo ts+aa ba b+ha man+dzu sh+r+ai war rma dang /
NK069(tu)001:23679: bran ka mu ri ta dang /
NK069(tu)001:23680: myang mchog rab gzhon nu dang /
NK069(tu)001:23682: 'jam dpal go cha rnams kyis sgyur /
NK069(tu)001:23683: phyis sangs rgyas gsang ba'i slob ma /
NK069(tu)001:23684: kha che'i mkhas pa chen po b+hi ma la mi ta la /
NK069(tu)001:23685: mkhas pa sna cha can dang /
NK069(tu)001:23687: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra dang /
NK069(tu)001:23688: sog po lha dpal gyi ye shes dang rnams kyis sgyur zhing zhus /
NK069(tu)001:23689: rma rin chen mchog gis skad gsar cad kyis bsabs /
NK069(tu)001:23691: lha dpal gyi ye shes kyis gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che la bshad /
NK069(tu)001:23692: des gnubs yon tan rgya mtsho la bshad /
NK069(tu)001:23693: des mya shes rab mchog la bshad /
NK069(tu)001:23694: des myang ye shes 'byung gnas la bshad /
NK069(tu)001:23695: des zur po che sh+aaka 'byung la bshad /
NK069(tu)001:23696: des zur chung shes rab grags pa la bshad /
NK069(tu)001:23697: des gong bu ba skyo ston sh+aaka yes la bshad /
NK069(tu)001:23698: des skyo g.yung drung rdo rje la bshad /
NK069(tu)001:23699: des skyi nag 'od gsal la bshad /
NK069(tu)001:23700: des mkhas pa dbus gru la bshad /
NK069(tu)001:23701: des gnas snying ba chen po la /
NK069(tu)001:23704: bdag 'be'i ston pa ye shes rdo rje la gnang ba'o //
NK069(tu)001:23705: gsang ba sgru 'phrul gyi rgyud pa rkyang par bgrangs na /
NK069(tu)001:23706: dpal chos kyi dbyings nas kun tu bzang pos rdo rje sems 'og min gnas dpa' la bshad /
NK069(tu)001:23707: des bsdus pa ca' lo can po phyag na rdo rje la /
NK069(tu)001:23708: des rgyal po pho brang yang thog tu yo gi'i char bab dza la /
NK069(tu)001:23709: des dge slong ku ku ra dza la /
NK069(tu)001:23710: des in tra bo de la /
NK069(tu)001:23711: des sras mo mgo' ma de wi la /
NK069(tu)001:23712: des sangs rgyas gsang ba la /
NK069(tu)001:23713: bod kyi ri bo gangs can zhes bya ste gangs ti rtse la /
NK069(tu)001:23714: des kha che'i bi ma mi tra la /
NK069(tu)001:23715: des rma rin chen mchog la /
NK069(tu)001:23716: 'phan yul gyi sman sna ki ku pa /
NK069(tu)001:23717: des zhang rgyal ba'i yon tan la /
NK069(tu)001:23718: des gnubs sangs rgyas sgrags yang rdzong ba /
NK069(tu)001:23720: des so ye shes dbang phyug rtsang gi lhan pa la /
NK069(tu)001:23721: des ngab thung byang chub rgyal mtshan la /
NK069(tu)001:23722: des skor thung shes rab ye shes la /
NK069(tu)001:23723: des ra thung shes rab tshul khrims la /
NK069(tu)001:23724: des mya shes rab mchog la /
NK069(tu)001:23725: rog la ban po pa la /
NK069(tu)001:23726: des mya ye shes 'byung gnas la /
NK069(tu)001:23728: des zur po che sh+aakya 'byung gnas la /
NK069(tu)001:23729: des zur chung shes rab grags pa la /
NK069(tu)001:23731: des go bu'i skyo ston shag ye shes la /
NK069(tu)001:23733: des skyo g.yung drung g.yor po'i yar lu pa kyi phu thang gi rgyu 'chag pa /
NK069(tu)001:23736: dmyal stod me rag gnas pa /
NK069(tu)001:23737: des mkhas pa'i slob dpon mal gro bya nong pa /
NK069(tu)001:23738: dbus gru smon lam seng ge gru gu blo gros
NK069(tu)001:23739: seng ge 'dis rje phag gru'i slob ma rin po
NK069(tu)001:23742: gru gu ston pa blo gros seng ge /
NK069(tu)001:23743: rgyan thang pa rnams la yi ge ma yi bu
NK069(tu)001:23744: bzhi zer ba yin ces 'gos lo gzhon nu dpal
NK069(tu)001:23746: des bla ma chen po la /
NK069(tu)001:23748: des 'be'i ston pa ye shes rdo rje bdag la gnang ba lags so //
